inherit;\"/><img src=\"http://mh.tuishang.com.cn/data/upload/ueditor/20170310/58c2779298968.jpg\" width=\"300\" height=\"200\" alt=\"\" style=\"outline: none; border: none; padding: 0px; font-style: inherit; margin: 0px auto; font-family: inherit;\"/></p><p style=\"outline: none; border: 0px; padding: 0px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;; color: rgb(35, 35, 35); font-size: 14px; line-height: 28px; white-space: normal; text-align: center;\"><img src=\"http://mh.tuishang.com.cn/data/upload/ueditor/20170310/58c2779376417.jpg\" width=\"300\" height=\"200\" alt=\"\" style=\"outline: none; border: none; padding: 0px; font-style: inherit; margin: 0px auto; font-family: inherit;\"/><img src=\"http://mh.tuishang.com.cn/data/upload/ueditor/20170310/58c2779489544.jpg\" width=\"300\" height=\"200\" alt=\"\" style=\"outline: none; border: none; padding: 0px; font-style: inherit; margin: 0px auto; font-family: inherit;\"/><br style=\"outline: none;\"/></p><p style=\"outline: none; border: 0px; padding: 0px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;; color: rgb(35, 35, 35); font-size: 14px; line-height: 28px; white-space: normal; text-align: center;\"><img src=\"http://mh.tuishang.com.cn/data/upload/ueditor/20170310/58c2779598968.jpg\" width=\"300\" height=\"200\" alt=\"\" style=\"outline: none; border: none; padding: 0px; font-style: inherit; margin: 0px auto; font-family: inherit;\"/><img src=\"http://mh.tuishang.com.cn/data/upload/ueditor/20170310/58c277965f5e1.jpg\" width=\"300\" height=\"200\" alt=\"\" style=\"outline: none; border: none; padding: 0px; font-style: inherit; margin: 0px auto; font-family: inherit;\"/></p><p><br/></p>','5月便利店商品促销信息','5月便利店商品促销信息','1','1','2017-03-10 17:53:00','','0','','','0','{\"thumb\":\"20170310\\/58c278486ea05.jpg\",\"photo\":[{\"url\":\"20170310\\/58c277f20f424.jpg\",\"alt\":\"SUNSIDES\\u4e0a\\u8d28\\u201c\\u6d77\\u5916\\u73cd\\u9009\\u201d\\u539f\\u88c5\\u8fdb\\u53e3\\u7eaf\\u725b\\u5976200ml20-09533722974\"},{\"url\":\"20170310\\/58c277f9ca2dd.jpg\",\"alt\":\"\\u7231\\u8299\\u5a01\\u53165\\u8fde\\u5305-09534821047\"},{\"url\":\"20170310\\/58c2780fc28cb.jpg\",\"alt\":\"\\u53cb\\u81e3\\u679c\\u7c92\\u571f\\u53f8-09542320512\"},{\"url\":\"20170310\\/58c278217a120.jpg\",\"alt\":\"\\u54c8\\u6839\\u8fbe\\u65af48\\u51432\\u676f-09540212341\"},{\"url\":\"20170310\\/58c27830baeb9.jpg\",\"alt\":\"\\u4e1c\\u9e4f\\u7279\\u996e-09535777575\"},{\"url\":\"20170310\\/58c2784029f63.jpg\",\"alt\":\"\\u7edf\\u4e00\\u7f07\\u62c9\\u56fe-09541416913\"}]}','3','0','0','0','','');INSERT INTO ts_posts ( `id`, `post_author`, `post_keywords`, `post_source`, `post_date`, `post_content`, `post_title`, `post_excerpt`, `post_status`, `comment_status`, `post_modified`, `post_content_filtered`, `post_parent`, `post_type`, `post_mime_type`, `comment_count`, `smeta`, `post_hits`, `post_like`, `istop`, `recommended`, `page_tpl`, `page_tpls` ) VALUES  ('153','1','江浙沪汽柴油资源紧张','','2017-03-11 14:40:46','<p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　受国际油价节后急剧上涨提振，多家分析机构监测的原油变化率持续正向拉宽，截至</span>5<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">7</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">日原油变化率已经突破</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">7%</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">大关，国内油价下周一迎来“三连涨”已几无悬念。受此影响，国内汽柴油批发市场成交火热，各地主营及社会单位纷纷上调汽柴油批发价，华东江浙沪一带汽柴油资源甚至再次出现紧张的状况，分析师表示，国内成品油市场已慢慢走出</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">2014</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年下半年的低谷。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　美国原油库存自</span>1<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月以来首度下降，加上美元疲软，均助长油价周三大涨，美原油涨破</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">60</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">美元</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">/</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">桶关口，创下自</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">2014</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">12</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">11</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">日以来的最高位，与此同时，布伦特原油现货价格也涨至</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">2014</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">12</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">5</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">日以来的最高位，由此拉宽成品油上调的预期幅度。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　截至</span>5<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">7</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">日新机制执行后第</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">53</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">轮计价期第</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">8</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">个工作日，中宇、隆众、卓创三家资讯机构监测的原油变化率已涨至</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">7.13%-7.15%</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">，对应上调幅度达到</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">235-245</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">元</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">/</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">吨。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　中宇分析师马燕表示，以目前原油价格估测，预计</span>5<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">12</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">日零时将迎今年来首度“三连涨”，上调幅度将拉宽至为</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">280</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">元</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">/</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">吨，折合汽柴油标准品分别为</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">0.20</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">元</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">/</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">升、</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">0.24</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">元</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">/</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">升。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　国际原油突破高位及上调预期支撑下，今日国内各地主营及社会单位纷纷上推汽柴油批发价。马燕称，华南汽油价格已涨至批发到位价上方，华东江浙沪一带汽柴油资源甚至再次出现紧张的状况。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\">　　“山东地炼更是出现 “火爆”局面，五一小长假归来后，区内炼厂油价步步上涨，汽柴油均价已累计上涨两三百元，汽油成交价格已回升至<span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">7000</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">元上方，涨至</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">2014</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">11</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月中旬以来的相对高位的水平。”马燕说，在原油市场涨势带动下，国内成品油市场已慢慢走出</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">2014</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年下半年的低谷。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　不过，原油能否延续反弹走势仍是未知数，马燕分析称，近期全球大部分国家发布的经济数据不及预期，能源需求及需求前景令人堪忧，而欧佩克仍将坚持寻求提高市场份额，市场供需基本面表现较为疲软，或将令后市原油走势承压。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　投资银行巴克莱在报告中也表示，油价持续反弹需要坚挺的需求和比市场预期更为确实的供应数据。而现在的情况是本末倒置，对近期的价格前景应该持有谨慎的态度。几乎没有多少增加表明需求开始增加，而在供应方面，上个月公布的预测显示，油价在每桶</span>60-71<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">美元的范围，页岩油产量将会重新增长。</span></span></p><p><br/></p>','油价三连涨已无悬念 江浙沪汽柴油资源紧张','　　受国际油价节后急剧上涨提振，多家分析机构监测的原油变化率持续正向拉宽，截至5月7日原油变化率已经突破7%大关，国内油价下周一迎来“三连涨”已几无悬念。受此影响，国内汽柴油批发市场成交火热，各地主营及社会单位纷纷上调汽柴油批发价，华东江浙沪一带汽柴油资源甚至再次出现紧张的状况，分析师表示，国内成品油市场已慢慢走出2014年下半年的低谷。','1','1','2017-03-11 14:38:47','','0','','','0','{\"thumb\":\"\"}','1','0','0','0','','');INSERT INTO ts_posts ( `id`, `post_author`, `post_keywords`, `post_source`, `post_date`, `post_content`, `post_title`, `post_excerpt`, `post_status`, `comment_status`, `post_modified`, `post_content_filtered`, `post_parent`, `post_type`, `post_mime_type`, `comment_count`, `smeta`, `post_hits`, `post_like`, `istop`, `recommended`, `page_tpl`, `page_tpls` ) VALUES  ('154','1','汽柴油国标','','2017-03-11 14:48:48','<p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　记者</span>7<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">日从国家发改委了解到，我国将抓紧启动第六阶段汽、柴油国家</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">(</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">国</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">VI)</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">标准制订工作，力争</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">2016</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年底颁布，并于</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">2019</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年实施。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　发改委等七部门日前印发《加快成品油质量升级工作方案》。根据方案，我国将参考国际先进标准并结合我国实际，加快油品标准制修订步伐，完善标准体系。</span>2015<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">6</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月底前发布新的普通柴油强制性国家标准。尽快发布第五阶段车用乙醇汽油标准</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">(E10)</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">、车用乙醇汽油调合组分油及生物柴油调合燃料</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">(B5)</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">标准。尽快修订出台船用燃料油强制性国家标准，力争</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">2015</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年底前发布。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　方案明确，</span>2016<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">1</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">1</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">日起，东部地区</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">11</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">个省市</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">(</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">北京、天津、河北、辽宁、上海、江苏、浙江、福建、山东、广东和海南</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">)</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">全面供应符合国Ⅴ标准的车用汽油</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">(</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">含</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">E10</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">乙醇汽油</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">)</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">、车用柴油</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">(</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">含</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">B5</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">生物柴油</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">)</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\">　　2017<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">1</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">1</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">日起，全国全面供应符合国Ⅴ标准的车用汽油</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">(</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">含</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">E10</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">乙醇汽油</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">)</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">、车用柴油</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">(</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">含</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">B5</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">生物柴油</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">)</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">，同时停止国内销售低于国Ⅴ标准车用汽、柴油。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\">　　2016<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">1</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">1</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">日起，开始在东部地区重点城市供应与国</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">IV</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">标准车用柴油相同硫含量的普通柴油；</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">2017</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">7</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">1</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">日，全国全面供应国</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">IV</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">标准普通柴油，同时停止国内销售低于国</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">IV</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">标准的普通柴油。</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">2018</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">1</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">1</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">日起，全国供应与国Ⅴ标准车用柴油相同硫含量的普通柴油，停止国内销售低于国Ⅴ标准普通柴油。</span></span></p><p><br/></p>','第六阶段汽柴油国标将启动制订','　记者7日从国家发改委了解到，我国将抓紧启动第六阶段汽、柴油国家(国VI)标准制订工作，力争2016年底颁布，并于2019年实施。','1','1','2017-03-11 14:47:52','','0','','','0','{\"thumb\":\"\"}','1','0','0','0','','');INSERT INTO ts_posts ( `id`, `post_author`, `post_keywords`, `post_source`, `post_date`, `post_content`, `post_title`, `post_excerpt`, `post_status`, `comment_status`, `post_modified`, `post_content_filtered`, `post_parent`, `post_type`, `post_mime_type`, `comment_count`, `smeta`, `post_hits`, `post_like`, `istop`, `recommended`, `page_tpl`, `page_tpls` ) VALUES  ('155','1','国际油价','','2017-03-11 14:51:38','<p><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14px; line-height: 150%; text-align: justify;\">　　欧佩克调高</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14px; line-height: 150%; text-align: justify;\">2015</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14px; line-height: 150%; text-align: justify;\">年的全球原油需求预测，国际油价</span><span style=\"font-size: 14px; line-height: 150%; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri;\">5</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14px; line-height: 150%; text-align: justify;\">月</span><span style=\"font-size: 14px; line-height: 150%; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri;\">12</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14px; line-height: 150%; text-align: justify;\">日大幅上涨。</span><br/></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　欧佩克</span>12<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">日发布的月度原油市场报告，将</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">2015</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年原油需求的日均增幅上调</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">1</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">万桶至</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">118</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">万桶，日均需求达到</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">9250</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">万桶。上调的主要原因是由于预期美国的原油需求上升。欧佩克将</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">2015</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年市场对欧佩克原油的需求预测小幅上调至日均</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">2930</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">万桶，</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">2014</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年市场对欧佩克原油的需求为日均</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">2900</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">万桶。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　供应方面，报告说今年</span>4<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月份欧佩克的日均原油产量增加</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">1.8</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">万桶至</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">3084</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">万桶。预计非欧佩克国家</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">2015</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年的日均原油产量的增幅为</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">68</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">万桶，去年的增幅为</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">217</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">万桶。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　另外美国能源信息局</span>12<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">日发布的短期能源展望报告说，预计</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">2015</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年美国的日均原油产量为</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">920</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">万桶，较上个月的预测低</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">4</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">万桶。</span></span></p><p><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　截至当日收盘时，纽约商品交易所</span>2015<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">6</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月交货的轻质原油期货价格上涨</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">1.5</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">美元，收于每桶</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">60.75</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">美元，涨幅为</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">2.53%</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">。</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">2015</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">6</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月交货的伦敦布伦特原油期货价格上涨</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">1.95</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">美元，收于每桶</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">66.86</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">美元，涨幅为</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">3%</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">。 &nbsp;</span></span></p><p><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"></span></span><br/></p>','国际油价5月12日大幅上涨','　　欧佩克调高2015年的全球原油需求预测，国际油价5月12日大幅上涨。','1','1','2017-03-11 14:49:54','','0','','','0','{\"thumb\":\"\"}','1','0','0','0','','');INSERT INTO ts_posts ( `id`, `post_author`, `post_keywords`, `post_source`, `post_date`, `post_content`, `post_title`, `post_excerpt`, `post_status`, `comment_status`, `post_modified`, `post_content_filtered`, `post_parent`, `post_type`, `post_mime_type`, `comment_count`, `smeta`, `post_hits`, `post_like`, `istop`, `recommended`, `page_tpl`, `page_tpls` ) VALUES  ('156','1','原油降温','','2017-03-11 15:01:48','<p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　近期国际油价的高位降温，让国内油价调整搁浅的预期越来越浓。《经济参考报》记者从多家社会监测机构了解到，新一轮油价调整窗口将于</span>5<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">25</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">日</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">(</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">下周一</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">)</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">开启，但从目前原油走势来看，届时因调价幅度不满</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">50</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">元</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">/</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">吨而出现搁浅是大概率事件。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　自</span>5<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">11</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">日国内油价“三连涨”之后，在美国原油库存减少、美元强劲反弹以及中东局势不稳等多因素影响下，国际原油开始出现熄火局面，五个交易日连续下跌，</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">19</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">日跌幅更是在</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">3%</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">以上。截至</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">20</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">日收盘，纽约商品交易所</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">7</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月交货的轻质原油期货价格收于每桶</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">58.98</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">美元，</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">7</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月交货的伦敦布伦特原油期货价格收于每桶</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">65.03</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">美元。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　与此相一致，国内成品油调价参考的原油变化率也是先涨后跌。卓创调价模型显示，截至</span>5<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">20</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">日收盘，第</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">8</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">个工作日原油变化率</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">0.37%</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">，汽柴油对应上调</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">15</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">元</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">/</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">吨。而金银岛测算的变化率为</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">0.39%</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">，对应上调幅度为</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">20</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">元</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">/</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">吨。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　按照成品油定价新机制，国内汽柴油价格根据国际市场原油价格变化每</span>10<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">个工作日调整一次，当调价幅度低于每吨</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">50</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">元时，不做调整，纳入下次调价时累加或冲抵。据了解，</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">2015</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年以来，国内成品油零售价格经历了五涨三跌一搁浅共计九轮调价周期。其中，汽油价格累计每吨上调</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">570</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">元，柴油价格累计每吨上调</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">490</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">元。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\">　　“根据模型测算，若未来两日原油出现<span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">5.5</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">美元</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">/</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">桶的涨幅，油价上调窗口才能开启；若原油出现</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">5</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">美元</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">/</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">桶的跌幅，则下调窗口开启。”卓创资讯分析师张斌认为，短期原油或保持震荡，出现持续暴跌暴涨的可能性不大，</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">5</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">25</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">日国内油价调整面临搁浅将是大概率事件。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　中宇资讯分析师石泽睿也认为，国际油价上行趋势转为震荡下行，从而抵消了前期涨幅，成品油调价对应幅度为</span>0<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">元</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">/</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">吨，搁浅成定局，国内大部分地区汽柴油将仍处于“</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">6</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">元时代”。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　受国际原油价格的大幅走低及油价调整趋势呈现逆转迹象影响，国内汽柴油批发市场也开始逐渐转冷。据张斌介绍，经济复苏缓慢导致柴油需求难有大的提升，再加上</span>“三连涨”之后，油价出现超涨局面，因此在搁浅预期下，炼厂及销售公司出货不佳，油价也难维持涨势；而汽油方面因夏季来临，支撑了汽油的消费，但是整体环境不乐观，也影响到其整体的消费。但受零售市场需求相对稳定支撑，汽油批发价格跌势弱于柴油。 &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></p><p><span style=\";font-family:Calibri;font-size:14px\">&nbsp;</span></p><p><br/></p>','原油降温 国内油价调整面临搁浅','近期国际油价的高位降温，让国内油价调整搁浅的预期越来越浓。《经济参考报》记者从多家社会监测机构了解到，新一轮油价调整窗口将于5月25日(下周一)开启，但从目前原油走势来看，届时因调价幅度不满50元/吨而出现搁浅是大概率事件。','1','1','2017-03-11 15:01:15','','0','','','0','{\"thumb\":\"\"}','1','0','0','0','','');INSERT INTO ts_posts ( `id`, `post_author`, `post_keywords`, `post_source`, `post_date`, `post_content`, `post_title`, `post_excerpt`, `post_status`, `comment_status`, `post_modified`, `post_content_filtered`, `post_parent`, `post_type`, `post_mime_type`, `comment_count`, `smeta`, `post_hits`, `post_like`, `istop`, `recommended`, `page_tpl`, `page_tpls` ) VALUES  ('157','1','原油使用权','','2017-03-11 15:05:37','<p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\">　　27<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">日，国家发改委发布通知称，初步确认山东东明石化集团可使用进口原油</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">750</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">万吨</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">/</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年。这是我国首家获得进口原油使用权的民营地方炼厂。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　国家发改委表示，根据《国家发展改革委关于进口原油使用管理有关问题的通知》的有关要求，中国石油和化学工业联合会组织开展申请用油企业核查评估工作。经核查，该公司申请使用进口原油的炼油装置规模，安全、环保、消防、储运等设施，及产品质量和能耗指标符合有关规定，初步确认该公司可使用进口原油</span>750<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">万吨</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">/</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　据记者了解，东明石化是山东第一大地方炼厂，也是第一家申报使用进口原油的地方炼厂。隆众石化网分析师张萌告诉新京报记者，对地炼开放进口原油使用权，主要原因之一即民营地炼长期面临原料短缺问题，尤其是原油，严重遏制了地炼的生产。目前，山东地炼平均开工率只有</span>40%<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">左右，大部分产能处于停滞状态。东明石化获得进口原油使用权，为地炼解决原料问题开启了一个良好开端。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　卓创资讯分析师刘孟凯也对记者表示，</span>2015<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年至今，山东地炼一次常减压装置平均开工负荷为</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">42.27%</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">，虽然较之前出现较大提升，但整体开工负荷依然处于偏低状态。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　刘孟凯说，长期以来，由于原油供应体制的原因，国内原油进口权牢牢控制在国企手中，众多地方炼油厂时常面临</span>“断炊”的境地。目前，地炼企业国内原油资源计划仅有<span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">122.2</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">万吨，但相对于山东地炼</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">12735</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">万吨</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">/</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年的一次加工产能而言，可谓是杯水车薪。地炼企业常常“望油兴叹”，只好依靠进口劣质燃料油进行生产，生产产品质量与加工利润均不乐观。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　今年</span>5<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月初，中国石油和化学工业联合会发布《核查评估申请用油企业工作细则》，意图通过原油进口使用权的下放，鼓励企业自主淘汰落后产能，促进产业结构升级。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　中宇资讯燃料油分析师高青翠认为，在中国原油对外依存度高达</span>60%<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">的情况下，进口原油使用权地炼名单的确立，可以解决部分民营地炼“无米下锅”的尴尬现状。</span></span></p><p><br/></p>','民营地炼首获进口原油使用权 油气改革提速','　　27日，国家发改委发布通知称，初步确认山东东明石化集团可使用进口原油750万吨/年。这是我国首家获得进口原油使用权的民营地方炼厂。','1','1','2017-03-11 15:02:24','','0','','','0','{\"thumb\":\"\"}','1','0','0','0','','');INSERT INTO ts_posts ( `id`, `post_author`, `post_keywords`, `post_source`, `post_date`, `post_content`, `post_title`, `post_excerpt`, `post_status`, `comment_status`, `post_modified`, `post_content_filtered`, `post_parent`, `post_type`, `post_mime_type`, `comment_count`, `smeta`, `post_hits`, `post_like`, `istop`, `recommended`, `page_tpl`, `page_tpls` ) VALUES  ('158','1','油价第四次下调','','2017-03-11 15:07:41','<p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　多空博弈下的国际油价震荡下行，让国内油价下调的预期越来越浓。记者从多家社会监测机构了解到，新一轮油价调整窗口将于</span>6<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">8</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">日</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">(</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">下周一</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">)</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">开启，从目前的原油走势看，下调幅度预计在</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">100</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">元</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">/</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">吨左右，这将是年内第四次下调油价。受此预期影响，国内成品油批发价承压下行，两桶油加大优惠力度但效果不佳。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　自</span>5<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">25</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">日国内油价调整搁浅以来，国际油价在多空力量拉锯战中涨跌互现。在前一个交易日大涨后，国际市场普遍担心，周五（</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">6</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">5</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">日）石油输出国组织即将召开的维也纳会议将维持石油产出，由此将增加原油市场供应过剩的问题，加之美元地位反弹以及中国经济数据欠佳，利空因素削弱投资者需求，</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">6</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">1</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">日国际原油重拾跌势。截至当日收盘时，纽约商品交易所</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">7</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月交货的轻质原油期货价格下跌</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">0.1</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">美元，收于每桶</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">60.2</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">美元。</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">7</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月交货的伦敦布伦特原油期货价格下跌</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">0.68</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">美元，收于每桶</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">64.88</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">美元。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　与此相一致，国内成品油参考的原油变化率也负向发展。监测数据显示，北京时间</span>6<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">2</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">日，新机制执行后第</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">55</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">轮计价期第</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">6</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">个工作日，原油变化率为</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">-2.88%</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">，对应下调幅度为</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">95</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">元</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">/</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">吨。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\">　　“虽然美国原油库存持续下滑、石油需求增长提振市场气氛，但是美元汇率震荡走强、钻井平台降幅趋缓以及全球石油供应充裕局面未改。”分析师胡慧春认为，短期美元汇率仍有继续走强可能，未来欧美原油期货或保持震荡下滑态势，变化率延续跌势，<span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">6</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">8</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">日国内下调窗口将会开启，届时，国内成品油市场将迎来年内第四次下调。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　分析师孙雪君也表示，当前原油变化率为</span>-3.01%<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">。</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">OPEC</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">的年度例会会在本周五做出是否减产的决定，很多成员国代表认为可能宣布维持产量配额不变，加重了投资者对供应过剩的担忧，所以预计维也纳会议前国际原油或仍维持震荡走势，若按照目前原油现货价位运行， </span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">6</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">8</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">日</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">24</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">时成品油零售价格下调幅度在</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">105</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">元</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">/</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">吨。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　受此预期影响，国内西南、沿江等市场油价承压下滑，华东、华南以及华北等地区油价持稳为主，但中下游用户对后市油价持悲观心态，缓慢消化库存，购货意愿较低。</span>6<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">2</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">日监测国内</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">28</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">个主要省市中石油、中石化批发均价：国三</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">0#</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">柴油为</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">5764</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">元</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">/</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">吨，较前一个工作日跌</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">14</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">元</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">/</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">吨，国四</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">93#</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">汽油为</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">7927</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">元</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">/</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">吨，较前一个工作日跌</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">11</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">元</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">/</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">吨</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">;</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">国四</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">0#</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">柴油为</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">6288</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">元</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">/</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">吨，较前一工作日跌</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">8</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">元</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">/</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">吨。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　据孙雪君介绍，部分中石化、中石油主营单位油价明稳暗降，加大优惠让利幅度，但终端需求未有明显提升。山东地炼也在油价下调预期作用下实施降价动作，幅度在</span>30-50<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">元</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">/</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">吨，目前国内油市整体成交较差，预计未来仍将延续零星下滑走势。</span></span></p><p><br/></p>','油价8日或迎年内第四次下调','　　多空博弈下的国际油价震荡下行，让国内油价下调的预期越来越浓。记者从多家社会监测机构了解到，新一轮油价调整窗口将于6月8日(下周一)开启，从目前的原油走势看，下调幅度预计在100元/吨左右，这将是年内第四次下调油价。受此预期影响，国内成品油批发价承压下行，两桶油加大优惠力度但效果不佳。','1','1','2017-03-11 15:06:41','','0','','','0','{\"thumb\":\"\"}','1','0','0','0','','');INSERT INTO ts_posts ( `id`, `post_author`, `post_keywords`, `post_source`, `post_date`, `post_content`, `post_title`, `post_excerpt`, `post_status`, `comment_status`, `post_modified`, `post_content_filtered`, `post_parent`, `post_type`, `post_mime_type`, `comment_count`, `smeta`, `post_hits`, `post_like`, `istop`, `recommended`, `page_tpl`, `page_tpls` ) VALUES  ('159','1',' 油价1年内遇5涨4降','','2017-03-11 15:09:59','<p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　昨日，国家发改委宣布下调成品油价格，省物价局同步调整我省汽、柴油价格，今起我省</span>93<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">号汽油最高零售价调至</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">6.42</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">元</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">/</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">升，降低</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">0.09</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">元</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">/</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">升。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　调价后，今日零时起，我省</span>93<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">号汽油、</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">97</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">号汽油、车用</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">0</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">号柴油最高零售价依次为</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">6.42</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">元</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">/</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">升、</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">6.85</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">元</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">/</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">升、</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">6.06</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">元</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">/</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">升，分别下调</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">0.09</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">元</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">/</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">升、</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">0.1</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">元</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">/</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">升、</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">0.09</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">元</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">/</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">升。此次调价是今年内第四次下调。至此，今年以来，成品油价格共经历了五次上涨、四次下调、两次搁浅。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　总体算下来，今年汽油价格累计上涨每吨</span>460<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">元，柴油上涨</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">385</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">元，折合汽油零售价格每升上涨约</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">0.34</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">元，柴油零售价格每升上涨约</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">0.32</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">元。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　今日零时起，中石化森美、中石油旗下加油站的油价将调整到最高零售价。福州一些民营加油站则将继续推出优惠活动。三兴加油站相关负责人介绍，会提前</span>1<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">个小时（</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">8</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">日</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">23</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">时）下调加油站里的油价，</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">93</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">号汽油零售价将调整为</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">6.02</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">元</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">/</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">升，比最高限价低</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">0.4</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">元</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">/</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">升，</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">97</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">号汽油、车用</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">0</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">号柴油则依次调整为</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">6.65</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">元</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">/</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">升、</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">5.91</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">元</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">/</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">升，分别比最高限价低</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">0.2</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">元</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">/</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">升、</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">0.15</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">元</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">/</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">升。此外，市政加油站负责人也称，站内</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">93</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">号汽油、</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">97</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">号汽油、车用</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">0</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">号柴油将分别调整为</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">6.1</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">元</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">/</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">升、</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">6.6</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">元</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">/</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">升、</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">5.8</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">元</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">/</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">升，分别比我省最高限价低</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">0.32</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">元</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">/</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">升、</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">0.25</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">元</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">/</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">升、</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">0.26</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">元</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">/</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">升。</span></span></p><p><br/></p>','福建93号汽油降至6.42元/升 油价1年内遇5涨4降','　　昨日，国家发改委宣布下调成品油价格，省物价局同步调整我省汽、柴油价格，今起我省93号汽油最高零售价调至6.42元/升，降低0.09元/升。','1','1','2017-03-11 15:08:39','','0','','','0','{\"thumb\":\"\"}','1','0','0','0','','');INSERT INTO ts_posts ( `id`, `post_author`, `post_keywords`, `post_source`, `post_date`, `post_content`, `post_title`, `post_excerpt`, `post_status`, `comment_status`, `post_modified`, `post_content_filtered`, `post_parent`, `post_type`, `post_mime_type`, `comment_count`, `smeta`, `post_hits`, `post_like`, `istop`, `recommended`, `page_tpl`, `page_tpls` ) VALUES  ('160','1','成品油价格指数','','2017-03-11 15:12:41','<p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　依据新华</span>(<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">大庆</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">)</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">国际石油资讯中心发布的报告，截至</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">6</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">12</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">日，全国成品油价格指数为</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">735.32</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">，增幅</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">0.39%</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">，全国成品油价格指数小幅反弹。 </span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　全国成品油价格指数运行结果表明，上周</span>93#<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">汽油平均价格报收于</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">7690</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">元</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">/</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">吨，较前一报告周期下跌</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">4</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">元</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">/</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">吨</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">(</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">与前一报告期基本持平</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">)</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">；</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">0#</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">柴油平均价格报收于</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">6046</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">元</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">/</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">吨，较前一报告周期上涨</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">40</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">元</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">/</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">吨</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">(</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">折合</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">0.03</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">元</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">/</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">升</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">)</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">。综合来看，全国柴油平均价格上涨带动全国成品油价格指数小幅反弹。 </span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　新华</span>(<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">大庆</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">)</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">国际石油资讯中心分析师蒋冰认为，近日因欧佩克及美国日产量提升至高位，国际油价小幅回落。国内成品油市场利空氛围浓厚，因国内市场需求一般，市场交投清淡。山西省太原市某加油站负责人表示，国际油价小幅收低，但变化率维持正向发展，中石油柴油价格低位反弹，石化报价暂稳，但前期优惠政策取消，目前中下游用户小单采购，整体成交略有升温。 </span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　蒋冰分析认为，本周国内成品油市场整体走势较弱，因油品需求不佳以及业者观望情绪浓厚，汽柴油销量欠佳。外盘油价近期下行利空国内市场加之南方多阴雨天气、部分地区进入禁渔时节影响了市场交投，主营柴油出货量依然有限。国际市场，国际能源署</span>11<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">日发布的原油市场报告利空国际油价。观望后市，虽然美国原油库存继续下降，但美国及沙特日产量逐步提升，供应充裕格局难改，预计国际油价短期内将继续震荡下行格局。</span></span></p><p><br/></p>','全国成品油价格指数小幅反弹','       依据新华(大庆)国际石油资讯中心发布的报告，截至6月12日，全国成品油价格指数为735.32，增幅0.39%，全国成品油价格指数小幅反弹。','1','1','2017-03-11 15:11:50','','0','','','0','{\"thumb\":\"\"}','2','0','0','0','','');INSERT INTO ts_posts ( `id`, `post_author`, `post_keywords`, `post_source`, `post_date`, `post_content`, `post_title`, `post_excerpt`, `post_status`, `comment_status`, `post_modified`, `post_content_filtered`, `post_parent`, `post_type`, `post_mime_type`, `comment_count`, `smeta`, `post_hits`, `post_like`, `istop`, `recommended`, `page_tpl`, `page_tpls` ) VALUES  ('161','1','低油价影响','','2017-03-11 15:14:24','<p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　同亚洲其他国家一样，中国在国际油价的剧烈震荡中也受到了严重的影响。</span>FGE<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">全球能源咨询公司认为，在石油市场中，这是价格的结构性变化，我们已经进入的低油价时代很可能要持续很长一段时间。因此，低油价对中国的影响不会很快结束。大体估计，这轮国际油价下跌对中国的影响涉及从经济、环境到能源安全、区域合作等多个领域。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\">　　</span><strong><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;font-size: 14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">经济影响</span></span></strong></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　国际油价持续下跌带来的影响波及中国经济的多个方面。从积极方面来看，会带来以下的变化。第一，低油价将增加中国经常账户盈余。以原油为例，</span>2014<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年，中国日均进口原油</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">620</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">万桶，需要花费</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">2280</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">亿美元（国际油价在平均</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">101</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">美元</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">/</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">桶时）。原油进口占中国商品进口数量的</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">12%</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">。据</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">FGE</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">估算，</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">2015</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年中国每天会进口</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">650</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">万桶原油。如果今年布伦特原油均价在</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">60</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">美元</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">/</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">桶上下，那么，中国原油进口总花销将降至</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">1400</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">亿美元左右。在中国进口商品中，石油所占份额将跌落至</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">8%</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">（商品进口总额亦可能下降）。第二，低油价将刺激中国国内生产总值（</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">GDP</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">）增长。尽管估算存在差异，但这影响很可能是正面的。第三，低油价促使中国财政和税收体制改革。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　然而，消极的影响同样不可避免，低油价可能增加对全球通货紧缩的担忧。考虑到中国在能源相关行业有过剩产能，一旦出现通货紧缩，后果将不堪设想。同时，国内能源投资，尤其是石油和天然气，将受到低油价带来的负面影响，导致这些行业拉低中国</span>GDP<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">增长率。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\">　</span><strong><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;font-size: 14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　环境和能源安全影响</span></span></strong></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　对于中国政府实现环保目标，低油价是不小的挑战。当然对不同燃料影响也是不同的。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　在天然气方面，面对油价的崩塌，中国政府调整气价速度较慢。</span>2014<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年，由于政府定价上涨，影响天然气需求增长。而随着国际油价进一步降低，天然气需求量会再次受到影响。在石油产品中，天然气主要的竞争对手是柴油和液化石油气。随着柴油价格的走低，液化天然气（</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">LNG</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">）汽车和其他燃气汽车的市场越来越不景气。尽管在油价高的年代，家庭用气方面液化石油气不是天然气的对手，但是目前由于油价低，液化石油气竞争力在上升。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　在煤炭方面，由于中国的石油发电厂极少，主要以煤炭发电为主，所以煤炭消费量不会立刻发生变化，但是煤化工产业受到的影响最大。因为汽、柴油价格较低，所以煤制油受到较大冲击。当然煤炭价格本身下跌，一定程度上能缓解这种冲击带来的压力。而煤制气紧跟着其他煤炭化工行业也会受到影响，在可再生能源和生物燃料方面，可再生能源需要和煤炭竞争，因此受油价下跌的影响并不大。但是从长远来看，如果油价持续走低，将有可能阻碍再生能源的向前发展。由于中国能源规模效益表现欠佳，生物燃料进展缓慢，因此生物燃料同样面临着低油价带来的挑战。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　就能源安全而言，低油价对中国政府也是挑战。一方面，国内石油产量由于低油价受到重创；另一方面，由于进口成本更低，刺激石油进口。油价降低一定程度上被成品油消费税上涨所抵消，但（假定其他条件不变）仍然能够推动石油需求增长。因此，石油净进口量上扬，政府在降低对进口能源（尤其是石油）依赖方面所做的努力也将受到抑制。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　然而，在能源安全方面，低油价的一个重大利好，是中国有机会提高石油战略储备。事实确实如此，前几年一直进展缓慢的中国能源战略储备二期建设，在</span>2014<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年下半年以后进展速度加快。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\">　　</span><strong><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;font-size: 14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">政策影响</span></span></strong></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　低油价为政府改革税收、财政制度和石油价格机制提供了一个难得的机会。政府于</span>2014<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">11</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">29</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">日、</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">12</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">13</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">日和</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">2015</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">1</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">13</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">日，三次提高成品油消费税，这是中国改革和完善消费税制度的一项重要举措。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　低油价也带来</span>LNG<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">较低的进口价格，不仅对于中国，同时对于亚洲其他采购天然气的国家也是一样。利用这次机会，中国政府完成了天然气价改“三步走”战略中的最后一步。今年</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">4</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">1</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">日，中国非居民用两档天然气价格正式并轨。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\">　　</span><strong><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;font-size: 14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">稳定石油市场</span> <span style=\"font-family:宋体\">加强区域合作</span></span></strong></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　当前国际油价已经下跌到</span>100<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">美元</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">/</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">桶以下，全球进入了一个价格剧烈波动的时期。市场对于石油定价起着决定性作用，石油供应根据价格上下起伏而摇摆不定。对亚太国家而言，要通过区域合作确保能源市场的稳定，就要应对低油价持续波动带来的新挑战。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　对于亚太地区的发展中国家来说，低油价对于政府改革石油天然气价格机制是一次取消补贴、理顺税收的黄金时机。中国、印度、泰国、印尼、马来西亚都抓住了这个时机。尽管每个国家情况不同，但在促进地区间合作时可以充分分享经验。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　很多亚洲国家是主要的石油天然气进口国，石油和天然气的价格降低大大降低了他们的进口费用。在这种环境下，日本、韩国和中国台湾省等亚洲发达经济体，由于能源进口花费减少而获益，印尼、马来西亚、文莱、巴布亚新几内亚和澳大利亚等能源生产国由于油气价格降低，上游生产收入减少，因此，亚洲发达国家应该考虑帮助石油生产国克服困难。同样，在油价剧烈波动的时期保证供应稳定，能源进口国和生产国的合作至关重要。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\">&nbsp;</span></p><p><br/></p>','低油价给中国带来的多重影响','　　同亚洲其他国家一样，中国在国际油价的剧烈震荡中也受到了严重的影响。FGE全球能源咨询公司认为，在石油市场中，这是价格的结构性变化，我们已经进入的低油价时代很可能要持续很长一段时间。因此，低油价对中国的影响不会很快结束。大体估计，这轮国际油价下跌对中国的影响涉及从经济、环境到能源安全、区域合作等多个领域。','1','1','2017-03-11 15:13:13','','0','','','0','{\"thumb\":\"\"}','0','0','0','0','','');INSERT INTO ts_posts ( `id`, `post_author`, `post_keywords`, `post_source`, `post_date`, `post_content`, `post_title`, `post_excerpt`, `post_status`, `comment_status`, `post_modified`, `post_content_filtered`, `post_parent`, `post_type`, `post_mime_type`, `comment_count`, `smeta`, `post_hits`, `post_like`, `istop`, `recommended`, `page_tpl`, `page_tpls` ) VALUES  ('162','1','油价下跌','','2017-03-11 15:18:47','<p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　近一个月来，国际油价围绕</span>60<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">美元</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">/</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">桶的价格打响了“争夺战”。油价后市走势陡生分歧，也令油气公司的神经绷得更紧。油价低位徘徊，一方面令手握高成本油气资产的公司担忧“钱景”；另一方面，也给觊觎上游资产已久的资本开启了收购窗口期，增加了谈判的筹码。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　业内人士认为，油价恢复到</span>100<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">美元</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">/</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">桶不甚乐观。面对低价油气资产的诱惑，企业需精心判断油价走势，合理选择并购时机和并购资产；而对已有高成本油气资产在手的企业，较佳的策略还是收缩成本，等待“冬天”过去。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　高成本项目面临转让</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　半年内油价</span>“腰斩”，无疑令开发成本较高的油气项目面临赢利前景不明的困扰，不少项目处于被股东转让或者停产的境地。</span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　北京产权交易所信息显示，山东海右石化集团公司和山东恒祥化工公司拟以</span>7.36<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">亿元、联合转让所持陕西欧赛利新能源开发公司</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">100%</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">股权。这家新能源公司的主业即为在陕西开发油页岩项目。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　无独有偶，山东昌华集团也欲将其子公司拥有的加拿大艾伯塔省卡尔加里油田项目通过产权交易所进行融资转让。尽管该油田项目产油约</span>500<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">桶</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">/</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">日左右，并拥有页岩油气储量价值</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">57.21</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">亿美元，但不断下跌的油价影响了该项目的开发前景，大股东也萌生退意。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　曾豪掷数十亿元开发油页岩项目的上市公司辽宁成大也正遭遇</span>“低油价危机”。该公司近日公告，由于国际油价下跌，无法覆盖生产运营成本，决定近期停止公司页岩油开发生产平台——成大弘晟的生产运营活动。公司称，由于油价持续低位，成大弘晟<span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">2014</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年亏损</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">44524</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">万元，</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">2015</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年第一季度亏损</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">9678</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">万元。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　海外收购窗口期渐显低迷的油价也为企业出海并购打开了较好的窗口期。自去年下半年以来，中国企业出海收购油气资产的案例频频见诸报端，且民企扮演了重要角色。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\">　　5<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">30</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">日，新潮实业公告，拟非公开发行股票约</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">2.35</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">亿股，购买浙江犇宝</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">100%</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">股权，从而获得浙江犇宝位于美国得克萨斯州</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">Crosby</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">郡的二叠纪盆地的油田资产。该油气资产为海外成熟油气资产，已证实储量</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">2445.62</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">万桶，拥有资质完备的外包服务供应商和销售客户资源，周边运输管线和配套设施齐全。新潮实业同时拟以每股</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">10.19</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">元价格配套融资</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">21</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">亿元，其中</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">13</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">亿元用于油田开发项目，包括勘探井部署及水平开发井建设。这也意味着，本来以房地产和电缆为主营的新潮实业进军油气开发业务战略实现落地。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　今年</span>4<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月完成中天能源借壳重组、由百货零售业变身为能源企业的长百集团</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">5</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">20</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">日公告，拟与产业并购基金共同出资设立公司，并购加拿大油气资产，长百集团出资额不超过</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">1000</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">万美元</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">(</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">约合</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">6200</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">万元人民币</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">)</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">。长百集团表示，这次拟收购的加拿大油气田资产对于公司的长期发展具有重要战略意义，尽管这次并购公司出资额偏低，但根据该项目运营情况，当其发展潜能显现，公司不排除进一步收购权益的可能性。</span></span></p><p><br/></p>','油价下跌凸显海外收购窗口期','　　近一个月来，国际油价围绕60美元/桶的价格打响了“争夺战”。油价后市走势陡生分歧，也令油气公司的神经绷得更紧。油价低位徘徊，一方面令手握高成本油气资产的公司担忧“钱景”；另一方面，也给觊觎上游资产已久的资本开启了收购窗口期，增加了谈判的筹码。','1','1','2017-03-11 15:18:21','','0','','','0','{\"thumb\":\"\"}','0','0','0','0','','');INSERT INTO ts_posts ( `id`, `post_author`, `post_keywords`, `post_source`, `post_date`, `post_content`, `post_title`, `post_excerpt`, `post_status`, `comment_status`, `post_modified`, `post_content_filtered`, `post_parent`, `post_type`, `post_mime_type`, `comment_count`, `smeta`, `post_hits`, `post_like`, `istop`, `recommended`, `page_tpl`, `page_tpls` ) VALUES  ('163','1','弱势运行','','2017-03-11 15:21:15','<p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　依据新华</span>(<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">大庆</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">)</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">国际石油资讯中心发布的报告，截至</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">7</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">7</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">日，全国成品油价格指数为</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">717.13</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">，降幅</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">0.31%</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">，全国成品油价格指数继续弱势运行。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　全国成品油价格指数运行结果表明，上周</span>93#<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">汽油平均价格报收于</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">7529</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">元</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">/</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">吨，较前一报告周期下跌</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">28</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">元</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">/</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">吨</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">(</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">折合</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">0.02</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">元</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">/</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">升</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">)</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">；</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">0#</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">柴油平均价格报收于</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">5883</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">元</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">/</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">吨，较前一报告周期下跌</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">16</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">元</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">/</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">吨</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">(</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">折合</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">0.01</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">元</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">/</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">升</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">)</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">。综合来看，全国汽柴油平均价格均小幅下降带动全国成品油价格指数继续回落。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　新华</span>(<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">大庆</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">)</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">国际石油资讯中心分析师李振国认为，近日受希腊债务危机及伊朗核谈判影响，国际油价维持震荡盘整走势。国内成品油市场呈弱势格局，业者多有买涨不买跌心理，市场交投清淡。广东省广州市某加油站负责人表示：“本周国际原油价格持续震荡走势，国内一揽子原油价格变化率负向加深。原油价格持续波动，市场下行压力加重，成品油市场业者前期逢低采购后陆续退市观望，且终端需求延续低迷，市场购销气氛延续清淡，主营单位价格持续波动，实际成交商谈空间较大。”</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　李振国分析认为，近期外盘持续震荡，受此影响国内油品市场交投疲弱，业者多看空后市，操作积极性减弱。国际市场，美国石油协会</span>(API)6<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">30</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">日公布的数据显示，美国原油库存增加</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">187.5</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">万桶，至</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">4.68861</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">亿桶，预期为减少</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">200</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">万桶，该消息利空国际油价。观望后市，数据显示近日欧佩克主要产油国产量持续上升，供应过剩局面未改，预计国际油价短期内将继续震荡下行格局。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\">&nbsp;</span></p><p><br/></p>','全国成品油价格指数弱势运行','　　依据新华(大庆)国际石油资讯中心发布的报告，截至7月7日，全国成品油价格指数为717.13，降幅0.31%，全国成品油价格指数继续弱势运行。','1','1','2017-03-11 15:20:34','','0','','','0','{\"thumb\":\"\"}','1','0','0','0','','');INSERT INTO ts_posts ( `id`, `post_author`, `post_keywords`, `post_source`, `post_date`, `post_content`, `post_title`, `post_excerpt`, `post_status`, `comment_status`, `post_modified`, `post_content_filtered`, `post_parent`, `post_type`, `post_mime_type`, `comment_count`, `smeta`, `post_hits`, `post_like`, `istop`, `recommended`, `page_tpl`, `page_tpls` ) VALUES  ('164','1','中国油气勘查','','2017-03-11 15:23:04','<p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　中国国土资源部</span>7<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">日发布新疆石油天然气勘查区块招标公告，以新疆为试点的油气资源上游领域改革正式拉开序幕。中国油气上游领域国有石油公司专营局面有望终结。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　本次改革试点先拿出</span>6<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">个油气勘查区块，面向社会公开招标，符合准入条件的企业均可参与投标，承诺勘查工作量多的企业中标。中标企业按承诺投入的</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">10%</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">提交履约保函，领取勘查许可证，取得探矿权。探矿权三年到期后，对勘查投入进行考核，完成承诺勘查工作量的，按原面积延续探矿权；未完成承诺勘查工作量的，按照未完成比例执行履约保函，核减区块面积后延续探矿权。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　与此同时，有关部门将积极协调、支持新疆企业与中石油、中石化建立合作共赢、利益共享机制，在石油公司矿业权区块内，通过合资合作的方式开展油气勘查开采。在油气勘查区块招标中，企业承诺的勘查工作量相同时，新疆企业优先获得区块；中标企业转入开采后应当在资源地注册企业；国家将加大新疆油气基础地质调查工作力度，探索完善既适合油气勘查开采特点又能发挥市场配置资源决定性作用的竞争性出让制度，同时落实地方政府的生产安全和环保监管责任。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　中国油气资源丰富，勘查开采尚处于初期至中期阶段。</span>2014<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年中央财经领导小组第六次会议提出推动能源消费、供给、技术和体制四项革命，部署油气勘查开采体制改革，破除体制障碍，加大国内油气勘查开采力度。为此国务院决定，首先在油气资源潜力较大的新疆开展油气勘查开采改革试点工作。此次试点将及时总结出可推广的制度经验，适时向全国推开。</span></span></p><p><br/></p>','中国油气勘查开采改革试点启动 上游领域破冰','　　中国国土资源部7日发布新疆石油天然气勘查区块招标公告，以新疆为试点的油气资源上游领域改革正式拉开序幕。中国油气上游领域国有石油公司专营局面有望终结。','1','1','2017-03-11 15:21:52','','0','','','0','{\"thumb\":\"\"}','0','0','0','0','','');INSERT INTO ts_posts ( `id`, `post_author`, `post_keywords`, `post_source`, `post_date`, `post_content`, `post_title`, `post_excerpt`, `post_status`, `comment_status`, `post_modified`, `post_content_filtered`, `post_parent`, `post_type`, `post_mime_type`, `comment_count`, `smeta`, `post_hits`, `post_like`, `istop`, `recommended`, `page_tpl`, `page_tpls` ) VALUES  ('165','1','油价两连跌','','2017-03-11 15:24:23','<p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　多空博弈下的国际油价震荡下行，让国内油价下调的概率逐渐增大。《经济参考报》记者从多家社会监测机构了解到，新一轮油价调整窗口于下周二</span>(7<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">21</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">日</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">)</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">开启，从目前的原油变化率及后期影响因素来看，“两连跌”将是板上钉钉，下调幅度或超过</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">0.2</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">元</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">/</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">升。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　自</span>7<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">7</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">日国内油价下调落实以来，伊朗达成核协议后对外强势表态将全力回归原油市场，浙江继续加重国际油市供应过剩的局面，同时美元走强，美国日均原油产量仍处于历史高位，国际油价下行风险愈加明显，周三国际原油双双收跌，美原油</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">WTI</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">跌至近三个月低位。截至</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">15</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">日收盘，纽约商品交易所</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">8</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月交货的轻质原油期货价格收于每桶</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">51.41</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">美元，</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">8</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月交货的伦敦布伦特原油期货价格收于每桶</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">57.05</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">美元。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　原油变化率也随之持续下跌。卓创调价模型显示，截至</span>7<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">15</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">日收盘，第七个工作日原油变化率为</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">-7.21%</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">，对应下调</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">265</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">元</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">/</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">吨。“从目前的原油价格及后期影响因素判断，本轮成品油价下调落实将是板上钉钉。”卓创资讯分析师王能表示，这将是年内第六次下调油价。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　安迅思研究中心高级研究员梁丹也认为，尽管美国原油库存下跌，但美国库欣地区原油库存增长，且美国石油库存增量增长。加上近期希腊退出欧元区担忧、伊朗原油解禁、中国股市震荡等因素强烈打压着原油期货市场。此外，在油价大幅下挫的行情下，中东地区欧佩克产油国仍在不遗余力的增产原油，以适应夏季到来本国电厂需求。未来一周，国际油价继续下行的可能性更大，下周二国内汽柴油零售价将迎来</span>“两连跌”，预计幅度在<span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">270</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">元</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">/</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">吨，测算到零售价格，</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">90</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">号汽油和</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">0</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">号柴油</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">(</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">全国平均</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">)</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">每升分别降低</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">0.2</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">元和</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">0.23</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">元。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　据了解，国内经济增速缓慢，钢铁、煤矿、房地产等各行业均较疲软，开工率不高，使得柴油刚性需求持续呈现旺季不旺局面。而汽油受油品升级、价格偏高影响，直批环节客户需求也相对较低，基本面供大于求持续利空市场。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　同时，受油价下调预期影响，目前市场看空情绪浓重。贸易商按需操作不改，</span>100<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">吨以上大单极少，以致中石油、中石化等主营直批环节进度拖欠严重，促销压力巨大，价格继续承压下行。卓创数据显示，截至</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">16</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">日，主营</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">93</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">号汽油均价已从</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">5</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">11</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">日最高点下跌</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">1024</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">元</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">/</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">吨，</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">0</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">号柴油跌幅也已高达</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">768</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">元</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">/</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">吨。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\">　　“上半年国内成品油批发行情在不温不火的疲软走势中结束，下半年也在<span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">7</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月的两连跌中暗淡开幕。目前国内经济疲软，加上后期原油走势堪忧的外围环境，国内成品油后期走势或难乐观。”王能称。</span></span></p><p><br/></p>','下周二国内油价两连跌已成定局 幅度或超0.2元每升','　　多空博弈下的国际油价震荡下行，让国内油价下调的概率逐渐增大。《经济参考报》记者从多家社会监测机构了解到，新一轮油价调整窗口于下周二(7月21日)开启，从目前的原油变化率及后期影响因素来看，“两连跌”将是板上钉钉，下调幅度或超过0.2元/升。','1','1','2017-03-11 15:23:28','','0','','','0','{\"thumb\":\"\"}','1','0','0','0','','');INSERT INTO ts_posts ( `id`, `post_author`, `post_keywords`, `post_source`, `post_date`, `post_content`, `post_title`, `post_excerpt`, `post_status`, `comment_status`, `post_modified`, `post_content_filtered`, `post_parent`, `post_type`, `post_mime_type`, `comment_count`, `smeta`, `post_hits`, `post_like`, `istop`, `recommended`, `page_tpl`, `page_tpls` ) VALUES  ('166','1','国际油价','','2017-03-11 15:25:19','<p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　市场预期原油供应过剩，国际油价</span>24<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">日继续下跌。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　美国油田技术服务公司贝克休斯</span>24<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">日发布的数据显示，尽管油价持续走低，本周美国运营的油田钻井数量却上升。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　此外，页岩油开采技术的革新令美国国内原油供应充裕。美国能源信息局的数据显示，上周美国全国商业原油库存增加</span>250<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">万桶。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　当天美元上涨也对油价形成压力。市场对于美联储年内启动加息的预期增强，美元走强降低了以美元计价的石油的投资吸引力。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　截至当天收盘，纽约商品交易所</span>9<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月交货的轻质原油期货价格下跌</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">0.31</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">美元，收于每桶</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">48.14</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">美元，跌幅为</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">0.64%</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">。</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">9</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月交货的伦敦布伦特原油期货价格下跌</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">0.65</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">美元，收于每桶</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">54.62</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">美元，跌幅为</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">1.18%</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">。</span></span></p><p><br/></p>','国际油价24日下跌 收于每桶48.14美元','　　市场预期原油供应过剩，国际油价24日继续下跌。','1','1','2017-03-11 15:24:37','','0','','','0','{\"thumb\":\"\"}','1','0','0','0','','');INSERT INTO ts_posts ( `id`, `post_author`, `post_keywords`, `post_source`, `post_date`, `post_content`, `post_title`, `post_excerpt`, `post_status`, `comment_status`, `post_modified`, `post_content_filtered`, `post_parent`, `post_type`, `post_mime_type`, `comment_count`, `smeta`, `post_hits`, `post_like`, `istop`, `recommended`, `page_tpl`, `page_tpls` ) VALUES  ('167','1','闽汽柴油价','','2017-03-11 15:26:59','<p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　昨日，国家发改委宣布下调国内成品油价格。省物价局同步调整汽柴油价格，今日零时起，</span>93<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">号汽油最高零售价下调</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">0.17</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">元</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">/</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">升，降至</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">5.96</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">元</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">/</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">升。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　据了解，我省</span>93<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">号汽油最高零售价格从</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">8167</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">元</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">/</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">吨调整为</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">7934</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">元</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">/</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">吨，</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">97</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">号汽油从</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">8630</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">元</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">/</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">吨调整为</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">8383</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">元</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">/</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">吨，车用</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">0</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">号柴油从</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">6720</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">元</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">/</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">吨调整为</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">6505</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">元</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">/</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">吨。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　调价后，我省</span>93<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">号汽油、</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">97</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">号汽油、车用</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">0</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">号柴油最高零售价依次为</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">5.96</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">元</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">/</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">升、</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">6.36</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">元</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">/</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">升、</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">5.57</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">元</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">/</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">升，每升分别下调</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">0.17</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">元、</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">0.19</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">元、</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">0.18</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">元。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　今年初以来，我省油价经历了</span>5<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">次上调，</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">7</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">次下调，</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">3</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">次搁浅。此次是我省油价年内第</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">7</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">次下调，也是油价的“四连跌”。</span></span></p><p><br/></p>','闽汽柴油价迎“四连跌” 今起93号汽油5.96元/升','　　昨日，国家发改委宣布下调国内成品油价格。省物价局同步调整汽柴油价格，今日零时起，93号汽油最高零售价下调0.17元/升，降至5.96元/升。','1','1','2017-03-11 15:26:24','','0','','','0','{\"thumb\":\"\"}','1','0','0','0','','');INSERT INTO ts_posts ( `id`, `post_author`, `post_keywords`, `post_source`, `post_date`, `post_content`, `post_title`, `post_excerpt`, `post_status`, `comment_status`, `post_modified`, `post_content_filtered`, `post_parent`, `post_type`, `post_mime_type`, `comment_count`, `smeta`, `post_hits`, `post_like`, `istop`, `recommended`, `page_tpl`, `page_tpls` ) VALUES  ('168','1','国内油价调整','','2017-03-11 15:28:22','<p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　根据</span>“十个工作日原则”，下轮汽柴油调价窗口将于<span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">8</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">18</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">日开启。据多家能源机构预测，国际原油价格如果继续保持或下降，国内成品油价格将迎来“五连跌”，预计下调幅度将在</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">250</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">—</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">300</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">元</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">/</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">吨。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　进入本周期以来，国际原油依旧深受供需面的打压，加之美国钻井数量的持续上涨、人民币意外贬值以及美国原油库存降幅低于预期等因素影响，欧美原油期货价格持续下跌。美国原油期货</span>8<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">13</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">日更是大跌逾</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">3%</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">至每桶</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">42</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">美元之下，创下</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">6</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年半新低。受此拖累，参考原油变化率持续负向发展。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　据中国新闻网报道，由于需求低迷，资源外销不畅，主营炼厂库存多处于高位，因此纷纷开始降量生产。中石化旗下沧州石化、济南炼厂等，中石油旗下大庆炼化、广西石化、乌鲁木齐石化等炼厂均调低了</span>8<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月份的原油计划加工量。另外，具备出口配额的炼厂后期也计划加大出口，以缓解国内高库存压力。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">附：</span>2015<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年国内成品油价格历次调整：</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\">8<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">4</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">日</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">24</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">时下调汽柴油最高零售限价每吨</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">220</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">元、</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">215</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">元</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\">7<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">21</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">日</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">24</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">时下调汽柴油最高零售限价每吨</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">265</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">元、</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">265</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">元</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\">7<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">7</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">日</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">24</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">时下调汽柴油最高零售限价每吨</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">95</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">元、</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">90</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">元</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\">6<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">23</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">日汽柴油价调价搁浅</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\">6<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">8</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">日</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">24</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">时下调汽柴油最高零售限价每吨</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">110</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">元、</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">105</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">元</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\">5<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">25</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">日汽柴油价调价搁浅</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\">5<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">11</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">日</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">24</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">时上调汽柴油最高零售限价每吨</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">255</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">元、</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">245</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">元</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\">4<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">24</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">日</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">24</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">时上调汽柴油最高零售限价每吨</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">300</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">元、</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">285</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">元</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\">4<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">10</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">日</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">24</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">时上调汽柴油最高零售限价每吨</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">120</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">元、</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">115</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">元</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\">3<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">26</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">日</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">24</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">时下调汽柴油最高零售限价每吨</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">240</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">元、</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">230</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">元</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\">3<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">12</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">日汽柴油价调价搁浅</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\">2<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">27</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">日</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">24</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">时上调汽柴油最高零售限价每吨</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">390</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">元、</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">375</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">元</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\">2<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">9</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">日</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">24</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">时上调汽柴油最高零售限价每吨</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">290</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">元、</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">280</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">元</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\">1<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">26</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">日</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">24</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">时下调汽柴油最高零售限价每吨各</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">365</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">元、</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">350</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">元</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\">1<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">12</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">日</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">24</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">时下调汽柴油最高零售限价每吨各</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">180</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">元、</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">230</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">元</span></span></p><p><br/></p>','国内油价调整窗口明日打开 或将迎 年内5连跌','　　据中国新闻网报道，由于需求低迷，资源外销不畅，主营炼厂库存多处于高位，因此纷纷开始降量生产。中石化旗下沧州石化、济南炼厂等，中石油旗下大庆炼化、广西石化、乌鲁木齐石化等炼厂均调低了8月份的原油计划加工量。另外，具备出口配额的炼厂后期也计划加大出口，以缓解国内高库存压力。','1','1','2017-03-11 15:27:14','','0','','','0','{\"thumb\":\"\"}','2','0','0','0','','');INSERT INTO ts_posts ( `id`, `post_author`, `post_keywords`, `post_source`, `post_date`, `post_content`, `post_title`, `post_excerpt`, `post_status`, `comment_status`, `post_modified`, `post_content_filtered`, `post_parent`, `post_type`, `post_mime_type`, `comment_count`, `smeta`, `post_hits`, `post_like`, `istop`, `recommended`, `page_tpl`, `page_tpls` ) VALUES  ('169','1','融租租赁+互联网','','2017-03-11 15:39:25','<p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\">　　8<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">26</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">日，国务院常务会议明确指出要加快融资租赁和金融租赁行业发展，会议指出，加快发展高端核心装备进口、清洁能源、社会民生等领域的租赁业务。鼓励通过租赁推动装备走出去和国际产能合作。鼓励创新业务模式，用好“互联网</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">+</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">”，坚持融资与融物结合，建立租赁物与二手设备流通市场，发展售后回租业务。同时，加大政策支持，鼓励各地通过奖励、风险补偿等方式，引导融资租赁和金融租赁更好服务实体经济。同时，有关部门要协调配合，加强风险管理。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　中国人民大学金融与证券研究所副所长赵锡军在接受媒体采访时表示：</span>“融资租赁和金融租赁给企业发展提供了资金和设备的便利，是目前经济新常态下，降低企业负债、降低企业融资成本、经济结构调整和产业升级换代的好方法、好手段。”</span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　困境破局</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　随着国家对新能源产业扶持力度不断加大</span>,<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">新能源产业在我国的发展速度也逐步加快</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">,</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">但融资困境依然存在。比如，太阳能光伏产业，由于它属于新兴产业</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">,</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">虽然且具有低风险等特点</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">,</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">但可利用的融资渠道仍然相当有限</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">,</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">金融支持新能源产业发展中存在的深层次矛盾和问题也日益突出。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　相关专家指出，目前我国多层次能源金融市场体系和服务体系尚未形成，不少新能源企业在资本市场的融资几乎是空白。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　值得注意的是，这次会议不仅为新能源的融资现状提供了具体的方向，而且也提出用好</span>“互联网<span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">+</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">”等创新业务模式。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\">　　“互联网<span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">+</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">”自不必说，从去年蓬勃发展后，传统企业纷纷尝试互联网转型之路。在国务院常务会议上通过的《“互联网</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">+</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">”行动指导意见》的颁布，正式将“互联网</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">+</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">”纳入了经济发展的重要政策。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　有行业专家认为，</span>“融租租赁<span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">+</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">互联网”市场想象空间很大。由于融资租赁合同期限较长，资金回流较慢，与互联网金融平台结合具备先天的契合点。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\">　　SPI<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">绿能宝董事长彭小峰在接受记者采访时认为，“目前我国融资租赁在经济活动中的比例较低，跟美国、日本等发达国家比差距很大，在发达国家融资租赁已经进入了工业、汽车、生活日用品等诸多领域，应用十分广泛，我们急需创新商业模式，服务更多领域。”</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　据了解，我国未来绿色产业的投资每年需要两万亿元以上，占</span>GDP<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">的</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">3%</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">。不过，目前政府财政仅能拿出</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">3000</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">亿元左右投入节能、环保、新能源等绿色领域，在全部绿色投资中，预计政府出资仅占</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">10%</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">—</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">15%</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">，其余</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">85%</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">—</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">90%</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">需要民间出资。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　作为资本密集型产业，新能源项目需要大量的资金，由于其短期内难以获得经济效益，商业金融机构投资兴趣不大，导致新能源行业缺乏优惠的长期贷款资金。现阶段政策支持是新能源项目融资的一个重要方面。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　国外经验说明，现阶段新能源还缺乏竞争力，政府需要采取各种积极有效的政策给以支持。政府需要加大政策性资金投入，包括政策性贷款、贴息贷款、税收减免、直接补贴等方面。政府还需要通过协助项目融资等方式，使新能源项目获得开发资金的支持。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　对此，业内专家认为，</span>“融资租赁<span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">+</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">互联网”的市场发展空间很大，这一政策必将带动新能源的快速发展，从而加快行业结构调整，促进企业做大做强。同时融资租赁作为我国的朝阳产业，未来几年内仍将维持较快的增长，再加上借助“互联网</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">+</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">”为跳板，未来依然具有广阔的市场前景</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　中国经济腾飞了</span>30<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年后已经进入了新常态，经济转型升级已经成为国家大政方针，但是今年是个全球经济秩序重新构建的转折之年，内因外患交加，使得中国经济维持</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">7%</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">的增长率。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　尽管国家统计局公布的宏观经济数据，尤其是</span>GDP<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">的增长速度依然比较稳定，整个上半年依然维持在</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">7%</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">左右，但是我们都清楚这</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">7%</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">的增长很大一部分的贡献来自上半年的股票市场。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　有金融机构分析认为，在过去一直以来金融业对</span>GDP<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">增长的贡献大概是</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">10%</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">左右，而今年上半年，</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">GDP</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">增长的贡献中来自金融业的贡献已经达到了将近</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">30%</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">。换句话说，我们经济增长速度尽管维持了</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">7%</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">左右，但是这个速度是有虚高的成份的，而相当程度上是跟我们上半年的金融活动活跃是有关系的，而金融活动的活跃很显然是跟上半年的股票市场的繁荣是密切相关的。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　想办法鼓励以民营资本为代表的中小微企业在实体经济方面积极投资便是最重要的策略选择，引导中小微企业投资实体经济就必须解决他们融资难、融资贵的问题，帮助他们对技术设备快速更新，拓宽产品销售渠道，压缩他们的生产成本，而只有融资租赁行业能够为企业引进高端制造业技术设备，促进机器设备的销售，帮助中小微企业融资融物，促进制造业和实体经济的发展，助力中国经济转型升级，所以在</span>26<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">号国务院常务会议上将发展融资租赁作为重点支持内容。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　另外，随着</span>“互联网<span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">+</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">”战略的推进，互联网金融在中国快速发展，这丰富了融资租赁公司将其资产证券化的手段，增加了其资金流动性，扩大了融资租赁公司的投资能力，能够更好更快的服务于制造业企业发展实体经济。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　融资租赁行业虽然从</span>2013<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">开始进入快速发展时期，但在中国渗透率依旧很小，尚属于新兴行业，但其独特的经营方式对实体经济的发展是极具推动作用的，尤其在经济下行周期中，以投资拉动经济增长势在必行，融资租赁行业极有可能成为支撑中国经济保持平稳增长的新引擎。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　业内专家指出，金融行业如今在全球范围内都有合作，如何让我们的资金流动起来，可以用到真正有绿色效应的事情上是一个重要的发展方向，应该让资金更多地投入到新兴的能源领域，投入到如何让能源更清洁的行业中。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　国家层面此次出台加快金融租赁和融资租赁发展的相关政策，面对政策环境利好和融资租赁队伍的壮大，融资租赁专家屈延凯认为，在当前应当努力发挥融资租赁的特色，根据客户的实际需求，解决银行信贷解决不了的问题。面对经济增长压力较大、实体经济转型的局面，他建议大力发展具有产业背景的租赁公司，走产融结合的道路，通过搭建整体金融服务平台，切实推动实体经济的发展。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　蓄势待发</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　由于历史原因，我国融资租赁出现三类公司形式。此次国务院常务会议明确加快融资租赁和金融租赁行业发展的措施，表明对三类融资租赁公司的充分重视。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　天津租赁行业协会会长杨海田表示，此时国务院以常务会议的形式对融资租赁在缓解融资难、融资贵，拉动企业设备投资，带动产业升级，推动外贸进出口，盘活国有资产，支持实体经济等方面的作用给予明确肯定，对融资租赁行业来说尚属首次，必将进一步加快整个行业的发展进程。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　实际上，本届中央政府一直高度重视融资租赁行业对于促进实体经济、推动制造业发展以及加速中国制造</span>“走出去”的作用。早在<span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">2013</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">12</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月，国务院总理李克强在视察工银租赁时，就充分肯定金融租赁产业是我国的一个新高地，鼓励金融机构往前闯、往前试，闯出自己的新天地，使整个融资租赁行业受到了巨大鼓舞。随后，一系列促进融资租赁发展的税务、法律措施纷纷出台，有力地推动了全行业的发展。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　屈延凯表示，从宏观政策的制定，到微观业务的推动，本届政府为我国融资租赁发展注入了极大的动力。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　据杨海田介绍，自</span>2013<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年以来，融资租赁业始终保持快速发展的态势，截至今年</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">6</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月底，全国融资租赁总部企业达到</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">3185</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">家，比上年底增加</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">983</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">家。在北京、天津、上海、广州等一些城市和地区，融资租赁业不仅成为金融创新的亮点，也成了推动经济发展的一个强力支撑。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　中国租赁联盟此前发布的《</span>2014<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年融资租赁业发展报告》指出，融资租赁中国属于朝阳产业，有广阔的市场前景，预计</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">2020</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年市场规模达到</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">12</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">万亿元。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　平安证券研究报告指出，融资租赁行业的业绩增长并不随着经济增长的下行而下行。是由于在经济下行的时间段内，企业获得资金将会比较困难。而融资租赁有利于产品销售、增强企业的盈利能力。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　事实上，当此次国务院常务会议内容公开后，</span>“绿能宝”便再次进入公众视野，它也被也内称为当前新能源领域的利用“互联网＋”进行“融资租赁”的典范。</span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　虽然前景广阔，但是模式创新必不可少。</span>8<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">26</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">日的国务院常务会议也提出：创新业务模式，用好“互联网</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">+</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">”，坚持融资与融物结合，建立租赁物与二手设备流通市场，发展售后回租业务。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　在此方面彭小峰感触颇深。他曾表示，绿能宝最大的优势就是融资租赁以及对整个链条中风险的把控，融资租赁可以帮助资金密集型的产业健康发展，而融资租赁公司的钱从哪里来呢？过去来说，这部分资金可以是公司自有资金或者从银行获得贷款，但互联网金融时代的到来，让融资租赁可以借力</span>“互联网<span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">+</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">”获得广阔融资渠道。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　据了解，</span>“绿能宝”是今年年初创建的新能源理财品牌，一经上市，便以“新能源”<span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">+</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">“互联网”</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">+</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">“融资租赁”创新模式迅速引起了媒体和行业的广泛关注。在“绿能宝模式”中，投资人通过购买太阳能电池板，并将其委托绿能宝租赁给太阳能发电项目，参与光伏电站建设，同时有效解决光伏电站融资难问题。与总理提出的“用好“互联网</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">+</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">”，坚持融资与融物结合，加快发展新能源租赁业务”理念相通。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　细看绿能宝，可以发现，</span>“新能源”、“互联网金融”、“融资租赁”，每一部分都顺应了各属行业的发展趋势，并都陆续得到了政府的大力支持。</span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　作为国内最成功的</span>“互联网<span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">+</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">融资租赁</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">+</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">新能源”平台，其建立了新能源网络理财平台，既能为分布式光伏电站建设解决融资难，同时也为百姓打开了一条安全、稳定、高收益理财渠道。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\">　　“绿能宝”首创了“互联网<span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">+</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">融资租赁</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">+</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">新能源”的创新模式，为新能源行业解决融资难、融资贵，同时为老百姓提供了安全、稳健、高收益的理财渠道，将</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">C</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">端理财需求与</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">B</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">端资金需求相结合。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\">　　“绿能宝”相关负责人还表示，在国家政策的大力扶持下，绿能宝将不断加强业务创新，继续推动太阳能应用进程，“让人人成为太阳能的生产者与收获者”不再是一句空谈。</span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　而此次，国务院常务会议提出的融资租赁与新能源的联姻发展，不仅有助于新能源的发展，也是对国内</span>“绿色金融”之路一条有效的尝试。</span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　中国人民银行研究局首席经济学家马骏认为，现在发展绿色金融是</span>“天时地利人和”。中共中央、国务院此前印发《关于加快推进生态文明建设的意见》，要求把生态文明建设放在突出战略地位，融入经济建设、政治建设、文化建设、社会建设各方面和全过程。同时，公众的期望促使政府部门加大污染治理力度，对外投资过程中的环境责任问题也受到越来越多的重视。</span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　中国金融学会副会长、中国人民银行副行长潘功胜指出，作为一种市场化的制度安排，金融在促进环境保护和生态建设方面具有十分重要的作用。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\">　　SPI<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">绿能宝董事长彭小峰表示，站在国家对“互联网</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">+</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">融资租赁</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">+</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">新能源”的风口，未来绿能宝将上线更多创新业务，加快太阳能的推广应用。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　对此，业内人士普遍认为，此次国务院常务会议的决定将成为我国融资租赁发展历史上的又一个里程碑，以此为契机，我国融资租赁业将进入一个新的发展阶段，回归融资租赁的本质，走专业化发展道路，更好地支持实体经济发展。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\">&nbsp;</span></p><p style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-left: 0px; text-indent: 0px; text-align: justify; line-height: 150%;\"><br/></p>','融租租赁+互联网成新能源发展新引擎','　　8月26日，国务院常务会议明确指出要加快融资租赁和金融租赁行业发展，会议指出，加快发展高端核心装备进口、清洁能源、社会民生等领域的租赁业务。鼓励通过租赁推动装备走出去和国际产能合作。鼓励创新业务模式，用好“互联网+”，坚持融资与融物结合，建立租赁物与二手设备流通市场，发展售后回租业务。同时，加大政策支持，鼓励各地通过奖励、风险补偿等方式，引导融资租赁和金融租赁更好服务实体经济。同时，有关部门要协调配合，加强风险管理。','1','1','2017-03-11 15:38:14','','0','','','0','{\"thumb\":\"\"}','1','0','0','0','','');INSERT INTO ts_posts ( `id`, `post_author`, `post_keywords`, `post_source`, `post_date`, `post_content`, `post_title`, `post_excerpt`, `post_status`, `comment_status`, `post_modified`, `post_content_filtered`, `post_parent`, `post_type`, `post_mime_type`, `comment_count`, `smeta`, `post_hits`, `post_like`, `istop`, `recommended`, `page_tpl`, `page_tpls` ) VALUES  ('170','1','非OPEC石油产量','','2017-03-11 15:40:46','<p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　近日，国际能源署</span>(IEA)<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">发布月度报告指出，油价暴跌将迫使包括美国在内的非</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">OPEC(</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">石油输出国组织</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">)</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">产油国削减产量，同时将推高对</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">OPEC</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">原油的需求。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\">　　IEA<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">同时预计，</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">2016</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年非</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">OPEC</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">国家原油日产量将下降近</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">50</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">万桶，至</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">5770</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">万桶，创下近二十年来最大降幅，将进一步促使供需失衡的原油市场的再平衡。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　分析人士指出，其实</span>2015<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年初，原油价格就已经进入区间底部，其间虽有反弹。这也使得</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">OPEC</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">主要成员国沙特备受煎熬，但如今看来，其利用低油价打压竞争对手以维持市场份额的策略正在奏效。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\">　　IEA<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">指出，美国石油产量可能受到冲击，而美国原油产量下降可能使</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">OPEC</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">在</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">2016</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年的市场占有率上具有更大的优势，因此</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">OPEC</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">明年可能扩大产量。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　美国能源信息署</span>(EIA)<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">公布的数据显示，</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">8</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月，美国石油产量降至近</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">11</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">个月低点，且可能在</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">2016</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年继续下降。而石油生产商已削减新生产计划的支出，美国钻井平台数自</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">2014</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年底以来也大幅减少。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\">　　“低油价环境迫使市场缩减产量和刺激需求，从表面上看，<span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">OPEC</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">不顾价格以保护市场份额的策略似乎达到了预期效果，挤走了高成本、低效率的生产商。”</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">IEA</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">表示。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　目前，由于原油长期维持低位，这使得原油需求出现增长迹象。从</span>IEA<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月度报告提供的数据来看，大部分的需求增长来自发达国家，其中包括美国市场。不过，沙特逐渐提高的产量满足了上述额外的原油需求。</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">IEA</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">预计，</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">2015</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年全球石油需求增长</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">170</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">万桶</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">/</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">天，升至五年新高，</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">2016</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年将增长</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">140</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">万桶</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">/</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">天。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　不过，在这场石油战中，沙特为首的</span>OPEC<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">成员国也受到了重创。此前数据显示，沙特</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">90%</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">的财政收入来自原油产业。而根据国际货币基金组织</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">(IMF)</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">估计，沙特预算赤字将占到其国内生产总值</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">(GDP)</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">的</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">20%</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">左右，即约</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">1400</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">亿美元。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　标准普尔也曾在今年</span>2<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月下调沙特经济前景至“负面”，并指出沙特的经济太过单一，无法应对油价持续大幅度下降。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　而今年</span>7<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月，沙特阿拉伯央行行长法哈德·穆巴拉克</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">(Fahadal-Mubarak)</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">在接受外媒采访时表示，沙特政府今年向当地银行出售了</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">150</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">亿里亚尔</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">(</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">约合</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">40</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">亿美元</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">)</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">的本币债券。这是沙特自</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">2007</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年以来发行的首批主权债券，主要筹集资金以填补低油价造成的财政预算赤字。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　与此同时，即便通过低油价策略，打击了美国页岩油生产，但是目前原油市场供远大于求的局面并没有得到根本性改变。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\">　　EIA10<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">日公布最新的库存数据显示，截至</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">9</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">4</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">日当周，美国原油库存增加</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">257</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">万桶，增幅高于预期。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　对此，高盛在其研究报告中指出，油市供应过剩预计将持续到明年。高盛预估</span>2015<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">NYMEX</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">原油价格为每桶</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">48.10</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">美元，此前预估为</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">52</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">美元。高盛并将</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">2016</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">NYMEX</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">原油价格从先前预估的每桶</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">57</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">美元下调至</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">45</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">美元。高盛同时调降</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">2015</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年布伦特原油价格预估，从稍早预估的每桶</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">58.2</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">美元下调至</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">53.7</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">美元，</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">2016</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年预估从每桶</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">62</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">美元下调至</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">49.5</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">美元。</span></span></p><p><br/></p>','明年非OPEC石油产量创20年最大降幅','　　近日，国际能源署(IEA)发布月度报告指出，油价暴跌将迫使包括美国在内的非OPEC(石油输出国组织)产油国削减产量，同时将推高对OPEC原油的需求。','1','1','2017-03-11 15:39:42','','0','','','0','{\"thumb\":\"\"}','0','0','0','0','','');INSERT INTO ts_posts ( `id`, `post_author`, `post_keywords`, `post_source`, `post_date`, `post_content`, `post_title`, `post_excerpt`, `post_status`, `comment_status`, `post_modified`, `post_content_filtered`, `post_parent`, `post_type`, `post_mime_type`, `comment_count`, `smeta`, `post_hits`, `post_like`, `istop`, `recommended`, `page_tpl`, `page_tpls` ) VALUES  ('171','1','我国将择机放开成品油价格','','2017-03-11 15:42:42','<p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\">　　10<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">15</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">日，《中共中央国务院关于推进价格机制改革的若干意见》（下简称《意见》）下发。意见明确了</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">6</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">大重点领域价格改革方向，包括完善农产品价格形成机制、加快推进能源价格市场化、完善环境服务价格政策、理顺医疗服务价格、健全交通运输价格机制、创新公用事业和公益性服务价格管理。到</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">2017</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年，竞争性领域和环节价格基本放开。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\">&gt;&gt;<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">能源</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">成品油价格择机放开</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　《意见》明确，凡是能由市场形成价格的都交给市场，政府不进行不当干预。在推进能源价格市场化方面，要按照</span>“管住中间、放开两头”总体思路，推进电力、天然气等能源价格改革。</span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　《意见》提出，要择机放开成品油价格，尽快全面理顺天然气价格，加快放开天然气气源和销售价格。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　目前国内原油价格一般随国际油价、美元汇率等发生变动，并不能清楚反映国内市场的供需情况，成品油价格放开的呼吁早在多年前就有提出。有专家认为，放开成品油价格将有利于油品资源的合理化配置，减少出现</span>“油荒”的体制因素，炼制加工、物流营销成本会逐渐降低，对节能减排也会有促进作用。</span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　另外，《意见》提出要有序放开上网电价和公益性以外的销售电价。按照</span>“准许成本加合理收益”原则，政府部门将合理制定电网、天然气管网输配价格，并扩大输配电价改革试点范围，逐步覆盖到各省级电网，科学核定电网企业准许收入和分电压等级输配电价，改变对电网企业的监管模式，逐步形成规则明晰、水平合理、监管有力、科学透明的独立输配电价体系。</span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　在放开竞争性环节电价之前，相关部门还将完善煤电价格联动机制和标杆电价体系，使电力价格更好反映市场需求和成本变化。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\">&gt;&gt;<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">医疗</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">药品价格由市场形成　</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　《意见》要求，到</span>2020<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年要基本理顺医疗服务比价关系，落实非公立医疗机构医疗服务市场调节价政策。公立医疗机构的医疗服务项目价格将实行分类管理，对市场竞争比较充分、个性化需求比较强的医疗服务项目价格实行市场调节价，其中医保基金支付的服务项目由医保经办机构与医疗机构谈判合理确定支付标准。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　药品采购机制将进一步完善，并发挥医保控费作用，药品实际交易价格主要由市场竞争形成。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\">&gt;&gt;<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">交通</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">铁路票价与车速挂钩</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　《意见》明确，将逐步放开铁路运输竞争性领域价格，扩大由经营者自主定价的范围。完善铁路货运与公路挂钩的价格动态调整机制，简化运价结构，构建以列车运行速度和等级为基础、体现服务质量差异的旅客运输票价体系。这也意味着，铁路车票的价格，会与列车速度、等级、服务质量等挂钩。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　同时，逐步扩大道路客运、民航国内航线客运、港口经营等领域由经营者自主定价的范围，适时放开竞争性领域价格，完善价格收费规则，并放开邮政竞争性业务资费，理顺邮政业务资费结构和水平。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\">&gt;&gt;<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">其他</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">推进宽带提速降费</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　《意见》提出，规范电信资费行为，推进宽带网络提速降费，为</span>“互联网<span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">+</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">”提供有力支撑。推动电信企业简化资费结构，切实提高宽带上网等业务的性价比，并为城乡低收入群体提供更加优惠的资费方案。督促电信企业合理制定互联网接入服务资费标准和计费办法，促进电信网间互联互通。严禁利用不正当定价行为阻碍电信服务竞争，扰乱市场秩序。加强资费行为监管，清理宽带网络建设环节中存在的进场费、协调费、分摊费等不合理费用，严厉打击价格违法行为。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　《意见》还提出，要全面实行居民用水用电用气阶梯价格制度，推行供热按用热量计价收费制度，并根据实际情况进一步完善。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\">&gt;&gt;<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">相关</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">政府定价范围限定三领域</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　根据《意见》提出的目标，到</span>2017<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年，竞争性领域和环节价格基本放开，政府定价范围主要限定在重要公用事业、公益性服务、网络型自然垄断环节。到</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">2020</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年，市场决定价格机制基本完善，科学、规范、透明的价格监管制度和反垄断执法体系基本建立，价格调控机制基本健全。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　《意见》提出，对于极少数保留的政府定价项目，要推进定价项目清单化。中央和地方要在加快推进价格改革的基础上，于</span>2016<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年以前制定发布新的政府定价目录。凡是政府定价项目，一律纳入政府定价目录管理。对纳入政府定价目录的项目，要制定具体的管理办法、定价机制、成本监审规则，进一步规范定价程序，并加强成本监审和成本信息公开。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\">&gt;&gt;<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">影响</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">成品油价格涨跌或更频繁</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　发改委价格司相关负责人此前接受采访时曾表示，推进资源环境价格改革，特别是资源性产品价格市场化，不能等同于变相涨价。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　该负责人以成品油为例指出，随着国内成品油市场经营体制的改革，特别是市场竞争的形成，成品油的价格将完全放开，交给市场，</span>“到那个时候，油价调整可能会比现在更加频繁，就像如今的股票市场一样，涨涨跌跌，成为一种大众习惯的常态”。</span></p><p><br/></p>','我国将择机放开成品油价格 价格涨跌或更频繁','　　10月15日，《中共中央国务院关于推进价格机制改革的若干意见》（下简称《意见》）下发。意见明确了6大重点领域价格改革方向，包括完善农产品价格形成机制、加快推进能源价格市场化、完善环境服务价格政策、理顺医疗服务价格、健全交通运输价格机制、创新公用事业和公益性服务价格管理。到2017年，竞争性领域和环节价格基本放开。','1','1','2017-03-11 15:41:05','','0','','','0','{\"thumb\":\"\"}','1','0','0','0','','');INSERT INTO ts_posts ( `id`, `post_author`, `post_keywords`, `post_source`, `post_date`, `post_content`, `post_title`, `post_excerpt`, `post_status`, `comment_status`, `post_modified`, `post_content_filtered`, `post_parent`, `post_type`, `post_mime_type`, `comment_count`, `smeta`, `post_hits`, `post_like`, `istop`, `recommended`, `page_tpl`, `page_tpls` ) VALUES  ('172','1',' 油价调整幅度','','2017-03-11 15:43:43','<p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　昨日，国家发改委宣布上调国内成品油价格。省物价局同步调整汽柴油价格，今日零时起，</span>93<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">号汽油最高零售价上调</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">0.04</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">元</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">/</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">升，涨至</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">5.80</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">元</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">/</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">升。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　据了解，我省</span>93<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">号汽油最高零售价格从</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">7674</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">元</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">/</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">吨调整为</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">7727</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">元</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">/</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">吨，</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">97</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">号汽油从</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">8109</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">元</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">/</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">吨调整为</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">8165</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">元</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">/</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">吨，车用</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">0</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">号柴油从</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">6270</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">元</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">/</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">吨调整为</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">6320</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">元</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">/</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">吨。调价后，我省</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">93</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">号汽油、</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">97</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">号汽油、车用</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">0</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">号柴油最高零售价依次为</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">5.80</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">元</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">/</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">升、</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">6.19</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">元</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">/</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">升、</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">5.41</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">元</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">/</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">升，每升均比此前上调了</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">0.04</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">元。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　今年初以来，我省油价经历了</span>7<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">次上调，</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">9</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">次下调，</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">4</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">次搁浅。上一轮调价时间在</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">10</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">1</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">日零时，但由于调价金额每吨不足</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">50</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">元而搁浅。这是成品油零售限价调整以来的最小上调幅度。因幅度较小，对消费者的油耗成本影响也较为有限。</span></span></p><p><br/></p>','93号汽油涨至5.80元/升 油价调整幅度为年内最小','　　昨日，国家发改委宣布上调国内成品油价格。省物价局同步调整汽柴油价格，今日零时起，93号汽油最高零售价上调0.04元/升，涨至5.80元/升。','1','1','2017-03-11 15:42:58','','0','','','0','{\"thumb\":\"\"}','0','0','0','0','','');INSERT INTO ts_posts ( `id`, `post_author`, `post_keywords`, `post_source`, `post_date`, `post_content`, `post_title`, `post_excerpt`, `post_status`, `comment_status`, `post_modified`, `post_content_filtered`, `post_parent`, `post_type`, `post_mime_type`, `comment_count`, `smeta`, `post_hits`, `post_like`, `istop`, `recommended`, `page_tpl`, `page_tpls` ) VALUES  ('173','1','油气价格将择机放开','','2017-03-11 15:44:45','<p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\">　　10<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">21</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">日，国家发展改革委副主任胡祖才在国新办发布会上表示，成品油价改未来将择机放开。天然气价格也按与可替代能源挂钩的联动机制进行调整。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　胡祖才说，成品油定价机制未来要继续朝市场化方向改革，择机放开成品油价格。他同时表示，放开成品油价格最重要的是要与石油体制机制改革紧密结合起来。改革以后也要进一步完善竞争环境，条件具备了，才可以完全放开由市场决定。这之前还是严格按照原机制来执行。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　关于天然气价格改革，胡祖才表示要</span>“管住中间、放开两头”：管网价格要政府定，两头要实行放开，由供需双方来确定。目前，页岩气、煤制气等放开价格的气量已占到<span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">40%</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">，发改委还在推进大用户的直接交易，提高协商价格比重。对非居民用气，建立了与可替代能源挂钩的联动机制并将继续完善该机制。天然气交易中心今年也已在上海建立，现在正在试行交易，总体情况较好。胡祖才介绍，现在天然气有</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">30%</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">左右从境外进口，消费市场上约</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">25%</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">是居民用气，其他是非居民用气。居民用气价格暂时不会调整。</span></span></p><p><br/></p>','发改委：油气价格将择机放开','　　10月21日，国家发展改革委副主任胡祖才在国新办发布会上表示，成品油价改未来将择机放开。天然气价格也按与可替代能源挂钩的联动机制进行调整。','1','1','2017-03-11 15:43:59','','0','','','0','{\"thumb\":\"\"}','1','0','0','0','','');INSERT INTO ts_posts ( `id`, `post_author`, `post_keywords`, `post_source`, `post_date`, `post_content`, `post_title`, `post_excerpt`, `post_status`, `comment_status`, `post_modified`, `post_content_filtered`, `post_parent`, `post_type`, `post_mime_type`, `comment_count`, `smeta`, `post_hits`, `post_like`, `istop`, `recommended`, `page_tpl`, `page_tpls` ) VALUES  ('174','1','柴油消费严重低迷','','2017-03-11 15:45:50','<p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　柴油消费与经济增长关系紧密，是反映工业活动的风向标，运输、制造业、建筑业等行业与柴油消费联系密切。随着国内经济放缓，从去年开始，国内柴油消费开始下滑，</span>2015<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年四季度以来，市场更是持续严重低迷。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　国家统计局</span>10<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">19</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">日公布的数据显示，三季度</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">GDP</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">同比增长</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">6.9</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">％，这是</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">6</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年来</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">GDP</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">增速首度“破</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">7</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">”，中国的经济下行压力仍旧很大；另外，</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">PPI</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">（生产价格指数）已经连续数月为负，创下历史新低。经济形势下行压力对柴油消费的抑制作用增强。并且，今年以来，全球经济增长并不乐观，欧佩克原油产量再创新高，总体上原油供需基本面仍将保持宽松，后期国际油价不确定性因素较多，仍存在较大下行压力。同时，天然气、电动汽车等替代能源快速发展以及非标柴油、轻质燃料油等隐形资源增多，也将对正品油柴油消费带来较大抑制作用。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　而且，阅兵小长假和国庆长假期间，建筑施工、物流运输以及工矿企业停工停运较多，抑制柴油消费需求。长假过后，生产建筑运输等行业陆续恢复以及</span>“三秋”农业用油增加，有效拉动了柴油消费增长。但是，由于国内实体经济难有实质性改善，柴油消费仍将保持低迷态势。</span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　在国内柴油市场严重低迷的情况下，中国柴油竞相出口，并且连续创下历史新高，成为大宗商品的又一</span>“负面清单”。中国海关公布的数据显示，<span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">8</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月份柴油出口同比飙升</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">77%</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">，创纪录达到</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">72.25</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">万吨；</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">9</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月份，中国柴油出口同比增长</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">391.6%</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">，创纪录达到</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">111</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">万吨。</span></span></p><p><br/></p>','柴油消费严重低迷','　　柴油消费与经济增长关系紧密，是反映工业活动的风向标，运输、制造业、建筑业等行业与柴油消费联系密切。随着国内经济放缓，从去年开始，国内柴油消费开始下滑，2015年四季度以来，市场更是持续严重低迷。','1','1','2017-03-11 15:45:05','','0','','','0','{\"thumb\":\"\"}','2','0','0','0','','');INSERT INTO ts_posts ( `id`, `post_author`, `post_keywords`, `post_source`, `post_date`, `post_content`, `post_title`, `post_excerpt`, `post_status`, `comment_status`, `post_modified`, `post_content_filtered`, `post_parent`, `post_type`, `post_mime_type`, `comment_count`, `smeta`, `post_hits`, `post_like`, `istop`, `recommended`, `page_tpl`, `page_tpls` ) VALUES  ('175','1','原油进口','','2017-03-11 15:48:21','<p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　原油进口双权放开的进程继续提速，日前，商务部发文批复宁夏宝塔石化及东营亚通石化正式获得原油非国营贸易进口资质。而此前宁夏宝塔及东营亚通已经先行获得原油进口使用权，这意味着双权皆有的地炼数量增加至六家。而山东汇丰石化、万达天弘化学、寿光鲁清石化、京博石化等四家已经进入公示环节，这意味着其原油进口使用资质已经基本确认。中宇资讯统计数据显示，截至目前获得原油进口使用权的地方炼厂扩容至</span>11<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">家，配额数量总计达</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">4978.88</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">万吨，共淘汰及承诺淘汰重组装置产能</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">3357</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">万吨</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">/</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年。据悉，目前地炼企业继续踊跃申报原油进口相关资质。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">进口权伴环保承诺</span> <span style=\"font-family:宋体\">产业升级兵不血刃</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　中宇资讯分析师张永浩表示，原油进口相关权限的放开，将增进地炼炼油原料的多元化，拓宽地炼原料油获取渠道。原油进口权相关权限的分割将确保政府部门对成品油市场的控制。首先，原油进口使用权的获取伴随着地炼装置淘汰以及油品升级的承诺，政府使得炼厂在环保升级方面</span>“自动缴械”，这在很大程度上推进了成品油市场去产能化以及环保升级的过程。另外，非国营贸易进口允许量总额设定了“上限”，政府部门将综合考虑上年度该炼厂的原油实际加工量以及各分项指标的达标情况用以确认新一年的非国营贸易进口允许量，以确保原油进口不会出现无序增长，扰乱内部资源流通生态。</span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　能源变革大幕拉开，目前油气改革各环节正齐头并进。张永浩表示，中国油气改革的主要框架涵盖以下几个方向：主体改革，体现在市场多元化及自主经营权的推进方面；上游垄断破除，体现在勘探环节及原油进口等方面垄断的放松；财税改革，体现在清费立税、税收法定等方面；价格改革。原油进口权放开仅是油气改革的一个细节，更多的改革正在同时推进。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">炼油原料多样化</span> <span style=\"font-family:宋体\">进口原油现优势</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　中宇资讯分析师高青翠表示，上述</span>11<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">家地炼厂需要常年保持</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">89.4%</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">的开工率，才能满额用掉进口原油使用权。炼厂在逐渐摒弃燃料油等低轻油产率的产品后，购买的炼油原料中原油占比优势愈加明显。</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">2014</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年以来，国内海洋油大批量外放，马瑞油及稀释沥青等进口量大幅提升，原料市场逐渐由吃紧过渡到充裕。而地方炼厂开工率在效益缩水的利空影响下，无奈进入低负荷开工、原料渠道多样化的状态中。从另外一个角度分析，随着原料多样化局面逐渐明确，原料“自由选择度”明显提升，对于地方炼厂而言，高额的消费税成本及低汽、柴油收率，逐渐将进口燃料油“踢出”原料圈。而对于当前暂无原油进口权的炼厂而言，海洋油及稀释沥青仍有较大吸引力，获得进口原油资质的地炼厂，后期将部分采购目光放在中东及东南亚等轻、中质原油上。</span></span></p><p><br/></p>','原油进口放开促能源变革','　　原油进口双权放开的进程继续提速，日前，商务部发文批复宁夏宝塔石化及东营亚通石化正式获得原油非国营贸易进口资质。而此前宁夏宝塔及东营亚通已经先行获得原油进口使用权，这意味着双权皆有的地炼数量增加至六家。而山东汇丰石化、万达天弘化学、寿光鲁清石化、京博石化等四家已经进入公示环节，这意味着其原油进口使用资质已经基本确认。中宇资讯统计数据显示，截至目前获得原油进口使用权的地方炼厂扩容至11家，配额数量总计达4978.88万吨，共淘汰及承诺淘汰重组装置产能3357万吨/年。据悉，目前地炼企业继续踊跃申报原油进口相关资质。','1','1','2017-03-11 15:47:43','','0','','','0','{\"thumb\":\"\"}','1','0','0','0','','');INSERT INTO ts_posts ( `id`, `post_author`, `post_keywords`, `post_source`, `post_date`, `post_content`, `post_title`, `post_excerpt`, `post_status`, `comment_status`, `post_modified`, `post_content_filtered`, `post_parent`, `post_type`, `post_mime_type`, `comment_count`, `smeta`, `post_hits`, `post_like`, `istop`, `recommended`, `page_tpl`, `page_tpls` ) VALUES  ('176','1','能源规划工作座谈会','','2017-03-11 15:51:41','<p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　为深入学习贯彻党的十八届五中全会精神，交流国家和省级能源规划编制情况，安排部署下一阶段规划工作，</span>11<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">9</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">日，国家能源局在京召开全国“十三五”能源规划工作座谈会。国家发展改革委副主任、国家能源局局长努尔·白克力同志出席会议并作重要讲话。国家能源局副局长刘琦同志主持会议。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　会议传达学习了党的十八届五中全会精神。会议认为，五中全会审议通过的《</span>“十三五”规划建议》阐明了党和国家的战略意图，明确了今后五年发展的指导思想、基本原则、目标要求、基本理念和重大举措，体现了“四个全面”战略布局和“五位一体”总体布局，顺应了我国经济发展新常态的内在要求，具有很强的思想性、战略性、前瞻性、指导性。创新、协调、绿色、开放、共享五大发展理念，在理论和实践上有新的突破，对破解发展难题、增强发展动力、厚植发展优势具有重大指导意义。</span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　会议指出，</span>“十三五”时期是全面建成小康社会、实现第一个百年奋斗目标的决胜阶段，是贯彻落实习近平总书记关于能源发展“四个革命、一个合作”战略思想的第一个五年规划期。做好能源规划工作，必须深入贯彻落实党的十八大和十八届三中、四中、五中全会精神，以转变能源发展方式和提高能源发展质量为中心，着力推进能源生产和消费革命，着力推进能源创新发展、协调发展、绿色发展、开放发展和共享发展，努力建设清洁低碳、安全高效的现代能源体系，为全面建成小康社会、实现建党百年奋斗目标提供安全可靠的能源保障。</span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　会议强调，遵循五中全会确定的</span>“五大发展理念”，“十三五”时期能源发展改革的主要任务，要从以下五个方面来谋划：</span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　一是坚持创新发展。加快成熟技术的产业化推广应用和关键核心技术的集中攻关，争取在新一轮能源科技革命中走在世界的前列。加快能源体制机制创新，破解制约能源创新发展的体制约束。大力推动能源发展模式和商业模式创新，实施合同能源管理、需求侧管理等市场化机制。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　二是坚持协调发展。优化产业布局，合理调控煤炭、火电、炼油产能建设，提高资源配置效率。着力推进能源系统优化，实施电力和天然气调峰能力提升、分布式能源和智能电网发展、互联网</span>+<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">智慧能源等行动计划，显著提高能源系统的智能化水平和运行效率。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　三是坚持绿色发展。围绕</span>“两增加、一提高”三个目标（即增加非化石能源消费比重，增加天然气消费比重，提高煤炭清洁利用水平），继续控制能源消费总量，推进重点地区煤炭减量替代，大力发展非化石能源，大力推进化石能源清洁高效利用，加快重点领域用能方式变革。</span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　四是坚持开放发展。重点落实</span>“一带一路”战略，深化周边和沿线能源国际合作，推动重大能源项目落地。继续推进核电、水电、火电及特高压输电“走出去”，带动相关装备、技术与服务贸易“走出去”。</span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　五是坚持共享发展。适应人民群众生活条件改善要求，加快天然气管网建设，推进城乡配电网升级改造，为扩大民用天然气和电力消费创造条件。把能源发展和扶贫攻坚有机结合起来，重大能源工程项目优先向贫困地区倾斜。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　会议要求，能源战线要深入学习贯彻十八届五中全会精神，按照习近平总书记提出的</span>“四个革命、一个合作”总要求和全会确立的新理念、新思路，以强烈的使命感和高度的责任感，扎实做好各项工作，尽心尽力编制出一部经得起历史检验、符合经济社会发展规律、让党和人民群众满意的“十三五”能源规划，为推动能源生产和消费革命，实现“两个百年”奋斗目标和中华民族伟大复兴的中国梦做出应有贡献。</span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　国家能源局党组成员、总经济师、有关司负责同志，国家有关部门相关司负责同志，各省能源主管部门、有关中央能源企业负责同志，有关行业协会、国家能源规划专家委员会、国家能源规划咨询工作组成员单位有关负责同志参加会议。</span></span></p><p><br/></p>','全国“十三五”能源规划工作座谈会召开','　　为深入学习贯彻党的十八届五中全会精神，交流国家和省级能源规划编制情况，安排部署下一阶段规划工作，11月9日，国家能源局在京召开全国“十三五”能源规划工作座谈会。国家发展改革委副主任、国家能源局局长努尔·白克力同志出席会议并作重要讲话。国家能源局副局长刘琦同志主持会议。','1','1','2017-03-11 15:50:37','','0','','','0','{\"thumb\":\"\"}','1','0','0','0','','');INSERT INTO ts_posts ( `id`, `post_author`, `post_keywords`, `post_source`, `post_date`, `post_content`, `post_title`, `post_excerpt`, `post_status`, `comment_status`, `post_modified`, `post_content_filtered`, `post_parent`, `post_type`, `post_mime_type`, `comment_count`, `smeta`, `post_hits`, `post_like`, `istop`, `recommended`, `page_tpl`, `page_tpls` ) VALUES  ('177','1','国家降低成品油价格','','2017-03-11 15:54:54','<p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　今日，国家发展改革委发出通知，决定将汽、柴油价格每吨分别降低</span>85<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">元和</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">80</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">元，测算到零售价格</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">90</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">号汽油和</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">0</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">号柴油（全国平均）每升分别降低</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">0.06</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">元和</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">0.07</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">元，调价执行时间为</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">11</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">17</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">日</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">24</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">时。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　此次成品油价格调整幅度，是按照现行成品油价格形成机制，根据</span>11<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">17</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">日前</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">10</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">个工作日国际市场原油平均价格变化情况计算确定的。</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">11</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月上旬以来，受美国原油库存增加等因素影响，国际市场油价呈震荡下行走势，前</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">10</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">个工作日平均价格有所下降。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　通知要求，中石油、中石化、中海油三大公司要组织好成品油生产和调运，确保市场稳定供应，严格执行国家价格政策。各级价格主管部门要加大市场监督检查力度，严厉查处不执行国家价格政策的行为，维护正常市场秩序。</span></span></p><p><br/></p>','国家降低成品油价格　汽油每吨降低85元','　　今日，国家发展改革委发出通知，决定将汽、柴油价格每吨分别降低85元和80元，测算到零售价格90号汽油和0号柴油（全国平均）每升分别降低0.06元和0.07元，调价执行时间为11月17日24时。','1','1','2017-03-11 15:54:18','','0','','','0','{\"thumb\":\"\"}','1','0','0','0','','');INSERT INTO ts_posts ( `id`, `post_author`, `post_keywords`, `post_source`, `post_date`, `post_content`, `post_title`, `post_excerpt`, `post_status`, `comment_status`, `post_modified`, `post_content_filtered`, `post_parent`, `post_type`, `post_mime_type`, `comment_count`, `smeta`, `post_hits`, `post_like`, `istop`, `recommended`, `page_tpl`, `page_tpls` ) VALUES  ('178','1','汽、柴油价格','','2017-03-11 15:56:16','<p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\">&nbsp; &nbsp; 12<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">1</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">日，国家发展改革委发出通知，决定将汽、柴油价格每吨分别降低</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">145</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">元和</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">140</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">元，测算到零售价格</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">90</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">号汽油和</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">0</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">号柴油</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">(</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">全国平均</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">)</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">每升分别降低</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">0.11</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">元和</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">0.12</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">元，调价执行时间为</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">12</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">1</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">日</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">24</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">时。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　此次成品油价格调整幅度，是按照现行成品油价格形成机制，根据</span>12<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">1</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">日前</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">10</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">个工作日国际市场原油平均价格变化情况计算确定的。</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">11</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月中旬以来，受全球石油市场供给充裕等因素影响，国际市场油价呈震荡下行走势，前</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">10</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">个工作日平均价格有所下降。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　通知要求，中石油、中石化、中海油三大公司要组织好成品油生产和调运，确保市场稳定供应，严格执行国家价格政策。各级价格主管部门要加大市场监督检查力度，严厉查处不执行国家价格政策的行为，维护正常市场秩序。</span></span></p><p><br/></p>','发改委：汽、柴油价格每吨分别降低145元和140元','    12月1日，国家发展改革委发出通知，决定将汽、柴油价格每吨分别降低145元和140元，测算到零售价格90号汽油和0号柴油(全国平均)每升分别降低0.11元和0.12元，调价执行时间为12月1日24时。','1','1','2017-03-11 15:55:26','','0','','','0','{\"thumb\":\"\"}','0','0','0','0','','');INSERT INTO ts_posts ( `id`, `post_author`, `post_keywords`, `post_source`, `post_date`, `post_content`, `post_title`, `post_excerpt`, `post_status`, `comment_status`, `post_modified`, `post_content_filtered`, `post_parent`, `post_type`, `post_mime_type`, `comment_count`, `smeta`, `post_hits`, `post_like`, `istop`, `recommended`, `page_tpl`, `page_tpls` ) VALUES  ('179','1','国际原油市场“痛苦”去产能','','2017-03-11 16:09:26','<p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\">&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">在全球市场供大于求、美元持续走强的背景下，国际油价持续走低，今年至今已下跌约</span>30<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">％。市场普遍认为，原油市场供需再平衡会是一个“痛苦”的过程，低油价将成未来的新常态。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　尽管原油价格大幅下跌，已低于很多原油生产商的生产成本。不过大多数原油生产商仍在顶着亏损的压力继续生产。而欧佩克也放手一搏，增加产量与非欧佩克国家争夺市场份额。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　华尔街投行高盛</span>4<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">日发布报告指出，根据保守预测，预计全球原油市场在</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">2016</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年第四季度才能实现供需平衡。该行指出，原油市场在明年下半年实现平衡的前提是美国原油产量下降。但目前从美国的油井钻机数来看，还难以实现预期的降幅，因此高盛重申预计油价需要在低位维持更长的时间才能令油价出现上升。</span></span></p><p><br/></p>','国际原油市场“痛苦”去产能','    在全球市场供大于求、美元持续走强的背景下，国际油价持续走低，今年至今已下跌约30％。市场普遍认为，原油市场供需再平衡会是一个“痛苦”的过程，低油价将成未来的新常态。','1','1','2017-03-11 16:08:54','','0','','','0','{\"thumb\":\"\"}','0','0','0','0','','');INSERT INTO ts_posts ( `id`, `post_author`, `post_keywords`, `post_source`, `post_date`, `post_content`, `post_title`, `post_excerpt`, `post_status`, `comment_status`, `post_modified`, `post_content_filtered`, `post_parent`, `post_type`, `post_mime_type`, `comment_count`, `smeta`, `post_hits`, `post_like`, `istop`, `recommended`, `page_tpl`, `page_tpls` ) VALUES  ('180','1','国内石油行业','','2017-03-11 16:11:24','<p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:28px;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">油价不断下降、供需矛盾突出成为</span>2015<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年石油行业的缩影。日前，欧佩克决定不减产后，国际油价接连暴跌。与此同时，在国内以“三桶油”为代表的石油巨头也进行了一轮大洗牌，从</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">5</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月的“三桶油”集体换帅到近来中石油宣布整合旗下天然气管道业务以及油气改革方案上报国务院，业内认为，随着国企改革以及即将到来的“十三五”油气改革的实施，国内石油行业有望实现向全面市场化转变。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:28px;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><strong><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;font-size: 14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">业绩下滑下的改革压力</span></span></strong></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:28px;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">在油价持续下跌的情况下，国内石油业的代表</span>“三桶油”在<span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">2015</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年前三季度的业绩均出现下滑的状况。数据显示，中石油前三季度实现营收</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">13051</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">亿元，较去年同期下降</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">25.6%</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">，归属母公司股东的净利润为</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">305.9</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">亿元，较去年同期下降</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">68.1%</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">。中石化前三季度实现营收</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">15368.3</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">亿元，较去年同期下降</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">27.36%</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">，归属母公司净利润</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">258.4</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">亿元，较去年同期下降</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">49.49%</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">。此外，中海油业绩报告显示，前三季度实现营收</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">1167.4</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">亿元，同比下降</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">33.4%</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:28px;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">业内认为，今年前三季度连跌的原油价格和成品油价格是油企业绩下滑的主要原因。资料显示，</span>12<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月初，欧佩克宣布不减产后，国际油价接连出现暴跌，在四年来首次跌破每桶</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">70</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">美元重要关口后，继续深度下跌，并跌至每桶</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">67</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">美元下方，成为</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">2009</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">9</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月以来最低水平。而这对于“三桶油”的业绩产生很大的影响，据了解，上游勘探开发领域一直是“三桶油”重要的业绩贡献来源。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:28px;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><strong><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;font-size: 14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">政策助推市场化变革</span></span></strong></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:28px;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">除了石油企业自身的革新外，国家也针对石油行业市场化变革吹响了号角，第一轮措施就是</span>“三桶油”换帅。</span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:28px;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">今年</span>5<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月，“三桶油”官网分别发布了人事变动的消息，王宜林任中国石油天然气集团公司董事长、党组书记</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">;</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">王玉普任中国石油化工集团公司董事长、党组书记；杨华任中海油董事长、党组书记，免去其总经理职务。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:28px;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">有业内人士表示，除去高压反腐下的人事动荡因素，国企改革的加速推进是此次</span>“三桶油”集体换帅的主要原因。另外，据新华社消息，国家发改委新闻发言人施子海<span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">12</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">11</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">日表示，石油天然气行业的改革方案已经上报国务院，值得注意的是，“三桶油”已经加紧实施各自产业的改革。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:28px;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">以中石油为例，资料显示，</span>11<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">25</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">日，中石油宣布，批准公司子公司中油勘探开发有限公司对中亚天然气管道有限公司进行内部重组，并通过中油勘探全资子公司天津泰普天然气管道有限责任公司出售完成内部重组后天津泰普持有的中亚管道公司的</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">50%</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">股权给国新国际投资有限公司控制的曼松控股有限公司。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:28px;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">厦门大学能源经济与能源政策协同创新中心主任林伯强认为，中石油逐步剥离天然气管道符合国家油气改革的方向。有业内人士也表示，这是中石油实践国家油气改革计划的一小步，随着</span>“十三五”开幕以及国企改革速度的加快，未来会有更大的动作。</span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:28px;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><strong><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;font-size: 14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">产业向市场化全面转变</span></span></strong></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:28px;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">有业内人士表示，中石油日前的一系列动作也表明了石油行业改革的方向，即实现行业的全面市场化。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:28px;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">资料显示，已经上报国务院的《石油天然气体制改革总体方案》有望放宽油气全产业链市场准入，核心内容指向上游放开、管网分离和价格机制改革。</span>“十三五”时期，油气产业的上中下游各主要环节都将进行市场化改革，最终形成市场化的定价机制。</span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:28px;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">林伯强也表示，一直以来，油气行业的上游和管输环节被</span>“三桶油”垄断，实现石油业的全面市场化，这些环节一定要有变动。“油气勘探开发资质的条件限制有望放宽，拟实行矿权招投标制度，从申请在先改为竞争性出让，严格油气探矿权退出机制，建立油气矿权流转和储量转让制度，最大限度地提升民营及其他企业的市场竞争力，使市场价格更加反映市场，使资源得到更好配置。”林伯强说。</span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:28px;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">此外，中国国际经济交流中心特邀研究员范必表示，油气产业改革就是要从不完全市场产业链转向市场化产业链，建立公平竞争、开放有序、市场对油气资源配置起决定性作用的现代油气市场体系，不断提高油气保障能力，加快能源代际更替步伐。</span>“中国油气产业选择了上下游一体化的国家公司经营模式，对迅速提高油气企业规模发挥了积极作用。但少数企业的上下游一体化经营也扭曲了市场价格和供求关系，成为油气供求矛盾加剧和价格居高不下的主要原因。”范必说。</span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:28px;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\">&nbsp;</span></p><p><br/></p>','国内石油行业有望实现向全面市场化转变','      油价不断下降、供需矛盾突出成为2015年石油行业的缩影。日前，欧佩克决定不减产后，国际油价接连暴跌。与此同时，在国内以“三桶油”为代表的石油巨头也进行了一轮大洗牌，从5月的“三桶油”集体换帅到近来中石油宣布整合旗下天然气管道业务以及油气改革方案上报国务院，业内认为，随着国企改革以及即将到来的“十三五”油气改革的实施，国内石油行业有望实现向全面市场化转变。INSERT INTO ts_posts ( `id`, `post_author`, `post_keywords`, `post_source`, `post_date`, `post_content`, `post_title`, `post_excerpt`, `post_status`, `comment_status`, `post_modified`, `post_content_filtered`, `post_parent`, `post_type`, `post_mime_type`, `comment_count`, `smeta`, `post_hits`, `post_like`, `istop`, `recommended`, `page_tpl`, `page_tpls` ) VALUES  ('181','1','成品油价格','','2017-03-11 16:14:16','<p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:28px;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">未来几年国际油价可能都会低位徘徊，本着市场化的原则，新的油价机制要使油价切实与国际接轨，呼应国际油价的变动，取而代之的是以增减消费税调节油品消费市场。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:28px;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">据报道，国家发改委宣布进一步完善成品油价格形成机制，预计新机制出台前，成品油价格将继续暂缓调整。而据最新消息，国家发改委正在就进一步完善成品油价格形成机制，征求有关部门和单位意见。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:28px;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">在油价完全放开之前，油价怎么调，主要看制度。按照我国现行的《石油价格管理办法</span>(<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">实行</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">)</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">》，如果正常调整，调整后国内成品油价差不多要打九折，不是一个小数目。今年国际油价跌跌不休，近期更是创出</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">2008</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年以来的新低，而目前我国油价几乎比美国油价贵一倍，确有不合理的地方。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:28px;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">不过，成品油价格调整搁浅惹争议，真正的问题或许在于成品油价格机制，这也是人们对有关方面接下来完善成品油价格形成机制的期待所在。目前我国的油价调整机制</span>(<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">即《石油价格管理办法</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">(</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">实行</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">)</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">》</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">)</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">是</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">2013</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年制定的，可能存在不足，但作为长期执行的制度，在新的油价机制形成之前，严格的执行可以避免消费者的不解、甚至误解。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:28px;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">应看到，虽然以目前情况来看，成品油定价的完全市场化难以很快实现，但市场化也应是油价定价机制的最终目标。早在</span>2015<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">10</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月发布的《中共中央、国务院关于推进价格机制改革的若干意见》中，国家就明确，将加快推进能源价格市场化，择机放开成品油价格。“到</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">2020</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年，市场决定价格机制基本完善，科学、规范、透明的价格监管制度和反垄断执法体系基本建立，价格调控机制基本健全。”这意味着，最迟要到</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">2020</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年，政府对成品油价格的干预程度大幅降低，甚至完全放开，实现市场化定价。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:28px;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">而在国际上，实现了市场化国家或地区的成品油定价机制，都是根据市场自主定价，政府利用税收、利率、补贴等经济手段间接影响石油企业的价格政策。而市场化定价这一改革方向，也有利于将成品油的实际供需情况如实反映到油价上来。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:28px;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">值得注意的是，新的油价形成机制也应该税归税，价归价，不含税的油价应呼应国际油价的变动，因税增导致的油价不降，也有必要形成动态的调整机制，而这其中提升的成品油税额，用到了哪里，对环境起到了哪些有益的地方，也得有评估，有考核，做到机制的透明化。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:28px;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">从国际经验来看，韩国的成品油价格改革历程值得我们借鉴。目前韩国的油价是与国际市场接轨的，但韩国也曾经历过政府定价的阶段，在两种机制的变轨过程中，韩国先是实行原油价格联动机制，后来才实行成品油价格联动机制，最终实现了完全的市场化。总之，油价的完全市场化必然是一个渐进而漫长的过程。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:28px;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">就当下而言，市场和消费者最为关心的是新的价格机制，有关方面在就成品油价格机制征求社会各方面意见的时候，也需要全面听取，尤其是听取处于弱势一方的广大消费者的意见。未来几年国际油价可能都会低位徘徊，本着市场化的原则，新的油价机制要使油价切实与国际接轨，呼应国际油价的变动，取而代之的是以增减消费税调节油品消费市场。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:28px;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\">&nbsp;</span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:28px;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\">&nbsp;</span></p><p><br/></p>','发改委将完善价格机制征求意见缓调整成品油价格','       未来几年国际油价可能都会低位徘徊，本着市场化的原则，新的油价机制要使油价切实与国际接轨，呼应国际油价的变动，取而代之的是以增减消费税调节油品消费市场。','1','1','2017-03-11 16:13:02','','0','','','0','{\"thumb\":\"\"}','0','0','0','0','','');INSERT INTO ts_posts ( `id`, `post_author`, `post_keywords`, `post_source`, `post_date`, `post_content`, `post_title`, `post_excerpt`, `post_status`, `comment_status`, `post_modified`, `post_content_filtered`, `post_parent`, `post_type`, `post_mime_type`, `comment_count`, `smeta`, `post_hits`, `post_like`, `istop`, `recommended`, `page_tpl`, `page_tpls` ) VALUES  ('182','1','低油价倒逼成品油定价','','2017-03-11 16:15:54','<p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:28px;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\">12<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">29</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">日，国内成品油价再次迎来调价窗口，但</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">2015</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年最后一次调价却再次落空。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:28px;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">就在当天，国家发改委召开了专题会议，就进一步完善成品油价格形成机制征求有关部门和单位意见。新华社报道预计，新机制出台前，成品油价格将继续暂缓调整。而昨日，国家发改委确实没有发布调价通知。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:28px;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">改革箭在弦上，针对新机制的改革方向，也引起了业内的热烈讨论。分析认为，从</span>2013<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年开始运行的现行成品油调价机制可能已经不太适合当前的低油价环境了，而联系上一次的改革内容，本次改革或也将从三方面加以完善，调价周期有望进一步缩短。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:28px;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\">11<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">17</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">日，山西太原一加油站，工作人员正在清点加油款。中新社记者 张云 摄</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">11</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">17</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">日，山西太原一加油站，工作人员正在清点加油款。中新社记者 张云 摄</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:28px;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">低油价为改革创造契机</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:28px;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">十三五，能源改革是重头戏。日前，《中共中央、国务院关于推进价格机制改革的若干意见》发布。意见指出，将加快推进能源价格市场化，择机放开成品油价格和天然气销售价格。而在推动价格放开前，定价机制改革就显得迫在眉睫。而当前较低的油价水平也恰好为改革提供了一个良好的契机。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:28px;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">另一方面，国际原油的低迷使得成品油价格频现下调，虽然利好普通消费者，但对炼厂及石化行业均是重压。数据显示，</span>2014<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年下半年以来，国际油价进入连跌模式，累计跌幅已超过</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">50%</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">。而在近期，欧美原油期货价格更双双跌破</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">40</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">美元大关，创下近</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">11</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年新低。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:28px;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">隆众石化网分析师李彦对中新网能源频道表示：</span>“持续低迷的国际油价已经让相关部门感觉相当棘手，从<span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">2013</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年开始运行的现行成品油调价机制可能已经不太适合当前的低油价环境了。”</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:28px;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">中国石油</span>(8.410, 0.00, 0.00%)<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">大学教授董秀成也表示，从大的形势来看，目前成品油价格机制确实应该作调整了，总的方向应该是越来越市场化。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:28px;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">分析称调价周期或进一步缩短</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:28px;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">在</span>2013<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年，国内成品油定价机制也曾进行过一次改革。改革主要集中在三个方面。一是将调价周期缩短，由</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">22</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">个工作日缩短至</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">10</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">个工作日；二是取消了挂靠国际市场油种平均价格波动</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">4%</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">的调价幅度限制，将正负</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">50</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">元</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">/</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">吨作为是否调价的界限；三是适当调整了国内成品油价格挂靠的国际市场原油品种。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:28px;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">李彦认为，如果成品油定价机制继续革新，也必然会基于这三个方面进行增强和创新。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:28px;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">她预计调价周期或进一步缩短，由</span>10<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">个工作日缩短至</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">5</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">个工作日。“这样会使国际原油价格的波动更好地反映出来，成品油价格的涨跌也会更加频繁。而且，在国际油价持续低迷的时候，国内成品油价格也不会连续大幅下跌。”</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:28px;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">另外，挂靠的国际市场原油品种可能继续调整，而调价机制的计算公式和内容可能会更加清晰。</span>“据传，目前国家挂靠的是布伦特、迪拜和辛塔三个油种。辛塔由于产油量日渐萎缩，不太可能继续参考。而我国进口原油主要来源地中东和俄罗斯可能会成为新的参考。”</span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:28px;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">李彦还表示，在我国石油产业日益透明化的背景下，国家可能会给出清晰的调价计算公式，这样有助于增强民众的知情权，也能减少许多无端的猜测。另外也可能会有类似股市的熔断机制，比如设置国际油价的上下限，或者对油价的涨跌幅度进行界限控制。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:28px;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">新的成品油价格机制已经提上了日程，而政府不干预或少干预、成品油价格完全由市场调控则是终极目标。成品油定价改革的新方案很可能将在</span>2016<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年浮出水面。”李彦补充说。</span></span></p><p><br/></p>','低油价倒逼成品油定价机制改革调价周期或再缩短','12月29日，国内成品油价再次迎来调价窗口，但2015年最后一次调价却再次落空。','1','1','2017-03-11 16:14:33','','0','','','0','{\"thumb\":\"\"}','0','0','0','0','','');INSERT INTO ts_posts ( `id`, `post_author`, `post_keywords`, `post_source`, `post_date`, `post_content`, `post_title`, `post_excerpt`, `post_status`, `comment_status`, `post_modified`, `post_content_filtered`, `post_parent`, `post_type`, `post_mime_type`, `comment_count`, `smeta`, `post_hits`, `post_like`, `istop`, `recommended`, `page_tpl`, `page_tpls` ) VALUES  ('183','1','汽柴油','','2017-03-11 16:17:07','<p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:28px;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">国家发改委</span>1<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">13</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">日通知称，自当日</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">24</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">时起，将汽、柴油价格每吨分别降低</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">140</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">元人民币和</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">135</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">元，测算到全国平均零售价格</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">90</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">号汽油和</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">0</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">号柴油每升分别降低</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">0.10</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">元和</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">0.11</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">元。</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">2015</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">12</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月，国家发改委曾两度暂缓成品油价下调，理由包括“改善空气质量”和“酝酿新的定价机制”。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:28px;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">国际上，</span>2014<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年中以来国际原油价格重挫。本月召开的欧佩克会议未达成减产决议，居高不下的原油产量和低迷的市场需求使得国际油价一路暴跌。欧佩克</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">11</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">9</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">日公布的月度报告数据显示，</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">2015</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年，非欧佩克国家的约为石油产量每天</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">5724</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">万吨，较去年增长了</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">0.72%</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">，欧佩克成员国的总体石油产量约为每天</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">3100</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">万吨，虽较</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">9</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月略有下降，但仍然维持在高位状态。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:28px;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\">2015<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年，中国国内油价共下调</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">12</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">次，上调</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">7</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">次且大多在上半年完成，下半年完全进入继续下行通道，全年油价总体下跌</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:28px;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">具体到居民日常油价，由于各地方的吨升折算系数不同难以做地区间比较。以北京</span>92<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">号汽油为例，</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">2015</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年下半年一直维持在“</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">5</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">元时代”。如果不是发改委暂缓调整，油价或早已逼近</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">4</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">元关口。</span></span></p><p><br/></p>','发改委：汽柴油每吨分别下降140元和135元','       国家发改委1月13日通知称，自当日24时起，将汽、柴油价格每吨分别降低140元人民币和135元，测算到全国平均零售价格90号汽油和0号柴油每升分别降低0.10元和0.11元。2015年12月，国家发改委曾两度暂缓成品油价下调，理由包括“改善空气质量”和“酝酿新的定价机制”。','1','1','2017-03-11 16:16:06','','0','','','0','{\"thumb\":\"\"}','1','0','0','0','','');INSERT INTO ts_posts ( `id`, `post_author`, `post_keywords`, `post_source`, `post_date`, `post_content`, `post_title`, `post_excerpt`, `post_status`, `comment_status`, `post_modified`, `post_content_filtered`, `post_parent`, `post_type`, `post_mime_type`, `comment_count`, `smeta`, `post_hits`, `post_like`, `istop`, `recommended`, `page_tpl`, `page_tpls` ) VALUES  ('184','1','国内成品油价','','2017-03-11 16:19:14','<p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:28px;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">明日</span>24<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">时是“十个工作一调整”的汽柴油零售价调整窗口。根据成品油新调价机制，国际原油在</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">40</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">美元</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">/</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">桶的价格之下，国内成品油价格不再下调。也正是如此，昨日多家机构预测明日成品油零售价停止下调。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:28px;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\">1<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">13</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">日，发改委发出关于进一步完善成品油价格形成机制有关问题的通知，提到当国内成品油价格挂靠的国际市场原油价格低于每桶</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">40</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">美元时，国内成品油价格不再下调。另外，建立油价调控风险准备金。当原油价格低于</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">40</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">美元调控下限时，成品油价格未调金额全部纳入风险准备金，设立专项账户存储。由于新的调价机制出台较为匆忙，只是制定出了大致框架，而一些具体的执行措施没有同步跟出。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:28px;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">过去几周时间内，全球股市下跌引发市场对经济增长减缓的担忧，加上原油市场供大于求的趋势难以缓解，拖累</span> WTI<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">及</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">Brent</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">原油期货价格不断探底，并于</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">1</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月中旬跌破</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">30</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">美元</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">/</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">桶。安迅思成品油行业分析师杨丹表示，截至</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">1</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">22</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">日，国际原油在“地板价”之下长达</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">1</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">个半月的时间，且即使今明两日国际原油大幅反弹，也难以跳至“地板价”之上，因此，明日国内汽柴油零售价下调将冰冻。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:28px;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">昨天，还有关于国家财政部、税务总局等相关部门正在酝酿成品油消费税将再次上调的传闻。如果本次消费税上调落实，将成为</span>2015<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">1</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月之后，第四次调整成品油消费税单位税额。据了解，许多发达国家在能源消费量达到一定水平后，多会提高成品油消费税，油品税费在发达国家财政税收中所占比重较大。而当前我国整体汽车保有量已处于世界领先水平，逐步成为成品油消费大国，成品油需求量仍在增加，由此来看，后期国内消费税上涨也是必然趋势。昨天还有业内人士透露，本次消费税调整只是本年度税费改革的开端，</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">2016</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年，国家在能源行业的税改仍将会有大的举措。</span></span></p><p><br/></p>','多家机构预测国内成品油价27日或停止下调','       明日24时是“十个工作一调整”的汽柴油零售价调整窗口。根据成品油新调价机制，国际原油在40美元/桶的价格之下，国内成品油价格不再下调。也正是如此，昨日多家机构预测明日成品油零售价停止下调。','1','1','2017-03-11 16:17:35','','0','','','0','{\"thumb\":\"\"}','0','0','0','0','','');INSERT INTO ts_posts ( `id`, `post_author`, `post_keywords`, `post_source`, `post_date`, `post_content`, `post_title`, `post_excerpt`, `post_status`, `comment_status`, `post_modified`, `post_content_filtered`, `post_parent`, `post_type`, `post_mime_type`, `comment_count`, `smeta`, `post_hits`, `post_like`, `istop`, `recommended`, `page_tpl`, `page_tpls` ) VALUES  ('185','1','中国石油需求放缓','','2017-03-11 16:20:37','<p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:28px;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">根据中国政府发布的数据计算得出，中国</span>2015<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年共消费原油</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">1032</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">万桶每天，较</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">2014</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年增长</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">25.6</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">万桶每天。但</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">2016</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年或放缓。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:28px;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">自</span>2014<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年年中以来，国际原油价格累计下跌超过</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">70%</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">至</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">12</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年以来新低。中国需求成为原油价格暴跌期间的一个主要亮点。一方面中国汽车市场庞大，另一方面中国政府也在借机扩充战略石油储备。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:28px;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">目前支撑中国原油需求的一个主要因素就是中国</span>2015<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年你下半年减免汽车购置税导致汽车销售量大幅增长。中国汽车工业协会本月早期发布的报告预计，</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">2016</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年中国汽车销售量增幅有望加快至</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">6%</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:28px;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">另据调查数据，作为世界最大的大宗商品消费国，中国</span>2016<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年的原油进口增速将达到</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">8%</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">，进口量将达到</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">720</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">万桶</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">/</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">日。中国海关发布的数据显示，中国</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">2015</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年前</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">11</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">个月原油进口上涨</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">8.8%</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">至</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">663</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">万桶</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">/</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">日，其中十月份进口量刷新</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">740</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">万桶</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">/</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">日的记录高位。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:28px;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">然而，随着中国经济增速降至</span>25<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年来新低，</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">2016</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年中国石油需求或放缓。渣打银行发布研究报告称，中国</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">2016</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年石油需求预计增加</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">42</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">万桶每天，大幅低于预估的</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">2015</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">60</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">万桶每天增幅。国际能源署近期发布的报告也做出类似预测。</span></span></p><p><br/></p>','中国石油需求放缓是影响油价的重要因素','        根据中国政府发布的数据计算得出，中国2015年共消费原油1032万桶每天，较2014年增长25.6万桶每天。但2016年或放缓。','1','1','2017-03-11 16:19:28','','0','','','0','{\"thumb\":\"\"}','0','0','0','0','','');INSERT INTO ts_posts ( `id`, `post_author`, `post_keywords`, `post_source`, `post_date`, `post_content`, `post_title`, `post_excerpt`, `post_status`, `comment_status`, `post_modified`, `post_content_filtered`, `post_parent`, `post_type`, `post_mime_type`, `comment_count`, `smeta`, `post_hits`, `post_like`, `istop`, `recommended`, `page_tpl`, `page_tpls` ) VALUES  ('186','1','中国2016年石油需求','','2017-03-11 16:21:53','<p style=\"margin-right:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\">&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">中国石油集团经济技术研究院发布报告称，中国</span>2016<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年石油需求预计将增长</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">4.3%</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">，表观消费量达到</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">5.66</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">亿吨，原油净进口预计增长</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">7.3%</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">至</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">3.57</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">亿吨，石油对外依存度上升到</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">62%</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:28px;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">报告预计，中国今年成品油需求</span>3.3<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">亿吨，增长</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">3.9%</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">。原油加工量预计为</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">5.49</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">亿吨，成品油产量</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">3.56</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">亿吨，增长</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">5.5%</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:28px;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">报告指出，</span>“<span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">2016</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年国内成品油供需盈余继续扩大，成品油出口尤其是柴油出口将呈现常态化和规模化的特征。预计</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">2016</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年成品油净出口将达到</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">2500</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">万吨，增长</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">31%</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">。”</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:28px;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:28px;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\">&nbsp;</span></p><p><br/></p>','中国2016年石油需求预增4.3%','       中国石油集团经济技术研究院发布报告称，中国2016年石油需求预计将增长4.3%，表观消费量达到5.66亿吨，原油净进口预计增长7.3%至3.57亿吨，石油对外依存度上升到62%。','1','1','2017-03-11 16:21:05','','0','','','0','{\"thumb\":\"\"}','0','0','0','0','','');INSERT INTO ts_posts ( `id`, `post_author`, `post_keywords`, `post_source`, `post_date`, `post_content`, `post_title`, `post_excerpt`, `post_status`, `comment_status`, `post_modified`, `post_content_filtered`, `post_parent`, `post_type`, `post_mime_type`, `comment_count`, `smeta`, `post_hits`, `post_like`, `istop`, `recommended`, `page_tpl`, `page_tpls` ) VALUES  ('187','1','油价回调','','2017-03-11 16:26:26','<p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:28px;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">刚刚开始，大宗商品便开始一转年前颓势，接连反弹。金价反弹、有色金属等也纷纷回暖，持续下行的油价也在</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14px;\">猴年</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14px; line-height: 150%;\">上周五强势反弹。大宗商品，是</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14px; line-height: 150%;\">“乍暖还寒”还是将迎来转折？这是市场当下最关注的事情。</span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:28px;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">不过，不可忽视的是，大宗商品在过去一年的下跌已经如巨石入水，掀起波澜。除了紧密相连的矿业巨头由盈利转为亏损之外，上周，渣打银行也暴露出</span>26<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年首次亏损，其中重要原因即是受大宗商品市场带累。引人关注的是，这一影响又将如何发酵？　　 油价带领大宗商品回暖 </span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:28px;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">持续暴跌之后，油价终于强势</span>“反弹”。<span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">26</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">日，受伊拉克和尼日利亚两国均出现输油管中断事故信息影响，国际油价</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">26</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">日盘中反弹逾</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">2%</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">。美国</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">WTI</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">原油期货价格盘中最高触及</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">34.66</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">美元</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">/</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">桶，布伦特原油期货价格盘中最高触及</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">36.99</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">美元</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">/</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">桶。 </span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:28px;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">黄金市场</span>2<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月以来也整体处于上升状态。国际现货黄金</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">2</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">26</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">日当周累计收跌</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">3.70</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">美元，跌幅</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">0.3%</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">，尽管有所回调，但整体看，现货黄金</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">2</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月至今已累计上涨</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">104.50</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">美元，涨幅达到</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">9.35%</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">。 </span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:28px;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">除了原油和黄金，大宗商品中，近期有色金属、钢铁和煤炭价格也纷纷上行。一度引发市场对于大宗商品市场见底回升的猜测。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:28px;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">不过，原油近两日的上涨或是受短期因素影响。据报道，此前伊拉克和尼日利亚两国均出现输油管中断事故，导致两国原油日均总供应量暂时减少</span>80<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">万桶，预计将维持两周时间。由于事故造成的供应量下降对油价提供支撑。 </span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:28px;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">除了周五上升，回顾全周，油价整体也处于上行状态。数据显示，</span>NYMEX<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">原油期货</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">2</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">26</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">日当周上涨</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">11%</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">，报</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">32.78</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">美元</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">/</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">桶。布伦特原油期货也收涨逾</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">6%</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">。 </span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:28px;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">另一方面，美国产油量持续减少，也为油价上行提供了一些支撑。美国油服公司贝克休斯公布数据显示，截至</span>2016<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">2</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">26</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">日当周美国石油活跃钻井数减少</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">13</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">座至</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">400</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">座，连续第</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">10</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">周减少，降至自</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">2009</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">12</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">11</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">日以来最低位。美国能源信息署（</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">EIA</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">）公布最新的库存数据也显示，截至</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">2</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">19</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">日当周，美国汽油库存减少</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">223.6</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">万桶，预期减少</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">103.3</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">万桶，为</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">2015</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">11</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">6</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">日以来首次录得下降，美国上周原油日均产量环比减少</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">3.3</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">万桶至</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">910.2</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">万桶</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">/</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">日。 </span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:28px;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">国际能源署近期发布的原油市场中期展望报告显示，国际油市将在</span>2017<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年开始恢复平衡，届时美国原油产量在低油价的压力下会进一步下降。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:28px;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">大宗商品是否已见底？</span> </span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:28px;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">尽管大宗商品是否见底仍是未知数，但大宗商品市场对世界经济影响已经越来越明显。首当其冲的是矿业。</span>25<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">日，矿业巨头淡水河谷公布</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">2015</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年度业绩。营收总额</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">260.47</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">亿美元，亏损达到</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">121.29</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">亿美元。公司方面把亏损原因归咎于铁矿粉、球 团矿、镍及其他产品价格下滑。而另外两家矿业巨头必和必拓和力拓也难以幸免。必和必拓</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">16</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年来首次亏损，</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">2016</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">上半财年亏损额达到</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">56.69</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">亿美元。力拓集团则亏损了</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">17.19</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">亿美元。 </span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:28px;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">除了矿业，一些金融机构也因大宗商品市场下行而元气大伤。渣打银行</span>23<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">日公布</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">2015</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年业绩，净亏损</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">21.94</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">亿美元，成为渣打银行自</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">2002</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年在香港上市以来首次亏损。据渣打方面表示，很大一部分亏损原因在于受到大宗商品市场的拖累。 </span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:28px;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">据了解，去年，渣打银行的整体大宗商品投资减少</span>28%<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">。</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">2015</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年，渣打银行的贷款减值规模高达</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">40</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">亿美元，同比增加</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">87%</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">，大宗商品价格下跌及印度金融市场情况恶化正是造成减值金额大幅增加的主要原因。 </span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:28px;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">若未来大宗商品的走势进一步下行，相关影响或将继续扩散。不过，尽管近期油价反弹让不少人期待原油市场回调，但不少机构对油价仍持悲观态度。</span> </span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:28px;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">巴克莱银行</span>24<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">日发布报告称，</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">2016</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年上半年国际油价可能仍将继续承压，预计上半年布伦特原油均价在每桶</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">33</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">美元，下半年布伦特原油均价在每桶</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">41.50</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">美元。 </span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:28px;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">巴克莱表示，美国产量下滑预计将削减美国库存的囤积率。同时，该行预计</span>2016<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年美国能源企业的资本支出将格外下降</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">50%</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">，对产量构成调整。巴克莱同时认为，流动性收紧是导致生产商缩减运营，节约资金以及着重关注最高产区域的主要原因。 </span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:28px;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">巴克莱预计，</span>2016<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年全球原油每日供应过剩在</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">80</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">万桶，到</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">2017</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年将转变为供应赤字</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">40</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">万桶。同时维持</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">2016</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年全球原油需求日增长在</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">100</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">万桶的预估不变。 </span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:28px;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">国际评级机构惠誉</span>24<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">日也发布声明称，越来越多证据表明今年全球经济增长将弱于预期，该机构宣布下调</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">2016</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年布伦特原油以及美原油（</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">WTI</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">）价格预期。惠誉将今年布伦特原油价格预期下调至每桶</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">35</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">美元，同时将布伦特原油价格预期也下调至每桶</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">35</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">美元。惠誉还将</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">2016</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年“压力情形下”的美原油和布伦特原油价格预期下修至每桶</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">25</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">美元，且认为市场可能要到</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">2017</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年才达到平衡。</span></span></p><p><br/></p>','油价回调：“乍暖还寒”还是复苏开始','       刚刚开始，大宗商品便开始一转年前颓势，接连反弹。金价反弹、有色金属等也纷纷回暖，持续下行的油价也在猴年上周五强势反弹。大宗商品，是“乍暖还寒”还是将迎来转折？这是市场当下最关注的事情。','1','1','2017-03-11 16:25:05','','0','','','0','{\"thumb\":\"\"}','0','0','0','0','','');INSERT INTO ts_posts ( `id`, `post_author`, `post_keywords`, `post_source`, `post_date`, `post_content`, `post_title`, `post_excerpt`, `post_status`, `comment_status`, `post_modified`, `post_content_filtered`, `post_parent`, `post_type`, `post_mime_type`, `comment_count`, `smeta`, `post_hits`, `post_like`, `istop`, `recommended`, `page_tpl`, `page_tpls` ) VALUES  ('188','1','我国原油期货市场建设','','2017-03-11 16:35:06','<p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:28px;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">全国人大代表孙焕泉建议，要加快推进我国原油期货市场建设，增强我国对国际原油市场的影响力，降低油价波动带来的风险，保障国家能源安全。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:28px;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">当前，我国已成为世界第二大石油消费国和第一大石油进口国，但从国际石油市场定价格局看，主要以美国纽约、英国伦敦期货交易市场价格为主导。我国尚未建立成熟的石油期货市场，只能被动接受国际油价变化，一定程度上导致我国在国际贸易中处于不利地位。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:28px;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">孙焕泉建议，一要抓住低油价时机开放我国原油期货市场。</span>2014<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年下半年以来，国际石油市场呈现供大于求的态势，国际油价一路走低，为我国建设原油期货市场创造有利条件。针对原油期货上市，国家相关部门已出台一系列政策，开放我国原油期货市场的条件基本成熟，应加快推进我国原油期货市场建设的步伐，尽快形成规模，充分发挥其应有的作用。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:28px;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">二要建立健全原油期货市场相关法律体系。在推进原油期货市场建设的同时，尽快出台《期货法》，以立法的形式对参与各方的权责关系、交易规则、违约责任及纠纷解决等做出明确规定。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:28px;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">三要引导多元投资主体共同参与原油期货市场交易。在我国原油期货市场建立初期，建议加强政策推动，采取降低费率等优惠政策，引导国内相关企业将套期保值业务由国外转到我国原油期货市场，吸引金融机构、社会投资者和国外投资者积极参与交易。</span></span></p><p><br/></p>','【记者跑两会】全国人大代表孙焕泉建议加快推进我国原油期货市场建设','       全国人大代表孙焕泉建议，要加快推进我国原油期货市场建设，增强我国对国际原油市场的影响力，降低油价波动带来的风险，保障国家能源安全。','1','1','2017-03-11 16:34:04','','0','','','0','{\"thumb\":\"\"}','0','0','0','0','','');INSERT INTO ts_posts ( `id`, `post_author`, `post_keywords`, `post_source`, `post_date`, `post_content`, `post_title`, `post_excerpt`, `post_status`, `comment_status`, `post_modified`, `post_content_filtered`, `post_parent`, `post_type`, `post_mime_type`, `comment_count`, `smeta`, `post_hits`, `post_like`, `istop`, `recommended`, `page_tpl`, `page_tpls` ) VALUES  ('189','1','中石油有望成首批国企改革试点','','2017-03-11 16:37:40','<p style=\"margin-right:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\">&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">国企改革如火如荼</span>,<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">中石油的改革有望进一步深入。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:28px;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">消息称</span>,<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">中石油将是中国国企改革试点的首批企业之一。改革后</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">,</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">中石油将成为战略控股公司。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:28px;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\">“战略控股就是中石油以后不做垂直管理<span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">,</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">不直接管理各业务单元的经营</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">,</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">而是作为协调者、统筹安排各分支结构的关系。”香颂资本执行董事沈萌告诉《证券日报》记者。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:28px;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">作为我国最大的油气公司</span>,<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">中石油对油气上下游垄断已久</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">,</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">油气改革和国企改革正在逐步深入</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">,</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">以期望在各产业链环节打破这种垄断。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:28px;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">卓创资讯分析师高健向《证券日报》记者表示</span>,<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">应该不断疏通管理通道</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">,</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">简化办事流程</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">,</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">提高管理效率</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">,</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">以后集团会从战略高度给予方向和原则上的指引</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">,</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">让下属子公司拥有更多自主权</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">,</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">中石油集团组织太过庞大</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">,</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">控股公司统管是不现实的</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">,</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">难免会影响效率</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">,</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">滋生各种问题。未来的趋势也是集团内部放权</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">,</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">行业也会逐步放开引入竞争。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:28px;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">在高健看来</span>,<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">中石油是国内最大的油气公司</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">,</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">而石油和天然气领域是国有资本相对集中的领域</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">,</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">也是政府进行混合所有制改革的重点领域</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">,</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">所以中石油作为首批国企改革试点企业也是情理之中。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:28px;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">中石油相关人士向《证券日报》记者表示</span>,<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">公司的改革一直在推进</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">,</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">试点一事应该是由国资委层面来主导</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">,</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">目前还没有收到相关通知。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:28px;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">值得注意的是</span>,<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">中石油董事长王宜林日前表示</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">,</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">公司正考虑将旗下油田服务业务分拆并独立上市。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:28px;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\">“中石油将旗下的油田服务业务分拆上市<span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">,</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">有助于缩减成本、精减增效。”野村控股驻香港亚洲油气研究主管指出</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">,</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">中石油这一次的钻井业务分拆是中国国有企业改革蓝图中的一项内容。面对能源价格的下挫</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">,</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">国有石油公司在进行资产重组的同时也一直在实行缩减成本改革。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:28px;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\">&nbsp;</span></p><p><br/></p>','中石油有望成首批国企改革试点',' 国企改革如火如荼,中石油的改革有望进一步深入。','1','1','2017-03-11 16:36:06','','0','','','0','{\"thumb\":\"\"}','0','0','0','0','','');INSERT INTO ts_posts ( `id`, `post_author`, `post_keywords`, `post_source`, `post_date`, `post_content`, `post_title`, `post_excerpt`, `post_status`, `comment_status`, `post_modified`, `post_content_filtered`, `post_parent`, `post_type`, `post_mime_type`, `comment_count`, `smeta`, `post_hits`, `post_like`, `istop`, `recommended`, `page_tpl`, `page_tpls` ) VALUES  ('190','1','经济体制改革','','2017-03-11 16:39:46','<p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:28px;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\">18<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">日召开的国务院常务会议确定了今年经济体制改革重点工作，包括政府职能转变、财税金融、国有企业、农业农村、对外开放、社会事业等十大领域</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">50</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">项重点改革任务。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:28px;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">今年是全面建成小康社会决胜阶段的开局之年，也是推进结构性改革的攻坚之年。这次会议强调，要突出问题和目标导向，推进结构性改革尤其是供给侧结构性改革，推动有利于创造新供给、释放新需求的体制创新，推出一批具有重大牵引作用的改革举措。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:28px;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\">“当前，我国发展中面临的各种困难和风险，有需求问题和总量问题，但结构性问题更为突出，特别是供给结构不适应需求结构变化。一方面，要强化供给创新，通过补短板，扩大有效供给，增加和激活有效需求，提高供给体系质量和效率；另一方面，找准结构性改革方向，加快破除制约供给创新的体制机制障碍，完善公平竞争、优胜劣汰的市场环境，清除市场壁垒和地方保护，激发企业活力和消费者潜力，为更高质量发展增添新动力。”国家发展改革委主任徐绍史说。</span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:28px;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">会议明确了今年经济体制改革的三大方向：</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:28px;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\">——紧扣促发展，深入推进简政放权、放管结合、优化服务和重点行业等改革，健全有利于去产能、去库存、去杠杆、降成本、补短板的体制机制，围绕深入实施创新驱动发展战略，进一步推动大众创业、万众创新，加快突破束缚生产力发展的重点、难点、堵点，增添持续发展动能；</span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:28px;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\">——聚焦惠民生，在教育、医药卫生、养老、新型城镇化等领域改革上迈出更大步伐，加快就业、社保、扶贫等制度创新，完善基本公共服务投入、收入分配等机制，促进城乡居民增收，增强人民群众获得感；</span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:28px;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\">——围绕防风险，健全监管体制机制，及时发现并努力消除食品安全、环境保护、金融等重点领域风险隐患，坚决守住风险防范底线。各地区各部门要拿出打硬仗的勇气，真抓实干，发挥基层首创精神，鼓励差别化探索，使改革更加精准对接发展所需、群众所盼。</span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:28px;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">中国人民大学校长刘伟表示：</span>“把握住机遇，应对好挑战，我国可以用一些宏观政策调整赢得时间，但更根本的是要全面推进经济体制改革，用我们的制度创新来唤醒民族技术创新活力，在技术创新和制度创新两个车轮的承载下，转变我们的经济发展方式，解决我国经济的深层次结构性矛盾，使得中国经济发展可持续。”</span></p><p><br/></p>','今年经济体制改革明确三大方向','       18日召开的国务院常务会议确定了今年经济体制改革重点工作，包括政府职能转变、财税金融、国有企业、农业农村、对外开放、社会事业等十大领域50项重点改革任务。','1','1','2017-03-11 16:38:21','','0','','','0','{\"thumb\":\"\"}','1','0','0','0','','');INSERT INTO ts_posts ( `id`, `post_author`, `post_keywords`, `post_source`, `post_date`, `post_content`, `post_title`, `post_excerpt`, `post_status`, `comment_status`, `post_modified`, `post_content_filtered`, `post_parent`, `post_type`, `post_mime_type`, `comment_count`, `smeta`, `post_hits`, `post_like`, `istop`, `recommended`, `page_tpl`, `page_tpls` ) VALUES  ('191','1','中海油有限公司去年净利润','','2017-03-11 16:42:45','<p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:28px;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">中国海洋石油有限公司</span>24<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">日公布</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">2015</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年年度业绩。根据公告，</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">2015</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年中海油有限公司实现净利润</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">202.5</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">亿元，同比下降</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">66.4%</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">。每股基本盈利为</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">0.45</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">元。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:28px;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">根据年报，</span>2015<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年中海油有限公司油气净产量为</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">4.957</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">亿桶油当量，同比增长</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">14.6%</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">。受低油价影响，全年储量替代率为</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">67%</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">。截至</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">2015</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年年底，公司净证实储量达</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">43.2</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">亿桶油当量。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:28px;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\">2015<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年，中海油有限公司平均实现油价为</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">51.27</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">美元</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">/</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">桶，同比下降</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">46.6%</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">；平均实现天然气价为</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">6.39</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">美元</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">/</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">千立方英尺，同比下降</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">0.8%</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">。油气销售收入同比下降</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">32.8%</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">，至</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">1466</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">亿元。公司桶油成本同比下降</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">5.9%</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">，为</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">39.82</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">美元</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">/</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">桶油当量，实现连续两年下降。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:28px;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\">2015<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年，中海油有限公司资本支出同比大幅下降近</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">38%</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">，为</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">665</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">亿元。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:28px;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">中海油有限公司是中国海洋石油总公司专注于上游油气勘探生产的上市子公司，是中国最大的海上原油及天然气生产商。</span></span></p><p><br/></p>','中海油有限公司去年净利润下滑66％','       中国海洋石油有限公司24日公布2015年年度业绩。根据公告，2015年中海油有限公司实现净利润202.5亿元，同比下降66.4%。每股基本盈利为0.45元。','1','1','2017-03-11 16:40:22','','0','','','0','{\"thumb\":\"\"}','0','0','0','0','','');INSERT INTO ts_posts ( `id`, `post_author`, `post_keywords`, `post_source`, `post_date`, `post_content`, `post_title`, `post_excerpt`, `post_status`, `comment_status`, `post_modified`, `post_content_filtered`, `post_parent`, `post_type`, `post_mime_type`, `comment_count`, `smeta`, `post_hits`, `post_like`, `istop`, `recommended`, `page_tpl`, `page_tpls` ) VALUES  ('192','1','油品升级进行时','','2017-03-11 16:46:09','<p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:28px;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">我国已成为全球第二大炼油国，但油品质量升级面临不少困难。由于我国炼油装置结构不同于国外，无法借鉴欧美国家技术路线，因此必须开发自主知识产权技术，实现同步降低催化裂化汽油中硫和烯烃含量及保持辛烷值三重目标，以满足油品质量升级需要。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:28px;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">近日，中国石油企业协会、中国油气产业发展研究中心发布的《</span>2016<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">中国油气产业发展分析与展望报告蓝皮书》显示，</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">2015</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年底中国炼油总能力达到</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">5.03</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">亿吨</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">/</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年，成为仅次于美国的全球第二大炼油国。如今，中国油品质量进入快速转型升级的轨道。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:28px;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">由于我国炼油装置结构不同于国外，重油催化裂化占比较大，导致我国车用汽油组分中，催化裂化汽油占比高达</span>74%<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">。催化裂化汽油需要脱硫和降烯烃同时进行才能达到清洁油品标准。此外，催化裂化汽油中的烯烃是汽油辛烷值</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">(</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">汽油标号</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">)</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">的主要贡献者。在常规加氢脱硫过程中，烯烃容易被饱和成烷烃，造成汽油辛烷值损失，导致油品达不到国Ⅳ、国Ⅴ标准。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:28px;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">因此，我国汽油质量升级需要同步实现降低催化裂化汽油中硫和烯烃含量及保持辛烷值三重目标，无法借鉴欧美国家技术路线，必须开发自主知识产权技术。相比之下，升级到同等标准，我国油品升级面临的困难要比国外多很多。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:28px;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">油品质量升级是关系国计民生的大事，国家迫切需要改善油品质量、提供经济高效的汽油质量升级技术。中国石油化工研究院联合中国石油大学等，依托国家</span>973<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">项目、国家自然科学基金项目和中国石油集团重大科技专项，历时</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">12</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年攻关，自主创新开发了脱硫、降烯烃并保持辛烷值催化汽油清洁化成套技术，并依托工程建设公司华东设计分公司和大连设计分公司，在玉门石化、大港石化、乌石化等实现大规模应用，有效满足油品升级的需求。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:28px;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">油品升级，深度脱硫是关键。针对催化汽油硫含量高的特点，研发团队开发了</span>“全馏分催化汽油预加氢—轻重汽油切割—重汽油选择性加氢脱硫—接力脱硫”分段加氢脱硫新工艺，实现了催化汽油不同含硫化合物的高选择性脱除。</span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:28px;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">由于各炼厂催化汽油硫、烯烃含量和辛烷值差异很大，如何满足多元化的需求？研发团队根据不同炼厂催化汽油性质和产品质量要求，将分段脱硫、醚化和烯烃芳构化</span>(<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">辛烷值恢复</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">)</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">技术有机耦合，形成了三种工艺模式，满足了各炼厂汽油质量升级的不同需求。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:28px;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:28px;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\">&nbsp;</span></p><p><br/></p>','油品升级进行时','       我国已成为全球第二大炼油国，但油品质量升级面临不少困难。由于我国炼油装置结构不同于国外，无法借鉴欧美国家技术路线，因此必须开发自主知识产权技术，实现同步降低催化裂化汽油中硫和烯烃含量及保持辛烷值三重目标，以满足油品质量升级需要。','1','1','2017-03-11 16:44:55','','0','','','0','{\"thumb\":\"\"}','1','0','0','0','','');INSERT INTO ts_posts ( `id`, `post_author`, `post_keywords`, `post_source`, `post_date`, `post_content`, `post_title`, `post_excerpt`, `post_status`, `comment_status`, `post_modified`, `post_content_filtered`, `post_parent`, `post_type`, `post_mime_type`, `comment_count`, `smeta`, `post_hits`, `post_like`, `istop`, `recommended`, `page_tpl`, `page_tpls` ) VALUES  ('193','1','石化行业','','2017-03-11 16:54:42','<p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:28px;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">中国石化联合会日前透露，石化行业转型升级三年实施方案</span>(<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">下简称“实施方案”</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">)</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">已经在国家发改委多次讨论并会签，预计最快</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">4</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月正式公布。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:28px;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">石化联合会副会长兼秘书长赵俊贵称，</span>“实施方案”主要由协会操作，衔接政府规划，三年实施方案从<span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">2016</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年起，涵盖</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">2016</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年、</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">2017</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年和</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">2018</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:28px;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">他介绍说，实施方案将以石化联合会名义发布，涵盖石化行业各细分领域，尤其关注化工新兴产业的发展，比如新材料等行业的机会。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:28px;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">石化联合会研究统计数据显示，</span>2015<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年持续的低油价导致煤制油产能利用率下降。</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">2015</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年煤制油平均产能利用率仅</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">16%</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">，煤制气、煤制烯烃、煤制乙二醇等现代煤化工行业开工率虽未见明显下降，但企业效益大幅下滑。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:28px;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">石化联合会产业发展部副主任王孝峰解释说，煤制油平均产能利用率低，主要是因为有些装置刚建成，尚未投产，已经投产的神华煤制油项目也没有全负荷运行，造成产能利用率很低。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:28px;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">石化行业产能过剩情况在各个细分领域都很突出。淘汰落后产能、去产能脚步未停止。中石油经济技术研究院《</span>2015<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年国内外油气行业发展报告》统计，截至</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">2015</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年底，国内炼油总能力为</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">7.1</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">亿吨</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">/</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:28px;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">截至</span>2015<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年底，按照</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">85%</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">的合理开工率计算，国内炼油能力过剩</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">1</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">亿吨</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">/</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年，全国原油加工量约为</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">5.22</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">亿吨，增长</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">3.8%</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">。“十二五”期间，全国炼厂平均开工率不断下降，从</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">2011</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年的</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">81.5%</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">下降至</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">2015</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年的</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">75.4%</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:28px;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">石油和化工行业的落后产能退出加快，新增产能放缓。尿素、烧碱等退出产能都很明显，部分装置推迟投产。另外。石化联合会的《石化行业产能预警报告》提示，化工新材料结构性过剩有扩大的趋势。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:28px;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">针对外界关注的煤化工行业未来的发展前景，是否会重回增长轨道，赵俊贵分析说，现代煤化工总体依然是示范工程，预计</span>“十三五”也会延续这一定位，应该有足够长的时间完善、示范技术，要避免过快、过热发展。</span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:28px;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">赵俊贵表示，炼油和石化行业存在的明显特征是结构性过剩，各个细分领域的产能都出现不同程度的过剩，但是中国依然有</span>40%<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">的化工产品依赖进口。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:28px;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">赵俊贵称，三年实施方案将衔接政府规划，将产业升级转型落到实处。石化联合会在《石油和化学工业</span>“十三五”发展指南》中预计，石化行业“十三五”期间主营业务收入年均增长将达到<span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">7%</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">左右，化工新材料等新兴产业将在结构调整中脱颖而出，行业的创新能力显著提高。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:28px;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">按照石化联合会的统计，国内石化工业在短期内取得了成绩。</span>“十二五”的<span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">2011</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年到</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">2015</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年，石油和化工规模以上企业主营业务收入年均增长</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">9.2%</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">、资产年均增长</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">12.5%</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">、投资年均增长</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">14%</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">、利税年均增</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">3.8%</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">、进出口总额年均增</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">2.8%</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:28px;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\">2015<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年石油和化工行业主营业务收入达到</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">13.14</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">万亿，比</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">2010</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年增长</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">55.2%</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">，税金总额达</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">1.02</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">万亿，占全国工业税收比重的</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">20.7%</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">，位列工业行业之首。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:28px;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">其中国内石油产量、天然气产量和原油加工量分别位居世界第四、第六和第二位，其它主要的大宗化工品产量也居世界前列。但是在</span>2014<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年开始的低油价冲击下，国内石化产业也开始进入增长速度换挡期。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:28px;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">石化联合会判断，我国石化行业面临增速放缓、效益下降、国际油价低位震荡、结构性矛盾凸显等挑战。在此前提下，石化联合会认为，未来石油和化工行业要巩固提升传统产业、培育壮大战略新兴产业，将创新驱动和绿色发展作为新动力和新途径。</span></span></p><p><br/></p>','石化行业“转型三年实施方案”有望4月发布','       中国石化联合会日前透露，石化行业转型升级三年实施方案(下简称“实施方案”)已经在国家发改委多次讨论并会签，预计最快4月正式公布。','1','1','2017-03-11 16:52:36','','0','','','0','{\"thumb\":\"\"}','0','0','0','0','','');INSERT INTO ts_posts ( `id`, `post_author`, `post_keywords`, `post_source`, `post_date`, `post_content`, `post_title`, `post_excerpt`, `post_status`, `comment_status`, `post_modified`, `post_content_filtered`, `post_parent`, `post_type`, `post_mime_type`, `comment_count`, `smeta`, `post_hits`, `post_like`, `istop`, `recommended`, `page_tpl`, `page_tpls` ) VALUES  ('194','1','油价跌后反弹','','2017-03-11 17:00:40','<p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:28px;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">近日，在美国库存下降少于预期、俄罗斯产量下降、多哈会议又被看好等消息作用下，本已经下跌至近</span>35<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">美元的国际油价</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">(WTI)</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">，又反弹并回升至</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">40</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">多美元，几乎是下跌之前的顶点价位。这些消息真有这么大的能量吗？近日油价波动的原因到底是什么？反弹之后会改变下行趋势的形成吗？</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:28px;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">实际上，在</span>2000<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年之后的各种油价因素中，作用油价的主导力量已经被持仓者的态度所左右。</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">2014</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年下半年之后的油价大跌荡，是在美国强化金融监管政策的背景下，投机商在持仓行为方面的调整而引起的，这应是这一历史时期内判断油价演进的主要出发点。近期，由于持仓者将进入空头仓位的调整阶段，油价必将会在此力量的主导下而进入下行阶段。很长时期以来，油价规律性地呈现着一波波有升必有跌的对应形态，其背后的主导力量就是这些持仓者的态度变化。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:28px;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">那么，为什么在持仓者即将调整仓位、油价将被驱使下行之际，油价不跌反而会逆势而上呢？初步判断，这与近日空头仓位太高，再次出现了</span>“逼空”行为有关。期间，其他因素都应是从属性的。</span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:28px;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">一年多以来，油价在理由并不充分的情景下突然窜高已有多次。在</span>2015<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">9</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月初，当油价达到当期高位约</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">50</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">美元后掉头下行时，连续出现了两次在油价下跌至</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">45</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">美元后突然反弹回趋近</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">50</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">美元的情景，这与当下油价在降至近</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">35</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">美元时又反弹至</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">40</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">美元顶点极为相似。在这些时点上的突然反弹，均与当时空头仓位太高，疑似被“逼空”有很大关系。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:28px;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">前几日，空头仓位在刚趋下降后又大增了</span>11%<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">，同期，油价连续上涨了约</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">4</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">美元。一边是空头不愿放手，一边是油价连续反弹，相信这种背离不会太久。在这轮油价下跌力量已基本形成的前提下，下跌的大趋势不会因为这次短暂的“逼空”行为而改变，有所改变的仅是这轮下行拐点被延后而已。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:28px;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">预计，只要不再出现新的意外，近日</span>“逼空”告一段落后，油价将重回下跌。但是，需要时刻警惕的是，由于空头仓位仍在历史高位期，即使在下行之势形成之后，仍不排除途中再现“逼空”情景下的油价短暂性反弹。在下行途中，不时出现短暂的强烈反弹，这是当前空头仓位创下历史高位时期的特有现象。</span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:28px;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\">&nbsp;</span></p><p><br/></p>','油价跌后反弹仅是下行拐点后移','       近日，在美国库存下降少于预期、俄罗斯产量下降、多哈会议又被看好等消息作用下，本已经下跌至近35美元的国际油价(WTI)，又反弹并回升至40多美元，几乎是下跌之前的顶点价位。这些消息真有这么大的能量吗？近日油价波动的原因到底是什么？反弹之后会改变下行趋势的形成吗？','1','1','2017-03-11 17:00:09','','0','','','0','{\"thumb\":\"\"}','1','0','0','0','','');INSERT INTO ts_posts ( `id`, `post_author`, `post_keywords`, `post_source`, `post_date`, `post_content`, `post_title`, `post_excerpt`, `post_status`, `comment_status`, `post_modified`, `post_content_filtered`, `post_parent`, `post_type`, `post_mime_type`, `comment_count`, `smeta`, `post_hits`, `post_like`, `istop`, `recommended`, `page_tpl`, `page_tpls` ) VALUES  ('195','1','20省份公布十三五能源规划','','2017-03-11 17:05:17','<p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　日前，《国民经济和社会发展第十三个五年规划纲要》出台，在此前后，已有多个省份出台了地方</span>“十三五”规划。截至记者统稿，已有北京、上海、山西、陕西、四川、浙江、江苏、天津等<span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">20</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">个省份公布“十三五”规划全文。地方发展形势不同，能源规划的侧重点也有所不同。记者梳理了</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">20</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">个省份的能源脉络，为您呈现不同地区“十三五”期间的能源发展格局。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　非化石能源比例提升任重道远</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　地方</span>“十三五”规划虽然较宏观，但普遍都对能源未来五年发展作出约束性或预期性规划。建设清洁低碳、安全高效的现代能源体系是一致的目标。清洁化成为普遍追求的方向。</span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　在能源结构方面，非化石能源占一次能源消费比重和可再生能源占电力总装机比例是多数省份都提及的两个发展指标。其中，前者是约束性的、必须实现的指标。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　为应对气候变化，实现我国自主贡献，我国向国际社会庄严承诺，到</span>2020<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年非化石能源占一次能源消费比重将达到</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">15%</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">。国家层面的“十三五”规划重申了这一目标。五年需累计增长</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">3%</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　从各省情况看，北京、甘肃等省的预期较为乐观。到</span>2020<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年，北京将建成以电力和天然气为主体、地热能和太阳能等为补充的清洁能源体系，优质能源消费比重力争提至</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">90%</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">以上，其中可再生能源比重将达</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">8%</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">。甘肃目前非化石能源占比为</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">19.1%</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">，未来五年将继续完成国家分解任务。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　江苏、江西、宁夏等省份</span>2020<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年非化石能源占比目标略低于</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">15%</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">。江苏当前比例为</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">8.5%</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">左右，</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">2020</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年将达到</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">10%</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">左右。宁夏到</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">2020</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年也将达到</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">10%</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">。而江西提出到</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">2020</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年非化石能源消费占比将提至</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">11%</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">。同时，我们看到，辽宁、山东等省预期目标与</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">15%</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">相距更远。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　另外，青海、山西、上海等地虽未明确规划</span>2020<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年非化石能源比例，但在追求能源清洁化方面也提出了相应规划。青海明确要提高绿色能源在用能结构中的比重。山西提出到</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">2020</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年煤炭占一次能源比重下降至</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">73%</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">。上海则明确增加天然气供给能力，到</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">2020</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年，天然气占一次能源消费比重提高到</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">12%</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　由此可以看出，我国提升清洁能源消费比例任重道远。但随着我国发展动能转换，能源需求增速放缓，结构调整获得了难得的良机，调整将呈现加速趋势。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　电力装机清洁化比例持续提升</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　电力装机是观察能源结构的另一个维度。而各地</span>“十三五”规划在这一方面有更细致的描绘。</span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　未来五年，各省电力装机总量仍将呈增长态势，装机结构清洁化看点多多。同时，较发达地区外受电比例将进一步提升。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　北京制定了雄心勃勃的装机清洁化蓝图。</span>2020<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年，北京将建成以四大热电中心为主、区域能源中心为辅、新能源和可再生能源电站为补充的多元本地电源支撑体系，清洁能源发电装机比重将达</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">100%</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　福建提出到</span>2020<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年，力争全省电力装机达到</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">7000</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">万千瓦。记者了解到，</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">2013</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年该省电力总装机为</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">4201</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">万千瓦。同时，该省提出力争</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">2020</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年风电装机规模比</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">2015</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年翻一番，加快建设宁德、福清、漳州、霞浦等沿海核电站。可以预见，未来风电、核电在福建电力装机结构中的比重将会显著增加。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　江浙地区等经济大省重点建设本地清洁能源体系。江苏提出到</span>2020<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年电力装机将达到</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">1.3</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">亿千瓦，其中风电、光伏各形成</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">800~1000</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">万千瓦装机，生物质能源装机将达到</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">150</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">万千瓦。浙江提出到</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">2020</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年光伏发电达到</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">800</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">万千瓦，基本与江苏相当，风电力争达到</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">300</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">万千瓦以上，核电将达到</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">900</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">万千瓦。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　甘肃、山西、内蒙古等能源大省将继续扩大电源规模，侧重发展清洁能源，并提高外送电能力。甘肃提出到</span>2020<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年，全省电力装机达到</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">7500</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">万千瓦，其中可再生能源装机占比将达到</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">60%</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">，电力外送规模达到</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">600</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">亿千瓦时</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">/</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年。内蒙古提出到</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">2020</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年火电装机将达到</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">1.4</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">亿千瓦，新能源装机将达到</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">8000</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">万千瓦，占总装机的</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">36%</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">。对于新能源发电的消纳，内蒙古提出将通过</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">4</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">条电力通道外送</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">3300</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">万千瓦，自治区内消纳</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">4700</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">万千瓦。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　东部地区多省提出增加外购电比重。北京提出，</span>2020<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年外受电能力将达到</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">3200</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">万千瓦。山东届时接纳省外来电能力将达到</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">2400</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">万千瓦。天津外购电比例将达到</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">1/3</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">以上。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　普遍设定能源消耗</span>“天花板”</span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　在提升能源结构清洁的同时，各地</span>“十三五”规划也显示出对于能源消费总量进行科学管理的特征。</span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　记者梳理发现，</span>20<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">个省份都在规划中提及控制能源消费总量。多数省份提出能源消费总量控制在国家下达的指标以内。以全国为参照，“十三五”规划提出全国能源消费总量控制在</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">50</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">亿吨标准煤以内，而</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">2015</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年这一数字约为</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">43</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">亿吨标准煤，预期增长幅度约为</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">16%</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　但各省份情况不同，控制目标也有很大差别。除了提出以国家下达的指标为准的省份以外，很多省份还提出了独立的控制目标。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　最典型的是上海和广西。上海提出，到</span>2020<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年能耗总量控制在</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">1.25</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">亿吨标准煤以下。而</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">2014</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年该市耗能约为</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">1.1</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">亿吨标准煤，未来五年增长幅度略高于</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">13%</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">，明显低于全国能耗涨幅预期。广西提出</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">2020</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年能耗总量控制在</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">1.3</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">亿吨标准煤左右。</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">2014</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年广西能耗总量为</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">0.95</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">亿吨标准煤，依此目标计算，未来五年累计涨幅将达</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">37%</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">，远高于全国预期涨幅。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　值得注意的是，在控制能耗总量增幅的同时，很多省份还提出煤炭消费的减量计划。在这一增一减中，能源结构的清洁化又向前迈进一步。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　北京提出未来五年将大幅压减电厂、工业、采暖、民用燃煤总量，</span>2020<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年煤炭消费总量控制在</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">900</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">万吨以内。江苏则将煤炭消费总量控制与能耗强度、能耗总量一道纳入“三控”制度，力争到</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">2017</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年煤炭消费实现负增长。陕西提出</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">2020</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年关中地区再削减燃煤</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">600</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">万吨以上。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　同时，能源生产大省也相应提出煤炭产量的控制目标，山东提出</span>2020<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年，省内煤炭产量控制在</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">1</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">亿吨左右，并且实现</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">2017</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年煤炭消费量比</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">2012</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年削减</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">2000</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">万吨，</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">2020</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年继续实现下降。山西提出到</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">2020</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年原煤产量控制在</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">10</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">亿吨以内，同时优化提升现代载能产业，实现能源就地消纳增值。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\">&nbsp;</span></p><p><br/></p>','20省份公布十三五能源规划','　　日前，《国民经济和社会发展第十三个五年规划纲要》出台，在此前后，已有多个省份出台了地方“十三五”规划。截至记者统稿，已有北京、上海、山西、陕西、四川、浙江、江苏、天津等20个省份公布“十三五”规划全文。地方发展形势不同，能源规划的侧重点也有所不同。记者梳理了20个省份的能源脉络，为您呈现不同地区“十三五”期间的能源发展格局。','1','1','2017-03-11 17:03:22','','0','','','0','{\"thumb\":\"\"}','1','0','0','0','','');INSERT INTO ts_posts ( `id`, `post_author`, `post_keywords`, `post_source`, `post_date`, `post_content`, `post_title`, `post_excerpt`, `post_status`, `comment_status`, `post_modified`, `post_content_filtered`, `post_parent`, `post_type`, `post_mime_type`, `comment_count`, `smeta`, `post_hits`, `post_like`, `istop`, `recommended`, `page_tpl`, `page_tpls` ) VALUES  ('196','1','国际油价19日上涨','','2017-03-11 17:08:21','<p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　美元</span>19<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">日下跌，美元走弱增加了以美元计价的石油的投资吸引力，国际油价当日收盘走高。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　科威特石油工人罢工的消息继续对油价起到支撑。作为欧佩克第四大产油国，</span>17<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">日起举行的罢工令科威特的日均石油产量减少</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">60%</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">至</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">110</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">万桶。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　分析人士指出，短期而言，科威特石油减产对油价的利好盖过了多哈会议的负面影响。来自</span>23<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">个石油生产国的官员</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">17</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">日在卡塔尔首都多哈举行会议，就冻结石油产量进行磋商，但会议最终未能就冻产达成协议。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　截至当日收盘时，纽约商品交易所</span>5<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月交货的轻质原油期货价格上涨</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">1.3</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">美元，收于每桶</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">41.08</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">美元，涨幅为</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">3.27%</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">。</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">6</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月交货的伦敦布伦特原油期货价格上涨</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">1.12</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">美元，收于每桶</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">44.03</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">美元，涨幅为</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">2.61%</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;</span></p><p><br/></p>','国际油价19日上涨','　　美元19日下跌，美元走弱增加了以美元计价的石油的投资吸引力，国际油价当日收盘走高。','1','1','2017-03-11 17:06:50','','0','','','0','{\"thumb\":\"\"}','1','0','0','0','','');INSERT INTO ts_posts ( `id`, `post_author`, `post_keywords`, `post_source`, `post_date`, `post_content`, `post_title`, `post_excerpt`, `post_status`, `comment_status`, `post_modified`, `post_content_filtered`, `post_parent`, `post_type`, `post_mime_type`, `comment_count`, `smeta`, `post_hits`, `post_like`, `istop`, `recommended`, `page_tpl`, `page_tpls` ) VALUES  ('197','1','国际油价','','2017-03-11 17:09:22','<p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　受产油国多哈会议未能达成冻结产量协议影响，国际油价</span>18<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">日开盘后大幅下跌，但随后科威特石油工人罢工的消息令油价从低位逐渐走高，收盘的跌幅有限。一些市场人士指出，尽管产油国未能达成冻产协议，但低油价带来的原油市场供需平衡已在进行中。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　花旗集团大宗商品研究主管埃德</span>·莫尔斯说，罢工导致的减产对市场的支撑是当日油价收复失地的主要原因，这远远强于多哈会议预期达成的效果。</span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　资深交易员、石油经纪公司派拉蒙期权总裁雷蒙德</span>·卡本指出，大多数交易员上周就认为多哈会议不会取得实质性成果。纽约油价<span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">17</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">日早盘大幅低开于</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">37.6</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">美元附近，从技术上看，这是油价的一个重要支撑位。此后油价逐步走高，这令市场人士认为油价不会跌到更低的水平，低开成为买点，买盘助油价收复失地。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　他认为，油价已经走过低谷，不太可能再跌到每桶</span>30<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">美元以下，他预计今年纽约油价会在每桶</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">35</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">美元到</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">55</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">美元之间波动。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　近期的数据显示，低油价正令原油厂商减产，市场供需平衡正在进行中。美国能源信息局</span>13<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">日公布的数据显示，此前的一周美国日均原油产量继续下降，减少</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">3.1</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">万桶至</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">897.7</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">万桶，跌破</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">900</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">万桶大关。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　美国能源信息局</span>4<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月份的报告预计，今明两年美国的日均原油产量分别为</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">860</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">万桶和</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">800</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">万桶，这两个预期值较上个月的报告均下调了</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">10</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">万桶。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　加拿大皇家银行大宗商品首席策略师克罗夫特指出，低油价已令不少高成本的产油商退出市场，油价预计会在今年四季度上涨到每桶</span>50<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">美元左右。如果原油厂商减产的速度加快，那么油价达到</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">50</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">美元的时间可能会提前。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\">&nbsp;</span></p><p><br/></p>','国际油价今年有望涨到每桶50美元','　　受产油国多哈会议未能达成冻结产量协议影响，国际油价18日开盘后大幅下跌，但随后科威特石油工人罢工的消息令油价从低位逐渐走高，收盘的跌幅有限。一些市场人士指出，尽管产油国未能达成冻产协议，但低油价带来的原油市场供需平衡已在进行中。','1','1','2017-03-11 17:08:37','','0','','','0','{\"thumb\":\"\"}','0','0','0','0','','');INSERT INTO ts_posts ( `id`, `post_author`, `post_keywords`, `post_source`, `post_date`, `post_content`, `post_title`, `post_excerpt`, `post_status`, `comment_status`, `post_modified`, `post_content_filtered`, `post_parent`, `post_type`, `post_mime_type`, `comment_count`, `smeta`, `post_hits`, `post_like`, `istop`, `recommended`, `page_tpl`, `page_tpls` ) VALUES  ('198','1','长江经济带规划纲','','2017-03-11 17:12:10','<p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　从发改系统获悉，已获通过的《长江经济带发展规划纲要》出台在即。相对</span>2014<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年出台的《关于依托黄金水道推动长江经济带发展的指导意见》，《纲要》最大的变化是，重新定调保护长江生态，共抓大保护，不搞大开发。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　据</span>21<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">世纪经济报道</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">4</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">19</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">日报道，长江沿线一直是我国传统石化产业聚集区，沿线化工产量约占全国的</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">46%</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">，其污染威胁一直饱受诟病。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　《纲要》出台前夕，地方闻风而动，纷纷</span>“亮剑”，长江沿线省份化工企业进入密集关停期，化工产业或面临重新洗牌。</span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\">　　4<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月中旬，从湖北某省级部门获悉，位于湖北省荆州市石首市的楚源高新科技集团股份有限公司</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">(</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">以下简称“楚源集团”</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">)</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">，被“重点停工整顿”，目前进一步的处理还在进行中。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　根据楚源集团网站介绍，该公司是国家重点高新技术企业，湖北省百强企业，年销售</span>30<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">多亿元，占地面积</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">1600</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">亩，总资产</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">20</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">多亿元，员工</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">4000</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">余人。主要生产经营染料中间体及活性染料、有机化工原料、生物医药和化工机械包装，产品涵盖了生产染料</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">80%</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">的中间体。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　今年</span>2<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月底，湖北省环保厅发文称，其配合华南环境保护督查中心对楚源集团进行了现场检查，并将存在的环境问题及监察意见向荆州市环保局下达监察通知。此次楚源集团被“重点停工整顿”，目前尚在处理中，结果暂未对外公开。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\">　　“省领导下决定整顿，这次动真格，排除各种阻力。”上述湖北某省级部门负责人介绍说，此次处理力度不小。</span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　从楚源集团内部求证获悉，近期楚源一直处于停工整顿状态，不清楚什么时候复产，有污染相关责任人被带走。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　湖北一位官员还透露，湖北另一家涉及百亿投资的制造业项目，因涉及环保问题，也全面停工，开工时间尚未明确。</span></span></p><p><br/></p>','长江经济带规划纲要出台在即 沿线化工企业密集关停','　　从发改系统获悉，已获通过的《长江经济带发展规划纲要》出台在即。相对2014年出台的《关于依托黄金水道推动长江经济带发展的指导意见》，《纲要》最大的变化是，重新定调保护长江生态，共抓大保护，不搞大开发。','1','1','2017-03-11 17:10:45','','0','','','0','{\"thumb\":\"\"}','1','0','0','0','','');INSERT INTO ts_posts ( `id`, `post_author`, `post_keywords`, `post_source`, `post_date`, `post_content`, `post_title`, `post_excerpt`, `post_status`, `comment_status`, `post_modified`, `post_content_filtered`, `post_parent`, `post_type`, `post_mime_type`, `comment_count`, `smeta`, `post_hits`, `post_like`, `istop`, `recommended`, `page_tpl`, `page_tpls` ) VALUES  ('199','1','国内油价今迎调价窗口','','2017-03-11 17:20:44','<p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\">　　4<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">26</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">日，国内成品油调价窗口将再次开启。有监测机构称，由于国际原油均价突破</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">40</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">美元，国内油价或结束“六连停”，迎来今年首次上调，预计</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">90</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">号汽油每升上涨</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">0.14</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">元。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">是否调价？</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\">——监测机构：国际油价突破<span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">40</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">美元 国内油价或上调</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　能源资讯服务商安迅思分析师杨丹在接受中新网记者采访时称，</span>4<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">26</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">日，国内汽柴油零售价涨幅预计在</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">190</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">元</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">/</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">吨，测算到零售价格</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">90</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">号汽油和</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">0</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">号柴油</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">(</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">全国平均</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">)</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">每升分别上涨</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">0.14</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">元和</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">0.16</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">元。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　另据隆众石化网监测，预计本次汽柴油上调</span>160-180<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">元</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">/</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">吨，折合每升</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">0.12-0.15</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">元。不过，隆众石化网成品油分析师李彦指出，这一数值只是监测机构根据原油综合变化率等测算的结果，具体调价幅度还要看发改委通知。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\">&nbsp;&nbsp;<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　上述机构预测油价上调的原因何在？这需要了解一下我国最新的成品油定价机制与近期国际油价走势。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　据发改委今年</span>1<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">13</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">日发布的新规，国际油价低于每桶</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">40</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">美元时，国内汽柴油最高零售价“不再下调”；国际油价高于每桶</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">130</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">美元时，国内汽柴油最高零售价“不提或少提”；中间区间，则该降就降，该升就升。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　在为成品油价格调整设置</span>“地板价”之后，除了<span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">1</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">13</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">日当天油价略有下调，我国成品油价格已连续六个周期没有调整。根据“调价间隔</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">10</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">个工作日”的原则，</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">4</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">26</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">日</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">24</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">时是新一轮调价窗口。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　近期国际油价的上涨为</span>“上调油价”的预测提供了依据。李彦指出，<span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">4</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">22</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">日是本轮调价的第</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">9</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">个工作日，国际原油现货均价为</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">41.58</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">美元</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">/</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">桶，稳居</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">40</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">美元之上。也就是说，调价窗口有望打开。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　隆众石化网成品油分析师薛群则认为，我国成品油定价机制没有明确指出挂靠的国际油种和采取的计算公式，所以虽然部分原油价格突破了</span>40<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">美元，但仍不能完全断定成品油价一定会上调。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">有何影响？</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\">——若涨价 普通汽车加满一箱油或多花<span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">9</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">元</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　首先，消费者方面，如果油价上调，私家车车主的出行成本将有所增加。根据安迅思的测算，普通家用轿车使用的</span>93<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">号汽油折合每升上涨</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">0.15</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">元（略高于</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">90</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">号汽油），以一辆油箱为</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">60L</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">的普通汽车为例，加满一箱油，车主需要多支付</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">9</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">元的燃油成本。</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14px; line-height: 150%;\">&nbsp;</span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　杨丹认为，对于刚性需求的消费者而言，</span>0.15<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">元</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">/</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">升的价格涨幅不会对消费习惯有太大影响。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\">　　“油价上调的主要影响是会给消费者带来一种心理担忧”，杨丹说，“由于美国减少石油钻井数量且国际原油需求较为稳定，国际油价走势向好，如果国内成品油本次上调价格的话，消费者会担心这预示着下一次、甚至于未来油价的持续上涨。”</span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　其次，油价上调后加油站利润会有所增加。李彦解释说，加油站的批发价</span>(<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">进价</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">)</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">通常会提前上涨，等发改委公布上调消息后，一般而言批发价就不再上涨，所以零售价的提高意味着加油站利润空间的增大。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\">　　“加油站利润整体处在高位，所以小幅的利润变化其实意义不大”，李彦说，“<span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">2016</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年以来，中石油等国营加油站的平均利润在</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">800-1000</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">元</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">/</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">吨。”</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　值得注意的是，发改委公布的是成品油最高零售价，只要不超过这一</span>“天花板”，加油站就可以自主定价。与国营加油站相比，一些民营加油站的油价相对较低。<span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">4</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">23</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">日，记者咨询北京丰台区西道口某民营加油站的油价，</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">92</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">号汽油为</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">5.26</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">元</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">/</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">升，比中石油中石化便宜</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">0.30</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">元。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\">　　“如果发改委上调成品油最高零售价，加油站也会迅速调整挂牌价，但由于现在竞争比以前激烈，加油站可能在一段时间后自行降价，并推出一些优惠活动”，李彦说。</span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　另外，针对</span>“上调油价是否会造成物流交通成本上升、进而推高物价”的担忧，李彦称，本次上调幅度应该不大，所以这种影响可以忽略。</span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　他同时强调，目前国际原油价格的反弹趋势并不稳固，供需面仍无实质性好转，后市油价仍存跌破</span>40<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">美元的风险，所以“地板价”不会马上消失，未来仍可能会再度发挥威力。</span></span></p><p><br/></p>','国内油价今迎调价窗口 或年内首涨结束“六连停”','　　4月26日，国内成品油调价窗口将再次开启。有监测机构称，由于国际原油均价突破40美元，国内油价或结束“六连停”，迎来今年首次上调，预计90号汽油每升上涨0.14元。INSERT INTO ts_posts ( `id`, `post_author`, `post_keywords`, `post_source`, `post_date`, `post_content`, `post_title`, `post_excerpt`, `post_status`, `comment_status`, `post_modified`, `post_content_filtered`, `post_parent`, `post_type`, `post_mime_type`, `comment_count`, `smeta`, `post_hits`, `post_like`, `istop`, `recommended`, `page_tpl`, `page_tpls` ) VALUES  ('200','1','油价升至五个月来高点','','2017-03-11 17:24:55','<p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　纽约原油价格</span>26<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">日收于五个多月最高水平，有迹象显示全球供应过剩正在逐步缓解，随着美联储加息预期降温，油价正处于企稳态势。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　纽约商业交易所</span>6<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月交割德克萨斯轻质原油</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">(WTI)</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">期货上涨</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">1.40</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">美元，收盘于</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">44.04</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">美元</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">/</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">桶，上涨</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">3.3%</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">，这是自</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">2015</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">11</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">10</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">日以来最高收盘价。伦敦期货交易所</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">6</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月交割布伦特原油期货上涨</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">1.26</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">美元，涨幅</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">2.8%</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">，至</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">45.74</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">美元</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">/</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">桶。英国石油公司执行官杜德利</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">2</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月曾开玩笑说，需要动用游泳池来贮放全球过剩的原油，但他本月</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">26</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">日表示，市场到年底可能重新平衡。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　路透社文章说，尽管未能达成全球冻产协议，但布伦特原油</span>66%<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">的涨幅似乎已能保持住，越来越多迹象显示，绵延了</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">18</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">个月之久的油价跌势，光靠自身力量就已经令生产停歇且供给减少。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　美国能源信息局当地时间</span>27<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">日将发布美国库存报告，接受彭博调查的分析师预计上周美国原油库存增加</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">175</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">万桶。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　油价的企稳还与美联储货币政策预期息息相关。市场认为美联储会本周加息可能性为零，</span>6<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月加息可能性也只有</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">20%</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　国际油价自</span>2014<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">6</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月的每桶</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">100</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">多美元，一路下滑至目前的每桶</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">40</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">美元左右，跌幅超过</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">60%</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">。其中美联储去年</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">12</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月进行</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">10</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年来的首次加息之后，市场便担忧美国利率上升和美元升值，也加剧了油价跌势。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　至于黄金价格，随着避险情绪下降，今年第一季度表现最好的金属品种走势已现强弩之末。经过涨涨跌跌，金价本月几乎持平。纽约市场金价</span>26<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">日盘中在每盎司</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">1242</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">美元徘徊。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　作为今年来率先发动上涨攻势的大宗产品，国际金价从</span>2015<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">12</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月的低点到</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">3</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月的高点累计反弹超过</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">20%</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">，但</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">3</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月中旬以来，黄金市场再度陷入“涨不上去、跌不下来”的震荡格局。</span></span></p><p><br/></p>','油价升至五个月来高点 走势料已企稳','　　纽约原油价格26日收于五个多月最高水平，有迹象显示全球供应过剩正在逐步缓解，随着美联储加息预期降温，油价正处于企稳态势。','1','1','2017-03-11 17:24:25','','0','','','0','{\"thumb\":\"\"}','1','0','0','0','','');INSERT INTO ts_posts ( `id`, `post_author`, `post_keywords`, `post_source`, `post_date`, `post_content`, `post_title`, `post_excerpt`, `post_status`, `comment_status`, `post_modified`, `post_content_filtered`, `post_parent`, `post_type`, `post_mime_type`, `comment_count`, `smeta`, `post_hits`, `post_like`, `istop`, `recommended`, `page_tpl`, `page_tpls` ) VALUES  ('201','1','《标本兼治遏制重特大事故工作指南》','','2017-03-11 17:26:30','<p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\">　　5<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">3</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">日，记者从国家安全监管总局获悉，为认真贯彻落实党中央、国务院决策部署，坚决遏制重特大事故频发势头，国务院安委会办公室制定了《标本兼治遏制重特大事故工作指南》</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">(</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">以下简称《指南》</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">)</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">，并于近日下发通知就贯彻落实提出要求。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　通知指出，要进一步提高对防范遏制重特大事故重要性、紧迫性和事故规律性的认识，把遏制重特大事故工作作为安全生产</span>“牛鼻子”工程，摆在重中之重的突出位置，采取有力措施抓实抓好，带动安全生产各项工作全面推进。</span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　通知强调，要结合事故规律特点，抓住关键时段、关键地区、关键单位、关键环节，从构建双重预防性工作机制、强化技术保障、加大监管执法力度、推进保护生命重点工程建设、加强源头治理、提高应急处置能力等方面入手，从制度、技术、工程、管理等多个角度，制定采取有针对性的措施，对症下药、精准施策，力争尽快在减少重特大事故数量、频次和减轻危害后果上见到实效。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　《指南》提出，要着力构建安全风险分级管控和隐患排查治理双重预防性工作机制。根据存在的主要风险隐患可能导致的后果并结合本地区、本行业领域实际，研究制定区域性、行业性安全风险和事故隐患辨识、评估、分级标准，为开展安全风险分级管控和事故隐患排查治理提供依据。按照</span>“分区域、分级别、网格化”原则，实施安全风险差异化动态管理，明确落实每一处重大安全风险和重大危险源的安全管理与监管责任，强化风险管控技术、制度、管理措施，把可能导致的后果限制在可防、可控范围之内。</span></p><p><br/></p>','国务院安委办印发《标本兼治遏制重特大事故工作指南》','　　5月3日，记者从国家安全监管总局获悉，为认真贯彻落实党中央、国务院决策部署，坚决遏制重特大事故频发势头，国务院安委会办公室制定了《标本兼治遏制重特大事故工作指南》(以下简称《指南》)，并于近日下发通知就贯彻落实提出要求。','1','1','2017-03-11 17:25:50','','0','','','0','{\"thumb\":\"\"}','0','0','0','0','','');INSERT INTO ts_posts ( `id`, `post_author`, `post_keywords`, `post_source`, `post_date`, `post_content`, `post_title`, `post_excerpt`, `post_status`, `comment_status`, `post_modified`, `post_content_filtered`, `post_parent`, `post_type`, `post_mime_type`, `comment_count`, `smeta`, `post_hits`, `post_like`, `istop`, `recommended`, `page_tpl`, `page_tpls` ) VALUES  ('202','1','强化安全生产','','2017-03-11 17:27:47','<p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　据国家安监总局网站</span>4<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">日消息，安监总局近日下发通知，要求进一步加强生产经营单位安全生产不良记录“黑名单”制度管理，切实发挥“黑名单”制度在强化社会监督和有效防范遏制重特大事故等方面的作用。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　通知指出，</span>“黑名单”制度目的在于深化行政审批制度改革、强化事中事后监管，推进社会诚信体系建设；建立健全跨部门失信联合惩戒机制，形成“一处失信、处处受限”，督促生产经营单位诚信守法、落实安全生产主体责任，有效遏制重特大事故发生。</span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　各地要提高对</span>“黑名单”制度重要性的认识，进一步增强责任意识，进一步增强运用“黑名单”制度的意识，切实抓好这项制度的贯彻执行，积极发挥这项制度的作用。</span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　通知要求，要明确各单位主要负责人是</span>“黑名单”信息报送的第一责任人，建立生产经营单位安全生产失信行为信息采集、报送、发布和管理的制度化、规范化、常态化机制，在日常工作中及时全面采集发现的生产经营单位安全生产失信行为信息，及时向“黑名单”发布部门提供和更新信息，确保“黑名单”信息全面及时准确发布；要注重结合隐患排查治理、安全生产举报等制度，推动曝光一批重大安全隐患、惩治一批典型违法行为、通报一批“黑名单”企业、取缔一批非法违法企业、关闭一批不符合安全生产条件的企业。</span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　通知强调，加大对纳入</span>“黑名单”管理的生产经营单位的监管力度，要将纳入“黑名单”管理的生产经营单位作为重点监管监察对象，加大对纳入“黑名单”管理的生产经营单位的执法检查频次，确保每半年至少进行<span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">1</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">次检查，每年至少约谈</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">1</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">次其主要负责人；发现有新的安全生产违法行为的，要依法依规从重处罚。</span></span></p><p><br/></p>','安监总局要求强化安全生产“黑名单”制度','　　据国家安监总局网站4日消息，安监总局近日下发通知，要求进一步加强生产经营单位安全生产不良记录“黑名单”制度管理，切实发挥“黑名单”制度在强化社会监督和有效防范遏制重特大事故等方面的作用。','1','1','2017-03-11 17:26:56','','0','','','0','{\"thumb\":\"\"}','0','0','0','0','','');INSERT INTO ts_posts ( `id`, `post_author`, `post_keywords`, `post_source`, `post_date`, `post_content`, `post_title`, `post_excerpt`, `post_status`, `comment_status`, `post_modified`, `post_content_filtered`, `post_parent`, `post_type`, `post_mime_type`, `comment_count`, `smeta`, `post_hits`, `post_like`, `istop`, `recommended`, `page_tpl`, `page_tpls` ) VALUES  ('203','1','全国成品油价格指数平稳运行','','2017-03-11 17:28:38','<p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　依据新华</span>(<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">大庆</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">)</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">国际石油资讯中心发布的报告，截至</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">5</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">4</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">日，全国成品油价格指数为</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">583.75</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">，跌幅</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">0.04%</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">，全国成品油价格指数平稳运行。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　全国成品油价格指数运行结果表明，上周</span>93#<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">汽油平均价格报收于</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">5872</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">元</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">/</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">吨，较前一报告周期上涨</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">1</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">元</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">/</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">吨</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">(</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">与前一报告期基本持平</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">)</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">；</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">0#</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">柴油平均价格报收于</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">4910</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">元</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">/</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">吨，较前一报告周期下跌</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">3</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">元</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">/</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">吨</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">(</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">与前一报告期基本持平</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">)</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">。综合来看，全国汽柴油平均价格起伏不大，全国成品油价格指数平稳运行。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　新华</span>(<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">大庆</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">)</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">国际石油资讯中心分析师蒋冰认为，因石油输出国组织</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">(</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">欧佩克</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">)</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">增加原油产量，国际油价持续走低。国内成品油市场业者观望心态加深，多消化前期库存，交投清淡。河北省石家庄市某加油站负责人表示：“原油市场接连三个工作日下行，市场观望心态加深。虽新的计价周期成品油调价窗口依然处于上调预期，但是下游刚需一般，多数上月末已经备货完毕，目前正处于消化库存期间。华北主营汽柴油价格稳定为主，零星波动。预计短期内主营汽柴油价格稳定为主，小幅波动。”</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　蒋冰分析认为，美国石油学会</span>(API)<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">近日公布数据显示，截至</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">4</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">29</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">日当周，美国原油库存增加</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">126.5</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">万桶，至</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">5.397</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">亿桶，低于预期，该消息利好国际油价。观望后市，美国石油库存和欧佩克产量持续攀升对油价上涨形成抑制作用，预计短期内国际油价将维持震荡走势。</span></span></p><p><br/></p>','全国成品油价格指数平稳运行','　　依据新华(大庆)国际石油资讯中心发布的报告，截至5月4日，全国成品油价格指数为583.75，跌幅0.04%，全国成品油价格指数平稳运行。','1','1','2017-03-11 17:27:58','','0','','','0','{\"thumb\":\"\"}','0','0','0','0','','');INSERT INTO ts_posts ( `id`, `post_author`, `post_keywords`, `post_source`, `post_date`, `post_content`, `post_title`, `post_excerpt`, `post_status`, `comment_status`, `post_modified`, `post_content_filtered`, `post_parent`, `post_type`, `post_mime_type`, `comment_count`, `smeta`, `post_hits`, `post_like`, `istop`, `recommended`, `page_tpl`, `page_tpls` ) VALUES  ('204','1','原油市场回暖 ','','2017-03-11 17:29:55','<p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　自</span>4<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月多哈冻产协议未能达成后，据石油输出国组织</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">(OPEC)</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">两名代表称，在将于</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">6</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月举行的</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">OPEC</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">会议上，并不包含恢复原油产量限制的计划。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　彭博社援引两名</span>OPEC<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">代表称，</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">OPEC</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">成员国代表周三</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">(5</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">4</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">日</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">)</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">在维也纳举行会议，讨论了原油供应和需求基本面的改善情况。由于原油市场价格有所好转，冻产计划或将不再必要。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\">　　2016<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年早些时候，原油价格一再下滑，至</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">2003</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年以来最低水平，直至美国产量下降令全球供应过剩的局面有所缓解。尽管由于沙特坚持要求伊朗加入，</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">4</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">OPEC</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">成员国和非</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">OPEC</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">产油国的冻产协议最终未能达成，油价依然有所复苏。虽然这在一定程度上缓解了产油国的压力，但</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">OPEC</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">成员国仍未就长期战略达成一致。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\">　　OPEC<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">理事会在周一</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">(5</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">2</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">日</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">)</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">举行的会议中，就</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">OPEC</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">长期战略</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">(LTS)</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">的最新草案展开讨论。尽管在一些问题上取得进展，然而由于沙特不同意伊朗提出的对原油市场进行“有效的产量管理”的措辞，长期战略未能达成。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　截至周三</span>(5<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">4</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">日</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">)</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">收盘，</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">WTI6</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月原油期货收涨</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">0.13</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">美元，涨幅</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">0.3%</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">，报每桶</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">43.78</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">美元，结束之前连跌三日的颓势。布伦特</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">6</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月原油期货收跌</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">0.35</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">美元，跌幅</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">0.78%</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">，报每桶</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">44.62</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">美元。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\">　　4<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月，国际能源机构</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">(IEA)</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">表示，由于较低油价将在一定程度上影响非</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">OPEC</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">产油国产量，全球供需将在</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">2016</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年下半年接近平衡。美国能源信息署</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">(EIA)</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">数据显示，美国原油产量上周下降至日均</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">883</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">万桶，已连续第八周下降，且上周</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">(4.25-29)</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">降幅创下</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">2015</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">7</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月以来最大。</span></span></p><p><br/></p>','原油市场回暖 冻产计划或将不再必要','　　自4月多哈冻产协议未能达成后，据石油输出国组织(OPEC)两名代表称，在将于6月举行的OPEC会议上，并不包含恢复原油产量限制的计划。','1','1','2017-03-11 17:29:16','','0','','','0','{\"thumb\":\"\"}','0','0','0','0','','');INSERT INTO ts_posts ( `id`, `post_author`, `post_keywords`, `post_source`, `post_date`, `post_content`, `post_title`, `post_excerpt`, `post_status`, `comment_status`, `post_modified`, `post_content_filtered`, `post_parent`, `post_type`, `post_mime_type`, `comment_count`, `smeta`, `post_hits`, `post_like`, `istop`, `recommended`, `page_tpl`, `page_tpls` ) VALUES  ('205','1','天然气市场行情','','2017-03-11 17:31:07','<p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　据国家统计局近日发布的我国天然气市场的相关数据显示，今年一季度我国天然气产量、进口量及消费量同比均出现了增长。具体来看，一季度我国天然气产量</span>371<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">亿立方米，同比增长</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">5.4%;</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">天然气进口量</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">204.85</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">亿立方米，同比增长</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">28.1%;</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">天然气消费量</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">597</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">亿立方米，同比增长</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">18.9%</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　多因素保驾产销量稳定增长</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　记者查阅资料显示，</span>2015<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年一季度，我国天然气产量、进口量及消费量同比增长分别为</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">6.3%</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">、</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">16.5%</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">、</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">4.8%</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">。通过对比两年数据可以发现，除产量增速基本保持一致外，</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">2016</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年一季度我国天然气进口量及消费量增速远超</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">2015</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年同期。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\">　　“<span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">2016</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年一季度，我国天然气产量增速尽管与去年相比有所下降，但仍保持了增长的态势。综合来看，一季度天然气产量同比出现增长主要是由原有气田增产及新气田投产这两个利好因素推动的。”卓创资讯分析师张林向记者表示。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　据了解，</span>2015<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年下半年至今，牛东气田、东坪气田、涩北气田及大庆气田等原有气田都实现了天然气产量的增加。此外，安岳气田磨溪区块龙王庙组气藏，罗家寨气田等大型气田也实现竣工投产。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　而且在页岩气方面的天然气产量也在增加。数据显示，</span>2016<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年一季度涪陵页岩气田生产页岩气</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">13.75</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">亿立方米，同比也增长</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">260.8%</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　另外，据国土资源部公布的数据显示，</span>2015<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年全国天然气新增探明地质储量</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">6772.20</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">亿立方米，新增探明技术可采储量</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">3754.35</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">亿立方米，剩余技术可采储量</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">51939.45</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">亿立方米。“探明可开采储量总体来说比较充裕，这为后期我国天然气产量的增加提供了有效地保障。”张林表示。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　而在天然气消费量方面，张林认为，</span>2015<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">4</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月至今，我国共两次调低非民用气门站价，总计下调</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">1.1</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">元</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">/</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">立方米。门站价格下调后，各地的非民用气终端零售价也纷纷随之下调。另外，这一时期，国际油价大跌也引起了国际天然气价格的大幅下降，我国进口的管道气及</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">LNG</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">的价格也不断下调。价格的下跌引起了天然气使用成本的下降，更多的工厂企业及居民家庭开始选择使用天然气，天然气消费量增加也就成了必然。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　此外，张林表示，国家大力推动节能减排，压缩降低煤炭使用比例，推广天然气发电，提高天然气等清洁能源的利用普及率也是造成天然气消费量增速提高的重要原因。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　二季度有望保持增长态势</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　当然天然气在进口量方面的增长也不逊色。</span>2016<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年一季度我国天然气进口量保 持了两位数的高速增长，其增速与去年同期相比增幅超过</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">70%</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\">　　“天然气进口量的高速增长既得益于低油价引发的低气价的推动，也得益于我国天然气消费需求的迅速提升。”张林表示，此外，中亚、中缅天然气管道输气能力的提升及新的<span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">LNG</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">接收站的建成投用也提高了我国的天然气进口能力，为我国天然气进口量的增加起到了助推作用。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　而对于未来天然气市场的相关发展，张林认为，</span>4<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月份，供暖期正式结束，加之各地气温逐步回升，我国天然气取暖消费需求大幅下降。因此，二季度，我国天然气总体消费量环比将出现下降，进口量及产量环比也预计会有不同程度的回落。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　不过部分业内人士表示，随着我国签署旨在控制气候变化及碳排放量的《巴黎协定》后，未来我国节能减排的力度预计将会进一步加大，并继续减少煤炭、石油等造成污染的化石燃料的使用，提高天然气等清洁能源的利用比例，大力推动天然气汽车的发展。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　另外，张林强调，我国新一轮的天然气价格改革正在酝酿，低油价引起的低气价也将会持续很长时间。所以综合来看，二季度以至未来更长一段时期内，我国天然气产量、消费量及进口量同比将继续保持增长态势。</span></span></p><p><br/></p>','一季度我国天然气市场行情总结及展望','　　据国家统计局近日发布的我国天然气市场的相关数据显示，今年一季度我国天然气产量、进口量及消费量同比均出现了增长。具体来看，一季度我国天然气产量371亿立方米，同比增长5.4%;天然气进口量204.85亿立方米，同比增长28.1%;天然气消费量597亿立方米，同比增长18.9%。','1','1','2017-03-11 17:30:06','','0','','','0','{\"thumb\":\"\"}','0','0','0','0','','');INSERT INTO ts_posts ( `id`, `post_author`, `post_keywords`, `post_source`, `post_date`, `post_content`, `post_title`, `post_excerpt`, `post_status`, `comment_status`, `post_modified`, `post_content_filtered`, `post_parent`, `post_type`, `post_mime_type`, `comment_count`, `smeta`, `post_hits`, `post_like`, `istop`, `recommended`, `page_tpl`, `page_tpls` ) VALUES  ('206','1','4月中国地炼原油进口量达到120万桶/天','','2017-03-11 17:31:57','<p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\">　　4<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月份中国地方炼油厂的原油进口量可能达到</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">120</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">万桶</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">/</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">天，较</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">3</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月份的</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">85</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">万桶</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">/</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">天的进口量大幅增加。然而，由于码头拥堵且炼油厂将进行年度检修， </span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">5</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月份地方炼油厂的原油进口量可能减少</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">35</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">万桶</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">/</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">天，</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">6</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月份进口量可能减少</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">51</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">万桶</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">/</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">天。</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">Energy Aspects</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">在研究报告中称：“到了</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">7</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月份，青岛正在兴建中的原油储罐（规划总储量为</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">246</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">万立方米）将有</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">120</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">万立方米储量投入使用，加之烟台新的超大型油船</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">(VLCC)</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">泊位将投入使用，将帮助缓解码头拥堵局面，进而推高原油进口量。”</span></span></p><p><br/></p>','4月中国地炼原油进口量达到120万桶/天','4月份中国地方炼油厂的原油进口量可能达到120万桶/天，较3月份的85万桶/天的进口量大幅增加。','1','1','2017-03-11 17:31:19','','0','','','0','{\"thumb\":\"\"}','0','0','0','0','','');INSERT INTO ts_posts ( `id`, `post_author`, `post_keywords`, `post_source`, `post_date`, `post_content`, `post_title`, `post_excerpt`, `post_status`, `comment_status`, `post_modified`, `post_content_filtered`, `post_parent`, `post_type`, `post_mime_type`, `comment_count`, `smeta`, `post_hits`, `post_like`, `istop`, `recommended`, `page_tpl`, `page_tpls` ) VALUES  ('207','1','能源趋势','','2017-03-11 17:35:03','<p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　始于</span>2014<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年下半年的油价下行及低位运行已持续近两年，这一段时期可以说是石油行业发展的寒冬期。由于油价低迷，石油行业在高油价时期形成的发展模式短期内难以适应突如其来的油价下行，导致行业内出现许多不适应现象。典型的表现是石油公司业务盈利空间缩小，投资大幅萎缩，现金流吃紧甚至倒闭。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　低油价来袭，石油公司使出浑身解数，采取各种应对手段。一时间，低油价如同洪水猛兽一样冲刷着石油人的心灵，媒体为此一度惊呼石油行业扛不住了，称其即将变成夕阳产业。不过，在石油行业与低油价的抗争中，时不时也有亮点出现。这些亮点的存在昭示着石油产业并没有到山穷水尽的地步，依然有无限潜力。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　全球一次能源中油气的主体地位短期内难以撼动，石油行业依然有着不可替代的发展空间。数据显示，全球一次能源消费结构中，石油消费占</span>33%<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">，天然气占</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">24%</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">，其余是煤炭和新能源。</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">57%</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">的消费比例意味着石油天然气资源短期内是不可能被其他能源替代的，油气行业在能源工业中的主体地位还很稳固。更何况如今天然气时代来临，对油气行业本身就是个难得的机遇。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　纵使今后油价持续低迷，</span>57%<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">的一次能源消费比例也依然会使油气行业有足够的时间和空间去适应和转型。如果将目前的油价波动视为“不速之客”或者石油行业的“来犯之敌”，那么目前的石油工业正处于“战略防御”阶段，日后一定会有“战略相持”与“战略反攻”。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　当然，</span>“战略相持与反攻”的最高境界并不意味着石油行业从业者一定要推高油价、一定要在高油价下才能生存，而是指任何油价下石油行业都能具有创造与获取自己的生存与发展空间的能力。换句话说，如果油价上扬，石油公司压力下降，可以开足马力生产，不排除获得丰厚利润；如果油价下降，石油公司也有自如应对的措施和手段。</span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　实际上，经过近两年的</span>“战略防御”，石油行业在与低油价较量的过程中已经取得阶段性胜利，并非一蹶不振或一无是处。目前，全球石油行业正在进入与低油价抗争的相持阶段，理由有以下几个方面。</span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　一是石油行业的成本在下降。相比于两年前的情形，石油公司的运营成本有一定程度的下降，部分减缓了石油公司在突如其来的低油价面前表现出的经营压力。有咨询机构的统计数据显示，近两年来石油行业的生产成本下降幅度近</span>20%<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">。国际油价是全球经济的“晴雨表”。当经济形势不好的时候，油价一般比较低迷，当前的情况基本符合这一特点。经济形势低迷时，与能源生产相关的各类生产要素的价格也会出现不同程度的下降，从而减缓或者抵消油价下行给石油行业带来的成本压力。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　二是石油行业在低油价下的科技创新与效率提升已有进展，为日后的发展奠定了基础。低油价下石油企业、服务企业等石油行业从业主体除了管理方面之外，在科技创新方面也收效不错，部分企业已在低油气价格下突破困境，实现扭亏增盈。例如，油气商与服务商就以</span>“抱团取暖”的方式，通过对传统成熟的技术进行集成，以及新技术的应用，实现了在低油价、低气价下的盈利。</span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　可以肯定的是，如果油价继续低迷下去，石油企业的科技创新动机会越来越强，经营效率必将因科技元素的投入而逐渐改善。前一段时间，埃克森美孚、</span>BP<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">、壳牌、雪佛龙、道达尔陆续公布了</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">2015</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年经营年报。数据显示，在低油价的冲击下，石油公司积极寻求资产在全球范围内优化布局的途径，全力进行科技创新。</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">2015</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年各家石油公司的营业收入都在下降，有些下降幅度甚至很大，但他们的科技投入普遍在增加，依靠科技应对低油价的发展思路显而易见。由此可见，石油行业绝非死水一潭，不会在低油价面前无能为力或者无动于衷。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　三是油价的下跌会有一定的度，有自己的底线，这个底线应该就是成本。目前支撑低油价的供给侧因素主要是欧佩克的稳产与美国页岩油产量的相对稳定。关于这两个主要原油供应者的生产成本目前也是众说纷纭，莫衷一是。但可以肯定的是，在目前的油价水平下，欧佩克成员国和美国国内越来越多的油气商正在感受到日益高涨的成本压力。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　若当前的稳产甚至增产现象长期持续下去，无异于产油国用自己的财富补贴全球消费者，这样的赔本买卖估计不会长久。更何况以沙特为代表的欧佩克国家对石油高度依赖，对其石油生产成本的判断绝不可简单停留在生产层面，而是要从国家经济运行层面去考量，或者说从国家财政油价角度考量。有分析认为，沙特等欧佩克国家财政层面的石油盈亏平衡点在</span>80<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">美元</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">/</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">桶至</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">100</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">美元</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">/</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">桶之间；中东地区国家财政油价最低的卡塔尔，其财政油价也在</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">50</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">美元</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">/</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">桶至</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">70</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">美元</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">/</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">桶。这个价格水平可是远远高于目前的油价水平的。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　尽管沙特等国家提出了到</span>2030<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年的“去石油计划”，旨在摆脱国家经济运行对石油的高度依赖，但沙特的计划很可能是远水解不了近渴。沙特作为主要产油国，</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">2015</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年因为低油价，财政赤字已达数千亿美元。沙特首先要做的是摆脱目前的困境，之后再设法谋求以后的长久发展，整个过程需要借助石油来“去石油”。因此，在当前油价已经进入基本由供需层面决定，地缘政治事件、投机炒作对油价影响力日渐衰微，油价处于长期“裸奔”状态的条件下，油价再度下行的可能性已经很小了。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　对石油行业而言，现在是黎明前的黑暗；对石油从业者而言，坚持就是胜利。从过去一两年全球石油产量走势看，在油价大幅下降的不利形势下，产量基本上保持了稳定。欧佩克、俄罗斯等主要油气生产者在低油价的长期困扰下也有了冻产的意向。尽管新近召开的多哈会谈因为伊朗重返市场不愿减产等原因无果而终，但主要产油国对于冻产讨论的从无到有本身就是一个信号，这个信号会随着时间的推移而逐渐加强，最终变现的可能性不是没有。因此，未来油价触底反弹，石油行业迎来发展新机会的可能性是存在的。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　不过，即使油价真的回暖了，石油行业从业者也不要期望一夜暴富。价格的回暖是有限的，因为从目前的发挥态势看，低油价下能源供应的多元化趋势在加强而不是削弱。特别是在</span>2015<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年巴黎气候大会召开之后，全球各国就绿色低碳发展模式达成空前一致的形势下，绿色低碳发展道路成为共识和普选，新能源发展呈欣欣向荣之势的形势下，新能源很大程度上已经摆脱了油价对其发展的束缚而走上快速发展道路。未来油价回暖之际，新能源等清洁能源的发展机会更会因为整个经济形势的好转而得以提速。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　因此，对石油行业而言，即使成功度过了与低油价的</span>“战略相持”而进入“战略反攻”阶段，也不能放松警惕，而是要大力推进发展模式的转型。一方面依靠科技创新提高效率，另一方面转变发展方式，大力创建绿色低碳发展道路。唯有如此，石油产业方能具有竞争力，在新形势下开辟出新天地。 （作者为经济学博士，能源经济学者）</span></p><p><br/></p>','能源趋势：低油价下石油工业同样需要争上游','　　始于2014年下半年的油价下行及低位运行已持续近两年，这一段时期可以说是石油行业发展的寒冬期。由于油价低迷，石油行业在高油价时期形成的发展模式短期内难以适应突如其来的油价下行，导致行业内出现许多不适应现象。典型的表现是石油公司业务盈利空间缩小，投资大幅萎缩，现金流吃紧甚至倒闭。','1','1','2017-03-11 17:34:05','','0','','','0','{\"thumb\":\"\"}','0','0','0','0','','');INSERT INTO ts_posts ( `id`, `post_author`, `post_keywords`, `post_source`, `post_date`, `post_content`, `post_title`, `post_excerpt`, `post_status`, `comment_status`, `post_modified`, `post_content_filtered`, `post_parent`, `post_type`, `post_mime_type`, `comment_count`, `smeta`, `post_hits`, `post_like`, `istop`, `recommended`, `page_tpl`, `page_tpls` ) VALUES  ('208','1','特约解盘','','2017-03-11 17:36:30','<p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\">　　2014<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">7</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月本轮国际油价暴跌拉开序幕，截至目前已经历</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">22</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">个月。其间，布伦特期货价格于</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">2016</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">1</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">20</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">日跌至</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">27.88</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">美元</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">/</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">桶低点，</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">WTI</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">于</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">2</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">11</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">日跌至</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">26.21</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">美元</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">/</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">桶低点，均跌破</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">2008</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年国际金融危机期间最低水平。</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">2</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月中旬以来，国际油价呈触底反弹态势，</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">WTI</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">和布伦特期货价格相对最低点反弹分别达到</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">76%</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">和</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">73%</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　对于近期的油价反弹，市场上主要存在两种观点，一是认为国际油价未来仍有再探新低的可能，二是认为油价已触底，未来呈逐步反弹趋势。经研院分析认为，油价最坏的时期已经过去，石油行业在经历寒冬之后有望重新迎来春天，主要因为当前石油市场受到以下几个因素的支撑。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　第一，世界石油市场供需关系出现改善。根据</span>IEA<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">数据，从年度水平来看，</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">2016</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年全年世界石油需求为</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">9590</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">万桶</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">/</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">日，比上年增长</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">120</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">万桶</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">/</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">日，非欧佩克石油供应为</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">5700</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">万桶</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">/</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">日，比上年减少</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">70</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">万桶</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">/</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">日，欧佩克凝析油产量为</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">690</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">万桶</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">/</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">日，比上年增长</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">20</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">万桶</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">/</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">日。若欧佩克原油产量维持在一季度</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">3260</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">万桶</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">/</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">日的历史高位水平，则</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">2016</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年世界石油供应富余</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">60</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">万桶</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">/</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">日，相比</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">2015</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年缩窄</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">110</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">万桶</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">/</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">日。从季度水平来看，由于一方面非欧佩克石油供应的调整逐步到位，另一方面下半年石油需求通常高于上半年，</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">2016</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年世界石油市场基本面将逐季改善。如果欧佩克原油产量维持在一季度的水平，那么三、四季度石油市场供需将基本回归平衡。值得注意的是，导致世界石油市场严重供应过剩的美国原油产量已出现大幅下降，</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">4</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月已降至每日</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">895</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">万桶，相比</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">2015</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">4</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月高点减少</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">74</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">万桶</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">/</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">日。</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">EIA</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">预计未来美国原油产量将进一步下降，年底将为</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">820</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">万桶</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">/</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">日左右。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　第二，从成本角度来看，油价下跌已接近底线。非欧佩克国家勘探开发和生产运营的成本相对较高，油价走低将首先迫使其减产，从而缓解供应过剩局面，为油价运行设置底线。根据相关资料测算，</span>2016<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年全球石油上游项目的平均全周期成本约为</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">50</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">美元</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">/</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">桶，其中除了中东国家成本大多数低于</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">30</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">美元</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">/</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">桶之外，其他产油国包括美国最高效的“甜品区”的全周期成本均高于</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">30</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">美元</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">/</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">桶。此外，对于已完成勘探、处于生产阶段的油井，短期内决定其能否继续生产的主要是生产运营成本，虽然中东和俄罗斯地区的运营成本可低至</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">10</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">美元</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">/</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">桶以下，但英国、巴西和加拿大的运营成本相对最高，平均在</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">32</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">至</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">40</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">美元</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">/</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">桶。在低油价的影响下，美国原油产量已经大幅下降，若油价继续保持在当前低位，运营成本较高的英国、加拿大、巴西等国家的产量也将出现明显的下降，从而对油价构成支撑。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　第三，弱势美元为油价提供支撑。自去年年底开启十年来第一次加息后，美联储迟迟未有新动作，美元持续走弱。虽然美国失业率已降至</span>5%<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">的八年低位，但通胀水平距</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">2%</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">的目标仍有明显距离，加之全球经济和金融市场不稳定因素凸显，美联储主席耶伦一再强调将放缓加息步伐，随着加息预期的减弱，预计短期内美元将继续维持偏弱走势，继续为油价提供支撑。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　第四，期货市场技术分析也表明国际油价已触底。从油价形态来看，国际油价已结束单边下滑趋势，年初走出了典型的</span>“<span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">w</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">”型底部形态，而</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">3</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月以来又冲破了</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">40</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">美元</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">/</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">桶的强阻力位，技术形态上也说明油价已经触底。从持仓结构来看，自年初油价触及低点以来，原油期货市场中的基金空头大量撤离，</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">WTI</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">基金空头仓位下降</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">43%</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">，布伦特基金空头仓位下降</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">34%</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">，看空氛围减弱。从期限结构来看，现货价格贴水幅度已较年初缩小一半以上，表明石油现货市场承受的压力大大减小。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　第五，从原油与其他大宗商品的比价关系看，黄金、铜、大豆等大宗商品与原油的价格比均处于高位，表明当前原油价格偏低。长期来看，不同种类的大宗商品之间具有高度的价格趋同性，统计分析显示，原油与食品、金属类商品月均价的相关系数均在</span>0.8<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">以上。然而，近期原油与其他大宗商品走势出现明显分化。特别是</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">2015</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年年底以来，原油与其他大宗商品之间的比价关系超出了常见范围。首先，从黄金与原油比价关系来看，</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">1983</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年以来，黄金与原油价格比（金油比）均值为</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">16</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">，而</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">2</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月金油比达到前所未有的</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">40</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">。其次，与金属和农产品的典型铜和大豆价格相比，</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">2000</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年以来，铜</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">/</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">原油与大豆</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">/</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">原油的价格比均值分别为</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">0.036</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">和</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">15.45</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">，而二者</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">2</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月的价格比最高达到</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">0.068</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">和</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">28.5</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">，为</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">2000</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年以来最高，亦表明当前市场对原油价格的估计相对偏低。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　第六，世界石油消费支出与全球</span>GDP<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">的比值处于相对低位，同样表明当前油价偏低。从历史规律来看，世界石油消费支出（世界石油消费量×国际油价）与全球</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">GDP</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">的比值基本处在一个相对稳定的范围内，</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">2005</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年至</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">2014</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年为</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">3.2%</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">至</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">4.97%</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">。</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">2015</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年国际油价年均水平大幅下挫，石油消费支出占</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">GDP</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">的比重降至</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">2.25%</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">，处于阶段底部。另外，历史上布伦特实际价格（考虑通胀影响）与</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">2015</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年水平相当的时期（</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">1974</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年至</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">1978</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年）石油消费支出占</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">GDP</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">的比值范围为</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">3.81%</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">至</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">4.45%</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">，也高于</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">2015</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年的</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">2.25%</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">。可以进一步来看</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">2016</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年的情况，如果</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">2016</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年布伦特年均价维持在目前</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">37</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">美元</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">/</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">桶的水平，则</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">2016</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年全球石油消费支出占全球</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">GDP</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">的比值将为</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">1.55%</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">左右，相比</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">2015</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年的</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">2.25%</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">进一步大幅下降，这表明当前的原油价格在现阶段而言明显偏低。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　（本文特约中国石油经济技术研究院原油市场研究团队供稿，主要执笔人：霍丽君、王婧、陈蕊）</span></span></p><p><br/></p>','特约解盘：油价最坏的时期已经过去','　　2014年7月本轮国际油价暴跌拉开序幕，截至目前已经历22个月。其间，布伦特期货价格于2016年1月20日跌至27.88美元/桶低点，WTI于2月11日跌至26.21美元/桶低点，均跌破2008年国际金融危机期间最低水平。2月中旬以来，国际油价呈触底反弹态势，WTI和布伦特期货价格相对最低点反弹分别达到76%和73%。','1','1','2017-03-11 17:35:26','','0','','','0','{\"thumb\":\"\"}','1','0','0','0','','');INSERT INTO ts_posts ( `id`, `post_author`, `post_keywords`, `post_source`, `post_date`, `post_content`, `post_title`, `post_excerpt`, `post_status`, `comment_status`, `post_modified`, `post_content_filtered`, `post_parent`, `post_type`, `post_mime_type`, `comment_count`, `smeta`, `post_hits`, `post_like`, `istop`, `recommended`, `page_tpl`, `page_tpls` ) VALUES  ('209','1','油价调价窗口今开启','','2017-03-11 17:41:05','<p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　新一轮成品油调价窗口将于</span>5<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">25</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">日</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">24</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">时开启。机构预测国内油价将迎来“三连涨”，本次调价或创年内最大涨幅。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　据卓创资讯测算，截至</span>23<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">日，参考原油变化率为</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">5.77%</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">，对应汽柴油上调</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">170</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">元</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">/</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">吨，折合</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">0</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">号柴油上调</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">0.14</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">元</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">/</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">升，</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">90</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">号汽油涨</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">0.12</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">元</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">/</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">升，</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">93</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">号汽油涨</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">0.13</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">元</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">/</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">升，</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">97</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">号汽油涨</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">0.14</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">元</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">/</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">升。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　另据隆众石化网预计，本次汽柴油将上调</span>180-200<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">元</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">/</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">吨，折合每升</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">0.13-0.17</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">元。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　卓创资讯成品油分析师徐娜在接受中新网</span>(<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">微信公众号：</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">cns2012)</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">记者采访时指出，本次油价上调有可能创下年内最大涨幅，且考虑到前两次上调的幅度，“三连涨”的累计涨幅将直逼</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">500</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">元</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">/</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">吨。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　此前，国内成品油价曾两次上调：</span>4<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">26</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">日，汽、柴油每吨分别上调</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">165</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">元和</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">160</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">元；</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">5</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">11</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">日，汽、柴油每吨分别上调</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">120</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">元和</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">115</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">元。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　为何预测国内油价将再次上调</span>?<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">根据《石油价格管理办法》，国内汽柴油最高零售价与国际油价挂钩，并设置了每桶</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">40</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">美元的“地板价”和每桶</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">130</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">美元的“天花板价”，在中间区间时该降就降，该升就升。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　截至</span>23<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">日收盘，</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">WTI</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">原油</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">6</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月期货收跌</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">0.33</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">美元，报</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">48.08</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">美元</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">/</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">桶；布伦特</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">7</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月原油期货跌</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">0.37</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">美元，报</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">48.35</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">美元</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">/</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">桶。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\">　　“尽管国际原油近日出现小幅下跌，但均价一直高于<span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">40</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">美元”，徐娜说，“在加拿大野火以及美国原油库存下降的利好消息提振下，国际油价供应过剩的负面影响被冲淡，本计价周期内，原油价格震荡上行，原油变化率持续在正值范围内攀升”。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　在影响方面，隆众石化网成品油分析师薛群表示，本轮油价上调将继续提升成品油零售板块利润。</span>5<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月上半月，国内加油站汽油综合零售利润为</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">1752</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">元</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">/</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">吨，柴油为</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">1509</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">元</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">/</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">吨。预计此次调价后，零售利润会有</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">100-150</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">元</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">/</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">吨左右的涨幅。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　关于未来国际油价的走势，广发期货</span>23<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">日发布的报告称，随着加拿大及尼日利亚供应回归的消息传来，油价涨势开始减弱。上周公布的北美钻井平台数维持不变，或是油价已阶段性见顶的信息，加之美元连涨三周，更加大了油价的上涨压力，预计油价将开始回调。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　国内成品油下一轮调价窗口将于</span>6<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">8</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">日</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">24</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">时开启。徐娜说，很多人关心国内油价是否会持续上涨，这需要看后期国际原油价格的走势。目前市场观望色彩浓厚，国际原油出现震荡走势的可能性较大，如果利空消息延续，则下一轮调价可能搁浅。</span></span></p><p><br/></p>','油价调价窗口今开启 或“三连涨”创年内最大涨幅','　　新一轮成品油调价窗口将于5月25日24时开启。机构预测国内油价将迎来“三连涨”，本次调价或创年内最大涨幅。','1','1','2017-03-11 17:39:48','','0','','','0','{\"thumb\":\"\"}','1','0','0','0','','');INSERT INTO ts_posts ( `id`, `post_author`, `post_keywords`, `post_source`, `post_date`, `post_content`, `post_title`, `post_excerpt`, `post_status`, `comment_status`, `post_modified`, `post_content_filtered`, `post_parent`, `post_type`, `post_mime_type`, `comment_count`, `smeta`, `post_hits`, `post_like`, `istop`, `recommended`, `page_tpl`, `page_tpls` ) VALUES  ('210','1','原油供需变化','','2017-03-11 17:42:27','<p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　由于部分产油国原油供给中断与主要经济体需求增长，有市场人士指出，原油市场将很快趋于供需再平衡，油价也将在几个月后逐步回升。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　美国杰弗里斯咨询公司分析师贾森</span>·甘默尔认为，由于尼日利亚与加拿大原油生产中断，<span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">4</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月份原油市场日均供给量减少约</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">200</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">万桶，这使一直以来的供给过剩情况得到缓解。甘默尔还说，在需求端，主要经济体进口增长明显，这有助于石油市场到年底趋于供需平衡。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　瑞银此前预测，布伦特原油到</span>2016<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年第四季度将达每桶</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">49</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">美元，到</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">2017</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年进一步回升至每桶</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">55</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">美元。不过，甘默尔认为，油价回升至每桶</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">50</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">美元上方后，美国石油开采活动将增加，这又会抑制油价上涨。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　截至</span>23<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">日，纽约商品交易所</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">7</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月份交货的布伦特原油期货价格收于每桶</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">48.35</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">美元。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　国际投行高盛则认为，国际原油市场基本面的转变要比预期更早，或转为供给不足。但欧佩克认为，由于成员国产量激增，</span>2016<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年石油供应过剩的局面正在扩大。</span></span></p><p><br/></p>','市场人士认为原油供需变化将促使油价回升','　　由于部分产油国原油供给中断与主要经济体需求增长，有市场人士指出，原油市场将很快趋于供需再平衡，油价也将在几个月后逐步回升。','1','1','2017-03-11 17:41:40','','0','','','0','{\"thumb\":\"\"}','0','0','0','0','','');INSERT INTO ts_posts ( `id`, `post_author`, `post_keywords`, `post_source`, `post_date`, `post_content`, `post_title`, `post_excerpt`, `post_status`, `comment_status`, `post_modified`, `post_content_filtered`, `post_parent`, `post_type`, `post_mime_type`, `comment_count`, `smeta`, `post_hits`, `post_like`, `istop`, `recommended`, `page_tpl`, `page_tpls` ) VALUES  ('211','1','我国煤炭消费量占世界一半','','2017-03-11 17:43:28','<p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　昨日，中国煤炭工业协会会长王显政在出席</span>2016<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年世界煤炭协会技术委员会会议时表示，虽然我国一直在减少煤炭在能源消费结构中的比例，但是</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">2015</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年中国的煤炭消费量仍占世界的一半。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　王显政介绍称，</span>2015<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年，世界煤炭产量约</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">80</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">亿吨，全国产量达</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">37.5</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">亿吨，虽然同比减少</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">3.3%</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">，但仍占世界的</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">47%</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">；我国煤炭消费量为</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">39.65</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">亿吨，同比下降</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">3.7%</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">，但仍占世界煤炭消费量的一半。煤炭在我国能源消费结构的比重达到</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">64%</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">，远高于</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">30%</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">的世界煤炭平均水平。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　虽然煤炭在我国的能源消费中占比很高，但煤炭行业依然是困难重重。王显政表示，当前，煤炭行业进入了需求增速放缓、过剩产能和库存消化、环境制约及结构调整的</span>“四期并存”发展阶段。</span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　数据显示，</span>2015<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年的煤炭消费结构中，我国的煤炭消费主要为商品煤，消费量</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">36.98</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">亿吨，其中电力行业用煤</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">18.39</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">亿吨，钢铁行业用煤</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">6.27</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">亿吨，建材行业用煤</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">5.25</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">亿吨，化工行业用煤</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">2.53</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">亿吨，但由于我国经济的放缓，四个行业的煤炭需求均有不同程度的下降，下降幅度分别为</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">6.2%</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">、</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">3.6%</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">、</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">8%</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">、</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">8.4%</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　王显政就煤炭行业转型表示，煤炭行业要围绕安全高效智能化开采、清洁高效集约化利用等组织开展技术攻关，建设示范工程，提升煤炭工业的可持续发展能力。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　据了解，</span>“十三五”期间，我国把控制能源消费总量作为重要任务，其中煤炭作为控制总量的重点，煤炭的消费比重将降到<span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">60%</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">以下，并将加快研究制定商品煤系列标准和煤炭清洁利用标准。</span></span></p><p><br/></p>','我国煤炭消费量占世界一半','　　昨日，中国煤炭工业协会会长王显政在出席2016年世界煤炭协会技术委员会会议时表示，虽然我国一直在减少煤炭在能源消费结构中的比例，但是2015年中国的煤炭消费量仍占世界的一半。','1','1','2017-03-11 17:42:39','','0','','','0','{\"thumb\":\"\"}','1','0','0','0','','');INSERT INTO ts_posts ( `id`, `post_author`, `post_keywords`, `post_source`, `post_date`, `post_content`, `post_title`, `post_excerpt`, `post_status`, `comment_status`, `post_modified`, `post_content_filtered`, `post_parent`, `post_type`, `post_mime_type`, `comment_count`, `smeta`, `post_hits`, `post_like`, `istop`, `recommended`, `page_tpl`, `page_tpls` ) VALUES  ('212','1','原油市场正接近新的平衡','','2017-03-11 17:44:21','<p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　随着国家油价的大幅上行，国内市场成品油已连续三次上调。作为决定国内市场价格涨跌的核心因素国际原油价格，此间举行的上海衍生品市场论坛上，不少业界专家预计，伴随大宗商品市场重新回暖，原油市场也正接近新的平衡。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　由于一系列利多因素的累积，国际油价从</span>4<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月份开始持续上涨，到目前，纽约市场原油期货价格逼近每桶</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">50</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">美元大关，另一基准油价伦敦北海布伦特油价则重新回到每桶</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">50</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">美元上方，与前期</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">1-2</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月份期间创下的低点相比，短短近</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">4</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">个月时间，累积反弹接近</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">50%</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　国际能源署石油行业及市场部负责人</span>NeilAtkinson<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">表示，</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">2016</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年原油的需求依然强劲，尤其是亚洲地区的原油需求旺盛，而供应增速受制于价格的影响正在下降，原油价格上涨的时间可能会比市场的预期更快一些。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　此前国际能源署上调了全球原油的需求增速。</span>“虽然北半球冬季较为温暖，但为什么还会上调，主要因素就是印度的增长特别强劲。”<span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">NeilAtkinson</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">表示，和中国市场的情况相比，印度的增长潜力巨大，目前印度每千人拥有车辆仅中国的四分之一左右，而美国大约是中国的</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">5</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">倍，虽然汽车保有量上升有一个过程，但到</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">2015</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年末已经看到印度的这一增速增加得非常快。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\">　　“未来随着油耗标准的不断提升，以及电动车等其他能源的替代，油品需求会逐渐进入一个下降通道，但总体而言，<span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">5</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">到</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">10</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年油品的需求还是相对稳定的。”剑桥能源咨询研究经理刘海全则表示，而从供应的角度看，虽然也面临很多的不确定因素，但一定也会达到新的平衡，同时很多新增的能源供应，也是需要投资来拉动，由于低油价的原因，一些新项目很可能需要更长的周期，甚至可能取消。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　能源专家认为，未来欧佩克对油价的影响力将继续减弱。</span>“实际上欧佩克<span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">2014</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年执行不减产的政策，是希望挤走一些高成本的非欧佩克生产量，但这一战略并未奏效，反而在亚洲特别是中国市场，失去了不少市场份额。”阿格斯亚太区副总裁</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">Alejandro</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">表示，中国一直在推动多元化的石油供应计划，到</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">3</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月份中国从欧佩克的进口量占整个原油进口量的比重创下了历史低点。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　此外，在一些业界专家看来，未来推动油价上行的另一因素将是投资资金的涌入。据新兴市场研究公司的统计，虽然市场的动荡使得部分资金遭遇赎回，但包括黄金基金在内的商品基金继续</span>“吸金”，到目前的新增资金流入规模超过<span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">200</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">亿美元，在主要行业基金的排名中较为靠前。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　事实上，近期油价的上涨，投机的资金身影闪现。美国商品期货交易委员会</span>(CFTC)<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">的数据显示，到</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">5</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月中旬，包括对冲基金、管理基金等在内的投机力量持有的美国原油期货期权净多头寸超过</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">25</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">万手，创下约一年来的新高。</span></span></p><p><br/></p>','原油市场正接近新的平衡','　　随着国家油价的大幅上行，国内市场成品油已连续三次上调。作为决定国内市场价格涨跌的核心因素国际原油价格，此间举行的上海衍生品市场论坛上，不少业界专家预计，伴随大宗商品市场重新回暖，原油市场也正接近新的平衡。','1','1','2017-03-11 17:43:40','','0','','','0','{\"thumb\":\"\"}','0','0','0','0','','');INSERT INTO ts_posts ( `id`, `post_author`, `post_keywords`, `post_source`, `post_date`, `post_content`, `post_title`, `post_excerpt`, `post_status`, `comment_status`, `post_modified`, `post_content_filtered`, `post_parent`, `post_type`, `post_mime_type`, `comment_count`, `smeta`, `post_hits`, `post_like`, `istop`, `recommended`, `page_tpl`, `page_tpls` ) VALUES  ('213','1','国内首个码头油气回收装置投用','','2017-03-11 17:45:14','<p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　上海石化在其化工码头的两个泊位投建了油气回收装置，防止装卸中油气散入大气。目前，该回收装置已通过上海市环保局评估，正式投用，成为国内首个投用的码头油气回收装置。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　由于汽油等油品易挥发，在储运、装卸过程中容易散入到空气中，不仅造成资源浪费，也会带来大气污染和安全隐患。目前，国内加油站建设油气回收装置已经成为共识，并在全国各地的加油站大力推广，但这样的油气回收装置在成品油水运装卸码头还难得一见。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　上海石化此次在码头建设投用的油气回收装置，采用了中国石化自主知识产权技术，工程技术人员和设计单位通力合作，通过船岸对接设施，将船舱油气回收到油气回收设施，采用先冷凝、后吸附的技术路线，回收装船过程中产生的无组织排放油气，降低非甲烷总烃的排放量。</span></span></p><p><br/></p>','国内首个码头油气回收装置投用','　　上海石化在其化工码头的两个泊位投建了油气回收装置，防止装卸中油气散入大气。目前，该回收装置已通过上海市环保局评估，正式投用，成为国内首个投用的码头油气回收装置。','1','1','2017-03-11 17:44:36','','0','','','0','{\"thumb\":\"\"}','0','0','0','0','','');INSERT INTO ts_posts ( `id`, `post_author`, `post_keywords`, `post_source`, `post_date`, `post_content`, `post_title`, `post_excerpt`, `post_status`, `comment_status`, `post_modified`, `post_content_filtered`, `post_parent`, `post_type`, `post_mime_type`, `comment_count`, `smeta`, `post_hits`, `post_like`, `istop`, `recommended`, `page_tpl`, `page_tpls` ) VALUES  ('214','1','国际油价5月31日收盘下跌 ','','2017-03-11 17:46:01','<p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\">　 &nbsp;<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">当天石油交易量清淡，纽约油价</span>5<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">31</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">日收盘下跌。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　当天没有重要的石油数据发布，投资者主要关注将于</span>6<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">2</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">日在维也纳召开的石油输出国组织</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">(</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">欧佩克</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">)</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">会议。分析人士指出，在会议前几个交易日，石油交易量将保持清淡。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　前一交易日，受美元走强影响，国际油价</span>27<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">日下跌。美联储主席耶伦</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">27</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">日在哈佛大学参加活动时表示，如果经济数据继续好转，美联储在未来几个月内再次加息很可能是合适的。耶伦的表态当天支撑美元大幅上涨。美元走强降低了以美元计价的石油的投资吸引力。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　数据方面，美国油田技术服务公司贝克休斯</span>27<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">日发布的数据显示，截至</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">5</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">27</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">日的一周，美国运营的油田钻井平台数量减少。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　截至当日收盘时，纽约商品交易所</span>2016<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">7</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月交货的轻质原油期货价格下跌</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">0.23</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">美元，收于每桶</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">49.10</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">美元。</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">2016</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">7</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月交货的伦敦布伦特原油期货价格上涨</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">0.37</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">美元，收于每桶</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">49.69</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">美元。</span></span></p><p><br/></p>','国际油价5月31日收盘下跌 报每桶49.10美元','　  当天石油交易量清淡，纽约油价5月31日收盘下跌。','1','1','2017-03-11 17:45:25','','0','','','0','{\"thumb\":\"\"}','0','0','0','0','','');INSERT INTO ts_posts ( `id`, `post_author`, `post_keywords`, `post_source`, `post_date`, `post_content`, `post_title`, `post_excerpt`, `post_status`, `comment_status`, `post_modified`, `post_content_filtered`, `post_parent`, `post_type`, `post_mime_type`, `comment_count`, `smeta`, `post_hits`, `post_like`, `istop`, `recommended`, `page_tpl`, `page_tpls` ) VALUES  ('215','1','&quot;京六&quot;油品接近&quot;世界最严&quot;标准','','2017-03-11 17:47:47','<p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　为减少机动车污染排放，改善空气质量，必不可少的措施之一是不断改善车用燃油品质。昨日，</span>“京六”阶段车用汽柴油品标准征求意见。车用汽柴油品质从第五阶段升级为第六阶段，将实现在用车碳氢化合物减排<span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">5%-10%</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\">　</span><strong><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;font-size: 14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　升级油品可提高净化器转化效率</span></span></strong></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　按照《北京市清洁空气行动计划》有关要求，市环保局组织起草了北京市地方标准《车用汽油》（征求意见稿）和《车用柴油》（征求意见稿）。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　减少机动车污染，除了提高机动车的排放标准，还可以改善车用燃油的品质。此前北京于</span>2004<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年、</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">2005</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年、</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">2008</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年、</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">2012</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年在全国率先实施了第二、三、四和五阶段地方油品标准，其中每阶段标准都对硫含量进一步加严。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　升级油品后对车有何影响？市环保局机动车排放管理处副调研员吴迪介绍，车用燃油品质的提高不但可以保障新车的正常使用，还会提高净化器转化效率，使得全部在用车排放同步大幅度削减。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\">　　</span><strong><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;font-size: 14px\">“京六”油品参照美国加州和欧洲标准</span></strong></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　吴迪介绍，该标准征求意见稿中技术指标主要参照美国加利福尼亚州第</span>III<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">阶段车用燃油标准和欧洲</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">VI</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">车用燃油标准，硫含量维持不变。同时，进一步加严汽油中的烯烃、芳烃、苯、蒸气压、馏程和柴油中的多环芳烃、密度等主要环保指标。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　其中，对于烯烃含量，美国加利福尼亚州第</span>III<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">阶段新配方汽油标准为不大于</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">10%</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">（体积分数），欧洲车用汽油标准为不大于</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">18%</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">（体积分数），考虑到我国石油炼制工艺的实际情况，并尽可能向世界上最严的标准靠拢，提升燃油品质，所以此次将烯烃含量由五阶段的“不大于</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">25%</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">（体积分数）”加严为“不大于</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">15%</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">（体积分数）”。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　据科学研究，烯烃化学活性强，会形成胶质，会通过蒸发排放造成光化学污染，因此烯烃含量大幅度降低，将减少胶质的形成，从而减少发动机进气系统的沉积物，同时对减少臭氧和</span>PM2.5<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">排放有贡献。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　另外，降低柴油中多环芳烃限值将减少氮氧化物和颗粒物排放。国内外研究结果表明，车用汽柴油品质升级对减排的贡献较大，预计从第五阶段升级为第六阶段，将实现在用车碳氢化合物减排</span>5%<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">至</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">10%</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　第六阶段油品适配性研究从</span>2014<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年开始。记者从市环保局获悉，北京将力争在明年</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">1</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月开始实施第六阶段油品地方标准。</span></span></p><p><br/></p>','&quot;京六&quot;油品接近&quot;世界最严&quot;标准 预计明年实施','　　为减少机动车污染排放，改善空气质量，必不可少的措施之一是不断改善车用燃油品质。昨日，“京六”阶段车用汽柴油品标准征求意见。车用汽柴油品质从第五阶段升级为第六阶段，将实现在用车碳氢化合物减排5%-10%。','1','1','2017-03-11 17:46:12','','0','','','0','{\"thumb\":\"\"}','1','0','0','0','','');INSERT INTO ts_posts ( `id`, `post_author`, `post_keywords`, `post_source`, `post_date`, `post_content`, `post_title`, `post_excerpt`, `post_status`, `comment_status`, `post_modified`, `post_content_filtered`, `post_parent`, `post_type`, `post_mime_type`, `comment_count`, `smeta`, `post_hits`, `post_like`, `istop`, `recommended`, `page_tpl`, `page_tpls` ) VALUES  ('216','1','世界最大油轮船队','','2017-03-11 17:50:31','<p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\">&nbsp;&nbsp;　6<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">6</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">日，中远集团和中国海运油运业务重组整合落地，中远海运能源运输股份有限公司在上海成立，标志着世界最大油轮船队在中国建成。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　重组后，中远海运能源的油轮船队规模位居全球第一，拥有和控制油轮运力</span>105<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">艘，计</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">1704</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">万载重吨；液化天然气（</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">LNG</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">）运输共投入运营</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">9</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">艘，参与投资</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">LNG</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">船舶</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">25</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">艘。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　据中远海运相关人士介绍，目前能源板块总资产占中远海运集团总资产的比重达到</span>11%<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">，油轮船队占集团综合运力比重达到</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">20%</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">，是全球船型结构最均衡、船龄最年轻、现代化程度最高的油轮船队。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　近年来，国际航运市场总体低迷，但低油价利好加上中国计划持续增加原油储备，进一步提振了油轮租赁市场。重组后，中远海运能源规模效益得到体现，其与国内外</span>200<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">多家石化企业和油品贸易公司保持着良好的合作关系，对于保障国家能源运输安全具有重要作用。</span></span></p><p><br/></p>','我国建成世界最大油轮船队发力石油航运','  　6月6日，中远集团和中国海运油运业务重组整合落地，中远海运能源运输股份有限公司在上海成立，标志着世界最大油轮船队在中国建成。','1','1','2017-03-11 17:48:19','','0','','','0','{\"thumb\":\"\"}','0','0','0','0','','');INSERT INTO ts_posts ( `id`, `post_author`, `post_keywords`, `post_source`, `post_date`, `post_content`, `post_title`, `post_excerpt`, `post_status`, `comment_status`, `post_modified`, `post_content_filtered`, `post_parent`, `post_type`, `post_mime_type`, `comment_count`, `smeta`, `post_hits`, `post_like`, `istop`, `recommended`, `page_tpl`, `page_tpls` ) VALUES  ('217','1','国土资源部公布我国油气资源家底','','2017-03-11 17:54:31','<p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\">　　6<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">13</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">日，国土资源部召开新闻通气会，公开发布</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">2015</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">全国油气资源动态评价成果。评价结果表明：我国油气资源总量丰富，非常规油气资源潜力可观，重点地区天然气资源大幅增长，尽管勘探开发难度逐步增大，但未来稳油增气有基础。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　据介绍，目前我国油气资源总量丰富。石油地质资源量</span>1257<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">亿吨、可采资源量</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">301</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">亿吨，与</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">2007</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年全国油气资源评价结果相比，石油地质与可采资源量分别增加</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">64%</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">和</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">42%</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">。天然气地质资源量</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">90.3</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">万亿立方米、可采资源量</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">50.1</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">万亿立方米，与</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">2007</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年全国油气资源评价结果相比，天然气地质与可采资源量分别增加</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">158%</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">和</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">127%</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">。资源量大幅增长的主要原因是勘探工作量的增加和地质认识的深化拓展了勘探领域，技术的进步降低了资源的门槛。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　非常规油气资源潜力可观。全国埋深</span>4500<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">米以浅页岩气地质资源量</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">122</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">万亿立方米，可采资源量</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">22</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">万亿立方米，具有现实可开发价值的有利区可采资源量</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">5.5</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">万亿立方米。埋深</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">2000</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">米以浅煤层气地质资源量</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">30</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">万亿立方米，可采资源量</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">12.5</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">万亿立方米，具有现实可开发价值的有利区可采资源量</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">4</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">万亿立方米。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　可喜的是，重点地区天然气资源大幅增长。四川盆地天然气地质资源量</span>20.7<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">万亿立方米、可采资源量</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">11.2</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">万亿立方米，与</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">2007</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年评价相比，分别增长</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">2.8</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">倍和</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">2.3</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">倍。近海海域各盆地天然气地质资源量</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">20.8</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">万亿立方米、可采资源量</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">12.2</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">万亿立方米，与</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">2007</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年评价相比，分别增长</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">157%</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">和</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">132%</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">。此外，鄂尔多斯、塔里木等盆地天然气资源量也有较大增长。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　油气勘探开发难度逐步增大。首先，剩余资源品质整体降低，</span>80%<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">的油气资源为低品质、高风险类型，煤层气和页岩气尚处于局部突破、全面探索阶段。其次，勘探开发对象复杂化，资源隐蔽性增强，发现难度加大，施工难度增加，对技术装备水平的要求不断提高，生态文明建设也对油气勘探开发提出高要求。尽管如此，未来稳油增气仍有基础。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　下一步，我国将重点在大型盆地的新层系、新领域和海域寻找优质储量，形成</span>“东部可持续、西部快发展、海域大突破”的油气勘探开发格局。</span></p><p><br/></p>','国土资源部公布我国油气资源家底','　　6月13日，国土资源部召开新闻通气会，公开发布2015全国油气资源动态评价成果。评价结果表明：我国油气资源总量丰富，非常规油气资源潜力可观，重点地区天然气资源大幅增长，尽管勘探开发难度逐步增大，但未来稳油增气有基础。','1','1','2017-03-11 17:53:23','','0','','','0','{\"thumb\":\"\"}','0','0','0','0','','');INSERT INTO ts_posts ( `id`, `post_author`, `post_keywords`, `post_source`, `post_date`, `post_content`, `post_title`, `post_excerpt`, `post_status`, `comment_status`, `post_modified`, `post_content_filtered`, `post_parent`, `post_type`, `post_mime_type`, `comment_count`, `smeta`, `post_hits`, `post_like`, `istop`, `recommended`, `page_tpl`, `page_tpls` ) VALUES  ('218','1','新修订《生产安全事故应急预案管理办法》公布','','2017-03-11 17:55:22','<p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　记者从国家安全生产监督管理总局了解到，新修订的《生产安全事故应急预案管理办法》（以下简称</span>“办法”）将于<span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">2016</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">7</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">1</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">日起施行。“办法”的制定将能更好地规范生产安全事故应急预案管理工作，迅速有效处置生产安全事故。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\">　　“办法”规定，应急预案的管理实行属地为主、分级负责、分类指导、综合协调、动态管理的原则。生产经营单位主要负责人负责组织编制和实施本单位的应急预案，并对应急预案的真实性和实用性负责。生产经营单位应急预案分为综合应急预案、专项应急预案和现场处置方案。</span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\">　　“办法”规定，应急预案的编制应当遵循以人为本、依法依规、符合实际、注重实效的原则，以应急处置为核心，明确应急职责、规范应急程序、细化保障措施。</span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\">　　“办法”规定，易燃易爆物品、危险化学品等危险物品的生产、经营、储存企业，使用危险化学品达到国家规定数量的化工企业，应当每<span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">3</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年进行一次应急预案评估。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　生产经营单位发生事故时，应当第一时间启动应急响应，组织力量救援，并按规定将事故信息及应急响应启动情况报告安全生产监督管理部门和其他负有安全生产监督管理职责的部门。</span></span></p><p><br/></p>','新修订《生产安全事故应急预案管理办法》公布','　　记者从国家安全生产监督管理总局了解到，新修订的《生产安全事故应急预案管理办法》（以下简称“办法”）将于2016年7月1日起施行。“办法”的制定将能更好地规范生产安全事故应急预案管理工作，迅速有效处置生产安全事故。','1','1','2017-03-11 17:54:45','','0','','','0','{\"thumb\":\"\"}','1','0','0','0','','');INSERT INTO ts_posts ( `id`, `post_author`, `post_keywords`, `post_source`, `post_date`, `post_content`, `post_title`, `post_excerpt`, `post_status`, `comment_status`, `post_modified`, `post_content_filtered`, `post_parent`, `post_type`, `post_mime_type`, `comment_count`, `smeta`, `post_hits`, `post_like`, `istop`, `recommended`, `page_tpl`, `page_tpls` ) VALUES  ('219','1','产业绿色发展路径','','2017-03-11 17:58:12','<p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\">　 &nbsp;<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">应对气候变化，建立绿色低碳经济不仅是世界的共同责任，也是中国的担当。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　记者从</span>13<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">日至</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">14</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">日举办的“第二届绿色经济与气候变化国际合作会议”了解到，发改委、工信部、能源局等部门在能源结构、工业制造等多领域，制定了绿色发展的规划和路径。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　发改委：正抓紧全国碳交易市场建设顶层设计</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　国家发改委副主任张勇表示，发改委将加快推动经济发展方式向绿色低碳转型，具体措施包括推动产业绿色低碳循环发展、探索低碳发展新模式、加快形成市场化减碳新机制、主动适应气候变化不利影响和积极参与全球气候治理。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　在推动产业绿色低碳循环发展方面，发改委将加快发展节能低碳环保等战略性新兴产业和服务业，加快推进能源生产和消费革命，探索集约、智能、绿色、低碳的新型城镇化模式，推广绿色建筑和新能源交通工具。将低碳作为推进供给侧结构性改革和大众创业、万众创新的重要抓手。推进工业、能源、建筑、交通等重点领域的低碳发展。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　在探索低碳发展新模式上，发改委将把低碳城市试点扩大到</span>100<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">个；深化低碳城市、低碳园区和低碳社区试点，形成一批可复制、可推广的低碳发展典型案例；探索近零碳发展模式。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　在发挥市场机制方面，发改委将加快出台《碳排放权交易管理条例》及实施细则，强化全国碳排放交易法规的支撑，确保</span>2017<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年全国碳排放权交易市场启动运行。“目前碳排放权交易试点进展顺利，全国碳排放交易市场建设稳步推进。全国碳交易市场建设顶层设计正在抓紧进行，将覆盖石化、化工、建材、钢铁、有色、造纸、电力、航空八个行业，占全国的碳排放量将达到</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">40%</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">—</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">50%</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">。”张勇说。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　工信部：已编制《绿色制造工程实施指南</span>(2016-2020<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">)</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">》</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\">　　“工信部已经编制了《绿色制造工程实施指南<span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">(2016-2020</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">)</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">》，将以此为组织实施绿色制造工程的抓手，全面推行绿色制造，力争率先实现《中国制造</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">2025</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">》的绿色发展目标。”工信部办公厅主任莫玮说，“十三五”期间，工信部将全面推行绿色制造，加快构建高效、清洁、低碳、循环的绿色制造体系。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　中国工业总体仍处于产业链中低端，资源、能源消耗较高，全面推行绿色制造是推动中国经济可持续发展的必然要求。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　莫玮说，工信部把实施绿色制造工程作为全面推行绿色制造的切入点，重点实施传统制造业绿色化改造，推进资源循环利用绿色发展，推动绿色制造技术创新及产业化，构建涵盖绿色产品、绿色工厂、绿色园区、绿色供应链的绿色制造体系。建设绿色制造服务平台，依托</span>‘一带一路’推进绿色制造产业合作，实施节能环保产业“走出去”工程，推动在沿线国家和地区建设绿色制造示范项目，加强绿色低碳技术装备和产业等方面的国际合作。</span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　工信部的数据显示，</span>2015<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年，中国能源消费总量为</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">43</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">亿吨标准煤，其中煤炭消费量约占</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">64%</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">。工业作为资源、能源消耗的主要领域，其能源消耗约占全社会的</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">70%</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">，大宗资源和水资源的消耗量占全社会的</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">90%</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">以上和</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">25%</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">左右。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　能源局：全面推进电动汽车充电设施建设</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　国家能源局副局长王晓林说，</span>“十三五”期间，中国将大力发展绿色能源，并将从供给侧和需求侧两端采取具体举措。</span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　在供给侧优化能源结构方面，中国将增加天然气供给；大力发展水电，特别是重点开发西南地区的水电资源，积极有序推进大型水电建设；安全发展核电；大力发展风电，力争到</span>2020<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年，风电装机达到</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">2.1</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">亿千瓦；大力发展太阳能，力争到</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">2020</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年，光伏装机达到</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">1.1</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">亿千瓦；积极开发利用生物质能、地热能等新能源，争取到</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">2020</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年，地热能利用规模达到</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">5</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">千万吨标准煤。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　在需求侧挖掘潜力方面，王晓林说，一方面是坚持集约优先战略。力争到</span>2020<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年，一次能源消费总量控制在</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">50</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">亿吨标准煤以内，煤炭消费总量控制在</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">41</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">亿吨以内。另一方面是培育新型能源消费业态，包括大力发展绿色交通，推进清洁能源汽车，全面推进电动汽车充电设施建设，加快发展轨道交通等。推进新能源城市建设，实施绿色建筑行动计划，加快绿色建筑建设和既有建筑的改造，推广节能电器和绿色照明。有序替代散煤和燃油消费，在居民采暖、工农业生产等领域，因地制宜发展电采暖、电锅炉等项目。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　国家电网：</span>2020<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年基本建成中国能源互联网</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　国家电网公司副总经理杨庆说，预计到</span>2020<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年，中国将形成统一电网，基本建成中国能源互联网。届时，西南地区的清洁能源、可再生能源可通过中国能源互联网传输到东部地区。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　杨庆说，围绕构建全球能源互联网的目标，国家电网公司已经在资源评估、科技攻关、装备研制、组织建设、规划研究、示范工程等方面做了大量工作，并取得重要进展和成果，包括积极推进蒙古到天津、俄罗斯到河北、新疆到巴基斯坦的电力互联工程，与俄罗斯电网、日本软银、韩国电力签署了合作协议，推动东北亚电网的互联互通。</span></span></p><p><br/></p>','多部委勾画产业绿色发展路径','　  应对气候变化，建立绿色低碳经济不仅是世界的共同责任，也是中国的担当。','1','1','2017-03-11 17:57:35','','0','','','0','{\"thumb\":\"\"}','1','0','0','0','','');INSERT INTO ts_posts ( `id`, `post_author`, `post_keywords`, `post_source`, `post_date`, `post_content`, `post_title`, `post_excerpt`, `post_status`, `comment_status`, `post_modified`, `post_content_filtered`, `post_parent`, `post_type`, `post_mime_type`, `comment_count`, `smeta`, `post_hits`, `post_like`, `istop`, `recommended`, `page_tpl`, `page_tpls` ) VALUES  ('220','1',' 原油市场将在年底达到平衡','','2017-03-11 17:59:34','<p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　欧佩克在</span>13<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">日发布的月报中维持对</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">2016</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年全球原油需求和供给预期不变，并表示随着原油供需情况进一步明朗，全球经济环境的改善将推动原油市场在今年底前达到平衡。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　欧佩克在月报中指出，原油价格走强主要受到美元疲软、美国汽油消费强劲、多地供应中断、美国原油产出加速下滑以及预期今年非欧佩克原油供应将大幅下降等因素的提振。此外，投机者对原油期货创纪录的多头押注也支撑了市场情绪。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　欧佩克表示，尽管今年伊始表现疲软，但预计全球经济在今年剩余时间内将有所反弹，全年增速达到</span>3.1%<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">，高于去年的</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">2.9%</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">。预计下半年全球原油日均需求将较去年同期增长</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">120</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">万桶，其中经合组织原油日均需求预计增长</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">20</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">万桶，非经合组织增长</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">100</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">万桶。非经合组织原油需求增长很大一部分来自印度，目前印度的宏观经济指标表现稳健。预计中国的原油需求增长将主要来自于运输和石化行业，而工业燃料消费将下降。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　供应方面，欧佩克预计下半年非欧佩克日均原油供应量将较上半年减少</span>14<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">万桶，较去年同期减少</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">100</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">万桶。美国方面，尽管墨西哥湾产出增长，但整体日均产出将较上半年下降</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">15</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">万桶。</span></span></p><p><br/></p>','欧佩克：原油市场将在年底达到平衡','　　欧佩克在13日发布的月报中维持对2016年全球原油需求和供给预期不变，并表示随着原油供需情况进一步明朗，全球经济环境的改善将推动原油市场在今年底前达到平衡。','1','1','2017-03-11 17:58:39','','0','','','0','{\"thumb\":\"\"}','1','0','0','0','','');INSERT INTO ts_posts ( `id`, `post_author`, `post_keywords`, `post_source`, `post_date`, `post_content`, `post_title`, `post_excerpt`, `post_status`, `comment_status`, `post_modified`, `post_content_filtered`, `post_parent`, `post_type`, `post_mime_type`, `comment_count`, `smeta`, `post_hits`, `post_like`, `istop`, `recommended`, `page_tpl`, `page_tpls` ) VALUES  ('221','1','高库存将压制油价','','2017-03-11 18:14:46','<p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　国际能源署</span>(IEA)14<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">日发布的月度报告称，庞大的库存压力将抑制油价上涨，这与</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">13</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">日石油输出国组织</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">(OPEC)</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月度石油报告的观点一致。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　美国油田技术服务公司贝克休斯发布的数据显示，截至</span>6<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">10</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">日的一周，美国运营的油田钻井数量连续第二周上涨。这显示，近期油价反弹已令美国页岩油厂商开始增产，不利油价回升。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\">　　</span><strong><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;font-size: 14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">庞大库存待消化</span></span></strong></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　国际能源署报告指出，全球经济增势稳定，全球原油需求稳步回升，而加拿大火灾、尼日利亚局势和美国页岩油产量下降等因素却导致供应下滑。这些因素推动国际油价近期向着每桶</span>50<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">元的关键价位回升，供需正在逐步恢复平衡，预计将在今年年底达到供需平衡。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　国际能源署表示，尽管如此，原油市场仍然有庞大的库存有待消化，并很可能会抑制油价的明显回升。国际能源署表示，对于高库存的担忧已经导致国际油价从上个月每桶</span>51<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">美元的近一年高点回落。但目前原油库存少于预期。由于产量减少导致的供应量减少，而消费增长却强于预期，今年上半年每日供应较需求多出</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">80</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">万桶，比</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">1</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">个月前的估计减少了约</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">40%</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　在供应方面，国际能源署指出，目前也存在一系列变动因素令原油市场面临巨大的不确定性，比如伊朗的大幅度增产，利比亚的政治危机和尼日利亚局势可能会导致产量减少，加拿大在经历大火后恢复产量尚需时日，以及油价回升趋势下美国的石油产量也可能随之回升，等等。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　在西方国家解除了对伊朗的制裁措施后，目前伊朗正在大幅增加原油产量。国际能源署表示，今年伊朗是</span>OPEC<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">中产量增长最快的成员，其产量已经达到近</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">5</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年高点。由于油价近期持续回升，限制原油产量的压力也在减少，</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">OPEC</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">本月早些时候的关键会议未能就冻结原油产量的事宜达成一致。</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">OPEC</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">主要成员沙特阿拉伯表示，对目前的原油市场感到满意。国际能源署表示，这一立场向市场发出了明确的信号。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　在需求方面，低油价有利于促进消费的增长。国际能源署预计，全球原油需求预计今年平均每日将增长</span>130<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">万桶，高于原先预计的每日</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">120</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">万桶，明年平均每日将增长</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">130</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">万桶。今年的原油需求预计为每日</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">9610</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">万桶，比之前的预估略高</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">10</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">万桶。一些经合组织之外的成员将为原油需求提供强劲的增长动力，其中印度将引领需求的增长，韩国和中国的需求也料将强劲增长。在美国市场，自去年年底遭遇增长疲态之后，最近数月增速正在加快，也将为需求增长提供强劲动力。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　国际油价自今年</span>2<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月降至每桶</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">25</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">美元左右的低点后，目前已经大幅反弹至每桶</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">48</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">美元的水平，但是与</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">2014</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年超过</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">100</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">美元的高点相比仍然有很大距离。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\">　</span><strong><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;font-size: 14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　供过于求局面改善</span></span></strong></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　国际能源署的报告与</span>13<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">日</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">OPEC</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">的月度石油报告观点类似。</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">OPEC</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">在月度报告中指出，全球原油市场供过于求的局面正在改善，今年年底将更加平衡，但库存压力也令投资者不看好油价长期的回升前景。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\">　　OPEC<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">表示，油价回升的原因包括美元走弱，美国页岩油产量降低，以及非</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">OPEC</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">国家原油产量预计将下滑，其中包括加拿大火灾引起的减产，尼日利亚紧张局势以及法国炼油厂罢工等因素。</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">OPEC</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">也认为稳固的全球经济增长将有助于需求回升，预计今年下半年全球原油需求每日将增长</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">120</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">万桶，今年全球原油需求将达到每日</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">9418</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">万桶。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　但</span>OPEC<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">仍然警告称，目前原油库存仍然远高于需求，且库存压力依然巨大。对高库存的担忧情绪令一些</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">5</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月份开始再次进入市场的投资者，对于原油市场长期投资前景的热情在月底明显减弱。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　有分析指出，国际能源署和</span>OPEC<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">的报告均向市场传递了多重信息。一方面指出原油需求增势好于预期，另一方面警告称高库存压力下，原油价格仍然可能出现下滑。这愈加显示出，国际原油市场正在趋于达成新的平衡状态，在产能过剩时，油价下跌导致产量减少，支撑油价回升，因此油价不会跌至过低水平；但竞争中产油国仍不会大幅减产，原油市场不会再现供不应求局面，因此油价也难以回升至以往超过每桶</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">100</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">美元那样的高水平。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\">&nbsp;</span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　国际能源署的报告发布后，国际油价</span>14<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">日连续第四个交易日下滑。截至</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">14</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">日收盘时，纽约商品交易所</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">7</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月交货的轻质原油期货价格下跌</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">0.39</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">美元，收于每桶</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">48.49</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">美元。</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">8</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月交货的伦敦布伦特原油期货价格下跌</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">0.52</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">美元，收于每桶</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">49.83</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">美元。</span></span></p><p><br/></p>','国际能源署：高库存将压制油价','　　国际能源署(IEA)14日发布的月度报告称，庞大的库存压力将抑制油价上涨，这与13日石油输出国组织(OPEC)月度石油报告的观点一致。','1','1','2017-03-11 18:13:19','','0','','','0','{\"thumb\":\"\"}','1','0','0','0','','');INSERT INTO ts_posts ( `id`, `post_author`, `post_keywords`, `post_source`, `post_date`, `post_content`, `post_title`, `post_excerpt`, `post_status`, `comment_status`, `post_modified`, `post_content_filtered`, `post_parent`, `post_type`, `post_mime_type`, `comment_count`, `smeta`, `post_hits`, `post_like`, `istop`, `recommended`, `page_tpl`, `page_tpls` ) VALUES  ('222','1','全国成品油价格指数小幅下行','','2017-03-11 18:15:38','<p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　依据新华</span>(<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">大庆</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">)</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">国际石油资讯中心发布的报告</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">,</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">截至</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">6</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">15</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">日</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">,</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">全国成品油价格指数为</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">602.76,</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">跌幅</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">0.12%,</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">全国成品油价格指数小幅下行。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　全国成品油价格指数运行结果表明</span>,<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">上周</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">93#</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">汽油平均价格报收于</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">6053</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">元／吨</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">,</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">较前一报告周期下降</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">55</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">元／吨</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">(</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">折合</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">0.04</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">元／升</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">);0#</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">柴油平均价格报收于</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">5074</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">元／吨</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">,</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">较前一报告周期上涨</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">17</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">元／吨</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">(</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">折合</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">0.01</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">元／升</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">)</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">。综合来看</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">,</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">全国汽油平均价格下跌带动全国成品油价格指数小幅下行。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　新华</span>(<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">大庆</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">)</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">国际石油资讯中心分析师蒋冰认为</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">,</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">因美元走强及美国原油库存升高</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">,</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">国际油价持续走低。国内成品油市场交投清淡</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">,</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">市场价格以稳定为主。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　蒋冰分析认为</span>,<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">本周国际原油期货价格受多种因素影响持续下行</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">,</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">目前一揽子原油平均价格变化率正向收窄</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">,</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">业者购销情绪萎靡。近期国内大部分地区持续阴雨天气</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">,</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">油品销售受到影响</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">,</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">抑制业者的投资热情</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">,</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">市场成交较为清淡</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">,</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">各地油品价格多以稳定为主。地炼汽油行情较为稳定</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">,</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">柴油延续上涨行情</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">,</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">出货较好。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　国际市场方面</span>,<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">美国石油协会</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">(API)</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">近日公布的数据远超预期</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">,</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">库欣原油库存增加</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">,</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">该消息利空国际油价。观望后市</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">,</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">美国活跃钻井数上升</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">,</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">原油日产量增加且本周原油库存意外增加</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">,</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">供应过剩格局未改</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">,</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">预计短期内国际油价或将继续承压。</span></span></p><p><br/></p>','全国成品油价格指数小幅下行','　　依据新华(大庆)国际石油资讯中心发布的报告,截至6月15日,全国成品油价格指数为602.76,跌幅0.12%,全国成品油价格指数小幅下行。','1','1','2017-03-11 18:14:59','','0','','','0','{\"thumb\":\"\"}','1','0','0','0','','');INSERT INTO ts_posts ( `id`, `post_author`, `post_keywords`, `post_source`, `post_date`, `post_content`, `post_title`, `post_excerpt`, `post_status`, `comment_status`, `post_modified`, `post_content_filtered`, `post_parent`, `post_type`, `post_mime_type`, `comment_count`, `smeta`, `post_hits`, `post_like`, `istop`, `recommended`, `page_tpl`, `page_tpls` ) VALUES  ('223','1','油价“五连涨”','','2017-03-11 18:17:20','<p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　国际油价先抑后涨的行情下，国内油价</span>“五连涨”或将落空。记者从多家社会监测机构了解到，目前原油变化率仍处于低位，<span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">6</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">23</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">日国内成品油零售价将迎来新一轮调价窗口，届时大概率因涨幅不足</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">50</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">元</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">/</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">吨而出现年内首次调价搁浅，汽油全面回归“</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">6</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">时代”尚需时日。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　随着支持英国留欧投票的增加、美国股市上涨的影响，近两日原油出现持续大涨。其中，</span>WTI<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">累计上涨</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">3.16</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">美元</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">/</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">桶，涨幅在</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">6.84%</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">，布伦特累计上涨</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">3.46</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">美元</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">/</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">桶，涨幅在</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">7.33%</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　但国内油价调整参考的原油变化率仍处于低位。卓创资讯监测数据显示，截至</span>6<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">20</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">日</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">(</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">调整期第</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">8</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">个工作日</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">)</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">，参考原油变化率为</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">0.36%</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">，对应上调</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">15</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">元</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">/</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">吨。“即便剩余两日原油保持每日</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">1</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">美元</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">/</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">桶的上涨趋势，变化率也难有大的反弹，汽柴油上调幅度仍会低于每吨</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">50</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">元，本轮油价调整仍面临较大概率搁浅的局面。”卓创资讯分析师胡慧春称。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　安迅思成品油行业分析师王玫元也表示，截至</span>6<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">20</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">日，安迅思成品油价格变化率指数为</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">0.54%</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">，国内汽柴油零售预计上涨幅度约</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">20</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">元</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">/</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">吨。根据目前国际原油走势分析，未来两日国际原油或继续反弹，但幅度将收窄，变化率仍将维持小幅波动，本次调价或因幅度不足而搁浅。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　卓创资讯统计数据显示，截至本次调价，今年共经历</span>12<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">次调价窗口，其中，</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">1</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">次下调，</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">4</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">次上调，</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">1</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">次搁浅，</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">6</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">次不做调整。涨跌互抵后，汽油累计上涨</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">465</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">元</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">/</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">吨，柴油累计上涨</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">450</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">元</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">/</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">吨，目前仅有实施国五汽油标准的省市</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">92</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">号处于</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">6</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">元之上。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　王玫元介绍说，国内柴油受国际原油持续下跌影响，加之北方农忙结束，需求下行。而汽油虽然将进入需求旺季，但全国各地持续雨季，一定程度上抑制汽油销量。加之本轮零售价调整或将搁浅，目前下游库存消耗速度放缓，业者仍将谨慎操作为主，市场成交仍将以小单为主，购销气氛难有改善。整体来看，近期国内汽柴油行情将稳中小跌。</span></span></p><p><br/></p>','油价“五连涨”或落空 年内料将首次搁浅','　　国际油价先抑后涨的行情下，国内油价“五连涨”或将落空。记者从多家社会监测机构了解到，目前原油变化率仍处于低位，6月23日国内成品油零售价将迎来新一轮调价窗口，届时大概率因涨幅不足50元/吨而出现年内首次调价搁浅，汽油全面回归“6时代”尚需时日。','1','1','2017-03-11 18:15:52','','0','','','0','{\"thumb\":\"\"}','1','0','0','0','','');INSERT INTO ts_posts ( `id`, `post_author`, `post_keywords`, `post_source`, `post_date`, `post_content`, `post_title`, `post_excerpt`, `post_status`, `comment_status`, `post_modified`, `post_content_filtered`, `post_parent`, `post_type`, `post_mime_type`, `comment_count`, `smeta`, `post_hits`, `post_like`, `istop`, `recommended`, `page_tpl`, `page_tpls` ) VALUES  ('224','1','低碳交通','','2017-03-11 18:18:50','<p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\">　　6<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月上旬，在第二届中美气候智慧型</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">/</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">低碳城市峰会期间，能源与交通创新中心（</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">iCET</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">）承办了“低碳交通大变革”分论坛，探讨在新时代、新驱动背景下，寻求如何利用新技术、新模式与新机制来加速交通低碳化、清洁化进程，来自中美城市市长、各级政府交通主管领导，研究机构、汽车企业、互联网出行平台行业领袖就中美两国汽车电动化、智能化、互联化技术创新，共享出行模式、大数据应用与互联交通等话题进行了探讨。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　北京市交通委副主任李晓松从交通体系完善到交通能源结构优化等方面介绍了北京在推动低碳交通方面的努力，截至</span>2015<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年底，北京公共领域推广新清能源车</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">2.2</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">万辆，私人领域推广</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">1.34</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">万辆，每年可减少汽柴油消耗</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">3.4</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">亿升。中国汽车工业协会常务副会长董扬表示，美、日、欧等以市场驱动为主，中国以政府推动与市场驱动并行的模式，催生了大量的电动汽车制造者、基础设施构建者和无数先驱使用者，催化了技术与市场的成熟，他预计未来中国新能源汽车将会以更快的速度发展。他还呼吁关注智能汽车的发展。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　同期举行的</span>“低碳城市发展的监测和评估”分论坛中，也就降低能源需求、支持低碳创新、降低清洁能源技术成本、实现清洁技术规模化应用，以及低碳试点提出了政策性建议。</span></p><p><br/></p>','低碳交通让汽车“口粮”清洁','　　6月上旬，在第二届中美气候智慧型/低碳城市峰会期间，能源与交通创新中心（iCET）承办了“低碳交通大变革”分论坛，探讨在新时代、新驱动背景下，寻求如何利用新技术、新模式与新机制来加速交通低碳化、清洁化进程，来自中美城市市长、各级政府交通主管领导，研究机构、汽车企业、互联网出行平台行业领袖就中美两国汽车电动化、智能化、互联化技术创新，共享出行模式、大数据应用与互联交通等话题进行了探讨。','1','1','2017-03-11 18:17:42','','0','','','0','{\"thumb\":\"\"}','0','0','0','0','','');INSERT INTO ts_posts ( `id`, `post_author`, `post_keywords`, `post_source`, `post_date`, `post_content`, `post_title`, `post_excerpt`, `post_status`, `comment_status`, `post_modified`, `post_content_filtered`, `post_parent`, `post_type`, `post_mime_type`, `comment_count`, `smeta`, `post_hits`, `post_like`, `istop`, `recommended`, `page_tpl`, `page_tpls` ) VALUES  ('225','1','国家安监总局对重点工作进行安排部署','','2017-03-11 18:19:52','<p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　为深刻吸取事故教训，督促有关地区和中央企业认清形势，切实贯彻落实今年重点工作安排部署，有效防范遏制化工和危化品重特大事故，</span>6<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">24</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">日，国家安全监管总局分别召开遏制危化品较大以上事故专题会议和中央企业事故警示会议。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　会议指出，今年年初以来，全国未发生化工重特大事故，同比减少</span>1<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">起，但发生化工较大事故</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">11</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">起、死亡</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">32</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">人，较大事故多发势头仍未得到有效遏制，化工和危化品安全生产形势依然严峻复杂。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　会议强调，各级安全监管部门要充分认清形势，进一步增强做好化工和危化品安全生产工作的责任感、紧迫感和使命感，加大工作力度，狠抓工作落实，重心前移，抓早抓小，抓小防大，以全力遏制化工和危化品较大以上事故为手段，严防重特大事故发生。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　会议要求，有关中央企业要深刻吸取事故教训，在举一反三上狠下功夫；要加强对安全生产工作重要性、科学性、系统性、紧迫性的再认识，切实提高对安全生产工作的准确认知水平；要全面深入排查风险，加快构建风险防控、隐患治理及事故前期处置三重屏障；要积极采用先进的技术和管理理念，进一步做好化工和危化品安全生产工作。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　会议指出，当前正处于夏季，高温、雷电、暴雨天气频繁，是化工和危化品事故易发期，各地要高度重视夏季化工和危化品安全生产工作，采取针对性措施，坚决遏制重特大事故。</span></span></p><p><br/></p>','国家安监总局对重点工作进行安排部署','　　为深刻吸取事故教训，督促有关地区和中央企业认清形势，切实贯彻落实今年重点工作安排部署，有效防范遏制化工和危化品重特大事故，6月24日，国家安全监管总局分别召开遏制危化品较大以上事故专题会议和中央企业事故警示会议。','1','1','2017-03-11 18:19:03','','0','','','0','{\"thumb\":\"\"}','0','0','0','0','','');INSERT INTO ts_posts ( `id`, `post_author`, `post_keywords`, `post_source`, `post_date`, `post_content`, `post_title`, `post_excerpt`, `post_status`, `comment_status`, `post_modified`, `post_content_filtered`, `post_parent`, `post_type`, `post_mime_type`, `comment_count`, `smeta`, `post_hits`, `post_like`, `istop`, `recommended`, `page_tpl`, `page_tpls` ) VALUES  ('226','1','去产能要遵循市场原则','','2017-03-11 18:21:29','<p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　世界经济论坛</span>2016<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年新领军者年会</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">(</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">第十届“夏季达沃斯论坛”</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">)</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">于</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">6</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">26</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">日至</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">28</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">日在天津举办。国务院总理李克强今日上午会见出席论坛的企业家代表。在回答代表关于化解过剩产能的问题时，李克强表示，我们既要坚定地淘汰落后产能，又要遵循市场化的原则。毫无疑问，我们还要保障职工的合法权益，政府有责任。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　【文字实录】</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　美国铝业公司董事会主席兼首席执行官柯菲德：刚才您谈到了</span>“云”的重要性，那么我的问题要从“云”转到重工业，虽然重工业也产生很多的云彩。中国政府一直在下大力气解决过剩产能的问题，过剩产能也受到了国际社会的广泛关注，包括国际媒体的高度关注。我知道中国为应对该问题已经出台了一系列的政策措施，所以我的问题就是想具体问中国政府将如何实际应对去产能将对中国经济、社会等方面产生的影响？</span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　国务院总理李克强：刚才我们讨论了好像浮在天上的</span>“云”，你也讲到我们现在要看看立在地上的重工业。实际上这两者之间已经在发生密切联系，云计算正在对传统工业倾注很大的力量，通过搜集传统工业的数据，使它们能够找到新的路径进行改造，而重工业本身正是云计算能够产生的基础之一。</span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　重工业是传统工业，但是我们也不能放弃重工业，因为没有重工业，在座各位拿的手机的许多材料就没有来源。我们现在去产能要去的是过剩的重工业产能，是落后的重工业产能。而这种过剩的重工业产能是世界经济复苏乏力、贸易增长低迷造成的，需要各国共同来应对。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　中国在某些行业确实有过剩产能，这几年来我们一直在消化这些过剩产能，淘汰落后产能。中国的决心是坚定的，既为解决国内的问题，也是履行一个负责任大国的责任。但是有一点我要强调，中国重工业的过剩产能主要是面向国内市场，是受到国内需求影响产生的过剩，并不是大量的出口。我们去年乃至今年</span>1-5<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月份出口是下降的。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　我们现在正在着力推进消化钢铁、煤炭产业的过剩产能，未来几年要消化</span>1<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">到</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">1.5</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">亿吨钢和</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">8</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">亿吨煤，涉及到近</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">200</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">万人的就业。但是因为我们的新经济、新业态支撑就业的能力超出预期，所以我们有能力来消化这些过剩产能，又能使工人转岗而不下岗。中央政府已经拿出</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">1000</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">亿元的资金，同时也要求地方政府有相应的配套资金，一起来使富余员工的安置能够得到比较妥善的安排。在这个过程当中，我们还是要坚持市场化、法治化的原则。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　我们不能用行政化的手段说哪个厂要关、哪个厂不关，还是要用环保、质量、标准等来使这些过剩的，甚至落后的产能淘汰。总而言之，我们既要坚定地淘汰落后产能，又要遵循市场化的原则。毫无疑问，我们还要保障职工的合法权益，政府有责任。在座的各位企业家，相信你们在经营当中都不缺履行社会责任的意识。</span></span></p><p><br/></p>','李克强：去产能要遵循市场原则 同时保障职工权益','　　世界经济论坛2016年新领军者年会(第十届“夏季达沃斯论坛”)于6月26日至28日在天津举办。国务院总理李克强今日上午会见出席论坛的企业家代表。在回答代表关于化解过剩产能的问题时，李克强表示，我们既要坚定地淘汰落后产能，又要遵循市场化的原则。毫无疑问，我们还要保障职工的合法权益，政府有责任。','1','1','2017-03-11 18:20:37','','0','','','0','{\"thumb\":\"\"}','1','0','0','0','','');INSERT INTO ts_posts ( `id`, `post_author`, `post_keywords`, `post_source`, `post_date`, `post_content`, `post_title`, `post_excerpt`, `post_status`, `comment_status`, `post_modified`, `post_content_filtered`, `post_parent`, `post_type`, `post_mime_type`, `comment_count`, `smeta`, `post_hits`, `post_like`, `istop`, `recommended`, `page_tpl`, `page_tpls` ) VALUES  ('227','1','国际油价29日上涨','','2017-03-11 18:30:10','<p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\">&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">国际油价</span>29<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">日上涨。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　美国能源信息局当天公布的原油数据显示，上周美国全国商业原油库存</span>5.266<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">亿桶，下降</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">410</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">万桶，连续第六周下降。这一数据当天利好油价。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　市场对欧盟出台应对措施以减少英国</span>“脱欧”的冲击有所期待，投资者避险情绪缓解。当天国际油价连续第二个交易日上涨。</span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　此外，美元走弱增加了以美元计价的石油的投资吸引力，当天也支撑了油价。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　截至当天收盘，纽约商品交易所</span>8<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月交货的轻质原油期货价格上涨</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">2.03</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">美元，收于每桶</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">49.88</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">美元，涨幅为</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">4.24%</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">。</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">8</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月交货的伦敦布伦特原油期货价格上涨</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">2.03</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">美元，收于每桶</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">50.61</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">美元，涨幅为</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">4.18%</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">。</span></span></p><p><br/></p>','国际油价29日上涨 纽约市场收于每桶49.88美元','    国际油价29日上涨。','1','1','2017-03-11 18:29:45','','0','','','0','{\"thumb\":\"\"}','0','0','0','0','','');INSERT INTO ts_posts ( `id`, `post_author`, `post_keywords`, `post_source`, `post_date`, `post_content`, `post_title`, `post_excerpt`, `post_status`, `comment_status`, `post_modified`, `post_content_filtered`, `post_parent`, `post_type`, `post_mime_type`, `comment_count`, `smeta`, `post_hits`, `post_like`, `istop`, `recommended`, `page_tpl`, `page_tpls` ) VALUES  ('228','1','我国将大力提高天然气消费规模和比重','','2017-03-11 18:31:19','<p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　国家能源局副局长李凡荣</span>29<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">日说，为保护大气环境、有效防治雾霾，中国政府已制定行动计划，将大力提高天然气消费规模和比重。预计到</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">2030</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年，天然气在我国一次能源消费中的比重将达到</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">15%</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">左右。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　李凡荣在当日举行的</span>“<span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">G20</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">天然气日”活动上介绍，天然气是清洁高效的化石能源，在供应稳定性、技术可行性和使用灵活性方面有独特优势。近年来，勘探开发技术的突破大幅提高了天然气开发水平，深刻改变了世界能源格局。同时，天然气的清洁性和灵活性使其在发电、交通等领域得到快速应用。从</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">2006</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年到</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">2015</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年，全球煤炭和石油消费比重下降了</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">2.3%</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">，天然气比重则提高了约</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">1%</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　他介绍，过去</span>10<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年间，中国天然气消费量年均增长</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">13%</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">以上。</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">2015</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年，中国天然气进口量比</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">2011</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年翻了一番。即便如此，天然气在中国仍有很大发展前景。目前，天然气在中国一次能源消费中的比例仅为</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">5.8%</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">，人均用气量仅为国际水平的三分之一。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　李凡荣说，在看到巨大潜力和机遇的同时，也不能忽视天然气行业面临的困难和挑战。天然气的成本特别是储存运输成本居高不下，在距离气田较远的市场，天然气在与低价传统化石能源的竞争中处于不利地位。此外，可再生能源在政策支持下快速发展，一旦储能技术取得重大突破，将可能从根本上改变现有能源格局，给天然气行业带来竞争压力。全行业要共同努力，降低成本，提高竞争力。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\">　　2016<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年二十国集团能源部长会议</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">29</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">日至</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">30</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">日在北京召开，“</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">G20</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">天然气日”活动是此次会议的一部分。 &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\">&nbsp;</span></p><p><br/></p>','我国将大力提高天然气消费规模和比重','　　国家能源局副局长李凡荣29日说，为保护大气环境、有效防治雾霾，中国政府已制定行动计划，将大力提高天然气消费规模和比重。预计到2030年，天然气在我国一次能源消费中的比重将达到15%左右。','1','1','2017-03-11 18:30:25','','0','','','0','{\"thumb\":\"\"}','0','0','0','0','','');INSERT INTO ts_posts ( `id`, `post_author`, `post_keywords`, `post_source`, `post_date`, `post_content`, `post_title`, `post_excerpt`, `post_status`, `comment_status`, `post_modified`, `post_content_filtered`, `post_parent`, `post_type`, `post_mime_type`, `comment_count`, `smeta`, `post_hits`, `post_like`, `istop`, `recommended`, `page_tpl`, `page_tpls` ) VALUES  ('229','1','油价第二季录得升幅超25%','','2017-03-11 18:32:28','<p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　据路透社报道，油价周四重挫逾</span>3%<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">，受尼日利亚及加拿大恢复原油供应拖累，且交易商在第二季末获利了结，油价本季录得七年最大升幅。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　第二季油价猛涨逾</span>25%<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">，在年初触及</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">12</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年低点后累积反弹</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">85%</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">，因加拿大和尼日利亚石油产量意外减少，缓和了拖累油价崩跌的供应过剩情况。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　不过，尼日利亚国有石油公司表示，该国日产油量已经由</span>160<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">万桶增至约</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">190</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">万桶，因尼日尔三角洲地区的输油管没有遭到新的大规模袭击。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　高盛表示，尼日利亚供应恢复将令油价承压，且加拿大野火造成停产也会在</span>9<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月前基本结束。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　路透调查显示，石油输出国组织</span>(OPEC)6<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月产油量增至历史最高，因尼日利亚石油生产部分恢复，以及伊朗和海湾成员国增产。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\">　　EnergyManagementInstitute<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">高级合伙人</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">DominickChirichella</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">表示，美国长周末假期前市场也遭遇一轮卖盘，周四午后市场流动性可能降低。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\">　　8<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月布兰特原油期货周四到期，收低</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">0.93</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">美元，或</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">1.8%</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">，报每桶</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">49.68</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">美元。交投更活跃的</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">9</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月合约结算价报</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">49.71</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">美元，重挫</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">3.1%</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　美国原油期货收挫</span>1.55<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">美元，或</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">3.1%</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">，报每桶</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">48.33</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">美元。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　交易商表示，在今日最后几分钟的交易中，布兰特和美国原油期货急跌超过</span>1<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">美元，因基金经理和基金要结清仓位，以确保账面上为获利。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　美国原油期货和布兰特原油期货在</span>6<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月基本持平。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\">　　“我预计未来六个月油市将继续呈区间波动。”<span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">McNamaraOptionsLLC</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">交易部门董事</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">AlanHarry</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">表示。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\">　　“我认为，如果今年驾车出游季的需求不够强劲，油价可能进一步回落，因仍须要应对供应严重过剩的事实。”</span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　挪威石油企业和工会开始为期两日的薪资谈判，以图避免罢工。罢工可能最初令挪威油气产量减少</span>6%<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">。</span></span></p><p><br/></p>','油价第二季录得升幅超25% 为七年最大','　　据路透社报道，油价周四重挫逾3%，受尼日利亚及加拿大恢复原油供应拖累，且交易商在第二季末获利了结，油价本季录得七年最大升幅。','1','1','2017-03-11 18:31:31','','0','','','0','{\"thumb\":\"\"}','0','0','0','0','','');INSERT INTO ts_posts ( `id`, `post_author`, `post_keywords`, `post_source`, `post_date`, `post_content`, `post_title`, `post_excerpt`, `post_status`, `comment_status`, `post_modified`, `post_content_filtered`, `post_parent`, `post_type`, `post_mime_type`, `comment_count`, `smeta`, `post_hits`, `post_like`, `istop`, `recommended`, `page_tpl`, `page_tpls` ) VALUES  ('230','1','油价调价窗口今日开启 ','','2017-03-11 18:33:31','<p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　新一轮成品油调价窗口将于</span>7<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">7</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">日</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">24</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">时开启。从国际油价走势来看，多家机构预测国内成品油调价将再次搁浅，出现“两连停”。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　据隆众石化网测算，截至</span>7<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">5</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">日，原油综合变化率为</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">-2.38%</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">，对应汽柴油下调幅度</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">45</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">元</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">/</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">吨。卓创资讯测算的原油变化率为</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">-1.08%</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">，预计对应下调幅度</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">20</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">元</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">/</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">吨。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　《石油价格管理办法》规定，</span>“当调价幅度低于每吨<span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">50</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">元时，不作调整，纳入下次调价时累加或冲抵”。因此，上述机构预测本次油价调整将出现搁浅。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　国内油价上一轮调价窗口为</span>6<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">23</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">日。由于国际油价在计价周期内小幅波动，对应的国内油价调整幅度低于每吨</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">50</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">元，所以价格暂不调整。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　在本轮计价周期内，国际油价持续震荡。英国退欧引发全球股市大跌，美元上扬，油价大跌；随后利空影响有所缓和，欧美股市回暖，美元回跌，交易商重新关注石油市场基本面，油价出现反弹。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　截至</span>7<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">5</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">日收盘时，当天，美国</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">WTI</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">原油期货主力合约下跌</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">2.39</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">美元，报每桶</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">46.6</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">美元；布伦特原油期货主力合约跌</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">2.14</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">美元，报每桶</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">47.96</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">美元。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　卓创资讯成品油分析师刘新章在接受中新网记者采访时指出，国内汽柴油零售价暂时不作调整，批发价出现下滑，这将推动加油站利润进一步提升。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　他说，受降雨增多影响，汽柴油终端需求减少，导致炼厂销售压力较大，进而致使汽柴油的批发价格出现下滑。从年初至今，对于</span>“吨进升出”的加油站来说，汽、柴油的利润空间累计扩大<span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">0.56</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">元</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">/</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">升及</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">0.64</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">元</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">/</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">升。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　今年以来，国内成品油已经历</span>12<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">次调价窗口，其中</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">4</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">次上调，</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">1</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">次下调，</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">7</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">次不作调整。据卓创资讯测算，涨跌互抵后，汽油零售限价累计上调</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">0.34</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">元</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">/</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">升，柴油累计上调</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">0.39</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">元</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">/</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">升。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　关于后期国际油价的走势，联讯证券在报告中指出，英国脱欧只在情绪上对油价产生冲击，一旦情绪平复，</span>“油价坑”就会自动填平。而且加拿大大火事件余温未了，加拿大原油产量的恢复恐怕短时间内难以实现，对油价仍会形成支撑。</span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　安迅思成品油行业助理分析师邹亚男表示，国际油价在年初低点之后于</span>4<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月份缓慢回升，至今已经站稳“地板价”上，并徘徊于</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">50</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">美元</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">/</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">桶附近，虽然短期内仍受到欧佩克产量增加、美国原油库存继续下降、全球需求增长及美元汇率变动等诸多因素影响，但有迹象表明，国际油价正在建立起新的平衡。</span></span></p><p><br/></p>','油价调价窗口今日开启 或再次搁浅出现“两连停”','　　新一轮成品油调价窗口将于7月7日24时开启。从国际油价走势来看，多家机构预测国内成品油调价将再次搁浅，出现“两连停”。','1','1','2017-03-11 18:32:42','','0','','','0','{\"thumb\":\"\"}','0','0','0','0','','');INSERT INTO ts_posts ( `id`, `post_author`, `post_keywords`, `post_source`, `post_date`, `post_content`, `post_title`, `post_excerpt`, `post_status`, `comment_status`, `post_modified`, `post_content_filtered`, `post_parent`, `post_type`, `post_mime_type`, `comment_count`, `smeta`, `post_hits`, `post_like`, `istop`, `recommended`, `page_tpl`, `page_tpls` ) VALUES  ('231','1','中企进军非洲新能源领域优势明显','','2017-03-11 18:34:39','<p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　中非之间的贸易和投资在过去二十年间飞速发展。</span>2015<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">12</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月，习近平主席在南非召开的中非合作论坛约翰内斯堡峰会上正式公布中非“十大合作计划”，其中引人注意的是，中方将使用多种融资方式，支持非洲光伏、生物质能等发电项目和输变电、电网项目的建设，从而助力非洲改善电力短缺掣肘经济增长的现状。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　在过去十余年间，中国新能源投资和装机容量迅速成长为全球第一，相关产业的快速发展也为全球新能源成本的大幅度下降立下汗马功劳。无论是中国政府还是产业界，已经积极参与到非洲的新能源建设中。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　中国新能源技术造福非洲</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　在人大重阳金融研究院近日举行的</span>&quot;<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">一带一路</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">&quot;</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">大背景下中非新能源合作展望”会议上，加州理工大学博士、中国人民大学重阳金融研究院客座研究员文佳筠介绍了中非能源合作中的机遇和挑战，对比了中国与欧美对非合作的不同之处，探讨了如何进一步深化对非新能源合作。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　目前，一批中国企业已经走进非洲开展可再生能源合作，项目涉及水电、太阳能、风能、生物质能、地热能等众多领域。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　文佳筠列举了中国企业在非洲建设的一些重要的新能源项目。其中，中国水电承建的赞比亚卡里巴水电站最大坝高</span>128<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">米，水库总库容</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">1840</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">亿立方米，是世界上蓄水量最大的水库之一。水资源由赞比亚和津巴布韦共享。该电站距赞比亚首都卢萨卡</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">192</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">公里，主要功能是发电。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　埃塞俄比亚阿达玛一期和二期风电工程是东非已完成的最大风电项目。中国进出口银行为该项目提供</span>85%<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">的融资支持，金风科技</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">(002202,</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">股吧</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">)</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">为项目提供风机。工程装机容量分别为</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">51</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">兆瓦和</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">153</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">兆瓦。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　此外，中国企业参与的新能源项目还有乌干达卡鲁玛水电站工程，该工程设计装机容量为</span>600<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">兆瓦，是乌最大的水电站；加纳布维水电站的装机容量是</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">400</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">兆瓦，年发电量</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">10</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">亿度；加纳阿科松博水电站大坝的总装机容量是</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">882</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">兆瓦；阳光能源控股有限公司于</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">2013</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年与加纳萨凡纳区域加速开发部签署合资协议书，成立合资公司，在加纳建设</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">200</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">兆瓦的太阳能电站项目；莱索托高地发电项目是非洲最大的新能源项目。中国为该项目提供</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">150</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">亿美元融资，中国明阳风电集团有限公司为项目提供风机。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　中国为非洲新能源发展贡献力量</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　根据国际能源署近日发布的一份报告，中国公司在过去几年为非洲撒哈拉以南地区修建了近三分之一的新电力设施。为了抵消日益趋缓的国内经济的影响，中国公司在海外市场大举扩张，于</span>2010<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年至</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">2015</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年在非洲撒哈拉以南地区完成了</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">30%</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">的新电力设施修建项目。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　上述报告预计，从</span>2010<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年至</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">2020</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年，中国公司在非洲撒哈拉以南地区已建成或已签订合约修建</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">17</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">座千兆瓦发电站，相当于芬兰同期修建的新电站总数。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　由于非洲巨大的能源潜力和普遍的电力短缺，可再生能源开发成为未来中非能源合作的一个重要方向。中国国家主席习近平近日在中非合作论坛峰会上倡议实施</span>“中非绿色发展合作计划”，在该计划项下，将实施<span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">50</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">个清洁能源和野生动植物保护项目，主要是与非方开展防灾减灾、野生动植物保护示范、环境治理、气象监测、清洁能源等方面的合作；还将实施</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">50</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">个环境友好型农业项目和智慧型城市建设项目，主要是帮助非方实施农业研发、种植、生产、仓储、加工等环境友好型农业合作项目。以及低碳城市规划、交通、建筑、智能电网、大数据有利于城市实现低碳环保的合作项目。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　中国企业优势明显</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　谈及中国与欧美对非合作的不同之处，文佳筠表示中国企业的优势明显，主要体现在执行力强、性价比高，没有殖民主义的历史负担。而欧美企业则在软实力以及高层设计方面拥有更多优势。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　她表示，欧美企业在参与非洲高层设计时拥有更多的话语权，软实力更强。</span>2015<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年巴黎气候大会许多非洲国家提交的减排计划都是在欧美国家协助下完成的。中国在对非新能源合作方面应该加强顶层设计，制定总体的发展规划，提高到战略层面。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　国务院参事、中国可再生能源学会理事长石定寰强调说，中国在对外合作方面</span>“重硬轻软”，虽然做了许多具体的项目，但是中国缺少具有国际影响力的人才和部门，主要以输出产品为主。因此在对外合作时，帮助提高当地软实力，协助当地制定总体战略、发展方向，注重当地人才的培养，长期发挥作用。中国的星火计划就是在世界银行的帮助下，依靠科学技术促进中国农村经济发展，以经济援助带动当地人才培养和能力提高。</span></p><p><br/></p>','中企进军非洲新能源领域优势明显','　　中非之间的贸易和投资在过去二十年间飞速发展。2015年12月，习近平主席在南非召开的中非合作论坛约翰内斯堡峰会上正式公布中非“十大合作计划”，其中引人注意的是，中方将使用多种融资方式，支持非洲光伏、生物质能等发电项目和输变电、电网项目的建设，从而助力非洲改善电力短缺掣肘经济增长的现状。','1','1','2017-03-11 18:33:43','','0','','','0','{\"thumb\":\"\"}','0','0','0','0','','');INSERT INTO ts_posts ( `id`, `post_author`, `post_keywords`, `post_source`, `post_date`, `post_content`, `post_title`, `post_excerpt`, `post_status`, `comment_status`, `post_modified`, `post_content_filtered`, `post_parent`, `post_type`, `post_mime_type`, `comment_count`, `smeta`, `post_hits`, `post_like`, `istop`, `recommended`, `page_tpl`, `page_tpls` ) VALUES  ('232','1','2020年石化民企主营收入将达6.5万亿元','','2017-03-11 18:35:35','<p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\">　　“十二五”期间，我国石油和化工行业民营企业取得长足发展。截至<span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">2015</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年底，民企主营业务收入已占全行业的</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">30.6%;</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">五年来，民企资产利润增长一直高于行业平均水平，获利能力和资产盈利能力明显优于行业平均水平，显示了民营企业的勃勃生机和良好成长性。这是</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">7</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">2</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">日在北京召开的</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">2016</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">中国石油和化工民营企业发展大会上传出的消息。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　本次大会评选出了</span>192<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">家优秀民营企业和</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">167</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">位优秀民营企业家。十届全国人大常委会副委员长顾秀莲在会上对民营企业取得的成就表示肯定。她指出，五年来，石油和化工民营企业抓住行业转型升级的新机遇，加快产业结构调整步伐，大批民营企业发展成为行业细分市场的龙头和骨干力量，逐步走上国际竞争的大舞台，向世界展现了中国石化行业的新形象。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　据联合会统计数据，截至</span>2015<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年底，石油和化学工业规模以上民营企业达到</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">16212</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">家，占行业规模以上企业总数的</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">54.5%;</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">实现主营业务收入</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">4.06</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">万亿元，占全行业主营业务收入总额的</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">30.9%;</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">资产总额</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">2.43</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">万亿元，占全行业资产总额的</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">20.1%;</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">利润总额</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">2404.61</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">亿元，占全行业利润总额的</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">47.3%;</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">上缴税金</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">1253.66</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">亿元，占全行业上缴税金总额的</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">12.2%</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">。民企在盈利能力上展现出优良的成长性，</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">2011</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">～</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">2015</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年，石油和化工民营企业年实现利润增速分别达到</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">48.7%</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">、</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">13.4%</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">、</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">12.8%</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">、</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">11.4%</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">和</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">2.5%</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">，而全行业利润只在</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">2011</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">和</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">2013</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年实现增长，增速分别为</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">19.0%</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">和</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">5.7%</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\">　　“我们的民营企业经受住了近几年经济下行、需求放缓、产品价格大幅下滑等的考验，显示出了体制灵活、市场反应灵敏、运营管理高效的优势。”中国石油和化学工业联合会会长李寿生表示。</span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　大会提出了</span>“十三五”期间全行业民营企业的发展目标：主营业务收入年平均增速达到<span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">10%</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">，到</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">2020</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年达到</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">6.5</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">万亿元，占全行业主营业务收入总额的比重达到</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">35%</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">以上</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">;</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">培育了一批具有较强国际竞争优势的大型民营企业和企业集团，到</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">2020</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年主营业务收入超过</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">1000</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">亿元以上的民营企业达到</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">5</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">家，</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">800</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">亿～</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">1000</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">亿元的民营企业达到</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">10</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">家，</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">500</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">亿～</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">800</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">亿元的民营企业达到</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">10</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">家</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">;</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">在能源化工、化工新材料、精细和专用化学品、节能环保等领域培育了一批“专、精、新、特”的创新型民营企业</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">;</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">民营企业的创新能力、盈利能力、竞争能力和抗风险能力进一步提升，成为推动我国由石油和化工大国向强国跨越的重要力量。</span></span></p><p><br/></p>','2020年石化民企主营收入将达6.5万亿元','　　“十二五”期间，我国石油和化工行业民营企业取得长足发展。截至2015年底，民企主营业务收入已占全行业的30.6%;五年来，民企资产利润增长一直高于行业平均水平，获利能力和资产盈利能力明显优于行业平均水平，显示了民营企业的勃勃生机和良好成长性。这是7月2日在北京召开的2016中国石油和化工民营企业发展大会上传出的消息。','1','1','2017-03-11 18:34:50','','0','','','0','{\"thumb\":\"\"}','0','0','0','0','','');INSERT INTO ts_posts ( `id`, `post_author`, `post_keywords`, `post_source`, `post_date`, `post_content`, `post_title`, `post_excerpt`, `post_status`, `comment_status`, `post_modified`, `post_content_filtered`, `post_parent`, `post_type`, `post_mime_type`, `comment_count`, `smeta`, `post_hits`, `post_like`, `istop`, `recommended`, `page_tpl`, `page_tpls` ) VALUES  ('233','1','国际石油市场走向再平衡','','2017-03-11 18:37:34','<p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　国际石油巨头、英国石油</span>BP<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">集团首席经济学家戴思攀</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">8</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">日在上海表示，当下全球石油需求正在快速增长，而供应增速放缓，预计今年下半年国际石油市场逐渐走向再平衡。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\">　　2014<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年下半年是全球石油市场的转折点。维持了数年高位的国际油价从每桶</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">100</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">美元上方一直跌到</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">2016</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年年初的</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">26</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">美元附近，全球石油产业遭受重创。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　戴思攀认为，</span>2014<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年国际油价大跌的根源在于供应过剩。当时石油市场每日需求增长</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">100</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">万桶，而供应量每日增长</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">200</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">万桶，主要来自于美国非常规油气产量的激增。在这种情况下，必然导致国际油价接连大跌。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　不过，低油价的状态也刺激着市场需求快速增长。在</span>2015<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年，全球石油需求每日增长</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">190</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">万桶，这是过去</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">10</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年平均值的两倍。而低油价同样打压着石油的供应，生产企业对价格的变化做出了快速反应。美国页岩油生产在</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">2015</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年春天达到峰值后，开始逐月下降。非欧佩克国家普遍减少了上游油气投资。目前，美国页岩油日产量比高峰时期下降了</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">100</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">万桶。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\">　　“去年全球油气投资减少了<span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">1600</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">亿美元，今年可能继续减少</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">1000</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">亿美元。上次出现这种现象要追溯到</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">70</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年代。”戴思攀告诉记者，全球油气上游投资持续削减将影响到未来几年内油气的产出。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　戴思攀认为，当前全球石油供需形势的变化将促使市场加速再平衡，预计今年下半年可以见到成效。从今年年初的十二年低点至今，国际油价累计反弹了逾</span>80%<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">。这一反弹的支撑动力一方面来自于金融市场对石油价格信心的恢复，另一方面来自于基本面不断改善的良好预期。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　不过，石油市场形势好转并不意味着高油价将卷土重来。在戴思攀看来，当前仍有两大因素制约着油价反弹的空间。首先，全球石油库存仍维持高位，比正常阶段多出</span>6<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">亿桶，大约需要一年或一年半的时间才能消化。其次，北美页岩油气仍保持着旺盛的生命力。低油价倒逼页岩油气企业不断降低成本，提高生产效率。去年它们的生产效率提升了</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">30%</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">，今年还在继续提升。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　戴思攀认为，目前来看，如果纽约原油期货价格维持在每桶</span>50<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">美元上方，美国页岩油开采会不断恢复。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　戴思攀认为，英国脱欧给全球市场增加了很多不确定性，使得金融市场上避险情绪急剧升温。石油作为风险类投资产品短期内或难以受到市场的追捧。</span></span></p><p><br/></p>','专家：国际石油市场走向再平衡','　　国际石油巨头、英国石油BP集团首席经济学家戴思攀8日在上海表示，当下全球石油需求正在快速增长，而供应增速放缓，预计今年下半年国际石油市场逐渐走向再平衡。','1','1','2017-03-11 18:36:48','','0','','','0','{\"thumb\":\"\"}','0','0','0','0','','');INSERT INTO ts_posts ( `id`, `post_author`, `post_keywords`, `post_source`, `post_date`, `post_content`, `post_title`, `post_excerpt`, `post_status`, `comment_status`, `post_modified`, `post_content_filtered`, `post_parent`, `post_type`, `post_mime_type`, `comment_count`, `smeta`, `post_hits`, `post_like`, `istop`, `recommended`, `page_tpl`, `page_tpls` ) VALUES  ('234','1','脱欧不会影响油价中长期走势','','2017-03-11 18:38:42','<p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\">　　6<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">23</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">日英国脱欧事件导致全球金融市场波动， 投资资金纷纷流向包括黄金在内的避险产品，国际原油期货价格在欧洲交易时段持续下挫。“脱欧”会使略有回暖的国际油市陷入困境吗？</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　只是市场暂时的绊脚石</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　美国《国际商业周刊》认为，脱欧导致的油价下跌只是原油市场暂时的绊脚石，长期来看不会对强劲的市场产生冲击。英国</span>“脱欧”公投结果揭晓当日，尽管布伦特原油价格下跌<span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">4.75%</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">，但仍比今年第一季度上涨了</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">80%</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">。随着北美钻机数量连续第三周增加（贝克休斯数据）， 过去两年原油产量过剩、市场承压的局面已近尾声，对原油价格持续上涨的乐观情绪依然存在。国际能源署（</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">IEA</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">）</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">6</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月中旬的报告显示，</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">5</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月份，全球原油日供应量同比下降</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">0.6%</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">，这也是</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">2013</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年以来原油供应量首次出现显著下降。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　政治风险咨询公司欧亚集团</span>CEO<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">约翰斯顿认为，尽管脱欧导致油价在短期内大幅波动，但这不会改变原油市场的供需基本面。“市场目前更关注沙特及美国页岩油生产商的动向，相比之下，‘脱欧’只是一个很小的因素。”相对而言，美国原油产量回升、沙特长期原油政策等因素可能对原油市场产生更为深刻的影响。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　不会对行业产生负面影响</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　当然，脱欧会在短期内削弱石油需求，同时阻碍英国北海的油气投资。但是欧洲不是原油需求增长的主要地区，北海的原油产量在全球总产量中也只占微小份额。因此，油气公司纷纷表态，脱欧不会对行业产生负面影响。荷兰皇家壳牌公司在公投结果揭晓后第一时间表示，公司首要任务是继续向欧洲和英国客户提供能源。法国</span>Engie<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">集团（前苏伊士环能）</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">CEO</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">克歇尔表态称，公司目前在英国当地拥有雇员</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">1.7</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">万人，将持续为欧洲及英国供应能源，公司对英国的发展战略不会改变。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　银行继续看涨原油市场</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　大型银行也继续看涨原油市场。脱欧发生后，高盛、摩根士坦利、花旗及德意志等银行观点趋同，即油价最低的时期已经过去，英国公投</span>“脱欧”会增加原油市场风险，但不会影响需求量上涨、供应量下降的趋势。</span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　高盛分析师认为，如果说公投会给油市带来影响，那就是减少全球</span>0.1%<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">，即</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">13</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">万桶的原油日需求量。德意志银行估测的数字更少，仅为</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">10</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">万桶，而尼日利亚危机曾使石油日供应量减少</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">40</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">万桶。高盛表示：“从需求侧看，公投对大宗商品的影响十分有限，而从供应侧来讲，美元走强降低生产成本，这已经在</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">6</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">24</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">日的市场中有所体现。”摩根士坦利分析师在报告中指出，除非经济出现衰退，否则原油市场中期实现再平衡的迹象已经出现。花旗银行分析团队认为，英国“脱欧”会促使投资者将高风险资产转入传统“藏身之所”，大宗商品价格可能下跌</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">5%</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">至</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">10%</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">，但银行对</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">2017</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年石油市场依然看涨。无论如何，目前原油价格都到了平稳发展期，与今年</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">1</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月的</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">27</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">美元</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">/</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">桶不可同日而语。第一能源咨询公司认为：“英国脱欧会使油价上涨的脚步放缓，但不会阻止这一趋势。”相比之下，美国的高库存可能会对当前原油市场产生更大影响。</span></span></p><p><br/></p>','脱欧不会影响油价中长期走势','　　6月23日英国脱欧事件导致全球金融市场波动， 投资资金纷纷流向包括黄金在内的避险产品，国际原油期货价格在欧洲交易时段持续下挫。“脱欧”会使略有回暖的国际油市陷入困境吗？','1','1','2017-03-11 18:37:44','','0','','','0','{\"thumb\":\"\"}','0','0','0','0','','');INSERT INTO ts_posts ( `id`, `post_author`, `post_keywords`, `post_source`, `post_date`, `post_content`, `post_title`, `post_excerpt`, `post_status`, `comment_status`, `post_modified`, `post_content_filtered`, `post_parent`, `post_type`, `post_mime_type`, `comment_count`, `smeta`, `post_hits`, `post_like`, `istop`, `recommended`, `page_tpl`, `page_tpls` ) VALUES  ('235','1','全国成品油价格指数小幅回落','','2017-03-11 18:39:31','<p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　依据新华</span>(<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">大庆</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">)</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">国际石油资讯中心发布的报告，截至</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">7</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">8</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">日，全国成品油价格指数为</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">590.54</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">，跌幅</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">0.28%</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">，全国成品油价格指数小幅回落。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　全国成品油价格指数运行结果表明，上周</span>93#<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">汽油平均价格报收于</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">5996</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">元</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">/</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">吨，较前一报告周期下跌</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">2</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">元</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">/</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">吨</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">(</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">与前一报告期基本持平</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">)</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">；</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">0#</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">柴油平均价格报收于</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">4941</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">元</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">/</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">吨，较前一报告周期下跌</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">20</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">元</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">/</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">吨</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">(</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">折合</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">0.02</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">元</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">/</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">升</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">)</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">。综合来看，全国柴油平均价格小幅回落，带动全国成品油价格指数继续走低。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　新华</span>(<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">大庆</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">)</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">国际石油资讯中心分析师李振国认为，近日美元走强及英国脱欧引发市场动荡，国际油价持续下行。国内成品油市场近期成交清淡，主营整体销售情况不佳。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　李振国分析认为，国内成品油市场近期成交清淡，南方地区受降水影响，主营销售情况不佳。北方地区高温天气影响了柴油需求，市场基本以消化库存为主。本轮成品油价格调整搁浅，加之天气因素影响，目前业者观望情绪浓厚。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　国际市场方面，美国能源信息署</span>(EIA)<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">近日公布数据显示，截至</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">7</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">1</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">日当周美国原油库存减少</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">222.3</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">万桶，低于预期，目前库存量达到</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">5.244</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">亿桶，该消息利空国际油价。观望后市，美元走强加之英国脱欧带来的担忧情绪持续影响国际市场，预计短期内油价或维持震荡格局。</span></span></p><p><br/></p>','全国成品油价格指数小幅回落','　　依据新华(大庆)国际石油资讯中心发布的报告，截至7月8日，全国成品油价格指数为590.54，跌幅0.28%，全国成品油价格指数小幅回落。','1','1','2017-03-11 18:38:52','','0','','','0','{\"thumb\":\"\"}','0','0','0','0','','');INSERT INTO ts_posts ( `id`, `post_author`, `post_keywords`, `post_source`, `post_date`, `post_content`, `post_title`, `post_excerpt`, `post_status`, `comment_status`, `post_modified`, `post_content_filtered`, `post_parent`, `post_type`, `post_mime_type`, `comment_count`, `smeta`, `post_hits`, `post_like`, `istop`, `recommended`, `page_tpl`, `page_tpls` ) VALUES  ('236','1','石化产业的五大投资机会','','2017-03-11 18:42:32','<p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">对话人</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　解树江</span>| <span style=\"font-family:宋体\">中国能源报总编辑</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　赵俊贵</span>| <span style=\"font-family:宋体\">中国石油化工联合会副会长兼秘书长</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　经过近三十年的快速发展，我国石油化工行业已从高速增长的发展阶段进入中高速增长的新常态。取得成绩的同时，也面临着创新不足、产能过剩、环保压力增大等各种考验。在传统石化行业发展增速下降、产能过剩矛盾突出、要素推动日益减弱和资源环境约束进一步强化的新形势下，主要依靠资源要素投入、规模扩张的粗放发展模式难以为继，必须重新思考未来石化行业发展的思路和方法。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\">　　2016<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年是“十三五”开局之年，也是推进结构性改革的攻坚之年。在此背景下，中国能源报社总编辑解树江对话中国石油化工联合会副会长兼秘书长赵俊贵，就石化行业供给侧改革、行业创新及石化领域民间投资等问题进行深入探讨。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　投资减缓传统产业升级不容忽视</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　解树江：根据中石油和中石化的最新数据，</span>5<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月份日均成品油销量比</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">4</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月减少</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">3.81</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">万吨，同比下降</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">1.34%</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">。您认为这是一个长期的趋势还是短期现象？</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\">　　▍赵俊贵：经济增长总体放缓、相关产业投资下降，重化工程减少，工程用车使用减少，成品油主要是柴油用量随之降低。同时油品商业投资下降，也体现业内对未来油品市场的一种判断和思考。特别是电动汽车等新能源汽车的发展直接影响未来石油市场的走向，未来石油的使命可能更多是作为原料，而非燃料，这或将是能源结构调整的结果。</span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　解树江：今年以来，中国民间投资增速结束了两位数增长，并出现加速下滑态势，同比增速从去年全年的</span>10%<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">降至今年前</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">5</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">个月的</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">3.9%</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">，创下多年来的新低。石化领域投资情况如何？</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\">　　▍赵俊贵：从石化联合会最新数据来看，<span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">5</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月份，石油和化工全行业固定资产投资继续下降，但降幅有所收窄。</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">1-5</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月，石油和天然气开采业投资同比下降</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">16.9%</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">，比前</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">4</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">个月收窄</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">10.6</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">个百分点；化学原料和化学品制造业投资降幅</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">4.2%</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">，缩小</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">2.2</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">个百分点。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　总体看，目前石油化工行业投资疲软的局面没有明显改变，但已现降势趋缓的迹象。石油和化工各行业效益分化明显，但整体上保持向好态势。全行业利润下降，主要受上游拖累，炼油和化工利润均呈现恢复性增长势头，预计二季度中后期，行业利润增长仍将延续这种格局。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　解树江：您认为行业投资增幅下降并处于低点的原因何在？是市场原因还是技术原因？</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\">　　▍赵俊贵：造成目前行业投资下降的原因应该是多方面的，</span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　一是国际油价处于低位，直接导致上游投资大幅减少；</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　二是传统大宗石化产品普遍出现产能过剩，许多企业盈利能力大幅下降，同时企业的融资成本、用人成本、物流成本、安全环保成本却刚性上升，企业投资意愿不强；</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　三是企业技术储备不足，创新能力不强。我国民营化工企业历史比较长的不过</span>30<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">多年，大部分是近</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">10</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年在化工产业高速增长过程中成长起来的中小企业，资本和技术的积累都很薄弱，使一些项目资金和技术不完全匹配，也造成投资减缓；</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　此外，新技术产品对市场品牌要求极高，品牌打造也需要时间检验。比如，中国企业和跨国公司生产同一款高档材料，中国企业同时研发成功，价格或许更低，但往往厂商极有可能仍选择具有口碑的跨国公司产品。越高档的产品，对价格越不敏感，对技术和工艺要求更严更高。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　我想行业投资下降有结构调整的客观原因，最根本的原因还是我们技术创新体系还没建立起来，创新对行业增长的支撑作用还不够，甚至可能出现有钱却无处可用的现象。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　解树江：民营企业在石化行业还有哪些投资机会？</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\">　　▍赵俊贵：传统产业的过剩倒逼行业经济转型是一个客观的历史发展阶段，对当前行业投资下降，我们既不能惊慌失措，也不能束手无策，而要看到石化产业的希望。</span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　一是传统石化产业的改造大有可为。中国不仅是世界石化生产大国也是消费大国，中国用</span>30<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年时间建立了世界上最为完整的石化原料产业链，巨大的石化市场潜力既是我们的优势，也是我们打造世界最优化、最绿色石化原料产业的理由，特别是借助新一代信息技术改造提升传统石化产业仍具有巨大投资价值。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　二是石化产业的材料化、专用化、精细化大有可为。随着传统石化行业日益走向成熟，延伸石化产品产业链，高端化、专用化、精细化发展就成为石化行业转型升级的重要方向。特别是随着国民经济的整体提升，航空航天、高速铁路、电子信息、健康产业等新兴产业的快速发展，急需相应的化工新材料、各种专用化学品相配套。化工新材料等精细化工领域，往往具有批量小、附加值高等特点，非常适合民营企业投资发展。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　三是石化产品绿色化环保化大有可为。随着石化产品日益走进百姓生活，更多地从工业原料变成了日用消费品，生产更多安全环保型的化工产品成为了人民群众的新期待，可以成为大众创新、万众创业的重要领域。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　四是石化产业国际化发展大有可为。中国石化产业发展到今天，上游原油资源严重依赖国际市场，下游石化产品已深度融入国际市场，国际化经营的趋势不可逆转，只有乘势而上，加快资本走出去步伐，才能拓展中国石化产业石化企业发展的新境界新高度，创造国际投资与合作的新机会。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　五是石化产业结构调整大有可为。由于历史上的多种原因，中国民营石化化工企业规模小而分散、集约程度不高的问题长期得不到解决，产能过剩形成的市场倒逼机制，为行业的兼并重组提供了历史机遇，适时采用政策、标准、金融等手段，充分运用市场之手的推动力量，改造提升石化行业产业结构，也会创造许多新的投资机会。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　解树江：石化行业产能过剩在很多领域都很突出。针对外界关注的行业未来发展是否会重回增长轨道，您认为应该如何去做？</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\">　　▍赵俊贵：我个人认为，我国石油化工行业还未达到峰值。石化行业目前是结构性过剩而非周期性问题。石油化工在传统行业中是唯一处于逆差局面的领域。今年前<span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">5</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">个月，我国有机化学原料进口量达到</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">2402</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">万吨，增幅</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">31.6%</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">，混合芳烃进口量</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">556</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">万吨，增长</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">2.4</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">倍。高端新材料领域进口依存度更高，有的已严重制约我国新产业的发展。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　未来如何去改变，我想最重要的一条就是遵循市场规律和行业发展规律，政府、企业、行业协会各自找准定位，破除一切阻碍行业进步的体制机制障碍，在公正的法制环境下，激发要素活力和动力，最大程度释放石化生产力和创新力。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　对政府最重要的是要转变职能，该管的一定守住法律底线，最大程度营造公平竞争的法律环境和市场环境；</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　对企业要坚定信心，树立绿色发展新理念，不断形成创新发展的新机制新动力；</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　对行业协会要重塑公益之心，切实提高行业公共服务能力，提高行业的组织协调水平。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　客观地说，我国实体经济在转型，与市场经济深度发展相适应的行业管理体制与服务体系等配套软实力建设也亟待重塑和转型，而且可能直接关系中国实体经济转型的成败。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　创新与平稳改革并行</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　解树江：企业缺乏自主创新，没有优势产品和特色技术，就会出现问题。面对复杂的宏观经济形势，石化行业是否将面临更大的经营压力？</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\">　　▍赵俊贵：企业投资下降是表象，根本原因还是产业结构问题。以目前形势来看，政府和企业切忌急功近利。要想解决石油化工长远发展问题，不是“做手术”那么简单，而是需要像中医一样循序渐进进行“调理”。改造完善市场环境，提升产业素质绝非易事，必然是一个循序渐进的过程。工人素质的提高、智能化配套设施的建设都需要时间，我们必须把握新常态的新特点，着眼于整体的行业创新与竞争能力的提高，阶段目标与长远目标相结合，把稳增长和调结构作为“十三五”行业发展的两大主要任务，把提升传统产业和培育战略性新兴产业作为两大主攻方向，把创新驱动和深化改革作为两大动力。只要坚持不懈、久久为功，中国石化产业一定会有一个美好的未来。</span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　解树江：近几年，面对经济下行压力和传统动能减弱，政府没有实施</span>“强刺激”，而是把推进“放管服”作为宏观调控的关键性工具，着力推动结构性改革尤其是供给侧结构性改革，充分调动市场主体积极性。油气体制改革受到广泛关注，我们注意到在有关部门的工作安排中，对油气改革用的词汇是“稳步推进”，而对电力体制改革用的却是“积极推进”，这是否意味着改革的力度和节奏有所不同？</span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\">　　▍赵俊贵：油气资源地位重要、属性复杂、国际关联程度高，与国民经济各部门和人民生活密切相关。</span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　中国的油气体制改革一定要从国情出发，尊重历史脉络，充分考量市场主体和消费者的心理承受能力，尊重市场主体的改革积极性，切勿简单照搬国外机制。因为我国的管理体制市场体系与国外形成的历史过程和条件完全不同，法制监管仍待进一步加强，诚信体系和市场条件也并不成熟，生搬硬套有可能</span>“水土不服”。市场经济就是协商化的契约经济，通过沟通协商，利益博弈，寻求最大公约数，是解决市场问题的常态。</span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　和任何领域改革一样，油气改革也一定会遇到各种矛盾和问题，出现不同的意见和建议，关键是要建立利益相关方的法制化协商沟通机制，力求建立最大共识，在理解与宽容中，趋利避害，稳步推进。</span></span></p><p><br/></p>','赵俊贵：石化产业的五大投资机会','　　经过近三十年的快速发展，我国石油化工行业已从高速增长的发展阶段进入中高速增长的新常态。取得成绩的同时，也面临着创新不足、产能过剩、环保压力增大等各种考验。在传统石化行业发展增速下降、产能过剩矛盾突出、要素推动日益减弱和资源环境约束进一步强化的新形势下，主要依靠资源要素投入、规模扩张的粗放发展模式难以为继，必须重新思考未来石化行业发展的思路和方法。','1','1','2017-03-11 18:40:39','','0','','','0','{\"thumb\":\"\"}','0','0','0','0','','');INSERT INTO ts_posts ( `id`, `post_author`, `post_keywords`, `post_source`, `post_date`, `post_content`, `post_title`, `post_excerpt`, `post_status`, `comment_status`, `post_modified`, `post_content_filtered`, `post_parent`, `post_type`, `post_mime_type`, `comment_count`, `smeta`, `post_hits`, `post_like`, `istop`, `recommended`, `page_tpl`, `page_tpls` ) VALUES  ('237','1','我国进口石油去哪了？','','2017-03-11 18:44:39','<p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　巨大的油轮默默排起长队，拥挤在海面上，等待着不知何时才能实现的卸货。家住在青岛港附近的李先生说，</span>“有些大船一停就是半个月。还有新的船源源不断开过来。”</span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　近段时间，中国原油进口相当火爆。跨洋巨型油轮源源不断地将世界各地的原油运往中国。青岛港并不是特例。上海港的停靠船只也已经密密麻麻，给这号称世界最繁忙的港口又增加了几分运输压力。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　全球供应过剩的原油，距离消化完还很遥远</span>——全球<span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">660</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">多艘超级油轮</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">(VLCC)</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">几乎全都用于将中东地区原油运往亚洲。而日前路透社发布的一系列海上油轮及储油船的卫星照片，则清晰地描绘了全球供油严重壅塞情况：约</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">2</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">亿桶石油被迫在海上漂流或停泊，甚至不停加入新船只充当浮动储油槽。严重的海上交通拥挤问题背后，不难看出的是全球石油供应过剩的问题。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\">　　7<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">14</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">日，国际油价亚盘时段低位反弹，此前一天油价因</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">EIA</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">原油库存数据公布值不及预期，加之</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">13</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">日早间公布</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">API</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">数据意外增加，油价收跌，跌幅逾</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">4%</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　波动背后，国际原油的价格依然持续走低。目前，国际原油市场需求并没有较大改善，依然呈现疲弱态势。英国退欧及其可能带来的脱欧蔓延、中东地缘政治风险、美联储加息不明朗等诸多情况，造成国际原油价及成品油价的跌宕起伏。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　最近一个季度，国际油价触底反弹，主营汽柴油价格也进入筑底反弹过程。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　据发改委公告显示，年内第</span>14<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">次国内成品油价格调整将于下周</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">7</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">21</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">日</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">24</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">时开启。一位长期从事石油交易的研究员对经济观察报表示，得益于近期多次成品油限价调价搁浅，国内成品油零售限价将继续不作调整，但批发市场或将持续承压，压力主要来自以下三方面。第一，柴油消费处于淡季，市场需求持续疲弱。第二，南方抗洪形势严峻，影响油品需求及销售。第三，前期累积库存处于高位，中下游多消化库存，进购稀少，加之部分大型贸易商甩货，对主营销售形成抑制。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\">　　6<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">PMI</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">官方数据</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">50%</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">，引起注意的是国内需求的持续疲弱。在此经济下行情况下，中国大量进口的原油都去了哪里，成为人们关注的焦点。国务院发展研究中心国际技术经济研究所客座研究员张捷对经济观察报表示，目前中国对于原油的大量进口主要用于石油储备，其他方面还包括成品油</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">(</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">主要包括汽油和柴油</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">)</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">的国内消费及出口、来料加工、汽车的普及所带来的消耗等。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\">　　</span><strong><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;font-size: 14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">汽油柴油新动向</span></span></strong></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　与石油进口大幅增加相伴的是，国内的石油需求也在持续上升。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　中国农业大学期货与金融衍生品研究中心主任常清认为，对原油的需求，一类是刚性需求，炼成汽油，汽车越多，需求越大；另一部分是工业需求、能源需求，即炼制燃料油，这部分与经济增长有关系。</span>6<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月份</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">PMI</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">的数据表明，经济放缓与能源需求的放缓息息相关。汽油的主要用途发生变化，从过去的工业型经济为主，发展到人民的消费型经济。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　中国粮食研究培训中心研究员胡文国也认为，</span>“石油是混合物，根据沸点不同，原油炼化产生的是一个系列的成品油：汽油、柴油、煤油、沥青、油渣、重油等。目前，汽油生产主要是直接消费，柴油生产出来，可能是一种原料，也有可能直接消费。”</span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　在消费型经济中，不可忽视的是汽车使用量的增加，以及随之对汽油需求的影响。根据中国汽车工业协会</span>(CAAM)<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">的数据，</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">2016</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">6</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月乘用车销量达</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">178</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">万辆，比去年同期增长</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">17.7%</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">，仅比</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">5</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月销量减少</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">0.5%</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　中国石油大学人文学院社会发展研究所所长黄秉杰的看法是：</span>“私家车数量的逐年稳步上升，对汽油的需求上涨有很大的推动作用。即使油价上升，买了车也必须要开，这类消费是无弹性的；值得关注的是，现在的小轿车就像十几年前的冰箱彩电一样，开始在农村乡镇普及，千千万万的农民开始买车，对汽油的需求也随之提升。”</span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　统计显示，</span>2016<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年国内成品油共经历</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">13</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">次调价窗口，其中</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">4</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">次上调，</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">1</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">次下调，</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">6</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">次不作调整，</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">2</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">次搁浅。涨跌互抵后，汽油零售限价累计上调</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">0.34</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">元</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">/</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">升，柴油累计上调</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">0.39</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">元</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">/</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">升。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　一位从事石油交易的相关人士对经济观察报表示，柴油作为主要动力用油，市场需求难有太大下滑。特别是中国市场，因为电商、物流配送的需求极为旺盛，因此价格一直呈现稳中有涨的态势。柴油的价格未来</span>6-12<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">个月小幅上涨的概率较大。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　然而，值得注意的是，在</span>PMI<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">指数显示的经济下行过程中，今年前</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">5</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">个月，柴油产量下降</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">2.2%</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">——这也许与货物运输和建筑施工密切相关的交通运输行业的境况有关。目前，柴油主要用于基础设施、工程机械和物流运输方面。鉴于柴油生产下降和出口大规模激增，考虑到柴油主要用于货物运输和施工，这表明中国经济依然苦苦挣扎。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　上述石油交易相关人士告诉经济观察报：</span>“过去柴汽油的炼化比例是<span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">2</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">：</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">1</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">，柴油作为农业、船业用油的用量比较大；近几年，主要应用于工业用油、矿山用油</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">(</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">修路</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">)</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">和大的物流运输。如果经济下行，跟国家的数据是有一定吻合性的。”</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　张捷对经济观察报说，</span>“拿煤炭运输来举例子：中国目前的煤需求减少了；中国内陆采煤后运到东南沿海，其陆路运输成本相对于目前沿海地区海外进口煤更高，比如从澳大利亚直接进口，海运方便、成本较低。货物运输不景气，对柴油的需求减少，一定程度上表现出中国的工业经济并不景气。”</span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　此外，中国粮食研究培训中心分析师胡文国认为，近期南方洪水对生产经济活动的影响、渔民的柴油补贴改革、农民的农业用油综合改革，也可能成为减少柴油使用需求的因素。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\">　　</span><strong><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;font-size: 14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">石油储备增加</span></span></strong></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　近来全球油价的持续走跌，刺激了中国这个全球最大石油进口国进口原油用于战略储备的步伐。海关总署数据显示，今年</span>1-5<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月，全国原油累计进口</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">15591</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">万吨，同比增长</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">16.5%</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">，成品油累计进口</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">1326</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">万吨，同比增长</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">4.5%</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　中国石油集团经济技术研究院近期发布的</span>2016<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年度《国内外油气行业发展报告》指出，</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">2015</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年中国的石油进口依存度约为</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">59.3%</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">，逼近</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">60%</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　中国海关总署公布的初步数据显示，</span>6<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月的原油进口量为</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">3062</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">万吨，创下了五个月以来的最低水平。摩根大通近日发布的一份研究报告也指出，中国的石油储备可能正在接近结束，随着油价暴跌，中国今年为储备目的进行的石油采购量增加了一倍。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　黄秉杰教授表示，就世界经济发展的方向来看，目前加大石油储备是正确的。</span>“因为经济迟早会回升，很快需求就上来了，价格也会随之上升——现在是最好的时机。”他说。</span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　常清教授认为，原油价格下跌至三四十美元</span>/<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">桶时，中国适时加大购买力度，为国家节约了大量的外汇，值得肯定。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　一位在石油交易领域研究多年的分析师则表示，进口原油增加的另外一个原因是国内原油产量的不断下降。从表面来看，作为全球第二大原油消费国，中国的原油进口情况显得很稳健，今年</span>1-5<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月进口同比增长</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">16.5%</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">，相当于每日大约</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">749</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">万桶。同时，来自路透社的官方数据也显示，</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">5</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月原油产量较上年同期减少</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">7.3%</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">，</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">1-5</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月中国总共生产</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">8500</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">万吨石油，相当于日产</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">408</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">万桶，较</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">2015</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年同期日产量减少大约</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">17</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">万桶。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　对于原油产量下降的问题，张捷认为，目前中国的石油开采成本在</span>70<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">美元</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">-90</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">美元</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">/</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">桶，而国际油价低于中国石油开采成本，目前进行石油开采是不盈利的；但若中国完全不采油，世界的油价就会立刻水涨船高。目前中国只能采取减少采油量的方式减少亏损。还有一点，对已知的石油资源，存储地下也算一种石油储备。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　在储备方面，中国目前基本依靠政府主导，国有储备与商业储备尚未彻底分离。中国还有一些地炼厂，其成本相对来说比较低，以进口油来进行来料加工、炼制，成品油出口也在增加，也增加了原油的进口量。</span></span></p><p><br/></p>','我国进口石油去哪了？','　　巨大的油轮默默排起长队，拥挤在海面上，等待着不知何时才能实现的卸货。家住在青岛港附近的李先生说，“有些大船一停就是半个月。还有新的船源源不断开过来。”','1','1','2017-03-11 18:42:43','','0','','','0','{\"thumb\":\"\"}','0','0','0','0','','');INSERT INTO ts_posts ( `id`, `post_author`, `post_keywords`, `post_source`, `post_date`, `post_content`, `post_title`, `post_excerpt`, `post_status`, `comment_status`, `post_modified`, `post_content_filtered`, `post_parent`, `post_type`, `post_mime_type`, `comment_count`, `smeta`, `post_hits`, `post_like`, `istop`, `recommended`, `page_tpl`, `page_tpls` ) VALUES  ('238','1','明年原油将供不应求','','2017-03-11 18:45:40','<p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　石油输出国组织</span>(OPEC)<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">上周二</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">(12</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">日</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">)</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">发布了对于</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">2017</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年油市的乐观预估，指出全球原油市场的需求将高于目前的产量，这意味着石油市场将出现供不应求的情况，而不是让油价下跌的供应过剩。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　报告同时指出，明年的石油需求增长速度将略微放缓。</span>OPEC<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">透露，</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">2017</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年全球石油需求将增长</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">115</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">万桶</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">/</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">日，而</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">2016</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">的预计增长需求为</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">119</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">万桶</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">/</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">日。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　目前国际石油价格几乎是两年前的一半。自从</span>2014<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年底</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">OPEC</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">拒绝通过减少产量来稳固油价之后，油价的下跌趋势日益加深。</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">OPEC</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">希望通过较低的油价来遏制高成本的竞争对手，例如美国页岩油。最近国际油价更是在英国退欧的影响下，从</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">6</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月初的每桶</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">53</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">美元降至</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">47</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">美元。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\">　　OPEC<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">表示，他们的策略正在发挥作用，石油组织以外的石油供应将继续下降，这将有助于提高国际市场对</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">OPEC</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">原油的需求。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　另据报告，今年</span>OPEC<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">之外的石油供应将减少</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">88</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">万桶</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">/</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">日，明年将减少</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">11</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">万桶</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">/</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">日。</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">2014</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年以来的油价持续走低对非石油输出国造成很大的打击，一些公司已经推迟或取消了全球石油项目。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\">　　OPEC<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">表示，</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">OPEC</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">在</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">6</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月的日产量增加至</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">3286</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">万桶，比此前增加了</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">26.4</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">万桶，估计</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">2017</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年对</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">OPEC</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">原油的平均日需求量为</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">3298</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">万桶，这预示着如果</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">OPEC</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">维持产量稳定，将会出现供不应求的局面。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　世界最大的原油出口国沙特阿拉伯对</span>OPEC<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">表示，该国今年</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">6</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月将石油产量提高至</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">1055</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">万桶</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">/</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">日，而去年同期的产量为创纪录的</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">1056</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">万桶</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">/</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">日。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\">　　OPEC<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">的报告表明，今年平均</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">100</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">万桶的日产量造成的供应过剩的情况仍相当严重。而第三季度对</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">OPEC</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">原油的需求将超过当前的产量。根据</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">OPEC</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">以往的报告，上一次出现原油产量供不应求的情况是在</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">2013</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\">　　“今年非<span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">OPEC</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">供应下降的情况将持续到</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">2017</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年，但下降的速度将放缓。”</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">OPEC</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">称，“</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">2017</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年的市场情况将有助于消化过剩的石油库存。”</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　也有人表示，市场产能过剩的情况要持续到</span>2018<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年才会解决，他们预估的供应过剩的数量将至少达到</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">3</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">亿桶。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　此外，由于英国退欧造成越来越多的不确定性，</span>OPEC<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">降低了对今年全球经济增长的预估，“英国脱欧公投后，其潜在的负面影响已经导致对</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">2016</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年全球经济增长率的预估从</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">3.1%</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">下降到</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">3%</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">。”</span></span></p><p><br/></p>','OPEC：明年原油将供不应求','　　石油输出国组织(OPEC)上周二(12日)发布了对于2017年油市的乐观预估，指出全球原油市场的需求将高于目前的产量，这意味着石油市场将出现供不应求的情况，而不是让油价下跌的供应过剩。','1','1','2017-03-11 18:44:50','','0','','','0','{\"thumb\":\"\"}','1','0','0','0','','');INSERT INTO ts_posts ( `id`, `post_author`, `post_keywords`, `post_source`, `post_date`, `post_content`, `post_title`, `post_excerpt`, `post_status`, `comment_status`, `post_modified`, `post_content_filtered`, `post_parent`, `post_type`, `post_mime_type`, `comment_count`, `smeta`, `post_hits`, `post_like`, `istop`, `recommended`, `page_tpl`, `page_tpls` ) VALUES  ('239','1','国内油价 回归&quot;5元时代&quot;','','2017-03-11 18:47:47','<p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　我国年内第</span>14<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">次成品油零售价调价窗口期</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">7</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">21</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">日</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">24</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">时开启。经过前两次搁浅后，多家机构预测本次成品油价格将迎来年内第二次下调，每升油价再次回归</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">5</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">元时代。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\">　　6<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月份开始，国际原油价格一直处于</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">45-52</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">美元</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">/</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">桶的价格区间内震荡盘整。前两次调价周期</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">(6</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">9</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">日</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">-7</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">7</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">日</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">)</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">内，按国内成品油价格机制，调价金额每吨不足</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">50</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">元，成品油价格不调整。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　多家机构认为，本轮调价周期内，因美元上涨，美国库欣地区等全球各地燃油库存大涨，加重了市场对供应过剩的忧虑，导致国际油价震荡下行。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　截至</span>7<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">19</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">日收盘，伦敦洲际交易所布伦特原油期货结算价报</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">48.18</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">美元，</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">WTI</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">原油期货结算价报</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">47.6</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">美元；纽约商品交易所原油期货结算价收报</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">45.45</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">美元，相比</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">6</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">8</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">日的</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">51.23</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">美元，下跌幅度为</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">11.28%</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　中宇资讯认为，综合前两轮国内油价搁浅幅度后，预计</span>7<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">22</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">日零时成品油零售限价将下调</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">145</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">元</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">/</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">吨。隆众石化网监测预计，本次汽柴油价格下调</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">130-150</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">元</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">/</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">吨，折合每升</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">0.10-0.13</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">元。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　今年以来，国内成品油已经历</span>13<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">次调价窗口，其中</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">4</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">次上调，</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">1</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">次下调，</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">8</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">次不作调整——六次因国际油价低于每桶</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">40</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">美元的“地板价”而不调整。上一次国内油价下调发生在今年</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">1</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">13</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">日</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">24</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">时，汽、柴油价格每吨分别下调</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">140</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">元和</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">135</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">元。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　安迅思预计，若此次成品油零售价格下调，国内汽柴油零售市场将再次全面回归</span>“五元时代”。对于终端消费者来说，降低出行成本无疑是个好消息。</span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　中宇资讯分析师马建彩估算，按现在的</span>145<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">元</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">/</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">吨的下跌幅度计算，届时</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">92#</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">汽油下调约</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">0.11</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">元</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">/</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">升，</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">0#</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">柴油下调约</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">0.12</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">元</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">/</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">升。按一般家用汽车油箱</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">50L</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">的容量估测，加满一箱汽油将节省约</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">5.5</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">元。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　对于未来油价走势，中宇资讯分析师张津表示，近期国际油价重心继续下移，美联储加息预期再起和近期原油需求的担忧对市场打击较大，且本周五预计下调</span>145<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">元</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">/</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">吨，市场观望情绪浓郁。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　安迅思认为，近期的原油需求预测报告显示，全球需求增长正在减缓，而库存仍然居高不下，特别是成品油库存，预计未来一周，国际油价仍有下行风险。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　长期看，隆众石化通原油分析师李彦认为，当下国际原油市场的利好和利空均无压倒性优势，最基本的供需面将决定油价中长期走势。由于供应过剩逐渐缓解，今年下半年油价或难出现崩塌式下滑，整体表现或强于去年，</span>37-40<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">美元附近或成较坚固底部，若无突发性重大利好，</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">55</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">美元可能就是今年油价的“天花板”。</span></span></p><p><br/></p>','国内油价今日或年内第二次下调 回归&quot;5元时代&quot;','　　我国年内第14次成品油零售价调价窗口期7月21日24时开启。经过前两次搁浅后，多家机构预测本次成品油价格将迎来年内第二次下调，每升油价再次回归5元时代。','1','1','2017-03-11 18:46:43','','0','','','0','{\"thumb\":\"\"}','0','0','0','0','','');INSERT INTO ts_posts ( `id`, `post_author`, `post_keywords`, `post_source`, `post_date`, `post_content`, `post_title`, `post_excerpt`, `post_status`, `comment_status`, `post_modified`, `post_content_filtered`, `post_parent`, `post_type`, `post_mime_type`, `comment_count`, `smeta`, `post_hits`, `post_like`, `istop`, `recommended`, `page_tpl`, `page_tpls` ) VALUES  ('240','1','国内汽、柴油价格每吨分别降低155元和150元','','2017-03-11 18:48:41','<p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　据发改委</span>7<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">21</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">日消息，根据近期国际市场油价变化情况，按照现行成品油价格形成机制，自</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">2016</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">7</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">21</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">日</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">24</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">时起，国内汽、柴油价格（标准品，下同）每吨分别降低</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">155</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">元和</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">150</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">元。调整后，各省（区、市）和中心城市汽、柴油最高零售价格见附表。相关价格联动及补贴政策按现行规定执行。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　发改委表示，中石油、中石化、中海油三大公司要组织好成品油生产和调运，确保市场稳定供应，严格执行国家价格政策。各级价格主管部门要加大市场监督检查力度，严厉查处不执行国家价格政策的行为，维护正常市场秩序。消费者可通过</span>12358<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">价格监管平台举报价格违法行为。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　发改委正密切跟踪成品油价格形成机制运行情况，结合国内外石油市场形势变化，进一步予以研究完善。</span></span></p><p><br/></p>','发改委：国内汽、柴油价格每吨分别降低155元和150元','　　据发改委7月21日消息，根据近期国际市场油价变化情况，按照现行成品油价格形成机制，自2016年7月21日24时起，国内汽、柴油价格（标准品，下同）每吨分别降低155元和150元。调整后，各省（区、市）和中心城市汽、柴油最高零售价格见附表。相关价格联动及补贴政策按现行规定执行。','1','1','2017-03-11 18:48:01','','0','','','0','{\"thumb\":\"\"}','0','0','0','0','','');INSERT INTO ts_posts ( `id`, `post_author`, `post_keywords`, `post_source`, `post_date`, `post_content`, `post_title`, `post_excerpt`, `post_status`, `comment_status`, `post_modified`, `post_content_filtered`, `post_parent`, `post_type`, `post_mime_type`, `comment_count`, `smeta`, `post_hits`, `post_like`, `istop`, `recommended`, `page_tpl`, `page_tpls` ) VALUES  ('241','1','中国下半年石油产品出口将打破所有纪录','','2017-03-11 18:50:39','<p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　据普氏能源资讯</span>7<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">21</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">日新加坡报道，由于新的独立炼油企业准备加入这个行列以及国有石油巨头拥有大量的未使用出口配额，中国的石油产品出口在</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">6</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月份上升到接近纪录高位以后在今年下半年很可能保持强劲增长姿态。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　中国的几个独立炼油企业包括山东京博石化、山东鲁清石化、山东汇丰石化和山东利华益集团，计划在今年下半年开始石油产品出口。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　山东京博石化、山东鲁清石化、山东汇丰石化和山东利华益集团共拥有</span>25.5<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">万吨石油产品出口配额。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　此外，中化泉州石化有限公司在中国政府第三轮石油产品出口配额分配中赢得了</span>255<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">万吨石油产品的出口配额，远远超过了其在前两轮配额分配中获得的</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">200</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">万吨配额，这表明了这家公司的雄心勃勃出口计划。</span></span></p><p><br/></p>','中国下半年石油产品出口将打破所有纪录','　　据普氏能源资讯7月21日新加坡报道，由于新的独立炼油企业准备加入这个行列以及国有石油巨头拥有大量的未使用出口配额，中国的石油产品出口在6月份上升到接近纪录高位以后在今年下半年很可能保持强劲增长姿态。','1','1','2017-03-11 18:50:04','','0','','','0','{\"thumb\":\"\"}','1','0','0','0','','');INSERT INTO ts_posts ( `id`, `post_author`, `post_keywords`, `post_source`, `post_date`, `post_content`, `post_title`, `post_excerpt`, `post_status`, `comment_status`, `post_modified`, `post_content_filtered`, `post_parent`, `post_type`, `post_mime_type`, `comment_count`, `smeta`, `post_hits`, `post_like`, `istop`, `recommended`, `page_tpl`, `page_tpls` ) VALUES  ('242','1','供应过剩担忧致 ','','2017-03-11 18:52:01','<p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　由于投资者对原油市场供应过剩的担忧近期升温，国际油价</span>25<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">日下跌超</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">2%</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">至近</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">3</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">个月低点。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　截至</span>25<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">日收盘时，纽约商品交易所</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">9</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月交货的轻质原油期货价格下跌</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">1.06</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">美元，收于每桶</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">43.13</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">美元，跌幅为</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">2.40%</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">。</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">9</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月交货的伦敦布伦特原油期货价格下跌</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">0.97</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">美元，收于每桶</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">44.72</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">美元，跌幅为</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">2.12%</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　自上周美国库存数据发布以来，投资者持续担忧市场供应过剩。</span>20<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">日公布的数据显示，在截至</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">15</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">日的一周，尽管正在经历度假季带来的消费高峰，美国汽油库存意外增加</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">91.1</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">万桶至</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">2.41</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">亿桶，增幅创</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">4</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月份以来最高；美国全国的商业原油库存也处于同一时期的历史最高值。同时还有数据显示，美国运营的油田钻井数量增加</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">14</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">个至</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">371</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">个，为连续第四周上涨。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　由于一些可能导致供应减少的因素影响，上个月国际油价一度升至每桶</span>50<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">美元上方，但随着这些因素逐步消散、美国驾驶度假季接近尾声，以及全球需求疲弱趋势的延续，目前已经跌去约</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">15%</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">。分析人士表示，近期的数据引发了投资者对于市场供应过量的担忧，令油价承压下行。原油库存居高不下，加拿大火灾后原油生产逐步恢复以及伊拉克石油产量的增加，均令市场基本面难以支撑油价回升至每桶</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">55</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">美元上方。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　美元近期的走强趋势也令以美元计价的原油价格承压，美联储加息预期下，美元的走强预计仍将持续压制原油价格。美联储</span>27<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">日将结束为期两天的货币政策会议。外界普遍预期美联储此次会议不会再次提高利率，但是美联储的下一步行动预计仍将是加息，时点可能在今年年底之前。芝加哥商业交易所的交易员认为，</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">9</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月份加息的概率为</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">26%</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">，</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">12</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月加息的概率为</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">56%</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">。</span></span></p><p><br/></p>','供应过剩担忧致 油价跌至3月低点','　　由于投资者对原油市场供应过剩的担忧近期升温，国际油价25日下跌超2%至近3个月低点。','1','1','2017-03-11 18:51:12','','0','','','0','{\"thumb\":\"\"}','1','0','0','0','','');INSERT INTO ts_posts ( `id`, `post_author`, `post_keywords`, `post_source`, `post_date`, `post_content`, `post_title`, `post_excerpt`, `post_status`, `comment_status`, `post_modified`, `post_content_filtered`, `post_parent`, `post_type`, `post_mime_type`, `comment_count`, `smeta`, `post_hits`, `post_like`, `istop`, `recommended`, `page_tpl`, `page_tpls` ) VALUES  ('243','1','石化节能减排圈定五重点','','2017-03-11 18:52:57','<p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\">　　“十三五”期间环保产业投资规模将达到<span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">17</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">万亿元，一系列有关环保的政策正在制定。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　国家发改委环资司司长何炳华表示，发改委正在牵头</span>3<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">个行动计划，即全民节能行动计划、全民节水行动计划、循环发展引领行动。他指出，要以实施“大气十条”、“水十条”、“土十条”，以及城市环境基础设施建设等方面重大工程来拉动环保投资的增长，“比‘十二五’有很大的提升。”</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　工信部节能司司长高云虎透露：未来</span>5<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年，将大力推动节能环保、新能源装备、新能源汽车等绿色制造产业发展，积极推广节能环保的新产品、新技术、新工艺，发展壮大节能环保服务产业，支持一批节能环保产业示范基地建设和发展。力争到</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">2020</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年使绿色制造产业达到</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">10</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">万亿元，成为国民经济新的支柱产业。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　值得注意的是，除了产业政策外，有关环保领域的几大立法工作也是下半年关注重点。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　随着各项政策的推动，业内人士预测，</span>“十三五”期间，环保市场潜力巨大，总社会投资有望达到<span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">17</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">万亿元。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　桑德集团董事长文一波分析说，</span>“土十条”投资需求最大，约有<span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">10</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">万亿，“水十条”有</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">2</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">万亿，“大气十条”有</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">1.7</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">万亿。此外，海绵城市建设需求可达</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">3</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">万亿，地下管廊建设有</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">0.9</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">万亿，黑臭水体处理</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">0.7</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">万亿，乡镇污水处理</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">0.2</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">万亿。文一波表示，尽管目前环保投资增速很快，但尚有近</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">70%</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">环保领域治理需求未得到满足，未来投资空间很大。</span></span></p><p><br/></p>','石化节能减排圈定五重点 未来15年投入将达41万亿','　　“十三五”期间环保产业投资规模将达到17万亿元，一系列有关环保的政策正在制定。INSERT INTO ts_posts ( `id`, `post_author`, `post_keywords`, `post_source`, `post_date`, `post_content`, `post_title`, `post_excerpt`, `post_status`, `comment_status`, `post_modified`, `post_content_filtered`, `post_parent`, `post_type`, `post_mime_type`, `comment_count`, `smeta`, `post_hits`, `post_like`, `istop`, `recommended`, `page_tpl`, `page_tpls` ) VALUES  ('244','1','全国成品油价格指数小幅回落','','2017-03-11 18:54:20','<p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　依据新华</span>(<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">大庆</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">)</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">国际石油资讯中心发布的报告</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">,</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">截至</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">7</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">27</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">日</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">,</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">全国成品油价格指数为</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">576.62,</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">跌幅</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">0.61%,</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">全国成品油价格指数小幅回落。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　全国成品油价格指数运行结果表明</span>,<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">上周</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">93#</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">汽油平均价格报收于</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">5857</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">元</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">/</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">吨</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">,</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">较前一报告周期下跌</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">12</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">元</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">/</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">吨</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">(</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">与前一报告期基本持平</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">);0#</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">柴油平均价格报收于</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">4823</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">元</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">/</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">吨</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">,</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">较前一报告周期下跌</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">41</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">元</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">/</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">吨</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">(</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">折合</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">0.04</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">元</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">/</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">升</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">)</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">。综合来看</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">,</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">全国柴油平均价格小幅下跌</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">,</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">带动全国成品油价格指数小幅回落。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　新华</span>(<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">大庆</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">)</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">国际石油资讯中心分析师蒋冰认为</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">,</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">近日投资者对原油供应过剩的担忧情绪持续加深</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">,</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">国际油价持续下行。国内成品油市场交投清淡</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">,</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">业者悲观情绪浓厚。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　蒋冰分析认为</span>,<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">因美国成品油库存上升及活跃钻井数增加</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">,</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">国际原油期货价格持续承压。国内成品油市场受此影响</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">,</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">市场价格低位持稳。目前一揽子原油平均价格变化率负向加深</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">,</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">业者心态持续悲观</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">,</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">市场成交清淡。地炼方面</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">,</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">山东地区成品油价格波动显著</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">,</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">行情不佳</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">,</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">汽柴油价格整体下调。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　国际市场方面</span>,<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">美国石油学会</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">(API)</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">近日公布数据显示</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">,</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">上周美国原油库存减少</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">82.7</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">万桶至</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">5.20</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">亿桶</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">,</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">低于预期</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">,</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">库欣原油库存增加</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">137.8</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">万桶</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">,</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">该消息利空国际油价。观望后市</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">,</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">美元维持强势地位长期施压国际油价</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">,</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">加之美国活跃钻井数持续增加</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">,</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">预计短期内国际油价将维持低位震荡格局。</span></span></p><p><br/></p>','全国成品油价格指数小幅回落','　　依据新华(大庆)国际石油资讯中心发布的报告,截至7月27日,全国成品油价格指数为576.62,跌幅0.61%,全国成品油价格指数小幅回落。','1','1','2017-03-11 18:53:40','','0','','','0','{\"thumb\":\"\"}','1','0','0','0','','');INSERT INTO ts_posts ( `id`, `post_author`, `post_keywords`, `post_source`, `post_date`, `post_content`, `post_title`, `post_excerpt`, `post_status`, `comment_status`, `post_modified`, `post_content_filtered`, `post_parent`, `post_type`, `post_mime_type`, `comment_count`, `smeta`, `post_hits`, `post_like`, `istop`, `recommended`, `page_tpl`, `page_tpls` ) VALUES  ('245','1','中海油上半年预亏80亿','','2017-03-11 18:56:26','<p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　国际油价上半年持续低迷，石油巨头的日子仍不好过。</span>7<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">28</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">日晚，中国海洋石油有限公司</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">(</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">以下简称“中海油”</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">)</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">率先发布业绩预告称，预计上半年公司净亏损约为</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">80</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">亿元，同比盈转亏。此前在去年同期，中海油盈利</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">147.33</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">亿元。</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">wind</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">显示，</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">2001</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年上市以来中海油始终保持盈利，今年上半年将是其上市以来首度亏损。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\">　</span><strong><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;font-size: 14px\">　1-3<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月平均实现油价远低于成本价</span></span></strong></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　中海油为中海油总公司的主要业务主体和上市公司。此前在</span>2015<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年，中海油净利润</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">202.5</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">亿元，同比降幅</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">66.4%</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">。对于今年上半年亏损原因，中海油表示，第一就是与去年同期相比，</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">2016</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年上半年公司的原油实现价格的进一步下降。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　查询数据可知，今年上半年国际油价有所复苏，</span>WTI<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">原油价格从年初的每桶</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">36.76</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">美元升至年中的每桶</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">48.33</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">美元，布伦特原油价格则从每桶</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">37.22</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">美元升至每桶</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">49.68</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">美元。然而，对于生产成本较高的国内石油企业来说，这一复苏进度对于实现盈利仍然不够。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　根据中海油去年年报，尽管近年来中海油持续削减生产成本，不过</span>2015<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年的整体生产成本仍然达每桶</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">39.82</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">美元。而在</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">4</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月之前，原油价格却长期在</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">40</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">美元以下徘徊，</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">WTI</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">原油价格和布伦特原油价格最低时分别触及</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">26.21</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">美元和</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">27.88</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">美元的历史低点。查询一季报可知，</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">1-3</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月期间中海油平均实现油价仅为</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">32.54</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">美元</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">/</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">桶，远低于其成本价。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　中海油表示，上半年亏损的另一个原因是已经确认的减值和拨备，以及包括在加拿大的油砂资产在内的某些油气资产的账面金额减少到可回收金额。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　本次加拿大油砂资产的减值，也再次引发外界对于中海油海外并购项目在回报上的关注。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　此前，中海油总公司旗下另一家上市公司</span>——中海油服发布公告称，由于外油服资产价值大幅缩水<span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">71</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">亿元，公司对此计提后导致上半年亏损</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">84</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">亿元。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\">　　</span><strong><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;font-size: 14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">大幅度削减产量望</span>“止损”</span></strong></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　面对业绩持续下滑的态势，中海油昨日表示，公司坚持油气田的稳定和安全运营；提高生产效率；实施成本控制策略并且通过技术和管理创新提升效率；以及坚持审慎的财务政策。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　查询中海油历年年报可知，其除了上文所提及的削减成本外，还一改曾经的大手笔并购风格，转而大幅度削减资本开支。</span>2014<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年，中海油资本支出总额为</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">1070</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">亿元，</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">2015</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年降至</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">672</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">亿元，今年预计金额低于</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">600</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">亿元。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　此外，由于生产成本一度高于当前的国际油价，中海油还大幅度削减产量试图</span>“止损”：<span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">2015</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年，中海油油气产量为</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">495</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">百万桶油当量，而</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">2016</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年生产目标为</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">470</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">百万</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">-485</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">百万桶油当量，</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">2017</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年为</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">484</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">百万桶油当量。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　昨夜，新京报记者就上半年减产情况采访中海油方面，对方回应称：上半年净损失约</span>80<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">亿元，具体信息将于中期业绩时公布。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\">　　</span><strong><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;font-size: 14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">链接</span></span></strong></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\">　　</span><strong><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;font-size: 14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">中海油旗下上市公司业绩全面下滑</span></span></strong></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　除了中海油这一中海油总公司旗下最主要上市平台之外，中海油旗下其他上市公司在上半年业绩也不理想。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　中海石化</span>6<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月底发布盈利警示称，预计今年上半年净利润由盈转亏，亏损</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">1.5</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">亿</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">-2</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">亿元。此前在去年同期，公司盈利约</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">5.05</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">亿元。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　山东海化</span>7<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">7</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">日发布业绩预告，预计上半年净利润为</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">2200</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">万元至</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">3000</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">万元，上年同期为</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">8610.32</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">万元，同比下降</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">65%</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">至</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">74%</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　中海油服</span>7<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">25</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">日发布公告，预计上半年净利润为亏损</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">84</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">亿元左右，公司去年同期净利润</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">8.95</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">亿元。中海油服也凭借这一巨额亏损暂时登上目前</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">A</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">股预亏王。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　中海油总公司官网显示，其旗下共有中海油、中海石化、山东海化、中海油服以及海油工程等五家上市公司。除了海油工程尚未发布上半年业绩情况之外，上述四家业绩均全线下滑，且其中三家由盈转亏。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　近日在</span>2016<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年领导干部会上，中海油总公司董事长杨华坦言，“低油价的新常态，已经让公司面临异常严峻的生产经营压力，在这样一个时间节点召开这次会议，我们探讨的是公司的存亡问题，能不能活下来的问题。”</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\">　</span><strong><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;font-size: 14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　国内成品油或现三连跌</span></span></strong></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　近期，国际油价出现罕见的持续大跌。分析师预计，国内成品油价格已经出现三连跌的可能。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　截至</span>7<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">27</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">日收盘，纽约原油期货价格下跌</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">1.00</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">美元，收于每桶</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">41.92</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">美元，跌幅为</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">2.33%</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">。布伦特原油期货价格下跌</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">1.40</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">美元，收于每桶</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">43.47</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">美元，跌幅为</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">3.12%</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">。值得注意的是，布伦特原油也是</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">5</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月初以来首次跌破</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">44</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">美元</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">/</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">桶的关口。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　消息面上，美国能源信息局公布数据显示，在截至</span>7<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">22</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">日的一周，美国全国的商业原油库存意外增加</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">170</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">万桶至</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">5.211</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">亿桶，导致悲观情绪四起。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　据中宇资讯报告，截至北京时间</span>7<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">28</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">日，国内成品油调价周期进入第</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">5</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">个工作日，预计</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">8</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">5</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">日零时成品油零售限价将下调</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">100</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">元</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">/</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">吨。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　中宇资讯油品分析师马建彩表示，当前国际市场利好消息匮乏，加之美元保持高位的预期令原油上扬继续承压。本轮调价计价期已经过半，目前看来下调预期已成定局，对国内油市而言无疑雪上加霜。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\">&nbsp;</span></p><p><br/></p>','中海油上半年预亏80亿 去年同期盈利147亿','　　国际油价上半年持续低迷，石油巨头的日子仍不好过。7月28日晚，中国海洋石油有限公司(以下简称“中海油”)率先发布业绩预告称，预计上半年公司净亏损约为80亿元，同比盈转亏。此前在去年同期，中海油盈利147.33亿元。wind显示，2001年上市以来中海油始终保持盈利，今年上半年将是其上市以来首度亏损。','1','1','2017-03-11 18:54:45','','0','','','0','{\"thumb\":\"\"}','1','0','0','0','','');INSERT INTO ts_posts ( `id`, `post_author`, `post_keywords`, `post_source`, `post_date`, `post_content`, `post_title`, `post_excerpt`, `post_status`, `comment_status`, `post_modified`, `post_content_filtered`, `post_parent`, `post_type`, `post_mime_type`, `comment_count`, `smeta`, `post_hits`, `post_like`, `istop`, `recommended`, `page_tpl`, `page_tpls` ) VALUES  ('246','1','网约车终获合法身份','','2017-03-11 18:58:00','<p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　作为分享经济的业态之一，网络预约出租汽车</span>(<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">网约车</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">)</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">终于获得合法的身份，拼车、顺风车出行方式也得到支持、鼓励。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　经过</span>9<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">个多月漫长的“意见征求”后，《关于深化改革推进出租汽车行业健康发展的指导意见》和《网络预约出租汽车经营服务管理暂行办法》两个规范车市场的文件已于近日正式出台，新政将于</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">11</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">1</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">日起实施。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　交通运输部副部长刘小明</span>28<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">日在国新办发布会上说，明确网约车的合法地位，以及平台公司应承担的承运人责任、具体的营运条件和规范经营行为的要求，将支持网约车平台公司不断创新规范发展。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　业内人士表示，此次新政体现了监管部门</span>“依法治理，规范经营”的决心，有助于目前趋于无序竞争的用车出行市场回到健康发展的轨道。但新政效果如何，还有待通过地方细则制定与实际执行环节来检验。</span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\">　</span><strong><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;font-size: 14px\">　8<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年报废年限取消</span></span></strong></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　去年</span>10<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">10</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">日，交通运输部发布了《网络预约出租汽车经营服务管理暂行办法</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">(</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">征求意见稿</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">)</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">》，曾引起巨大争议。其中，网约车应将车辆更改为营运性质这一项，意味着报废年限变为</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">8</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年，这使很多专车司机萌生退意。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　相较此前的意见稿，《暂行办法》不再要求网约车辆登记为</span>“出租客运”，即不必执行<span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">8</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年报废，而代之以</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">60</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">万公里强行报废。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　对此，滴滴出行发文回应称，《暂行办法》在对网约车平台、驾驶员和车辆实行许可管理的基础上，取消了</span>8<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年报废的规定，改以行驶里程达到</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">60</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">万公里时报废，更符合兼职为主的网约车分享经济新业态。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　《暂行办法》还删除了原先的数量限制条款，规定原则上实行市场调节价。滴滴出行认为，这实际上给了市场、平台及司机更大的自主权，并肯定了顺风车、拼车等新的出行方式。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　值得注意的是，《暂行办法》规定，网约车平台需根据经营区域向相应的出租汽车行政主管部门提出申请，地方政府对网约车的具体管理标准和营运要求有一定的裁量权。这意味着网约车平台将面临上千个地方市县的属地线下审批和监管。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　大众交通董事长兼总经理杨国平说，对于网约出租车的车辆档次、价格和牌照所在地等，新政未作明确规定，希望地方在制定细则时有所考虑，应和出租车形成差异化经营。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　他认为，新政的效果重在执行，尤其是对新政发布后继续从事业务的不符合规范的车辆和人员，要切实追究法律责任。对于网约车辆保险和从业人员纳税的具体规定，也应尽快落地。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\">　　</span><strong><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;font-size: 14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">后续还有博弈过程</span></span></strong></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　在规范发展网约车管理的同时，政府对传统出租车</span>(<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">巡游出租汽车</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">)</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">的改革也提出了诸多思路。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　《关于深化改革推进出租汽车行业健康发展的指导意见》提出，要深化巡游出租汽车改革分为改革经营权制度、健全利益分配制度、理顺价格形成机制、推动行业转型升级。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　一直以来，社会上普遍担忧，新型网约车的出现会对传统的出租汽车造成冲击。某出租车公司员工对上证报记者透露，因为网约车的出现，公司之前的早晚两班倒变成了一班，曾经非常火爆的订车热线也日益冷清。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　杨国平也认为，新政允许网约车实行市场化价格，尤其在交通高峰和特殊天气条件下可以采取溢价，这样可能会对出租车产生影响，比如造成出租车司机与乘客私自议价或者拒接扬招业务行为。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　针对这种情况，《指导意见》鼓励巡游车企业转型提供网约车服务。鼓励巡游车通过电信、互联网等电召服务方式提供运营服务，推广使用符合金融标准的非现金支付方式，拓展服务功能，方便公众乘车。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　刘小明认为，网约车和传统出租车的发展主要还是取决于乘客和市场。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　他解释说，两者各有其特点，传统出租车最大的特点是很公平，不管会不会用手机，大家都能够公平地用。对于一些老同志，如果仅仅有网约车可能就是不方便。另外根据专家的研究，在出租需求比较集中的区域，传统出租车可能运行起来更加节约。因为它是政府定价，所以本身就实现了平峰、高峰的内部交叉补贴，价格是公开透明的，不会像网约车碰到恶劣天气时动态加价的问题。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\">　　“新政出台只是第一步，相当于制定了一个框架，后续还要通过各地出台的细则来填充，这仍将是一个各方博弈并考验监管者智慧的过程。”杨国平这样预言。</span></p><p><br/></p>','网约车终获合法身份 用车市场回归有序','　　作为分享经济的业态之一，网络预约出租汽车(网约车)终于获得合法的身份，拼车、顺风车出行方式也得到支持、鼓励。','1','1','2017-03-11 18:56:41','','0','','','0','{\"thumb\":\"\"}','0','0','0','0','','');INSERT INTO ts_posts ( `id`, `post_author`, `post_keywords`, `post_source`, `post_date`, `post_content`, `post_title`, `post_excerpt`, `post_status`, `comment_status`, `post_modified`, `post_content_filtered`, `post_parent`, `post_type`, `post_mime_type`, `comment_count`, `smeta`, `post_hits`, `post_like`, `istop`, `recommended`, `page_tpl`, `page_tpls` ) VALUES  ('247','1','石油巨头壳牌季度获利骤降逾70%','','2017-03-11 18:59:18','<p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　国际石油巨头皇家荷兰壳牌石油集团</span>(Royal Dutch Shell)<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">周四</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">(7</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">28</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">日</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">)</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">公布的财报显示，</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">2016</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年二季度的获利下降逾</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">70%</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">，远低于分析师预估，因油气价格疲弱进一步打压其营收。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　不过，壳牌第二季度的油气产量较上年同期增长</span>28%<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">，主要受益于</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">BG</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">资产的贡献。今年年初，壳牌曾以</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">540</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">亿美元收购了</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">BG</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　同时，财报亦显示，壳牌第二季度供应的当期成本为</span>10<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">亿美元，分析师预估为</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">22</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">亿美元，上年同期为</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">38</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">亿美元。该公司将当期供应成本定义为净利。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　该公司执行长</span>Ben van Beurden<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">称，“油价下跌持续对各业务构成重大挑战，尤其是对上游业务。”</span></span></p><p><br/></p>','石油巨头壳牌季度获利骤降逾70%','　　国际石油巨头皇家荷兰壳牌石油集团(Royal Dutch Shell)周四(7月28日)公布的财报显示，2016年二季度的获利下降逾70%，远低于分析师预估，因油气价格疲弱进一步打压其营收。','1','1','2017-03-11 18:58:44','','0','','','0','{\"thumb\":\"\"}','0','0','0','0','','');INSERT INTO ts_posts ( `id`, `post_author`, `post_keywords`, `post_source`, `post_date`, `post_content`, `post_title`, `post_excerpt`, `post_status`, `comment_status`, `post_modified`, `post_content_filtered`, `post_parent`, `post_type`, `post_mime_type`, `comment_count`, `smeta`, `post_hits`, `post_like`, `istop`, `recommended`, `page_tpl`, `page_tpls` ) VALUES  ('248','1','美元走强成油价最大风险','','2017-03-11 19:00:37','<p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　高盛</span>27<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">日发布的最新报告认为，美元进一步走强将成为短期内油价面临的最大风险。美国以外地区经济的不确定性，以及美联储潜在的加息预期，都可能推动美元进一步走强，从而导致油价下跌。自</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">6</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月初以来，布伦特油价已经下跌超过</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">15%</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">，同期美元指数涨幅接近</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">4%</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　美国能源信息署</span>27<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">日公布的数据显示，上周美国原油库存增加</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">167.1</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">万桶，创下</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">4</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月底来最大周度增幅，显著高于市场预期。原油库存的意外大增令油价蒙上阴影。受此影响，国际油价当天重挫近</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">3%</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">，布伦特油价自</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">5</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月初以来首次跌破</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">44</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">美元关口。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　高盛分析师认为，原油市场正处于典型的熊市后期阶段，预计全球原油市场将在下半年出现</span>“温和”的供过于求的状况，到<span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">2017</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年中油价将在每桶</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">45-50</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">美元附近交投。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　摩根士丹利上周发布的报告也不看好油价前景，预计下半年原油价格可能跌至每桶</span>35<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">美元。该行分析师表示，支撑近期原油价格上涨的积极因素正在消退，精炼油持续且严重供过于求，主要成品油需求明显放缓。经济增长前景下滑、宏观风险等都强化了原油价格的下行风险。</span></span></p><p><br/></p>','高盛预计美元走强成油价最大风险','　　高盛27日发布的最新报告认为，美元进一步走强将成为短期内油价面临的最大风险。美国以外地区经济的不确定性，以及美联储潜在的加息预期，都可能推动美元进一步走强，从而导致油价下跌。自6月初以来，布伦特油价已经下跌超过15%，同期美元指数涨幅接近4%。','1','1','2017-03-11 18:59:31','','0','','','0','{\"thumb\":\"\"}','0','0','0','0','','');INSERT INTO ts_posts ( `id`, `post_author`, `post_keywords`, `post_source`, `post_date`, `post_content`, `post_title`, `post_excerpt`, `post_status`, `comment_status`, `post_modified`, `post_content_filtered`, `post_parent`, `post_type`, `post_mime_type`, `comment_count`, `smeta`, `post_hits`, `post_like`, `istop`, `recommended`, `page_tpl`, `page_tpls` ) VALUES  ('249','1','原油日均产量升至3341万桶','','2017-03-11 19:01:42','<p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　外媒周五</span>(7<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">29</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">日</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">)</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">调查结果显示，石油输出国组织</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">(OPEC)7</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月原油产量或创近期历史最高水平，因伊拉克产量增加，同时尼日利亚石油设施尽管遭受军事袭击，出口仍小幅增加。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　调查显示，</span>OPEC<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">最大出口国沙特的产量保持在接近纪录高位，因国内季节性需求增加，同时该国继续贯彻不减产来提振价格的策略，全力以赴捍卫自身的市场份额。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　根据行业人士提供的船运数据和信息统计显示，</span>7<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月份</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">OPEC</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">原油日均供应量升至</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">3341</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">万桶，</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">6</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月日供应量修正后为</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">3331</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">万桶。如果重开部分利比亚石油设施的谈判取得成功，</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">OPEC</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">产量可能还会进一步增加。利比亚的冲突导致该国原油产量仅处于战前水平的一小部分。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　德国商业银行的</span>CarstenFritsch<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">指出，尽管早些时候重开部分设施的希望没能实现，但“可能很快将向已经供应充裕的市场释放更多原油”。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　印尼在</span>2015<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年重新成为</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">OPEC</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">成员，本月将有加蓬重返</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">OPEC</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">，该组织供应量将继续攀升，令历史比较数据也发生偏移。</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">7</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月来自其余成员国的日供应量为</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">3246</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">万桶，为自</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">1997</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年外媒开始进行调查以来的纪录最高水平。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　此外，</span>7<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月份伊拉克日均产量增加</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">9</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">万桶，为增幅最大的成员国，虽然一处管道泄漏限制了南部出口量，但伊拉克南部和北部港口出口仍增加。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　值得注意的是，尼日利亚的产量虽然受到原油设施遭受军事袭击的打击，但</span>7<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月出口仍高于</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">6</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月，但出口量仍大幅低于</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">2016</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年初的每日</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">200</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">万桶水平。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　更多数据显示，两大主要出口国产量基本维持稳定。调查发现，伊朗在西方制裁取消后，成为今年供应增加最快的成员国，虽然日均产量仅增加</span>2<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">万桶，但增幅目前最高。而沙特</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">7</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月日均产量经评估为</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">1050</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">万桶，接近</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">6</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月修正后的水平，也接近去年</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">6</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月录得的日产量</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">1056</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">万桶的纪录最高水平。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　在产量减少的国家中，利比亚产量小幅下降，因主要油田</span>Sarir<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">运营中断。委内瑞拉的供应则因现金紧缺承受下行压力，</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">7</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月产量进一步下滑。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　这项调查是依据外部消息人士提供的船运数据，以及石油公司、</span>OPEC<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">和咨询公司消息人士提供的信息。</span></span></p><p><br/></p>','7月OPEC原油日均产量升至3341万桶','　　外媒周五(7月29日)调查结果显示，石油输出国组织(OPEC)7月原油产量或创近期历史最高水平，因伊拉克产量增加，同时尼日利亚石油设施尽管遭受军事袭击，出口仍小幅增加。','1','1','2017-03-11 19:00:49','','0','','','0','{\"thumb\":\"\"}','0','0','0','0','','');INSERT INTO ts_posts ( `id`, `post_author`, `post_keywords`, `post_source`, `post_date`, `post_content`, `post_title`, `post_excerpt`, `post_status`, `comment_status`, `post_modified`, `post_content_filtered`, `post_parent`, `post_type`, `post_mime_type`, `comment_count`, `smeta`, `post_hits`, `post_like`, `istop`, `recommended`, `page_tpl`, `page_tpls` ) VALUES  ('250','1','加快能源绿色清洁可持续发展','','2017-03-11 19:03:14','<p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\">　 &nbsp;<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">新华社北京</span>7<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">28</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">日专电 “十三五”期间我国能源行业面临传统能源过剩、可再生能源发展遭遇瓶颈、能源运行效率有待提高等问题。专家认为，应该通过多种方式加快能源的绿色、清洁、可持续发展，以解决环境与能源发展矛盾。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　在</span>27<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">日中国华能集团等单位举办的“</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">2016</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">能源·绿色发展论坛”上，与会电力专家指出，当前，我国已经步入经济新常态和能源结构转型的新时代。随着环境问题日益凸显，能源系统优化迫在眉睫，推动能源的高效、清洁、可持续发展成为行业关注重点。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　国家能源局副局长郑栅洁表示，绿色低碳发展难题不仅是中国的难题，也是世界的难题，面对复杂多变的世界经济和能源形势，通过在能源领域实施一系列生产和消费革命，有信心让我国能源走上智能低碳发展道路。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　为推动建设绿色、低碳、清洁社会，中国华能集团公司总经理曹培玺建议，要加快实施终端电能替代，进一步提高电能在终端能源消费中的比例；推动可再生能源支持政策的有效落实，并增强清洁能源行业政策的稳定性和连续性；推动电力高新技术研发与应用，完善政策支持，加强规划引导。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　针对全球面临降低排放的同时要满足能源需求增长的难题，西门子股份公司总裁兼首席执行官凯飒认为，应该提升整个能源系统的效率，而灵活性和数字化是实现这一目标的有效途径。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　中国电力企业联合会专职副理事长王志轩建议，随着我国电力工业发展进入新阶段，应控制电源发展节奏，保证电源健康有序发展；可再生能源应坚持输出与就地消纳并重，并加快建立辅助服务市场，解决弃水、弃光、弃风问题；进一步规范电力市场化改革秩序，降低电力企业经营负担。</span></span></p><p><br/></p>','专家建议加快能源绿色清洁可持续发展','　  新华社北京7月28日专电 “十三五”期间我国能源行业面临传统能源过剩、可再生能源发展遭遇瓶颈、能源运行效率有待提高等问题。专家认为，应该通过多种方式加快能源的绿色、清洁、可持续发展，以解决环境与能源发展矛盾。','1','1','2017-03-11 19:02:29','','0','','','0','{\"thumb\":\"\"}','1','0','0','0','','');INSERT INTO ts_posts ( `id`, `post_author`, `post_keywords`, `post_source`, `post_date`, `post_content`, `post_title`, `post_excerpt`, `post_status`, `comment_status`, `post_modified`, `post_content_filtered`, `post_parent`, `post_type`, `post_mime_type`, `comment_count`, `smeta`, `post_hits`, `post_like`, `istop`, `recommended`, `page_tpl`, `page_tpls` ) VALUES  ('251','1','成品油价将两连跌','','2017-03-11 19:06:02','<p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　由于国际油价进入下行通道，调价周期内震荡走跌，国内汽柴油零售价也将再度迎来下调。根据多家分析机构预测，</span>8<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">4</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">日</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">24</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">时，国内成品油价格将进行下调，预计调整幅度在</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">150</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">元</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">/</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">吨至</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">205</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">元</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">/</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">吨之间。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　根据安迅思的预测，本轮国内汽柴油零售价跌幅预计在</span>205<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">元</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">/</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">吨，测算到零售价格</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">90</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">号汽油和</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">0</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">号柴油</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">(</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">全国平均</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">)</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">每升分别下调</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">0.15</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">元和</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">0.17</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">元。中宇资讯分析师朱英华表示，石油输出国组织</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">(OPEC)7</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月产量将创近期历史新高，令市场供应过剩担忧继续升温，同时美元回升对油价构成压力，预计</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">8</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">4</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">日</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">24</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">时成品油零售限价将下调</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">155</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">元</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">/</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">吨。金银岛分析师表示，预计本轮成品油下调幅度为</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">140</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">元</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">/</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">吨左右，折合升价约</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">0#0.12</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">元，</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">90#0.10</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">元。隆众石化成品油分析师王倩倩也表示，预计周四下调幅度会在</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">150</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">元</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">/</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">吨左右，下调趋势基本确定，年内首次“二连跌”将成为现实。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　对于成品油的后期走势，金银岛分析师表示，后期来看，由于国际油价仍将延续震荡下行，消息面利空因素不断，市场悲观氛围难消。安迅思成品油行业助理分析师邹亚男也表示，由于全球成品油供应充裕，欧佩克原油产量持续增加，预计短期内，国际油价下行趋势难有逆转。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\">&nbsp;</span></p><p><br/></p>','成品油价将两连跌 国际油价延续下行','　　由于国际油价进入下行通道，调价周期内震荡走跌，国内汽柴油零售价也将再度迎来下调。根据多家分析机构预测，8月4日24时，国内成品油价格将进行下调，预计调整幅度在150元/吨至205元/吨之间。','1','1','2017-03-11 19:05:22','','0','','','0','{\"thumb\":\"\"}','0','0','0','0','','');INSERT INTO ts_posts ( `id`, `post_author`, `post_keywords`, `post_source`, `post_date`, `post_content`, `post_title`, `post_excerpt`, `post_status`, `comment_status`, `post_modified`, `post_content_filtered`, `post_parent`, `post_type`, `post_mime_type`, `comment_count`, `smeta`, `post_hits`, `post_like`, `istop`, `recommended`, `page_tpl`, `page_tpls` ) VALUES  ('252','1','供给侧结构性改革','','2017-03-11 19:07:48','<p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　在当前我国正在进行的供给侧结构性改革中，去产能居于五大任务之首，也是我国经济转型升级的关键所在。半年来，从中央到地方，去产能的目标和方案逐渐明确，相关政策措施陆续出台，各地积极行动，找路径、想办法，去产能稳步推进。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　<strong>落后产能正加速出清</strong></span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　在河北张家口，提起刚刚拆除的</span>5<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">号高炉，河北钢铁集团宣钢公司炉工张继文仍是留恋不已。他曾为这座平均日产</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">1500</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">吨的高炉服务十多年，而如今，高炉已被解体。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　已有百年历史的煤炭</span>“老兵”徐州矿务集团，<span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">2015</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年先后关闭贵州兴隆等</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">8</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">对矿井，淘汰落后产能</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">447</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">万吨。今年将再退出产能</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">790</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">万吨。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　正是由于煤炭钢铁行业产能严重过剩，不断有矿井、高炉退出历史舞台。中国钢铁工业协会数据显示，去年我国粗钢产量近</span>8<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">亿吨，产能利用率不足</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">67%</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">。另据统计，去年我国原煤产量为</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">37.5</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">亿吨，煤炭产能超实际需求量</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">30%</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　过剩产能将钢煤行业拖入困境。</span>“一斤螺纹钢<span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">9</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">角多，一斤白菜</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">2</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">元多，以前常说便宜是卖个白菜价，现在连白菜价都卖不上。”在钢铁价格低谷时，冷水江钢铁集团董事长陈代富说，过剩行业去产能是绕不过去的坎。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　也就是在今年</span>2<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月，国务院出台《关于煤炭行业化解过剩产能实现脱困发展的意见》《关于钢铁行业化解过剩产能实现脱困发展的意见》，确定用</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">5</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年时间压减粗钢产能</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">1</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">亿吨至</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">1.5</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">亿吨，用</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">3</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年到</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">5</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年时间退出煤炭产能</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">5</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">亿吨左右、减量重组</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">5</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">亿吨左右。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　随后，国家设置千亿元专项奖补资金，鼓励钢煤行业通过市场化手段出清过剩产能；各地方政府结合自身实际，制定更为详细的操作方案，去产能按政府制定的路线图，进入实际操作阶段。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　中国企业研究院首席研究员李锦说：</span>“过去那些低端附加值以及能源消耗量大的企业要加速退出市场，特别是一些没有核心竞争力和先进技术的‘僵尸企业’，必须退出市场，不能有任何犹豫。”</span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\">　　</span><strong><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;font-size: 14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">人哪去、钱哪来，去产能面临诸多挑战</span></span></strong></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　任何一项改革都不是一帆风顺的，涉及众多企业和职工的去产能更是如此。人到哪里去，钱从哪里来，这些问题都是去产能面临的巨大挑战。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\">　　——山西大同煤矿集团今年将关闭<span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">7</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">座矿井，分流职工近万人；山西潞安矿业集团将在</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">3</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年内陆续分流</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">1</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">万人；武汉钢铁集团或需分流</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">5</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">万名职工……依国家去产能政策，钢铁、煤炭行业有近</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">180</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">万职工需要被分流安置。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\">　　——<span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">2015</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年年报数据显示，武汉钢铁股份有限公司亏损</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">75</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">亿元，鞍钢股份有限公司亏损近</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">46</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">亿元，大同煤业股份有限公司亏损</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">18</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">亿元……去年钢铁、煤炭出现行业性亏损，面对人员安置、转型升级，资金缺口仍大。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　为破解人员安置和资金难题，国家不仅专门设立主要用于职工安置的奖补资金，人社部还联合七部门制订去产能过程中职工安置的工作意见，要求从政策上引导、鼓励，多渠道分流安置职工，各地政府也纷纷出台相关支持政策。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　得益于此，</span>56<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">岁的武汉市民周汉华，去年底完成了从“武钢职工”向“快车司机”的角色转变。他现在每天能跑</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">10</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">多单，收入</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">100</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">元很轻松。加上车间按月发放的生活费，月收入基本赶上了武钢效益最好的时候。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　除了人与钱的难题之外，今年以来市场发生的价格波动让去产能之路更加艰难。据统计，螺纹钢主力合约价格从去年</span>12<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月的每吨</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">1600</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">多元一路上涨至今年</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">4</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月的每吨近</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">2800</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">元；动力煤期货价格从今年</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">1</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月每吨接近</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">300</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">元开始上涨，中间略有回调，截至</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">7</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">29</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">日，累计涨幅已达</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">50%</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　市场回暖引得部分停产企业复产，增加了去产能的复杂性。针对这一新情况，一些地方迅速采取措施予以应对。如，河北在</span>4<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月份紧急下文要求全省坚决禁止违规新建钢铁产能和已封停钢铁设备复产，湖北、江苏等多地，则是政府回头看，严禁关停企业复产。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><strong><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;font-size: 14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　在</span>“去”中谋求更高质量发展</span></strong></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　尽管困难重重，去产能这项工作一直在向前推进。据相关部门发布的数据，通过破产清算、减量置换等多种方式，上半年全国共退出煤炭产能</span>7227<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">万吨、钢铁产能</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">1300</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">多万吨，均完成今年目标的</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">30%</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">左右。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\">　　“去产能并不是简单的‘做减法’，而是在‘去’的过程中加快结构调整和产业布局。”徐矿集团董事长吴志刚说，通过合作开发建设大型煤电一体化项目，控股、参股电厂等方式，公司正不断向煤基产业链上下游延伸。</span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　去产能只是手段，助推企业和行业脱困才是目的。</span>“在钢铁和煤炭行业，化解过剩产能的目的都是要使产业结构得到优化，资源利用效率得到提高，行业扭亏脱困升级，企业经济效益好转，市场预期明显向好。”李锦说。</span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　近日，国务院常务会议提出，确保完成今年化解过剩粗钢产能</span>4500<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">万吨左右、煤炭产能</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">2.5</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">亿吨以上的硬目标，对于在产能过剩领域新上项目、新增产能或淘汰产能死灰复燃的，将被严肃追责。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　会议并再次提出，要坚持地方主责、企业主体，发挥市场机制作用，更有效推动去产能，明确强调注重运用法治化、市场化手段，支持企业加快兼并重组，提高产业集中度，并妥善做好职工转岗等工作。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\">　　“这意味着，下一阶段，去产能工作的力度将进一步加大。”李锦说，下半年将从目标任务的分解、政策的落地更多转到实质性推进阶段，去产能速度有望加快。</span></p><p><br/></p>','供给侧结构性改革 去产能稳步推进','　　在当前我国正在进行的供给侧结构性改革中，去产能居于五大任务之首，也是我国经济转型升级的关键所在。半年来，从中央到地方，去产能的目标和方案逐渐明确，相关政策措施陆续出台，各地积极行动，找路径、想办法，去产能稳步推进。','1','1','2017-03-11 19:06:12','','0','','','0','{\"thumb\":\"\"}','0','0','0','0','','');INSERT INTO ts_posts ( `id`, `post_author`, `post_keywords`, `post_source`, `post_date`, `post_content`, `post_title`, `post_excerpt`, `post_status`, `comment_status`, `post_modified`, `post_content_filtered`, `post_parent`, `post_type`, `post_mime_type`, `comment_count`, `smeta`, `post_hits`, `post_like`, `istop`, `recommended`, `page_tpl`, `page_tpls` ) VALUES  ('253','1','上半年原油进口量创历史最高','','2017-03-11 19:09:47','<p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　海关总署最新发布的数据显示，上半年中国进口原油</span>1.865<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">亿吨，比去年同期增</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">2315</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">万吨；增速达</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">14.2%</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">，高于</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">2013</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年、</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">2014</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年和</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">2015</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年的</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">4%</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">、</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">9.5%</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">和</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">8.8%</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">。其中，今年</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">3</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月、</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">4</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月和</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">5</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月，单月进口量都超过</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">3200</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">万吨，均为历史最高水平。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　专家分析认为，成品油设</span>“地板价”、进口权逐步放开等政策是上半年原油大量进口的主要原因。不过，随着近期国际油价再度出现下行苗头，加之国内需求放缓，后期成品油销售压力将进一步加大。</span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　近几年，国际石油市场的供需格局迅速变化。</span>2014<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年国际油价从年中每桶</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">100</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">美元以上一路下跌至每桶</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">60</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">美元左右，并于</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">2015</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年完全陷入低迷。到</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">2016</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">2</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月中旬，国际油价已跌到每桶</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">30</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">美元以下，纽约油价甚至一度跌至</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">12</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年来的低点。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　面对不断下跌的国际油价，</span>2016<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">1</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">13</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">日，国家发改委宣布为成品油价格调整设置“地板价”，即当国际市场油价低于每桶</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">40</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">美元时，汽柴油最高零售价格不降低。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　受这一政策影响，中国原油进口量从</span>1<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月份的</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">2669</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">万吨猛增至</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">2</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月份的</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">3180</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">万吨。随着</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">2</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月份国际油价进一步跌至每桶</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">30</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">美元以下，中国原油进口在</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">3</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月份迅速跃上</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">3200</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">万吨的历史最高水平，并在随后几个月保持高位。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　根据国家发改委的数据，今年上半年，我国原油产量同比下降</span>4.8%<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">，而原油加工量则同比增长</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">8.9%</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">。这说明，石油企业以更便宜的进口原油替代国产。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\">　　2015<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年中石油大庆油田就启动了减产计划，今年初中石化胜利油田</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">50</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年来首次关停下属</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">4</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">个小油田，中海油有限公司也下调了</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">2016</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年的产量目标。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\">　　“只是减少了一些成本较高的产量。”中石油一位内部人士对记者说，“是否关井，关键要看成本，一般情况下，只要油井的现金成本比油价低都不会停。”</span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　推动原油进口量猛增的另一股力量是民营炼油企业。来自国家发改委的数据显示，截至目前已有</span>15<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">家企业获得进口原油配额，总量超过</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">6000</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">万吨。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　山东是民营炼厂最集中的省份，同时也是进口原油重要的上岸港口之一。一家民营炼油企业相关负责人告诉记者，原油进口权放开后，企业进口原油到货比较集中，特别是去年年底集中批准了一批进口配额。</span>“突如其来的增量与港口吞吐能力以及储存能力不匹配，曾一度造成青岛港油轮积压。”</span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　但是，这位人士对国内成品油需求增量却不乐观。</span>“为了降低运行成本，炼厂基本都在满负荷生产，但销售压力很大。”</span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　业内人士指出，随着近期国际油价再度出现下行苗头，以及国内成品油销售压力加大，前期大量进口原油的企业面临着一定的库存上升压力。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　国家发改委数据显示，今年上半年中国成品油消费量同比增长</span>4.4%<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">，其中汽油增长</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">13.7%</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">，而与宏观经济景气更为相关的柴油消费量却下降</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">3.1%</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">。与此同时，上半年中国出口成品油</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">2147</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">万吨，同比大幅增长</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">45.2%</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　根据新华社石油价格系统数据，截至</span>2016<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">6</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月底，成品油库存较</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">2015</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">12</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月底上升了</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">13%</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">以上。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　分析人士指出，这说明国内成品油需求增速在放缓，企业销售压力加大。卓创资讯成品油分析师秦文平说，从国内成品油需求面看，七八月份，柴油需求处于传统淡季，加之目前库存量高企且压力巨大，预计三季度消库及销售压力仍将同时存在。另外随着原油进口量继续增加，国内炼厂开工负荷有望加大，受产量大增的影响，成品油市场竞争将再度升级，批发环节的竞争也将加剧。炼油企业下半年盈利水平或不及上半年。</span></span></p><p><br/></p>','上半年原油进口量创历史最高 需求放缓市场承压明显','　　海关总署最新发布的数据显示，上半年中国进口原油1.865亿吨，比去年同期增2315万吨；增速达14.2%，高于2013年、2014年和2015年的4%、9.5%和8.8%。其中，今年3月、4月和5月，单月进口量都超过3200万吨，均为历史最高水平。','1','1','2017-03-11 19:08:23','','0','','','0','{\"thumb\":\"\"}','0','0','0','0','','');INSERT INTO ts_posts ( `id`, `post_author`, `post_keywords`, `post_source`, `post_date`, `post_content`, `post_title`, `post_excerpt`, `post_status`, `comment_status`, `post_modified`, `post_content_filtered`, `post_parent`, `post_type`, `post_mime_type`, `comment_count`, `smeta`, `post_hits`, `post_like`, `istop`, `recommended`, `page_tpl`, `page_tpls` ) VALUES  ('254','1','国际油价3日大幅反弹逾3%','','2017-03-11 19:10:40','<p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　据新华社</span>8<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">4</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">日报道，美国能源信息局当天公布的数据显示，上周美国汽油库存下降</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">330</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">万桶，远超市场预期，提振国际油价。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">此外，国际油价经近期连续下跌之后也存在一定的技术性反弹要求。</span>2<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">日，纽约油价自</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">4</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月份以来首次跌破每桶</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">40</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">美元大关，收于每桶</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">39.51</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">美元。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　截至当日收盘时，纽约商品交易所</span>9<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月交货的轻质原油期货价格上涨</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">1.32</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">美元，收于每桶</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">40.83</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">美元，涨幅为</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">3.3%</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">。</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">10</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月交货的伦敦布伦特原油期货价格上涨</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">1.30</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">美元，收于每桶</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">43.10</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">美元，涨幅为</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">3.1%</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\">&nbsp;</span></p><p><br/></p>','国际油价3日大幅反弹逾3%','　　据新华社8月4日报道，美国能源信息局当天公布的数据显示，上周美国汽油库存下降330万桶，远超市场预期，提振国际油价。','1','1','2017-03-11 19:09:57','','0','','','0','{\"thumb\":\"\"}','0','0','0','0','','');INSERT INTO ts_posts ( `id`, `post_author`, `post_keywords`, `post_source`, `post_date`, `post_content`, `post_title`, `post_excerpt`, `post_status`, `comment_status`, `post_modified`, `post_content_filtered`, `post_parent`, `post_type`, `post_mime_type`, `comment_count`, `smeta`, `post_hits`, `post_like`, `istop`, `recommended`, `page_tpl`, `page_tpls` ) VALUES  ('255','1','海南建成国内最大商业石油储备基地','','2017-03-11 19:12:40','<p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　华信洋浦石油储基地项目</span>(<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">一期工程</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">)</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">投产庆典仪式</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">7</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">8</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">日在海南洋浦举行。洋浦的油气储备能力突破</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">1000</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">万立方米，成为国内最大的商业石油储备基地之一。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　华信洋浦石油储备基地是中国华信目前投入最大的石油储备项目之一。项目整体建设规模将达</span>1200<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">万立方米，用地</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">3300</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">亩，总投资达</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">150</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">亿元，分三期滚动建设。一期工程投资</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">30.5</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">亿人民币，用地</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">800</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">亩，库容</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">280</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">万立方米，是目前海南省最大的石油储备库。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　华信洋浦石油储备基地一期项目于</span>2013<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">10</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">28</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">日开工建设</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">, 2015</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">12</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">18</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">日实现中交</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">, 2016</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">7</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">2</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">日投产。中国华信董事会主席叶简明非常重视海南洋浦大型石油储备基地建设</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">,</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">亲自筹划</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">,</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">多次亲临现场深入指导。项目指挥部按照叶简明主席提出的“建成国内一流</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">,</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">国际领先的石油储备库”的要求</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">,</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">超前谋划，科学组织，克服建设规模大、施工周期长、作业条件艰苦等诸多困难</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">,</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">将一座宏伟壮观的油库展现在海南人民面前。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　华信洋浦石油储备基地一期项日采用</span>EPC<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">总承包的建设管理模式，始终坚持“设计一流、人才一流、管理一流、设备一流”的标准，牢牢把住项目建设“质量、安全、投资、进度”四控关</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">,</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">确保油库在自控、安全、消防、环保系统等方面均处于国内、国际先进水平。油库自控系统采用的是目前国际上最先进的</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">SCADA</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">系统，即数据采集与监视控制系统，可以对现场运行设备进行监视和远程控制。为了确保安全，油库配有有毒可燃气体检测系统、线型感温火灾报警系统、周界安防系统、视频监控系统等目前技术领先的安保系统。在消防方面</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">,</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">华信参建了洋浦化工园区的海陆消防站，库区消防用水、泡抹供给等按两个十万立方米的油罐同时灭火进行设计，并对原有的消防水罐、消防水泵、消防供水管道、泡沫罐、泡沫泵等进行了优化变更设计，油库所配置的消防系统是目前国内己经建成的大型油库中标准最高的。在环保设施建设方面</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">,</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">也采取了高标准的防止污染措施，油罐基础、罐区地面全部使用进口防渗膜做了防渗处理。同时，还建立了完善的库区污水和初期雨水的电控分流收集处理系统，确保污水排放达标。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　华信洋浦石油储备基地项目一期投产成功</span>,<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">为海南洋浦经济开发区打造“一港三基地”，促进洋浦石油资源和市场的合理配置、结构调整，建成可持续发展的国家级石化工业园区和油品自由贸易港区莫定了坚实基础，对实现国家“一带一路”战略和维护能源安全具有重要战略意义。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　据了解，华信洋浦一期项目是中国华信首个石油储备的投产项目，为中国华信关键战略节点布局打下坚实基础。中国华信以拓展国际能源经济合作为战略，打造有组织的能源国际投行，立足欧洲布局油气终端，在法国、西班牙、罗马尼亚等地中海、黑海周边国家拥有</span>1000<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">多座加油站和上百座油库中转站，依托炼化加工、储运销售为一体的规模化油气终端体系，不断在阿布扎比、乍得、哈萨克斯坦拓展上游油气资源权益，投资获取油气区块，获得长期稳定的石油供应，拥有</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">15</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年以上油气权益每年</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">6000</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">万吨。同时公司在国内海南洋浦、山东日照、广东珠海、江苏靖江等沿海沿江港口建设大型石油储备基地，与阿布扎比国家石油公司战略合作，在富察伊拉建立石油中转储备基地，在哈萨克斯坦拥有石油、天然气转换站，在格鲁吉亚拥有石油储备及巴统港船运、码头物流设施，通过中亚、黑海、地中海地区物流基础设施投资，推动与国内日照港、大连港、营口港的物流合作，与中铁建立中铁中亚物流公司，开展液化天然气铁路运输，与中船以新加坡为基地建立海上浮舱油储销，实现国内国际市场联动，提升资源配置能力和效率。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　洋浦一期油库运营后，依托在海外获取的上游资源优势，建立原油调油基地，与中化集团、山东地炼及台湾</span>“中油”合作，开展对外来料加工，拓展东南亚市场成品油销售，实现国内外能源资源互联互通。同时，华信在海南设立洋浦国际能源交易中心<span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">,</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">开展现货交易</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">,</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">把华信洋浦石油库建设成国际市场交割库</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">,</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">在海南打造面向亚太地区的能源金融中心。</span></span></p><p><br/></p>','海南建成国内最大商业石油储备基地','　　华信洋浦石油储基地项目(一期工程)投产庆典仪式7月8日在海南洋浦举行。洋浦的油气储备能力突破1000万立方米，成为国内最大的商业石油储备基地之一。','1','1','2017-03-11 19:11:55','','0','','','0','{\"thumb\":\"\"}','0','0','0','0','','');INSERT INTO ts_posts ( `id`, `post_author`, `post_keywords`, `post_source`, `post_date`, `post_content`, `post_title`, `post_excerpt`, `post_status`, `comment_status`, `post_modified`, `post_content_filtered`, `post_parent`, `post_type`, `post_mime_type`, `comment_count`, `smeta`, `post_hits`, `post_like`, `istop`, `recommended`, `page_tpl`, `page_tpls` ) VALUES  ('256','1','中石化出售管道公司50%股权','','2017-03-11 19:15:39','<p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">&nbsp; 　为川气东送管道公司引入外部资本，用于偿还营运资金和债务；上半年该公司资产负债率超</span>90%</span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　日前，伴随着中石化关于旗下管道业务引资的一纸公告，中国油气行业的混合所有制改革再次引发外界关注。中石化在北交所网站上公布了川气东送管道业务的混改引资方案，拟为这家资产负债率超过</span>90%<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">的管道公司募资超百亿元“解渴”。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><strong><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;font-size: 14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　负债压力倒逼对外增资</span></span></strong></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　中石化昨日发布公告称，公司董事会审议通过了关于川气东送管道业务引资的议案。出售完成后，中石化将继续持有运营川气东送管道公司的</span>50%<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">股份。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　新京报记者昨日自北交所获悉，本次增资截止日为</span>9<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">28</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">日，本次增资目的是通过增资扩股的方式引入外部资本，募集天然气管道业务未来发展的资金，促进中国石化天然气业务发展。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　方案显示，中石化拟公开征集投资方数量不超过</span>15<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">名，单个投资人的投资金额要求是不低于</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">10</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">亿元。如果吸引的投资方达到</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">15</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">个，则有望引资</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">150</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">亿元。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　公开信息显示，川气东送管道从</span>2007<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年开工，</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">2010</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年投产，总投资额约为</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">626</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">亿元，主要将中石化在四川盆地开采的天然气送到东部，气源包括涪陵页岩气田等。此前为补充管道建设资金，中石化已经于</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">2007</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">11</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月发行了总规模为</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">200</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">亿元川气东送工程公司债券。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　如今，该管道负债已经较高。截至</span>6<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月底，中石化川气东送天然气管道公司资产总计</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">196</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">亿元，而负债高达</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">178</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">亿元，资产负债率高达</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">90.8%</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　在川气东送管道处于高负债、迫切需要资金支持的情况下，来自中石化内部的支持要打个问号。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　近年来，伴随着油气行业下滑，中石化积累了较高债务。查阅一季报可知，截至</span>3<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月底负债总额为</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">6012</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">亿元，同期总资产为</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">13977</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">亿元，负债率</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">43%</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">。同时，查阅</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">2015</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年年报可知，中石化还大幅压缩了投资开支，</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">2016</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年资本开支</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">1122</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">亿元，同比降低</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">27.4%</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　北交所信息显示，在本次增资中，川气东送管道的原股东将不参与。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　中石化方面表示，本次募集资金将用于两方面，其一是继续推进天然气管道的建设，其二便是用于一般营运资金和偿还债务，改善资本结构。</span></span></p><p><br/></p>','中石化出售管道公司50%股权 负债压力倒逼对外增资','  　为川气东送管道公司引入外部资本，用于偿还营运资金和债务；上半年该公司资产负债率超90%','1','1','2017-03-11 19:14:22','','0','','','0','{\"thumb\":\"\"}','0','0','0','0','','');INSERT INTO ts_posts ( `id`, `post_author`, `post_keywords`, `post_source`, `post_date`, `post_content`, `post_title`, `post_excerpt`, `post_status`, `comment_status`, `post_modified`, `post_content_filtered`, `post_parent`, `post_type`, `post_mime_type`, `comment_count`, `smeta`, `post_hits`, `post_like`, `istop`, `recommended`, `page_tpl`, `page_tpls` ) VALUES  ('257','1','促进石化产业持续健康发展','','2017-03-11 19:17:36','<p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　据中国政府网</span>3<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">日消息</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">,</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">为贯彻落实党中央、国务院关于推进供给侧结构性改革、建设制造强国的决策部署</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">,</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">促进石化产业持续健康发展</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">,</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">国务院办公厅发布关于石化产业调结构促转型增效益的指导意见。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　主要目标方面</span>,<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">指导意见提出</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">,</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">产能结构逐步优化。加快淘汰工艺技术落后、安全隐患大、环境污染严重的落后产能</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">,</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">有效化解产能过剩矛盾。烯烃、芳烃等基础原料的保障能力显著增强</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">,</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">化工新材料等高端产品的自给率明显提高</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">,</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">产业发展质量和核心竞争能力得到进一步提升。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　产业布局趋于合理。全面启动城镇人口密集区和环境敏感区域的危险化学品生产企业搬迁入园或转产关闭工作。新建炼化项目全部进入石化基地</span>,<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">新建化工项目全部进入化工园区</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">,</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">形成一批具有国际竞争力的大型企业集团和化工园区。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　绿色发展全面推进。石化行业万元工业增加值能源消耗、二氧化碳排放量、用水量分别比</span>“十二五”末下降<span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">8%</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">、</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">10%</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">和</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">14%</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">。企业主要污染物排放达到石油炼制工业、石油化学工业、合成树脂工业、无机化学工业污染物排放标准要求。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　创新能力明显增强。科研投入占全行业主营业务收入的比例不低于</span>1.2%,<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">产学研用协同创新体系日益完善</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">,</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">突破一批关键共性技术</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">,</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">研制一批重大成套装备和核心零部件</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">,</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">建成一批综合性服务型研发平台</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">,</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">培育业务精湛、结构合理的创新型人才队伍。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　重点任务方面</span>,<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">指导意见提出</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">,</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">严格控制尿素、磷铵、电石、烧碱、聚氯乙烯、纯碱、黄磷等过剩行业新增产能</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">,</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">研究制定产能置换方案</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">,</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">充分利用安全、环保、节能、价格等措施</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">,</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">推动落后和低效产能退出</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">,</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">为先进产能创造更大市场空间。在中西部符合资源环境条件的地区</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">,</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">结合大型煤炭基地开发</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">,</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">按照环境准入条件要求</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">,</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">有序发展现代煤化工产业。鼓励建设加氢裂化、连续重整、异构化和烷基化等清洁油品装置</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">,</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">及时升级油品质量。加快炼油和乙烯装置技术改造</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">,</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">适时调整柴汽比</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">,</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">优化原料结构。落实财税、金融、土地、职工安置等支持政策</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">,</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">破除跨地区、跨所有制兼并重组的体制机制障碍</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">,</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">为企业兼并重组营造公平的市场环境。重点推动传统化工企业兼并重组</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">,</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">优化资金、技术、人才等要素配置</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">,</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">提升产业集中度和竞争力</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">,</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">形成一批具有国际竞争力的大型企业集团。</span></span></p><p><br/></p>','国务院发文促进石化产业持续健康发展','　　据中国政府网3日消息,为贯彻落实党中央、国务院关于推进供给侧结构性改革、建设制造强国的决策部署,促进石化产业持续健康发展,国务院办公厅发布关于石化产业调结构促转型增效益的指导意见。','1','1','2017-03-11 19:16:43','','0','','','0','{\"thumb\":\"\"}','1','0','0','0','','');INSERT INTO ts_posts ( `id`, `post_author`, `post_keywords`, `post_source`, `post_date`, `post_content`, `post_title`, `post_excerpt`, `post_status`, `comment_status`, `post_modified`, `post_content_filtered`, `post_parent`, `post_type`, `post_mime_type`, `comment_count`, `smeta`, `post_hits`, `post_like`, `istop`, `recommended`, `page_tpl`, `page_tpls` ) VALUES  ('258','1','11家石油化工类上市企业6家中报预喜','','2017-03-11 19:18:33','<p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\">　　“现阶段，石化产业在适应经济新常态方面仍然面临很大挑战，石化企业经营绩效欠佳。此次发布的《指导意见》在化解过剩产能、优化产业布局、推动企业兼并重组等方面的部署，有助于推动石化产业结构调整以及转型升级。此外，也会对相关企业的兼并重组产生促进作用。”国务院发展研究中心企业研究所国企研究室主任项安波在接受《证券日报》记者采访时表示。</span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　近日，国务院办公厅发布《关于石化产业调结构促转型增效益的指导意见》</span>(<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">以下简称《指导意见》</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">)</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">，部署石化产业结构调整和转型升级工作。《指导意见》提出，要努力化解过剩产能，优化产业布局，推动企业兼并重组等内容，这意味着我国石化产业去产能工作已逐渐提上日程。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　业内人士认为，与煤炭等行业的总量过剩不同，石化行业是典型的结构性过剩，即高端产品不足，低端品太多。随着国际油价的大幅走低，石化行业的结构矛盾更趋尖锐。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　卓创咨询成品油分析师徐娜在接受《证券日报》记者采访时表示，石化行业包括诸多板块，而在开采、炼化、批发、终端等环节中，如果国际原油价格长期低位徘徊，将对国内开采成本造成巨大压力，进而缩减企业利润。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　《证券日报》记者从同花顺数据得知，目前沪深两市共有</span>17<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">家石油化工类</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">(</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">包括石油加工、石油贸易两类</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">)</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">上市公司，而在这</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">17</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">家上市公司中，目前已有</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">11</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">家上市公司公布了</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">2016</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年中报预告，其中</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">3</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">家公司预增、</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">1</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">家续盈、</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">3</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">家公司预减、</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">1</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">家略减、</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">1</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">家首亏、</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">2</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">家扭亏。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　徐娜分析称，受油气价格长期低位运行影响，石油加工以及石油贸易领域将所有受益。具体来看，石油加工企业如果采用进口原油资源，其炼制成本得益于油价的下调将有所降低；对于石油贸易企业来说，由于原油价格出现大幅度降低，进而拖累国内成品油价格出现下滑。当前国内汽、柴油批零价差在不断扩大，有利于扩大贸易商的利润空间，并利好石油贸易发展。</span></span></p><p><br/></p>','11家石油化工类上市企业6家中报预喜','　　“现阶段，石化产业在适应经济新常态方面仍然面临很大挑战，石化企业经营绩效欠佳。此次发布的《指导意见》在化解过剩产能、优化产业布局、推动企业兼并重组等方面的部署，有助于推动石化产业结构调整以及转型升级。此外，也会对相关企业的兼并重组产生促进作用。”国务院发展研究中心企业研究所国企研究室主任项安波在接受《证券日报》记者采访时表示。','1','1','2017-03-11 19:17:47','','0','','','0','{\"thumb\":\"\"}','1','0','0','0','','');INSERT INTO ts_posts ( `id`, `post_author`, `post_keywords`, `post_source`, `post_date`, `post_content`, `post_title`, `post_excerpt`, `post_status`, `comment_status`, `post_modified`, `post_content_filtered`, `post_parent`, `post_type`, `post_mime_type`, `comment_count`, `smeta`, `post_hits`, `post_like`, `istop`, `recommended`, `page_tpl`, `page_tpls` ) VALUES  ('259','1','国内油价“两连跌”来袭','','2017-03-11 19:20:28','<p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\">　　4<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">日下午，国家发改委发布通知，根据近期国际市场油价变化情况，按照现行成品油价格形成机制，自</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">2016</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">8</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">4</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">日</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">24</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">时起，国内汽、柴油价格每吨分别降低</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">220</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">元和</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">215</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">元，测算到零售价格</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">90</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">号汽油和</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">0</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">号柴油（全国平均）每升分别降低</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">0.16</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">元和</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">0.18</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">元。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　至此，国内油价迎来年内第三次下调，也是年内首次</span>“两连跌”，降幅创年内最大。除海南外，国内大部分地区的<span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">92</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">号、</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">93</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">号汽油继续处于“五元”时代。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　记者梳理发现，</span>2015<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">8</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">4</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">日</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">24</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">时，国内成品油零售限价同样迎来下调，且跌幅与本轮调价完全吻合。以北京为例，</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">2015</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">8</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">5</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">日，</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">92</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">号汽油最高零售价格每升</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">6.11</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">元。时隔一年，得益于国际油价长期震荡走低，北京</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">92</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">号汽油汽油最高零售价格每升</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">5.75</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">元，同比下滑</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">0.36</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">元</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">/</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">升，跌幅达</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">5.9%</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　截至目前，今年以来，我国成品油价格已经历</span>15<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">轮调价周期，其中，三次下调、两次搁浅、四次上调、六次因国际油价低于每桶</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">40</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">美元的“地板价”而不调整。汽、柴油价格累计分别上涨每吨</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">90</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">元和</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">85</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">元。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　本次油价下调后，以</span>50<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">升油箱的车私家车为例，车主加满一箱油，大约可以节省</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">8</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">元钱。这对于消费者来讲无疑是一大喜事。隆众石化网薛群介绍，一辆普通私家车平均每行驶一千公里费用将会减少</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">15</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">元左右。大型物流运输车辆平均每行驶一万公里，燃油费用减少</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">680</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">元左右。下一次调价窗口将在</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">2016</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">8</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">18</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">日</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">24</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">时开启。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　对于国内成品油市场走势，卓创资讯成品油分析师刘新章表示，由于国际原油价格一路下探，成品油批发价格随之滑至谷底，而零售价格虽也下滑，但远不及批发价下滑幅度，从而导致批零价差达到近十年的峰值。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　据卓创统计，截至</span>8<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">4</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">日，全国汽油批发均价在</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">5551</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">元</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">/</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">吨，汽油批零价差在</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">2211</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">元</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">/</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">吨，同比上涨</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">809</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">元</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">/</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">吨，涨幅</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">57.7%</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">；全国柴油批发均价在</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">4611</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">元</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">/</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">吨，柴油批零价差在</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">1353</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">元</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">/</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">吨，同比上涨</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">237</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">元</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">/</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">吨，涨幅</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">22.2%</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">。以目前的原油及成品油供需基本面来看，国际和国内供应过剩问题依旧困扰着市场，后期汽柴油批发价格很难出现大幅改善。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　下一次调价窗口将在</span>2016<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">8</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">18</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">日</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">24</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">时开启。隆众石化网分析师李彦表示，以当前的国际原油价格水平计算，下一轮成品油调价仍存向下的趋势，不过油价并未出现崩塌式下滑，在</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">40</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">美元附近已遭遇较强的下行阻力。当前油价最大的问题在于反弹乏力，因此均价不排除维持弱势的表现。近期</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">OPEC</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">产量居高不下，全球原油和成品油高库存主导，供应过剩忧虑难解，市场看空情绪随之再度增强，预计下一轮成品油调价下调或搁浅的可能性较大。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　卓创资讯成品油分析师秦文平也认为，从近期原油走势来看，面对</span>40<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">美元</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">/</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">桶的心理价位，多空争夺比较激烈，但整体震荡下行仍为大概率事件，市场争夺的焦点在于国际原油能否落入地板价以下。因此下一轮调价窗口期即</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">8</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">18</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">日</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">24</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">时，成品油限价将遭“停调或者下行的命运”，而上调基本无望。（记者 杜燕飞）</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　附：</span>2016<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年国内油价调整一览：</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\">　　1<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">13</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">日</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">24</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">时 国内汽、柴油价格每吨分别降低</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">140</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">元、</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">135</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">元</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\">　　1<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">27</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">日</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">24</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">时 国际油价低于每桶</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">40</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">美元 国内汽、柴油价格不作调整</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\">　　2<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">15</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">日</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">24</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">时 国际油价低于每桶</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">40</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">美元 国内汽、柴油价格不作调整</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\">　　2<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">29</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">日</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">24</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">时 国际油价低于每桶</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">40</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">美元 国内汽、柴油价格不作调整</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\">　　3<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">14</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">日</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">24</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">时 国际油价低于每桶</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">40</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">美元 国内汽、柴油价格不作调整</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\">　　3<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">28</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">日</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">24</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">时 国际油价低于每桶</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">40</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">美元 国内汽、柴油价格不作调整</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\">　　4<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">12</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">日</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">24</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">时 国际油价低于每桶</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">40</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">美元 国内汽、柴油价格不作调整</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\">　　4<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">26</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">日</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">24</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">时 国内汽、柴油价格每吨分别提高</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">165</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">元、</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">160</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">元</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\">　　5<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">11</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">日</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">24</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">时 国内汽、柴油价格每吨分别提高</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">120</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">元、</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">115</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">元</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\">　　5<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">25</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">日</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">24</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">时 国内汽、柴油价格每吨分别提高</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">210</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">元、</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">200</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">元</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\">　　6<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">8</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">日</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">24</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">时 国内汽、柴油价格每吨均提高</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">110</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">元</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\">　　6<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">23</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">日</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">24</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">时 调价幅度不足</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">50</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">元</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">/</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">吨 国内汽、柴油价格不作调整</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\">　　7<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">7</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">日</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">24</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">时 调价幅度不足</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">50</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">元</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">/</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">吨 国内汽、柴油价格不作调整</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\">　　7<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">21</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">日</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">24</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">时 国内汽、柴油价格每吨分别降低</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">155</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">元和</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">150</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">元</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\">　　8<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">4</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">日</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">24</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">时 国内汽、柴油价格每吨分别降低</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">220</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">元和</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">215</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">元</span></span></p><p><br/></p>','国内油价“两连跌”来袭 创年内最大降幅','　　4日下午，国家发改委发布通知，根据近期国际市场油价变化情况，按照现行成品油价格形成机制，自2016年8月4日24时起，国内汽、柴油价格每吨分别降低220元和215元，测算到零售价格90号汽油和0号柴油（全国平均）每升分别降低0.16元和0.18元。','1','1','2017-03-11 19:19:06','','0','','','0','{\"thumb\":\"\"}','0','0','0','0','','');INSERT INTO ts_posts ( `id`, `post_author`, `post_keywords`, `post_source`, `post_date`, `post_content`, `post_title`, `post_excerpt`, `post_status`, `comment_status`, `post_modified`, `post_content_filtered`, `post_parent`, `post_type`, `post_mime_type`, `comment_count`, `smeta`, `post_hits`, `post_like`, `istop`, `recommended`, `page_tpl`, `page_tpls` ) VALUES  ('260','1','国际油价5日下跌 ','','2017-03-11 19:22:27','<p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　国际油价</span>5<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">日收盘下跌。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　美国劳工部当天公布的数据显示，</span>7<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月份美国非农部门新增就业岗位</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">25.5</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">万个，远高于市场预期的</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">18</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">万个。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　良好的就业数据提振了美元，而美元走强则降低了以美元计价的石油的投资吸引力。衡量美元对其他六种主要货币汇率的美元指数当天上涨</span>0.46%<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">，在汇市尾市涨至</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">96.196</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　此外，美国油田技术服务公司贝克休斯</span>5<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">日发布的数据显示，本周美国运营的油田钻井数量连续第</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">6</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">周上涨，显示美国页岩油厂商持续增产，这也令市场承压。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　截至当日收盘时，纽约商品交易所</span>9<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月交货的轻质原油期货价格下跌</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">0.13</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">美元，收于每桶</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">41.80</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">美元，跌幅为</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">0.3%</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">。</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">10</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月交货的伦敦布伦特原油期货价格下跌</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">0.02</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">美元，收于每桶</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">44.27</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">美元，跌幅不足</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">0.1%</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">。</span></span></p><p><br/></p>','国际油价5日下跌 报收每桶41.80美元','　　国际油价5日收盘下跌。','1','1','2017-03-11 19:21:36','','0','','','0','{\"thumb\":\"\"}','1','0','0','0','','');INSERT INTO ts_posts ( `id`, `post_author`, `post_keywords`, `post_source`, `post_date`, `post_content`, `post_title`, `post_excerpt`, `post_status`, `comment_status`, `post_modified`, `post_content_filtered`, `post_parent`, `post_type`, `post_mime_type`, `comment_count`, `smeta`, `post_hits`, `post_like`, `istop`, `recommended`, `page_tpl`, `page_tpls` ) VALUES  ('261','1','我国石化经济运行稳中有进筑底盘整','','2017-03-11 19:24:22','<p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　上半年，我国石油和化工行业累计增加值同比增长</span>8.7%<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">，经济运行总体平稳、稳中有进，呈筑底盘整的态势。这是记者近日在长沙召开的</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">2016</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">上半年全国石油和化工行业经济运行形势分析会上了解到的情况。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　会议发布了上半年石化行业经济运行报告。中国石油和化学工业联合会副会长傅向升将上半年石化行业经济运行形势概括为</span>5<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">句话，即经济运行总体平稳、主要产品消费增长较快、价格降幅收窄、结构优化取得进展、节能降耗效果明显。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　工业和信息化部运行监测协调局副局长黄利斌表示，全国主要行业工业增加值增速</span>2015<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年全年和</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">2016</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年上半年分别为</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">6.1%</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">和</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">6%</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">。而石化行业</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">2015</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年全年和</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">2016</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">上半年增速均高于全国平均水平。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　傅向升认为，石油和化工行业上半年经济运行总体情况与国民经济工业领域的运行态势基本一致。但当前行业经济运行的态势还不稳定，筑底盘整的基础还很脆弱，下行压力依然很大，矛盾和问题比较突出。主要表现为：效益分化明显、投资持续疲软、进出口压力持续加大、单位成本居高不下。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　对于全年的行业经济运行形势，傅向升提出了两点预测：一是综合分析国内外大环境和行业生产、价格走势等综合因素，预测全年石化行业增加值同比增幅约</span>8.8%<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">。主营业务收入</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">13.33</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">万亿元左右，同比增长</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">1.0%</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">，其中化工行业主营业务收入约为</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">9.28</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">万亿元，增长</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">5.0%</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">。行业利润总额约为</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">6300</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">亿元，同比下降</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">3.0%</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">，其中化工行业利润总额</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">5010</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">亿元左右，增幅</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">9.0%</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　二是从市场消费看，预计全年原油表观消费量约</span>5.83<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">亿吨，同比增加</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">6.5%;</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">天然气表观消费量约</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">2074</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">亿立方米，增幅约</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">10.0%;</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">成品油表观消费量约</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">3.16</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">亿吨，与上年持平，其中柴油表观消费量约</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">1.64</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">亿吨，下降</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">5.5%;</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">化肥表观消费量约</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">7036</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">万吨，增幅</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">5.0%</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">，其中尿素表观消费量约为</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">3030</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">万吨，增幅</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">8.0%;</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">合成树脂表观消费量约</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">1.10</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">亿吨，增长</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">5.5%;</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">乙烯表观消费量为</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">2056</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">万吨，增长</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">10.0%;</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">烧碱表观消费量约</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">3150</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">吨，增幅</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">6.5%</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　此次会议由石化联合会、工信部运行监测协调局主办，联合会会长李寿生以及国内</span>300<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">余名行业专家和企业代表出席会议。</span></span></p><p><br/></p>','我国石化经济运行稳中有进筑底盘整','　　上半年，我国石油和化工行业累计增加值同比增长8.7%，经济运行总体平稳、稳中有进，呈筑底盘整的态势。这是记者近日在长沙召开的2016上半年全国石油和化工行业经济运行形势分析会上了解到的情况。','1','1','2017-03-11 19:22:55','','0','','','0','{\"thumb\":\"\"}','1','0','0','0','','');INSERT INTO ts_posts ( `id`, `post_author`, `post_keywords`, `post_source`, `post_date`, `post_content`, `post_title`, `post_excerpt`, `post_status`, `comment_status`, `post_modified`, `post_content_filtered`, `post_parent`, `post_type`, `post_mime_type`, `comment_count`, `smeta`, `post_hits`, `post_like`, `istop`, `recommended`, `page_tpl`, `page_tpls` ) VALUES  ('262','1','建立全国碳交易体系仍需完善机制','','2017-03-11 19:25:40','<p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　全国碳排放交易体系将于</span>2017<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年启动，成为全球第一大碳市场。目前，国内</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">7</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">大国家级碳交易试点总体运行良好，但记者也了解到，碳价波动失真、企业不愿意履约等现象虽有好转但也持续存在，从区域试点过渡到全国市场仍需要进一步完善碳交易机制、约束机制和分配机制。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><strong><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;font-size: 14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　交易价格与减排成本仍未吻合</span></span></strong></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　碳交易的原理在于，在控制排放量的碳市场中，减排成本低的、减排空间大的企业可多减排，同时将因减排剩余的碳配额出售给减排成本高的企业，实现获利。因而，碳的价格应该反映一个国家或地区的平均减排成本。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\">　　2013<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年至</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">2014</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年，深圳、上海、北京、广东、天津、湖北、重庆七个国家级碳排放权交易试点先后启动，</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">3</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年多来，交易不连续、碳价波动大等现象都或多或少地在各个试点出现，且不同试点之间的碳价差异巨大，难以真实反映减排成本。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\">　　2013<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">6</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">18</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">日，深圳碳交易平台率先上线，然而，在首日交易</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">2</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">万多吨、成交金额</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">61</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">万多元后，深圳碳市场近</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">2</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">个月没有交易；广东省二级交易市场继开市首日和次日完成</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">720</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">多万元的交易额后也进入停滞，直到近</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">3</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">个月后才再度“开张”；重庆则更甚，曾经连续</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">9</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">个月没有线上成交量，目前仍然只有零星交易，交易总量只有</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">29.8</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">万吨。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　此外，碳价差别很大。深圳碳市的起始价位是每吨</span>30<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">元左右，后来一度飙升至</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">130</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">多元，接着又跌回到</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">70</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">多元并保持了一段时间，目前又在</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">30</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">至</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">50</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">元间徘徊；广东碳价从</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">60</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">元的开盘价下降到目前的</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">10</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">元左右；而上海碳价最近一度跌到每吨</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">5</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">元左右。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\">　　“碳是一种资产，碳的定价应该反映这个地区的减排成本，如果碳市场交易不连续，显示出的碳价都是交易‘个单行为’，总体减排成本难以有效反映出来。”天津科技大学能源环境与绿色发展研究中心主任孙振清说。</span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　虽然业内对我国的减排成本尚未有明确的计算结果，各种研究数据从每吨</span>20<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">美元至上百美元不等，但专家普遍认为，当前的碳价相对偏低，仍未完全实现碳交易的初衷。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\">　　</span><strong><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;font-size: 14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">企业履约不积极现象仍存在</span></span></strong></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　所谓碳配额履约，是指控排配额企业经过第三方审查机构审核后，按实际年度排放指标完成配额清缴。由于企业不配合等原因，</span>2014<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年，北京、广东、天津推迟履约期，</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">2015</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年，湖北、重庆、天津推迟履约期，</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">2016</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年，北京、深圳等地仍有企业不履约。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　目前，深圳、上海、北京、广东、天津已进入或完成第三个履约期，湖北、重庆也已进入第二个履约期，履约情况逐年向好，但也暴露出一些问题。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\">　　6<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">22</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">日，北京公布的上一年度未履约企业超过</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">80</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">家，其中包括北京妇产医院、故宫博物院、国家电网公司等“大单位”。两年前的</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">2014</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">7</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月，北京也曾对百盛、世邦魏理仕等单位开出碳排放超标罚单，按照当时碳价</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">3</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">到</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">5</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">倍征收罚款，最严重的一家企业面临上百万罚金。然而，从今年的未履约企业数量看，当年罚单的警示作用值得画个问号。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　在天津，一家化工厂</span>2014<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年、</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">2015</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">连续两年都未履约。</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">2014</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年，该厂负责人曾告诉记者，“不知道怎样就被纳入了碳排放管理”。今年</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">6</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月底，该负责人表示，虽然现在他愿意参加碳排放控制，但由于自己的厂子目前处于停产状态，恐怕还是没办法履约。不过，几天后的</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">7</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">1</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">日，天津市发改委发布的公告显示，目前天津的</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">109</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">家企业</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">100%</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">履约。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　记者查阅《天津市碳排放权交易管理暂行办法》发现，该文件并未规定处罚内容，上述化工厂的负责人也表示，两年多来天津市发改委多次规劝，但没有给他任何惩罚。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　孙振清等多位专家表示，虽然各地都有相应的惩罚措施，但大多为政府文件，约束力相对较弱，一些企业拒不履约，此外，由于碳价较低，也有企业购买超排配额草草了事。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\">　</span><strong><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;font-size: 14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　配额分配机制需进一步完善</span></span></strong></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　中国是碳排放大国，也正在成为碳交易大国，而建立碳市场的关键在于总量的设定和配额的分配，这一点直接影响碳市场的运行。环维易为公司的《中国碳市场调查报告</span>2016<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">》指出，重庆碳市场碳价低迷和交易稀疏就是因为配额的过度宽松。中国船级社质量认证公司一位负责人也表示，七大试点目前的碳价下降反映了我国碳配额不同程度地存在超发现象。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　汉能控股集团</span>6<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月发布的《全球新能源发展报告</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">2016</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">》显示，</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">2015</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年，欧盟碳配额</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">(EUA)</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">约为</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">7</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">欧元左右，而</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">2008</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年，这个价格曾一度超过</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">30</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">欧元。孙振清表示，欧盟虽然控制排放总量，但配额发放没有考虑经济危机的影响，在企业开工不足的情况下，配额大量过剩，碳交易对控排失去调节作用，中国要加以借鉴。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　根据《中美元首气候变化联合声明》，中国将于</span>2017<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年启动全国碳排放交易体系。清华大学能源环境经济研究所执行所长张希良说，届时将有钢铁、电力、化工、建材、造纸和有色金属等重点工业行业的</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">7000</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">多家企业纳入全国碳市场，中国碳排放总量的</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">45%-50%</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">将得到有效控制，成为全球第一大碳市场。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　当碳排放市场由区域试点向全国市场过渡时，不同区域之间的配额分配问题将显得更加重要。环保部环境规划院副院长王金南表示，碳排放意味着发展空间，我国东中西部发展差异明显，环境容量不同，在控制全国排放增量的前提下，应该明确不同地区承担</span>“共同而有区别的责任”。</span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　多位专家表示，进一步完善交易机制、约束机制和分配机制，尽快出台国家层面的</span>“应对气候变化法”或类似法律至关重要，通过法律明确配额总量的设定和变化、有效的惩罚以及区域分配和跨区域交易方法，用制度设计指导碳价格真实反映减排成本。</span></p><p><br/></p>','建立全国碳交易体系仍需完善机制','　　全国碳排放交易体系将于2017年启动，成为全球第一大碳市场。目前，国内7大国家级碳交易试点总体运行良好，但记者也了解到，碳价波动失真、企业不愿意履约等现象虽有好转但也持续存在，从区域试点过渡到全国市场仍需要进一步完善碳交易机制、约束机制和分配机制。','1','1','2017-03-11 19:24:32','','0','','','0','{\"thumb\":\"\"}','1','0','0','0','','');INSERT INTO ts_posts ( `id`, `post_author`, `post_keywords`, `post_source`, `post_date`, `post_content`, `post_title`, `post_excerpt`, `post_status`, `comment_status`, `post_modified`, `post_content_filtered`, `post_parent`, `post_type`, `post_mime_type`, `comment_count`, `smeta`, `post_hits`, `post_like`, `istop`, `recommended`, `page_tpl`, `page_tpls` ) VALUES  ('263','1','中国经济增长与煤炭消费增长脱钩','','2017-03-11 19:27:45','<p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　清华</span>-<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">布鲁金斯公共政策研究中心主任齐晔与英国国家学术院院长、世界银行原首席经济学家尼古拉斯·斯特恩等人近期在《自然</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">-</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">地球科学》刊文指出：中国经济增长已经与煤炭消费增长脱钩，中国煤炭消费的峰值或已提前到来，中国经济正积极走向绿色增长新阶段。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　改革开放以来的</span>30<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">多年，中国经济快速增长成为世界经济史的奇迹。但在这一时期，化石能源消费也急剧扩张。一般认为，中国煤炭消费或在</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">2020</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年至</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">2040</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年间达峰。但是，</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">2014</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年，中国煤炭消费下降了</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">2.9%</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">，</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">2015</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年则继续下降了</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">3.6%</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">；与此同时，中国经济仍保持较高速的增长。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　《中国的后煤炭增长》这篇文章指出，中国已经可以做到在保持经济稳步增长的同时减少煤炭的使用。原因有两点：第一，随着中国经济进入新常态，经济增速放缓，能源消费需求增速下降，经济结构趋于优化；第二，空气污染治理与应对气候变化政策，加快了煤炭在能源结构中比重的下降速度。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　文章认为，近两年煤炭消费的下降并非偶然现象，而是大势使然。首先，经济增速的放缓和第二产业比重的下降是中国新常态的基本特征。其次，为了实现</span>2030<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年前后碳排放达标及清洁能源比重达到</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">20%</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">，中国政府持续加大在非化石能源领域的投资和建设，投资规模占世界总量的三分之一。第三，中国正展开新一轮以能源、通讯、高科技制造业为主导的“工业革命”，能源技术的进步将成为经济增长的重要支柱。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　历史上，煤炭消费的达峰是一些发达国家发展过程中的重要里程碑。中国正在积极地终结煤炭时代，缩短油气时代，提前走向清洁能源时代，而且与英美两国相比，中国在一个更低的发展阶段完成了煤炭消费的达峰。作者们认为，煤炭在未来相当长一段时间里仍将在中国能源结构里扮演主要角色。然而，中国经济的增长和民生的改善将不再依赖煤炭消费的增加。</span></span></p><p><br/></p>','中国经济增长与煤炭消费增长脱钩','　　清华-布鲁金斯公共政策研究中心主任齐晔与英国国家学术院院长、世界银行原首席经济学家尼古拉斯·斯特恩等人近期在《自然-地球科学》刊文指出：中国经济增长已经与煤炭消费增长脱钩，中国煤炭消费的峰值或已提前到来，中国经济正积极走向绿色增长新阶段。','1','1','2017-03-11 19:27:07','','0','','','0','{\"thumb\":\"\"}','0','0','0','0','','');INSERT INTO ts_posts ( `id`, `post_author`, `post_keywords`, `post_source`, `post_date`, `post_content`, `post_title`, `post_excerpt`, `post_status`, `comment_status`, `post_modified`, `post_content_filtered`, `post_parent`, `post_type`, `post_mime_type`, `comment_count`, `smeta`, `post_hits`, `post_like`, `istop`, `recommended`, `page_tpl`, `page_tpls` ) VALUES  ('264','1','全国碳市场能力建设（广东）中心揭牌','','2017-03-11 19:34:44','<p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　全国碳交易市场将在</span>2017<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年启动运行。近日</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">,</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">经国家发改委气候司批复同意设立的全国碳市场能力建设</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">(</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">广东</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">)</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">中心</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">(</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">下称“广东中心”</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">)</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">在广州举行揭牌仪式。国家发改委、省发改委相关领导共同为广东中心揭牌。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　广州碳排放权交易所、广东省应对气候变化研究中心、中国质量认证中心广州分中心以及中国科学院广州能源研究所签署了广东中心合作共建协议。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　据广东省发改委气候处介绍</span>,<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">广东中心将在国家发改委的直接领导下</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">,</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">积极发挥辐射和带动作用</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">,</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">深入开展控排企业、核查机构和政府管理人员等多层次的碳交易能力建设和培训</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">,</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">为全国碳市场的顺利启动和有序运行提供重要支撑和保障。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　近日</span>,<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">广东省发改委发布通知</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">,</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">对拟纳入全国碳交易的首批企业开展历史温室气体排放信息报告核查工作。全国碳市场第一阶段将涵盖石化、化工、建材、钢铁、有色、造纸、电力、航空等重点排放行业</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">,</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">拟纳入全国碳交易市场的首批企业为</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">2013</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年至</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">2015</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年中任意一年综合能源消费总量达到</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">1</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">万吨标准煤以上</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">(</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">含</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">)</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">的企业法人单位或独立核算企业单位。全省共有</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">381</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">家企业首批纳入全国碳市场体系。从地市分布来看</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">,</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">珠三角地区的纳入企业较多</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">,</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">全省纳入企业最多的地市前三位是广州</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">51</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">家、东莞</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">42</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">家、佛山</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">32</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">家</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">(</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">深圳是与广东并列的低碳试点</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">,</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">所以省里名单不含深圳</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">),</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">而最少的汕尾仅有</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">1</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">家。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　广东还计划进一步发挥试点的辐射带动作用</span>,<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">于今年开展全国碳市场泛珠三角区域“</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">9+2</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">”全方位合作</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">,</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">并向国家申请在广东设立泛珠三角区域交流合作中心。</span></span></p><p><br/></p>','全国碳市场能力建设（广东）中心揭牌','　　全国碳交易市场将在2017年启动运行。近日,经国家发改委气候司批复同意设立的全国碳市场能力建设(广东)中心(下称“广东中心”)在广州举行揭牌仪式。国家发改委、省发改委相关领导共同为广东中心揭牌。','1','1','2017-03-11 19:29:05','','0','','','0','{\"thumb\":\"\"}','0','0','0','0','','');INSERT INTO ts_posts ( `id`, `post_author`, `post_keywords`, `post_source`, `post_date`, `post_content`, `post_title`, `post_excerpt`, `post_status`, `comment_status`, `post_modified`, `post_content_filtered`, `post_parent`, `post_type`, `post_mime_type`, `comment_count`, `smeta`, `post_hits`, `post_like`, `istop`, `recommended`, `page_tpl`, `page_tpls` ) VALUES  ('265','1','石化产业供给侧改革重在调结构促转型增效益','','2017-03-11 19:36:35','<p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;line-height:150%;font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　记者从国家能源局网站了解到</span>,<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">近日</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">,</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">国务院办公厅印发了《关于石化产业调结构促转型增效益的指导意见》</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">(</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">以下简称《指导意见》</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">),</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">部署石化产业结构调整和转型升级工作。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;line-height:150%;font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　《指导意见》指出</span>,<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">要推进供给侧结构性改革</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">,</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">积极开拓市场</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">,</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">坚持创新驱动</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">,</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">改善发展环境</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">,</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">着力去产能、降消耗、减排放</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">,</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">补短板、调布局、促安全</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">,</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">推动石化产业提质增效、转型升级和健康发展。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;line-height:150%;font-size:16px\">　　《指导意见》明确了七个方面的重点任务。</span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;line-height:150%;font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　一是努力化解过剩产能。严格控制产能严重过剩行业新增产能</span>,<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">对符合政策要求的先进工艺改造提升项目实行等量或减量置换。研究制定产能置换方案</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">,</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">充分利用安全、环保、节能、价格等措施</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">,</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">推动落后和低效产能退出</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">,</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">为先进产能创造更大市场空间。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;line-height:150%;font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　二是统筹优化产业布局。综合考虑资源、环境、安全等因素</span>,<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">完善石化产业布局</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">,</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">有序推进沿海七大石化产业基地建设。开展智慧化工园区试点</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">,</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">依法做好综合评估和信息公开。结合大型煤炭基地开发</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">,</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">按照环境准入条件要求</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">,</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">有序发展现代煤化工产业。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;line-height:150%;font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　三是改造提升传统产业。利用清洁生产、智能控制等先进技术改造提升现有生产装置</span>,<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">提高产品质量</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">,</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">降低消耗</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">,</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">减少排放</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">,</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">提高综合竞争能力。加快炼油和乙烯装置技术改造</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">,</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">适时调整柴汽比</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">,</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">优化原料结构。拓展传统化工产品应用领域</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">,</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">支持优势产能“走出去”。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;line-height:150%;font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　四是促进安全绿色发展。强化安全生产责任制</span>,<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">探索高风险危险化学品全程追溯</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">,</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">实施危险化学品生产企业安全环保搬迁改造。完善化工园区监控、消防、应急等系统平台</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">,</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">推进信息共享</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">,</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">夯实安全生产基础。实施能效领跑者制度</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">,</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">完善节能标准体系。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;line-height:150%;font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　五是健全完善创新体系。健全以企业为主体的产学研用协同创新体系</span>,<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">组建一批技术创新战略联盟</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">;</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">整合技术中心、工程研究中心、重点实验室、工程实验室等研发平台</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">,</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">加大人才培养和引进力度</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">,</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">加快科技研发及成果转化。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;line-height:150%;font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　六是推动企业兼并重组。落实财税、金融、土地、职工安置等支持政策</span>,<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">破除跨地区、跨所有制兼并重组的体制机制障碍</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">,</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">为企业兼并重组营造公平的市场环境。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;line-height:150%;font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　七是加强国际产能合作。充分发挥我国传统石化产业比较优势</span>,<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">结合“一带一路”战略</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">,</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">积极推动优势产业开展国际产能合作</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">,</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">建设海外石化产业园区</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">,</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">推动链条式转移、集约式发展</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">,</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">带动相关技术装备与工程服务“走出去”。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;line-height:150%;font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　另外</span>,<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">《指导意见》要求</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">,</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">各地区、各部门要高度重视</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">,</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">确保各项工作落到实处。各省级人民政府要结合本地实际</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">,</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">切实抓好组织实施。国家发展改革委、工业和信息化部要会同有关部门加强对地方的督促指导</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">,</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">各有关部门要根据职责分工抓紧完善配套政策</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">,</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">统筹推进各项工作。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;line-height:150%;font-size:16px\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;line-height:150%;font-size:16px\">&nbsp;</span></p><p><br/></p>','石化产业供给侧改革重在调结构促转型增效益','　　记者从国家能源局网站了解到,近日,国务院办公厅印发了《关于石化产业调结构促转型增效益的指导意见》(以下简称《指导意见》),部署石化产业结构调整和转型升级工作。','1','1','2017-03-11 19:35:17','','0','','','0','{\"thumb\":\"\"}','0','0','0','0','','');INSERT INTO ts_posts ( `id`, `post_author`, `post_keywords`, `post_source`, `post_date`, `post_content`, `post_title`, `post_excerpt`, `post_status`, `comment_status`, `post_modified`, `post_content_filtered`, `post_parent`, `post_type`, `post_mime_type`, `comment_count`, `smeta`, `post_hits`, `post_like`, `istop`, `recommended`, `page_tpl`, `page_tpls` ) VALUES  ('266','1','成品油价频降','','2017-03-11 19:37:48','<p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　近日</span>,<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">国内成品油价格有所下调</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">,</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">国内汽、柴油价格每吨分别降低</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">220</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">元和</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">215</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">元。业内人士表示</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">,</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">国际原油市场供需失衡加剧成为此次成品油价下调的主要因素。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><strong><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;font-size: 14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　国际原油市场供需失衡</span></span></strong></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　记者在国家发改委网站上发布的信息中看到</span>,<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">根据近期国际市场油价变化情况</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">,</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">按照现行成品油价格形成机制</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">,</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">自</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">2016</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">8</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">4</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">日</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">24</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">时起</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">,</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">国内汽、柴油价格每吨分别降低</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">220</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">元和</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">215</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">元。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　据卓创资讯分析师高健介绍</span>,<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">从</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">2015</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年至今国际原油走势情况可以看出</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">,</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">进入</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">7</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">、</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">8</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月份国内原油市场整体表现低迷</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">,</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">国际油价也延续了之前的下跌势头</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">,</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">而且跌幅和跌速都在加快</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">,</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">美原油价格也再次跌破</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">40</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">美元</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">/</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">吨的整数关口。“目前石油市场供应过剩的问题在持续发酵</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">,</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">也在油价的持续下跌中扮演了关键角色。美国油品的库存长期保持高位</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">,</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">钻井数量连续五周增长。与此同时</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">,</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">美国炼厂开工负荷持续大幅低于去年同期水平</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">,</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">原油加工需求表现低迷。此外</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">,</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">中东产油国及俄罗斯原油产出继续增加</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">,</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">供需失衡的局面进一步加剧。国际原油失控加剧成为此次成品油价下调的主要因素。”高健表示。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　记者从卓创资讯了解到</span>,<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">伴随着油价的不断下滑</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">,</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">国内批发环节价格已溃不成军。“据卓创资讯数据统计</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">,</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">截至目前</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">,</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">国内主营单位</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">93#</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">汽油车提批发均价为</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">5526</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">元</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">/</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">吨</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">,</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">堪称</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">10</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年来最低点</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">,</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">这一价格甚至低于年初国际原油价格跌破</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">30</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">美元</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">/</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">桶之时主营汽油批发均价</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">,</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">彼时尚维持在</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">6000</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">元</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">/</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">吨上下</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">;</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">其对应的批零价差高达</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">2229</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">元</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">/</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">吨</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">,</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">堪称历史最高点。柴油方面</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">,</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">国内主营单位</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">0#</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">柴油车提批发均价为</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">4569</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">元</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">/</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">吨</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">,</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">批零价差高达</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">1375</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">元</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">/</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">吨。地炼市场国四</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">93#</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">汽油均价在</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">4532</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">元</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">/</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">吨</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">,</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">较当地主营最高零售限价低</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">3259</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">元</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">/</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">吨</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">;0#</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">柴油均价在</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">3977</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">元</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">/</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">吨</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">,</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">较当地主营最高零售限价低</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">2403</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">元</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">/</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">吨。”卓创资讯分析师徐娜表示。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><strong><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;font-size: 14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　新型能源企业生存现状堪忧</span></span></strong></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\">　　“国际油价长时间下跌致使本轮成品油价格下调成为年内的跌幅之最<span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">,</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">传统石化能源价格也随之跌至年内低谷。然而原油价格的下跌所带来的消极影响也笼罩着新能源市场</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">,</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">以煤制油及生物柴油行业为主的新型能源</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">,</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">企业生存现状堪忧</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">,</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">原油价格愈发背离行业盈利点</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">(</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">煤制油</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">60~70</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">美元</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">/</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">桶、生物柴油</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">60</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">美元</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">/</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">桶</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">),</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">企业陷入生产即是亏损的境地</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">,</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">大量企业减产降负荷乃至停工多数是为了规避低油价下自身的销售亏损。煤制油行业在成品售价不断下跌的同时</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">,</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">还要考虑各类税费带来的压力。生物柴油在高价原料及低市场成交价的双重压力下</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">,</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">退市企业愈发增加。由上可见</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">,</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">除去疲软不堪的终端需求外</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">,</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">原油价格上不去</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">,</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">新能源恐无出头之日。”卓创资讯分析师巩秉鑫表示。</span></span></p><p><br/></p>','成品油价频降 能源企业现状堪忧','　近日,国内成品油价格有所下调,国内汽、柴油价格每吨分别降低220元和215元。业内人士表示,国际原油市场供需失衡加剧成为此次成品油价下调的主要因素。','1','1','2017-03-11 19:36:52','','0','','','0','{\"thumb\":\"\"}','0','0','0','0','','');INSERT INTO ts_posts ( `id`, `post_author`, `post_keywords`, `post_source`, `post_date`, `post_content`, `post_title`, `post_excerpt`, `post_status`, `comment_status`, `post_modified`, `post_content_filtered`, `post_parent`, `post_type`, `post_mime_type`, `comment_count`, `smeta`, `post_hits`, `post_like`, `istop`, `recommended`, `page_tpl`, `page_tpls` ) VALUES  ('267','1','神华上半年净利9828百','','2017-03-11 19:39:04','<p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　中国神华</span>8<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">9</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">日晚发布上半年业绩快报。公司上半年实现营业收入</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">78723</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">百万元，同比下降</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">12.5%</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">；实现归属于母公司所有者的净利润</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">9828</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">百万元，同比下降</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">18.6%</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">；加权平均净资产收益率为</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">3.29%</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">，同比下降</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">0.74</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">个百分点。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　对于上半年经营业绩下降的原因，公司表示，受煤炭市场持续低迷的影响，公司上半年煤炭平均销售价格约为</span>271<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">元</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">/</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">吨，同比下降</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">14%</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">；此外，受</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">2015</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年上网侧电价下调影响，上半年平均售电电价约为</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">306</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">元</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">/</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">兆瓦时，同比下降</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">11%</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">。</span></span></p><p><br/></p>','神华上半年净利9828百万 同比降18%','　　中国神华8月9日晚发布上半年业绩快报。公司上半年实现营业收入78723百万元，同比下降12.5%；实现归属于母公司所有者的净利润9828百万元，同比下降18.6%；加权平均净资产收益率为3.29%，同比下降0.74个百分点。','1','1','2017-03-11 19:38:28','','0','','','0','{\"thumb\":\"\"}','0','0','0','0','','');INSERT INTO ts_posts ( `id`, `post_author`, `post_keywords`, `post_source`, `post_date`, `post_content`, `post_title`, `post_excerpt`, `post_status`, `comment_status`, `post_modified`, `post_content_filtered`, `post_parent`, `post_type`, `post_mime_type`, `comment_count`, `smeta`, `post_hits`, `post_like`, `istop`, `recommended`, `page_tpl`, `page_tpls` ) VALUES  ('268','1','BP拟出售上海赛科石化股权','','2017-03-11 19:40:39','<p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　据外媒援引知情人士称</span>,<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">英国石油巨头</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">BP</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">正在寻觅买家</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">,</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">以收购</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">BP</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">在中国一家石化合资企业的</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">50%</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">股份</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">,</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">出售可能带来</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">20-30</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">亿美元收入。这家合资公司是</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">BP</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">在中国单一最大投资。如果成功脱手</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">,</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">这将是</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">BP</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">在中国业务的首次重大退出。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　而据</span>BP<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">官网</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">,</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">坐落在漕泾附近的赛科是由中国石油化工股份有限公司、中国石化上海石油化工股份有限公司和</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">BP</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">华东投资有限公司分别按</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">30% </span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">、</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">20% </span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">、</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">50%</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">的比例出资组建的</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">,</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">总投资额约</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">27</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">亿美元</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">,</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">是目前国内最大的中外合资石化项目之一。消息人士称</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">,</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">英国石油公司已聘请投资银行出售其股份来驱动企业的一部分现金流。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　虽然中石化拥有优先购买权</span>,<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">但是银行家们表示中国国有企业不太可能介入购买。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　目前</span>,BP<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">遭遇了</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">20</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">多年以来最严重的年度亏损。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　为帮</span>2010<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年致命的墨西哥湾漏油事件支付清理费用和法律费用</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">,BP</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">已经售出了超过</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">500</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">亿美元的资产。今年</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">,</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">它计划出售价值</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">30</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">到</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">50</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">亿美元的资产。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　此前</span>,BP<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">在向伦敦证交所提交的一份报告中表示</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">,</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">受原油价格低迷影响</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">,2016</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年上半年该公司亏损</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">20.02</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">亿美元</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">(18.17</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">亿欧元</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">),</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">同比下降</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">37.8%</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">。</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">2015</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年上半年</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">,BP</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">亏损</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">32.21</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">亿美元</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">(29.24</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">亿美元</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">)</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">。</span></span></p><p><br/></p>','BP拟出售上海赛科石化股权','　　据外媒援引知情人士称,英国石油巨头BP正在寻觅买家,以收购BP在中国一家石化合资企业的50%股份,出售可能带来20-30亿美元收入。这家合资公司是BP在中国单一最大投资。如果成功脱手,这将是BP在中国业务的首次重大退出。','1','1','2017-03-11 19:39:49','','0','','','0','{\"thumb\":\"\"}','1','0','0','0','','');INSERT INTO ts_posts ( `id`, `post_author`, `post_keywords`, `post_source`, `post_date`, `post_content`, `post_title`, `post_excerpt`, `post_status`, `comment_status`, `post_modified`, `post_content_filtered`, `post_parent`, `post_type`, `post_mime_type`, `comment_count`, `smeta`, `post_hits`, `post_like`, `istop`, `recommended`, `page_tpl`, `page_tpls` ) VALUES  ('269','1','国际油价10日下跌','','2017-03-11 19:48:47','<p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　美国原油库存高企，国际油价</span>10<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">日继续下跌。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　美国能源信息局当天发布的报告显示，在截至</span>8<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">5</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">日的一周，美国原油库存意外增加</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">110</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">万桶，为连续第三周上涨，超出市场预期。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　前一交易日，美国能源信息局发布月度报告指出，预测</span>2017<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年美国原油日产量为</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">831</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">万桶，高于</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">7</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月份预测的</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">820</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">万桶。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　分析人士指出，近期的数据加大了市场对于原油市场供应过量的担忧，令国际油价承压下行。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　截至当日收盘时，纽约商品交易所</span>9<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月交货的轻质原油期货价格下跌</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">1.06</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">美元，跌幅为</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">2.48%</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">，收于每桶</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">41.71</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">美元。</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">10</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月交货的伦敦布伦特原油期货价格下跌</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">0.93</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">美元，收于每桶</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">44.05</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">美元，跌幅为</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">2.07%</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">。</span></span></p><p><br/></p>','国际油价10日下跌 报收每桶41.71美元','　　美国原油库存高企，国际油价10日继续下跌。','1','1','2017-03-11 19:47:47','','0','','','0','{\"thumb\":\"\"}','0','0','0','0','','');INSERT INTO ts_posts ( `id`, `post_author`, `post_keywords`, `post_source`, `post_date`, `post_content`, `post_title`, `post_excerpt`, `post_status`, `comment_status`, `post_modified`, `post_content_filtered`, `post_parent`, `post_type`, `post_mime_type`, `comment_count`, `smeta`, `post_hits`, `post_like`, `istop`, `recommended`, `page_tpl`, `page_tpls` ) VALUES  ('270','1','全国成品油价格指数平稳运行','','2017-03-11 19:50:28','<p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　国际石油资讯中心</span>15<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">日发布的报告，截至</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">8</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">12</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">日，全国成品油价格指数为</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">560.48</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">，涨幅</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">0.21%</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">，全国成品油价格指数平稳运行。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　全国成品油价格指数运行结果表明，上周</span>93<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">＃汽油平均价格报收于</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">5622</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">元／吨，较前一报告周期上涨</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">4</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">元／吨</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">(</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">与前一报告期基本持平</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">)</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">；</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">0</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">＃柴油平均价格报收于</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">4722</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">元／吨，较前一报告周期上涨</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">13</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">元／吨</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">(</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">与前一报告期基本持平</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">)</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">。综合来看，全国汽柴油平均价格起伏不大，带动全国成品油价格指数平稳运行。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　新华</span>(<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">大庆</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">)</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">国际石油资讯中心分析师李振国认为，近期因沙特能源部长对油市的表态及美国原油库存数据变化，国际油价继续维持震荡行情。国内油品市场行情继续清淡，业者操作积极性低迷。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　李振国分析认为，本周外盘油价继续维持震荡走势，国内汽柴油价格低位运行，油品销售维持清淡行情，炼厂汽柴油销售价格低位持稳，成交多有优惠，业者多保持观望态度，按需补库为主。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　国际市场方面，美国能源信息署</span>(EIA)<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">近日公布的数据利空国际油价。观望后市，美国原油库存继续增加，加之</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">7</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月沙特原油产量创历史新高，原油基本面持续疲弱，预计短期内国际油价将维持低位震荡格局。</span></span></p><p><br/></p>','全国成品油价格指数平稳运行','　　国际石油资讯中心15日发布的报告，截至8月12日，全国成品油价格指数为560.48，涨幅0.21%，全国成品油价格指数平稳运行。','1','1','2017-03-11 19:49:22','','0','','','0','{\"thumb\":\"\"}','1','0','0','0','','');INSERT INTO ts_posts ( `id`, `post_author`, `post_keywords`, `post_source`, `post_date`, `post_content`, `post_title`, `post_excerpt`, `post_status`, `comment_status`, `post_modified`, `post_content_filtered`, `post_parent`, `post_type`, `post_mime_type`, `comment_count`, `smeta`, `post_hits`, `post_like`, `istop`, `recommended`, `page_tpl`, `page_tpls` ) VALUES  ('271','1','周四国内油价或迎年内第五次上调','','2017-03-11 19:51:36','<p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　记者从多家社会监测机构了解到，近期欧佩克非正式会议稳价消息弥漫市场，国际油价从</span>40<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">美元</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">/</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">桶的地板价附近涨至</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">45</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">美元</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">/</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">桶上下，业内人士判断短期仍有上升空间，本周四</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">(8</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">18</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">日</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">)</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">国内成品油零售限价或迎来年内第五次上调，幅度在</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">100</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">元</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">/</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">吨以内，届时国内的</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">92</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">号</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">/93</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">号汽油仍旧处于“五元时代”。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　上周国际油价累计上涨约</span>6%<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">，创</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">4</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月以来最大涨幅，提振国内成品油调价参考的原油变化率由负转正。据卓创资讯模型测算，截至</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">8</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">15</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">日，国内第</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">7</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">个工作日参考原油变化率为</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">2.08%</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">，对应汽柴油上调</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">83</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">元</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">/</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">吨。而中宇原油估价</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">43.058</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">美元</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">/</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">桶，较基准价涨</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">1.208</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">美元</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">/</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">桶，原油变化率为</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">2.89%</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\">　　“目前在利好因素的提振下，国际原油上涨速度较快，且市场多头信心备受鼓舞，原油短期或仍有上升空间，但回顾前两轮产油国会议均未对欧佩克国家原油产量的上升产生明显的约束作用，加之近期市场对于供应过剩的忧虑加重等因素影响，预计原油短期内上涨阻力将加大。”中宇资讯分析师高承莎预计，<span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">8</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">18</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">日国内成品油零售限价上调</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">70</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">元</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">/</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">吨。在成品油上调预期的刺激下，市场整体需求仍有明显提升，预计短期内全国汽柴油价格或将延续稳中小幅上涨趋势。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　卓创资讯分析师胡慧春表示，距离调价仅剩</span>3<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">个工作日，若原油呈现小幅震荡态势，则变化率或处于正值内小幅上涨，汽柴油对应上调幅度或在</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">100</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">元</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">/</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">吨以内，本轮油价上调窗口将会开启，届时国内成品油零售价将迎来年内第五次上调。</span></span></p><p><br/></p>','周四国内油价或迎年内第五次上调','　　记者从多家社会监测机构了解到，近期欧佩克非正式会议稳价消息弥漫市场，国际油价从40美元/桶的地板价附近涨至45美元/桶上下，业内人士判断短期仍有上升空间，本周四(8月18日)国内成品油零售限价或迎来年内第五次上调，幅度在100元/吨以内，届时国内的92号/93号汽油仍旧处于“五元时代”。','1','1','2017-03-11 19:50:40','','0','','','0','{\"thumb\":\"\"}','0','0','0','0','','');INSERT INTO ts_posts ( `id`, `post_author`, `post_keywords`, `post_source`, `post_date`, `post_content`, `post_title`, `post_excerpt`, `post_status`, `comment_status`, `post_modified`, `post_content_filtered`, `post_parent`, `post_type`, `post_mime_type`, `comment_count`, `smeta`, `post_hits`, `post_like`, `istop`, `recommended`, `page_tpl`, `page_tpls` ) VALUES  ('272','1','全球首座超深水、双钻塔半潜式钻井平台','','2017-03-11 19:53:51','<p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　全球首座在建的最新一代超深水、双钻塔半潜式钻井平台</span>D901#<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">，今年年底交付后，将为中国石油集团海洋工程有限公司</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">(</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">简称“中油海”</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">)</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">提供海上能源勘探服务。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　中油海与烟台中集来福士海洋工程有限公司</span>(<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">简称“中集来福士”</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">)</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">，</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">8</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">16</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">日在烟台签署该超深水钻井平台的技术服务合同。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　据总部设在深圳的中集集团透露，</span>D901#<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">由中集来福士完成全部的详细设计、施工设计、建造和调试。平台长</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">117</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">米，宽</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">92.7</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">米，高</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">118</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">米，配备</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">DP3</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">动力定位系统，入级挪威船级社。其最大作业水深</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">3658</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">米，最大钻井深度</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">15240</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">米，是目前全球作业水深、钻井深度最深的半潜式钻井平台，适用于全球深海作业。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　与传统单钻塔平台相比，该平台配置了高效的液压双钻塔和全球领先的西门子闭环动力系统，可提升</span>30%<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">作业效率，节省</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">10%</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">的燃料消耗。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\">　　D901#<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">将于</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">9</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月上旬出海试航，于今年年底交付使用。与</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">D901#</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">同系列的</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">D902#</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">超深水半潜式钻井平台也在中集来福士烟台基地紧张建造中。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　中集来福士自</span>2013<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年以来，先后为“中油海</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">61</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">”平台、“中油海</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">10</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">”平台进行维修改造，并建造交付了“中油海</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">15</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">”自升式钻井平台。多年来，中集来福士在深水半潜式钻井平台领域已积累了丰富的建造经验，交付的多座半潜式钻井平台得到国际主流客户的肯定。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　中油海总经理刘圣志表示，</span>D901#<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">技术服务合同的顺利签约，为深海能源开发项目顺利推进打下坚实的基础。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　中集来福士总裁王建中称，将两家公司紧紧联系在一起的是</span>“全球首座、最大、最先进、作业水深最深、自主建造”等这样的关键词，中集来福士希望能为中国石油的“海洋强国梦”提供实实在在的帮助。</span></p><p><br/></p>','全球首座超深水、双钻塔半潜式钻井平台花落中油','　　全球首座在建的最新一代超深水、双钻塔半潜式钻井平台D901#，今年年底交付后，将为中国石油集团海洋工程有限公司(简称“中油海”)提供海上能源勘探服务。','1','1','2017-03-11 19:52:06','','0','','','0','{\"thumb\":\"\"}','0','0','0','0','','');INSERT INTO ts_posts ( `id`, `post_author`, `post_keywords`, `post_source`, `post_date`, `post_content`, `post_title`, `post_excerpt`, `post_status`, `comment_status`, `post_modified`, `post_content_filtered`, `post_parent`, `post_type`, `post_mime_type`, `comment_count`, `smeta`, `post_hits`, `post_like`, `istop`, `recommended`, `page_tpl`, `page_tpls` ) VALUES  ('273','1','“海丝”合作加速福建泉港石化基地发展','','2017-03-11 19:55:34','<p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\">　　“除了已经合作比较久的欧美、南美地区<span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">,</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">如今也加快了与东南亚、中东地区的进出口往来。”福建泉州市泉港区商务局副局长庄俏忠</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">8</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">15</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">日接受记者采访时表示</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">,</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">“海丝”合作加速福建泉港石化基地发展。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　该石化基地依托福建联合石化</span>——福建最大“海丝”合作项目的产业基础<span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">,</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">以及湄洲湾南岸港区每年进口阿拉伯地区</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">1700</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">多万吨原油的合作基础</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">,</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">正深化与“海丝”沿线国家和地区的产业合作</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">,</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">加紧筹建湄洲湾石化物流贸易等</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">,</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">推动设立总投资</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">50</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">亿元</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">(</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">人民币</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">,</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">下同</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">)</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">的中国</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">-</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">阿拉伯石化产业合作园区。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　据介绍</span>,<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">由福建省政府、中石化与美国埃克森美孚公司、沙特阿美公司共同投资建设运营的福建联合石化公司</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">,2007</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年成立以来累计完成投资约</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">500</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">亿元</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">,</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">具备</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">1400</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">万吨炼油、百万吨乙烯的年生产能力</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">,</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">产能居国内同行业前列</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">,</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">也是目前福建最大的“海丝”合作项目。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　数据显示</span>,2014<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年泉港石化产值突破</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">800</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">亿元</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">,2015</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年在石化产品量价齐降的情况下仍完成产值</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">672.4</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">亿元</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">,</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">连续多年跻身中国化工园区前</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">8</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">强</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">,</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">入选国家级循环化改造示范试点园区。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　庄俏忠表示</span>,<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">目前泉港石化园区正筹划设立“海丝”石化产业合作园区</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">,</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">已吸引了卡塔尔海湾石油公司、世贸中心协会、阿联酋阿布扎比国家石油公司等一批企业机构前来投资、考察。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　当前</span>,<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">联合石化油品质量升级暨酸性气处理满足新标准改造工程</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">,</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">一大批在建石化重大项目也竣工投产。庄俏忠告诉记者</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">,</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">石油化工的发展也预示着与“海丝”沿线国家的联系逐渐增强。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　泉港是国家一类口岸和首批对台直航点</span>,<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">已建成投产码头</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">10</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">座</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">24</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">个泊位</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">,</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">正在开工建设</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">9</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">个泊位</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">,</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">拥有福建省唯一的检验检疫国家级石油化工检测中心实验室和泉州关区唯一的保税仓库、甲醇期货交割仓库</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">,</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">并在全市最早开展海铁联运业务</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">,2015</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年港口货物吞吐量达</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">4550</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">万吨</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">,</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">海关关税超</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">100</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">亿元。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　今年</span>5<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月“厦门</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">-</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">肖厝</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">-</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">上海”直航航线的试运营成功推动肖厝港区集装箱业务持续拓展</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">,</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">前</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">5</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">个月累计完成集装箱吞吐量</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">1.2</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">万</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">TEU,</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">同比增长</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">131%</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　伴随大型深水泊位群、通港铁路、保税仓库、高速公路、电子口岸等现代港口物流设施的完善</span>,<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">该区正在规划建设石化物流“一基地五中心”</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">,</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">开展《泉港海丝石化物流贸易基地总体规划与设计》初步思路研究</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">,</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">编制《泉港海丝石化物流贸易基地总体规划与设计》</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">,</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">加强同厦门两岸电子交易所、深圳石油交易所、中石化化销公司等企业进行洽谈对接</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">,</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">力争在与海丝国家能源贸易往来中起着重要的衔接纽带作用。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　今年</span>9<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月将正式投入使用福州大学石油化工学院还将建立石化研究院、技术转移中心、孵化基地</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">,</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">联合其他高校共同组建协同创新联盟</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">,</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">跟踪研究石化产业发展的前沿技术</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">,</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">推动技术研发协作</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">,</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">转化科技成果</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">,</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">构建产学研用一体化发展模式。而如今泉港既有中国石油化工园区、省级开发区的优势条件</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">,</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">又有联合石化这一目前福建最大海丝合作项目的产业基础</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">,</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">在该区的“十三五”规划中</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">,</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">预计该区石化产值至</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">2020</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年将超</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">1500</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">亿元。</span></span></p><p><br/></p>','“海丝”合作加速福建泉港石化基地发展','　　“除了已经合作比较久的欧美、南美地区,如今也加快了与东南亚、中东地区的进出口往来。”福建泉州市泉港区商务局副局长庄俏忠8月15日接受记者采访时表示,“海丝”合作加速福建泉港石化基地发展。','1','1','2017-03-11 19:54:13','','0','','','0','{\"thumb\":\"\"}','0','0','0','0','','');INSERT INTO ts_posts ( `id`, `post_author`, `post_keywords`, `post_source`, `post_date`, `post_content`, `post_title`, `post_excerpt`, `post_status`, `comment_status`, `post_modified`, `post_content_filtered`, `post_parent`, `post_type`, `post_mime_type`, `comment_count`, `smeta`, `post_hits`, `post_like`, `istop`, `recommended`, `page_tpl`, `page_tpls` ) VALUES  ('274','1','国际油价16日上涨 ','','2017-03-11 20:03:07','<p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　国际油价</span>16<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">日上涨。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　当天有消息说，在</span>9<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月召开的非正式会议上，欧佩克成员国和其他主要产油国将讨论当前市场形势，有可能采取限产等措施稳定国际油价。该消息助推当天油价上涨。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　此外，当天美元走低也提高了以美元计价的石油的投资吸引力，利好油价。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　截至当天收盘，纽约商品交易所</span>9<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月交货的轻质原油期货价格上涨</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">0.84</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">美元，收于每桶</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">46.58</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">美元，涨幅为</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">1.8%</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">。</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">10</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月交货的伦敦布伦特原油期货价格上涨</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">0.88</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">美元，收于每桶</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">49.23</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">美元，涨幅为</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">1.8%</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">。</span></span></p><p><br/></p>','国际油价16日上涨 收于每桶46.58美元','国际油价16日上涨。','1','1','2017-03-11 20:02:41','','0','','','0','{\"thumb\":\"\"}','0','0','0','0','','');INSERT INTO ts_posts ( `id`, `post_author`, `post_keywords`, `post_source`, `post_date`, `post_content`, `post_title`, `post_excerpt`, `post_status`, `comment_status`, `post_modified`, `post_content_filtered`, `post_parent`, `post_type`, `post_mime_type`, `comment_count`, `smeta`, `post_hits`, `post_like`, `istop`, `recommended`, `page_tpl`, `page_tpls` ) VALUES  ('275','1','国际油价三个交易日大涨10%','','2017-03-11 21:26:34','<p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　据经济之声《天下公司》报道，在过去三个交易日里油价上涨幅度达</span>10%<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">，美国</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">WTI</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">原油</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">9</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月合约现在已经是</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">45.47</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">美元，比两周之前</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">40</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">美元以下，强劲了不少。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　国际油价为什么在短期迅速上涨</span>?<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">来听理财投研部主管王融的分析</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">:</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　王融：上周，卡塔尔能源部长表示</span>OPEC<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">成员国会在</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">9</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">26</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">号到</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">28</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">号会召开会议，可能会讨论稳定油市的一些举措，受到这个消息油价当天一度刺激了油价当天就彪升了近</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">5%</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">。但这个问题上，但沙特仍在增产，而伊朗的石油部长曾经也说过，伊朗在推高原油产量上来是无需</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">OPEC</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">来批准的。在经济制裁解除之后，也会全力去恢复原油产量，重新夺取丧失的市场份额。很多的机构预测，会议召开之后可能没办法对冻结产量达成共识。另外，利比亚、尼日利亚的产油量已经是处于一个相对比较低的位置，他们也不会去同意去冻结产量，不能达到减产目标。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　石油输出国组织</span>opec<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">，成立于</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">1960</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年，宗旨是维护产油国的共同利益。现有</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">14</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">个成员国是：沙特、伊拉克、伊朗、科威特、阿联酋、卡塔尔、利比亚、尼日利亚、阿尔及利亚、安哥拉、厄瓜多尔、委内瑞拉、加蓬和印度尼西亚。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　不过很明显，</span>Opec<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">成员们的利益很难统一，比如伊朗、沙特这对“对头”，再比如委内瑞拉目前经济处于崩溃边缘，国内物资紧张，国民不得不去哥伦比亚采购生活必需品，想要达成减产目标谈何容易。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　国际油价在</span>2008<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年最高达到了每桶</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">140</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">美元，当时</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">opec</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">主席说，未来油价每桶</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">200</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">美元，但实际情况是从</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">2014</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年的每桶一百美元一路下滑到最低</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">30</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">美元一桶。委内瑞拉、沙特等国都感受到了压力，那么油价今年或者明年还有机会回到每桶</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">80</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">美元吗</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">?</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　王融：中短期来看，</span>OPEC<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">成员国很难达成一个冻产协议。第二，目前石油还是处于相对的供大于求的阶段。另外，我们观察到原油的消费占比，发达经济体在逐年的下滑，现在中国、印度、巴西这些新兴经济体的占比在上涨，但未来需求上升空间有限。最关键的一点是，石油是和美元呈一个负相关性的，未来受到美元加息的预期的影响，强势美元的走势现在基本上已经确定，同时现在也面临着美国大选以及英国脱欧之后的风险在逐步的释放，对原油市场产生一些利空的影响。因此，未来石油很难说有一个大幅度上升的追逐力，基本上会维持在</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">40</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">到</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">60</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">美元区间震荡的行情。</span></span></p><p><br/></p>','国际油价三个交易日大涨10%','　　据经济之声《天下公司》报道，在过去三个交易日里油价上涨幅度达10%，美国WTI原油9月合约现在已经是45.47美元，比两周之前40美元以下，强劲了不少。','1','1','2017-03-11 21:25:50','','0','','','0','{\"thumb\":\"\"}','1','0','0','0','','');INSERT INTO ts_posts ( `id`, `post_author`, `post_keywords`, `post_source`, `post_date`, `post_content`, `post_title`, `post_excerpt`, `post_status`, `comment_status`, `post_modified`, `post_content_filtered`, `post_parent`, `post_type`, `post_mime_type`, `comment_count`, `smeta`, `post_hits`, `post_like`, `istop`, `recommended`, `page_tpl`, `page_tpls` ) VALUES  ('276','1','成品油价格迎来下半年首次上调','','2017-03-11 21:27:29','<p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　根据近期国际市场油价变化情况，按照现行成品油价格形成机制，自</span>2016<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">8</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">18</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">日</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">24</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">时起，国内汽、柴油价格（标准品，下同）每吨分别提高</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">175</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">元和</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">170</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">元。全国平均来看，折合</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">90</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">号汽油每升上调</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">0.13</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">元，</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">92</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">号汽油每升上调</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">0.14</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">元，</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">95</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">号上调</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">0.15</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">元，</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">0</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">号柴油每升上调</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">0.15</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">元。按一般家用汽车油箱</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">50L</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">容量估测，加满一箱</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">92</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">号汽油将多花约</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">7</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">块钱。</span></span></p><p><br/></p>','成品油价格迎来下半年首次上调','根据近期国际市场油价变化情况，按照现行成品油价格形成机制，自2016年8月18日24时起，国内汽、柴油价格（标准品，下同）每吨分别提高175元和170元','1','1','2017-03-11 21:26:47','','0','','','0','{\"thumb\":\"\"}','1','0','0','0','','');INSERT INTO ts_posts ( `id`, `post_author`, `post_keywords`, `post_source`, `post_date`, `post_content`, `post_title`, `post_excerpt`, `post_status`, `comment_status`, `post_modified`, `post_content_filtered`, `post_parent`, `post_type`, `post_mime_type`, `comment_count`, `smeta`, `post_hits`, `post_like`, `istop`, `recommended`, `page_tpl`, `page_tpls` ) VALUES  ('277','1','全球能源转型特征与中国的选择','','2017-03-11 21:29:27','<p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\">　　</span><strong><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;font-size: 14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">编者按</span> </span></strong><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">能源是现代化的基础和动力。能源供应和安全事关我国现代化建设全局。当前，全球能源正在进行第三次转型，具有不少鲜明的新特征。从现在到</span>2020<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年，是能源发展转型的重要战略机遇期。我们要把握机遇，做好体制机制建设，真正推动能源生产和消费革命，打造中国能源升级版。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><strong><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;font-size: 14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　全球第三次能源转型的特征</span></span></strong></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　能源转型是指能源生产和消费结构发生根本性的改变，并对一国社会经济发展乃至全球地缘政治格局产生深刻影响。从全球来看，曾经发生过两次能源转型，第一次是煤炭取代木材成为主导能源，第二次是油气取代煤炭成为主要能源。当前正在进行第三次能源转型，尽管处于初期阶段，与前两次能源转型相比，已具有明显的区别。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　一是开发利用可再生能源是当前全球能源转型的重要内容。近年来，清洁、低碳、可再生能源发展迅速，并将取代化石能源成为主要能源。从电源结构来看，可再生能源已经成为仅次于煤炭的、全球第二大电力来源，</span>IEA<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">预计，到</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">2030</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年前后，可再生能源将超越燃煤发电，成为全球最大电力来源；到</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">2040</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年，可再生能源电力将占所有新增发电容量的一半以上。从燃料结构来看，生物燃料和电力已部分替代石油。</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">2014</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年，全球电动汽车销量迅速增长。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　二是以建立低碳、可持续的能源供给与能源消费体系为目标。前两次能源转型是伴随工业革命进行的，机械化、自动化的大工业生产，使得能源需求在短期内快速上升，形成了以提供高能量密度、大规模的能源生产体系供应。英美等先行工业化国家率先实现了前两次能源转型并充分享有能源转型的红利，大量的化石能源投入到生产中，创造了前所未有的物质繁荣，但也产生大量的温室气体，对全球气候变化和人类的生存安全产生严重的影响。而当前的能源转型源于对高碳能源使用后果的科学认识以及低碳能源利用技术的快速发展，人类的自觉行动加上科学技术进步构成推动第三次能源转型的基础。从现状与发展趋势来看，消费同等能量能源所排放的温室气体在一些国家已开始减少，以分布式为代表的适应于可再生能源特点、环境友好的能源生产体系正在形成，传统的能源消费正在向绿色、低碳方向发展。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　三是合作共赢、政策引导是当前能源转型的重要特征。能源转型所要解决的资源问题、气候变化问题和安全问题是全球性问题，仅依靠少数国家不能取得明显效果，需要在全球范围内形成国际合作机制，促进世界各国共同行动，实现能源转型。与前两次能源转型仅在少数发达国家率先进行不同，当前进行的第三次能源转型的全球化趋势非常突出。当前，各国政府采取积极的政策措施，除了一些能源消费大国加快能源转型的步伐外，一大批能源资源丰富的国家也在转型。</span>2015<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年，全球已有多个国家设立了可再生能源转型的目标。前两次的能源转型，分别经过了上百年和数十年，当前进行的能源转型，政府政策的引导至关重要。时不我待，主动作为，是当前能源转型与前两次能源转型的一个重要区别。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　四是能源转型乃科技进步推动下社会发展的必然趋势。当前正在进行的能源转型虽然政策引导的作用突出，但是推动能源转型的根本力量仍是科学技术。站在社会发展规律的高度来认识能源转型，要避免完全照搬他国的政策工具与措施；要避免从国家安全和国家竞争优势等角度片面地理解能源转型，影响对能源转型趋势性的认识；要避免把能源转型等同于能源革命或者转变能源发展方式。从能源发展规律来看，能源转型需要较长的时间，是一项长期的过程，推进能源革命，是要加速能源转型的进程。能源革命是手段，而不是目的。转变能源发展方式也只是解决我国当前能源转型过程中一些问题，不能完全替代能源转型，能源体制改革的重要目的是解放生产力和促进科技进步。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\">　　</span><strong><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;font-size: 14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">中国能源转型需要新措施</span></span></strong></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　中国能源转型需要新措施，跨越实现能源结构的演进与转变。当前世界能源转型均处于初期阶段，但各国有所差异。总体上，欧盟一些国家处于领先地位。</span>“十一五”时期以来，中国节能减排取得显著成效。能源消费增速减缓，能源结构与能源效率不断改进，新能源发电装机规模位居世界前列，单位<span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">GDP</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">能耗和温室气体排放持续下降。但从转型的基础来看，中国能源结构以煤炭为主，与已完成两次能源转型的其他国家相比，中国能源转型的任务非常艰巨。从经济发展水平对能源价格承受力来看，中国明显低于发达国家。因此，中国能源转型必须要有更强的变革才能与其他国家同步进行。中国能源结构的演进不可能像西方国家那样，依次完成由煤炭到油气，再从油气到可再生能源的变化，而可能要直接进入以可再生能源为主的发展阶段，跨越式地演进和迭代式地发展。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　用可再生能源替代化石能源，需要满足两个基本条件：一是资源量是否充足，二是价格是否被市场所接受。总体来看，中国可再生能源资源丰富，可以满足能源转型的需要，但分布不均衡，</span>2020<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年，一些资源条件较好的地区可再生能源发电可率先实现平价上网。我国要实现以清洁可再生能源为主的能源结构，一是要加快发展可再生能源，二是要大幅度提高能源利用效率。目前，尽管我国可再生能源发展较快，能源利用效率改进幅度较大，但在资源与温室气体排放的约束条件下，要在</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">2050</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年完成转型，仍需加快可再生能源发展和大幅度提高能源利用效率。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　世界经济长远发展的动力源自创新。国际金融危机后，全球技术创新活动在经历短期低潮后开始恢复，技术创新渐趋活跃。太阳能、风能、地热能等可再生能源开发、存贮和传输技术进步步伐加快，提升了新能源利用效率和发展速度，新能源产业发展日渐成熟，风电、光伏发电的成本不断下降，竞争能力日益增强。巴黎气候变化大会提出把全球平均气温升高幅度控制在</span>2<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">摄氏度以内的目标。中国在减排问题上，显示一个大国应尽的责任。中国承诺，二氧化碳排放</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">2030</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年左右达到峰值并争取尽早达峰；单位国内生产总值二氧化碳排放比</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">2005</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年下降</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">60%</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">至</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">65%</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">。中国温室气体排放源主要来自化石能源的生产与消费，解决环境污染与温室气体排放问题，重要出路是改变能源结构，减少化石能源生产与消费，发展清洁可再生能源，建立更加高效、清洁的能源生产和消费体系。与此同时，要实现降低温室气体减排的目标，要以大幅度提高能效为主，控制煤炭和能源消费总量。总之，中国是全球第一大能源消费国，以煤为主的能源结构使得中国的减排任务非常艰巨。中国的国情也决定了中国能源转型需要采取新的行动。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\">　</span><strong><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;font-size: 14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　从四个方面做好体制机制建设</span></span></strong></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　促进能源转型，需要探讨能源产业政策。能源转型有多种路径和政策工具选择，选择的标准简而言之就是成本低、效果好。我国实施的能源产业政策主要包括能源补贴、能源效率和能源结构</span>3<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">类产业政策。由于我国能源消费基数大、速度快，为了实现减排承诺，控制能源消费总量，亦是能源宏观管控的重要内容。当前我国正处于“三期叠加”的时期，经济发展进入新常态，有必要结合能源产业发展面临的新形势以及新问题，对我国已实施的能源产业政策进行评估调整，形成更好的政策组合。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　政策实施的效率是以体制为基础，体制机制是能源转型的重要保障。从能源转型的客观需要出发，中国当前体制机制改革与建设需要做好以下几方面的工作：</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　一是强化有利于能源转型的电力市场建设。新能源利用主要是以发电的形式，电力市场体制建设至关重要。在电力体制改革过程中，要注意以能源转型为重要目标，建立适应新能源发电的电力系统，发展智能电网和电动汽车，促进跨区域电力交易，开展新能源发电的辅助服务，在条件许可的地区，推动可再生电力与其他能源的综合供应。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　二是完善可再生能源发电补贴政策。虽然</span>2020<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年以后，一些地区的可再生能源发电可能不再需要补贴，但是从总体来看，可再生能源与常规能源相比在较长时间内仍不具有市场竞争力。目前，中国可再生能源补贴存在一定的缺口。随着我国可再生能源发展及其内外环境的变化，对可再生能源的补贴要实现发挥导向作用，注意对分布式发电的补贴，提高可再生能源发电装机的利用率，优化可再生能源补贴资金来源，保持补贴政策的稳定性。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　三是要发挥产业对节能减排的积极作用。产业具有双重身份，一方面是能源消耗的主体，另一方面也是推动节能减排和能源转型的技术载体。能源转型要坚持以产业为重点，强化节能减排措施，一方面降低能源需求增速，另一方面强化低碳清洁技术的供给与应用。要大力发展低碳绿色农业，积极构建低碳的工业体系，实施服务业的绿色发展，加强行业准入管理，规范新能源产业发展。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　四是建立健全能源转型的投资机制。可再生能源发展和化石能源的清洁利用，需要巨大的投入。资金投入不足会严重影响能源转型。要强化新能源产业的投融资机制建设，完善金融服务，扩大银行业对新能源产业的信贷支持，鼓励金融创新，推进与新能源相关的金融产品开发。完善资本市场，实现新能源产业金融支持的多元化，加快设立新能源产业投资基金，大力发展风险投资和创业投资，拓宽资金来源渠道，促进新能源投资主体多元化。</span></span></p><p><br/></p>','全球能源转型特征与中国的选择','　　编者按 能源是现代化的基础和动力。能源供应和安全事关我国现代化建设全局。当前，全球能源正在进行第三次转型，具有不少鲜明的新特征。从现在到2020年，是能源发展转型的重要战略机遇期。我们要把握机遇，做好体制机制建设，真正推动能源生产和消费革命，打造中国能源升级版。','1','1','2017-03-11 21:27:59','','0','','','0','{\"thumb\":\"\"}','0','0','0','0','','');INSERT INTO ts_posts ( `id`, `post_author`, `post_keywords`, `post_source`, `post_date`, `post_content`, `post_title`, `post_excerpt`, `post_status`, `comment_status`, `post_modified`, `post_content_filtered`, `post_parent`, `post_type`, `post_mime_type`, `comment_count`, `smeta`, `post_hits`, `post_like`, `istop`, `recommended`, `page_tpl`, `page_tpls` ) VALUES  ('278','1','单纯依靠市场机制解决不了产能过剩','','2017-03-11 21:30:22','<p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\">　　19<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">日，在国务院新闻办举行的国务院政策例行吹风会上，国家发展改革委副主任连维良表示，钢铁和煤炭之所以出现产能严重过剩，在一定意义上，市场机制已经不能充分发挥作用，单纯靠市场机制的作用不能解决产能过剩的问题，必须充分发挥市场配置资源的决定性作用和更好地发挥政府的作用。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\">　　“推进钢铁、煤炭去产能，必须充分发挥市场配置资源的决定性作用和更好地发挥政府的作用，要发挥市场和政府两只手的作用。”连维良说，“政府作用的发挥，也是以尊重市场规律作为前提。”</span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　连维良指出，推动去产能过程当中，采取落实责任，签订责任书的办法，这也是建立在遵循市场经济规律，发挥市场机制作用的基础上。去产能是要淘汰落后产能，保护先进产能，引导退出产能。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　对于一些落后产能，必须充分发挥政府的作用，使这些产能能够退出，避免出现</span>“劣币驱逐良币”的情况。对于先进产能要采取保护措施，先进产能不承担去产能任务，让先进产能充分发挥作用。对于其它不属于先进产能也不属于落后产能的，政府通过政策引导的办法，顺应市场经济规律，使这些产能按一定比例退出。</span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\">　　“无论地方政府或者中央政府，都不会采取补贴措施支持钢铁煤炭增加产能，专项奖补资金更不可能用于增产能，而是要用于去产能。”连维良说。</span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　但是，连维良强调，企业在退出产能的过程当中职工安置、债务处理面临很多困难和问题，单纯靠市场的作用，企业可能不愿意退出，产能过剩的问题就不可能得到解决，政府通过支持，使这些该退出的产能尽快退出，改变行业产能过剩的局面。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\">　　“从这个意义上说，发挥政府的作用和发挥市场机制的作用并不矛盾，而且这正是中国体制的一种优势，也正是我们这样一种体制能够加快解决产能过剩的突出矛盾。”连维良说。</span></p><p><br/></p>','发改委：单纯依靠市场机制解决不了产能过剩','　　19日，在国务院新闻办举行的国务院政策例行吹风会上，国家发展改革委副主任连维良表示，钢铁和煤炭之所以出现产能严重过剩，在一定意义上，市场机制已经不能充分发挥作用，单纯靠市场机制的作用不能解决产能过剩的问题，必须充分发挥市场配置资源的决定性作用和更好地发挥政府的作用。','1','1','2017-03-11 21:29:38','','0','','','0','{\"thumb\":\"\"}','0','0','0','0','','');INSERT INTO ts_posts ( `id`, `post_author`, `post_keywords`, `post_source`, `post_date`, `post_content`, `post_title`, `post_excerpt`, `post_status`, `comment_status`, `post_modified`, `post_content_filtered`, `post_parent`, `post_type`, `post_mime_type`, `comment_count`, `smeta`, `post_hits`, `post_like`, `istop`, `recommended`, `page_tpl`, `page_tpls` ) VALUES  ('279','1','&quot;十三五&quot;我国能源消费或保持低速增长','','2017-03-11 21:31:14','<p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\">　　“经济增长<span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">1%</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">，能源消费增长</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">0.5%</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">，这样是比较合理的状态。但现在来看，估计守不住了。”国家发展和改革委员会能源研究所高级研究员韩文科</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">19</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">日在上海表示，中长期来看，我国能源消费将保持低速增长状态。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　韩文科当日在上海国际能源创新中心举办的</span>“<span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">2016</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">上海能源创新论坛”上发言表示，“十二五”期间，我国能源消费增速平均</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">3.6%</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">左右，但最后一年</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">(2015</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">)</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">增速仅为</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">0.9%</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">。进入</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">2016</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年之后，这种低增长的状态仍在持续。今年</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">1-7</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月我国全社会用电量同比增长只有</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">3.6%</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">。按照目前的经济增速来说，用电量同比增幅保持在</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">4%</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">左右比较合理。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　韩文科预计，</span>“十三五”期间，我国能源消费低速增长的状态将延续，其中，煤炭消费维持负增长，电力消费增长不超过<span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">3%</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">，石油消费增速保持在</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">3%</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">左右。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　受能源供应不断增长，而能源消费增速逐步放缓影响，我国传统煤电大量过剩，发电利用小时数不断走低。在能源供需宽松的大背景下，我国需加快能源结构的优化，加速向绿色低碳方向转型。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　韩文科介绍，</span>“十三五”期间，我国能源领域将加快供给侧改革，压缩煤电比例，推动清洁能源的使用。同时加快电力、油气领域的市场化改革，推动价格体制改革。</span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　按照发展规划，</span>“十三五”末，我国天然气消费量要达到<span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">3500</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">亿立方米。虽然近一两年来，我国天然气消费增速明显放缓，但韩文科认为，这一目标还是可以实现的。“随着我国油气领域的改革逐步开展，煤炭消费的逐渐减弱，以气代煤仍有很大的市场空间。”</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　国家发展改革委发布的数据显示，今年上半年我国天然气消费量为</span>995<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">亿立方米，同比增长</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">9.8%</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">。</span></span></p><p><br/></p>','&quot;十三五&quot;我国能源消费或保持低速增长','　　“经济增长1%，能源消费增长0.5%，这样是比较合理的状态。但现在来看，估计守不住了。”国家发展和改革委员会能源研究所高级研究员韩文科19日在上海表示，中长期来看，我国能源消费将保持低速增长状态。','1','1','2017-03-11 21:30:33','','0','','','0','{\"thumb\":\"\"}','1','0','0','0','','');INSERT INTO ts_posts ( `id`, `post_author`, `post_keywords`, `post_source`, `post_date`, `post_content`, `post_title`, `post_excerpt`, `post_status`, `comment_status`, `post_modified`, `post_content_filtered`, `post_parent`, `post_type`, `post_mime_type`, `comment_count`, `smeta`, `post_hits`, `post_like`, `istop`, `recommended`, `page_tpl`, `page_tpls` ) VALUES  ('280','1','油企巨头应对低油价各出妙招','','2017-03-11 21:32:24','<p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　以美国为基地的石油巨头，包括雪佛龙、埃克森美孚和康菲石油都于近期发布了二季度季报。不出所料，由于国际油气价格持续走低，这些公司的季报都相当难看。雪佛龙报亏</span>15<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">亿美元，已是连续第三个季度亏损，但幅度小于预期；埃克森美孚利润同比减少</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">59%</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">；康菲石油则净亏损</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">10</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">亿美元。尽管季报一片惨淡，但从</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">3</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">家公司近期表现看，其对未来的信心并未丧失。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><strong><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;font-size: 14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　雪佛龙：优化资产组合</span></span></strong></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　雪佛龙在国际油价低迷的背景下，不断优化资产组合，以提高投入产出比。主要举措是一方面大力剥离资产，一方面加强核心资产投入。据最新消息，雪佛龙将以</span>50<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">亿美元的价格出售在亚洲的资产，同时核心资产勘探活动也在紧锣密鼓进行中。上游业务负责人在</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">8</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月初的会议上表示，年底前将在二叠纪盆地新增</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">4</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">台钻机，加大钻探力度。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　雪佛龙很重视二叠纪盆地的油气业务，目前已有</span>6<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">台钻机正在运行。在加大钻探力度的同时，考虑到当下全球石油行业局势，注重控制推进节奏，保持产能和提高资本效益是雪佛龙关注的两个要点。雪佛龙将二叠纪盆地的非常规油气资产视为核心资产，近年来更注重提高其在总资产中的占比，目前非常规油气资产占雪佛龙总资产的</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">25%</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">。而将在二叠纪盆地积累的经验推广至其他地区的非常规油气资产，也是雪佛龙未来发展的主要方向，包括马塞勒斯、</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">Duvernay</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">和阿根廷的</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">Vaca</span>　<span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">Muerta</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">等区块。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\">　　</span><strong><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;font-size: 14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">埃克森美孚：增加</span>PNG　<span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">LNG</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">产能</span></span></strong></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　埃克森美孚似乎选择了另一条道路，减少了二叠纪盆地的钻机数量，仅留下</span>10<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">台钻机。对于未来，埃克森美孚在关注供需基本面的同时，控制资产开发进度，既不错失机遇，又不突击冒进，同时加大必要的基础设施建设。其近年的重点颇有向天然气转向的意味，如近期打算斥巨资收购巴布亚新几内亚拥有大量资产的</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">InterOil</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">公司。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　埃克森美孚已多年不曾收购其他公司，主要购买土地和油气资产。此前埃克森美孚最大一笔收购案发生在</span>2009<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年，以</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">310</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">亿美元收购</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">XTO</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">能源公司，获得后者在美国大量待开发的页岩油气储备。接着</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">2013</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年，斥资</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">26</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">亿美元收购加拿大</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">Celtic</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">勘探公司，将加拿大的大量页岩油气资产收入囊中。如果这次收购交易顺利达成，埃克森美孚在该地的资产将因</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">InterOil</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">的加入而新增</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">400</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">万英亩和</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">6</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">个许可证区块，</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">PNG</span>　<span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">LNG</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">项目的年产能将达到</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">740</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">万吨，较</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">2015</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年的设计产能高</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">7%</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">。</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">LNG</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">产业的快速成长让巴布亚新几内亚跻身全球能源出口国行列，埃克森美孚看好天然气的未来发展，是想拿下</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">InterOil</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">公司的最重要原因，也反映了其未来的策略。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\">　　</span><strong><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;font-size: 14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">康菲石油：积极寻求熊市生存之道</span></span></strong></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　康菲石油二季度虽然报亏，但现金流有所改善，未来该公司将进一步压缩成本。除推迟一些油气钻探项目上马外，康菲石油裁员力度也很大。</span>7<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月底，康菲石油宣布，下半年将继续裁员</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">1000</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">人，主要是美国和加拿大的工作岗位，裁员人数约占公司员工总数的</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">6%</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">。去年</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">9</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月以来，康菲石油已裁员</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">3400</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">人，约占员工总数的</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">18%</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　现在，康菲石油通过一系列措施，取得很好的成效，产量增加，而资本支出和经营支出则有所减少，保本价也进一步降低。虽然仍面临国际油价下行的压力，但与之前相比，康菲石油已占据更有利的地位。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　国际油价在</span>2<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月的低点反弹后，</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">7</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月末再遇上行压力，一度跌破</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">40</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">美元</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">/</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">桶，未来对国际大型油气公司仍将造成巨大压力。但经历过业界无数次风雨的大型油气公司似乎并不会因此信心受挫，相反，经受住洗礼的公司，通过调整策略、重设重心、积极降本增效，未来更好的发展几乎是可以预见的。</span></span></p><p><br/></p>','油企巨头应对低油价各出妙招','　　以美国为基地的石油巨头，包括雪佛龙、埃克森美孚和康菲石油都于近期发布了二季度季报。不出所料，由于国际油气价格持续走低，这些公司的季报都相当难看。雪佛龙报亏15亿美元，已是连续第三个季度亏损，但幅度小于预期；埃克森美孚利润同比减少59%；康菲石油则净亏损10亿美元。尽管季报一片惨淡，但从3家公司近期表现看，其对未来的信心并未丧失。','1','1','2017-03-11 21:31:29','','0','','','0','{\"thumb\":\"\"}','1','0','0','0','','');INSERT INTO ts_posts ( `id`, `post_author`, `post_keywords`, `post_source`, `post_date`, `post_content`, `post_title`, `post_excerpt`, `post_status`, `comment_status`, `post_modified`, `post_content_filtered`, `post_parent`, `post_type`, `post_mime_type`, `comment_count`, `smeta`, `post_hits`, `post_like`, `istop`, `recommended`, `page_tpl`, `page_tpls` ) VALUES  ('281','1','中海油上半年净亏77.4亿元','','2017-03-11 21:36:22','<p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　中国海洋石油有限公司</span>(<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">以下简称中海油</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">)24</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">日公布公司截至</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">2016</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">6</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">30</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">日的中期业绩。报告显示，截至</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">2016</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">6</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">30</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">日，公司净亏损为人民币</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">77.4</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">亿元。公司油气销售收入为人民币</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">550.8</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">亿元，同比下降</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">28.5%</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　报告指出，上半年，公司勘探开发等各项业务稳步推进。勘探方面共获得</span>6<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">个新发现和</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">26</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">口成功评价井，其中，中国海域获得</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">6</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">个新发现及</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">20</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">口成功评价井；海外获得</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">6</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">口成功评价井。计划年内投产的</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">4</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">个新项目进展顺利，垦利</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">10-4</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">油田和番禺</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">11-5</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">油田已经投产，其他</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">2</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">个新项目顺利推进。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　中海油表示，得益于降本增效的各项得力措施，上半年公司成本控制效果显著，主要成本指标大幅下降，桶油主要成本为</span>34.86<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">美元</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">/</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">桶油当量，同比下降</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">15.5%</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">。其中作业费</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">7.42</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">美元</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">/</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">桶油当量，同比下降</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">22.7%</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">，中国海域和海外均同比下降。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　报告期内，公司油气净产量为</span>241.5<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">百万桶油当量，同比增长</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">0.6%</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">。其中，中国海域净产量为</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">160.1</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">百万桶油当量，同比增长</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">2.4%</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">，主要来自渤海和南海西部新投产项目的贡献；受长湖项目事故关停影响，海外净产量同比下降</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">2.9%</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">，为</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">81.5</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">百万桶油当量。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　受国际原油价格下降影响，公司上半年平均实现油价为</span>37.70<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">美元</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">/</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">桶，同比下降</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">34.5%</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">；平均实现天然气价为</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">5.49</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">美元</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">/</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">千立方英尺，同比下降</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">16.2%</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">，主要是由于中国政府去年下半年下调天然气价格，中国海域部分气田价格下降。公司油气销售收入为人民币</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">550.8</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">亿元，同比下降</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">28.5%</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">。净亏损为人民币</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">77.4</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">亿元。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　上半年，中海油的每股基本亏损为人民币</span>0.17<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">元，公司董事会决定派发</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">2016</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年中期股息每股</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">0.12</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">港元</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">(</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">含税</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">)</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">。</span></span></p><p><br/></p>','中海油上半年净亏77.4亿元','　　中国海洋石油有限公司(以下简称中海油)24日公布公司截至2016年6月30日的中期业绩。报告显示，截至2016年6月30日，公司净亏损为人民币77.4亿元。公司油气销售收入为人民币550.8亿元，同比下降28.5%。','1','1','2017-03-11 21:35:12','','0','','','0','{\"thumb\":\"\"}','0','0','0','0','','');INSERT INTO ts_posts ( `id`, `post_author`, `post_keywords`, `post_source`, `post_date`, `post_content`, `post_title`, `post_excerpt`, `post_status`, `comment_status`, `post_modified`, `post_content_filtered`, `post_parent`, `post_type`, `post_mime_type`, `comment_count`, `smeta`, `post_hits`, `post_like`, `istop`, `recommended`, `page_tpl`, `page_tpls` ) VALUES  ('282','1','降低实体经济用能成本','','2017-03-11 21:38:19','<p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　为了有效缓解实体经济企业困难、应对经济下行压力、增强经济可持续发展能力，日前，国务院出台《降低实体经济企业成本工作方案》</span>(<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">国发</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">[2016]48</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">号，以下简称工作方案</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">)</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">，将降低能源成本作为降低实体经济企业成本六大途径之一，明确提出“企业用电、用气定价机制市场化程度明显提升，工商业用电和工业用气价格合理降低”的目标任务。这是基于我国实体经济用能量巨大，用能成本相对较高，不同能源行业市场化程度不同，不同能源品种价格下降空间不一而做出科学决策。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　加快推进能源领域改革，放开竞争性环节价格。《工作方案》明确提出，</span>2017<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年基本放开竞争性领域和环节价格管制，形成充分竞争的机制，使能源价格充分反映市场供求变化，提高价格灵活性，突出强调做好以下两个方面的工作。一是加快推进电力、石油、天然气等领域市场化改革。尽可能在上述各领域、各环节打破垄断，引入竞争机制。二是完善光伏、风电等新能源发电并网机制。在当前能源和电力需求增长趋缓的形势下，随着可再生能源开发利用规模不断扩大，部分地区也出现了较为严重的弃风弃光弃水等突出问题，必须加以妥善解决。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　加快推进电力体制改革，合理降低企业用电成本。《工作方案》将降低企业用电成本作为降低企业用能成本的最有力、最直接、最有效的手段。明确要求以进一步深化电力体制改革作为推动电力价格下降。一是加快实施输配电价改革试点。</span>2014<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年，先行在蒙西、深圳电网启动输配电价改革试点。</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">2015</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年，将试点范围扩大到湖北、安徽、云南、贵州、宁夏等</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">5</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">省区。</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">2016</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年，进一步扩大到北京、天津、山西、陕西、江西、湖南、四川、重庆、广东、广西等</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">12</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">个省级电网和华北区域电网，同时将开展电力体制综合改革的试点省份也要纳入到输配电价改革试点。目前，国家发展改革委正在统一组织对上述试点地区的电网公司交叉开展成本监审。二是积极开展电力直接交易，扩大市场化交易电量的比例。</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">2016</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">3</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月，国家电网公司和南方电网公司分别挂牌成立北京电力交易中心和广州电力交易中心。国家电网公司经营范围内的山西、湖北和重庆很快成立电力交易机构；南方电网公司经营范围内的广东、广西、贵州和云南也相继成立股份制的电力交易中心。今年</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">1</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">至</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">7</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月，全国签订的电力交易量超过</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">7300</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">亿千瓦时，全年有可能实现电力交易量</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">1</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">万亿千瓦时。三是继续实施好煤电价格联动机制。</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">2015</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年，经过国务院批准，国家发展改革委对外公布了修订完善的煤电价格联动机制。主要内容归纳为“一个公开、四个明确、一个区间”。即电煤价格指数公开，明确依据、明确计算价格公式、明确周期、明确执行时间，电煤的波动区间</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">30</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">—</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">150</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">元。</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">2016</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">1</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月份，通过实施煤电价格联动，燃煤机组上网电价、一般工商业电价平均降低每千瓦时</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">3</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">分钱。四是简化企业用户电力增容、减容、暂停、变更等办理手续，缩短办理时限。</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">2016</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">6</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">30</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">日，国家发展改革委下发了《关于完善两部制电价用户基本电价执行方式的通知》，主要思路是：第一，要放宽基本电费变更周期，按容量申请由一年一申请调整到一季一申请，按最大需量计费的，由按季申请调整到按月变更。取消对暂停用电次数的限制。第二，将一年内规定暂停两次修改为不做暂停次数限制。第三，暂不执行申请过减容或暂停用电的两年内不得再申请减容和暂停用电的规定，暂不执行新装、增容用户两年内不得申请减容和暂停用电的规定。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　释放能源价格改革红利，有效减缓企业负担。随着《工作方案》逐步落实，企业用能成本将进一步下降。一是降低输配价格。初步核定蒙西、深圳和</span>2015<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年试点的</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">5</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">省区在第一个监管周期输配电后形成的降价空间</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">80</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">亿元。可以预计，</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">2017</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年，在全国范围内推行输配电价格改革带来的降价空间更大。二是降低交易成本。初步预计今年市场大用户直接交易电量可达到</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">1</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">万亿千瓦时，直接交易平均降低用户购电价格每千瓦时</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">5.1</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">分钱，可降低企业用电支出</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">374</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">亿元。今年市场交易电量占总消费量的比例尚不到</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">20%</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">，随着电力交易市场的不断扩大，企业用电支出将进一步减少。三是降低天然气价格。近两年，我国推行“净回值”法天然气价格机制改革，实现存量气与增量气价格并轨，调整了天然气门站价，非居民用气最高门站价格每千立方米降低</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">700</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">元，考虑到地方根据各自情况调整非居民用气销售价格的工作尚未完成，政策效果将进一步显现。</span></span></p><p><br/></p>','发改委：降低实体经济用能成本','　　为了有效缓解实体经济企业困难、应对经济下行压力、增强经济可持续发展能力，日前，国务院出台《降低实体经济企业成本工作方案》(国发[2016]48号，以下简称工作方案)，将降低能源成本作为降低实体经济企业成本六大途径之一，明确提出“企业用电、用气定价机制市场化程度明显提升，工商业用电和工业用气价格合理降低”的目标任务。','1','1','2017-03-11 21:36:38','','0','','','0','{\"thumb\":\"\"}','0','0','0','0','','');INSERT INTO ts_posts ( `id`, `post_author`, `post_keywords`, `post_source`, `post_date`, `post_content`, `post_title`, `post_excerpt`, `post_status`, `comment_status`, `post_modified`, `post_content_filtered`, `post_parent`, `post_type`, `post_mime_type`, `comment_count`, `smeta`, `post_hits`, `post_like`, `istop`, `recommended`, `page_tpl`, `page_tpls` ) VALUES  ('283','1','全国成品油价格指数小幅回落','','2017-03-11 21:39:55','<p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　依据新华</span>(<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">大庆</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">)</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">国际石油资讯中心发布的报告，截至</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">8</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">24</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">日，全国成品油价格指数为</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">577.08</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">，跌幅</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">0.37%</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">，全国成品油价格指数小幅回落。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　全国成品油价格指数运行结果表明，上周</span>93#<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">汽油平均价格报收于</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">5645</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">元</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">/</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">吨，较前一报告周期下跌</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">126</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">元</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">/</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">吨</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">(</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">折合</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">0.09</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">元</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">/</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">升</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">)</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">；</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">0#</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">柴油平均价格报收于</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">4929</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">元</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">/</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">吨，较前一报告周期上涨</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">31</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">元</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">/</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">吨</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">(</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">折合</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">0.03</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">元</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">/</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">升</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">)</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">。综合来看，全国汽油平均价格走低，带动全国成品油价格指数小幅回落。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　新华</span>(<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">大庆</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">)</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">国际石油资讯中心分析师蒋冰认为，近期因伊朗表态愿意共同削减原油产量加之美元低位震荡，国际油价继续上行。国内油品市场批零价格持稳为主，部分地区下游客户观望待市，价格小幅回落。四川省成都市某加油站负责人表示：“目前一揽子原油变化率继续正向运行，主营单位任务量基本完成，汽柴价格继续高位，目前业者入市采购积极性不佳，市场成交一般。”</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　蒋冰分析认为，近期外盘油价持续上涨，国内市场受此支撑，汽柴油价格小幅上扬，业者操作积极性转好，但贸易商基本已补仓完成，加之国内需求增长缓慢，市场交投继续维持平稳走势。陕西地炼汽柴油成交情况不一，汽油价格小幅下滑，柴油价格稳定。国际市场方面，美国石油学会</span>(API)<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">近日公布数据显示，截至</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">8</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">19</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">日当周，美国原油库存增加</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">446.4</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">万桶，至</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">5.242</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">亿桶；库欣原油库存增加</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">41.7</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">万桶，美国原油库存意外大幅增加，该消息利空国际油价。观望后市，近日国际油价受冻产预期持续上扬，但同时主要产油国产量持续攀升，基本面持续疲弱，预计短期内国际油价将维持震荡格局。</span></span></p><p><br/></p>','全国成品油价格指数小幅回落','　　依据新华(大庆)国际石油资讯中心发布的报告，截至8月24日，全国成品油价格指数为577.08，跌幅0.37%，全国成品油价格指数小幅回落。','1','1','2017-03-11 21:39:14','','0','','','0','{\"thumb\":\"\"}','1','0','0','0','','');INSERT INTO ts_posts ( `id`, `post_author`, `post_keywords`, `post_source`, `post_date`, `post_content`, `post_title`, `post_excerpt`, `post_status`, `comment_status`, `post_modified`, `post_content_filtered`, `post_parent`, `post_type`, `post_mime_type`, `comment_count`, `smeta`, `post_hits`, `post_like`, `istop`, `recommended`, `page_tpl`, `page_tpls` ) VALUES  ('284','1','成品油本周望迎“两连涨”','','2017-03-11 21:42:36','<p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　随着下月欧佩克会议可能达成冻产协议的消息持续发酵，近期国际油价继续呈现整体上涨。机构测算，由于本计价周期原油均价高于上周期均价，故而本周四（</span>9<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">1</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">日）</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">24</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">时，国内成品油限价将会再次迎来上调。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\">　　“上次计价周期末端，国际油价持续大幅上涨，导致本周期伊始，原油均价便处于高位。随后，产油国冻产预期导致原油价格继续震荡上涨，也造成了国内测算的原油变化率持续处于正值高位。据我们测算，截至<span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">8</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">26</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">日，国内第</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">7</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">个工作日，主要原油品种变化率为</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">9.03%</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">，对应汽柴油将上涨</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">300</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">元</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">/</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">吨左右，折合升价</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">92#/93#</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">汽油上涨</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">0.23</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">元</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">/</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">升；柴油上涨</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">0.26</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">元</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">/</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">升。”卓创资讯成品油分析师孟鹏说。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　他表示，此次上涨落实后，将迎来成品油限价的两连涨，也是今年以来的最大上调幅度。加上本周四的限价调整，今年以来，共经历了</span>17<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">次调价窗口，包括</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">6</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">次上涨、</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">3</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">次下调、</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">2</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">次搁浅以及</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">6</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">次因原油价格低于地板价而出现的不作调整。本次上调落实后，国内的汽油零售价格将较年初第一次调价后价格上涨</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">0.8</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">元</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">/</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">升，幅度较大。若是以一辆油箱为</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">50L</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">的私家车为例，加满一箱油将较年初增加</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">40</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">块钱左右，市民的出行成本或大幅增加。</span></span></p><p><br/></p>','成品油本周望迎“两连涨” 涨后价格较年初大幅提高','　　随着下月欧佩克会议可能达成冻产协议的消息持续发酵，近期国际油价继续呈现整体上涨。机构测算，由于本计价周期原油均价高于上周期均价，故而本周四（9月1日）24时，国内成品油限价将会再次迎来上调。','1','1','2017-03-11 21:41:32','','0','','','0','{\"thumb\":\"\"}','0','0','0','0','','');INSERT INTO ts_posts ( `id`, `post_author`, `post_keywords`, `post_source`, `post_date`, `post_content`, `post_title`, `post_excerpt`, `post_status`, `comment_status`, `post_modified`, `post_content_filtered`, `post_parent`, `post_type`, `post_mime_type`, `comment_count`, `smeta`, `post_hits`, `post_like`, `istop`, `recommended`, `page_tpl`, `page_tpls` ) VALUES  ('285','1','成品油价二连涨几成定局','','2017-03-11 21:44:00','<p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\">　　9<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">1</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">日</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">24</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">时，成品油调价时间窗口将启。受</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">8</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月以来国际油价持续回升影响，我国成品油价格将迎来“二连涨”，并可能创下今年以来最大涨幅。这也将是年内第六次成品油价格上调。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　受英国脱欧公投、美国页岩油复苏等因素打压，</span>7<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月份国际油价创出年内最大单月跌幅；</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">8</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">2</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">日，纽约油价一度跌至每桶</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">39</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">美元附近，布伦特油价跌至每桶</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">41</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">美元附近。但在产油国再度重拾冻产话题后，国际油价恢复涨势，不断上扬，至</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">8</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月下旬，纽约油价一度涨至每桶</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">48</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">美元上方，布伦特油价重返每桶</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">50</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">美元上方。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　其实，冻产话题并不新鲜。早在今年</span>2<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月，沙特等主要产油国就发出冻产倡议，但多个产油国因自身利益“不予理会”，因此，</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">4</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月份多哈谈判未果。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　虽然谈判结果难料，但话题重启已令投机基金再度</span>“热血沸腾”。美国商品期货管理委员会发布的统计数据显示，截至<span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">8</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">23</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">日当周，纽约商品交易所原油期货中投机基金净多持仓量冲到</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">35.4</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">万手，两周之内上涨了</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">37%</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">，到达年内次高点。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　易信金融总部中国区副首席交易官朱文灏认为，近日中东局势骤然收紧，尤其石油设施受到冲击，预计国际油价短期内将受到支撑，也给投机基金做多再添由头。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　但业内分析，当前全球原油资源仍供大于求，产油国冻产、地缘事件等对市场带来的实质性影响不会太大，因此本轮油价上涨仍面临供应过剩带来的天花板。同时，近期美联储主席耶伦表态偏</span>“鹰”，投资者增强了对美联储年内加息的预期，美元走强将减弱石油投资吸引力。</span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　不过截至</span>27<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">日收盘，</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">8</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月份纽约原油价格已累计上涨</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">12.9%</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">，布伦特累计上涨</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">16%</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">。由此，我国成品油价格“二连涨”几成定局。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　上一次国内成品油调价发生在</span>8<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">18</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">日</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">24</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">时，汽、柴油价格每吨分别提高</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">175</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">元和</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">170</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">元，是今年以来第五次油价上调。根据《石油价格管理办法》推算，</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">9</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">1</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">日</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">24</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">时，我国成品油调价时间窗口将开启。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　隆众资讯分析师王倩倩分析认为，本轮国际油价上涨，主因是冻产协议有可能达成的利好预期，在</span>9<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月欧佩克会议召开之前，此“利好”还会持续发酵，油价还有小幅攀升空间。因此，预计本轮成品油价格上调幅度在每吨</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">250</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">元以上，即每升汽、柴油价格涨幅超过</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">0.2</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">元。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　在此轮调价后，北京、上海等地汽油价格或重返每升</span>6<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">元时代。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　本轮成品油调价周期是今年以来第十七轮。在前十六轮周期内，我国汽、柴油价格经历了两次搁浅、三次下调、五次上调、六次因低于</span>“地板价”不调整。至此，今年以来，我国汽、柴油价格累计分别上涨了每吨<span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">265</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">元和</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">255</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">元。</span></span></p><p><br/></p>','成品油价二连涨几成定局 京沪油价或重返6元时代','　　9月1日24时，成品油调价时间窗口将启。受8月以来国际油价持续回升影响，我国成品油价格将迎来“二连涨”，并可能创下今年以来最大涨幅。这也将是年内第六次成品油价格上调。','1','1','2017-03-11 21:42:55','','0','','','0','{\"thumb\":\"\"}','0','0','0','0','','');INSERT INTO ts_posts ( `id`, `post_author`, `post_keywords`, `post_source`, `post_date`, `post_content`, `post_title`, `post_excerpt`, `post_status`, `comment_status`, `post_modified`, `post_content_filtered`, `post_parent`, `post_type`, `post_mime_type`, `comment_count`, `smeta`, `post_hits`, `post_like`, `istop`, `recommended`, `page_tpl`, `page_tpls` ) VALUES  ('286','1','G20峰会“中国方案”全球瞩目','','2017-03-11 21:45:50','<p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\">　　“作为参会企业家，非常期待这次峰会能够在推进全球经济互联互通、融合发展等方面取得更多进展。”浪潮集团董事长孙丕恕正在为即将开幕的二十国工商界活动<span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">(B20)</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">会议做着最后的准备，他对记者说，他将全程出席</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">B20</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">相关活动，非常关注大会创新全球经济增长方式等议题。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　不少与会嘉宾和专家学者均表示，二十国集团</span>(G20)<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">正在从危机应对平台转向长效治理机制，在此背景下，以“构建创新、活力、联动、包容的世界经济”为主题的</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">2016</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年杭州峰会上，即将出炉的“中国方案”，尤其是在经贸等领域的多个“首次”非常值得期待。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\">　</span><strong><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;font-size: 14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　期待中国方案将出炉</span></span></strong></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\">　　G20<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">杭州峰会设置了“创新增长方式”、“更高效全球经济金融治理”、“强劲的国际贸易和投资”、“包容和联动式发展”四大议题板块。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　此前，多个部长级会议和协调人会议已经充分预热和准备，相关成果有望在峰会中最终达成。业内预计，本次峰会将在多个方面达成重要成果，包括：制定创新增长蓝图；落实</span>2030<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年可持续发展议程行动计划；制定结构性改革优先领域、指导原则和指标体系；制定全球贸易增长战略；深化国际金融架构改革等。这将是中国作为轮值主席国对</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">G20</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">乃至全球贡献出的“中国方案”。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　值得关注的是，</span>“中国方案”中将会有多个“首次”。例如，将首次提出综合运用包括货币、财政、结构性改革措施促进增长；全球投资政策指导原则将是首份关于投资政策制订的多边纲领性文件；全球贸易增长战略将首次细致描绘全球贸易增长路径图等等。</span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　还有一些会是里程碑式的成果。例如，此前的财长和央行行长会议已经在加强结构性改革</span>“顶层设计”方面取得里程碑式的成果，明确了结构性改革的<span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">9</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">大优先领域和</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">48</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">项指导原则，并制定了一套衡量结构性改革进展和成效的指标体系。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\">　　“<span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">G20</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">的成果可以从‘稳定’和‘提速’两个层面期待。”联合国贸发会议经济事务官员梁国勇对记者表示，稳定层面，在中国的引导下，</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">G20</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">正在促进全球经济和金融稳定机制建设方面发挥日益重要的作用。之前的金融稳定委员会和国际金融架构工作组发挥作用之外，</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">7</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月成都财长和央行行长形成了“迈向更稳定、更有韧性的国际金融架构”的</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">G20</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">议程，杭州峰会上一个完善国际金融架构的“中国方案”可望诞生。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　提速层面，梁国勇指出，</span>2<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">G20</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">财长和央行行长会议公报强调“各自以及共同使用所有政策工具”促进增长、投资等目标。</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">7</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月的</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">G20</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">贸易部长会议实现了机制化，批准了《</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">G20</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">全球贸易增长战略》和《</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">G20</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">全球投资指导原则》，取得了极其重要的成果，杭州峰会的硕果可期。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　正如中国财政部部长楼继伟日前指出的，中方作为</span>G20<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">主席国，着力推动创新</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">G20</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">机制建设，推动</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">G20</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">从危机应对平台向全球经济的长效治理机制转型，从关注短期政策向更多关注结构性改革转变，并取得了里程碑式的成果，而这也是</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">G20</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">历史上第一次体现了“标本兼治”促增长的理念。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\">　</span><strong><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;font-size: 14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　背景全球经济多重风险待解</span></span></strong></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　本次</span>G20<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">杭州峰会召开之时，正值世界经济依然处于深度调整和不平衡的矛盾之中，这也是即将出炉的“中国方案”备受关注的原因之一。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　对于当前全球的经济形势，多位专家表示，世界经济仍处于国际金融危机后的深度调整期，延续了</span>“低增长、大分化”的格局，离“强劲、可持续、平衡”的增长目标还有一定距离。尽管经历年初国际金融市场波动后市场趋于平缓，但全球经济的不稳定、不确定因素增多，经济因素与非经济因素交织，一些风险有长期化、常态化趋势。</span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　梁国勇表示，全球金融危机爆发后，</span>G20<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">设定并持续强调的世界经济“强劲、可持续、平衡增长”的目标仍未实现。在他看来，当前世界经济面临的主要困难表现在以下几方面：其一，主要经济体经济增长情况普遍不佳且分化加剧，发达国家中欧洲、日本经济持续低迷，部分新兴经济体经济陷入困境；其二，来自国际金融体系的风险因素显著增强，加之基础商品价格大幅下跌，发展中国家面临持续的资本外流压力，部分国家经济、金融、国际收支和财政收入等方面均遭受严重冲击，个别国家经济濒于崩溃；其三，全球国际贸易增长失速，生产性国际投资复苏乏力，国际经贸对增长的推动尤显不足；其四，全球化动能减弱，逆全球化暗潮涌动，保护主义、孤立主义的政策影响不可低估。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　楼继伟指出，低增长已成为世界经济的新常态，主要发达经济体劳动力市场疲软，居民收入增长缓慢，投资乏力，近两年新兴经济体经济增速也有所放缓，全球总需求不足问题进一步凸显。此外，英国脱欧加剧金融市场波动，虽已趋于平稳，但金融市场对主要国家经济数据、政策变动和突发性事件的敏感度上升，对全球金融体系稳健性的挑战加大。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\">　　“美联储加息的持续预期，成为世界经济最大的不确定因素之一。”中国人民大学重阳金融研究院执行院长王文表示，<span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">2016</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年以来，对美元加息的预期仍在持续，国际大宗商品市场、国际外汇市场以及国际资本市场均受到影响，加大了</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">G20</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">政策协调的复杂性和难度。此外，全球贸易保护主义抬头也为全球经济复苏蒙上了阴影。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\">　　G20<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">联合研究中心</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">2016</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年的一份研究报告也指出，下行压力，转型缓慢和贸易保护主义抬头等将是短期内</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">G20</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">经济发展面临的主要困难和挑战。尤其是贸易和投资政策的分化已经难以适应当前全球价值链发展过程中贸易投资深度融合的趋势，因而迫切需要</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">G20</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">各国互相探讨、相互协作，提出各项有助于支持创新活动的贸易投资政策。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\">　　</span><strong><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;font-size: 14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">探路建立长效治理新机制</span></span></strong></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\">　　“<span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">G20</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">成员经济总量占全球的</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">85%</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">以上，对世界经济增长有着难以推卸的责任，需要加强宏观经济政策沟通和协调，形成政策和行动合力，维护金融市场稳定，共同提振世界经济。”王文表示，在当前全球经济面临不确定性的形势下，</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">G20</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">所需发挥的作用与</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">2008</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年国际金融危机爆发时同样重要。</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">G20</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">国家需要进一步团结起来，建立长效治理机制，以应对目前的全球经济增长乏力。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\">　　G20<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">联合研究中心</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">2016</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年的研究报告指出，未来，二十国集团应积极推进政策落实，并在创新增长、金融治理、推动就业、共同反腐、消除极端贫困等方面进一步协商，采取更加创新平衡有效的政策。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　商务部研究院国际市场研究部副主任白明也对《经济参考报》记者表示，</span>G20<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">正在从危机应对平台转向寻求世界经济长效治理机制，从“创新”位列此次峰会主题首位也可以看出，世界经济要寻求可持续的发展，那么结构性改革、创新发展这些就更具有重要意义。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\">　　“创新是企业发展的根本动力之一。只有创新才能实现技术进步、产品升级，从而更好地满足社会需求，在促进企业发展的同时，更好地推动经济发展和社会进步。”孙丕恕也从企业角度谈了他对创新主题的理解。</span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　在他看来，新一代信息技术等引领的第四次工业革命必将对旧的经济模式进行颠覆和重塑，以云计算、大数据、物联网、人工智能等为代表的新经济正在茁壮成长，并通过大数据与传统产业融合创新，引领人类社会由工业经济时代进入数据经济时代。在数据经济时代，数据将成为未来最有价值的资源，大数据的应用将推动跨产业的融合创新和传统产业创新升级，催生众多新型业态，推动创新、创业，从而激发新活力，激活全球经济发展。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\">　　“对科技创新而言，加强基础研究，增强微观主体的创新能力，完善国家创新体系的结构、提升其绩效是关键。”梁国勇说，而制度创新则与国家治理体系的完善和治理能力的提升密切相关，涉及到政治、经济、社会等各个领域。在各类政策工具中，货币政策和财政政策之外，创新政策、科技政策、产业政策、中小企业发展政策等的作用在寻求增长新动力方面的作用尤其值得关注。</span></p><p><br/></p>','G20峰会“中国方案”全球瞩目','　　“作为参会企业家，非常期待这次峰会能够在推进全球经济互联互通、融合发展等方面取得更多进展。”浪潮集团董事长孙丕恕正在为即将开幕的二十国工商界活动(B20)会议做着最后的准备，他对记者说，他将全程出席B20相关活动，非常关注大会创新全球经济增长方式等议题。','1','1','2017-03-11 21:44:12','','0','','','0','{\"thumb\":\"\"}','0','0','0','0','','');INSERT INTO ts_posts ( `id`, `post_author`, `post_keywords`, `post_source`, `post_date`, `post_content`, `post_title`, `post_excerpt`, `post_status`, `comment_status`, `post_modified`, `post_content_filtered`, `post_parent`, `post_type`, `post_mime_type`, `comment_count`, `smeta`, `post_hits`, `post_like`, `istop`, `recommended`, `page_tpl`, `page_tpls` ) VALUES  ('287','1','厦门自贸区航空煤油进口量实现三连涨','','2017-03-11 21:47:47','<p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　据厦门检验检疫局统计</span>,1-8<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月厦门口岸进口航空煤油达</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">19</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">批</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">,7.5</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">万吨</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">,3132.7</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">万美元</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">,</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">批次与重量同比去年分别增长</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">5.6%,5.3%,</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">已连续三年呈现上涨态势。值得关注的是</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">,</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">货值同比下滑</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">30.0%</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">。进口航空煤油单价由去年的每吨</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">623.2</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">下降到每吨</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">415.5</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">美元。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　据介绍</span>,<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">厦门口岸航空煤油进口货值的下滑系受国际石油价格持续走低影响</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">,</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">而进口量持续上涨与厦门航空港国际航线的平稳航行及新航线的陆续开展不无关系。进口航空煤油属于危险化学品中的三类易燃液体</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">,</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">厦门东渡检验检疫局一直以来对此类商品实行严密监管模式</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">,</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">双人持证上岗</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">,</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">批批现场检验并抽样送检</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">,</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">对涉及安全卫生品质项目进行检测。为保证其快速通检</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">,</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">厦门东渡局对进口航空煤油实现</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">24</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">小时电话预约</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">,</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">随到随验</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">,</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">为进口航空煤油保驾护航。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　相信在目前国际石油价格</span>“没有最低、只有更低”的持续下滑推动下<span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">,</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">借力快速通检的监管模式</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">,</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">厦门口岸航空煤油进口量还将处于上升通道。</span></span></p><p><br/></p>','厦门自贸区航空煤油进口量实现三连涨','　　据厦门检验检疫局统计,1-8月厦门口岸进口航空煤油达19批,7.5万吨,3132.7万美元,批次与重量同比去年分别增长5.6%,5.3%,已连续三年呈现上涨态势。值得关注的是,货值同比下滑30.0%。进口航空煤油单价由去年的每吨623.2下降到每吨415.5美元。','1','1','2017-03-11 21:46:59','','0','','','0','{\"thumb\":\"\"}','0','0','0','0','','');INSERT INTO ts_posts ( `id`, `post_author`, `post_keywords`, `post_source`, `post_date`, `post_content`, `post_title`, `post_excerpt`, `post_status`, `comment_status`, `post_modified`, `post_content_filtered`, `post_parent`, `post_type`, `post_mime_type`, `comment_count`, `smeta`, `post_hits`, `post_like`, `istop`, `recommended`, `page_tpl`, `page_tpls` ) VALUES  ('288','1','央企公司制改制明年底完成 ','','2017-03-11 21:49:36','<p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\">　　</span><span style=\";font-family:楷体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:楷体\">央企公司制改制明年底完成</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:楷体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:楷体\">　　专家称，整体上市是推进国企股份制改革重要方向</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　记者从权威人士处获悉，国资委划定公司制改制时间表，并积极推动企业改制上市、兼并重组、项目投资等方面积极引入民间资本和战略投资者，全面推进国有企业公司制股份制改革，中央企业要在</span>2017<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年底完成公司制改制。与此同时，各地方国企也将积极推进所属全民所有制的改制工作，力争今明两年完成这项工作。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　值得注意的是，上述人士告诉记者，下一步的国企改革路径，在公有制多元化股权改革的同时，还要积极稳妥地推进混合所有制改革，着力解决</span>“国企不愿意混，民企不敢混，企业难以混”的问题，在内部治理机制上，通过混合所有制引入市场机制。“在股份制和公司制改革完成的基础上，还要进一步建立现代企业制度，进一步深化治理结构的改革，包括规范董事长、总经理的行权行为，真正解决董事会虚设的问题，依法落实董事会应有责任。”他表示。</span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　作为国企改革的重要组成部分，以推进股份制改革和整体上市为主导的混合所有制改革，无疑是本轮国企改革的重头戏。国务院曾下发《关于深化国有企业改革的指导意见》，其中对于国有企业整体上市给予了高度重视，强调着力推进国有企业整体上市。但是，必须看到，目前我国国有企业仍处在市场化改革的关键阶段，由于外需不足，内需预期不稳定，企业增长模式和经营方式还比较粗放等多重原因，不少地方监管企业经济效益出现明显下滑的现象。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\">　　“长期以来，改革的举措很多，深究起来，突破性的改革举措并不常见。”一位国企人士表示，实际上，不管是股份制改革，还是改制上市、兼并重组、项目投资，都须建立在基本问题厘清的基础上，才能行之有效地推动改革。</span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　中国企业研究院首席研究员李锦对《经济参考报》记者表示，国有企业改革面临两个问题：国有企业的治理问题，即做实董事会制度的迫切性；还有就是体制机制问题，即制度细节方面的厘清。下一步特别要关注的是，央企一级公司如何进行公司制股份制改制，一些具备条件的国有上市公司如何通过股权、现金、融资等方式实施跨区域的并购重组。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　记者日前从国资委了解到，目前国企改革的十项改革试点已经全面展开，包括董事会职权、市场化选聘、薪酬改革、投资运营公司、兼并重组、混合所有制改革、混合所有制企业员工持股、国有企业信息公开等十项内容，目前国有企业改革领导小组已经把这十项试点分工到有关部门，有关部门也正在按照分工研究方案。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　另一方面，地方国企改革已经进入全面加速期。上海、广东、山东、江西等多省市近期纷纷制定相关细化方案和试点计划，加速国企改革步伐，其中，在分类监管基础上，继续深化混合所有制改革、推进股份制改革和整体上市将成为下一步改革重点。以江西省公布的国企改革方案为例，其中明确五年基本完成公司制股份制改革，</span>70%<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">左右的国企发展成为混合所有制经济，同时加快推进国企特别是竞争性领域企业改制上市，</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">5</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年左右时间省属国有资本证券化率提高到</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">60%</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　一位央企人士表示，在推进混合所有制改革过程中，从国有企业集团层面来看，混改难度较大，推进国企混合所有制改革重点应放在一般竞争性领域国企的分、子公司，通过合理确定国有股比重、完善公司治理，理顺政企关系，遏制贪腐案件，提高市场化水平，优化管理体制机制，从而发挥非公资本的作用，推进整体上市。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\">　　“推进国有企业整体上市是国企股份制改革的重要方向，有利于解决国企体制机制弊端。”李锦表示，截至<span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">2014</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年底，央企主营业务资产整体上市的共有</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">35</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">家，通过整体上市可以优化股权结构，解决“一股独大”问题，有利于为混合所有制改革创造条件，有利于为保护中小投资人或中小股东合法权益提供制度性保障，有利于国有资本流动做强做优做大，有利于建立健全现代企业制度，有利于政企分开、政资分开、所有权与经营权分离。他还表示，目前国企改革仍存在很多问题，包括市场主体地位还没有真正确立，现代企业制度还不完善，经营效益不高，国有资产流失问题很多，监管体制有待完善等。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　此外，多位专家表示，在国企改革提速的同时，如何守住</span>“底线”成为包括中央和地方国有企业本轮改革成败的关键所在。对改革中可能出现的“灰色地带”加强监管，保证国企改革顺利进行，是实现本轮国企改革目标的“底线”。</span></p><p><br/></p>','央企公司制改制明年底完成 整体上市或是改革重要方向','　　记者从权威人士处获悉，国资委划定公司制改制时间表，并积极推动企业改制上市、兼并重组、项目投资等方面积极引入民间资本和战略投资者，全面推进国有企业公司制股份制改革，中央企业要在2017年底完成公司制改制。与此同时，各地方国企也将积极推进所属全民所有制的改制工作，力争今明两年完成这项工作。','1','1','2017-03-11 21:48:03','','0','','','0','{\"thumb\":\"\"}','0','0','0','0','','');INSERT INTO ts_posts ( `id`, `post_author`, `post_keywords`, `post_source`, `post_date`, `post_content`, `post_title`, `post_excerpt`, `post_status`, `comment_status`, `post_modified`, `post_content_filtered`, `post_parent`, `post_type`, `post_mime_type`, `comment_count`, `smeta`, `post_hits`, `post_like`, `istop`, `recommended`, `page_tpl`, `page_tpls` ) VALUES  ('289','1','纽约油价6日上涨','','2017-03-11 21:52:02','<p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　继美国劳动节假期休市一天后，纽约油价</span>6<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">日微涨。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\">　　5<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">日，俄罗斯和沙特阿拉伯发表联合声明，同意在油市方面进行合作。受该消息提振，伦敦布伦特油价盘中一度暴涨</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">6%</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　然而，沙特石油大臣</span>5<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">日表示，目前原油市场在稳定提升中，暂时没有必要冻结产能。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　分析人士表示，这一表态降低了市场对于产油国将于近期削减产能的预期，在</span>6<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">日使得布伦特油价回落。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　截至</span>6<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">日收盘时，纽约商品交易所</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">10</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月交货的轻质原油期货价格上涨</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">0.39</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">美元，收于每桶</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">44.83</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">美元，涨幅为</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">0.88%</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">。</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">11</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月交货的伦敦布伦特原油期货价格下跌</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">0.37</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">美元，收于每桶</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">47.26</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">美元，跌幅为</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">0.78%</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">。</span></span></p><p><br/></p>','纽约油价6日上涨 收于每桶44.83美元','　　继美国劳动节假期休市一天后，纽约油价6日微涨。','1','1','2017-03-11 21:51:14','','0','','','0','{\"thumb\":\"\"}','0','0','0','0','','');INSERT INTO ts_posts ( `id`, `post_author`, `post_keywords`, `post_source`, `post_date`, `post_content`, `post_title`, `post_excerpt`, `post_status`, `comment_status`, `post_modified`, `post_content_filtered`, `post_parent`, `post_type`, `post_mime_type`, `comment_count`, `smeta`, `post_hits`, `post_like`, `istop`, `recommended`, `page_tpl`, `page_tpls` ) VALUES  ('290','1','最坏时期或结束 ','','2017-03-11 21:54:27','<p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　截至北京时间</span>9<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">6</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">日晚</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">8</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">点，</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">WTI</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">原油十月期货涨</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">0.47%</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">，报</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">44.65</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">美元</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">/</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">桶，伦敦布伦特原油十一月期货跌</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">0.9%</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">，报</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">47.20</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">美元</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">/</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">桶。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　就在前一日，产油大国俄罗斯和沙特阿拉伯联手放出重磅消息，国际油价大幅波动。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　沙特和俄罗斯在</span>G20<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">峰会间隙发布联合声明，称已经签署一项协议，两国同意成立工作组，评估油市基本面并建议要采取的措施和行动，但称双方不会立即采取行动，未来可能会限制产量，以维持油市稳定。在宣布合作计划后，布伦特原油一度暴涨</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">6%</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">至</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">49.4</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">美元。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　不过，发布会与联合声明并未透露协议的具体内容，也没有披露恢复原油市场均衡的</span>“重大措施”的细节，沙特石油部长<span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">Al-Falih</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">在接受阿拉伯卫星电视台采访时更称，现在没有必要冻结原油产量。由此，市场预期落空，布油快速回落至</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">47</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">美元附近，此前大多数涨幅几乎全部抹去。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　消息过后油价的表现也体现了市场参与者对于这份联合声明比较失望，大部分人认为这是没有实质内容的</span>“空头支票”。</span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\">　　</span><strong><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;font-size: 14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">增产空间有限使得冻产协议可期</span></span></strong></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　但也有市场观察者认为不该完全否认这份联合声明的意义。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;“据<span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">BP</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">数据显示，俄罗斯与沙特石油产量分别占全球产量的</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">12.4%</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">和</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">13%</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">，总共占全球产量总数的</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">25.4%</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">，这两个国家若能联合行动稳定油价，将对全球石油市场有较大的影响。其他</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">OPEC</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">国家可能会表示迎合。”上海外国语大学中东研究所副研究员潜旭明对</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">21</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">世纪经济报道记者表示。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　在野村证券亚洲区石油和天然气主管关容乐看来，值得注意的是俄罗斯同意参加</span>OPEC<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">组织于月底在阿尔及利亚的非正式会议，“我相信届时俄罗斯将与其他产油国如委内瑞拉、伊拉克和伊朗一起，将讨论出更多的细节来冻产以稳定油价。不过在这之前到九月底之间，市场将等待更多的细节。”</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\">　　OPEC<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">组织将于</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">11</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月在维也纳召开正式会议。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\">　　“如果九月底的会议没有结果，那么<span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">11</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月份还有机会，我认为他们达成冻产协议的概率已经增加了，原因是他们没有什么可损失的，包括沙特、伊拉克、伊朗及俄罗斯在内，这些国家近期的产量已经达到了其近期的极限，如果你已经不能通过增产来抢占市场份额，那么你肯定会希望竞争对手能够冻结产量，所以他们有了更多的动机来达成冻产协议，背后的原因其实是已经没有增产空间了。”关容乐补充道。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　据国际能源署</span>(IEA)<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">八月份发布的月度石油市场报告显示，</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">OPEC</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">产量处于</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">8</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年高点，该组织成员国</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">7</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月份的总产量环比上涨</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">15</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">万桶</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">/</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">日达</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">3340</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">万桶</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">/</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">日，主要是由伊拉克、沙特阿拉伯及伊朗的增产引起的。而非欧佩克石油产量在</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">7</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月份反弹了</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">55</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">万桶</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">/</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">日，其中大部分来自加拿大，该国此前遭遇了大面积的野火导致部分原油停产，现已逐渐恢复。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　不过，报告还指出，非</span>OPEC<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">石油产量的减产幅度超过了</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">OPEC</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">的增产幅度，目前全球的总产量较去年同期减少了</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">21.5</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">万桶</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">/</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">日。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　据</span>BP<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">数据显示，美国、加拿大、墨西哥分别占全球产量的</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">13%</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">、</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">4.9%</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">、</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">2.9%(</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">总共占全球产量</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">20.8%)</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">，中国占到</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">4.9%</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\">　　“近期我们看到了供给端的大幅收紧，比如美国方面，油企更削减了资本支出，钻机数量也显著下降了，因此美国的产量在过去<span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">12</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">个月以来下跌了</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">10%</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">。中国方面，中石油等的产量也下跌了，过去</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">12</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">个月以来产量下降了</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">5%-10%</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">。这是因为中国的许多油田比如大庆油田，已经是三四十年的老油田了，目前的产量和以往比起来下降了不少。基于上述原因，中国原油产量降至了</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">5</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年来最低水平。”关容乐说。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\">　　</span><strong><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;font-size: 14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">供需将逐步平衡</span></span></strong></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　关容乐认为，油价最坏的时期已经结束，一方面需求正稳步上升，另一方面供给也在收紧，这意味着供需在未来两年会更趋平衡。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\">　　“近期全球石油的需求达到了历史峰值，今年增速<span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">1%</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">。不过因为过去几年的产量过剩导致全球累积了大量原油库存，使得今年的油价仍在低位徘徊。我认为基本面连同政治形势，未来油价的回升可期。”关容乐说。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　不过需要指出的是英国公投退欧对全球经济前景产生负面影响，进而影响全球的能源需求。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\">　　IEA8<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月发布的月度石油市场报告显示，因英国公投退欧对全球经济前景产生负面影响，</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">IEA</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">将</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">2017</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年的全球石油需求增长预期，由</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">2016</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年的</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">140</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">万桶</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">/</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">日下调至</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">120</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">万桶</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">/</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">日。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\">　　OPEC<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">组织内也存在伊朗这个变数。俄罗斯总统普京上周五在接受彭博社专访时表示，伊朗应该被允许增产。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\">　　“据<span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">BP</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">数据，伊朗的产量占到</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">4.2%</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">。伊朗之前被制裁很久，急需出口石油，换取国家经济发展的外汇及其他产品，伊朗目前的角色变成了全球原油供给额外的补充者。”潜旭明说。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　据路透社报道，伊朗曾表示，唯有其他石油出口国承认伊朗有权利全面重新获得自己的市场份额，伊朗才会配合冻产协商。伊朗国家石油公司</span>(NIOC)<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">的一位高级官员表示，伊朗准备好在几个月内将原油日产量增加至</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">400</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">万桶，具体将取决于市场需求。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　虽然年内是否能达成冻产协议还不是板上钉钉的事，不过石油市场供需将逐步恢复平衡。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\">　　IEA<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">此前发布的月度报告预计，石油市场供需将逐步恢复平衡。报告分析，精炼厂对于原油需求的上涨，将吸收海湾地区创纪录的原油产量，</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">2016</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">下半年基本无供应过剩，第三季库存将大幅减少。</span></span></p><p><br/></p>','最坏时期或结束 产油国冻产协议可期','　　截至北京时间9月6日晚8点，WTI原油十月期货涨0.47%，报44.65美元/桶，伦敦布伦特原油十一月期货跌0.9%，报47.20美元/桶。','1','1','2017-03-11 21:52:19','','0','','','0','{\"thumb\":\"\"}','1','0','0','0','','');INSERT INTO ts_posts ( `id`, `post_author`, `post_keywords`, `post_source`, `post_date`, `post_content`, `post_title`, `post_excerpt`, `post_status`, `comment_status`, `post_modified`, `post_content_filtered`, `post_parent`, `post_type`, `post_mime_type`, `comment_count`, `smeta`, `post_hits`, `post_like`, `istop`, `recommended`, `page_tpl`, `page_tpls` ) VALUES  ('291','1','北京福建甘肃三省市电改方案获批','','2017-03-11 21:56:01','<p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　记者</span>6<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">日从发改委获悉，日前，国家发展改革委、国家能源局批复同意福建省开展售电侧改革试点，同意北京市开展电力体制改革综合试点，以及同意甘肃省开展电力体制改革试点。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　在对福建省方案的批复中，复函要求，规范售电侧市场主体准入与退出机制，多途径培育售电侧市场竞争主体，健全电力市场化交易机制、加强信用体系建设与风险防范，加快构建有效竞争的市场结构和市场体系，并在试点基础上及时总结经验，尽快扩大改革覆盖面。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　在对甘肃省方案的批复中，复函强调，在专项试点方案基础上，结合实际完善配套措施、突出工作重点，加快组建相对独立的电力交易机构，统筹推进输配电价、电力市场建设、电力交易机制、发用电计划、配售电侧等改革任务落实，确保改革取得实质性突破。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　而在对北京市方案的批复中，复函提出，在综合试点和专项试点方案基础上，结合实际完善配套措施、突出工作重点，积极配合组建电网企业相对控股的京津冀电力交易机构，统筹推进输配电价、电力市场建设、电力交易机制、发用电计划、配售电侧等改革任务落实。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　值得注意的是，国家发改委副主任胡祖才在近日召开的加快推进输配电价改革座谈会议上表示，将力争今年底前核定这些试点的输配电价并向社会公布。同时将原定</span>2017<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年开展的</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">14</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">个省级电网输配电价改革提前到今年</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">9</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月份启动，计划于明年</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">1</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月底完成成本监审工作。</span></span></p><p><br/></p>','北京福建甘肃三省市电改方案获批','　　记者6日从发改委获悉，日前，国家发展改革委、国家能源局批复同意福建省开展售电侧改革试点，同意北京市开展电力体制改革综合试点，以及同意甘肃省开展电力体制改革试点。','1','1','2017-03-11 21:55:13','','0','','','0','{\"thumb\":\"\"}','0','0','0','0','','');INSERT INTO ts_posts ( `id`, `post_author`, `post_keywords`, `post_source`, `post_date`, `post_content`, `post_title`, `post_excerpt`, `post_status`, `comment_status`, `post_modified`, `post_content_filtered`, `post_parent`, `post_type`, `post_mime_type`, `comment_count`, `smeta`, `post_hits`, `post_like`, `istop`, `recommended`, `page_tpl`, `page_tpls` ) VALUES  ('292','1','全国成品油价格指数继续上行','','2017-03-11 21:57:06','<p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　依据新华</span>(<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">大庆</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">)</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">国际石油资讯中心发布的报告，截至</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">9</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">2</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">日，全国成品油价格指数为</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">598.71</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">，涨幅</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">1.99%</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">，全国成品油价格指数继续上行。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　全国成品油价格指数运行结果表明，上周</span>93#<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">汽油平均价格报收于</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">5934</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">元</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">/</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">吨，较前一报告周期上涨</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">186</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">元</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">/</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">吨</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">(</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">折合</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">0.14</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">元</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">/</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">升</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">)</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">；</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">0#</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">柴油平均价格报收于</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">5078</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">元</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">/</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">吨，较前一报告周期上涨</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">66</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">元</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">/</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">吨</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">(</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">折合</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">0.06</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">元</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">/</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">升</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">)</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">。综合来看，全国汽油平均价格上涨，带动全国成品油价格指数继续上行。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　新华</span>(<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">大庆</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">)</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">国际石油资讯中心分析师李振国认为，近期因美国原油库存增幅超预期，国际油价继续下行。国内成品油市场价格上调落实，因油品需求欠佳，交投清淡。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　李振国分析认为，因前期国际油价涨幅较大，国内成品油价格上调落实，主营顺势推涨价格。国内需求恢复缓慢，终端用户采购积极性较弱，业者持观望态度，多按需购进，市场交投清淡。国际市场方面，美国能源信息署</span>(EIA)<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">近日公布的数据显示，上周美国原油库存增加</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">227.6</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">万桶，库存增幅大于预期，原油库存连续两周增加，该消息利空国际油价，预计短期内国际油价将维持震荡格局。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\">&nbsp;</span></p><p><br/></p>','全国成品油价格指数继续上行','　　依据新华(大庆)国际石油资讯中心发布的报告，截至9月2日，全国成品油价格指数为598.71，涨幅1.99%，全国成品油价格指数继续上行。','1','1','2017-03-11 21:56:24','','0','','','0','{\"thumb\":\"\"}','0','0','0','0','','');INSERT INTO ts_posts ( `id`, `post_author`, `post_keywords`, `post_source`, `post_date`, `post_content`, `post_title`, `post_excerpt`, `post_status`, `comment_status`, `post_modified`, `post_content_filtered`, `post_parent`, `post_type`, `post_mime_type`, `comment_count`, `smeta`, `post_hits`, `post_like`, `istop`, `recommended`, `page_tpl`, `page_tpls` ) VALUES  ('293','1','国际油价7日上涨 ','','2017-03-11 21:58:47','<p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\">　 &nbsp;<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">国际油价</span>7<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">日上涨。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　俄罗斯和沙特阿拉伯</span>5<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">日发表联合声明，同意在油市方面进行合作。受该消息提振，伦敦布伦特油价盘中一度暴涨</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">6%</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　石油输出国组织</span>(<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">欧佩克</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">)</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">成员国将于</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">9</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月底在阿尔及利亚召开非正式会议，或将采取减产等措施维持国际油价的稳定。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　然而，沙特石油部长</span>5<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">日表示，目前原油市场在稳定提升中，暂时没有必要冻结产能。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　分析人士表示，投资者正在权衡市场供应过量的现状和产油国达成减产协议的可能性，国际油价</span>7<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">日盘中波动剧烈。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　截至当日收盘时，纽约商品交易所</span>10<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月交货的轻质原油期货价格上涨</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">0.67</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">美元，收于每桶</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">45.50</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">美元，涨幅为</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">1.49%</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">。</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">11</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月交货的伦敦布伦特原油期货价格上涨</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">0.72</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">美元，收于每桶</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">47.98</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">美元，涨幅为</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">1.52%</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">。</span></span></p><p><br/></p>','国际油价7日上涨 纽市收报45.50美元','　  国际油价7日上涨。','1','1','2017-03-11 21:58:04','','0','','','0','{\"thumb\":\"\"}','0','0','0','0','','');INSERT INTO ts_posts ( `id`, `post_author`, `post_keywords`, `post_source`, `post_date`, `post_content`, `post_title`, `post_excerpt`, `post_status`, `comment_status`, `post_modified`, `post_content_filtered`, `post_parent`, `post_type`, `post_mime_type`, `comment_count`, `smeta`, `post_hits`, `post_like`, `istop`, `recommended`, `page_tpl`, `page_tpls` ) VALUES  ('294','1','今晚24时油价调价窗口开启 ','','2017-03-11 21:59:54','<p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　根据</span>“十个工作日”原则，新一轮成品油调价窗口将于今天（<span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">9</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">18</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">日）</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">24</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">时打开。本周期内，国际原油市场利好利空消息交织，价格急涨急跌。在美元投资反弹消息出现后，原油再次走低。市场机构认为，新一轮调价窗口国内油价将迎来节后首次下调，即今年年内的第四次降价。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　中宇资讯监测的数据显示，截至本周期内第</span>9<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">个工作日，原油变化率为</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">-4.41%</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">，估价</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">45.897</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">美元</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">/</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">桶，较基准价跌</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">2.117</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">美元</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">/</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">桶。中宇资讯预计，新一轮成品油零售限价下调</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">115</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">元</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">/</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">吨。隆众资讯油品分析师李彦认为，目前来看，本轮成品油调价可能是今年以来的最小降幅。预计</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">9</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">18</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">日</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">24</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">时调价窗口开启时，国内汽、柴油降幅分别为每吨</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">120</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">元和</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">115</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">元。折合升价，</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">92</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">号汽油每升下调</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">0.09</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">元、</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">0</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">号柴油每升下调</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">0.1</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">元。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　中宇资讯分析师高承莎表示，本轮计价周期内，投资者对产油国会议结果持乐观预期助升油价，但之后美国钻井数量上升、美元走势反弹等消息出现后，原油再次回头走低，由此在市场利好利空消息的交替主导下，国际原油急涨急跌，出现了极大的幅度波动。资本方面，投资者对于产油国会议结果预期的乐观心态近日也开始摇摆，加之美联储议息会议消息的多变，导致美元出现涨跌拉锯走势。由此预计，短期内国际原油或将延续宽幅震荡，全国汽柴油价格或将出现稳中窄幅下跌趋势。</span></span></p><p><br/></p>','今晚24时油价调价窗口开启 将迎今年第4次下调','　　根据“十个工作日”原则，新一轮成品油调价窗口将于今天（9月18日）24时打开。本周期内，国际原油市场利好利空消息交织，价格急涨急跌。在美元投资反弹消息出现后，原油再次走低。市场机构认为，新一轮调价窗口国内油价将迎来节后首次下调，即今年年内的第四次降价。','1','1','2017-03-11 21:59:03','','0','','','0','{\"thumb\":\"\"}','1','0','0','0','','');INSERT INTO ts_posts ( `id`, `post_author`, `post_keywords`, `post_source`, `post_date`, `post_content`, `post_title`, `post_excerpt`, `post_status`, `comment_status`, `post_modified`, `post_content_filtered`, `post_parent`, `post_type`, `post_mime_type`, `comment_count`, `smeta`, `post_hits`, `post_like`, `istop`, `recommended`, `page_tpl`, `page_tpls` ) VALUES  ('295','1','全球最大的石油公司之一埃克森美孚遭调查','','2017-03-11 22:01:22','<p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　纽约总检察长</span>EricSchneiderman<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">正在就会计问题，对全球最大的石油公司之一——埃克森美孚展开调查。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　油价下跌时，这家石油巨无霸并没有按照会计准则进行资产计提。这一做法，与包括中国石油企业在内的其他油气公司有所不同。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　自</span>2014<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年以来，全球原油价格大跌了</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">60%</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">，迫使大量的石油公司计提了设备、厂房及物业。如果不把它们做计提减值的话，就会误导公众，以为该企业的财务状况仍然是健康的。然而埃克森美孚就没有对此做任何的计提准备。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　中石油（</span>601857.SH<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">，</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">00857.HK</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">，</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">PTR.NYSE</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">）就“资产计提”是这样解释的：由于事件的发生或环境的变化，使资产账面价值可能无法回收时，需对物业、厂房及机器设备，包括油气资产进行减值测试。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　一般情况下，石油企业会对坏账、与油价下跌而产生的不良资产、商誉进行计提。在中石油的</span>2015<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年年报中，《第一财经日报》记者看到，该公司当年的折旧、折耗及摊销为</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">2028.75</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">亿元，比</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">2014</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年增加了</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">14.3%</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">。其解释，主要是据会计准则计提资产减值准备</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">250.22</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">亿元，同口径同比增长了</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">2.3%</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　中石油还表示，</span>2015<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年公司的海外业务实际营业额为</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">5402.39</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">亿元，占集团总营业额的</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">31.3%</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">，税前亏损高达</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">83.49</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">亿元，主要是由于部分海外附属公司计提的油气资产减值准备所致。全年，中石油的油气资产计提影响损益的减值准备金额为</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">198.93</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">亿元，这些资产的减值主要是生产运营成本较高和低油价共同导致的，这些资产的账面价值已减计至可收回金额。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　有会计专家也认为，埃克森美孚未计提是否需要受到指责，现在下结论为时过早。会计规则在这方面给予了企业一定的选择。由于计提方法的不同，是否做减值计提、计提的结果等都差异很大。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\">　　“这是一个比较主观的领域”，一位会计博主<span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">TomSelling</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">说，“每个人会基于公司的成本和油井的年限，得出不同的计提结论。”</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　中石油曾对外表示，确定资产是否减值及减值金额的大小，包含管理层的估计和判断，比如未来原油价格、炼油产品和化工产品的价格、生产情况等。而减值准备的测试和计算是考虑目前的经济形势，基于与集团的经营计划一致的假设而做出。某些假设没有变化或发生对其有利的变化，可能会使集团免于对这些资产计提减值，对某些假设不利的变化可能导致集团对资产计提减值。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　埃克森美孚公司的发言人称，公司遵循了美国证券交易委员会和财务会计准则委员会的规定。</span>“从历史上看，在大宗商品价格暴跌时，埃克森美孚都不会进行大额计提。”爱德华·琼斯公司的石油分析师说道。</span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　路易斯安那州立大学一位名誉教授</span>LarryCrumbley<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">则表示，“公司一般不愿意计提。因为一旦减少收入及资产负债表的资产，你就很难再转回。”</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　俄克拉何马大学的名誉教授</span>TerryCrain<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">则对媒体表示，在石油价格暂时下降时，企业不需要进行计提，这是会计准则规定的。但是该准则也没有明确过“暂时下跌”的时间范围是多少，“是</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">1</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">个月、</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">2</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">个月还是半年</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">?</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">这不好说，这是一个灰色地带。”</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　值得留意的是，雪佛龙公司在今年第二季度对公司部分业务进行了</span>28<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">亿美元的计提。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\">　　Carter<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">，</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">Ledyard&amp;Milburn</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">公司的律师</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">RobertMcTamaney</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">表示，如果公司判断短期内油价将很快上升，那么减值就是一种错误的行为。他也表示，埃克森美孚是美国历史最悠久的石油生产商，它所拥有的钻机及其他设备成本都较低，因此没有必要计提。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　作为国内最大的石油设备企业之一，中海油服（</span>601808.SH<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">，</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">02883.HK</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">）</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">8</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">29</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">日的公告显示，企业净利润为</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">-84.03</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">亿元。净利润的下降与计提有着密切的关系。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　受市场形势影响，中海油服的部分海外钻井平台可收回金额低于资产的账面价值，故计提固定资产减值准备约</span>36.88<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">亿元。而</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">2008</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年，中海油服也收购了</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">AwilcoOffshoreAS</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">，形成了商誉。由于全球油田服务市场持续恶化、近期油价继续低位运行，全球石油勘探和生产领域的资本支出也在持续减少，厂房及机器的服务价格、平台使用率下降，因此据减值评估结果，中海油服同样计提了上述商誉减值损失约</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">34.55</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">亿元，两项合计</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">71.43</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">亿元。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　再看埃克森美孚公司，它并不是首例在美国纽约总检察长办公室监督下进行会计核算的公司。前美国国际集团首席执行官也曾就</span>AIG<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">的会计实务与纽约检方进行过讨论。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　此外，</span>2013<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年时，尽管埃克森美孚的天然气业务一落千丈也“没有赚钱”，但公司也坚持不计提，美国证监交易委员会和分析师们都对此提出过质疑。</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">2010</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年，埃克森美孚曾收购天然气开采商</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">XTO</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">能源公司并变身为美国最大的天然气生产商，但谁曾料想天然气价格出现了下滑，且在</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">2012</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年时滑落到了十年低点。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　今年二季度，埃克森美孚的净利为</span>17<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">亿美元，合每股盈利</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">41</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">美分，低于去年同期的</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">41.9</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">亿美元。该季度公司营收也锐减了</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">22%</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">至</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">576.9</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">亿美元。与石油价格紧密相关的是“油气勘探与生产”这个板块，企业这部分业务的营收下降</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">17</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">亿美元至</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">2.94</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">亿美元。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\">&nbsp;</span></p><p><br/></p>','全球最大的石油公司之一埃克森美孚遭调查','　　纽约总检察长EricSchneiderman正在就会计问题，对全球最大的石油公司之一——埃克森美孚展开调查。','1','1','2017-03-11 22:00:05','','0','','','0','{\"thumb\":\"\"}','1','0','0','0','','');INSERT INTO ts_posts ( `id`, `post_author`, `post_keywords`, `post_source`, `post_date`, `post_content`, `post_title`, `post_excerpt`, `post_status`, `comment_status`, `post_modified`, `post_content_filtered`, `post_parent`, `post_type`, `post_mime_type`, `comment_count`, `smeta`, `post_hits`, `post_like`, `istop`, `recommended`, `page_tpl`, `page_tpls` ) VALUES  ('296','1','油价终结“二连涨” ','','2017-03-11 22:02:17','<p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　国家发改委今日下午宣布下调成品油价格，福建省物价局同步调整当地汽、柴油价格。明日零时起，福建省汽柴油每升降</span>0.13<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">元，</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">92</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">号汽油最高零售价重回“</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">5</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">元时代”，每升</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">5.9</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">元。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　根据福建省物价局的通知，明日零时起，福建省</span>92<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">号汽油最高零售价从</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">8030</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">元</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">/</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">吨调整为</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">7865</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">元</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">/</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">吨；</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">95</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">号汽油最高零售价从</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">8484</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">元</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">/</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">吨调整为</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">8310</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">元</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">/</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">吨；车用</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">0</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">号柴油最高零售价从</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">6590</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">元</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">/</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">吨调整为</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">6440</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">元</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">/</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">吨。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　调整后，</span>92<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">号汽油、</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">95</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">号汽油、车用</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">0</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">号柴油最高零售价依次为</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">5.9</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">元</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">/</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">升、</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">6.31</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">元</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">/</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">升、</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">5.51</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">元</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">/</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">升，均比之前降</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">0.13</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">元</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">/</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">升。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\">&nbsp;&nbsp;<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　此次调整终结了此前的</span>“二连涨”，是国内油价年内的第四次下调。按一般家用汽车油箱<span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">50</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">升容量计算，加满一箱</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">92</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">号汽油将少花</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">6.5</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">元钱。</span></span></p><p><br/></p>','油价终结“二连涨” 闽92号汽油将至每升5.9元','　　国家发改委今日下午宣布下调成品油价格，福建省物价局同步调整当地汽、柴油价格。明日零时起，福建省汽柴油每升降0.13元，92号汽油最高零售价重回“5元时代”，每升5.9元。','1','1','2017-03-11 22:01:35','','0','','','0','{\"thumb\":\"\"}','0','0','0','0','','');INSERT INTO ts_posts ( `id`, `post_author`, `post_keywords`, `post_source`, `post_date`, `post_content`, `post_title`, `post_excerpt`, `post_status`, `comment_status`, `post_modified`, `post_content_filtered`, `post_parent`, `post_type`, `post_mime_type`, `comment_count`, `smeta`, `post_hits`, `post_like`, `istop`, `recommended`, `page_tpl`, `page_tpls` ) VALUES  ('297','1','石油市场维稳协议或将持续一年','','2017-03-11 22:03:26','<p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\">　　OPEC<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">秘书长</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">Mohammed Barkindo</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">于本周二</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">(9</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">20</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">日</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">)</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">表示，全球石油大国旨在支撑油价的协议一经达成，或将持续一年时间。该预期比其他官方给出的时间预期有所延长。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\">　　OPEC<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">成员国及非成员国正在就稳定石油市场进行谈判，最终协议将至少包含冻产协议。不过包括时间线以及基准线等具体细节还未上桌讨论。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　俄罗斯及</span>OPEC<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">成员国将于</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">9</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">28</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">日在阿尔及利亚展开非正式会晤。阿尔及利亚能源部长在周一</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">(9</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">19</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">日</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">)</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">表示，任何冻产协议都能够在至少六个月内维持市场稳定。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　曾在今年</span>4<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月份阻碍了冻产协议达成的伊朗在本次谈判中将不再棘手。伊朗方面表示，其产量已经与制裁前水平非常接近。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　对于本次位于阿尔及利亚的谈判，</span>OPEC<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">内部已经传来乐观的声音。尽管对于是否能够在本次会议上完成谈判的所有细节表示了顾虑，不过相关方面对于各方达成冻产协议的意愿表示了肯定。</span></span></p><p><br/></p>','OPEC主席：石油市场维稳协议或将持续一年','　　OPEC秘书长Mohammed Barkindo于本周二(9月20日)表示，全球石油大国旨在支撑油价的协议一经达成，或将持续一年时间。该预期比其他官方给出的时间预期有所延长。','1','1','2017-03-11 22:02:31','','0','','','0','{\"thumb\":\"\"}','0','0','0','0','','');INSERT INTO ts_posts ( `id`, `post_author`, `post_keywords`, `post_source`, `post_date`, `post_content`, `post_title`, `post_excerpt`, `post_status`, `comment_status`, `post_modified`, `post_content_filtered`, `post_parent`, `post_type`, `post_mime_type`, `comment_count`, `smeta`, `post_hits`, `post_like`, `istop`, `recommended`, `page_tpl`, `page_tpls` ) VALUES  ('298','1','OPEC有望冻产API库存锐减','','2017-03-11 22:05:28','<p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　周二</span>(9<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">20</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">日</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">)</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">，美国纽约商品期货交易所最新原油近月合约的</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">11</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">WTI</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">原油期货价格则收盘上涨</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">0.19</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">美元，涨幅</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">0.4%</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">，收报</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">44.05</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">美元</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">/</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">桶。周二美国</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">WTI</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">原油和布伦特涨跌不一，布伦特原油小幅收低而美油小幅收涨，但在随后的电子盘交易中均录得上涨。因有消息称俄罗斯赞同制定为期一年的稳定油市协议，且</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">OPEC</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">“非正式石油会议”或将变为“正式石油会议”，这均表明</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">OPEC</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">采取限产行动的可能性进一步提升。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　在原油期货收盘后的电子盘交易中，美国</span>API<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">原油库存再次意外锐减</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">749.7</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">万桶的消息则令油价短线飙升。</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">11</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">ICE</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">布伦特原油期货价格收盘下跌</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">0.07</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">美元，涨幅不足</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">0.2%</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">，收报</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">45.88</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">美元</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">/</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">桶。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　周二下午，俄罗斯官员向国际文传电讯社表示，俄罗斯赞同与</span>OPEC<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">达成为期一年的稳定油市协议。俄罗斯方面的这一消息使得市场对下周</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">OPEC</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">石油会议预期得到一定程度逆转，这无疑暗示</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">OPEC</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">和俄罗斯最终通过控制石油产出来维稳油市可能性有所提升。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　但是，</span>ClipperData<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">大宗商品研究主管</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">Matt Smith</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">却对此持有怀疑态度， </span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">Smith</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">表示，俄罗斯同意限产是荒谬的，因俄罗斯能源部最近才宣布其</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">9</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月石油输出将刷新前苏联时期所创下的</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">1100</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">万桶</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">/</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">日的纪录高位。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　与此同时，据新闻媒体报道，尼日利亚、利比亚以及委内瑞拉等</span>OPEC<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">成员国近期均在不断增加石油产出。</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">Smith</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">强调，如果</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">OPEC</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">在阿尔及利亚真正能够就产量问题达成一致，或许将暗示双方将允许伊朗、尼日利亚、利比亚以及委内瑞拉增加石油产量，这也就意味着国际原油供应将进一步增加。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　另尼日利亚能源部长</span>Noureddine Bouterfa<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">表示，</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">OPEC</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">下周</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">9</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">28</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">日的“非正式石油会议”可能将会变为“正式石油会议”。</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">Bouterfa</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">指出，如果每一个产油国均出席阿尔及利亚会议，那么这次会议将可能变为“正式会议”。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　据路透援引消息人士称，因与阿联酋国有石油公司的谈判陷入僵局，印度打算转为购买</span>600<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">万桶伊朗原油用于战略储备；印度是全球第三大石油进口国，这次购买若能成功势必将加大伊朗在抢占市场份额方面的动力，令其出口更接近制裁前水平，从而加大其参与冻产协议的可能性。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　石油输出国组织</span>(OPEC)<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">秘书长</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">Mohammed Barkindo</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">在接受意大利《共和报》采访时说，</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">9</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">26-28</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">日的阿尔及尔会议能够达成非正式供应协议，其对此抱有信心。</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">Barkindo</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">计划在阿尔及尔会议后召集正式会议批准所作决定，称所有成员国都同意降低库存水平，并指出，伊朗总统卢哈尼已经郑重表示会予以配合。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　此外，美国汽油期货扩大跌幅，盘中一度急跌</span>5%<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">，之前美国最大汽车燃料油承运商</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">Colonial Pipeline</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">称现预计</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">LINE 1</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">输油管道将于周三全面恢复营运。此前，美国最大汽车燃料油承运商</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">Colonial Pipeline</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">因泄露于</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">9</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">9</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">日关闭，其日输送量为</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">120</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">万桶汽油。汽油价格盘中的暴跌对油价构成下行压力。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　北京时间周三</span>(9<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">21</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">日</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">)</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">凌晨</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">4:30</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">，在原油期货电子盘交易中，美国石油协会</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">(API)</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">公布的数据显示，截至</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">9</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">16</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">日当周，美国</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">API</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">原油库存再次意外锐减</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">749.7</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">万桶，预期增加</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">225</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">万桶。库欣原油库存减少增加</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">40.7</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">万桶，与此同时，</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">API</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">汽油库存意外大减</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">245.3</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">万桶。美国</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">WTI</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">原油期货价格应声短线跳涨。</span></span></p><p><br/></p>','OPEC有望冻产API库存锐减 油价涨势可期','　　周二(9月20日)，美国纽约商品期货交易所最新原油近月合约的11月WTI原油期货价格则收盘上涨0.19美元，涨幅0.4%，收报44.05美元/桶。周二美国WTI原油和布伦特涨跌不一，布伦特原油小幅收低而美油小幅收涨，但在随后的电子盘交易中均录得上涨','1','1','2017-03-11 22:04:02','','0','','','0','{\"thumb\":\"\"}','1','0','0','0','','');INSERT INTO ts_posts ( `id`, `post_author`, `post_keywords`, `post_source`, `post_date`, `post_content`, `post_title`, `post_excerpt`, `post_status`, `comment_status`, `post_modified`, `post_content_filtered`, `post_parent`, `post_type`, `post_mime_type`, `comment_count`, `smeta`, `post_hits`, `post_like`, `istop`, `recommended`, `page_tpl`, `page_tpls` ) VALUES  ('299','1','宝钢武钢合并迈出第一步','','2017-03-11 22:06:23','<p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　两家中国钢铁集团向着各方期待已久的合并迈出第一步，将缔造全球第二大钢铁制造商，中国政府希望此举将引发并购浪潮，并提高这个臃肿行业的效率。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　然而，分析师表示，宝钢股份</span>(Baoshan Iron and Steel)<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">和武钢股份</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">(Wuhan Iron &amp; Steel)</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">之间的协议只是整合中国分散的钢铁行业过程的一部分，这个过程很可能是漫长且复杂的。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　周二，中国第二大钢铁制造商宝钢集团</span>(Baosteel Group)<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">的上市子公司宝钢股份表示，将发行新股，以吸收合并中国第五大钢铁制造商（按产量计算）武汉钢铁集团</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">(Wuhan Iron &amp; Steel Group)</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">的上市子公司。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　根据两家公司递交的监管申报文件，宝钢上市子公司吸收合并武钢上市公司是两家母公司合并的预备步骤，并将有待中国监管部门审批。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　北京梅塔科咨询公司</span>(Beijing Metal Consulting)<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">分析师许中波表示，此次合并不仅意味着这一“测试案例”的成功。他表示：“最重要的是钢铁生产迅速合并。”</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　他补充称：</span>“这两个集团有很多小企业，需要很长时间才能确定哪些企业将被出售或关闭，这可能是一个代价高昂的过程。”</span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　宝武钢铁集团（这是中国媒体给合并后实体起的名字）的缔造被视为北京方面计划的起点，目的是促使僵尸企业破产，提高中国工业效率。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　中国钢铁业的产能过剩导致全球钢铁行业去年陷入危机，当时不断激增的中国廉价钢铁出口拖低了全球价格。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　据受尊敬的财经杂志《财新》</span>(Caixin)<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">报道，武钢与宝钢整体合并为一个实体的计划已得到国资委</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">(SASAC)</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">批准。合并后实体的总资产将达到</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">7000</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">亿元人民币（合</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">1049</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">亿美元），年产能为</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">6000</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">万吨。</span></span></p><p><br/></p>','宝钢武钢合并迈出第一步','　　两家中国钢铁集团向着各方期待已久的合并迈出第一步，将缔造全球第二大钢铁制造商，中国政府希望此举将引发并购浪潮，并提高这个臃肿行业的效率。','1','1','2017-03-11 22:05:47','','0','','','0','{\"thumb\":\"\"}','0','0','0','0','','');INSERT INTO ts_posts ( `id`, `post_author`, `post_keywords`, `post_source`, `post_date`, `post_content`, `post_title`, `post_excerpt`, `post_status`, `comment_status`, `post_modified`, `post_content_filtered`, `post_parent`, `post_type`, `post_mime_type`, `comment_count`, `smeta`, `post_hits`, `post_like`, `istop`, `recommended`, `page_tpl`, `page_tpls` ) VALUES  ('300','1','将成为中国第一世界第二大钢铁厂','','2017-03-11 22:07:38','<p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><strong><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;font-size: 14px\">1<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">股武钢股份换取</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">0.56</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">股宝钢股份</span></span></strong></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><strong><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;font-size: 14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">将成为中国第一世界第二大钢铁厂</span></span></strong></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　我国钢铁行业两大巨头宝钢集团和武钢集团，今天正式宣布合为一家。其旗下各自的核心主业上市公司</span>——宝钢股份和武钢股份，则将通过吸收合并的方式实现重组，根据换股价格测算，相当于每<span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">1</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">股武钢股份的股份可以换取</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">0.56</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">股宝钢股份的股份。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　据披露，国务院国资委已批准宝钢集团与武钢集团进行联合重组，宝钢集团将更名为</span>“中国宝武钢铁集团有限公司”；武钢集团股权将无偿划转至中国宝武集团，成为其全资子公司。</span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　作为两家集团旗下各自的上市平台，宝钢股份将通过向武钢股份全体换股股东发行</span>A<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">股股票，换股吸收合并武钢股份。换股价格主要参考两公司董事会决议公告日前</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">20</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">个交易日股票交易均价，最终确定宝钢股份的换股价格为</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">4.60</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">元每股，武钢股份的换股价格为</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">2.58</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">元每股，相当于每</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">1</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">股武钢股份的股份可以换取</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">0.56</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">股宝钢股份的股份。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　吸并方案同时为异议股东提供了行使现金选择权的通道，现金选择权的价格与换股价格相同，即宝钢股份为</span>4.60<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">元每股，武钢股份为</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">2.58</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">元每股，均低于两家上市公司各自停牌前的股价，更低于其每股净资产。有券商人士预期，投资者最终行使现金选择权的可能性不大。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　在不考虑有股东行使现金选择权的条件下进行测算，换股结束后，新的宝武集团将持有存续公司</span>65.58%<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">的股份。此前被划转了部分宝钢股份或武钢股份的战略股东如中石油集团等，其在合并后上市公司中的持股比例都不到</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">5%</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">。存续主体将承担起“成为全球最具竞争力的钢铁企业，成为最具投资价值的上市公司”的重任。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　据公开资料，武钢集团是新中国成立后兴建的第一个特大型钢铁联合企业，于</span>1955<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年开始建设，是钢铁行业的“共和国长子”；宝钢集团于</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">1978</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">12</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月动工，是国家改革开放的典型企业代表，目前已发展成为我国最具竞争力的钢铁企业，在</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">2016</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年世界企业</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">500</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">强中排名第</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">275</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">位。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\">　　“合则强，孤则弱。两大钢企集团的合并，既是市场形势的需要，符合钢铁行业 去产能 、产业转型升级的要求，也是进一步深化国企改革的需要，对优化产业结构、提高产业集中度、推动资源向优势企业集中、提升企业竞争力等，都具有极其重要的意义。”有钢铁行业分析师分析认为。</span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　数据显示，</span>2015<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年度我国钢铁行业粗钢产量</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">8.04</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">亿吨，占全球钢铁行业粗钢产量的</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">49.5%</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">，产能利用率仅为</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">67%</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">，全行业销售利润率只有</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">0.7%</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">，创历史新低。同时，中国钢铁行业前十名的市场占有率（</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">CR10</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">）回落至</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">34.2%</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">，产业集中度降至近十年来的最低点。具体到此次整合的主体，宝钢股份在</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">2015</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年盈利</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">10.85</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">亿元，武钢股份则亏损</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">75</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">亿元。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\">　　“宝武合并”后，新诞生的宝武钢铁集团去年粗钢总产量达到<span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">6070</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">万吨，成为仅次于安赛乐米塔尔的世界第二大钢铁厂，并问鼎中国第一大钢铁公司。相较于全国</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">8.04</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">亿吨的粗钢产量，其市场占有率将达到</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">7.5%</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">。上市公司层面，合并后的新主体在全球上市钢铁企业中粗钢产量排名第三、在全球汽车板材市场产量排名第三、在全球取向硅钢市场产量排名第一。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　重组预案披露，两家公司计划用</span>3<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年左右时间，深入推进主要业务板块及区域市场的整合融合，逐步建立统一研发、统一销售和统一采购的新型管理体系，充分挖掘协同效应，全面优化资源配置。两家公司将对其同质化产线进行优化，调整产能结构，减少产能重复投资，盘活存量产能资产，并不断扩大独有和独特优势产品市场份额；每个基地对应具有竞争力的周边市场，以市场化机制实践钢铁去产能和供给侧改革。</span></span></p><p><br/></p>','宝武出世：将成为中国第一世界第二大钢铁厂','　　我国钢铁行业两大巨头宝钢集团和武钢集团，今天正式宣布合为一家。其旗下各自的核心主业上市公司——宝钢股份和武钢股份，则将通过吸收合并的方式实现重组，根据换股价格测算，相当于每1股武钢股份的股份可以换取0.56股宝钢股份的股份。','1','1','2017-03-11 22:06:33','','0','','','0','{\"thumb\":\"\"}','1','0','0','0','','');INSERT INTO ts_posts ( `id`, `post_author`, `post_keywords`, `post_source`, `post_date`, `post_content`, `post_title`, `post_excerpt`, `post_status`, `comment_status`, `post_modified`, `post_content_filtered`, `post_parent`, `post_type`, `post_mime_type`, `comment_count`, `smeta`, `post_hits`, `post_like`, `istop`, `recommended`, `page_tpl`, `page_tpls` ) VALUES  ('301','1','发改委重申煤炭去产能 ','','2017-03-11 22:09:19','<p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;font-size: 14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　环渤海动力煤</span>13<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">周连涨的态势，并未让煤炭业人士乐观起来。在</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">9</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">25</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">日举办的第十一届榆林国际煤炭暨能化装备技术博览会上，《经济参考报》记者了解到，当前煤炭需求持续回落、产能过剩、企业经营困难的态势并没有发生实质性改变，截至</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">7</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月底，全国规模以上煤炭企业负债总额同比增长</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">4.7%</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">，至</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">3.66</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">万亿元。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;font-size: 14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　国家发改委</span>23<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">日在《理性看待当前煤炭市场供需形势，坚定不移推进化解过剩产能》一文中再次重申坚定不移去产能，将采取适度微调政策，在日增加煤炭产量</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">30</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">万吨左右的基础上，近日拟日增加产能规模</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">50</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">万吨。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;font-size: 14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　据悉，自</span>2012<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年下半年以来，历经四年煤炭经济下行，需求下降，价格持续下跌，全社会煤炭库存居高不下，应收账款增加，煤炭企业盈利水平大幅下降。今年以来，在推动煤炭行业化解过剩产能实现脱困发展综合政策措施指导下，煤炭总量控制取得成效，市场供大于求的态势有所缓解。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;font-size: 14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　数据显示，全国煤炭消费量在</span>2014<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年下降</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">2.9%</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">、</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">2015</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年下降</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">3.7%</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">的基础上，测算今年前八个月，全国煤炭消费</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">24.4</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">亿吨，同比减少</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">7500</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">万吨，下降</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">3.1%</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">。而全国煤炭产量同比下降约</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">10%</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;font-size: 14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　在此背景下，各地煤炭价格均实现不同程度的回升。</span>9<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">21</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">日，作为市场风向标的环渤海动力煤价格指数报收</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">554</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">元</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">/</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">吨，比前一周上涨了</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">17</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">元</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">/</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">吨。这是该指数连续</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">13</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">周上涨，继续刷新年内最高纪录，较年初</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">371</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">元</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">/</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">吨上涨了</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">183</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">元</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">/</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">吨，累计涨幅达到</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">49.3%</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;font-size: 14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　不过，中国煤炭工业协会会长王显政表示，当前煤炭需求持续回落、产能过剩、企业经营困难的态势并没有发生实质性改变，煤炭市场仍存在不确定和不稳定因素，不可盲目乐观。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;font-size: 14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　据介绍，受煤炭企业盈利水平下降、亏损扩大等影响，企业融资困难、融资成本高的问题十分突出。同时，煤炭企业负债总额高，资产负债率增加。截至</span>7<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月底，全国规模以上煤炭企业负债总额</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">3.66</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">万亿元，同比增长</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">4.7%</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">，平均资产负债率达到</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">70%</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;font-size: 14px\">　　“要高度重视企业债务风险问题，控制企业经营风险。”中国煤炭工业协会副会长梁嘉琨称，加大金融支持力度，建立和完善正常的融资渠道，确保企业生产经营的资金需求，控制经营风险，还有大量工作要做。同时，要坚定信心、保持定力，推动煤炭行业转型升级。</span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;font-size: 14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　国家发改委也在上述文章中指出，从大的供需关系看，我国煤炭产能严重过剩、供大于求的趋势没有根本改变。今后一个时期，我国能源消费强度将有所回落，特别是随着可再生能源和清洁能源的快速发展，煤炭的市场需求很难有绝对增长的空间。</span>2020<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年我国能源消费总量预期在</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">50</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">亿吨标准煤以内，煤炭消费量至多</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">41</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">亿吨。目前，全国各类煤矿产能总规模全部形成有可能超出</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">60</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">亿吨，扣除净进口</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">2</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">亿吨，国内煤炭的市场空间仅在</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">34</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">亿至</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">36</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">亿吨。因此，煤炭去产能控产量不仅信心不容动摇，力度也不能减弱。否则，煤炭价格有可能再度下滑，煤炭行业的脱困发展将难以实现。　在坚定不移去产能的同时，针对当前出现的煤价上涨、局部供应偏紧的情况，国家发改委表示，将采取适度微调政策，灵活实施先进产能煤矿减量化制度。</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">9</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月初，国家发展改革委会同有关部门制定了稳定煤炭供应、抑制煤炭价格过快上涨的预案，并启动二级响应，日增加煤炭产量</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">30</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">万吨左右，近日又启动了一级响应，拟日增加产能规模</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">50</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">万吨。有关部门已经研究了后续政策措施，下一步，视煤炭市场变化情况，如果情况仍在延续，将科学加大先进产能投放量，确保煤炭稳定供应。此外，在建煤矿通过增减挂钩，还可以释放一部分产能、产量。</span></span></p><p><br/></p>','发改委重申煤炭去产能 政策适度微调','　　环渤海动力煤13周连涨的态势，并未让煤炭业人士乐观起来。在9月25日举办的第十一届榆林国际煤炭暨能化装备技术博览会上，《经济参考报》记者了解到，当前煤炭需求持续回落、产能过剩、企业经营困难的态势并没有发生实质性改变，截至7月底，全国规模以上煤炭企业负债总额同比增长4.7%，至3.66万亿元。','1','1','2017-03-11 22:07:50','','0','','','0','{\"thumb\":\"\"}','0','0','0','0','','');INSERT INTO ts_posts ( `id`, `post_author`, `post_keywords`, `post_source`, `post_date`, `post_content`, `post_title`, `post_excerpt`, `post_status`, `comment_status`, `post_modified`, `post_content_filtered`, `post_parent`, `post_type`, `post_mime_type`, `comment_count`, `smeta`, `post_hits`, `post_like`, `istop`, `recommended`, `page_tpl`, `page_tpls` ) VALUES  ('302','1','伊朗石油部长暗示不会加入冻产协议','','2017-03-11 22:14:00','<p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;font-size: 14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　国际能源论坛</span>27<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">日在阿尔及利亚首都阿尔及尔举行开幕式。会议期间各产油国将讨论采取相关措施稳定油市，但据媒体报道，伊朗石油部长赞加内在开幕式上的表态暗示此次会议很难达成冻产协议。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;font-size: 14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　赞加内指出，阿尔及尔会议只会交换观点，没有其他内容。伊朗不愿意按照当前的原油产量水平实行冻产，伊朗希望把产量增加至</span>400<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">万桶</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">/</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">日。伊朗寻求恢复原油市场份额占比在</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">12%-13%</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">，这需要时间来进行更多的磋商。未来两天达成协议并不在该国的议程中。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;font-size: 14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　沙特能源部长法利赫在会上表示，阿尔及尔会议是</span>“咨询”会议。对油市持积极态度，但油市复苏进程比该国希望的要缓慢。他还表示，沙特经济当前表现良好。原油基本面将需要长期推升价格，当前原油库存正在下滑，原油供需状态已经相互靠近，油市正在朝着正确的方向前进。</span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;font-size: 14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　俄罗斯能源部长诺瓦克指出，俄罗斯希望将石油产量冻结在当前水平，俄罗斯将与伊朗讨论维护原油市场稳定。</span></span></p><p><br/></p>','伊朗石油部长暗示不会加入冻产协议','　　国际能源论坛27日在阿尔及利亚首都阿尔及尔举行开幕式。会议期间各产油国将讨论采取相关措施稳定油市，但据媒体报道，伊朗石油部长赞加内在开幕式上的表态暗示此次会议很难达成冻产协议。','1','1','2017-03-11 22:13:14','','0','','','0','{\"thumb\":\"\"}','1','0','0','0','','');INSERT INTO ts_posts ( `id`, `post_author`, `post_keywords`, `post_source`, `post_date`, `post_content`, `post_title`, `post_excerpt`, `post_status`, `comment_status`, `post_modified`, `post_content_filtered`, `post_parent`, `post_type`, `post_mime_type`, `comment_count`, `smeta`, `post_hits`, `post_like`, `istop`, `recommended`, `page_tpl`, `page_tpls` ) VALUES  ('303','1','我国连续4年清洁能源投资全球第一','','2017-03-11 22:15:08','<p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;font-size: 14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　日前，由中国能源研究会编制的《中国能源发展报告</span>2016<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">》在京发布。报告显示，</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">2015</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年我国能源工业投资额合计</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">3.25</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">万亿元，同比增长</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">4.1%</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">。其中，清洁能源投资总额同比增长</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">17%</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">，已经连续第四年居全球清洁能源投资第一大国的位置。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;font-size: 14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　报告显示，</span>2015<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年煤炭开采和洗选业投资额连续三年出现负增长，同比下滑</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">14.4%</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">，石油和天然气开采业，燃气生产和供应业有所增长，增幅为</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">4.0%</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">，石油和天然气开采业和石油加工、炼焦及核燃料加工业投资由增转降，同比分别下降</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">5.7%</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">和</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">20.9%</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">；电力、热力的生产和供应投资同比增长</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">15.7%</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">。管道运输业固定投资同比降</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">5.2%</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;font-size: 14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　在能源消费方面，报告显示，</span>2015<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年，我国能源消费增速继续放缓，能源消费总量</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">43.0</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">亿吨标准煤，比上年增长</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">0.9%</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">，增速比</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">2014</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年放缓</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">1.3</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">个百分点，是</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">1998</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年以来最低增速。我国节能降耗和生态建设成效显著，能源消费强度明显下降，全国万元国内生产总值能耗下降</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">5.6%</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;font-size: 14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　在供给方面，能源供应总量保持增长，</span>2015<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年我国一次能源生产总量为</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">36.2</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">亿吨标准煤，与上年持平，能源自给率为</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">84.4%</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">，其中，原煤产量</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">37.5</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">亿吨，同比下降</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">3.3%</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">，原油产量</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">2.15</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">亿吨，同比增长</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">1.7%</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">，天然气产量</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">1346</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">亿立方米，同比增长</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">3.4%</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">，发电量</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">5.81</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">万亿千瓦时，同比增长</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">0.3%</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;font-size: 14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　另外，报告显示，</span>2015<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年，我国能源互联网发展迅猛。在分布式能源的接入、电改的推进以及新能源汽车与储能的蓬勃发展下，电力已经从</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">B2B</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">逐渐向</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">C2C</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">交易转变，能源互联网在中国萌芽。</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">2015</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">3</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">2</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">日，由中国主导的</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">IEEE1888</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">能源互联网标准，成为全球能源互联网产业首个</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">ISO/IEC</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">国际标准。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;font-size: 14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　展望</span>“十三五”，报告指出，能源行业改革发展面临诸多挑战以及需要重点关注的问题。</span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;font-size: 14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　一是我国煤炭行业已进入</span>“需求增速放缓期、超前产能和库存消化期、环境约束强化期、结构调整攻坚期”的“四期并存”阶段，短期内煤炭市场供大于求的态势很难改变。企业经营困难、产业集中度低、科技创新能力弱等伴生问题将制约煤炭产业“绿色、清洁、高效”发展。</span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;font-size: 14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　二是新常态下石化产业如何针对当前的问题进行规划调整，企业又该如何认识当前面临的突出矛盾和问题，准确把握行业发展的走向和趋势，以何种智慧实现下一个五年的健康发展，为我国成为石化工业强国奠定基础，牵动着每个石化从业者的神经。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;font-size: 14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　三是受经济增速放缓、气候温和、气价缺乏竞争力等因素影响，我国天然气需求增速明显放缓，天然气市场供应过剩，消费不足局势严峻。居民用气是增加天然气消费的一个重要突破口，而近期的天然气价格始终未触碰居民用气，并且居民用气价格远低于非居民用气价，存在交叉补贴问题。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;font-size: 14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　四是电力发展面临的严峻挑战：我国能源资源约束日益加剧，生态环境问题突出，环境承载能力已经达到或接近上限；我国人均用电与发达国家相比仍有明显差距，能源利用效率较低；清洁能源发电缺乏统筹规划和刚性约束。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;font-size: 14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　五是</span>“十二五”期间，非化石能源总体呈现出快速发展的态势，但随着经济进入新常态，能源体制机制约束问题日益突出，“三弃”问题加剧、投资建设放缓、价格形成机制不合理等各种发展矛盾凸显。</span></p><p><br/></p>','我国连续4年清洁能源投资全球第一','　　日前，由中国能源研究会编制的《中国能源发展报告2016》在京发布。报告显示，2015年我国能源工业投资额合计3.25万亿元，同比增长4.1%。其中，清洁能源投资总额同比增长17%，已经连续第四年居全球清洁能源投资第一大国的位置。','1','1','2017-03-11 22:14:16','','0','','','0','{\"thumb\":\"\"}','1','0','0','0','','');INSERT INTO ts_posts ( `id`, `post_author`, `post_keywords`, `post_source`, `post_date`, `post_content`, `post_title`, `post_excerpt`, `post_status`, `comment_status`, `post_modified`, `post_content_filtered`, `post_parent`, `post_type`, `post_mime_type`, `comment_count`, `smeta`, `post_hits`, `post_like`, `istop`, `recommended`, `page_tpl`, `page_tpls` ) VALUES  ('304','1','中国经济平稳增长略超预期','','2017-03-11 22:16:00','<p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;font-size: 14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　三季度是观察全年经济的关键窗口。中国社科院财经战略研究院</span>(NAES)27<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">日发布报告显示，今年三季度以来，中国经济平稳增长略超市场预期，四季度面对经济潜在风险和下行压力，建议继续推进供给侧改革，使经济运行保持在合理区间。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;font-size: 14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　在此间举行的</span>“<span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">NASE</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">宏观经济形势季度分析会”上，中国社科院财经院综合经济战略研究部副主任汪红驹代表财经院课题组做主题报告指出，今年三季度以来，我国政府继续推进供给侧改革和相关政策措施，经济增长略超市场预期，成绩来之不易。消费、投资和工业增加值平稳增长，服务业增幅略有回落，中上游企业利润增速回升。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;font-size: 14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　对于四季度宏观经济走势，汪红驹认为受去产能、去泡沫和清理债务等因素影响，基建投资、房地产投资、民间投资增速存在回落压力。房地产市场结构性矛盾加重，宏观政策操作难度加大，经济增长仍有下行压力；物价涨幅分化，</span>PPI<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">同比降幅继续缩小趋向转正，</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">CPI</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">温和增长。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;font-size: 14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　报告建议，当前应抓住时机，进一步实施积极有效的财政政策和稳健灵活的货币政策，创新宏观调控方式方法，在保证国内需求基本平稳的前提下，继续推进供给侧改革，增强经济发展的可持续性，化解经济中潜藏的风险，使经济运行保持在合理区间。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;font-size: 14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　具体政策建议包括：针对少数地区陷入区域性经济衰退，加大力度推进区域经济结构调整；针对房地产市场区域分化严重，冷热不均，在统一城镇化发展的前提下，要因城而异，制定差别化的房地产调控政策，化解局部城市的潜在泡沫风险；增加地方政府债务透明度，把握好经济增长与债务增长的平衡；提高环保标准，加大企业合并和改革力度，做好转岗再就业帮扶工作，防止落后产能死灰复燃，巩固供给侧改革成果；加强国际合作，推动落实</span>G20<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">会议成果，为我国经济发展拓展国际空间，创造好的国际经济环境。</span></span></p><p><br/></p>','社科院：中国经济平稳增长略超预期','　　三季度是观察全年经济的关键窗口。中国社科院财经战略研究院(NAES)27日发布报告显示，今年三季度以来，中国经济平稳增长略超市场预期，四季度面对经济潜在风险和下行压力，建议继续推进供给侧改革，使经济运行保持在合理区间。','1','1','2017-03-11 22:15:19','','0','','','0','{\"thumb\":\"\"}','2','0','0','0','','');INSERT INTO ts_posts ( `id`, `post_author`, `post_keywords`, `post_source`, `post_date`, `post_content`, `post_title`, `post_excerpt`, `post_status`, `comment_status`, `post_modified`, `post_content_filtered`, `post_parent`, `post_type`, `post_mime_type`, `comment_count`, `smeta`, `post_hits`, `post_like`, `istop`, `recommended`, `page_tpl`, `page_tpls` ) VALUES  ('305','1','中国可从三方面增强原油市场话语权','','2017-03-11 22:17:57','<p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;font-size: 14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　中银国际大宗商品市场策略主管傅晓</span>27<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">日接受中新网记者采访时表示，虽然中国在石油方面的进口依存度较高，但中国在全球原油市场上并不被动，未来也可以从三方面进一步提高自己的话语权。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;font-size: 14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　近年来，中国能源对外依存度持续上升。官方</span>2012<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年披露的数据显示，中国石油对外依存度在本世纪初时还仅为</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">32%</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">，但到</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">2012</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年这一数据已经上升到</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">57%</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">。对外依存度的上升，引发了各方对于能源安全的关注。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;font-size: 14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　傅晓表示，当前全球原油的供需关系是供大于求的，中国可以借此机会增加消费方的影响力。尤其是目前沙特、伊朗，包括石油输出国组织</span>(OPEC)<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">内部，都在积极争取亚洲市场，而中国是他们的必争战场。在这种情况下，中国可以利用几个原油输出国之间的竞争来增加自身在全球市场中的话语权。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;font-size: 14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　优化能源结构也是提高话语权的可行之策。傅晓表示，中国可以通过进一步发展风能、电能、核电、水能等绿色能源，将能源结构调整的更加多元化，降低对化石能源的依赖度。同时，提高原油等能源的使用效率，也可以减轻对原油的依存度。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;font-size: 14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　金融市场的影响也是一个不可忽视的方面。傅晓指出，从金融市场来看，目前中国在稀土、铁矿石等能源市场的影响力和话语权比往年增加了很多，其中上海期货交易所发行的铜、镍、锌等人民币计价期货在国际上的影响力非常大，包括英国等海外金融市场的交易员和情报师都会在半夜去关注中国市场。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;font-size: 14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　傅晓表示，预计原油方面下一步也可能会推出以人民币计价的国际原油合约。以上这一点是从金融市场的角度增加原油市场影响力的方式。</span></span></p><p><br/></p>','中国可从三方面增强原油市场话语权','　　中银国际大宗商品市场策略主管傅晓27日接受中新网记者采访时表示，虽然中国在石油方面的进口依存度较高，但中国在全球原油市场上并不被动，未来也可以从三方面进一步提高自己的话语权。','1','1','2017-03-11 22:17:14','','0','','','0','{\"thumb\":\"\"}','1','0','0','0','','');INSERT INTO ts_posts ( `id`, `post_author`, `post_keywords`, `post_source`, `post_date`, `post_content`, `post_title`, `post_excerpt`, `post_status`, `comment_status`, `post_modified`, `post_content_filtered`, `post_parent`, `post_type`, `post_mime_type`, `comment_count`, `smeta`, `post_hits`, `post_like`, `istop`, `recommended`, `page_tpl`, `page_tpls` ) VALUES  ('306','1','油价低迷态势或在2017年后改变','','2017-03-11 22:18:54','<p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;font-size: 14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　国际能源论坛秘书长孙贤胜</span>27<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">日在阿尔及尔说，国际油价要扭转低迷态势并达到稳定需要一段时间，有可能在</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">2017</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年后才会实现。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;font-size: 14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　孙贤胜当天在阿尔及利亚首都阿尔及尔召开的第</span>15<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">届国际能源论坛上接受新华社记者采访时说，此次论坛对参会的政府官员、专家学者和其他能源界专业人士进行了问卷调查，大多数受访者认为目前油价低迷态势要等到</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">2017</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年以后才会改变。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;font-size: 14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　孙贤胜说，目前国际原油市场明显供大于求，</span>2014<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年以来出现“三大两跌”的情况，即原油、成品油和天然气供大于求，油价和天然气价格剧跌，这种局面直到现在没有明显改变。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;font-size: 14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　孙贤胜表示，油价过低对于生产国和消费国都不利。由于过去两年油价持续低迷，全球石油工业投资减少了</span>3000<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">亿美元，最近两年的新探明储量是历史上最少的，这为今后石油生产带来极大不确定性。石油投资减少和产量下降可能在一段时间后导致市场供不应求，从而造成新一轮油价暴涨。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;font-size: 14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　他说，包括石油生产国和消费国在内的大多数国家认为油价应处在一个较为合理的区间，这不仅对各方有利，也是能源供应安全的一个保证。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;font-size: 14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　国际能源论坛总部设在沙特阿拉伯首都利雅得，它主张促进能源生产国与消费国对话，以增加石油天然气市场透明度，保障国际能源市场稳定运行。</span></span></p><p><br/></p>','国际能源论坛秘书长称油价低迷态势或在2017年后改变','　　国际能源论坛秘书长孙贤胜27日在阿尔及尔说，国际油价要扭转低迷态势并达到稳定需要一段时间，有可能在2017年后才会实现。','1','1','2017-03-11 22:18:06','','0','','','0','{\"thumb\":\"\"}','0','0','0','0','','');INSERT INTO ts_posts ( `id`, `post_author`, `post_keywords`, `post_source`, `post_date`, `post_content`, `post_title`, `post_excerpt`, `post_status`, `comment_status`, `post_modified`, `post_content_filtered`, `post_parent`, `post_type`, `post_mime_type`, `comment_count`, `smeta`, `post_hits`, `post_like`, `istop`, `recommended`, `page_tpl`, `page_tpls` ) VALUES  ('307','1','国际油价28日上涨 ','','2017-03-11 22:19:49','<p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;font-size: 14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　国际油价</span>28<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">日上涨。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;font-size: 14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　消息人士称，欧佩克成员国当天已达成一项减产协议，各成员国减产数量将在</span>11<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月的欧佩克正式会议上决定。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;font-size: 14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　分析人士表示，此消息当天助推国际油价上涨。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;font-size: 14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　截至当天收盘，纽约商品交易所</span>11<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月交货的轻质原油期货价格上涨</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">2.38</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">美元，收于每桶</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">47.05</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">美元，涨幅为</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">5.33%</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">。</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">11</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月交货的伦敦布伦特原油期货价格上涨</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">2.72</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">美元，收于每桶</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">48.69</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">美元，涨幅为</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">5.92%</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">。</span></span></p><p><br/></p>','国际油价28日上涨 纽约市场收于每桶47.05美元','国际油价28日上涨。','1','1','2017-03-11 22:19:09','','0','','','0','{\"thumb\":\"\"}','1','0','0','0','','');INSERT INTO ts_posts ( `id`, `post_author`, `post_keywords`, `post_source`, `post_date`, `post_content`, `post_title`, `post_excerpt`, `post_status`, `comment_status`, `post_modified`, `post_content_filtered`, `post_parent`, `post_type`, `post_mime_type`, `comment_count`, `smeta`, `post_hits`, `post_like`, `istop`, `recommended`, `page_tpl`, `page_tpls` ) VALUES  ('308','1','需求回升推动天然气价格波动率放大','','2017-03-11 22:20:56','<p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;font-size: 14px\">　　9<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月，在国际原油市场波动加剧的同时，另一大能源市场——天然气市场也不甘落后。美国天然气价格在历经</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">16</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">个月低迷后，于近日首度突破</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">3</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">美元</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">/</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">百万英热单位，从今年</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">4</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月初至今涨幅已超过</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">50%</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">。从驱动天然气价格反弹的因素来看，主要是美国天然气产出放缓，而需求出现回升。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;font-size: 14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　从供需层面来看，</span>2016<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年供应过剩压力出现明显的缓解。供应端方面，</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">2015</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年无疑是天然气的丰收年。</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">2015</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年美国天然气的平均日产量为</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">719</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">亿立方英尺，比</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">2014</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年提高了</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">32</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">亿立方英尺</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">/</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">天。而天然气储量第二大国俄罗斯</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">2014</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年的天然气日产量才</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">570</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">亿立方英尺，全球天然气储量第一大国伊朗的日产量也仅为</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">165</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">亿立方英尺。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;font-size: 14px\">　　2016<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年随着石油和钻井平台减少，美国天然气产量增长势头基本上停止。</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">IHSMarkit</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">分析数据显示，美国</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">48</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">州</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">8</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月天然气生产水平环比增长</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">1.4%</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">，是自</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">2015</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">9</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月以来首次录得环比增长。美国东北部产区</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">8</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月天然气产量较</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">7</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月增长</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">4</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">千万立方英尺</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">/</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">日。不过，美国</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">48</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">州</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">8</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月天然气较去年同期略微下滑</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">1%(</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">或</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">7</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">千万立方英尺</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">/</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">日</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">)</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;font-size: 14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　需求端则出现恢复的势头。芝商所高级经济学家</span>BlufordPutnam<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">在报告中称，美国更多发电原料从煤炭转移至天然气。事实上，作为发电原料之一，天然气极有可能在</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">2016</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年首次超越煤炭。自</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">2013</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年以来没有新的煤炭发电厂投产，使天然气、风力和太阳能成为主要发电来源。而</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">2015</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年天然气消费表现温和，</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">2015</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年美国天然气平均每天的需求量为</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">728</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">亿立方英尺，与</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">2014</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年相比该数值仅增加了</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">17</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">亿立方英尺</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">/</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">天。</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">2016</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年，由于发电需求增加，美国南方天然气现货价格上升。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;font-size: 14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　结合即将到来的、可能出现的拉尼娜现象，天然气需求可能会较往年出现明显的增加。原因在于厄尔尼诺现象过后，北美许多地区夏季温度格外高，用电需求增加。芝商所高级经济学家</span>ErikNorland<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">发布报告表示，高库存量还需要时间来消化，但反厄尔尼诺现象的冬季有可能加快其消化速度。虽然供应停滞不前，而需求继续增长的可能性很大。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;font-size: 14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　对于拉尼娜现象是否会对天然气消费产生拉动效应，</span>BlufordPutnam<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">认为，目前，厄尔尼诺现象已经远离，天气分析师正观察拉尼娜现象形成的可能性</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">(</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">目前介于</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">60%</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">至</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">70%</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">之间</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">)</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">，换言之赤道太平洋一带海水变得比往常寒冷。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;font-size: 14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　气候从厄尔尼诺现象急转为拉尼娜现象非常常见，尤其厄尔尼诺现象像</span>2015<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年那样严重时。</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">1998</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">—</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">1999</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年的拉尼娜现象出现时，冬天非常寒冷，耗尽美国的天然气供应量，最终经过一段滞后期，导致天然气价格急剧飙升。这一次情况可能有所不同，取决于北美洲太平洋沿岸海水温度是否会下降，令拉尼娜现象如</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">1999</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年及</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">2007</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年般严重，或者是否会比往常温暖，部分抵消拉尼娜现象的严重程度而定。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;font-size: 14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　不过，天然气价格未来走势并非确定性表现为上涨，存在较大的不确定性，其中最大的不利因素是美国页岩油井已经开始持续恢复。美国油服贝克休斯公布的数据显示，截至</span>9<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">23</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">日当周，美国石油钻井平台数量增加</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">2</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">座，增至</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">418</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">座，刷新</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">7</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">个月高位，过去</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">17</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">周美国原油钻井平台数量有</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">15</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">周录得上涨，且总共增加</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">102</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">座；美国天然气钻井平台数量增加</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">3</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">座，增至</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">92</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">座。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;font-size: 14px\">　　QuickStrike<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">期权分析工具显示，</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">9</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月到期的天然气期权合约波动率在</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">3.2</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">美元</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">/</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">百万英热单位以上就开始急剧攀升，这意味着未来天然气价格在突破</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">3.2</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">美元</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">/</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">百万英热单位后对冲需求会大幅增加，波动率交易机会也会攀升，但是目前还处于振荡走势中。 &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;font-size: 14px\">&nbsp;</span></p><p><br/></p>','需求回升推动天然气价格波动率放大','　　9月，在国际原油市场波动加剧的同时，另一大能源市场——天然气市场也不甘落后。美国天然气价格在历经16个月低迷后，于近日首度突破3美元/百万英热单位，从今年4月初至今涨幅已超过50%。从驱动天然气价格反弹的因素来看，主要是美国天然气产出放缓，而需求出现回升。','1','1','2017-03-11 22:20:00','','0','','','0','{\"thumb\":\"\"}','1','0','0','0','','');INSERT INTO ts_posts ( `id`, `post_author`, `post_keywords`, `post_source`, `post_date`, `post_content`, `post_title`, `post_excerpt`, `post_status`, `comment_status`, `post_modified`, `post_content_filtered`, `post_parent`, `post_type`, `post_mime_type`, `comment_count`, `smeta`, `post_hits`, `post_like`, `istop`, `recommended`, `page_tpl`, `page_tpls` ) VALUES  ('309','1','欧佩克8年来首次达成限产协议','','2017-03-11 22:21:56','<p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;font-size: 14px\">　　9<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">28</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">日，欧佩克组织在阿尔及利亚召开第</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">170</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">次特别会议（</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">Extraordinary meeting</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">）</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">,</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">决定将</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">14</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">个成员国原油日产量目标定在</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">3250</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">万桶至</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">3300</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">万桶之间。这是该组织</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">8</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年来首次达成限产协议。消息一出，布伦特上涨</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">2.72</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">美元至每桶</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">48.69</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">美元，涨幅</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">5.9%</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">，</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">WTI</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">涨至</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">47.05</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">美元。消息还拉动埃克森美孚、雪佛龙等能源巨头股价飙升。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;font-size: 14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　欧佩克会后在官网发布声明称，目前，全球石油行业投资持续下滑，失业率上升，正在影响未来世界石油供应安全。而原油库存依旧高企，石油需求保持强劲。鉴于此，欧佩克组织需要采取措施，积极推动石油市场再平衡进程。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;font-size: 14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　一名欧佩克官员</span>27<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">日表示，欧佩克在讨论中打算将产量每日削减至少</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">100</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">万桶，如此以来一年可减少</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">3.5</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">亿桶。这将缓解全球原油库存过剩。</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">8</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月份欧佩克日产量已达到</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">3324</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">万桶。按照此次会议的产量提议，减产量将主要由沙特、伊拉克、科威特等国家承担，减产行动将“豁免”伊朗、利比亚和尼日利亚。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;font-size: 14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　会议上，欧佩克还决定成立由成员国代表组成的委员会，负责研究和提出各国产量水平的建议。今年</span>11<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月，欧佩克会议将进一步落实限产措施，届时还将与非欧佩克产油国接洽，寻求进一步合作，推动原油市场再平衡进程。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;font-size: 14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　有分析师认为，此次限产对油价提振作用有限。限产具体细节、措施尚未出台，欧佩克将产量削减至</span>8<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月份之前的水平并非易事。到</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">11</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月限产执行前，主要产油国仍将继续保持增产势头，并将冲抵美国库存下降带来的利好。此外，要让限产对市场产生系统性影响，也需要俄罗斯等非欧佩克国家的合作。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;font-size: 14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　中国石油经济技术研究院石油市场所陈蕊认为，欧佩克限产虽然达成，但难以对基本供需面带来根本改善，后期限产执行效果也待观望，对于油价的提振效果有限。</span></span></p><p><br/></p>','欧佩克8年来首次达成限产协议 国际油价大涨近6%','　　9月28日，欧佩克组织在阿尔及利亚召开第170次特别会议（Extraordinary meeting）,决定将14个成员国原油日产量目标定在3250万桶至3300万桶之间。这是该组织8年来首次达成限产协议。消息一出，布伦特上涨2.72美元至每桶48.69美元，涨幅5.9%，WTI涨至47.05美元。消息还拉动埃克森美孚、雪佛龙等能源巨头股价飙升。','1','1','2017-03-11 22:21:13','','0','','','0','{\"thumb\":\"\"}','1','0','0','0','','');INSERT INTO ts_posts ( `id`, `post_author`, `post_keywords`, `post_source`, `post_date`, `post_content`, `post_title`, `post_excerpt`, `post_status`, `comment_status`, `post_modified`, `post_content_filtered`, `post_parent`, `post_type`, `post_mime_type`, `comment_count`, `smeta`, `post_hits`, `post_like`, `istop`, `recommended`, `page_tpl`, `page_tpls` ) VALUES  ('310','1','国际油价29日上涨 ','','2017-03-11 22:22:44','<p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;font-size: 14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　国际油价</span>29<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">日收盘上涨。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;font-size: 14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　石油输出国组织</span>(<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">欧佩克</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">)28</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">日在阿尔及尔举行特别会议，决定将石油日产量减至</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">3250</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">万至</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">3300</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">万桶，以平衡市场供求。受此提振，国际油价</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">28</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">日大涨逾</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">5%</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;font-size: 14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　由于</span>29<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">日并无重要石油数据公布，受减产乐观情绪鼓舞，当天国际油价延续之前涨势继续上扬。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;font-size: 14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　截至当日收盘时，纽约商品交易所</span>11<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月交货的轻质原油期货价格上涨</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">0.78</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">美元，收于每桶</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">47.83</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">美元，涨幅为</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">1.7%</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">。</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">11</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月交货的伦敦布伦特原油期货价格上涨</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">0.55</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">美元，收于每桶</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">49.24</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">美元，涨幅为</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">1.1%</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">。</span></span></p><p><br/></p>','国际油价29日上涨 纽约市场收于每桶47.83美元','　　国际油价29日收盘上涨。','1','1','2017-03-11 22:22:08','','0','','','0','{\"thumb\":\"\"}','2','0','0','0','','');INSERT INTO ts_posts ( `id`, `post_author`, `post_keywords`, `post_source`, `post_date`, `post_content`, `post_title`, `post_excerpt`, `post_status`, `comment_status`, `post_modified`, `post_content_filtered`, `post_parent`, `post_type`, `post_mime_type`, `comment_count`, `smeta`, `post_hits`, `post_like`, `istop`, `recommended`, `page_tpl`, `page_tpls` ) VALUES  ('311','1','中国战略石油储备对油价举足轻重','','2017-03-11 22:24:33','<p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;font-size: 14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　国际石油专家认为，中国原油储备可能成为全球原油价格和市场动态的不确定因素。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;font-size: 14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　根据国际能源署的数据，中国是全球第二大石油消费国。近年来，随着油价走弱，中国成为与印度一样的主要原油进口国，很大程度上为全球原油需求增长提供了支撑。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;font-size: 14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　根据美国</span>CNBC<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">报道，中国大部分低价进口原油转变成为战略石油储备，外界认为已接近其最大容量。</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">9</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">26</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">日至</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">28</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">日，全球主要石油生产国正齐聚阿尔及利亚，商讨如何支撑原油价格，令市场摆脱供需不平衡的矛盾。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;font-size: 14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　但无论石油输出国组织</span>(OPEC)<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">作何决策，石油领域专家认为，中国可能会利用油价上涨的机会出口战略石油储备，令稳定原油市场的举措失效。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;font-size: 14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　标普道琼斯指数大宗商品和实体资产全球主管</span>JodieGunzberg<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">周二出席标普全球石油市场新闻发布会时表示，无论供给端如何变化，中国战略石油储备都是市场的不确定因素。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;font-size: 14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　他称，既然中国购买了如此多的低价石油来补充战略石油储备，如果</span>OPEC<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">确定冻产并试图提振油价，中国就可能推动价格下跌，因其不会选择以更高的价格购买原油，只会使用战略石油储备，或自己进行石油出口。因此，</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">Gunzberg</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">称，中国战略石油储备可能成为决定低油价持续时间的因素。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;font-size: 14px\">　　2009<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年，中国宣布将分阶段建立国家石油储备。</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">2014</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">11</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月，中国政府披露战略石油储备第一阶段规模大约为</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">9100</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">万桶。</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">2016</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">5</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月，根据路透社报道，中国处于第二阶段建设，规模接近</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">2.45</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">亿桶，建设可能在年底前完成。路透社报道称，中国战略石油储备将于</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">2020</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年完成，目标是达到</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">90</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">天进口量。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;font-size: 14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　中国政府对其石油储备一向讳莫如深，认为公开其储备规模将令其在购油时的商业谈判上处于劣势。然而，中国需求增长却正放缓，而印度在石油需求增速方面已取代了中国的领跑地位。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;font-size: 14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　标普全球普氏能源资讯的油料全球负责人</span>DaveErnsberger<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">在上述新闻发布会上表示，中国战略石油储备对市场造成挑战，是一系列可能影响全球原油市场的未知因素之一。由于规模未知，其对市场的风险也难以量化。</span></span></p><p><br/></p>','标普：中国战略石油储备对油价举足轻重','　　国际石油专家认为，中国原油储备可能成为全球原油价格和市场动态的不确定因素。','1','1','2017-03-11 22:23:31','','0','','','0','{\"thumb\":\"\"}','1','0','0','0','','');INSERT INTO ts_posts ( `id`, `post_author`, `post_keywords`, `post_source`, `post_date`, `post_content`, `post_title`, `post_excerpt`, `post_status`, `comment_status`, `post_modified`, `post_content_filtered`, `post_parent`, `post_type`, `post_mime_type`, `comment_count`, `smeta`, `post_hits`, `post_like`, `istop`, `recommended`, `page_tpl`, `page_tpls` ) VALUES  ('312','1','全国成品油价格指数持稳','','2017-03-11 22:25:38','<p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;font-size: 14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　依据新华</span>(<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">大庆</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">)</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">国际石油资讯中心发布的报告，截至</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">9</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">28</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">日，全国成品油价格指数为</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">611.74</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">，涨幅</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">0.08%</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">，全国成品油价格指数持稳。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;font-size: 14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　全国成品油价格指数运行结果表明，上周</span>93#<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">汽油平均价格报收于</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">5968</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">元</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">/</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">吨，较前一报告周期下跌</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">1</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">元</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">/</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">吨</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">(</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">与前一报告期基本持平</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">)</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">；</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">0#</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">柴油平均价格报收于</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">5233</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">元</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">/</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">吨，较前一报告周期上涨</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">7</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">元</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">/</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">吨</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">(</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">与前一报告期基本持平</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">)</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">。综合来看，全国汽柴油平均价格起伏不大，全国成品油价格指数持稳。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;font-size: 14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　新华</span>(<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">大庆</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">)</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">国际石油资讯中心分析师蒋冰认为，近期受冻产预期及美元走势影响，国际油价呈震荡格局。国内成品油市场价格继续持稳，市场交投情况转好。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;font-size: 14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　蒋冰分析认为，近期外盘国际油价受冻产协议预期影响持续震荡，国内成品油推涨意愿浓厚，加之十一长假出行需求增加，市场价格小幅推涨。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;font-size: 14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　国际市场方面，美国石油学会</span>(API)<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">近日公布数据显示，截至</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">9</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">23</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">日当周，美国原油库存减少</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">75.2</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">万桶至</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">5.064</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">亿桶，美国原油库存意外减少，库欣原油库存减少</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">83.2</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">万桶，该消息利好国际油价。观望后市，近期美元低位反弹加之供应持续过剩，预计短期内国际油价将维持震荡格局。</span></span></p><p><br/></p>','全国成品油价格指数持稳','　　依据新华(大庆)国际石油资讯中心发布的报告，截至9月28日，全国成品油价格指数为611.74，涨幅0.08%，全国成品油价格指数持稳。','1','1','2017-03-11 22:24:44','','0','','','0','{\"thumb\":\"\"}','1','0','0','0','','');INSERT INTO ts_posts ( `id`, `post_author`, `post_keywords`, `post_source`, `post_date`, `post_content`, `post_title`, `post_excerpt`, `post_status`, `comment_status`, `post_modified`, `post_content_filtered`, `post_parent`, `post_type`, `post_mime_type`, `comment_count`, `smeta`, `post_hits`, `post_like`, `istop`, `recommended`, `page_tpl`, `page_tpls` ) VALUES  ('313','1','油价或年内第9次搁浅 ','','2017-03-11 22:26:41','<p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;font-size: 14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　今日，国内成品油调价窗口再次开启。多家机构预测，国内油价或出现年内第九次搁浅。不过分析师认为，十一长假广大车主仍能享受到低油价的福利。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;font-size: 14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　本轮调价周期以来，围绕美国原油库存降低及欧佩克冻产协议的影响，国际原油期货价格宽幅震荡。</span>28<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">日，纽约商品交易所</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">11</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月交货的轻质原油期货收于每桶</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">47.05</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">美元，涨幅为</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">5.33%</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">。</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">11</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月交货的伦敦布伦特原油期货收于每桶</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">48.69</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">美元，涨幅</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">5.92%</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;font-size: 14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　据媒体报道，欧佩克成员国</span>28<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">日已达成一项减产协议，各成员国减产数量将在</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">11</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月的欧佩克正式会议上决定。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;font-size: 14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　隆众资讯、卓创资讯、中宇资讯等多家机构认为，这一消息推动了国际油价</span>28<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">日的大涨。以当前测算幅度来看，对应调价幅度将收缩至</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">50</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">元</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">/</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">吨之内，国内油价</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">30</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">日搁浅的概率非常大。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;font-size: 14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　上一轮调价窗口</span>(9<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">18</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">日</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">)</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">，国内汽、柴油价格每吨分别下调了</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">155</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">元和</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">150</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">元。调折合</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">89/90</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">号汽油每升降</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">0.11</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">元；</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">92/93</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">号汽油每升降</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">0.12</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">元；</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">97</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">号汽油每升降</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">0.13</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">元；</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">0</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">号柴油每升降</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">0.13</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">元。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;font-size: 14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　隆众资讯油品分析师李彦认为，即便本轮调价搁浅，十一长假广大车主仍能享受到低油价的福利。目前国内成品油资源供应过剩、终端消费疲软，加油站一直在竞相优惠促销，部分民营加油站的优惠力度已达</span>0.4-1.2<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">元</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">/</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">升左右，且部分中石油旗下的加油站也有限时优惠措施。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;font-size: 14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　卓创资讯成品油分析师王能表示，车主们国庆过后仍有</span>“喜事”。<span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">10</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月份起，多地将陆续置换“国五”油品；且按照以往惯例，至少置换期间，高标准油品零售价将不做调整。到时，除东部十一省份及陕西等已经实施“国五”标准的地区外，全国大部分地区将以“国四”油价享受“国五”油品。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;font-size: 14px\">　　2016<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年以来，国内成品油调价已呈现“六涨四跌八搁浅”的格局。成品油调价</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">8</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">次搁浅中</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">2</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">次正常搁浅，</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">6</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">次因地板价新政而不作调整；</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">6</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">次上调，共计上调汽油价格</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">985</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">元</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">/</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">吨，柴油价格</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">955</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">元</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">/</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">吨，折合约</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">0.7-0.8</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">元</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">/</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">升；</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">4</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">次下调，共计下调汽油价格</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">670</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">元</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">/</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">吨，柴油价格</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">650</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">元</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">/</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">吨，折合约</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">0.5-0.6</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">元</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">/</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">升。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;font-size: 14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　国内油价下一轮调价窗口将于</span>10<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">19</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">日</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">24</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">时开启。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;font-size: 14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　卓创资讯原油分析师李烨预计，由于冻产预期在</span>11<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月底的欧佩克年会前会继续为原油市场背书，这会对油价形成一个托底。国际油价或冲高回落，然后再度维持震荡局面，但整体水平会较目前小幅上涨。</span></span></p><p><br/></p>','油价或年内第9次搁浅 多地节后将享受低价“国五”油','　　今日，国内成品油调价窗口再次开启。多家机构预测，国内油价或出现年内第九次搁浅。不过分析师认为，十一长假广大车主仍能享受到低油价的福利。','1','1','2017-03-11 22:25:51','','0','','','0','{\"thumb\":\"\"}','0','0','0','0','','');INSERT INTO ts_posts ( `id`, `post_author`, `post_keywords`, `post_source`, `post_date`, `post_content`, `post_title`, `post_excerpt`, `post_status`, `comment_status`, `post_modified`, `post_content_filtered`, `post_parent`, `post_type`, `post_mime_type`, `comment_count`, `smeta`, `post_hits`, `post_like`, `istop`, `recommended`, `page_tpl`, `page_tpls` ) VALUES  ('314','1','OPEC冻产协议拖延至11月 ','','2017-03-11 22:28:16','<p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;font-size: 14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　石油输出国之间的冻产协议或需要再等几个月了。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;font-size: 14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　周三在阿尔及利亚首都阿尔及尔举行的石油输出国组织</span>OPEC<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">会议上，伊朗石油部长表示不愿意在此生产水平上冻结其原油产量，也拒绝与其他原油输出国商讨相关的冻产协议。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;font-size: 14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　这意味着有关于冻产协议的讨论要延迟到下一次会议，也就是</span>11<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月了。自美国页岩气革命伊始，原油价格开始一路狂泻，在经历过今年至今的低迷状态后，目前国际原油市场尚未找到一个供需平衡点。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;font-size: 14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　伊朗石油部长赞加内向媒体表示，希望将目前的产量提升至</span>400<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">万桶</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">/</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">日，而目前该国的原油产量为</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">360</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">万桶</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">/</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">日，排名</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">OPEC</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">成员国中第三的位置。就在会议期间，国际能源署</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">(IEA)</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">预计原油后市将会持续恶化。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;font-size: 14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　尽管没有达成统一的冻产意见，两年来第一次实质性讨论产油国产量目标的阿尔及尔会议还是取得了一定成果。沙特石油部长法利赫就表示，产油国之间在冻产水平的分歧正在逐步缩小，而具体的协议也越来越近。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;font-size: 14px\">　</span><strong><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;font-size: 14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　各方意见形势翻转</span></span></strong></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;font-size: 14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　从会议自始至终，伊朗的态度始终如一</span>——拒绝冻产。</span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;font-size: 14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　早在周二，伊朗方面就向外界表示，两天时间内针对冻产问题一事达成协议几乎不可能，沙特方面也表示，并不预期会议会达成一致的协议。倒是一向强硬的沙特主动提议两国各自减少日产量各</span>60<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">万桶，不过这一让步并没有得到伊朗的回应。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;font-size: 14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　伊朗和沙特的矛盾早有渊源，今年四月份的欧佩克会议上，各方就冻产问题未能达成统一认识的重要原因，就是伊朗坚持增产。事实上，从</span>4<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月份的日产</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">300</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">万桶，到现在日产</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">360</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">万桶，伊朗已经到达其历史产量的峰值。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;font-size: 14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　除了这两个国家以外，其他国家的意见分歧也不小。委内瑞拉、安哥拉、利比亚和尼日利亚各自都表达了其主张。但总体情况看，这些国家对于冻产均没有强烈的意愿。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;font-size: 14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　值得注意的是，在欧佩克会议召开的前一个月，利比亚将其原油日产量由</span>26<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">万桶上升至</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">45</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">万桶，幅度高达</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">70%</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">。尼日利亚石油部长在会上更是表示，在目前的产量水平达成冻产协议不会有任何意义，并希望免于遵守冻产协议。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;font-size: 14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　这似乎与上次会议形成了强烈的反差。原油生产小国对于冻产协议的态度五个月内发生了</span>180<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">°的反转。“像沙特、伊拉克和伊朗这些国家，目前的生产水平基本都是历史峰值，在这种水平下冻产对于他们影响不大。”卓创资讯分析师高健告诉记者。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;font-size: 14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　而对于那些小国来说，此时冻产意味着今后只能看那些产油大国的脸色行事，无法参与市场份额的竞争。</span>“所以这些小国对于冻产协议的态度已经发生了很大的转变。”高健说。</span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;font-size: 14px\">　</span><strong><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;font-size: 14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　油价持续疲软</span>?</span></strong></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;font-size: 14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　尽管最终没有达成统一的协议，但并不会再对油价有较大负面影响。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;font-size: 14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　就在伊朗宣布希望将其原油产量限制在</span>400<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">万桶</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">/</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">日的水平</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">(</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">这一水平已是伊朗历史峰值</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">)</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">上时，布伦特油价应声上涨</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">2%</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">，截至记者发稿，布伦特原油价格为</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">47.34</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">美元</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">/</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">桶，涨幅</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">1.76%</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;font-size: 14px\">　　“市场对于目前欧佩克产油国之间的矛盾，和冻产协议本身的难度早有预期，所以冻产协议搁浅并不会对油价造成多大的负面影响。”高健说。“预计后市油价基本还是会维持在<span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">40-50</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">美元</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">/</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">桶的区间内。”</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;font-size: 14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　在得到了确切的消息后，市场已经开始期待</span>11<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">30</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">日在维也纳举行的欧佩克会议，而目前的种种迹象表明，对原油市场影响最大的两国——沙特和伊朗，已经开始在动产的问题上达成一定共识。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;font-size: 14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　过去的一年，油价的大幅度下降已经对国际市场和石油工业产生了巨大的影响。而伊朗和沙特能否在冻产甚至减产协议上达成一致，也将决定</span>2017<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年石油市场的命运。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;font-size: 14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　不过，从目前来看，石油行业的问题还将存在。</span>IEA<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">方面就预计，直到</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">2017</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年年底以前，供大于需的情况都不会得到根本性改变。</span></span></p><p><br/></p>','OPEC冻产协议拖延至11月 对油价影响有限','　　石油输出国之间的冻产协议或需要再等几个月了。','1','1','2017-03-11 22:26:53','','0','','','0','{\"thumb\":\"\"}','1','0','0','0','','');INSERT INTO ts_posts ( `id`, `post_author`, `post_keywords`, `post_source`, `post_date`, `post_content`, `post_title`, `post_excerpt`, `post_status`, `comment_status`, `post_modified`, `post_content_filtered`, `post_parent`, `post_type`, `post_mime_type`, `comment_count`, `smeta`, `post_hits`, `post_like`, `istop`, `recommended`, `page_tpl`, `page_tpls` ) VALUES  ('315','1','欧佩克达成减产协议 ','','2017-03-11 22:29:13','<p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;font-size: 14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　石油输出国组织</span>(<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">欧佩克</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">)28</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">日在阿尔及尔举行特别会议，决定将石油日产量减至</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">3250</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">万至</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">3300</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">万桶，以平衡市场供求。受此影响，国际油价</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">28</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">日大幅上涨。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;font-size: 14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　欧佩克当前原油实际产量大约维持在每天</span>3340<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">万桶水平，而欧佩克此前确定的原油产量限额为每天</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">3000</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">万桶。这意味着不少成员国事实上在进行超限额生产。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;font-size: 14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　欧佩克轮值主席、卡塔尔能源和工业大臣萨达在会后举行的新闻发布会上说，欧佩克</span>14<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">个成员国代表经过</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">6</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">个小时的闭门磋商，最终达成协议。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;font-size: 14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　萨达表示，欧佩克将成立一个技术委员会，以确定各成员国的产量配额，具体结果将在</span>11<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月于维也纳召开的正式会议上公布。他还强调，欧佩克将与其他主要产油国加强沟通协商，以尽快达成市场供需平衡。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;font-size: 14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　阿尔及利亚能源部长努尔丁</span>·布塔法在发布会上说，欧佩克国家这次“以一个声音对外说话”，希望欧佩克能恢复在原油市场上的主导作用。</span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;font-size: 14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　受欧佩克成员国达成减产协议影响，国际油价</span>28<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">日大幅上涨。截至当天收盘，纽约商品交易所</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">11</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月交货的轻质原油期货价格上涨</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">2.38</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">美元，收于每桶</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">47.05</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">美元，涨幅为</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">5.33%</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">。</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">11</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月交货的伦敦布伦特原油期货价格上涨</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">2.72</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">美元，收于每桶</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">48.69</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">美元，涨幅为</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">5.92%</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">。</span></span></p><p><br/></p>','欧佩克达成减产协议 国际油价大涨','　　石油输出国组织(欧佩克)28日在阿尔及尔举行特别会议，决定将石油日产量减至3250万至3300万桶，以平衡市场供求。受此影响，国际油价28日大幅上涨。','1','1','2017-03-11 22:28:28','','0','','','0','{\"thumb\":\"\"}','1','0','0','0','','');INSERT INTO ts_posts ( `id`, `post_author`, `post_keywords`, `post_source`, `post_date`, `post_content`, `post_title`, `post_excerpt`, `post_status`, `comment_status`, `post_modified`, `post_content_filtered`, `post_parent`, `post_type`, `post_mime_type`, `comment_count`, `smeta`, `post_hits`, `post_like`, `istop`, `recommended`, `page_tpl`, `page_tpls` ) VALUES  ('316','1','黄金周自驾游带动国内汽油消费','','2017-03-11 22:30:22','<p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;font-size: 14px\">　　“十一”黄金周里，“五元时代”的低油价加上“高速免费”的福利进一步刺激了自驾游热潮，带动国内汽油消费迎来小高峰。与此同时，国际石油市场也热度不减。在产油国冻产协议的持续影响下，时隔一个多月，国际油价重返每桶<span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">50</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">美元上方。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;font-size: 14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　今年</span>8<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">2</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">日，纽约原油期货价格一度跌破每桶</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">40</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">美元。产油国担心国际油价走势再度失控，赶紧抛出了冻产言论。</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">9</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">28</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">日，石油输出国组织</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">(</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">欧佩克</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">)</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">在阿尔及利亚宣布达成冻产协议，决定将石油日产量减至</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">3250</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">万桶至</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">3300</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">万桶。这则消息令前期预期悲观的市场投资者倍感意外。当日国际油价大涨近</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">6%</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;font-size: 14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　进入</span>10<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月，国际市场仍在消化欧佩克冻产协议带来的利好预期。此前，曾被市场认为欧佩克内部增产最迫切的成员国之一的伊朗，</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">10</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">3</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">日出乎意料地呼吁非欧佩克产油国与欧佩克成员国共同稳定并提升国际油价。伊朗的态度继续推动了国际油价上涨。当日，布伦特原油期货价格突破每桶</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">50</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">美元，收于每桶</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">50.89</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">美元，创出近三个月以来的高点。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;font-size: 14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　厦门大学能源经济协同创新中心主任林伯强认为，产油国之间的合作对国际石油市场会产生正面影响，国际油价突破每桶</span>50<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">美元在预期之中。近年来，在低油价的影响下，全球石油上游开发领域投资大幅下滑，而需求仍在稳定增长，预计后期国际油价仍有上行空间。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;font-size: 14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　国际油价的不断高攀，也传导到我国成品油市场。在国庆假期前夕，</span>9<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">30</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">日是我国成品油调价的时间窗口。不过预期中的国内油价“二连降”因为国际油价突然暴涨而落空，最终由于降幅不足每吨</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">50</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">元的门槛而导致调价搁浅。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;font-size: 14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　虽然国内油价无缘</span>“二连降”，但今年“十一”黄金周期间我国汽柴油价格与去年同期相比基本持平，仍处于“五元时代”的低油价水平。以上海地区油价为例，目前<span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">92</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">号汽油零售价格为每升</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">5.89</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">元，比去年同期价格略高</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">0.01</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">元。</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">0</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">号柴油零售价格为每升</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">5.49</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">元，与去年同期持平。而</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">2014</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年同期，上海汽、柴油价格分别为每升</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">7.32</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">元和每升</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">7.22</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">元。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;font-size: 14px\">　　“十一”黄金周是我国传统的旅游旺季，同样也是出行旺季。高速公路在<span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">10</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">1</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">日</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">0</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">时到</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">7</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">日</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">24</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">时对</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">7</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">座及以下</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">(</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">含</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">7</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">座</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">)</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">载客车辆实行免收通行费。“高速免费”的福利加上“五元时代”的低油价进一步助推了自驾游的热潮，进而刺激汽油消费。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;font-size: 14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　在上海生活的刘云英组织了小伙伴们一起自驾回到内蒙古大草原的家乡。</span>“今年国庆期间，汽油价格每升才五块多，前年每升要七块多，算起来路费省了一大笔。”刘云英说。</span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;font-size: 14px\">　　10<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">4</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">日，家住杭州的李澈带着家人自驾到临安的浙西大峡谷游玩，“自己开车路程不到两个小时，可以说走就走。”</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;font-size: 14px\">　　“国庆期间自驾游的火爆带动了国内汽油消费出现小高峰。”能源研究机构中宇资讯成品油分析师许磊表示，其实在节前，国内汽油批发行情已经开始启动涨势。通常在假期结束后，由于汽油库存消耗较大，市场还将迎来一轮补货行情。再加上近期国际油价涨幅较大，预计下轮国内成品油调价上调概率较大，因此，节后成品油批发行情或持续走强。</span></p><p><br/></p>','黄金周自驾游带动国内汽油消费','　　“十一”黄金周里，“五元时代”的低油价加上“高速免费”的福利进一步刺激了自驾游热潮，带动国内汽油消费迎来小高峰。与此同时，国际石油市场也热度不减。在产油国冻产协议的持续影响下，时隔一个多月，国际油价重返每桶50美元上方。','1','1','2017-03-11 22:29:26','','0','','','0','{\"thumb\":\"\"}','0','0','0','0','','');INSERT INTO ts_posts ( `id`, `post_author`, `post_keywords`, `post_source`, `post_date`, `post_content`, `post_title`, `post_excerpt`, `post_status`, `comment_status`, `post_modified`, `post_content_filtered`, `post_parent`, `post_type`, `post_mime_type`, `comment_count`, `smeta`, `post_hits`, `post_like`, `istop`, `recommended`, `page_tpl`, `page_tpls` ) VALUES  ('317','1','油价如何走出暴跌漩涡','','2017-03-12 09:52:07','<p><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　供给过剩的情况下想要抬高油价，或者大量减产，或者提振需求，如此才能返回到供给和需求的平衡状态。</span></span></p><p><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　一个月前</span>(9<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">5</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">日</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">)</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">，全球两大石油生产商沙特阿拉伯和俄罗斯达成协议，表示他们不会立即采取行动，但是未来可能会限制产量，共同应对世界石油市场供给过剩，希望拉高石油价格。当两国能源部长的联合声明发布后，当天油价立刻上升</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">5%</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">，之后获利回吐涨幅为</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">2%</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">。这是</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">8</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年来，欧佩克首次意外达成限产协议，将把每日原油产量缩减至</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">3250</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">万～</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">3300</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">万桶之间，目前的产量估计在每日</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">3324</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">万桶，减产幅度为</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">0.7%</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">～</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">2.2%</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">。</span></span></p><p><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　过去两年油价崩溃，与</span>2014<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">6</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月的水平相比，从某一个点切入的话下跌超过</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">70%</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">以上，去年油价不停地上下起伏，眼下似乎徘徊于每桶</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">40</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">至</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">50</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">美元之间。尽管石油业已设法削减成本，许多油井仍然无利可图。</span></span></p><p><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　虽说油价下降是一个复杂的问题，不过归根究底，还是供求关系这个简单的经济学。过去几年，美国国内产油量几乎翻了一番，迫使石油进口商需要另找买家，像是原本销往美国的沙特、尼日利亚和阿尔及利亚的石油，突然转向亚洲市场，生产商被迫降价。加拿大和伊拉克石油生产和出口，连年攀升，即使是俄罗斯也无视他们的经济问题，产油量保持在创纪录的水平。</span></span></p><p><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　然而，勘探投资回落使得生产下降已有迹可循。据加拿大皇家银行资本市场的计算，仅仅</span>2015<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年，每天具有能力出产</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">50</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">万桶原油的项目，都被欧佩克国家取消、延迟或搁置，今年的产油量有望减产更多。</span></span></p><p><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　此外，石油产出国委内瑞拉因政局不稳，石油产出迅速下降，尼日利亚由于叛军袭击，该地区的石油也削减了供应，利比亚的战火阻碍了该国的石油工业重新站起来。当然，这些波动有可能是短暂的。</span></span></p><p><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　但是在石油的需求方面，欧洲经济体和发展中国家需求薄弱，汽车将朝着更为节能的方向发展。虽然美国和中国的需求有强劲的迹象，但总体来说对于燃料的需求减弱了。</span></span></p><p><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　那么，谁又将从油价下跌中获益呢？</span></span></p><p><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　当然是拥有汽车一族。随着汽油价格的下降，柴油、取暖油和天然气价格也大幅下滑。截至</span>9<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">26</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">日，美国的普通汽油平均每加仑是</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">2.22</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">美元，相比一年前下跌了</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">10</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">美分，从而帮助了低收入群体，因为燃料成本较大份额吃掉了他们的有限收入，比如冬天的取暖油消费下降，从另一个角度增加了储蓄。</span></span></p><p><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　当前，油价直线下降谁的损失最大？当属正在遭受经济、甚至政治动荡的几个产油国如委内瑞拉、尼日利亚、厄瓜多尔、巴西和俄罗斯。因受西方制裁的影响，封锁了伊朗引进西方最新的油田技术和设备，近年来伊朗的石油产量每天下降约一百万桶，现在随着制裁的解除，伊朗的石油工业等于打开了水龙头。</span></span></p><p><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　在美国，现在几乎没有获利的油井可钻。雪佛龙、荷兰皇家壳牌和</span>BP<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">都宣布裁减工资以节省现金，他们的状况比许多独立石油和天然气小生产商好。据埃克森公司公布的报告，其季度的盈利为历史最低水平，近期它的</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">AAA</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">顶级信用评级也被取消了。</span></span></p><p><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　像阿拉斯加、北达科他州、得克萨斯州、俄克拉何马州和路易斯安那州也面临经济挑战。与此同时，下降的天然气价格已转化为提高道路行驶的频率，以致出现了交通死亡人数的上扬。也使许多年轻的沙特人，看到了消失的轻松的工作岗位。</span></span></p><p><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　因此在过去的一年，伊朗、委内瑞拉、厄瓜多尔和阿尔及利亚向欧佩克施压削减产量，以帮助他们抬高油价。与此同时，伊拉克实际上在拼命生产，伊朗根本拒绝冻结生产，再次向海外大量出口石油。</span></span></p><p><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\">　　9<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">28</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">日，欧佩克达成了一个临时协议，在今年晚些时候适度降低生产，但是并没有决定哪些国家必须减产，这个问题将留在十一月维也纳的欧佩克会议上正式决定。市场分析人士表示，在目前石油高产出的情况下设定减产上限，对于调节油价是极其有限的，因为这是全球市场供应过剩的结果。</span></span><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\">&nbsp;</span></p><p><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　因此，在供给过剩的情况下想要抬高油价，或者大量减产，或者提振需求，如此才能返回到供给和需求的平衡状态。以前主要石油产出国的协议之所以被打破，是因为没有强制坚定执行的机制。</span></span></p><p><br/></p>','油价如何走出暴跌漩涡','　　供给过剩的情况下想要抬高油价，或者大量减产，或者提振需求，如此才能返回到供给和需求的平衡状态。','1','1','2017-03-12 09:33:50','','0','','','0','{\"thumb\":\"\"}','1','0','0','0','','');INSERT INTO ts_posts ( `id`, `post_author`, `post_keywords`, `post_source`, `post_date`, `post_content`, `post_title`, `post_excerpt`, `post_status`, `comment_status`, `post_modified`, `post_content_filtered`, `post_parent`, `post_type`, `post_mime_type`, `comment_count`, `smeta`, `post_hits`, `post_like`, `istop`, `recommended`, `page_tpl`, `page_tpls` ) VALUES  ('318','1','国际原油市场现状难以改变','','2017-03-12 09:53:17','<p><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\">　　9<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月底，石油输出国组织</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">(</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">欧佩克</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">)</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">成员国宣布计划在今年</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">11</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月底的部长级会议上讨论将现有产量减少</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">70</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">万桶左右。数据显示，欧佩克</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">9</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月份的产量已经达到</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">3360</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">万桶</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">/</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">天，这是近年来欧佩克产量的最高纪录，较此前欧佩克规定的产能上限多出近</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">75</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">万桶。尽管欧佩克近期决定减产</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">70</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">万桶，也仅为国际原油市场总产能的</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">1%</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">不到。分析指出，如此小规模减产无法对平衡原油市场供求关系产生实际效果。</span></span></p><p><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　数据显示，得克萨斯中质原油</span>(WTI)<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">近日持续在</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">50</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">美元附近震荡盘整；北海布伦特原油也未能保持持续上涨势头，停留在</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">52</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">美元</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">/</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">桶左右的价位上。</span></span></p><p><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　对于欧佩克的减产意向，一部分专家认为，欧佩克的减产协议已经证明，欧佩克试图重新夺回国际原油市场的话语权。市场分析认为，欧佩克此次减产计划更具象征意义，预示着欧佩克将重新开始通过调节产量来平衡油价。但也有观点认为，这份协议仅是意向性的，最终结果还要等到</span>11<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月份部长级会议才能知晓。分析人士认为，这仅仅是欧佩克为了平息市场波动，采取的短期提振油价举措，这样的价格走势并不具有持续性。因此，近期各大金融机构纷纷下调了对今明两年的油价预期，认为今年国际油价仍难超过</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">50</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">美元</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">/</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">桶大关。</span></span></p><p><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　目前市场最关注的问题是，欧佩克能否在</span>11<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月底的部长级会议上就减产问题达成最终一致协议并付诸实施。鉴于此前伊朗与沙特之间的紧张关系，以及伊朗在产量问题上的强硬立场，市场和投资者对此次欧佩克的减产协议持较强的怀疑态度。对于欧佩克而言，“原则上同意减产”这种说法仍然存在很大的变数，特别是目前距下一次部长级会议仍有近两个月的时间，这期间可能发生的变化都会给减产协议带来直接威胁。</span></span></p><p><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　此外，页岩油产能的重新回归，仍是欧佩克决定减产后面临的主要问题。两年前欧佩克做出</span>“不减产”决定的一个重要考量就是遏制页岩油产能的增长，维护欧佩克的市场份额。在未来几个月内，如果国际油价在短期内上涨<span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">10</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">美元左右，则页岩油产能将很快回归。美国页岩油开采企业近年来通过技术创新等途径不断降低开采成本，其生存能力已经得到大幅改善。一旦油价开始上升，这部分产能将很快重回国际市场，届时国际油价又将面临新的下行压力。</span></span></p><p><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　当前，国际原油市场价格涨跌仍然取决于供求关系。欧佩克等产油国的减产措施仅仅是在供给侧作出调整，无法真正控制国际原油市场上的需求。沙特等欧佩克产油国原本希望通过压低油价刺激世界经济增长，从而有效提升国际市场对原油的需求。但过去两年中，世界经济复苏缓慢，国际市场对原油的需求增长十分有限。近期，国际能源机构不断下调世界范围内原油需求增长预期，显示今明两年国际原油市场的需求增长仍不乐观。</span></span></p><p><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　有分析指出，欧佩克此次</span>“重回舞台”给国际原油市场带来的影响十分有限，也不可能在短期内修正过去两年国际原油市场发生的结构性变化。</span></p><p><br/></p>','国际原油市场现状难以改变','　　9月底，石油输出国组织(欧佩克)成员国宣布计划在今年11月底的部长级会议上讨论将现有产量减少70万桶左右。','1','1','2017-03-12 09:52:26','','0','','','0','{\"thumb\":\"\"}','1','0','0','0','','');INSERT INTO ts_posts ( `id`, `post_author`, `post_keywords`, `post_source`, `post_date`, `post_content`, `post_title`, `post_excerpt`, `post_status`, `comment_status`, `post_modified`, `post_content_filtered`, `post_parent`, `post_type`, `post_mime_type`, `comment_count`, `smeta`, `post_hits`, `post_like`, `istop`, `recommended`, `page_tpl`, `page_tpls` ) VALUES  ('319','1','国际油价“高飞” ','','2017-03-12 09:54:13','<p><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　国际油价受益于</span>“限产”协议，连续<span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">7</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">日红盘走高，再次到了</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">50</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">美元关口，自</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">9</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月末至今的累计涨幅为</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">14.5%</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">，机构正在观望产油国</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">10</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月的会议结果。</span></span></p><p><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　十一长假之前，欧佩克限产协议初步达成</span>(<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">在欧佩克</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">8</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月产量的基础上减产</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">79.6</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">万桶</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">/</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">日，将产量限制在</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">3250</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">万</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">~3300</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">万桶</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">/</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">日区间</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">)</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">，助推油价反弹，从</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">9</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月底开始至上周末，已连续大涨了</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">7</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">个交易日，其间纽约原油价格自</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">6</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月英国“脱欧”以来盘中首次突破</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">50</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">美元</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">/</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">桶，上周六报收在</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">49.55</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">美元</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">/</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">桶的位置。</span></span></p><p><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　基本面方面喜忧参半。欧佩克及非欧佩克产油国计划于</span>10<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">8~13</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">日在土耳其召开非正式会议，讨论阿尔及尔协议的实施情况。市场机构一直对欧佩克能否真正实施此协议心存疑虑。虽然俄罗斯表示欧佩克内部达成协议后将参与冻产，但此刻俄罗斯的石油产量也处在高位。因此，在具体细节出台之前，欧佩克产油国和非欧佩克产油国仍将以接近创纪录的产量水平生产石油。一旦新一轮的协议谈判失败，所谓的限产将被搁置，国际油价将受到巨大打击。</span></span></p><p><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　而从技术面图形来看，国际油价在</span>40~50<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">美元之间已经走了五个来回，目前再次走到了多空博弈的关键阻力位</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">50</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">美元，要想突破，需要非常大的动力，而一旦突破，上一个强阻力位高达</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">60</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">美元，距离</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">50</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">美元还有</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">20%</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">的走高空间。广东金矿的油品分析师陈志豪认为：如果“限产”协议顺利达成，国际油价有可能上行至</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">60</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">美元，突破今年以来的区间震荡走势。但如果无法达成，则冲高回落无疑，重回</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">40</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">美元。</span></span></p><p><br/></p>','国际油价“高飞” 再战50美元','　　国际油价受益于“限产”协议，连续7日红盘走高，再次到了50美元关口，自9月末至今的累计涨幅为14.5%，机构正在观望产油国10月的会议结果。','1','1','2017-03-12 09:53:34','','0','','','0','{\"thumb\":\"\"}','1','0','0','0','','');INSERT INTO ts_posts ( `id`, `post_author`, `post_keywords`, `post_source`, `post_date`, `post_content`, `post_title`, `post_excerpt`, `post_status`, `comment_status`, `post_modified`, `post_content_filtered`, `post_parent`, `post_type`, `post_mime_type`, `comment_count`, `smeta`, `post_hits`, `post_like`, `istop`, `recommended`, `page_tpl`, `page_tpls` ) VALUES  ('320','1','OPEC的没落江湖','','2017-03-12 09:55:06','<p><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　在秋意渐凉的地中海滨城市阿尔及尔，石油输出国组织（</span>OPEC<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">）于</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">9</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">28</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">日出人意料地达成了一项限产协议，决定将石油日产量从当前的</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">3340</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">万桶减至</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">3250</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">万到</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">3300</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">万桶，来平衡市场供求，拯救处于泥潭中的国际油价。</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">OPEC</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">表示将成立一个技术委员会，来确定各成员国的产量配额，具体结果将在</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">11</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月份的维也纳会议上公布。待这一限产目标实现后，</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">OPEC</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">还将寻求非</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">OPEC</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">产油国的支持，来共同支撑油价。</span></span></p><p><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　两年前，以沙特为首的</span>OPEC<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">成员国面对国际油价暴跌仍拒绝减产，进而导致国际油价断崖式跌落。</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">2014</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">11</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月至今的</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">OPEC</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">会议一直被各种花言巧语和勾心斗角所充斥，因而此次会议召开前并不被人看好，没想到结果却来了一个大逆转。尽管有许多评论低估此次会议的影响，但市场短期反应还是异常迅速，国际油价连续数日上涨，已越过</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">50</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">美元大关。</span></span></p><p><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　与许多持</span>“然并卵”观点的看法不同，我认为这是<span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">OPEC</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">从消极转向积极、从放任转向有为的一个标志，说明他们的思路和策略已经从保份额为主转向了稳定价格为主。而其中的关键，在于“带头大哥”沙特的态度转变。《石油经济学家》专栏作家德里克·鲍尔斯就表示，从会前的情况来看，沙特对于达成协议的意愿是很强烈的，这是和</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">4</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月份多哈会议最大的不同。</span></span></p><p><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　鲍尔斯的说法并非空穴来风。沙特从去年以来便积极洽谈冻产相关事宜，希望借此应对油价持续下滑所带来的经济压力。但由于其他产油国尤其是</span>“死对头”伊朗坚决拒绝减产，无人配合的情况下，沙特也唱不了“独角戏”，冻产便一直无法从愿景变为现实。而到了现在，沙特的态度更为实际，放下了执念，允许伊朗、利比亚和尼日利亚获得“限产”豁免，从而扫清了达成限产协议的障碍。</span></p><p><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　而沙特的态度变化，说到底，又是经济压力增加和市场份额压力减弱两方面促成的。之前</span>OPEC<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">发动价格战，就是希望用泛滥的供应将美国页岩油气赶出市场，结果美国页岩油并没有很快倒下，战争进入了冗长、缓慢的拉锯过程。油价的低迷影响到世界上所有的石油生产者。从各大石油公司发布的半年业绩来看，上半年除了埃克森美孚等极少数公司外，上游生产者几乎全军尽墨。尽管页岩油气生产商受到很大冲击，一些公司倒闭关门，但战争另一端的</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">OPEC</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">成员国同样损失惨重，实力最雄厚的沙特财经压力也与日俱增，赤字扩大，外汇储备减少。甚至连作为石油竞争者的新能源商马斯克都在抱怨，油价太低对未来不利，因为低油价压制了新能源的发展。这样一个没有胜者的多输局面自然是持续不下去的。</span></span></p><p><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　而在另一方面，</span>OPEC<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">不减产争夺市场份额的策略取得了阶段性成功，中东国家获得</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">35%</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">的市场份额，达到</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">1975</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年来的历史新高。沙特在这个时候出牌，说明他们经过了压力测试，试图通过限产找到油价、市场份额和财政支出的最佳平衡，虽然减产对油价的抬升有利于页岩油气部分复苏，但这部分市场份额完全可以由油价收益来弥补。</span></span></p><p><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　除了页岩油气之外，</span>OPEC<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">的另一个潜在敌人是新能源，中东人对石油命运的关注比任何人都强烈，他们害怕新能源带来的釜底抽薪式的石油灾难。但从目前的情况来看，新能源发展得并没有那么可怕，短期内还不可能撼动石油的地位，</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">OPEC</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">产油国将地下资源变现的心态没那么强烈。而全球油气投资下降厉害，稳定油价也就间接稳定了投资预期，如果投资短缺导致未来几年油价短期蹿升，刺激新能源加速发展，这是沙特所不愿看到的。</span></span></p><p><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　同样值得注意的是，此次会议是在</span>OPEC<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">主要产油国产量均达到历史峰值的背景下开始的，沙特、伊拉克、伊朗、阿联酋等国此前都加大了马力生产，以便获得更优越的谈判条件和占据更多市场份额，之前产量中断的尼日利亚与利比亚也在逐渐恢复出口。在产量增长空间不大而油价持续低迷的情况下，</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">OPEC</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">国家的意见分歧逐步缩小，是什么都不做而坐视油价崩盘，还是适当限产来稳定市场，对于</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">OPEC</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">来说是一个并不太难的选择题。而且，由于季节的原因，夏天过后本来就面临减产，现在是达成共识的最佳时机。</span></span></p><p><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　一个相对温和的油价才是各方最大的合意。所有的生产者，最终的目的都是为了把生产出来的石油换成真金白银，其他的一切都不过是手段和策略。对于全球石油市场来说，最坏的时刻可能已经过去，限产有望把市场实现再平衡的时间提前。当然不容忽视的是，限产协议目前仍有大量问题待解，譬如协议的执行时间、限产的具体额度和执行速度等等，各国的小九九更是一刻也没有停过，谁也不知道会有什么变数。一旦处理不当，都可能给油价复苏蒙上阴影。</span></span></p><p><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　对于市场来说，此次限产究竟带来怎样的效应，除了要关注</span>11<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月份维也纳会议确定的细节，以及</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">OPEC</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">成员国的执行情况，还需要密切关注沙特等主要产油国产量与出口量的关系，因为沙特等国由于国内天然气替代等原因，产量减少并不意味着出口量同步减少，在出口量不变甚至增加的情况下，限产等于是虚晃了一枪。此外，限产协议要对油价产生实质影响，俄罗斯等非</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">OPEC</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">产油国的支持也不可或缺，但俄罗斯暧昧的态度，让人依然无法乐观。</span></span></p><p><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　显而易见的是，</span>OPEC<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">试图重新回到市场管理者的角色，夺回被页岩油抢去的话事权。这是一个曾经叱诧风云、鏖战江湖许多年的“老炮儿”的挣扎与回归。它曾经挑战旧的规则，建立了自己主导的“江湖秩序”，眼下这一套秩序也已经分崩离析，石油世界已经发生了翻天覆地的变化。这不是石油危机的时代，也已经没有了亚马尼那样德高望重的人物，</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">OPEC</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">的影响力已不大如前，页岩油气却在高歌猛进，它们的快速复产能力和金融运作技巧，令</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">OPEC</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">寝食难安。</span></span></p><p><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　历经艰辛达成的限产协议，饱含着</span>“老炮儿”捍卫昔日尊严和荣光的志向，但仍旧难掩其落寞。就像阿尔帕西诺主演的那部老电影《情枭的黎明》，曾经的黑道老大从狱中出来，却发现世道已经变了，过去的一套行不通了。</span></p><p><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　在江湖的游戏规则里，从来都是新的战胜旧的，新事物只有比上一代更生猛，他们生存发展的力量才能够超过保守的力量，成为又一个时代的强者，这是一种弱肉强食的自然选择。曾经的</span>OPEC<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">之于“七姊妹”是如此，今天的页岩油气之于</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">OPEC</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">，也同样如此。</span></span></p><p><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\">　　“老炮儿”这种旧时代的人物在和新时代交汇时的无力、没落和那种不甘心，更多是在提醒人们，是建立石油世界新的规则和新的治理体系的时候了，摆脱江湖周期律带来的剧烈变动，建立更良性、更透明的治理秩序，创造石油市场的多赢正和格局。这样我们期望的，就不仅仅是限产带来价格反弹的喘息之机，而是一个更稳定、更均衡、更持续发展的市场。</span></p><p><br/></p>','OPEC的没落江湖','　　在秋意渐凉的地中海滨城市阿尔及尔，石油输出国组织（OPEC）于9月28日出人意料地达成了一项限产协议，决定将石油日产量从当前的3340万桶减至3250万到3300万桶，来平衡市场供求，拯救处于泥潭中的国际油价。','1','1','2017-03-12 09:54:24','','0','','','0','{\"thumb\":\"\"}','1','0','0','0','','');INSERT INTO ts_posts ( `id`, `post_author`, `post_keywords`, `post_source`, `post_date`, `post_content`, `post_title`, `post_excerpt`, `post_status`, `comment_status`, `post_modified`, `post_content_filtered`, `post_parent`, `post_type`, `post_mime_type`, `comment_count`, `smeta`, `post_hits`, `post_like`, `istop`, `recommended`, `page_tpl`, `page_tpls` ) VALUES  ('321','1','国际石油市场没有供给侧改革','','2017-03-12 09:56:19','<p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　石油市场当前面临的困境是世界经济以往</span>“资源国<span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">-</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">生产国</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">-</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">消费国”的模式难以持续，从旧均衡向新均衡过渡的过程中出现的系列问题之一，并非特例，类似的症状和困境在其他国家、其他行业也多有体现。例如中国煤炭、钢铁、平板玻璃、水泥等行业也出现了产能过剩，价格大幅下跌的情况；这些行业中很多传统生产企业也面临着盈利能力下滑、债务风险积聚的问题，其中一些甚至出现了现金流难以维系的情况，面临破产清算的风险。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　应对产能过剩的办法大体可分为两种。一种是通过市场机制自发调节，让过剩产能在市场竞争中被淘汰；另一种是通过外力干预来推进去产能化。不妨拿动物机体出现毒瘤来打比方。第一种办法就像是依靠机体自身免疫系统消化毒瘤，第二种办法则像是通过做外科手术挖出毒瘤，两种办法各有优缺点。但如果毒瘤很严重，通过自身免疫力很难治愈或者需要很长时间，承受巨大创伤，做手术就是更好的选择。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　针对相关行业的产能过剩问题，中国政府果断提出了</span>“去产能”的政策导向。对涉及到的企业、行业、区域经济而言，去产能带来的痛苦可以说是割肉，用“壮士断腕的决心”来形容并不夸张。有人或许会想：产能已经严重过剩，价格持续走低、利润削薄甚至变负，痛在何处？值得注意的是，即便是割去赘肉或毒瘤，也是一个痛苦的过程。如果没有行政的外力干预，产能过剩行业的企业很难有主动割肉的勇气，国际石油市场就是一个典型的例子。</span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　去产能的要害是打破</span>“囚徒困境”。石油生产国面临着“囚徒困境”——对于任何一个产油国而言，不论其他产油国减产与否，不减产都是最优选择，因此所谓的冻产协议或限产协议很难达成。</span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　去产能的要害就是要打破上述</span>“囚徒困境”，设计激励相容的激励机制让各方愿意遵守协议缩减产量。然而，在石油生产国之间现在并不存在这样的机制。</span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　在经济学理论上，打破囚徒困境的另外一个机制是通过无限多次重复博弈中的</span>“威胁”。产油国之间的博弈的确是无限多次重复博弈。历史上，沙特作为欧佩克内部影响力最大的成员国也确实曾以其他成员国无法承受之重的“威胁”来确保各方遵守限产协议，从而打破了囚徒困境。但从当前国际政治和经济的现实情况来看，沙特既不具备这样的实力，也不具备这样的意愿。</span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　作为一个大型的石油净进口国，中国不必要对</span>“别人的问题”过度担忧，毕竟油价下跌对中国经济整体而言不是坏事。但中国应当以邻为鉴，解决好自己的问题，努力在短期和长期两个层面做好产能过剩行业的产能去化和结构性改革。</span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　仔细对比上述行业，会发现一个有趣的特点，即这些行业的产品同质化倾向比较严重。尽管在密度、杂质含量等技术指标上存在差异，但整体来看不同产油国供给的石油可以看做是同质的、标准化的商品。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　如果一个行业的产品同质化比较严重，那么企业之间的竞争往往就只能通过打</span>“价格战”的方式来进行。因此在现实中大宗商品行业的价格波动往往是非常剧烈的，尤其是在下行周期往往会出现暴跌。</span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　面对产能过剩，中国政府选择采用行政手段强推去产能，但政府去产能比市场去产能更有效吗？煤炭、钢铁、水泥等产能过剩行业存在的核心困境与石油行业当前面临的困境类似，即如果在完全竞争的市场环境下，大家都缺乏激励主动减产，陷入了</span>“囚徒困境”。</span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　经济学理论中反对政府干预的一个常见理由是：市场机制能够识别好企业和坏企业，而政府难以做到这一点。但这一理由在当前的去产能过程中并不成立</span>——政府当然很难判断哪家初创企业会成为<span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">15</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年后的阿里巴巴或者谷歌；事实上即便是风投都很难判断，而是通过风险分散机制来解决这一问题的。但庆幸的是，判断同质的煤矿或水泥厂中哪一家更加高效还是比较容易的。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　市场与政府的关系是现实经济研究中无法回避的一个问题。相比于思想实验中</span>“完美的市场”而言，行政力量主导的去杠杆可能会造成一定的效率损失。但在特定的情况下，这种选择是优于市场的。因为在真实世界的经济学中，市场并不完美，至少是在一定的时间内并不完美。真实世界中的经济学不是“比较静态”，我们必须考虑从旧均衡点到新均衡点之间的过渡期。</span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　去产能政策实践的困难已经不在于</span>“效率”，而是在于“公平”或“平等”。去产能政策的纠结点常常不在于经济学分析，而在于决策者对公平的拿捏。<span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">(</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">作者系中国社会科学院财经战略研究院、清华大学中国与世界经济研究中心研究员</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">)</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\">&nbsp;</span></p><p><br/></p>','冯煦明：国际石油市场没有供给侧改革','　　石油市场当前面临的困境是世界经济以往“资源国-生产国-消费国”的模式难以持续，从旧均衡向新均衡过渡的过程中出现的系列问题之一，并非特例，类似的症状和困境在其他国家、其他行业也多有体现。','1','1','2017-03-12 09:55:18','','0','','','0','{\"thumb\":\"\"}','1','0','0','0','','');INSERT INTO ts_posts ( `id`, `post_author`, `post_keywords`, `post_source`, `post_date`, `post_content`, `post_title`, `post_excerpt`, `post_status`, `comment_status`, `post_modified`, `post_content_filtered`, `post_parent`, `post_type`, `post_mime_type`, `comment_count`, `smeta`, `post_hits`, `post_like`, `istop`, `recommended`, `page_tpl`, `page_tpls` ) VALUES  ('322','1','深化油气体制改革若干意见或将年内出台','','2017-03-12 09:57:30','<p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　经过近两个月时间的征求意见，</span>10<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">12</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">日，国家发改委在其官方网站正式公布《天然气管道运输价格管理办法</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">(</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">试行</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">)</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">》和《天然气管道运输定价成本监审办法</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">(</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">试行</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">)</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">》，明确按照“准许成本加合理收益”的原则定价，给予投资收益率</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">8%</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">，而且明确要求经营天然气管输的企业原则上应将管道运输业务与其他业务分离，暂不能实现业务分离的，应当实现管道运输业务财务独立核算。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　值得注意的是，在一个半月的时间里出台的油气管输环节重头文件已达四个。据国家发改委有关负责人介绍，</span>2017<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年将全面启动管输企业定价成本监审工作。在业内人士看来，这一系列动作标志着天然气价格改革将迈出“管住中间”的第一步，也就是为油气改革方案落地铺路。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　据了解，目前深化石油天然气体制改革的若干意见已经过数轮修改，近期有业内人士透露将在年内出台，最终改革目标是</span>“十三五”期间实现政府只监管自然垄断的管网输配气价格，气源和销售价格两头放开。</span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　当前，我国天然气中游输配环节高度集中在中石油、中石化和中海油三大国有石油公司手中。在保证国际长约和自己销售利益的情况下，</span>“三桶油”天然不具备开放基础设施的积极性。而且，当前管网管理体制复杂，多个环节层层加价。</span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　此外，</span>“现行天然气管道运输价格多数实行‘一线一价’，随着管道建设速度加快和供气安全要求提高，越来越多的管道连接成网，现行定价方法已不能适应形势发展需要。”上述负责人表示。</span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　在此背景下，改革后的管道运输价格机制中，将监管对象从单条管道变为管道运输企业，原来运用建设项目财务评价原理监管管道运输价格为主的定价方法，也调整为按照</span>“准许成本加合理收益”的原则定价。与征求意见稿相比，此次正式出台的文件进一步明确了<span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">8%</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">的准许收益率为税后全投资收益率、负荷率按</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">75%</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">计算。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\">　　“这意味着如果管道运输企业实际负荷率低于<span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">75%</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">，则实际收益率可能达不到</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">8%</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">甚至更低，只有加大向第三方开放力度、提高负荷率，才能获得准许收益甚至更高的收益水平。”国家发改委有关负责人表示，两个《办法》的出台，率先在重要网络型自然垄断领域实现价格监管办法和成本监审办法的全覆盖，将对国内天然气市场建设和相关行业发展产生深远影响，有利于激发社会资本投资建设管道积极性，推进天然气价格市场化改革。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　值得注意的是，两个《办法》还明确要求经营天然气管道运输业务的企业，原则上应将管道运输业务与其他业务分离，暂不能实现业务分离的，应当实现管道运输业务财务独立核算。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　这被视为油气改革中管网独立的第一步。按照此前的油气改革思路和征求意见稿的说法，管网独立采取分步走的路径，先在</span>“三桶油”内部实现管输业务的相对独立，业务和上游、下游彻底分离，资产和人员从母公司分离，财务独立核算，制定出管网无歧视向第三方放开的实施办法以及监管制度。等时机成熟，可以实现法律独立、统一调度等后续步骤。</span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　今年以来，国家出台了一系列加强天然气管网输配价格监管的政策措施，此前还印发了《关于加强地方天然气管网输配价格监管降低企业用气成本的通知》，《关于做好油气管网设施开放相关信息公开工作的通知》，构建起天然气产业链从长输管道到省内短途运输管道，再到城市配气管网的全流程价格监管体系。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　上述负责人透露，</span>2017<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年将全面启动管道运输企业定价成本监审工作，合理确定定价成本，制定和调整天然气管道运输价格。同时，督促地方切实加强输配价格监管，合理制定和调整地方天然气管网输配价格。此外，根据在实践中的运行情况，适时对两个《办法》进行完善，并结合国内天然气市场发展情况，积极开展“两部制”价格、热值计价等研究工作，条件成熟时推出。</span></span></p><p><br/></p>','深化油气体制改革若干意见或将年内出台','　　经过近两个月时间的征求意见，10月12日，国家发改委在其官方网站正式公布《天然气管道运输价格管理办法(试行)》和《天然气管道运输定价成本监审办法(试行)》，明确按照“准许成本加合理收益”的原则定价，给予投资收益率8%，而且明确要求经营天然气管输的企业原则上应将管道运输业务与其他业务分离，暂不能实现业务分离的，应当实现管道运输业务财务独立核算。','1','1','2017-03-12 09:56:36','','0','','','0','{\"thumb\":\"\"}','1','0','0','0','','');INSERT INTO ts_posts ( `id`, `post_author`, `post_keywords`, `post_source`, `post_date`, `post_content`, `post_title`, `post_excerpt`, `post_status`, `comment_status`, `post_modified`, `post_content_filtered`, `post_parent`, `post_type`, `post_mime_type`, `comment_count`, `smeta`, `post_hits`, `post_like`, `istop`, `recommended`, `page_tpl`, `page_tpls` ) VALUES  ('323','1','成品油调价窗口开启 ','','2017-03-12 09:59:05','<p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　受产油国纷纷表态支持石油输出国组织</span>(OPEC)<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">减少生产以提高油价的消息影响，近日国际油价整体保持强劲上升势头，也令市场看涨国内成品油走势。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　下一轮国内成品油调价窗口将在</span>10<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">19</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">日</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">24</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">时打开。目前计价周期仅过半，相关机构已抛出观点称，成品油零售价上调的概率较大。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\">　　“目前影响国际油价的关键因素仍围绕于俄罗斯、<span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">OPEC</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">能否如愿减产。不管后续发展如何，本轮计价周期国际原油整体均价已被拉高。”卓创资讯成品油分析师秦文平对记者表示，虽然计价周期才过半，基于国际原油基本面走势平稳，预计新一轮成品油零售价涨幅将被大幅刷新。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　卓创数据显示，截至</span>11<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">日欧美原油期货收盘，主要参考油种变化率为</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">10.62%</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">，对应汽柴油上涨幅度为</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">335</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">元</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">/</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">吨。此前，年内国内汽柴油零售价格最大涨幅出现在</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">5</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">25</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">日</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">24</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">时，汽柴油分别上涨</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">210</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">元</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">/</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">吨和</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">200</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">元</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">/</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">吨。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　除成品油零售价格即将调涨外，国庆节前后国内成品油批发价格也出现明显上扬。十一长假过后，用油客户不断追涨补库，国内三桶油销售公司及民营炼厂汽柴油涨幅普遍在</span>200<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">元</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">/</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">吨以上。西南个别地区中石油、中石化柴油批发价格一度上调</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">750</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">元</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">/</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">吨，从区内最低价区跃至区内最高价区。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　卓创资讯认为，当前国内成品油批发和零售市场一方面要参照基本面的现状，另一方面与国际原油走势的正相关性也表现得淋漓尽致。可以说国际原油的不断上涨，成就了</span>2016<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年国内成品油为数不多的一波“高涨”行情。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　生意社成品油分析师卢兴俊认为，国际油价将继续在</span>50<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">美元</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">/</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">桶关口以上运行，新一轮国内成品油价格存上调预期。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　截至北京时间</span>12<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">日</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">17</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">点</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">10</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">分，布伦特原油期货价格报</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">52.75</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">美元</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">/</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">桶，</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">WTI</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">原油期货价格为</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">50.98</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">美元</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">/</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">桶，均呈小幅上涨。</span></span></p><p><br/></p>','成品油调价窗口开启 机构预测价格将上调','　　受产油国纷纷表态支持石油输出国组织(OPEC)减少生产以提高油价的消息影响，近日国际油价整体保持强劲上升势头，也令市场看涨国内成品油走势。','1','1','2017-03-12 09:58:05','','0','','','0','{\"thumb\":\"\"}','1','0','0','0','','');INSERT INTO ts_posts ( `id`, `post_author`, `post_keywords`, `post_source`, `post_date`, `post_content`, `post_title`, `post_excerpt`, `post_status`, `comment_status`, `post_modified`, `post_content_filtered`, `post_parent`, `post_type`, `post_mime_type`, `comment_count`, `smeta`, `post_hits`, `post_like`, `istop`, `recommended`, `page_tpl`, `page_tpls` ) VALUES  ('324','1','油气开发等领域将进一步向民间投资开放','','2017-03-12 10:00:27','<p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　国家发改委</span>12<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">日印发《促进民间投资健康发展若干政策措施》</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">(</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">以下简称《政策措施》</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">)</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">。《政策措施》提出，研究制订“地方政府偿还欠款计划”。对于依法依规应由地方政府偿还的拖欠企业的工程款、物资采购款、保证金等，督促地方政府制定分期还款计划。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　《政策措施》强调，确保各类投资主体进入社会服务领域一视同仁。在医疗、养老、教育等民生领域完善已有的配套政策，出台实质性措施。重点解决民办养老机构在设立许可、土地使用、医保对接、金融支持、人才培养等方面的难题，民营医院在职称晋升、政府补贴、土地使用等方面的突出困难，民办学校在办学资格、职称评定等方面的突出矛盾。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　《政策措施》提出，进一步放开民间投资市场准入。按照国务院两个</span>“<span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">36</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">条”、一个“</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">39</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">条”要求，进一步开放民用机场、基础电信运营、油气勘探开发、配售电、国防科技等领域，市场准入对各类投资主体要一视同仁，鼓励民间投资进入；大力推广政府和社会资本合作</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">(PPP)</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">模式，进一步完善公共服务和基础设施领域鼓励民间投资参与的政策措施。研究出台相关行业、领域的</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">PPP</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">实施细则，切实解决民企与国企公平竞争问题，鼓励民间资本进入公共服务和基础设施领域。加快推动相关立法工作，明确适用范围、条件和程序，去除不合理门槛，保障各方的合法权益；抓紧建立市场准入负面清单制度。在部分地区试点的基础上，进一步明确市场准入负面清单以外的行业、领域、业务等，各类市场主体皆可依法平等进入；加快推动投资项目在线审批监管平台建设；加快修订政府核准的投资项目目录。</span></span></p><p><br/></p>','油气开发等领域将进一步向民间投资开放','　　国家发改委12日印发《促进民间投资健康发展若干政策措施》(以下简称《政策措施》)。《政策措施》提出，研究制订“地方政府偿还欠款计划”。','1','1','2017-03-12 09:59:48','','0','','','0','{\"thumb\":\"\"}','1','0','0','0','','');INSERT INTO ts_posts ( `id`, `post_author`, `post_keywords`, `post_source`, `post_date`, `post_content`, `post_title`, `post_excerpt`, `post_status`, `comment_status`, `post_modified`, `post_content_filtered`, `post_parent`, `post_type`, `post_mime_type`, `comment_count`, `smeta`, `post_hits`, `post_like`, `istop`, `recommended`, `page_tpl`, `page_tpls` ) VALUES  ('325','1','欧佩克新协议或为油市注入强心剂','','2017-03-12 10:01:52','<p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\">　　9<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">28</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">日欧佩克</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">(OPEC)</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">非正式会议后，该组织秘书长表示，该组织成员国达成了新的原油生产配额，决定将欧佩克产量上限维持在</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">3250</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">万～</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">3300</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">万桶</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">/</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">日的水平，意味着欧佩克需在当前产量水平减产</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">20</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">万～</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">70</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">万桶</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">/</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">日。这也是自</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">2008</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年以来欧佩克首次达成新的原油生产配额，引发石油市场强烈反响，国际油价自</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">9</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">28</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">日以来，累计反弹</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">7%</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">左右。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><strong><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;font-size: 14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　新协议细节不同以往具体方案有待研究</span></span></strong></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　从历史来看，欧佩克的产量配额往往是一个绝对数，如此前形成的</span>3000<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">万桶</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">/</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">日配额，但这次商议的配额却是一个区间值。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　从实际产量来看，今年</span>1<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">～</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">8</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月欧佩克全部成员国平均原油产量为</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">3286</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">万桶</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">/</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">日，其中</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">7</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月份原油产量为</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">3326</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">万桶</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">/</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">日，</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">8</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月份原油产量为</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">3324</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">万桶</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">/</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">日。也就是说当前产量超出上限</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">20</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">万～</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">70</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">万桶</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">/</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">日，意味着如果正式实施产量上限，欧佩克需减产</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">20</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">万～</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">70</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">万桶</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">/</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">日。此外，近期阿尔及利亚石油部长称，</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">11</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">30</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">日欧佩克成员国可能决定在新配额基础上再削减</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">1%</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">，即最终达成</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">100</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">万桶</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">/</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">日左右的削减幅度。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　这次达成的生产配额并未具体分配到每个成员国。市场消息称，考虑到实际情况，利比亚、尼日利亚等国享有豁免权，即可以不遵守限产或者减产的协议。业内人士分析，从</span>1<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">～</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">8</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月的情况来看，伊朗原油产量为</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">340</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">万桶</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">/</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">日，同比大增</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">58</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">万桶</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">/</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">日；伊拉克为</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">429</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">万桶</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">/</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">日，同比增加</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">52</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">万桶</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">/</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">日；沙特为</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">1030</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">万桶</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">/</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">日，同比增加</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">21</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">万桶</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">/</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">日。这三国原油产量增量合计达到</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">131</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">万桶</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">/</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">日，甚至高于该组织原油产量增量的总和。因此，沙特、伊朗和伊拉克三国</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">(</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">尤其是沙特和伊朗</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">)</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">的态度，成为欧佩克能否最终落实新配额协议的关键。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　从限产协议落实来看，欧佩克计划成立技术委员会来研究限产具体方案，并有望在</span>11<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">30</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">日该组织部长级会议上确认各国的产量配额、决定限产开始时间和实施期限。此外，主要产油国的代表还将于近日在土耳其伊斯坦布尔举行非正式会谈，主要目的是商谈如何落实限产协议，以便为</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">11</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">30</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">日会议奠定基础。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\">　　</span><strong><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;font-size: 14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">配额协议远超预期欧佩克政策或做重大调整</span></span></strong></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　欧佩克近</span>8<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年来首次达成新的配额协议，远超出市场预期，一定程度上可能意味着该组织核心成员国在石油政策方面的立场达成了妥协，由从过去两年来的“维护自身市场份额”转变为“共同限产保价”。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　业内人士分析，这一政策调整的背后，首先是欧佩克成员国饱受低油价之苦已有两年之久，多个成员国出现入不敷出、经济滑坡、失业骤增等现象，严重威胁经济社会稳定。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　其次，在与美国页岩油较量的两年多时间里，页岩油表现出了更顽强的韧性和抗击力，实际产量下降远低于预期，欧佩克在这场常规能源与非常规能源的对决中并未取得实质性胜利。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　再次，当前沙特、伊朗、伊拉克等主要成员国产量均提高至历史最高水平，尤其伊朗原油产量基本恢复至制裁前水平，具备与沙特等国共同限产的条件。因此，在这三个背景下该组织做出策略调整，也有其现实意义所在。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　从日程表安排来看，如果欧佩克在</span>11<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">30</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">日会议上决定减产</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">70</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">万桶</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">/</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">日左右，并在明年</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">1</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">1</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">日起开始严格执行，这将加速世界石油市场再平衡。业内人士预计，明年一季度，世界石油市场供不足需</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">80</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">万桶</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">/</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">日，有助于消化目前经合组织国家高企的石油库存，从而加速石油市场再平衡的过程。但同时也要注意到，油价上涨将为美国页岩油等非欧佩克生产商提供增产条件，进而使得石油市场再平衡过程可能出现反复。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\">　</span><strong><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;font-size: 14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　供过于求程度减弱油价有望企稳回升</span></span></strong></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　这次欧佩克超预期达成新的配额，大幅提振了市场多头情绪，对国际油价构成较强支撑。尽管此次欧佩克非正式会议尚没有做出实质性的政策决议，但欧佩克主席在会后释放出的信号，使得该组织在</span>11<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">30</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">日欧佩克会议上达成新的产量配额协议的可能性明显增加，有助于支撑国际油价反弹至</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">55</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">美元</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">/</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">桶附近水平。投资银行高盛甚至表示，如果欧佩克严格执行限产协议，明年上半年油价可能上涨</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">7</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">～</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">10</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">美元</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">/</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">桶。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　值得注意的是，尽管这次会议欧佩克称达成了限产协议，但是，若欧佩克主要成员国对给予自身的产量配额难以接受，欧佩克在</span>11<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">30</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">日的会议上不能达成新的产量配额的可能性仍然存在。此外，即使达成了新的产量配额协议，但没有约束力的话，该限产协议的执行将大打折扣。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　业内人士分析，即使欧佩克没能在</span>11<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">30</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">日的会议上达成最终有约束力的协议，鉴于当前世界石油市场供过于求的程度已大为减弱，全球石油库存上涨的局面较过去两年明显放缓，届时国际油价大幅下挫的可能性不大，预计今年四季度布伦特首行期货价格在</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">45</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">～</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">55</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">美元</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">/</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">桶区间波动的概率较大。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\">&nbsp;</span></p><p><br/></p>','欧佩克新协议或为油市注入强心剂','　　9月28日欧佩克(OPEC)非正式会议后，该组织秘书长表示，该组织成员国达成了新的原油生产配额，决定将欧佩克产量上限维持在3250万～3300万桶/日的水平，意味着欧佩克需在当前产量水平减产20万～70万桶/日。','1','1','2017-03-12 10:00:39','','0','','','0','{\"thumb\":\"\"}','1','0','0','0','','');INSERT INTO ts_posts ( `id`, `post_author`, `post_keywords`, `post_source`, `post_date`, `post_content`, `post_title`, `post_excerpt`, `post_status`, `comment_status`, `post_modified`, `post_content_filtered`, `post_parent`, `post_type`, `post_mime_type`, `comment_count`, `smeta`, `post_hits`, `post_like`, `istop`, `recommended`, `page_tpl`, `page_tpls` ) VALUES  ('326','1','9月全国进口煤炭同比增长37.54%','','2017-03-12 10:02:46','<p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　据海关总署</span>10<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">13</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">日公布的数据显示，中国</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">9</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月份进口煤炭</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">2444</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">万吨，同比增加</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">667</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">万吨，增长</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">37.54%</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">；环比减少</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">215</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">万吨，下降</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">8.09%</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　自</span>2013<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年以后，我国煤炭进口量呈逐年下降态势，且降幅有明显扩大。</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">2013</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年底，进口量创历史新高，高达</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">3.27</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">亿吨，占全国煤炭消费量的</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">9.1%</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">；</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">2014</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年底，进口量</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">2.91</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">亿吨，同比下降</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">11%</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">，占全国煤炭消费量的</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">8.3%</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">；</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">2015</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年底，进口量降至</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">2.04</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">亿吨，降幅近</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">30%</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">，占全国煤炭消费量仅为</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">5.1%</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">，占比达到近几年低点。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\">　　2014<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年年底煤炭行业脱困联席会议上，国家发改委曾建议主要发电企业减少进口动力煤，财政部甚至调整了动力煤进口关税。随后，进口煤在我国煤炭总供给中的占比不断下滑。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　然而今年以来，随着去产能的开展，产地煤炭供应量随之收缩，同时国内煤价大幅上涨，使得进口煤重新受到青睐，下游采购订货增加，进口量在近几个月出现持续递增的情况。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\">　　2016<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年除</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">1</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月、</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">2</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月、</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">4</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月、</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">7</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月外同比小幅下降以外，其他月份均同比上涨，且涨幅较大。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\">　　9<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月份煤炭进口额为</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">123123.7</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">万美元，同比增长</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">25.95%</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">，环比下降</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">10.11%</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">。据此推算进口单价为</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">50.38</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">美元</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">/</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">吨，环比增长</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">1.1</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">美元</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">/</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">吨，同比下跌</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">3.5</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">美元</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">/</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">吨。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\">　　1-9<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月中国累计进口煤炭</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">18018</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">万吨，同比增长</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">15.2%</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">。总金额</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">885988.5</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">万美元，同比下降</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">8.1%</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">。</span></span></p><p><br/></p>','9月全国进口煤炭同比增长37.54%','　　据海关总署10月13日公布的数据显示，中国9月份进口煤炭2444万吨，同比增加667万吨，增长37.54%；环比减少215万吨，下降8.09%。','1','1','2017-03-12 10:02:03','','0','','','0','{\"thumb\":\"\"}','0','0','0','0','','');INSERT INTO ts_posts ( `id`, `post_author`, `post_keywords`, `post_source`, `post_date`, `post_content`, `post_title`, `post_excerpt`, `post_status`, `comment_status`, `post_modified`, `post_content_filtered`, `post_parent`, `post_type`, `post_mime_type`, `comment_count`, `smeta`, `post_hits`, `post_like`, `istop`, `recommended`, `page_tpl`, `page_tpls` ) VALUES  ('327','1','海底石油开发成为中巴合作新亮点','','2017-03-12 10:03:39','<p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　海底石油是埋藏于海洋底层以下的沉积岩及基岩中的矿产资源之一，目前海上原油产量已占世界总量的相当比重。近年来，中国和巴西在海底石油开发领域的合作发展迅速，成为中巴经贸合作新亮点。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　中国和巴西同为海洋大国，科学开发海洋资源，加强海洋石油开发合作，是两国经贸合作的重要组成部分。</span>13<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">日，在由中海油巴西公司主办的海洋石油知识研讨会上，中国驻里约热内卢总领馆商务参赞白春晖表示，中巴石油合作前景广阔，通过普及海洋石油的基础知识，可以吸引更多中国企业参与中巴石油合作。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　在世界能源版图中，巴西是一个新兴深海石油大国。</span>2007<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年以来，巴西在东南部水域持续发现盐下层石油储藏。截至</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">2013</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">8</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月，巴西已探明油气储量</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">831</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">亿桶，在南美国家中位居第二，仅次于委内瑞拉。位于巴西东南部海域的里贝拉区块面积超过</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">1500</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">平方公里，为全球石油开采规模最大的海上油田之一。根据巴西石油管理局公布的预测数字，这一区域拥有高达</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">120</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">亿桶的可开采原油储量，开发后最高产量可达每天</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">140</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">万桶。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　中海油专家介绍说，与陆上石油开发相比，深海石油开发难度更大，具有高科技、高投资、高风险和高收益等特点。自</span>1967<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年中国首口工业油井在渤海湾建成以来，中国海洋石油快速发展，实现海上钻井从浅水到超深水开采的巨大跨越。与此同时，中国油企积极“走出去”，参与到以深水开采为代表的全球海上油气勘探开发，尤其是大力发展与巴西的盐下层石油开发合作。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\">　　2013<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年底，位于里约州外海桑托斯盆地的里贝拉区块顺利唱标，由巴西石油公司</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">(</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">巴油</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">)</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">、英荷壳牌、法国道达尔以及中海油、中石油两家中国油企组成的联合体作为唯一投标方中标。巴西石油管理局预计，该区块在开采合同签署</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">5</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年后可开始产油，届时整个区块日产量有望达到</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">140</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">万桶。在中标联合体中，巴油担任唯一作业者并持有</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">40%</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">的权益，两家中企各持有</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">10%</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">的权益，合约期限为</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">35</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　截至目前，里贝拉区块勘探开发进展顺利。据巴油披露的信息，里贝拉项目西北部已被证实为一个油层厚、规模大的</span>10<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">亿吨级储量巨型油田。深海石油开发投资巨大，但回报也相当丰厚。两家中国油企进入巴西油气市场，带动了众多上下游企业共同发展。从十多年前为巴西铺设油气运输管道开始，中国已经变成巴西深海石油开发的重要合作伙伴。除了中海油、中石化等几家主要油企，多家相关企业也先后进入巴西寻求发展。最新统计数字显示，今年中国将成为巴西在石油领域的最大贸易伙伴。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　最近，巴西政府取消了在盐下层石油开发中必须由巴油主导的限制。对国际石油公司来说，这无疑是一个巨大的利好消息。中海油巴西公司总经理盛建波表示，巴西深海油气资源丰富，勘探开发技术比较先进，再加上巴西整体政治环境比较稳定，外界对巴西油气市场比较看好。他预计，巴西取消在盐下层石油开发中的限制条件，将推动众多国际公司前来巴西发展。</span></span></p><p><br/></p>','海底石油开发成为中巴合作新亮点','　　海底石油是埋藏于海洋底层以下的沉积岩及基岩中的矿产资源之一，目前海上原油产量已占世界总量的相当比重。近年来，中国和巴西在海底石油开发领域的合作发展迅速，成为中巴经贸合作新亮点。','1','1','2017-03-12 10:02:55','','0','','','0','{\"thumb\":\"\"}','0','0','0','0','','');INSERT INTO ts_posts ( `id`, `post_author`, `post_keywords`, `post_source`, `post_date`, `post_content`, `post_title`, `post_excerpt`, `post_status`, `comment_status`, `post_modified`, `post_content_filtered`, `post_parent`, `post_type`, `post_mime_type`, `comment_count`, `smeta`, `post_hits`, `post_like`, `istop`, `recommended`, `page_tpl`, `page_tpls` ) VALUES  ('328','1','国际油价四周连阳 ','','2017-03-12 10:04:33','<p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　《经济参考报》记者从多家社会监测机构了解到，限产消息持续发酵，国际油价四周连阳，原油变化率持续正值升高。从目前走势来看，</span>10<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">19</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">日国内成品油零售限价将迎来年内最大涨幅，预计幅度超过</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">280</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">元</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">/</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">吨，而国际原油的不断上涨，也成就了国内成品油批发价一波“高涨”行情。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\">　　9<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">28</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">日在阿尔及利亚召开的欧佩克非正式会谈上，长期限产协议竟意外达成，之后俄罗斯也表态愿意参与此项协议，带动国际油价出现井喷式上涨，</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">WIT</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">和布伦特油价一度涨到</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">51.35</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">美元</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">/</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">桶和</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">53.14</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">美元</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">/</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">桶。国际油价当周累计上涨</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">1.1%</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">，且呈现四周连涨趋势。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　受此拉动，截至</span>10<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">14</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">日，中宇资讯测算原油变化率为</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">10.51%</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">，中宇原油估价</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">50.076</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">美元</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">/</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">桶，较基准价涨</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">4.763</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">美元</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">/</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">桶，亚洲原油估价</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">49.617</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">美元</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">/</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">桶，较基准价涨</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">4.304</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">美元</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">/</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">桶，综合上轮搁浅幅度后，暂预计</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">20</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">日零时成品油零售限价上调</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">285</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">元</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">/</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">吨。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　卓创资讯监测的原油变化率为</span>10.78%<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">，相对应的成品油限价上调幅度在</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">335</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">元</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">/</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">吨，折合升价为</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">92#/93#</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">汽油上调</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">0.26</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">元</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">/</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">升，</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">0#</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">柴油上调</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">0.28</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">元</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">/</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">升。“近期国际原油基本面走势平稳，整体均价已经被拉高。按目前走势分析，</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">10</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">19</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">日年内最大汽柴油零售价涨幅将被刷新。”卓创资讯分析师秦文平称。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　受到浓厚的涨价预期提振，近期国内的成品油批发价格出现持续上涨。以重庆地区为例，其柴油成交价格在上周二大幅上调</span>650<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">元</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">/</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">吨，自西南地区最低价直接涨至当地最高。成品油价格的持续上涨，导致加油站销售利润明显缩减。据卓创测算，目前国内加油站销售国营炼厂柴油的利润已缩减至</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">490</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">元</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">/</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">吨，较一个月前大幅缩减</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">600</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">元</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">/</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">吨；汽油的利润也已从</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">1800</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">元</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">/</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">吨降低到了</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">1400</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">元</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">/</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">吨。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\">　　“后期来看，原油近期仍将呈现震荡上涨走势，市场看涨预期将会持续发酵，国内成品油的批发价格也将继续推涨。当然，由于目前部分地区主营销售单位的柴油价格已经涨至限价，故而涨势将有所放缓。在这种情况下，在成品油上调落实前，国内加油站销售利润将会继续缩减。”卓创资讯分析师孟鹏称。</span></p><p><br/></p>','国际油价四周连阳 周三成品油价将迎年内最大涨幅','　　《经济参考报》记者从多家社会监测机构了解到，限产消息持续发酵，国际油价四周连阳，原油变化率持续正值升高。','1','1','2017-03-12 10:03:49','','0','','','0','{\"thumb\":\"\"}','1','0','0','0','','');INSERT INTO ts_posts ( `id`, `post_author`, `post_keywords`, `post_source`, `post_date`, `post_content`, `post_title`, `post_excerpt`, `post_status`, `comment_status`, `post_modified`, `post_content_filtered`, `post_parent`, `post_type`, `post_mime_type`, `comment_count`, `smeta`, `post_hits`, `post_like`, `istop`, `recommended`, `page_tpl`, `page_tpls` ) VALUES  ('329','1','油价上调料创年内最大涨幅 ','','2017-03-12 10:18:24','<p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　今日，国内成品油零售价格调整窗口再次开启。多家机构预测，油价将迎来年内第七次上调，预计本次汽柴油每吨上调幅度</span>300<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">元</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">-350</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">元区间，为年内最大涨幅，私家车加满一油箱要多花</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">15-20</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">元。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　上一轮调价窗口</span>(9<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">30</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">日</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">)</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">，国内油价因调价幅度在</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">50</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">元</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">/</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">吨之内而搁浅。</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">9</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月底欧佩克意外达成限产的声明助推油价上涨。本轮计价周期，国际油价国庆期间大涨，成品油调价首个工作日便呈现较大幅度的上调预期；随后国际油价供应过剩及美元走高影响下重回震荡走势，但本周期内国际油价均价继续上扬。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　国际原油期货价格周一收跌，纽约商品交易所</span>WTI<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">期货主力合约价格下跌</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">0.8%</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">，收于每桶</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">49.94</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">美元；伦敦洲际交易所布伦特原油期货主力合约价格下跌</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">0.8%</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">，收于每桶</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">51.52</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">美元。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　截至北京时间</span>10<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">18</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">日</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">(</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">本轮第</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">9</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">个工作日</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">)</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">，以隔夜国际油价交易数据测算，综合上轮搁浅幅度后，隆众石化网监测显示，预计本次汽柴油每吨上调</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">320-340</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">元，折合每升上调约</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">0.24-0.29</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">元，最终调价幅度亦有超越每升</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">0.3</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">元的可能。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　中宇资讯预计，汽柴油每吨上调幅度</span>300-350<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">元；以</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">300</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">元计算，折合升价为</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">92</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">号</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">/93</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">号每升上调</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">0.23</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">元，</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">0</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">号柴油每升上调</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">0.26</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">元。卓创资讯测算，汽柴油每吨上调</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">345</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">元，折合升价为，</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">92</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">号</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">/93</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">号汽油每升上调</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">0.27</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">元，</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">0</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">号柴油每升上调</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">0.29</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">元。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　国内成品油定价机制采用</span> &quot;<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">十个工作日一调</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">&quot;</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">的原则。</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">2016</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年以来，国内成品油调价已经历</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">19</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">轮计价周期，呈现“六涨四跌九搁浅”的格局。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　成品油调价</span>9<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">次搁浅中</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">3</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">次正常搁浅，</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">6</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">次因地板价新政而不作调整；汽柴油</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">6</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">次上调累计幅度分别为每吨</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">985</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">元、</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">955</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">元；</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">4</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">次下调累计幅度为每吨</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">670</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">元、</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">650</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">元。涨跌互抵后，截止到上一轮调价结束，年内汽柴油每吨分别上涨</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">315</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">元、</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">305</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">元。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　多家机构认为，此次成品油调价落实，将实现年内成品油价格最大幅度的调整。据卓创资讯监测数据显示，目前</span>“国五”<span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">92</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">号汽油零售价主流在每升</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">5.89-5.94</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">元，“国四”</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">93</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">号汽油零售价主流在每升</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">5.65-5.93</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">元。一旦本轮调价落实，实施“国五”和部分实施“国四”标准地区的汽油将全面回归到“六时代”。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　隆众资讯原油分析师李彦分析，若上调落实，一般私家车加满一油箱相当于要多花</span>15-20<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">元左右。不过当前民营加油站优惠力度较大，每升在</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">0.4-1</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">元左右，中石化、中石油旗下的加油站也有限时优惠活动，加油可供选择的选项较多，因此车主出行成本并不会受到明显影响。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　中宇资讯分析师孙晓飞认为，目前成品油市场受本轮调价宽幅凸显的上调预期影响，油价大幅推升，东北及华北地区负号柴油置换工作陆续展开，山东地炼方面</span>0<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">号柴油资源紧张，带动周边柴油价格大幅上涨至批发到位价。另外，四川、湖南及河南油品升级工作已提前展开，普柴资源显紧，油价持续高位保持。国内油市利好大于利空，后期伴随成品油调价落实，油价将有继续推涨的可能。</span></span></p><p><br/></p>','油价上调料创年内最大涨幅 私家车1油箱或多20元','　　今日，国内成品油零售价格调整窗口再次开启。多家机构预测，油价将迎来年内第七次上调，预计本次汽柴油每吨上调幅度300元-350元区间，为年内最大涨幅，私家车加满一油箱要多花15-20元。','1','1','2017-03-12 10:16:48','','0','','','0','{\"thumb\":\"\"}','1','0','0','0','','');INSERT INTO ts_posts ( `id`, `post_author`, `post_keywords`, `post_source`, `post_date`, `post_content`, `post_title`, `post_excerpt`, `post_status`, `comment_status`, `post_modified`, `post_content_filtered`, `post_parent`, `post_type`, `post_mime_type`, `comment_count`, `smeta`, `post_hits`, `post_like`, `istop`, `recommended`, `page_tpl`, `page_tpls` ) VALUES  ('330','1','发改委再对新能源标杆电价征意见','','2017-03-12 10:19:24','<p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　记者从业内获悉，</span>17<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">日，国家发改委将召集多个部门和大型发电企业、电网企业人士召开座谈会，听取各方对调整新能源标杆电价的意见建议。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　新能源行业人士认为，这是发改委对《关于调整新能源标杆上网电价的通知</span>(<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">征求意见稿</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">)</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">》</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">(</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">下称“《意见稿》”</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">)</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">进行第二轮征求意见。</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">9</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">29</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">日发布的《意见稿》提出，拟大幅下调光伏等标杆电价。这在业内引发激烈讨论，多数观点认为下调是必然趋势。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　根据相关会议通知，受邀参与第二轮征求意见的单位包括财政部经建司、能源局新能源司、五大发电集团、三峡、中广核、龙源、协鑫、天合财务部</span>(<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">新能源公司</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">)</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">、两大电网公司财务部等。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\">　　“这次是第二轮征求意见，之前相关部门已向各省级政府征求过一轮意见了。”中国循环经济协会可再生能源专业委员会政策研究部主管彭澎告诉记者。</span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　《意见稿》提出，将下调风电、光伏补贴力度，其中三类地面光伏标杆电价下调幅度降幅在</span>23.5-31.2%<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">之间，分布式发电项目的补贴标准也计划大幅下调近四成，远远超过行业预期。《意见稿》发布后，全国工商联新能源商会发出了《关于“光伏标杆上网电价调整”意见征集的紧急通知》，征求会员企业的意见，并计划汇总后上报国家发改委和能源局。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　新能源补贴为何计划大幅下调</span>?<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">这似乎能从国家能源局副局长李仰哲近日的公开讲话中找到答案。李仰哲称，截至今年上半年，可再生能源补贴缺口累计达到</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">550</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">亿元，原有的补贴模式难以为继。决策部门面临着极大的压力，关于产业发展未来的制度安排和政策选择遇到了现实的挑战。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　他说，通过市场进行竞争性配置光伏资源开发是一个很好的尝试，并透露正在研究制定可再生能源电力绿色证书交易制度，并逐步调整现有的补贴模式，即要把目前的固定电价逐步转变为定额补贴。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\">　　“我个人是支持降价的。”彭澎表示，短期来看，主要的矛盾是可再生能源基金不足导致相关部门计划大幅度下调电价。长期来看，新能源平价上网是大势所趋，最终将不再需要补贴。但政策变化太快会导致光伏市场骤冷骤热，不利于行业发展，应通过竞价分配指标的模式等市场手段来定价。因此，她建议三类地区光伏分别降价<span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">0.1-0.15</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">元</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">/</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">千瓦时，分布式补贴不变。风电在</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">2015</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年底的降价计划上，全部四类地区都再多降</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">0.01</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">元</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">/</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">千瓦时。生物质发电也可以竞价，但是还要纳入可再生能源补贴范围。可再生能源附加费的收取则需要明确责任主体。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　电力新能源行业分析师认为，补贴大幅下降或促使开发企业关注农、渔互补等以往关注度不够的领域。按照以往经验，在几轮征求意见结束后，最终版本将会有一定的调整，部分行业最终补贴价格存在高于《意见稿》公布价格的可能性。</span></span></p><p><br/></p>','发改委再对新能源标杆电价征意见','　　记者从业内获悉，17日，国家发改委将召集多个部门和大型发电企业、电网企业人士召开座谈会，听取各方对调整新能源标杆电价的意见建议。','1','1','2017-03-12 10:18:35','','0','','','0','{\"thumb\":\"\"}','2','0','0','0','','');INSERT INTO ts_posts ( `id`, `post_author`, `post_keywords`, `post_source`, `post_date`, `post_content`, `post_title`, `post_excerpt`, `post_status`, `comment_status`, `post_modified`, `post_content_filtered`, `post_parent`, `post_type`, `post_mime_type`, `comment_count`, `smeta`, `post_hits`, `post_like`, `istop`, `recommended`, `page_tpl`, `page_tpls` ) VALUES  ('331','1','将进一步推进外延收购','','2017-03-12 10:21:03','<p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\">　　10<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">17</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">日</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">,</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">在公司举行的重大资产重组媒体说明会上</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">,</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">洲际油气相关负责人表示</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">,</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">将坚定实施“双轮驱动”和“油气并举”的发展战略</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">,</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">在现有区块上精耕细作</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">,</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">充分发挥在“一带一路”沿线形成的网络体系</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">,</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">优选资产标的</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">,</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">多区域合理配置资源</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">,</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">进一步推进外延收购。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><strong><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;font-size: 14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　收购境外油气资产</span></span></strong></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　据了解</span>,<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">本次重大重组实质上属于收购境外的油气资产。按照实际操作惯例</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">,</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">通常设立一个平台公司以现金收购境外油气资产</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">,</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">然后上市公司通过发行股份购买平台公司的股份。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\">　　9<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">30</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">日早间</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">,</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">洲际油气发布公告称</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">,</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">公司本次拟收购的上海泷洲鑫科能源有限公司在加拿大卡尔加里完成了对班克斯公司</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">100%</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">股权的收购工作</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">,</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">并收到了阿尔博塔省登记的公司合并证书。就在</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">9</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">30</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">日</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">,</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">对于洲际油气两次调整资产重组预案</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">,</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">公司收到上交所问询函。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　洲际油气本次重组方案显示</span>,<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">通过发行股份购买资产的方式收购上海泷洲鑫科</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">96.7%</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">的股权</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">,</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">并间接拥有其持有或拟持有的班克斯公司</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">100%</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">股权和基傲投资</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">100%</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">股权</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">;</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">本次交易前持有上海泷洲鑫科</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">3.3%</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">的股权</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">,</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">交易完成后持有上海泷洲鑫科</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">100%</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">的股权</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">;</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">参考预估值</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">,</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">经交易各方协商</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">,</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">确定上海泷洲鑫科</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">96.7%</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">股权交易作价为</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">33.615</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">亿元</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">;</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">另外</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">,</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">本次拟募集配套资金</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">32</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">亿元</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">,</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">用于标的项目建设和并购重组相关税费</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">(</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">含中介机构费用</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">).</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　事实上</span>,<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">洲际油气的定增收购方案已经过两次调整。自去年</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">9</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月起</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">,</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">洲际油气因筹划收购上海泷洲鑫科而停牌</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">,</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">直到今年</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">4</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月定增收购方案公布后复牌。此前</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">,</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">收购的标的资产中还包括俄罗斯雅吉欧公司</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">,</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">后从标的资产中拿出。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　洲际油气称</span>,<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">从标的资产中剔除雅吉欧公司的主要原因是</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">,</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">今年第二季度国际油价从一季度的</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">30</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">美元</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">/</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">桶附近升高到</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">45</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">美元</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">/</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">桶左右</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">,</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">油气资产效益好转</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">,</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">雅吉欧公司的股东俄罗斯诺瓦泰克公司希望提高交易对价</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">,</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">买卖双方需进一步协商</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">,</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">上海泷洲鑫科难以按原计划完成此项收购。第二次方案调整则是由于上海泷洲鑫科原股东实缴资本未及时到位</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">,</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">除洲际油气外</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">,</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">其他</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">4</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">家股东都被更换。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　早些时候</span>,<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">洲际油气收购班克斯公司已获得国家发改委和上海自贸区管理委员会备案通过</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">,</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">并已分别获得加拿大政府和阿尔巴尼亚反垄断委员会批准</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">,</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">境外审批程序已履行完毕</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">,</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">于</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">5</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">31</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">日获班克斯公司股东大会通过。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　班克斯石油是一家加拿大独立石油公司</span>,<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">其前身为阿尔巴尼亚国家石油公司</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">,</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">是阿尔巴尼亚最大的工业企业</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">,</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">总部位于石油城卡尔加里。</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">2013</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">-2015</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">,</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">其年收入占阿国工业</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">GDP</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">的</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">28.29%,2015</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年缴纳的税收占阿国财政收入的</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">3.61%</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">。截至</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">2015</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">12</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">31</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">日</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">,</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">该油田剩余可采储量为</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">2.91</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">亿桶。班克斯石油目前日产原油</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">1.74</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">万桶</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">/</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">天</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">(</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">约</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">87</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">万吨</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">/</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">).</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　此前</span>,<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">洲际油气已拥有马腾公司</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">3</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">个油田、卡门区块和克山公司</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">3</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">个区块</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">,</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">可采储量</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">2.18</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">亿桶</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">,</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">已成功转型成专业化的中型油气公司。业内人士表示</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">,</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">本次收购完成后</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">,</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">公司将成为</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">A</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">股最大的民营油气生产商。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\">　　</span><strong><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;font-size: 14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">油价高低决定业绩弹性</span></span></strong></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　由于在低油价时收购油田资产</span>,<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">洲际油气的单位储量收购成本较低。根据相关分析师的报告预测</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">,</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">随着原油产量进一步增加</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">,</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">作为纯油气开采公司</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">,</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">洲际油气在油价反弹时业绩弹性较大。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　不过</span>,<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">上述预测的实现需要两方面因素支持</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">,</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">其一是油价</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">,</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">其二是产量。即便是油价预测准确</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">,</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">如果产量无法跟上</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">,</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">收益依然难以达到预期</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">,</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">反之亦然。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　洲际油气董事长姜亮认为</span>,<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">国际油价弹性巨大</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">,</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">油价的波动必然对公司业绩产生直接影响</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">,</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">未来油价的回升将直接增厚公司利润规模。姜亮亦称</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">,</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">本次收购完成后</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">,</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">洲际油气不排除继续利用自有资金或负债等形式进行更大规模的资产收购计划。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　受</span>2014<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年下半年以来石油价格行情低迷的影响</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">,</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">班克斯公司股票市值远低于其净资产</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">,</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">洲际油气间接收购班克斯公司</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">,</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">是对未来出于怎样的判断</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">?</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">在回答中国证券报记者有关提问时</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">,</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">洲际油气财务总监王临川表示</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">,</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">在收购班克斯之后</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">,</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">剩余</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">3.5</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">亿桶石油可采</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">,</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">等于每桶收购价格不到</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">1.6</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">美元。同时</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">,</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">班克斯公司净资产</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">4.72</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">亿美元</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">,</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">折价较大</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">,</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">且账户资产将近</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">10</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">亿美元。此外</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">,</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">班克斯在历史上特别是在</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">2011</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">3</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月份</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">,</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">市值总规模最高达到</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">26</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">亿美元</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">,</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">印证了班克斯的真实价值。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　在海外收购经验方面</span>,<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">洲际油气董秘樊辉表示</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">,</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">自</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">2014</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年收购马腾油田以来</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">,</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">洲际油气已成长为专业性的油气公司。公司</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">2015</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年还收购了克山油田。目前两个油田产量加起来约每年</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">70</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">万吨。在油价从</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">2014</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年下半年开始下跌以来</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">,</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">公司还可以维持这样的产量</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">,</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">表明通过对这两个油田的收购、整合</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">,</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">洲际油气已经积累了良好的海外油气资产收购经验。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　樊辉表示</span>,<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">未来油价波动还会给公司带来新的并购机遇</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">,</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">洲际油气将努力通过并购在</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">3</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">-5</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年内实现</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">500</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">万吨的产能。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\">　　</span><strong><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;font-size: 14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">交易风险引发关注</span></span></strong></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　对于洲际油气此次资产重组</span>,<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">油价走势、海外交易风险等因素广受关注。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　在重组说明会上</span>,<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">洲际油气财务总监王临川表示</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">,</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">在当前低油价下</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">,</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">班克斯等标的资产正在实施策略性措施</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">,</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">把产量控制在一定范围</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">,</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">由洲际油气增加投资</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">,</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">借油价的反弹增加产能。对班克斯来说</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">,</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">现在的石油储量和新技术的运用将大幅提升今后的产量</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">,</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">且其单位采油成本将得到较大降低。另外</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">,</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">在油价波动期间</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">,</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">班克斯一直采用套期保值的策略</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">,</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">未来洲际油气将重点研究这方面的情况</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">,</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">以锁定今后的汇率影响。班克斯计划在未来结合上下游一体化的企业进行一些合作</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">,</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">锁定更多的利润空间。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　对于洲际油气将在标的资产上采用的新技术</span>,<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">洲际油气研究院院长陈鸿表示</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">,</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">油气公司通过服务承包商或者第三方技术来整合开发是业内的常态。洲际油气计划采用的两项技术已经在南美市场取得成功。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　此次资产重组海外资产的交易风险也引发了各方关注。收购风险主要反映在两个方面</span>:<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">中国境内所需要履行的相关政府审批程序包括发改委、商务部门以及外汇相关的手续。截至目前</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">,</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">这些手续都已经取得</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">;</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">关于境外方面的相关手续</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">,</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">班克斯公司是一家在多伦多和英国伦敦两地上市的公司</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">,</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">此次收购需要履行相关私有化的法律程序</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">,</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">程序比较漫长。目前</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">,</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">这些程序已经全部走完。根据伦敦交易所发布的公告</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">,</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">班克斯在今年的</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">9</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">30</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">日已从伦敦交易所退市。根据多伦多交易所发布的公告</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">,</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">班克斯公司已在今年的</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">10</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">4</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">日从多伦多证券交易所退市</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">,</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">目前班克斯的私有化流程已全部完成。</span></span></p><p><br/></p>','洲际油气：将进一步推进外延收购','　　10月17日,在公司举行的重大资产重组媒体说明会上,洲际油气相关负责人表示,将坚定实施“双轮驱动”和“油气并举”的发展战略,在现有区块上精耕细作,充分发挥在“一带一路”沿线形成的网络体系,优选资产标的,多区域合理配置资源,进一步推进外延收购。','1','1','2017-03-12 10:19:35','','0','','','0','{\"thumb\":\"\"}','1','0','0','0','','');INSERT INTO ts_posts ( `id`, `post_author`, `post_keywords`, `post_source`, `post_date`, `post_content`, `post_title`, `post_excerpt`, `post_status`, `comment_status`, `post_modified`, `post_content_filtered`, `post_parent`, `post_type`, `post_mime_type`, `comment_count`, `smeta`, `post_hits`, `post_like`, `istop`, `recommended`, `page_tpl`, `page_tpls` ) VALUES  ('332','1','石油需求高峰正在逼近','','2017-03-12 10:21:55','<p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　石油输出国组织</span>(OPEC)<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">上月决定扭转其放任产量的政策并计划实施减产来提振油价，但这个做法可能与该行业最重要的长期趋势相悖，这个趋势就是对他们开采的原油的需求可能</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">15</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年内将开始下降。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　彭博社引述来自世界能源委员会的报告说，倘若新能源、电动汽车和其他突破性科技快速发展的势头能够持续，石油需求将在</span>2030<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年见顶，然后开始下降。全球最大几个产油国本周将在伦敦出席石油与货币会议，他们可能希望核实一下其对未来数十年市场走势的假设。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　新能源生产成本急速下降，如光伏组件成本从</span>2009<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年以来已降低</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">50%</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">，已在颠覆公用事业行业的经营模式。随着电动汽车开始比汽油或柴油汽车更加省钱，干扰或将蔓延至石油行业，到</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">2020-2030</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年末期每天可能少消耗数百万桶燃油，对未来数十年需求增长将支撑原油项目投资的预测可能是错误的。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　管理逾</span>1<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">万亿美元资产的</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">Amundi</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">驻伦敦能源投资组合经理</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">Alex</span>　<span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">Blein</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">说：“从更长远看，即</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">10</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年以后，行业前景肯定不那么乐观。鉴于电池技术的进展，到</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">2030</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年碳动力汽车将越来越少见，最终将影响原油需求。”</span></span></p><p><br/></p>','石油需求高峰正在逼近','　　石油输出国组织(OPEC)上月决定扭转其放任产量的政策并计划实施减产来提振油价，但这个做法可能与该行业最重要的长期趋势相悖，这个趋势就是对他们开采的原油的需求可能15年内将开始下降。','1','1','2017-03-12 10:21:15','','0','','','0','{\"thumb\":\"\"}','1','0','0','0','','');INSERT INTO ts_posts ( `id`, `post_author`, `post_keywords`, `post_source`, `post_date`, `post_content`, `post_title`, `post_excerpt`, `post_status`, `comment_status`, `post_modified`, `post_content_filtered`, `post_parent`, `post_type`, `post_mime_type`, `comment_count`, `smeta`, `post_hits`, `post_like`, `istop`, `recommended`, `page_tpl`, `page_tpls` ) VALUES  ('333','1','央企重点领域混改迎曙光 ','','2017-03-12 10:22:44','<p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　分析人士预计，混改将沿着三条主线推动，即七大垄断行业央企试点、混合所有制企业员工持股和地方国企混改试点。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　近日，央企混改</span>“<span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">6+1</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">”试点浮出水面，国企改革再度成为市场关注的焦点。业内人士认为，当前在企业去杠杆的政策背景下，国企改革更是搭乘政策“东风”，产业整合以及混合所有制改革均在提速，标志性项目有望陆续出炉。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　中国企业联合会研究部研究员刘兴国在接受《证券日报》记者采访时表示，推进混合所有制改革，在逐步淡化国有资本与非公资本的所有制差异基础上，有利于企业更好地按照市场化要求、遵循市场规律完善激励约束机制，充分调动积极性，提供劳动与资本的产出效率、资源的利用效率，进而实现企业整体效率的提升。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　值得注意的是，近日国家发展改革委副主任刘鹤主持召开专题会，研究部署国有企业混合所有制改革试点相关工作。会上东航集团、联通集团、南方电网、哈电集团、中国核建、中国船舶等中央企业和浙江省发展改革委负责人就列入第一批试点的混合所有制改革项目实施方案做了详细介绍。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　刘鹤指出，推进混合所有制改革是深化国企改革的重要突破口。当前，必须加快推进改革，解决国有企业市场主体地位不明确、国有经济布局过宽、效率低下等问题。在电力、石油、天然气、铁路、民航、电信、军工等关系国计民生和经济安全的重要领域开展混合所有制改革试点。改革的主要任务是开放竞争性业务、破除行政垄断、打破市场垄断，推进政企分开、政资分开、网运分开、特许经营等。允许乃至引入更多的非公资本发展混合所有制经济，是实现改革任务可探索的有效途径。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　中信证券分析师认为</span>,<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">随着混改试点逐步铺开</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">,</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">很可能出现一些好的样本和案例</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">,</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">将对整个混改进程和市场预期产生重大影响。预计混改将沿着三条主线推动，即七大垄断行业央企试点、混合所有制企业员工持股和地方国企混改试点。</span></span></p><p><br/></p>','央企重点领域混改迎曙光 “6+1”试点浮出水面','　　分析人士预计，混改将沿着三条主线推动，即七大垄断行业央企试点、混合所有制企业员工持股和地方国企混改试点。','1','1','2017-03-12 10:22:07','','0','','','0','{\"thumb\":\"\"}','1','0','0','0','','');INSERT INTO ts_posts ( `id`, `post_author`, `post_keywords`, `post_source`, `post_date`, `post_content`, `post_title`, `post_excerpt`, `post_status`, `comment_status`, `post_modified`, `post_content_filtered`, `post_parent`, `post_type`, `post_mime_type`, `comment_count`, `smeta`, `post_hits`, `post_like`, `istop`, `recommended`, `page_tpl`, `page_tpls` ) VALUES  ('334','1','现在是可再生柴油的时代吗？','','2017-03-12 10:23:49','<p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　每个人都知道传统的柴油燃料是来自石油中。许多人也许对一个术语</span>“生物柴油”非常熟悉，生物柴油就是从植物油和<span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">/</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">或动物油脂中提炼出来的。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　但是制作生物柴油的过程中需要引入氧气进入燃料中</span>——这就会引起一些问题，包括液体的冻结温度、存储过程的分离、在燃料箱中藻类的生长和更高的排放。生物柴油通常是与石化柴油混合在一起，保持一个<span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">5%</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">到</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">20%</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">的比例。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　最近出现了所谓再生柴油，也来自于可再生资源：如大豆、棕榈、油菜籽、或菜籽油、动物脂、植物油废物或棕色的地沟油和其他脂肪和植物油。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　可再生柴油与生物柴油最大的区别就是在生产的过程中。可再生柴油的生产过程与石化柴油的生产方式类似，这使得它在化学性能上与石化柴油一样。同时，可再生柴油并不包含氧气，因此使用者无需考虑像生物柴油呈现出来的冷冻温度和存储等的问题。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　由于会有加氢的过程，可再生柴油也会比生物柴油燃烧地更加清洁。也许最重要的是，因为可再生柴油与石化柴油有一样的化学结构，它可以被使用在原本设计用传统柴油燃料运行的发动机中，而不需要任何混合。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　根据</span>GreenFleet<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">杂志介绍，可再生柴油会带来很多好处。除了燃料的可再生性质，它燃烧更加清洁，并且它可以像传统柴油一样工作。</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">GreenFleet</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">杂志指出，交换机不再需要考虑性能问题，也不需要调整机器来适应燃料。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　可再生柴油也兼容现有柴油配送基础设施，这意味着它可以使用现有的管道、储罐或零售站泵。它可以使用现有的炼油厂生产能力来生产，并且不需要大量的新生产设施。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　就二氧化碳而言，根据混合程度，可再生柴油可减少其从</span>13%<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">到</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">90%</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">的排放。支持者还称如果从植物中来提取的话，这些新增的原料也能消除空气中的二氧化碳。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　有了所有这些好处，那么为什么没有可再生柴油没有开始真正地广泛使用呢？答案当然是成本。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　替代燃料数据中心报道，今年</span>4<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月最新数据表明，普通柴油价格约为每加仑</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">2.13</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">美元，相比可再生柴油是</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">2.81</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">美元——有</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">31%</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">的溢价。常规的生物柴油是仅仅每加仑</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">2.23</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">美元。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　但是，在加利福尼亚，成本的问题就不是那么重要了。美国的低碳燃料标准</span>(LCSF)<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">能够补偿一部分费用。这导致了奥克兰市整体都在转向可再生柴油。自</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">2015</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年秋天开始，他们已经在所有柴油动力设备中使用可再生柴油，包括消防器材、越野设备。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　奥克兰城市设备服务经理，巴特斯百</span>·理查德告诉<span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">GreenFleet</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">杂志：“我们希望取代消费大约</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">25</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">万加仑的石化柴油，并且消除每年超过</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">1500</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">吨的温室气体排放，我们目前还没有遇到任何问题。我经历过最常见的反应是很多人不相信有一种清洁燃烧直接柴油替代品来自可再生资源，且对燃料本身不需要任何额外费用，也不需要更新设备和基础设施。”</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\">　　2015<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">7</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月，交货量巨大的</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">UPS</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">快递公司宣布在未来三年内将购买多达</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">4600</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">万加仑的可再生柴油，帮助该公司实现节约燃料的目标：到</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">2017</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年取代</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">UPS</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">地面车队中</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">12%</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">的石油燃料。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\">　　UPS<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">全球能源和采购副总裁</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">Mike</span>　<span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">Whitlatch</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">同时说道：“实际上从性能角度来看，与传统燃料相比，可再生柴油是一样好、甚至更好的燃料。比如，在寒冷的天气使用可再生柴油能够更加容易地发动汽车。”</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　就天然气卡车来说，存在一个鸡和蛋的问题设想，加州以外的天然气卡车分布很少，需求会逐渐上升，同时需求也要供应能上升。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　关于这个问题，</span>Whitlatch<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">也观察到建设一个市场是“纯粹的有多少生物炼油厂建造出来，就有多少可再生柴油生产”的函数。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　然而，没有加利福利亚模式的激励政策，成本差异可能会阻止许多公司和政府机构使用可再生柴油。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　当然，希望随着产量的提高，未来可再生柴油的价格将会降低。考虑到其优于常规柴油和生物柴油，可再生柴油的长期前景是光明的。</span>(<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">编译：工业和信息化部国际经济技术合作中心高浚淇</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">)</span></span></p><p><br/></p>','现在是可再生柴油的时代吗？','　　每个人都知道传统的柴油燃料是来自石油中。许多人也许对一个术语“生物柴油”非常熟悉，生物柴油就是从植物油和/或动物油脂中提炼出来的。','1','1','2017-03-12 10:22:54','','0','','','0','{\"thumb\":\"\"}','1','0','0','0','','');INSERT INTO ts_posts ( `id`, `post_author`, `post_keywords`, `post_source`, `post_date`, `post_content`, `post_title`, `post_excerpt`, `post_status`, `comment_status`, `post_modified`, `post_content_filtered`, `post_parent`, `post_type`, `post_mime_type`, `comment_count`, `smeta`, `post_hits`, `post_like`, `istop`, `recommended`, `page_tpl`, `page_tpls` ) VALUES  ('335','1','成品油迎来年内最高涨幅 ','','2017-03-12 10:25:08','<p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　昨日下午，国家发改委宣布将于</span>19<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">日</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">24</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">时起上调成品油价格，汽、柴油价格每吨分别提高</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">355</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">元和</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">340</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">元，也是年内最高涨幅。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　成品油分析师认为，此轮调价后，国内成品油批零价差将大幅收窄，加油站高利润时代将结束，山东地炼利润将攀上年内高峰。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\">　　“虽然受到冻产利好消息支撑，国际油价在下一个调价周期内依然有上行空间，但很可能因无法触及涨价红线而搁浅。”分析师预测。</span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　此次为成品油年内第</span>7<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">次上调。据卓创数据统计，截至</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">19</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">日</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">24</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">时，今年来，国内成品油经历</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">20</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">次调价窗口，其中</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">4</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">次下调、</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">7</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">次上调、</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">9</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">次不调整（其中</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">3</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">次因幅度不足</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">50</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">元</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">/</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">吨而搁浅，</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">6</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">次因原油均价处于地板价之下而停调）。涨跌互抵后，今年来，汽油累计上涨</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">670</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">元</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">/</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">吨，柴油累计上涨</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">645</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">元</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">/</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">吨。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　在过去一段时间内，成品油价格调整后，国内成品油批发和零售之间价差往往会进一步放大，此次调整则出现了不同的情况。据行业人士介绍，受到浓厚的涨价预期提振，国内的成品油批发价格近期出现了持续的推涨。尤其是西南、西北等部分地区柴油资源紧张，导致部分地区的</span>“两桶油”（中石油、中石化）柴油价格涨到了批发最高限价。此外，山东地方炼厂柴油库存偏低，柴油价格持续大涨，也对山东周边地区的“两桶油”柴油价格形成支撑。而国内汽油需求处于淡季，加之资源供应正常，涨幅远不及柴油，但也将导致加油站的销售利润明显缩减。</span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　据卓创测算，目前国内加油站销售国营炼厂柴油的利润已缩减至</span>260<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">元</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">/</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">吨，较一个月前大幅缩减</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">73%</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">；汽油的利润也从</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">1800</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">元</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">/</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">吨降低到了</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">1400</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">元</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">/</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">吨，降幅达到</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">22%</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">。卓创成品油分析师孟鹏称：“利润的缩减将使加油站优惠力度明显减少，动辄优惠</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">1</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">元</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">/</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">升的情况未来将非常少见。”</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　中宇资讯市场分析师孙晓飞认为，大部分地区主营柴油批发价已涨至批发最高限价，油价的持续上扬带动业者补库增加，批发市场将逐渐活跃。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　成品油大幅价格上调，对于国内炼化企业则构成利好。根据卓创资讯数据统计模型显示，截至目前，山东地方炼厂综合炼油利润已达到</span>585<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">元</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">/</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">吨，较</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">9</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月底上涨</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">288</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">元</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">/</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">吨，利润登上年内最高峰。但成品油分析师王芦青认为，这样的高利润难以较长维持。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　现行的成品油定价机制与国际油价联系密切。近期受俄罗斯协同石油输出国组织（欧佩克）限产预期提振，国际油价在突破</span>50<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">美元</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">/</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">桶关口后继续走强。安迅思分析师黄丽芳认为，欧佩克与非欧佩克齐心限产仍阻力重重。如果美国不加入限产队伍，限制的产量会迅速被页岩油挤占，预计短期内国际油价恐反复波动。就目前走势而言，新一轮成品油变化率极低，后期走势有待观望。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\">　　“以当前的国际原油价格水平计算，下一轮成品油调价开局将呈现小幅向下的趋势，幅度仅有<span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">15</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">元</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">/</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">吨左右。”隆众石化网分析师李彦认为，这样的幅度意味着下调趋势并不稳固，如果最终不能突破±</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">50</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">元</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">/</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">吨，后一轮调价搁浅的可能性较大。</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">10</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月底，产油国还将对限产问题进行磋商，这是接下来的关注重点。</span></span></p><p><br/></p>','成品油迎来年内最高涨幅 炼化企业与加油站一喜一忧','　　昨日下午，国家发改委宣布将于19日24时起上调成品油价格，汽、柴油价格每吨分别提高355元和340元，也是年内最高涨幅。','1','1','2017-03-12 10:24:16','','0','','','0','{\"thumb\":\"\"}','1','0','0','0','','');INSERT INTO ts_posts ( `id`, `post_author`, `post_keywords`, `post_source`, `post_date`, `post_content`, `post_title`, `post_excerpt`, `post_status`, `comment_status`, `post_modified`, `post_content_filtered`, `post_parent`, `post_type`, `post_mime_type`, `comment_count`, `smeta`, `post_hits`, `post_like`, `istop`, `recommended`, `page_tpl`, `page_tpls` ) VALUES  ('336','1','全国成品油价格指数呈上行格局','','2017-03-12 10:26:07','<p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　依据新华</span>(<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">大庆</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">)</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">国际石油资讯中心发布的报告，截至</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">10</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">21</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">日，全国成品油价格指数为</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">683.99</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">，涨幅</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">2.93%</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">，全国成品油价格指数呈上行格局。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　全国成品油价格指数运行结果表明，上周</span>93#<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">汽油平均价格报收于</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">6213</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">元</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">/</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">吨，较前一报告周期上涨</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">129</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">元</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">/</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">吨</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">(</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">折合</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">0.10</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">元</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">/</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">升</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">)</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">；</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">0#</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">柴油平均价格报收于</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">6068</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">元</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">/</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">吨，较前一报告周期上涨</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">195</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">元</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">/</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">吨</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">(</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">折合</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">0.17</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">元</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">/</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">升</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">)</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">。综合来看，全国汽柴油平均价格均上涨，带动全国成品油价格指数继续上行。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　新华</span>(<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">大庆</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">)</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">国际石油资讯中心分析师李振国认为，近期因美元走弱及美国原油库存减少影响，国际油价继续小幅震荡。国内成品油市场上调落实，汽柴油批零价继续推涨。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　李振国分析认为，近期国际油价受美元及冻产会议预期影响持续小幅震荡。国内市场油品行情大幅走高，因终端需求恢复有限，市场交投情况一般。柴油资源偏紧，价格持续上行，但业者多适量补货，市场交投情况较清淡。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　国际市场方面，美国能源信息署</span>(EIA)<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">近日公布的数据显示，截至</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">10</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">14</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">日当周，美国原油库存减少</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">524.7</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">万桶至</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">4.687</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">亿桶，美国原油库存意外下降，该消息利好国际油价。观望后市，美国原油库存下降但欧佩克产油国石油产量持续上升，供应持续过剩，预计短期内国际油价将维持震荡格局。</span></span></p><p><br/></p>','全国成品油价格指数呈上行格局','　　依据新华(大庆)国际石油资讯中心发布的报告，截至10月21日，全国成品油价格指数为683.99，涨幅2.93%，全国成品油价格指数呈上行格局。','1','1','2017-03-12 10:25:22','','0','','','0','{\"thumb\":\"\"}','2','0','0','0','','');INSERT INTO ts_posts ( `id`, `post_author`, `post_keywords`, `post_source`, `post_date`, `post_content`, `post_title`, `post_excerpt`, `post_status`, `comment_status`, `post_modified`, `post_content_filtered`, `post_parent`, `post_type`, `post_mime_type`, `comment_count`, `smeta`, `post_hits`, `post_like`, `istop`, `recommended`, `page_tpl`, `page_tpls` ) VALUES  ('337','1','2017年能源产品价格将上涨近25%','','2017-03-12 10:27:04','<p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　世界银行发布消息称，</span>2017<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年，随着需求增长、供应减少，大部分原料商品价格将有所回升，预计包括石油、天然气、煤炭在内的能源价格将上涨近</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">25%</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">。该行将</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">2017</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年石油价格预期从此前的</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">53</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">美元</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">/</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">桶上调至</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">55</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">美元</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">/</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">桶，维持</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">2016</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年石油价格预期为</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">43</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">美元</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">/</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">桶不变；将</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">2017</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年金属价格上涨预期从此前的</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">3.6%</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">上调至</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">4.1%</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">，锌价将因部分大型锌矿关闭、产量减少而上涨</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">20%</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">，金价将因利率上调预期、安全资产需求下降而降至</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">1219</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">美元</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">/</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">盎司。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　世行高级经济学家约翰</span>·巴菲斯表示，预计<span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">2017</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年包括石油在内的能源价格将强劲上涨，不过其前景存在很大不确定性，欧佩克冻产协议的细节及协议执行无疑将对石油市场产生影响。</span></span></p><p><br/></p>','世行：2017年能源产品价格将上涨近25%','　　世界银行发布消息称，2017年，随着需求增长、供应减少，大部分原料商品价格将有所回升，预计包括石油、天然气、煤炭在内的能源价格将上涨近25%。','1','1','2017-03-12 10:26:32','','0','','','0','{\"thumb\":\"\"}','0','0','0','0','','');INSERT INTO ts_posts ( `id`, `post_author`, `post_keywords`, `post_source`, `post_date`, `post_content`, `post_title`, `post_excerpt`, `post_status`, `comment_status`, `post_modified`, `post_content_filtered`, `post_parent`, `post_type`, `post_mime_type`, `comment_count`, `smeta`, `post_hits`, `post_like`, `istop`, `recommended`, `page_tpl`, `page_tpls` ) VALUES  ('338','1','石油产业要向“技术为王”过渡','','2017-03-12 10:28:01','<p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　近年来，国际油价持续低迷，震荡幅度大，全球油企同度</span>“严寒”，这使得曾经坐拥丰富石油资源的“油企大佬”也度日如年。</span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　说到底，市场的供需变化也影响着石油行业的变革。面对</span>“严寒”，新的石油技术集群正在形成，石油产业将从“资源为王”向“技术为王”过渡，曾将资源视为“生命”的石油企业纷纷转型，将科技创新作为立身之本，影响供需格局的“技术因素”正在不断增强。</span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　纵观石油工业历史上的每一次跨越，几乎都得益于技术革命的推动。特别是一些颠覆性技术，往往都是在应对挑战的过程中破壳而出。以美国为例，随着新技术突破，美国</span>“页岩气革命”爆发，美国<span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">2014</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年原油日产量达到</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">30</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年以来最高水平。美国能源信息署预测，未来</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">5</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年，全球新增原油供应的三分之一将来自美国，美国将从原油主要进口国变成净出口国。不仅是美国，国际大石油公司近两年都将科技投入作为公司的战略投资，依靠创新培育核心竞争力、占领未来制高点。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　由此看来，在此轮影响世界石油行业供需格局变革的诸多不确定因素之中，石油行业技术革命是最确定的一个，也将是影响最深远的一个。随着国际石油大企业的创新带动，世界油气工业将进入智能化时代，这对我国石油企业来说是挑战更是机遇。</span></span></p><p><br/></p>','石油产业要向“技术为王”过渡','　　近年来，国际油价持续低迷，震荡幅度大，全球油企同度“严寒”，这使得曾经坐拥丰富石油资源的“油企大佬”也度日如年。','1','1','2017-03-12 10:27:16','','0','','','0','{\"thumb\":\"\"}','1','0','0','0','','');INSERT INTO ts_posts ( `id`, `post_author`, `post_keywords`, `post_source`, `post_date`, `post_content`, `post_title`, `post_excerpt`, `post_status`, `comment_status`, `post_modified`, `post_content_filtered`, `post_parent`, `post_type`, `post_mime_type`, `comment_count`, `smeta`, `post_hits`, `post_like`, `istop`, `recommended`, `page_tpl`, `page_tpls` ) VALUES  ('339','1','我国开启天然气储气供应价格改革','','2017-03-12 10:29:03','<p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\">　　10<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">18</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">日，国家发改委发布《关于明确储气设施相关价格政策的通知》，明确指出，今后我国的天然气储气服务价格、储气设施天然气购销价格将由市场自发形成，鼓励各方投资建设储气设施，增强天然气供应保障能力。业内人士指出，此政策出台后，储气服务价格及销售价格都将有所提升，社会资本对于建设天然气储气设施的积极性也会大幅提高。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　国家发改委指出，储气设施天然气购进价格和对外销售价格要由市场竞争形成。储气设施经营企业可统筹考虑天然气购进成本和储气服务成本，并根据市场供求情况自主确定对外销售价格。储气服务价格则由储气设施经营企业根据储气服务成本、市场供求情况等与委托企业协商确定。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　目前，天然气储气设施包括地面储气罐和地下储气库等，既有国企承建，也有民营企业兴办。在冬季用气高峰期、天然气供应不足时，储气库可以弥补上游供应量。截至</span>2014<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年年底，全国已建成地下储气库</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">25</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">座。</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">2014</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年调峰量为</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">30</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">亿立方米，占天然气年消费量的</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">1.7%</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">。国际天然气联盟统计数据显示，截至</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">2015</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年，全球正在运营的地下储气库约</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">630</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">座，工作气总容量</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">3588</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">亿立方米，占全球天然气消费总量的</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">10.3%</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">。目前，我国与国际平均水平仍有较大差距。</span></span></p><p><br/></p>','我国开启天然气储气供应价格改革','　　10月18日，国家发改委发布《关于明确储气设施相关价格政策的通知》，明确指出，今后我国的天然气储气服务价格、储气设施天然气购销价格将由市场自发形成，鼓励各方投资建设储气设施，增强天然气供应保障能力。业内人士指出，此政策出台后，储气服务价格及销售价格都将有所提升，社会资本对于建设天然气储气设施的积极性也会大幅提高。','1','1','2017-03-12 10:28:18','','0','','','0','{\"thumb\":\"\"}','2','0','0','0','','');INSERT INTO ts_posts ( `id`, `post_author`, `post_keywords`, `post_source`, `post_date`, `post_content`, `post_title`, `post_excerpt`, `post_status`, `comment_status`, `post_modified`, `post_content_filtered`, `post_parent`, `post_type`, `post_mime_type`, `comment_count`, `smeta`, `post_hits`, `post_like`, `istop`, `recommended`, `page_tpl`, `page_tpls` ) VALUES  ('340','1','中石化油服前三季度亏损88.58亿元','','2017-03-12 10:29:51','<p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\">　　10<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">26</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">日消息，中石化油服今日晚间发布公告，称</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">2016</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年前三季度，该公司营业收入</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">277.82</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">亿元，同比减少</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">24.1%</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">；亏损</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">88.58</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">亿元，上年同期亏损</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">20.6</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">亿元；每股亏损</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">0.626</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">元，上年同期每股亏损</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">0.149</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">元。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　此外，于</span>2016<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年第三季度，该公司营业收入</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">90.92</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">亿元，同比减少</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">32.45%</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">；亏损</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">43.49</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">亿元，上年同期亏损</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">6.8</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">亿元；每股亏损</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">0.306</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">元，上年同期每股亏损</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">0.048</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">元。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　此前</span>10<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月初中石化油服曾发布公告称，</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">2016</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年第三季度，受国际原油价格继续保持低位影响，国内外石油公司进一步减少上游勘探开发资本支出，全球油田服务行业持续低迷，油服市场量价齐跌局面未有实质性改变，本公司经营亏损进一步扩大，预计</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">1-9</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月归属净利润为</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">-89.0</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">亿元左右。中石化油服为央企中石化集团旗下上市公司。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　此前在今年上半年，中石化油服就曾亏损</span>45.09<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">亿元，在</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">A</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">股公司内亏损额居于前列。而在同期，中海油服亏损</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">84</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">亿元，成为上半年</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">A</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">股市场亏损王。中海油服为央企中海油总公司旗下上市公司。</span></span></p><p><br/></p>','中石化油服前三季度亏损88.58亿元','　　10月26日消息，中石化油服今日晚间发布公告，称2016年前三季度，该公司营业收入277.82亿元，同比减少24.1%；亏损88.58亿元，上年同期亏损20.6亿元；每股亏损0.626元，上年同期每股亏损0.149元。','1','1','2017-03-12 10:29:16','','0','','','0','{\"thumb\":\"\"}','2','0','0','0','','');INSERT INTO ts_posts ( `id`, `post_author`, `post_keywords`, `post_source`, `post_date`, `post_content`, `post_title`, `post_excerpt`, `post_status`, `comment_status`, `post_modified`, `post_content_filtered`, `post_parent`, `post_type`, `post_mime_type`, `comment_count`, `smeta`, `post_hits`, `post_like`, `istop`, `recommended`, `page_tpl`, `page_tpls` ) VALUES  ('341','1','沙特石油部长认为油价将大涨','','2017-03-12 10:32:27','<p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　据</span>Business Insider<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">文章，沙特能源部长</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">Khalid al-Falih</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">上周在伦敦石油和货币大会上发表讲话。他强烈地为</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">2014</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">OPEC</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">能源大会作出的不干越油价的决定做辩护。同时他还警告称，未来国际石油供给短缺将会导致国家油价大幅飙升。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\">　　al-Falih<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">称：“现在你可以想象一下，如果</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">OPEC</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">真的削减石油产量使石油的供需达到平衡，支撑了国际油价，最终的结果是，开发成本较高的页岩油、油砂以及大西洋深海的石油得到大量的投资，进一步得到开采。这样的话油价一定会再次下跌，</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">OPEC</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">也不得不年复一年地削减石油产量。”</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　但是由于油价的暴跌已经给石油市场带来了另外一个问题：缺乏投资。</span>al-Falih<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">继续称，原油市场的危机正在增加。目前许多分析师已经开始鸣响警钟称，随着油价的大跌，未来石油供给量将会大幅下降。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　实际上新发现的石油量非常少，已经创近</span>70<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年来新低，预计到</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">2020</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年底，新开发的石油产量将会非常低。国际能源署</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">(IEA)</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">和美国能源署</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">(EIA)</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">都警告称，未来数年石油的供给量都无法满足石油的需求量，原因是</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">2014</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年至</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">2016</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年之间，石油行业获得投资量微乎其微。</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">al-Falih</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">称：“许多分析师都在警告称，石油的供给量将大幅下跌，我也这样认为，未来将有一段时间石油市场会出现供不应求的情况。”</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　艾克森美孚石油公司的首席执行官</span>Rex Tillerson<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">却不这样认为。他认为石油的库存量太高了，要消耗这些库存量也需要数年时间。即使期间油价上涨，也需要数年时间。</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">Rex Tillerson</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">称：“我其他一些分析师的观点不一样，原因是北美的石油的产量也在不断增加。北美的页岩油产量非常高，增产的速度也非常快。”因此，</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">Rex Tillerson</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">认为国际油价并不会出现大幅上涨的情况。就算世界其它主要产油国降低石油产量也没有用。在这种情况下，我很难预见油价会大幅上涨，毕竟油价上涨有很多因素决定。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　尽管许多参会的人都把焦点放在原油供给上，石油的需求量仍然很难确定。沙特能源部长</span>Khalid al-Falih<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">预计全球石油需求量在</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">2015</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年到</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">2017</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年之间，将上涨</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">400</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">万桶</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">/</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">天。这些需求量大部分来自于中国和印度。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　但是由于中国经济增速的放缓，石油的需求量面临许多不确定的下行风险。如果中国经济下行幅度超出预期，印度经济增长幅度没有达到预期，国际原油的需求量就会大幅下跌。另外，其它国家和地区的经济增长速度也出现了疲弱。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　在</span>2020<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年以前，国际油价不会涨超其目前的水平。</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">EIU</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">预期在</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">2017</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年到</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">2021</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年之间，国际油价将在每桶</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">55</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">美元至每桶</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">65</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">美元之间徘徊。当然由于波动性的存在，国际油价将大幅起伏波动。由于美国石油产量的上升，国际油价不会涨超每桶</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">60</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">美元。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　现在也不缺乏油价将会上涨的观点。但是并不是所有的人都这样认为。美国能源署、国际能源署以及</span>OPEC<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">都认为未来油价将进一步上行。</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">EIU</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">、埃克森美孚石油公司的首席执行官则认为未来油价不会大幅上涨。未来油价到底会怎么样，主要还是要看全球经济的发展状况。</span></span></p><p><br/></p>','沙特石油部长认为油价将大涨','　　据Business Insider文章，沙特能源部长Khalid al-Falih上周在伦敦石油和货币大会上发表讲话。他强烈地为2014年OPEC能源大会作出的不干越油价的决定做辩护。同时他还警告称，未来国际石油供给短缺将会导致国家油价大幅飙升。','1','1','2017-03-12 10:31:42','','0','','','0','{\"thumb\":\"\"}','2','0','0','0','','');INSERT INTO ts_posts ( `id`, `post_author`, `post_keywords`, `post_source`, `post_date`, `post_content`, `post_title`, `post_excerpt`, `post_status`, `comment_status`, `post_modified`, `post_content_filtered`, `post_parent`, `post_type`, `post_mime_type`, `comment_count`, `smeta`, `post_hits`, `post_like`, `istop`, `recommended`, `page_tpl`, `page_tpls` ) VALUES  ('342','1','理性看待中国成为最大原油进口国','','2017-03-12 10:33:14','<p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　统计数据显示，今年</span>9<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月，我国原油进口同比增长</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">18%</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">，达到</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">3306</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">万吨，折约</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">804</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">万桶</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">/</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">天，高于同期美国的</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">798</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">万桶</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">/</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">天，成为世界最大原油进口国。这表明中国在国际能源格局中的角色发生重大转变，也警示进一步重视能源安全的重要。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　冷静分析后不难发现，这与美国原油进口放缓直接相关。作为最大原油消费国，美国各大炼油厂往往选择秋季进行维护检修。炼油厂的检修作业，短期内减少了原油的消费和进口。与此同时，中国</span>“茶壶”炼油厂进口原油却在飙升。去年下半年以来，中国政府放权民营油企，授予其原油进口权，导致有着“茶壶”之称的<span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">10</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">多家民营炼油厂大量进口原油，成为中国原油进口激增背后的主要推动力。同时，我国的国家石油储备建设在稳步推进。与美国战略储备石油可满足国内消费</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">139</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">天、日本可达</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">158</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">天相比，中国的石油储备尚处初期，需紧抓当前国际油价相对较低的机遇期，扩大进口、充实储备。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　应当看到，中国原油进口的增加，扩大了国内能源供应的风险敞口。能源独立是国家安全的一个重要方面。从</span>1993<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年首次成为石油净进口国，到</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">2015</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年石油净进口量</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">3.28</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">亿吨，中国的石油对外依存度已实现“三级跳”。从初期的自给自足，到</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">2009</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年突破国际公认的</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">50%</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">警戒线，到去年的超过</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">60%</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">，中国的石油进口风险敞口也越来越大。目前，中国最大的石油进口来源地包括中东、非洲和独联体国家，这些地区的热点问题常常牵动国际油市神经，能源供应的局部中断风险始终没有排除。如何确保稳定可靠的能源供给安全，始终被打上大大的问号。中国成为最大的石油进口国后，真正重要的不是进口量，而是进口源。为此，中国必须做好能源外交对策。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　中国原油进口的增加，使能源改革的紧迫性提上议事日程。当前，国际油价在低位徘徊，这并非常态。油价一旦再度高企，在扩大中国进口成本的同时，其影响还将传导至国内的其他经济和民生领域，比如，抬升国内物价、促发通胀、增加改革和结构调整的难度等等。因此，尽快优化能源结构，大力发展绿色能源，成为能源改革的共识。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　中国原油进口的增加，加速了国际能源格局的调整。伴随着亚洲国家经济实力的显著提升，国际油市的需求重心开始向东倾斜。亚洲将主导全球石油需求，成为最大的买方市场，议价能力不断提升。中国、印度、日本、韩国等主要经济体均为原油消费大国和进口大户，依赖以市场为导向的全球体系。各国在维护国际能源秩序方面有着共同的利益，合作大于竞争，需共同担当原油生产守卫者和运输线路保证者的角色。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　当然，中国原油进口的增加，还将提升中国货币的影响力。随着国际原油市场从卖方市场转向买方市场，一些原油出口国为巩固对华关系，争相吸引中国投资和技术，提议以</span>“石油换贷款”的方式与中国开展能源合作。“一带一路”的推进和人民币国际化的推进，将推动中国对沿线产油国以人民币计价方式的投资，增强中国在国际原油市场上的话语权。</span></p><p><br/></p>','理性看待中国成为最大原油进口国','　　统计数据显示，今年9月，我国原油进口同比增长18%，达到3306万吨，折约804万桶/天，高于同期美国的798万桶/天，成为世界最大原油进口国。这表明中国在国际能源格局中的角色发生重大转变，也警示进一步重视能源安全的重要。','1','1','2017-03-12 10:32:37','','0','','','0','{\"thumb\":\"\"}','2','0','0','0','','');INSERT INTO ts_posts ( `id`, `post_author`, `post_keywords`, `post_source`, `post_date`, `post_content`, `post_title`, `post_excerpt`, `post_status`, `comment_status`, `post_modified`, `post_content_filtered`, `post_parent`, `post_type`, `post_mime_type`, `comment_count`, `smeta`, `post_hits`, `post_like`, `istop`, `recommended`, `page_tpl`, `page_tpls` ) VALUES  ('343','1','全球十大油企携手应对气候变化','','2017-03-12 10:34:27','<p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　占据世界油气产量两成多的十家石油公司，正在采取一项集体行动，以应对全球气候变化。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　当地时间</span>11<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">4</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">日，油气行业气候倡议组织</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">(</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">以下简称</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">OGCI)</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">企业领导人峰会在伦敦召开，会议发布了由中国石油天然气集团公司董事长王宜林、</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">BP</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">公司</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">CEO</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">戴德利等</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">10</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">个成员公司领导签署的《</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">2016</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">OGCI</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年报》和《</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">OGCI</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">共同宣言》。会议期间，</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">OGCI</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">宣布设立总额为</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">10</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">亿美元的气候投资，以专业化运营的方式，促进低碳技术的创新和商业化应用。</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">OGCI</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">已明确和启动了从现在到</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">2040</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年需要开展的各项工作，并将致力于探索可实现本世纪下半叶净零排放宏伟目标的技术和项目。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　中国经济时报记者获悉，</span>10<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">亿美元的气候投资只是</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">OGCI</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">减排的一个起点，</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">OGCI</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">还将通过各种途径放大</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">10</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">亿美元的影响力，比如与其他倡议组织开展合作，撬动更多资金加入，在自营业务和主要生产运营领域增加投资，应用成熟的低碳技术，利用</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">OGCI</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">成员的专业资源、设施和运营网络的强大影响力，推动油气行业低碳减排工作向前发展。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　作为传统化石能源的生产者，油气行业被认为是具有减排潜力的产业之一。石油公司认为，在大规模减少温室气体排放的众多解决方案中，一定蕴含着很多创新和投资的机遇，这些投资合作将产生巨大的示范效应。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　《</span>OGCI<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">共同宣言》提出了油气行业控制和减少温室气体排放的行动方向，包括：减少天然气生产储运过程的甲烷排放；碳捕集、利用与封存</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">(CCUS)</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">；提高工业领域能效；减少交通运输业的碳排放强度。</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">OGCI</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">成员公司相信这些创新科技一旦实现商业化，在规模化削减温室气体排放方面将具有巨大的潜力。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　中国经济时报获悉，</span>OGCI<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">的气候投资将聚焦于与气候相关的技术和业务，并通过油气行业内合作、与油气产品用户合作获益。目前石油公司已经与许多利益相关者进行沟通，对一些油气行业关联度极强、对减排工作极为重要的项目进行评估。上述优先投资的领域，被认为将在短期和长期范围内产生积极影响。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　《巴黎协定》在短短一年后生效，被认为是为全球行动明确了方向</span>——帮助所有参与者、各国政府、工业界及个人采取措施，共同投资更加低碳的未来。《巴黎协定》签署后，国际社会正在加速制订完善后《京都议定书》时代应对气候变化行动规则。《<span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">OGCI2016</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年年报》全篇贯穿“付诸行动，加速构建低碳未来”的主旨，企业也在积极努力彰显责任担当。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　一年来，作为唯一的中国的石油公司成员</span>——中国石油<span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">(601857,</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">股吧</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">)</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">全面参与</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">OGCI</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">各项工作。特别是在《</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">OGCI</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">低碳发展路线图》的制订进程中，提出了多项建设性意见，发挥了中国石油企业在国际行业组织中的作用。中国石油目前正在加快制订完善公司自身的《低碳发展路线图》，加大研发投入，力争成为低碳技术的引领者；同时开展全面详实的碳盘查，建立完善碳排放管控体系，力争达到国际先进水平。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　在</span>2014<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">1</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月达沃斯论坛上，沙特阿美等多个石油公司</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">CEO</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">提议成立应对气候变化的国际组织，</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">2014</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">9</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月联合国气候峰会上，</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">OGCI</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">宣布正式成立，成员国包括英国石油公司、雷普索尔公司、英荷壳牌公司、埃尼集团、沙特阿拉伯石油公司、墨西哥国家石油公司、挪威国家石油公司、印度莱瑞斯实业公司、道达尔石油公司。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　中国石油董事长王宜林在书面致辞中指出，落实巴黎气候协定需要推动能源供给侧结构性变革，</span>OGCI<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">为全球油气行业低碳转型提供了良好的合作平台。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　作为自愿倡议组织，</span>OGCI<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">是唯一的自发组织，没有政府和联合国等机构参与，它是全球油气行业四大应对气候变化组织之一，致力于在油气行业应对气候变化中发挥领导作用，旨在通过油气公司共同努力，为全球经济发展提供更多清洁能源，同时减少温室气体排放，在国际社会树立油气行业整体绿色低碳发展的形象。目前</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">OGCI</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">成员油气产量占全球总产量的</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">25%</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">，能源供应占全球的</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">10%</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">。</span></span></p><p><br/></p>','全球十大油企携手应对气候变化','　　占据世界油气产量两成多的十家石油公司，正在采取一项集体行动，以应对全球气候变化。','1','1','2017-03-12 10:33:24','','0','','','0','{\"thumb\":\"\"}','2','0','0','0','','');INSERT INTO ts_posts ( `id`, `post_author`, `post_keywords`, `post_source`, `post_date`, `post_content`, `post_title`, `post_excerpt`, `post_status`, `comment_status`, `post_modified`, `post_content_filtered`, `post_parent`, `post_type`, `post_mime_type`, `comment_count`, `smeta`, `post_hits`, `post_like`, `istop`, `recommended`, `page_tpl`, `page_tpls` ) VALUES  ('344','1','国内成品油价年内难有波动','','2017-03-12 10:35:55','<p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\">　　2016<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年以来，在经历了“</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">4</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">跌</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">7</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">涨</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">6</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">地板</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">3</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">搁浅”共</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">20</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">轮调价窗口后，国内成品油价调整再度搁浅。据国家发改委</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">2</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">日消息，由于没有达到国内调价要求，本轮</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">(11</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">2</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">日</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">24</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">时</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">)</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">成品油价格不调整。据统计，这是今年第四次因调价幅度低于</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">50</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">元</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">/</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">吨而搁浅。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　依据国内成品油</span>“十个工作日一调”的定价机制，<span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">2016</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年内还有四次调价窗口，分别为</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">11</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">16</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">日和</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">30</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">日，</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">12</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">14</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">日和</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">28</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">日。对此，能源领域专家预测，短期内国内成品油价会受欧佩克冻产协议达成与否的影响，但影响有限，不会产生大幅波动。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　年初中石油经济技术研究院发布的《</span>2015<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年国内外油气行业发展报告》显示，中国石油消费对外依存度首次突破</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">60%</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">。国际原油市场直接影响着国内成品油价。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　中宇资讯分析显示，国际原油受市场对欧佩克</span>(<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">石油输出国组织</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">)</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">限产前景的担忧及美元走高等多空因素影响，震荡下行。目前国际油价在</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">50</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">美元</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">/</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">每桶左右徘徊。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　沙特《阿拉伯新闻报》</span>10<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">30</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">日消息显示，</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">10</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">29</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">日，欧佩克成员国官员和专家与阿塞拜疆、巴西、哈萨克斯坦、墨西哥、阿曼、俄罗斯等非成员国在维也纳举行会谈，但会后非欧佩克成员国并未就原油冻产的具体步骤做出承诺。在今年</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">9</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月举行的阿尔及尔会议上，欧佩克就减产达成一致，但并未确定具体减产数额。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><strong><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;font-size: 14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　欧佩克对国际原油市场影响有限</span></span></strong></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　中国能源网首席信息官韩晓平对中新经纬客户端表示，国际原油市场目前仍然是供过于求的局面，欧佩克成员国家产量已经达到历史最高点，在没有大的经济体对石油需求快速增加情况下，全球对原油需求趋于饱和，</span>“供求关系不会有太大变化，即使冻产协议达成，油价也不会有大幅度攀升。”</span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　韩晓平同时指出，美国已经具备强大的页岩油生产能力，一旦国际油价超过</span>50<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">美元</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">/</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">每桶，则美国会投入大量资金打井。为抑制美国打井开采页岩油，使国际油价在</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">50</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">美元</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">/</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">每桶保持平衡，欧佩克成员国以及俄罗斯等能够维持一定利润率，希望联合起来促成冻产协议。“短期来看，国际油价大幅调整的可能性较小，将会维持在</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">50</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">美元</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">/</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">每桶左右。”</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　厦门大学能源经济研究中心主任林伯强在接受中新经纬专访时指出，国际油价与欧佩克有一定关系，但欧佩克的影响能力有限。长远来看，随着近几年石油领域的投资越来越少，市场低迷到一定程度之后原油供应就会短缺，如果没有相应替代品，则会导致油价大幅上涨。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　林伯强认为，美国页岩油开采成本较高，若无利可图则打井概率较低。页岩油未来能否成为抑制油价复苏的利器，取决于油价走高到什么程度。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　中国石油流通协会副秘书长尹强告诉中新经纬客户端，对于国际原油市场，具有原油输出能力国家的增产能力和减产欲望是主要影响因素，</span>“所有增量都是抑制油价复苏的砝码。”此外，尹强认为，欧佩克即使促成冻产协议的达成，也没有约束力。</span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\">　</span><strong><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;font-size: 14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　欧佩克冻产协议影响短期市场</span></span></strong></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　林伯强指出，短期内欧佩克的冻产协议会影响国际原油市场。目前市场对冻产协议能否达成仍持怀疑态度，如果像其秘书长巴尔金表示的冻产协议有望在</span>11<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">30</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">日达成，则国际油价预计达到</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">55</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">至</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">60</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">美元</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">/</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">每桶，如果协议不能如期达成，则国际油价有可能重回</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">40</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">美元</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">/</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">每桶。此外，林伯强指出，美元升值、国内经济运行情况等短期因素，也使得中国国内成品油市场存在变数。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　尹强认为，国际原油市场波动对生产链上的企业影响更大，而对消费者来说影响有限。</span>“国内原油生产企业需要找到利润平衡点。”他分析说，“短期来看，国际油价将在<span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">40</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">至</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">60</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">美元</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">/</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">每桶价格区间徘徊，而换算成国内成品油价，对于百姓来说，加满一箱油多则增加</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">30</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">元人民币，少则便宜十几元，影响并不是很大。”</span></span></p><p><br/></p>','国内成品油价年内难有波动','　　2016年以来，在经历了“4跌7涨6地板3搁浅”共20轮调价窗口后，国内成品油价调整再度搁浅。据国家发改委2日消息，由于没有达到国内调价要求，本轮(11月2日24时)成品油价格不调整。据统计，这是今年第四次因调价幅度低于50元/吨而搁浅。','1','1','2017-03-12 10:34:41','','0','','','0','{\"thumb\":\"\"}','0','0','0','0','','');INSERT INTO ts_posts ( `id`, `post_author`, `post_keywords`, `post_source`, `post_date`, `post_content`, `post_title`, `post_excerpt`, `post_status`, `comment_status`, `post_modified`, `post_content_filtered`, `post_parent`, `post_type`, `post_mime_type`, `comment_count`, `smeta`, `post_hits`, `post_like`, `istop`, `recommended`, `page_tpl`, `page_tpls` ) VALUES  ('345','1','出口成品油增值税恢复全额退税','','2017-03-12 10:44:14','<p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　时隔十年出口成品油增值税恢复全额退税</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　有分析称，单纯依靠增值税完全退税，对相关生产企业的提振效果可能有限</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\">　　11<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">4</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">日，财政部和国税总局联合发布了《关于提高机电、成品油等产品出口退税率的通知》，经国务院批准，自</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">11</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">1</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">日起，提高成品油</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">(</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">汽油、柴油、航煤</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">)</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">等产品的增值税出口退税率至</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">17%</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　卓创成品油分析师胡慧春表示，这意味着时隔十年后，通过进料加工贸易出口的成品油增值税恢复了全额退税。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　中国能源网首席信息官韩晓平对《每日经济新闻》记者表示，以前国内的石油供应比较紧张，国家不鼓励出口，在退税方面采取了比较严格的措施。目前国内成品油市场的供求关系发生改变，例如柴油国内供给大于需求，可以通过退税，改善企业利润，鼓励柴油出口。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　胡慧春告诉《每日经济新闻》记者，国内成品油严重过剩，意在积极鼓励出口这一手段来缓解。不过，近年来，中国成品油消费税不断提高，低油价下，其占比越来越大，消费税对生产企业的影响较大，因此，单纯依靠增值税完全退税而目前消费税并没有提及如何退税来鼓励出口，则对相关生产企业的提振效果可能有限。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\">　　9<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月柴油出口量创最高纪录</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　国际油价的持续低迷，给予国内炼厂炼油利润向好机会。早在去年</span>2<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">16</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">日，国家发改委就发布了《关于进口原油使用管理有关问题的通知》，放开地方炼厂原油进口权，炼油企业由此提高产量。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　全国人大代表、中国石油天然气集团公司生产经营管理部总经理苏俊在今年两会期间表示，截至</span>2015<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年底，我国炼油能力已达</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">7.1</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">亿吨</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">/</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年，</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">2015</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年我国原油加工量为</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">5.21</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">亿吨，平均加工负荷仅为</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">75%</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">，远低于全球炼油开工率，目前我国炼油能力已过剩</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">1</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">亿吨</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">/</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年，呈现严重过剩态势。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　这种情况下，我国成品油的产量总体仍在持续提高。据国家统计局数据显示，</span>2016<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">1~9</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月我国成品油总产量达到</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">2.55</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">亿吨，同比上涨</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">1.6%</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">，其中汽油及航煤分别上涨</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">5.8%</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">和</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">9.4%</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">，而柴油下降</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">2.8%</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　金银岛讯市场分析师李杨表示，由于我国经济增速放缓，直接导致国内工矿、运输物流等行业开工不及往年，故而对于柴油的需求构成明显打压。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　李杨指出，相对于柴油需求的明显放缓，汽油和航煤的需求量仍保持增长。随着国民收入的不断提高，私家车普及程度进一步加快，我国庞大的私家车保有量为我国汽油需求提供支撑。但近年来，随着国家对于环保的重视程度日益加深，新能源汽车推广力度大大加强，也一定程度上阻碍了汽油需求的增长速度。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　数据显示，</span>2015<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年我国成品油表观消费量</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">3.16</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">亿吨，同比增长</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">4.3%</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">，而成品油产量为</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">3.37</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">亿吨，供大于求不断扩大。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　国内市场难以满足庞大的资源供应需求的情况下，中国正在向海外市场稳步迈进。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　据海关总署数据显示，今年</span>1~9<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月中国柴油累计出口</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">1079.22</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">万吨，同比大涨</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">148.14%</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">。汽油出口量达</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">693.11</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">万吨，同比上涨</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">72.26%</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　值得注意的是，</span>9<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月汽油出口量同比上涨</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">37%</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">至</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">84.1312</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">万吨；而</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">9</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月柴油出口量同比猛增</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">44%</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">至</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">160</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">万吨，创下了柴油出口以来的最高纪录。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　中国成品油走出去步伐加快</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\">　　“今年汽油和柴油的出口出现爆发式增长，这对缓解国内成品油资源过剩有一定的作用，未来成品油的出口依旧是缓解国内资源过剩的一个重要手段。”胡慧春说。</span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　对于提高成品油等产品的增值税出口退税率至</span>17%<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">的措施，胡慧春表示，目前来料加工贸易在汽油出口的占比在</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">88.89%</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">，柴油出口的占比在</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">87.07%</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">，而这种贸易方式可以完全免税。进料加工贸易所占比重不足</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">10%</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">，即使成品油增值税完全退税，但消费税未有任何改善，整体来看，政策对进料加工及纯贸易企业的环境改善有限。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　不过，胡慧春指出，受供求关系影响，接下来企业仍然会加大成品油出口，一些周边国家有成品油需求。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　《每日经济新闻》记者注意到，目前，国内成品油在亚太市场出口量较大。数据显示，今年</span>1~9<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月，我国通过一般贸易方式出口到亚太地区的汽柴油数量超过</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">1400</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">万吨，而这已经超过去年全年的出口量。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　李杨表示，中国的炼化行业也将继续发展壮大。国内供需博弈仍将持续，也决定了后期成品油出口量将长期维持在高位水平。随着我国成品油市场的逐步放开，出厂价格与国际逐步接轨之后，中国成品油</span>“走出去”也将更加积极和顺畅。美国、南美、欧洲及中东地区均有汽柴油出口贸易发生，而随着我国积极提升成品油质量，打开欧美高端市场或许并不是难事。</span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　韩晓平表示，尽管中国成品油产能过剩，一部分成品油需要出口，但炼油过程中，有些附产品中国是短缺的，中国可能还需要从国外进口。同时，不同国家对于成品油的要求及标准不同，所以中国炼油企业也应提升自身能力，以满足不同需求。</span></span></p><p><br/></p>','出口成品油增值税恢复全额退税','　　时隔十年出口成品油增值税恢复全额退税','1','1','2017-03-12 10:43:27','','0','','','0','{\"thumb\":\"\"}','1','0','0','0','','');INSERT INTO ts_posts ( `id`, `post_author`, `post_keywords`, `post_source`, `post_date`, `post_content`, `post_title`, `post_excerpt`, `post_status`, `comment_status`, `post_modified`, `post_content_filtered`, `post_parent`, `post_type`, `post_mime_type`, `comment_count`, `smeta`, `post_hits`, `post_like`, `istop`, `recommended`, `page_tpl`, `page_tpls` ) VALUES  ('346','1','国务院批复同意东北振兴','','2017-03-12 10:45:09','<p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\">　</span><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\">&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">中国政府网</span>7<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">日消息，国务院已于近日批复同意东北振兴“十三五”规划。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　根据《国务院关于东北振兴</span>“十三五”规划的批复》，原则同意《东北振兴“十三五”规划》。《规划》实施要以提高发展质量和效益为中心，以供给侧结构性改革为主线，着力完善体制机制，着力推进结构调整，着力鼓励创新创业，着力保障和改善民生，协同推进新型工业化、信息化、城镇化和农业现代化，因地制宜、分类施策，扬长避短、扬长克短、扬长补短，有效提升老工业基地的发展活力、内生动力和整体竞争力，努力走出一条质量更高、效益更好、结构更优、优势充分释放的振兴发展新路，与全国同步全面建成小康社会。</span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　辽宁省、吉林省、黑龙江省和内蒙古自治区人民政府要深化对全面振兴东北老工业基地重要性、紧迫性的认识，增强政治意识、大局意识、核心意识、看齐意识，将《规划》确定的重大工程、重大项目、重大政策、重要改革任务与本地区经济社会发展紧密衔接起来，完善推进机制，强化政策保障，分解落实各项工作，确保《规划》提出的目标任务如期完成。</span></span></p><p><br/></p>','国务院批复同意东北振兴“十三五”规划','　  中国政府网7日消息，国务院已于近日批复同意东北振兴“十三五”规划。','1','1','2017-03-12 10:44:28','','0','','','0','{\"thumb\":\"\"}','1','0','0','0','','');INSERT INTO ts_posts ( `id`, `post_author`, `post_keywords`, `post_source`, `post_date`, `post_content`, `post_title`, `post_excerpt`, `post_status`, `comment_status`, `post_modified`, `post_content_filtered`, `post_parent`, `post_type`, `post_mime_type`, `comment_count`, `smeta`, `post_hits`, `post_like`, `istop`, `recommended`, `page_tpl`, `page_tpls` ) VALUES  ('347','1','全国成品油价格指数小幅下行','','2017-03-12 10:46:43','<p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　依据新华</span>(<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">大庆</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">)</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">国际石油资讯中心发布的报告，截至</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">11</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">4</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">日，全国成品油价格指数为</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">679.97</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">，跌幅</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">0.42%</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">，全国成品油价格指数小幅下行。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　全国成品油价格指数运行结果表明，上周</span>93#<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">汽油平均价格报收于</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">6121</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">元</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">/</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">吨，较前一报告周期下跌</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">14</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">元</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">/</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">吨</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">(</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">折合</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">0.01</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">元</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">/</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">升</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">)</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">；</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">0#</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">柴油平均价格报收于</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">6059</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">元</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">/</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">吨，较前一报告周期下跌</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">31</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">元</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">/</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">吨</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">(</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">折合</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">0.02</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">元</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">/</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">升</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">)</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">。综合来看，全国汽柴油平均价格均下跌，带动全国成品油价格指数小幅下行。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　新华</span>(<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">大庆</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">)</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">国际石油资讯中心分析师李振国认为，近期受市场对欧佩克落实减产协议存疑及美国原油库存变化影响，国际油价持续走低。国内市场悲观情绪升温，中下游需求疲软薄弱，市场成交量低位运行，中间贸易商延迟补货。地炼方面，市场出货情况逐渐转淡，业者观望心态依旧较重，汽油价格开始下调以刺激外需。国际市场方面，美国能源信息署</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">(EIA)</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">近日公布的数据显示，截至</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">10</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">28</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">日当周，美国原油库存增加</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">1442</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">万桶，为</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">EIA</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">开始统计库存数据的</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">34</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年来最大增幅，至</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">4.8258</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">亿桶，美国原油库存连续两周下滑，该消息利空国际油价。观望后市，目前市场对欧佩克落实减产协议存疑加之美元维持强势地位，预计短期内国际油价将维持震荡格局。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\">&nbsp;</span></p><p><br/></p>','全国成品油价格指数小幅下行','　　依据新华(大庆)国际石油资讯中心发布的报告，截至11月4日，全国成品油价格指数为679.97，跌幅0.42%，全国成品油价格指数小幅下行。','1','1','2017-03-12 10:45:58','','0','','','0','{\"thumb\":\"\"}','1','0','0','0','','');INSERT INTO ts_posts ( `id`, `post_author`, `post_keywords`, `post_source`, `post_date`, `post_content`, `post_title`, `post_excerpt`, `post_status`, `comment_status`, `post_modified`, `post_content_filtered`, `post_parent`, `post_type`, `post_mime_type`, `comment_count`, `smeta`, `post_hits`, `post_like`, `istop`, `recommended`, `page_tpl`, `page_tpls` ) VALUES  ('348','1','国际油价7日上涨 ','','2017-03-12 10:47:55','<p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　国际油价</span>7<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">日上涨。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　美国联邦调查局</span>6<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">日宣布维持不建议就“邮件门”起诉民主党总统候选人希拉里的结论。该消息降低了市场对于</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">8</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">日美国总统选举不确定性的担忧，在</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">7</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">日支撑油价上涨。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　然而，美元对多数主要货币汇率</span>7<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">日上涨，这降低了以美元计价的石油等大宗商品的投资吸引力，从而抑制油价上涨。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　截至当日收盘时，纽约商品交易所</span>12<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月交货的轻质原油期货价格上涨</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">0.82</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">美元，收于每桶</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">44.89</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">美元，涨幅为</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">1.86%</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">。</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">2017</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">1</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月交货的伦敦布伦特原油期货价格上涨</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">0.57</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">美元，收于每桶</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">46.15</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">美元，涨幅为</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">1.25%</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">。</span></span></p><p><br/></p>','国际油价7日上涨 收于每桶44.89美元','　　国际油价7日上涨。','1','1','2017-03-12 10:47:12','','0','','','0','{\"thumb\":\"\"}','1','0','0','0','','');INSERT INTO ts_posts ( `id`, `post_author`, `post_keywords`, `post_source`, `post_date`, `post_content`, `post_title`, `post_excerpt`, `post_status`, `comment_status`, `post_modified`, `post_content_filtered`, `post_parent`, `post_type`, `post_mime_type`, `comment_count`, `smeta`, `post_hits`, `post_like`, `istop`, `recommended`, `page_tpl`, `page_tpls` ) VALUES  ('349','1','首批低凝点-35号柴油出厂 ','','2017-03-12 10:48:43','<p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　近日，首批</span>1500<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">余吨负</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">35</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">号京标Ⅴ柴油在燕山石化顺利装火车出厂，发往内蒙古地区，为京津冀周边地区提高环境质量做出贡献，同时又开拓了新的效益增长点。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　据了解，该公司此前批量生产的低凝点负</span>35<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">号柴油均为国Ⅲ及以下标准，京Ⅴ标准的低凝柴油只批量生产过负</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">10</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">号和负</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">20</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">号，一般也只在北京地区销售。这次批量生产负</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">35</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">号京标Ⅴ柴油还是第一次。　</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　据燕山石化高级专家宋以常介绍，该公司积极调整产品结构，努力增加新品种、新牌号，多创效益。目前公司低凝柴油组分齐全，资源丰富，具备了大批量生产低凝点柴油的条件。随着冬季来临，北方市场对低凝点柴油的需求量日益增加，尤其京津冀及周边地区，还要兼顾环保要求，对高质量油品的需求更加强烈。为此，该公司今后将进一步加大高品质低凝点柴油的生产，保证市场供应。与此同时，还将通过开展市场调研，为用户量身定制、开发、生产更加清洁、更高性能的低凝柴油产品，更好地满足下游客户需求。</span></span></p><p><br/></p>','首批低凝点-35号柴油出厂 为京津冀周边环境改善提速','　　近日，首批1500余吨负35号京标Ⅴ柴油在燕山石化顺利装火车出厂，发往内蒙古地区，为京津冀周边地区提高环境质量做出贡献，同时又开拓了新的效益增长点。','1','1','2017-03-12 10:48:11','','0','','','0','{\"thumb\":\"\"}','2','0','0','0','','');INSERT INTO ts_posts ( `id`, `post_author`, `post_keywords`, `post_source`, `post_date`, `post_content`, `post_title`, `post_excerpt`, `post_status`, `comment_status`, `post_modified`, `post_content_filtered`, `post_parent`, `post_type`, `post_mime_type`, `comment_count`, `smeta`, `post_hits`, `post_like`, `istop`, `recommended`, `page_tpl`, `page_tpls` ) VALUES  ('350','1','2020年我国充电设施将可满足超500万辆电动汽车','','2017-03-12 10:49:39','<p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　根据国家发展改革委、国家能源局</span>7<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">日发布的《电力发展“十三五”规划》，将加快充电设施建设，促进电动汽车发展，</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">2020</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年充电设施将可满足全国超过</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">500</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">万辆电动汽车的充电需求。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\">　　“十三五”期间，我国将以用户居住地停车位、单位停车场、公交及出租车场站等配建的专用充电设施为主体，以公共建筑物停车场、社会公共停车场、临时停车位等配建的公共充电设施为辅助，以独立占地的城市快充站、换电站和高速公路服务区配建的城际快充站为补充，推动电动汽车充电基础设施体系加快建设。</span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\">　　2020<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年，我国将新增集中式充换电站超过</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">1.2</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">万座，分散式充电桩超过</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">480</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">万个，基本建成适度超前、车桩相随、智能高效的充电基础设施体系，满足全国超过</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">500</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">万辆电动汽车的充电需求。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　此外，从节能减排、大气治理的角度，根据规划，将推进集中供热，逐步替代燃煤小锅炉，在风能、太阳能、生物质能等可再生能源资源富集区，因地制宜发展风电供暖、太阳能光热电联供、生物质热电联产等新能源供热应用。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　规划称，到</span>2020<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年，实现北方大中型以上城市热电联产集中供热率达到</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">60%</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">以上。</span></span></p><p><br/></p>','2020年我国充电设施将可满足超500万辆电动汽车','　　根据国家发展改革委、国家能源局7日发布的《电力发展“十三五”规划》，将加快充电设施建设，促进电动汽车发展，2020年充电设施将可满足全国超过500万辆电动汽车的充电需求。','1','1','2017-03-12 10:48:55','','0','','','0','{\"thumb\":\"\"}','2','0','0','0','','');INSERT INTO ts_posts ( `id`, `post_author`, `post_keywords`, `post_source`, `post_date`, `post_content`, `post_title`, `post_excerpt`, `post_status`, `comment_status`, `post_modified`, `post_content_filtered`, `post_parent`, `post_type`, `post_mime_type`, `comment_count`, `smeta`, `post_hits`, `post_like`, `istop`, `recommended`, `page_tpl`, `page_tpls` ) VALUES  ('351','1','油企三季度成绩单：恢复期远比预估长','','2017-03-12 10:50:49','<p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　从</span>10<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月最后一周开始，大型石油公司相继提交今年第三季度财报，业内普遍认为这份“成绩单”相当于今年上半年油企业绩的总结，虽然偶有亮点，但总体表现仍然相当黯淡。显然，油气公司要真正从这场低价周期中恢复过来，还需要一段不短的时间。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　率先于</span>10<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">27</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">日发布第三季度财报的挪威国油、埃尼、道达尔和康菲石油并没能开个好头，除道达尔之外其余</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">3</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">家公司仍然是净亏损状态，甚至有的比分析师普遍预估得还差。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　挪威国油第三季度亏损进一步扩大，计划再次削减资本支出</span>10<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">亿美元。数据显示，该公司净亏损从上年同期的</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">3.07</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">亿美元扩大至</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">4.32</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">亿美元，亏损幅度超过市场预期。分析师此前预计，该公司第三季度净利润</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">1.97</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">亿美元。此外，挪威国油营业收入下降</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">11%</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">至</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">120.9</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">亿美元。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　埃尼第三季度净亏损额有所减少，从去年同期的</span>7.83<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">亿欧元降至</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">5.62</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">亿欧元，营收则同比下降</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">18%</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">至</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">131.2</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">亿欧元。不过，剔除非经常费用的调整后净亏损额达到</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">4.84</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">亿欧元，是去年同期的逾</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">3</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">倍。虽然第三季度油气产量基本保持不变，但是旗下勘探和开采部门的营收同比下降</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">21%</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　康菲石油第三季度亏损</span>10<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">亿美元，合每股亏损</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">84</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">美分；上年同期亏损</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">11</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">亿美元，合每股亏损</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">87</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">美分。不包括重组支出、养老金相关支出、资产出售利得及其它项目，调整后每股亏损为</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">66</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">美分，上年同期为每股亏损</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">38</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">美分。此前接受汤森路透调查的分析师的预期为亏损</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">70</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">美分；总收入与其它收益下降</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">13%</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">，至</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">65.2</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">亿美元，分析师的预期为</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">68.2</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">亿美元。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　道达尔第三季度业绩超预期，实现约</span>19.5<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">亿美元的净利润。数据显示，第三季度该公司实现净利润同比增长</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">81%</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">；总收入下降</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">8%</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">至</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">374.1</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">亿美元。剔除库存和非经常项目影响后，道达尔调整后净利润下降至</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">20.7</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">亿美元，低于上年同期的</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">27.6</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">亿美元。自今年年初以来，道达尔股价已经累计上涨了近</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">8%</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">，在过去</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">12</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">个月时间里则小幅下跌。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　虽然道达尔是上述</span>4<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">家公司中唯一在第三季度实现净利润的公司，但这一结果仍然不够，该公司称只有</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">2017</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年布伦特油价达到约</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">55</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">美元</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">/</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">桶，其现金流才有望负担资本支出。法国巴黎银行</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">(BNP Paribas)</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">则指出，埃尼可能要在</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">60</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">美元</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">/</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">桶的价格下才可能达到同样效果。华尔街投行</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">Jefferies</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">也预计，挪威国油明年的盈亏平衡点可能高达</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">65</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">美元</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">/</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">桶。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　同于</span>10<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">28</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">日发布第三季度财报的埃克森美孚和雪佛龙，则出现了戏剧性的变化：炼油业务亏损致埃克森美孚营收远逊市场预期，而雪佛龙虽然营收降幅超过预期，却迎来了连续</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">3</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">个季度亏损后的首次扭亏为盈。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　埃克森美孚第三季度净利润连续第</span>8<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">个季度下滑，营收连续第</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">9</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">个季度下滑，营收不及市场预期。数据显示，这个全球最大私营石油公司的净利润约</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">26.5</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">亿美元，每股收益为</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">63</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">美分，相比之下去年同期分别为净利润</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">42.4</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">亿美元和每股收益</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">1.01</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">美元。营收同比下降</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">13%</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">至</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">586.8</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">亿美元，未能达到分析师平均预期的</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">638.5</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">亿美元。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　此外，埃克森美孚第三季度上游业务净利润同比下降</span>16%<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">至</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">6.2</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">亿美元，下游业务盈利下降则是其业绩受损的主因之一，此前一直因原油和天然气价格下跌而有较好表现。第三季度中，炼油和营销业务净利润约</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">12</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">亿美元，较去年同期低</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">8.04</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">亿美元。埃克森美孚表示，炼油业务利润率的疲弱表现，对盈利造成了</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">16</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">亿美元的负面影响。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　雪佛龙第三季度盈利达到</span>13<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">亿美元，约合每股盈利</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">68</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">美分，去年同期盈利约</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">20</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">亿美元，折合每股盈利</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">1.09</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">美元；营收下跌</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">12%</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">至</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">301.4</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">亿美元，与此前分析师预计的</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">303.3</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">亿美元营收相差不大。由于盈利数据好于预期，雪佛龙股价有所上涨，该公司表示，与今年头两个季度相比有了较大改进，未来将继续致力于实现上游产业现金流的收支平衡。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\">　　BP<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">和壳牌同时在</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">11</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">1</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">日发布了第三季度财报，前者利润继续下滑，后者表现意外超预期。虽然财务状况不同，但两家公司应对低油价的手段却出奇一致：为保证盈利将缩减资本支出。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\">　　BP<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">第三季度扣除一次性项目和库存变化的利润同比暴跌</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">49%</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">，从去年同期的</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">18</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">亿美元降至</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">9.33</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">亿美元，超出市场预期，其中勘探和生产业务出现亏损，从去年同期的盈利</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">8.23</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">亿美元降至亏损约</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">2.24</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">亿美元，炼油利润率萎缩也出现萎缩。</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">BP</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">盈利状况已经连续</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">9</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">个季度持续下滑，进一步加大该公司节支和出售资产的压力。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　与</span>BP<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">不同，壳牌第三季度受益于收购带来的成本缩减，盈利超出预期。数据显示，壳牌扣除一次性项目和库存变化的利润同比增加</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">17%</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">约</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">27.9</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">亿元。壳牌首席执行官范伯登表示，本季度公司显示出强劲的运营和成本表现，但低油价对整个行业的挑战持续，前景仍不明朗。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　油价暴跌这两年来，推迟项目、大砍投资、削减岗位</span>……石油公司连喘息的时间都不敢多用，就得火急火燎地调整业务，以防被低价挤压的被迫“搁浅”。随着油企第三季度财报陆续出炉，虽然潜伏的惊喜令人愉悦，但一隅微光仍然无法照亮整个行业，对油企来说，低油价恢复期仍然前路漫漫。</span></p><p><br/></p>','油企三季度成绩单：恢复期远比预估长','　　从10月最后一周开始，大型石油公司相继提交今年第三季度财报，业内普遍认为这份“成绩单”相当于今年上半年油企业绩的总结，虽然偶有亮点，但总体表现仍然相当黯淡。','1','1','2017-03-12 10:49:50','','0','','','0','{\"thumb\":\"\"}','0','0','0','0','','');INSERT INTO ts_posts ( `id`, `post_author`, `post_keywords`, `post_source`, `post_date`, `post_content`, `post_title`, `post_excerpt`, `post_status`, `comment_status`, `post_modified`, `post_content_filtered`, `post_parent`, `post_type`, `post_mime_type`, `comment_count`, `smeta`, `post_hits`, `post_like`, `istop`, `recommended`, `page_tpl`, `page_tpls` ) VALUES  ('352','1','广东首单国企市场化债转股落地','','2017-03-12 10:51:49','<p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\">　　11<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">8</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">日，中国建设银行、广东省国资委、广东省广晟资产经营有限公司共同签署市场化债转股框架合作协议，建设银行将安排</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">150</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">亿元资金与广晟公司开展市场化债转股合作。这是今年</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">10</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月国务院出台《关于积极稳妥降低企业杠杆率的意见》及《关于市场化银行债权转股权的指导意见》后，我省首单国有企业市场化债转股合作项目。省委常委、常务副省长徐少华、中国建设银行副行长庞秀生出席了签约仪式。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　广晟公司是我省省属大型骨干企业，截至</span>9<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月底，广晟公司资产总额达到</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">1353</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">亿元，旗下拥有</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">24</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">家一级企业，为境内</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">6</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">家上市公司的实际控制人，是我省矿产资源、电子信息、工程地产、金融、环保产业的支柱企业之一。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　探索市场化银行债转股是国务院和省委、省政府</span>“积极稳妥降低企业杠杆率”的重要举措。按照协议，建设银行与广晟公司开展市场化债转股合作后，<span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">150</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">亿元将作为新增资本金注入广晟公司，有力推动其供给侧结构性改革，优化其资产负债结构。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　广晟公司董事长李泽中表示，当前，广晟公司正处于深化改革、转型升级、加快发展的关键阶段，此次债转股突出了市场化原则，将进一步降低企业资产负债水平、优化治理结构、提升企业核心竞争力。</span>“<span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">150</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">亿元资金全部到位后，预计将降低企业资产负债率</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">6</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">个百分点，节约财务成本数亿元。”</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　建行广东分行行长刘军介绍，建行及其关联方将以权益投资等多种方式向广晟公司及下属企业提供约</span>150<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">亿元资金，用于满足广晟公司“去杠杆、清僵尸、调结构”需求。他说，这不仅降低公司资产负债率和财务成本，还将促进其完善现代企业制度，提高生产经营能力，促进产业转型升级。广晟是建行在全国第三家、广东首家债转股合作企业，建行还将在广东进一步扩大债转股范围，总规模将达到</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">1000</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">亿，以债转股方式支持广东经济建设。</span></span></p><p><br/></p>','广东首单国企市场化债转股落地','　　11月8日，中国建设银行、广东省国资委、广东省广晟资产经营有限公司共同签署市场化债转股框架合作协议，建设银行将安排150亿元资金与广晟公司开展市场化债转股合作。','1','1','2017-03-12 10:51:00','','0','','','0','{\"thumb\":\"\"}','2','0','0','0','','');INSERT INTO ts_posts ( `id`, `post_author`, `post_keywords`, `post_source`, `post_date`, `post_content`, `post_title`, `post_excerpt`, `post_status`, `comment_status`, `post_modified`, `post_content_filtered`, `post_parent`, `post_type`, `post_mime_type`, `comment_count`, `smeta`, `post_hits`, `post_like`, `istop`, `recommended`, `page_tpl`, `page_tpls` ) VALUES  ('353','1','石化行业智能工厂标准有望首批立项','','2017-03-12 15:20:04','<p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　　工信部原材料工业司司长周长益日前表示，工信部已提出了智能制造标准体系总体框架，目前正在加紧制定各个行业的智能制造标准，首批</span>12<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">个通用标准已开展了立项工作，石化行业的智能工厂标准有望成为首批立项。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　周长益还透露，目前，工信部正组织企业在工业以太网、工厂无线应用、工业云计算、工业大数据等领域开展创新应用示范，并结合智能制造试点示范专项行动遴选了</span>10<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">个工业互联网试点示范项目，支持工业互联网试验验证平台、工业互联网关键资源管理平台和工业互联网商用流转数据管理平台的建设。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\">　　“总体来看石化行业的信息化、智能化走在前列，智能制造已在各个领域全面推进。”周长益介绍说，石化行业超过<span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">90%</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">的规模以上生产企业应用了过程控制系统，生产优化系统、生产制造执行、企业资源计划管理系统也已在企业中大范围应用。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　工信部已连续两年实施了智能制造试点示范专项行动，确定了两批共</span>109<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">个试点示范项目，石化行业共有</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">11</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">个项目。从数量上看，在流程工业中遥遥领先。从行业来看，去年石化、轮胎和化肥行业的企业入选，今年又增加了油气开采、煤化工、氯碱、氟化工和磷化工等行业的企业。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　与其他行业相比，石化行业流程复杂，主要大宗原料和产品</span>80%<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">以上属于危险化学品，安全环保风险高，迫切需要推进智能制造。智能化改造不仅对石化行业安全生产、节能减排具有重要作用，也是提高生产效率，提升综合竞争力的有效途径。鲁西集团通过智能化改造，安全及环保事故率下降</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">60%</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">以上，综合能耗降低</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">5%</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">，给企业带来的直接经济效益上亿元。九江石化通过智能工厂建设，生产经营管理水平快速提升，经济效益、安全环保等主要经济技术指标从中国石化排名靠后跃升为沿江企业首位。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　去年天津港</span>“<span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">8</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">·</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">12</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">”爆炸发生以后，工信部推动了城镇人口密集区危化品企业搬迁改造专项的设立，并先后向国家开发银行、农业发展银行推荐了</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">4</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">批</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">269</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">个危化品生产企业搬迁改造专项建设基金项目，拟安排的专项建设基金总额达</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">251</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">亿元。截至</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">8</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月底，已通过</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">106</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">个项目，实际安排资金</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">130</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">亿元，分别占比</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">39.4%</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">和</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">54.7%</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\">　　“我们对申请危险化学品搬迁改造项目明确提出智能化改造要求，危化品企业的搬迁工作不能是简单异地重建，而是通过搬迁实施升级改造，特别是要以提高企业本质安全水平的信息化自动化智能化改造。”周长益说。</span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　周长益指出，只有进入安全和环保有保障的化工园区，危化品企业搬迁才有意义，而信息化技术正是解决园区安全环保问题的最好手段。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　中国石油和化学工业联合会副会长傅向升表示，我国现有的</span>502<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">家化工园区中，园区的信息化、智能化大部分由入驻企业自行完成，园区管理平台和入驻企业平台之间不能互动，缺乏远程、集中控制方式，各个业务系统大多封闭运行，“孤岛”现象比较严重。智慧化工园区的建设，将有效提升园区内部的政务管理能力，实现信息共享，并为城市、园区、企业运营做好统计分析、监测预警、循环经济、战略发展等决策服务。</span></span></p><p><br/></p>','石化行业智能工厂标准有望首批立项','　　　工信部原材料工业司司长周长益日前表示，工信部已提出了智能制造标准体系总体框架，目前正在加紧制定各个行业的智能制造标准，首批12个通用标准已开展了立项工作，石化行业的智能工厂标准有望成为首批立项。','1','1','2017-03-12 15:19:27','','0','','','0','{\"thumb\":\"\"}','2','0','0','0','','');INSERT INTO ts_posts ( `id`, `post_author`, `post_keywords`, `post_source`, `post_date`, `post_content`, `post_title`, `post_excerpt`, `post_status`, `comment_status`, `post_modified`, `post_content_filtered`, `post_parent`, `post_type`, `post_mime_type`, `comment_count`, `smeta`, `post_hits`, `post_like`, `istop`, `recommended`, `page_tpl`, `page_tpls` ) VALUES  ('354','1','纽约油价8日上涨','','2017-03-12 15:23:09','<p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　纽约油价</span>8<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">日上涨。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　但当天美元对主要货币汇率上涨，降低了以美元计价的石油等大宗商品的投资吸引力，抑制了油价上涨幅度。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　截至当日收盘时，纽约商品交易所</span>12<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月交货的轻质原油期货价格上涨</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">0.09</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">美元，收于每桶</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">44.98</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">美元，涨幅为</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">0.2%</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">。</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">2017</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">1</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月交货的伦敦布伦特原油期货价格下跌</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">0.11</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">美元，收于每桶</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">46.04</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">美元，跌幅为</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">0.23%</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">。</span></span></p><p><br/></p>','纽约油价8日上涨 收于每桶44.98美元','　　纽约油价8日上涨。','1','1','2017-03-12 15:22:27','','0','','','0','{\"thumb\":\"\"}','3','0','0','0','','');INSERT INTO ts_posts ( `id`, `post_author`, `post_keywords`, `post_source`, `post_date`, `post_content`, `post_title`, `post_excerpt`, `post_status`, `comment_status`, `post_modified`, `post_content_filtered`, `post_parent`, `post_type`, `post_mime_type`, `comment_count`, `smeta`, `post_hits`, `post_like`, `istop`, `recommended`, `page_tpl`, `page_tpls` ) VALUES  ('355','1','国内油价或迎年内最大降幅 ','','2017-03-12 15:24:25','<p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　根据</span>“十个工作日”原则，国内新一轮成品油调价窗口将在<span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">11</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">16</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">日</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">24</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">时打开。昨天（</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">11</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">14</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">日）记者获悉，国内多个研究机构预计，本轮汽柴油或将迎来年内最大幅度下调。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\">　　 <span style=\"font-family:宋体\">近期，随着市场逐渐消化，以及特朗普大选获胜带来的冲击，油价收盘一度小涨。此后，欧佩克成员国原油产量增长，又导致市场供应过剩忧虑持续升温，同时，美国石油活跃钻井数也继续提升，令市场悲观情绪加深，油价收盘大幅走低。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\">&nbsp;</span><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\">　 9<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月底，石油输出国组织欧佩克宣布减产意见达成一致，但是，实际执行情况却不尽如人意。欧佩克最新公布的月度报告显示，该组织</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">10</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月日均原油产量增至</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">3364</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">万桶，达到</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">2008</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年以来最高水平。这也预示着明年国际原油市场供应过剩情况将更严重。进入</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">11</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月之后，布伦特原油期货价格和纽约原油期货价格降幅超过</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">7</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">％。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\">　　 <span style=\"font-family:宋体\">据卓创资讯监测数据显示，截至</span>11<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">11</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">日收盘，原油变化率收于</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">-9.46%</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">，相对应的成品油限价下调幅度在</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">300</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">元</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">/</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">吨。折算为升价，即</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">92</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">号汽油下调</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">0.23</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">元</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">/</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">升，</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">0</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">号柴油下调</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">0.26</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">元</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">/</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">升。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\">　　 <span style=\"font-family:宋体\">根据国内现行成品油调剂机制，</span>11<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">16</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">日</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">24</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">时，我国成品油调价时间窗口将开启。基于近期低迷的国际油价，研究机构普遍认为，本轮国内成品油价格将迎来下调，很可能创出年内最大降幅。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\">　　 <span style=\"font-family:宋体\">昨天，隆众资讯油品分析师李彦表示，</span>14<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">日是本轮调价周期的第八个工作日，从目前看，国内油价下调已经是板上钉钉的事。“今年以来国内油价下调幅度最大的一次出现在</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">8</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月，汽柴油价格每吨降幅分别为</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">220</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">元和</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">215</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">元。而本轮油价下调幅度预计将超过</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">300</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">元。”</span></span></p><p><br/></p>','国内油价或迎年内最大降幅 跌回5元时代','　　根据“十个工作日”原则，国内新一轮成品油调价窗口将在11月16日24时打开。昨天（11月14日）记者获悉，国内多个研究机构预计，本轮汽柴油或将迎来年内最大幅度下调。','1','1','2017-03-12 15:23:38','','0','','','0','{\"thumb\":\"\"}','1','0','0','0','','');INSERT INTO ts_posts ( `id`, `post_author`, `post_keywords`, `post_source`, `post_date`, `post_content`, `post_title`, `post_excerpt`, `post_status`, `comment_status`, `post_modified`, `post_content_filtered`, `post_parent`, `post_type`, `post_mime_type`, `comment_count`, `smeta`, `post_hits`, `post_like`, `istop`, `recommended`, `page_tpl`, `page_tpls` ) VALUES  ('356','1','OPEC大会在即','','2017-03-12 15:26:35','<p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　据周六</span>(11<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">12</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">日</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">)</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">凌晨美国油服公司贝克休斯公布的数据显示，截至</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">2016</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">11</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">11</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">日当周美国石油活跃钻井数增加</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">2</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">座至</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">452</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">座，上周在短暂修正后大增</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">9</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">座，延续了近期的连续升势，过去</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">24</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">周内有</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">21</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">周录得上升。这表明在油价反弹的之际，美国页岩油产商重返油市，而国际原油也迎来连续三周下跌。市场目前的焦点已经转移到</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">11</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">30</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">日的欧佩克石油大会上</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">!</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　美国原油期货价格周五收跌</span>2.8%<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">，报每桶</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">43.41</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">美元，盘中险些跌破</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">43</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">美元</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">/</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">桶的关口，最低触及</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">43.04</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">美元</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">/</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">桶；布伦特原油收跌</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">2.4%</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">，盘中触及</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">8</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月以来最低的</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">44.19</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">美元。国际原油录得连续三周下跌</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">!</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　除了美国原油钻井增加之外，全球原油产量依旧处于居高不下之势，这使得原油市场更加风雨飘摇</span>!</span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\">　　OPEC<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">在最新的月报告中称，该组织</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">10</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月原油产量再创新高，上月日产量升至</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">3364</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">万桶，较</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">9</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月增加</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">24</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">万桶，其中增加的产量主要来自尼日利亚、利比亚与伊拉克。</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">IEA</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">在月度报告中称，</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">10</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月全球供应增长</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">80</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">万桶</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">/</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">日至</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">9780</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">万桶</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">/</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">日，受到</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">OPEC</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">创纪录高产及俄罗斯、巴西、加拿大和哈萨克斯坦等非</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">OPEC</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">国家产油量增长提振。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　国际能源署之前在报告中指出，如果石油输出国组织</span>(OPEC)<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">不减产，</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">2017</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年的油市有可能还会维持供应过剩局面，因全球产油商都在加速供应而需求增长下滑。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\">　　OPEC<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">石油大会在即可能寒了原油投资者的心</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">!</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\">　　OPEC<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">将于</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">11</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">30</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">日在维也纳召开会议，讨论减产协议。全球的原油投资者都将密切关注此次</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">OPEC</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">石油大会。但是从目前的情况来看，此次会议达成减产协议的可能性比较低，如果无法达成减产协议，那么等待原油市场的将是再次重击</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">!</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\">　　OPEC<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">石油大会即将召开，但是目前</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">OPEC</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">内部依旧有近三分之一的成员国拒绝减产</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">!</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　伊朗和伊拉克都希望获得减产豁免权，</span>OPEC<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">内部举行的谈判因此陷入了僵局，在这种情况下与非</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">OPEC</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">产油国磋商就没有可能再达成任何协议。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　分析师还指出，目前的基本面因素与技术图形均有利于原油空头，但如果</span>OPEC<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">在月底达成协议的话，油价可能迅速回升到每桶</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">50</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">美元上方。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　宝盛银行大宗商品分析师</span>CarstenMenke<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">指出，对油市而言，最重要的仍是即将到来的</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">OPEC</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">大会。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\">　　Strong?Petroleum<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">的</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">Berentsen</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">指出，若</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">OPEC</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">无法达成有利的协议，我们可能会看到油价大跌至</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">35</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">美元左右。考虑到中国国内石油产量已减少约</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">10%</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">，投资者对油市供应过剩渐失耐心。</span></span></p><p><br/></p>','OPEC大会在即 油价在等待中三周连跪','　　据周六(11月12日)凌晨美国油服公司贝克休斯公布的数据显示，截至2016年11月11日当周美国石油活跃钻井数增加2座至452座，上周在短暂修正后大增9座，延续了近期的连续升势，过去24周内有21周录得上升。','1','1','2017-03-12 15:25:14','','0','','','0','{\"thumb\":\"\"}','2','0','0','0','','');INSERT INTO ts_posts ( `id`, `post_author`, `post_keywords`, `post_source`, `post_date`, `post_content`, `post_title`, `post_excerpt`, `post_status`, `comment_status`, `post_modified`, `post_content_filtered`, `post_parent`, `post_type`, `post_mime_type`, `comment_count`, `smeta`, `post_hits`, `post_like`, `istop`, `recommended`, `page_tpl`, `page_tpls` ) VALUES  ('357','1','中国明年启动碳排放交易市场','','2017-03-12 15:27:39','<p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　中国国家发改委气候司副司长蒋兆理在马拉喀什气候大会期间表示，中国将于</span>2017<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年启动全国碳排放交易市场，钢铁、石化等高耗能行业将逐步纳入该市场。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　在马拉喀什气候大会中国角举行的</span>“中国城市达峰”主题边会上，蒋兆理称，未来中国全国性碳排放交易市场将采取中央和地方分工合作的模式，即中央政府负责确定配额方法，设计排放标准和市场监管，地方政府直接向企业发放配额，并监管企业履约。</span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　蒋兆理指出，中国以先进企业的单位产品二氧化碳排放作为标准，通过基准线法来编制配额分配方法，是基于生态文明建设的一个长期信号，将引导企业决策者的未来投资方向。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　此前，发改委已批准北京、天津、上海、重庆、湖北、广东和深圳</span>7<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">个省市开展碳排放交易试点。蒋兆理表示，从若干履约季的结果来看，试点地区碳排放强度的下降速度远远快于类似条件的省市，且地方经济发展也保持平稳。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　中国建设全国碳排放交易市场的努力得到世界银行的肯定。世行副行长劳拉</span>·塔克称，在区域性的<span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">7</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">个交易市场基础上迈向全球性市场，将使中国成为全球最大的碳排放交易市场，有效应对环境污染。“这个市场的建立将受到全世界欢迎。”</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　此次边会由国家发改委气候司指导举办，是马拉喀什气候大会中国角举办的系列主题边会之一。多国代表、世界银行等国际机构高管、中国地方政府官员和学者参加了会议。</span></span></p><p><br/></p>','中国明年启动碳排放交易市场','　　中国国家发改委气候司副司长蒋兆理在马拉喀什气候大会期间表示，中国将于2017年启动全国碳排放交易市场，钢铁、石化等高耗能行业将逐步纳入该市场。','1','1','2017-03-12 15:26:48','','0','','','0','{\"thumb\":\"\"}','1','0','0','0','','');INSERT INTO ts_posts ( `id`, `post_author`, `post_keywords`, `post_source`, `post_date`, `post_content`, `post_title`, `post_excerpt`, `post_status`, `comment_status`, `post_modified`, `post_content_filtered`, `post_parent`, `post_type`, `post_mime_type`, `comment_count`, `smeta`, `post_hits`, `post_like`, `istop`, `recommended`, `page_tpl`, `page_tpls` ) VALUES  ('358','1','汽柴油价将迎年内最大幅下调','','2017-03-12 15:29:36','<p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　近期，市场对欧佩克减产协议的执行前景较为悲观，加上产油国纷纷增产使得供应过剩担忧重现，</span>10<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月下旬以来，国际油价从年内高位快速跌落，此前减产协议推动的一波涨势已消失殆尽。本计价周期内，一揽子原油变化率以大幅负值开启，随后负向幅度还有所扩大，预计</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">11</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">16</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">日</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">24</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">时，国内汽柴油价格将迎来年内最大幅下调，每升下调幅度或超过</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">0.25</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">元。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　受供应面利空打压，</span>“疲弱”是近期原油市场的主基调，截至<span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">11</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">11</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">日，</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">WTI</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">和布伦特原油期货分别收于每桶</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">43.41</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">美元和</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">44.75</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">美元，较</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">10</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月创下的年内高点累计下滑均超过</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">15%</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\">　　11<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">9</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">日，美国大选结果公布，市场预期下一届美国政府可能减轻对石油开采以及能源基建项目的限制，今年以来刚露出减产迹象的美国页岩油或在不久后卷土重来。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　未来</span>“美国石油业大发展”的前景，为本就矛盾重重的欧佩克达成减产蒙上了一层阴影。事实上，在<span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">9</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月末于阿尔及利亚达成框架性减产协议后，产油国方面一直未有实质利好跟进。</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">10</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月，各大产油国更是竞相加大马力增产，供应压力释放明显。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　国际能源信息署</span>(IEA)<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月报显示，伴随着尼日利亚和利比亚产量的回归以及伊拉克产量触及新高，</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">10</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月欧佩克产量增至</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">3383</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">万桶</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">/</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">日的创纪录高位，这一产量较</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">1</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年前高出了近</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">130</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">万桶</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">/</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">日。而据俄罗斯能源部最新数据，</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">10</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月俄罗斯原油和凝析油产量攀升至</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">1120</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">万桶</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">/</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">日，再度刷新</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">9</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月创下的纪录高位。雪上加霜的是，</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">IEA</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">预计，受俄罗斯、巴西、加拿大和哈萨克斯坦等非欧佩克产油国增产的影响，非欧佩克供应在今年缩减</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">90</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">万桶</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">/</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">日之后，在</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">2017</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年将重回增长。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　根据新华社石油价格系统发布的数据，本计价周期内，一揽子原油平均价格变化率以</span>-9.62%<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">的大幅负值开启，随后负向幅度有所加深。截至</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">11</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">11</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">日，一揽子原油变化率为</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">-11.22%</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">，根据当前变化率水平测算，</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">11</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">16</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">日</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">24</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">时新一轮成品油调价窗口打开之际，国内汽柴油价格将迎来年内最大幅度下调，预计每吨下调幅度将达</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">330-360</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">元。折合</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">93#</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">汽油每升下调</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">0.26-0.28</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">元，</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">0#</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">柴油每升下调</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">0.28-0.31</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">元。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　隆众资讯原油分析师李彦表示，鉴于本次下调幅度较大，国内部分汽油零售价格将再度跌回</span>5<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">元时代，对于私家车主来说是个不错的消息。以一辆油箱为</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">60L</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">的普通汽车为例，加满一箱油将较之前节约超过</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">15</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">元。在</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">11</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">30</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">日</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">24</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">时下一轮调价窗口开启前，车主将可以享受一段时间的低油价。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\">　　10<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">19</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">日，汽柴油零售价格刚经历了年内最大幅度上调，汽油每吨上调了</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">355</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">元，柴油每吨上调了</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">340</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">元，预计此次下调将基本冲抵这一涨幅。截至目前，今年汽柴油零售价格共经历了</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">7</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">次上调和</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">4</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">次下调，汽油累计每吨上调了</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">670</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">元，柴油累计每吨上调了</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">645</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">元。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　国内市场方面，金银岛资讯分析师刘霞认为，本轮零售价下调已成定局，消息面利空施压。供应方面，随着部分地区负号资源置换到位，油品升级进程亦在有条不紊地进行，全国范围内资源偏紧态势已有所缓解。需求方面，随着天气转冷，私家车出行半径收窄，汽油进入消费淡季；受年前工矿、基建等户外作业赶工提振，柴油终端需求或仍有一定支撑。整体来看，因前期行情涨势过猛，汽柴价格开始高位回落，主营批发环节优惠力度不断放大。目前多方利空显现，预计短期国内成品油价格将持续跌势，后期行情难言乐观。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　原油方面，华泰期货分析师认为，近期石油市场供应压力集中释放，市场对</span>OPEC<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">能否达成减产疑虑较大。在初步豁免名单上的尼日利亚和利比亚近期供应量大增，而未来若有利好政策出台，美国原油产量很可能迎来反弹，此外，美联储加息预期转强也利空油价。不过后续需求回升可能帮助消化过剩的供应，预计原油在每桶</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">45</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">美元下方仍可能获得一定的支撑。</span></span></p><p><br/></p>','汽柴油价将迎年内最大幅下调','　　近期，市场对欧佩克减产协议的执行前景较为悲观，加上产油国纷纷增产使得供应过剩担忧重现，10月下旬以来，国际油价从年内高位快速跌落，此前减产协议推动的一波涨势已消失殆尽。','1','1','2017-03-12 15:28:12','','0','','','0','{\"thumb\":\"\"}','0','0','0','0','','');INSERT INTO ts_posts ( `id`, `post_author`, `post_keywords`, `post_source`, `post_date`, `post_content`, `post_title`, `post_excerpt`, `post_status`, `comment_status`, `post_modified`, `post_content_filtered`, `post_parent`, `post_type`, `post_mime_type`, `comment_count`, `smeta`, `post_hits`, `post_like`, `istop`, `recommended`, `page_tpl`, `page_tpls` ) VALUES  ('359','1','壳牌公司投资百亿美元开采巴深海石油','','2017-03-12 15:31:44','<p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\">　　11<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">10</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">日，荷兰皇家壳牌集团全球总裁范博尔登与巴西总统泰梅尔在总统府高原宫会议后宣布，未来</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">4</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年将在巴西投资</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">100</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">亿美元。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　巴西壳牌总裁艾拉乌乔</span>(Andre Araujo)<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">、外国投资代表、巴西财政部长梅雷莱斯</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">(Henrique Meirelles)</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">、矿业暨能源部长比瑟拉</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">(Fernando Bezerra)</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">与投资合作计划处长佛朗哥</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">(Moreira Franco)</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">一同出席会议。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　巴西参众两院已完成变更深海盐层石油开采规定法案表决程序，终结强制巴西石油公司成为深海盐层石油唯一作业公司的规定，提高其他石油业巨头在巴西生产石油和天然气的参与率。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　范博尔登指出，</span>100<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">亿美元将优先投资与巴西石油公司在巴西深海盐层有关的计划，包括壳牌公司通过收购英国天然气集团</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">(BG Group)</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">和里布拉</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">(Libra)</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">油田获得的投资组合。</span></span></p><p><br/></p>','壳牌公司投资百亿美元开采巴深海石油','　　11月10日，荷兰皇家壳牌集团全球总裁范博尔登与巴西总统泰梅尔在总统府高原宫会议后宣布，未来4年将在巴西投资100亿美元。','1','1','2017-03-12 15:31:01','','0','','','0','{\"thumb\":\"\"}','1','0','0','0','','');INSERT INTO ts_posts ( `id`, `post_author`, `post_keywords`, `post_source`, `post_date`, `post_content`, `post_title`, `post_excerpt`, `post_status`, `comment_status`, `post_modified`, `post_content_filtered`, `post_parent`, `post_type`, `post_mime_type`, `comment_count`, `smeta`, `post_hits`, `post_like`, `istop`, `recommended`, `page_tpl`, `page_tpls` ) VALUES  ('360','1','福建92号汽油跌至每升5.9元 ','','2017-03-12 15:33:04','<p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　时隔一个月，国内汽柴油价格再次调整。国家发改委今日下午宣布</span>16<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">日</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">24</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">时起国内汽柴油价格每吨分别下调</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">365</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">元和</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">355</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">元。福建省物价局同步调整当地成品油价格。</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">17</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">日零时起，福建</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">92</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">号汽油每升下调</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">0.29</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">元，最高零售价每升</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">5.9</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">元。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　根据福建省物价局的通知，</span>17<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">日零时起，福建省</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">92</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">号汽油最高零售价从</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">8242</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">元</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">/</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">吨调整为</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">7855</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">元</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">/</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">吨；</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">95</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">号汽油最高零售价从</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">8708</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">元</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">/</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">吨调整为</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">8299</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">元</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">/</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">吨；车用</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">0</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">号柴油最高零售价从</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">6780</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">元</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">/</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">吨调整为</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">6425</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">元</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">/</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">吨。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　调整后，</span>92<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">号汽油、</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">95</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">号汽油、车用</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">0</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">号柴油最高零售价依次为</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">5.90</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">元</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">/</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">升、</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">6.30</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">元</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">/</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">升、</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">5.50</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">元</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">/</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">升，分别较此前下调</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">0.29</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">元</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">/</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">升、</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">0.31</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">元</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">/</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">升、</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">0.30</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">元</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">/</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">升。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　此次调整创下了汽柴油年内最大降幅。按一般家用轿车油箱</span>50L<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">的容量计算，加满一箱</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">92</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">号汽油将少花</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">14.5</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">元。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　截至目前，今年来我国汽、柴油价格已经历了四次下调、七次上调、四次搁浅、六次因国际油价低于每桶</span>40<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">美元的“地板价”而不调整。至此，年内我国汽、柴油价格累计分别上涨了每吨</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">670</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">元和</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">645</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">元。</span></span></p><p><br/></p>','福建92号汽油跌至每升5.9元 创下年内最大跌幅','　　时隔一个月，国内汽柴油价格再次调整。国家发改委今日下午宣布16日24时起国内汽柴油价格每吨分别下调365元和355元。福建省物价局同步调整当地成品油价格','1','1','2017-03-12 15:32:13','','0','','','0','{\"thumb\":\"\"}','2','0','0','0','','');INSERT INTO ts_posts ( `id`, `post_author`, `post_keywords`, `post_source`, `post_date`, `post_content`, `post_title`, `post_excerpt`, `post_status`, `comment_status`, `post_modified`, `post_content_filtered`, `post_parent`, `post_type`, `post_mime_type`, `comment_count`, `smeta`, `post_hits`, `post_like`, `istop`, `recommended`, `page_tpl`, `page_tpls` ) VALUES  ('361','1','美国发现迄今最大石油储量 ','','2017-03-12 15:34:21','<p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　周二，美国地质调查局表示，发现了迄今为止美国最大的未开发石油储量，大约可产出</span>200<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">亿桶原油和</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">16</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">亿桶液态天然气。以美油</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">45</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">美元</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">/</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">桶计算，这些储量价值高达</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">9000</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">亿美元。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　这块未开发石油储量位于德州二叠纪盆地米德兰盆地的</span>Wolfcamp<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">页岩。下面地图显示的是这块巨大的未开发石油储量。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　这块石油储量大约可以生产出</span>200<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">亿桶原油和</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">16</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">亿桶液态天然气。如果按现在</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">WTI</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">原油价格</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">45</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">美元</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">/</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">桶计算，这些储量的价值高达</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">9000</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">亿美元。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\">　　2011<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年以来，二叠纪盆地的潜在价值就引起了许多独立石油公司和私人股本公司的注意。美国石油勘探公司纷纷涌入，利用页岩油钻井技术，获取大量石油。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　然而，由于页岩油的蓬勃发展，使得市场上的原油过剩，油价两年前出现暴跌。在近年来油价的熊途中，油井开发数大体呈减少态势。然而，随着今年二季度以来油价回暖，最近几个月石油钻井开发活动又有复苏。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　上周，美国油服公司贝克休斯</span>(Baker Hughes)<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">公布数据显示，</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">11</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">11</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">日当周，美国石油钻井平台增加</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">2</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">台，至</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">452</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">台，创九个月以来新高。当周油井平台总数减少</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">1</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">台，至</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">568</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">台。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\">　　USGS<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">能源资源项目协调人</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">Walter Guidroz</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">表示，这表明，即使是在已经开发了几十亿桶原油的领域，依然有可能发现巨大的未开发石油储量。</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">USGS</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">数据显示，在米德兰盆地的</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">Wolfcamp</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">页岩，已经开采完了</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">3000</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">多个油井。</span></span></p><p><br/></p>','美国发现迄今最大石油储量 价值9000亿美元','　　周二，美国地质调查局表示，发现了迄今为止美国最大的未开发石油储量，大约可产出200亿桶原油和16亿桶液态天然气。以美油45美元/桶计算，这些储量价值高达9000亿美元。','1','1','2017-03-12 15:33:25','','0','','','0','{\"thumb\":\"\"}','0','0','0','0','','');INSERT INTO ts_posts ( `id`, `post_author`, `post_keywords`, `post_source`, `post_date`, `post_content`, `post_title`, `post_excerpt`, `post_status`, `comment_status`, `post_modified`, `post_content_filtered`, `post_parent`, `post_type`, `post_mime_type`, `comment_count`, `smeta`, `post_hits`, `post_like`, `istop`, `recommended`, `page_tpl`, `page_tpls` ) VALUES  ('362','1','原油需求将持续增长','','2017-03-12 15:35:38','<p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　国际能源署</span>(IEA)<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">在近日公布的报告中表示，世界各国对化石燃料的依赖还远未结束，尽管去年巴黎气候变化峰会上各方做出了限制温室气体排放的承诺，但预计</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">2040</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年之前原油需求将持续增长。换言之，原油需求在</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">2040</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年之前不会“见顶”。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　报告指出，在公路货运、航空和石化领域很难找到原油的替代品，意味着</span>2040<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年以前，仅仅这三个领域的原油需求增幅就高于全球原油需求增幅。该报告提出的核心情境是，</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">2040</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年全球石油需求可能会增长近</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">12%</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">至</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">1.035</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">亿桶</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">/</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">日；与之相比，</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">2015</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年的全球石油需求为</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">9250</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">万桶</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">/</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">日。印度将成为需求增长的主要来源。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　对于近期而言，</span>IEA<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">维持</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">2016</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年全球原油需求增长预期</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">120</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">万桶</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">/</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">日不变，并预计</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">2017</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年与</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">2016</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年的需求增长预期持平。</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">IEA</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">称，并没有多少证据显示全球经济活动足够强劲，足以进一步提升原油需求增速。</span></span></p><p><br/></p>','IEA报告称：原油需求将持续增长','　　国际能源署(IEA)在近日公布的报告中表示，世界各国对化石燃料的依赖还远未结束，尽管去年巴黎气候变化峰会上各方做出了限制温室气体排放的承诺，但预计2040年之前原油需求将持续增长。换言之，原油需求在2040年之前不会“见顶”。','1','1','2017-03-12 15:34:44','','0','','','0','{\"thumb\":\"\"}','2','0','0','0','','');INSERT INTO ts_posts ( `id`, `post_author`, `post_keywords`, `post_source`, `post_date`, `post_content`, `post_title`, `post_excerpt`, `post_status`, `comment_status`, `post_modified`, `post_content_filtered`, `post_parent`, `post_type`, `post_mime_type`, `comment_count`, `smeta`, `post_hits`, `post_like`, `istop`, `recommended`, `page_tpl`, `page_tpls` ) VALUES  ('363','1','中国是国际石油贸易市场少有的亮点','','2017-03-12 15:41:07','<p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　中国商务部外贸司副司长支陆逊</span>17<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">日在上海表示，近年来世界经济增长乏力，世界石油的供求形势从供不应求变成供大于求，国际原油价格一直低迷，在这样的背景下，中国成为了国际石油贸易市场少有的亮点。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　在此间举办的</span>“第五届中国国际石油贸易大会”上，支陆逊称，经济的发展使中国对石油产品的需求不断扩大，<span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">2015</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年中国进口原油同比增长</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">8%</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">，贸易量占世界贸易总量的近</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">17%</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">，仅次于美国。当年中国石油消费量同比增长超过</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">6%</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">，占世界市场的份额也超过了一成，继续保持世界第一，今年</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">1</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">到</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">10</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月份，中国原油进口继续保持强劲增长态势，同比增幅</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">13.6%</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\">　　“中国正在推进原油进口体制改革，已逐步形成了主体多元、竞争有序、富有活力的原油进口经营体制。中国稳定的进口市场，对平衡全球油气市场具有重要作用。一个节能、高效、环境友好、开放合作的中国能源市场，有利于所有的能源生产国、消费国”，支陆逊说。</span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　国际能源署高级专家亚利桑德罗</span>·布拉西表示，<span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">2015</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年全球能源投资</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">1.8</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">万亿美元，比</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">2014</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年下降</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">8%</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">，其中可替代能源投资占比</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">17%</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">、能效方面的投资占比</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">12%</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">。全球排名前五位的能源市场，占据了全球能源供应的半壁江山。中国因为在电力系统方面创纪录的投资，而位列当年全球能源投资第一。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　据中国联合石油有限责任公司总裁赵勇透露，近十年来，中国原油消费年均增速为</span>16.4%<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">，</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">2015</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年中国消费原油</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">5.4</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">亿吨、进口原油</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">3.35</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">亿吨，原油对外依存度为</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">60.8%</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">，中东仍是中国最大的原油进口市场。与此同时，中国成品油出口增长迅速，</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">2016</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年前三季度，中国成品油累计出口已超过</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">2015</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年全年。不过他同时表示，</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">2015</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年中国的炼油能力已达</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">7.3</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">亿吨，过剩矛盾突出。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　中国发改委能源研究所副所长高世宪称，其实当前中国的能耗增量和增速是在趋缓的。他指出，中国将继续推动能耗供给改革，构建多元、清洁、低碳、安全、高效、现代的能源体系，提高非化石能源比重，促进煤炭等化石能源的清洁高效使用，至</span>2020<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年和</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">2030</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年，中国非石化能耗消费量在能耗总量中的占比将达到</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">15%</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">和</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">20%</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">。</span></span></p><p><br/></p>','中国是国际石油贸易市场少有的亮点','　　中国商务部外贸司副司长支陆逊17日在上海表示，近年来世界经济增长乏力，世界石油的供求形势从供不应求变成供大于求，国际原油价格一直低迷，在这样的背景下，中国成为了国际石油贸易市场少有的亮点。','1','1','2017-03-12 15:40:05','','0','','','0','{\"thumb\":\"\"}','3','0','0','0','','');INSERT INTO ts_posts ( `id`, `post_author`, `post_keywords`, `post_source`, `post_date`, `post_content`, `post_title`, `post_excerpt`, `post_status`, `comment_status`, `post_modified`, `post_content_filtered`, `post_parent`, `post_type`, `post_mime_type`, `comment_count`, `smeta`, `post_hits`, `post_like`, `istop`, `recommended`, `page_tpl`, `page_tpls` ) VALUES  ('364','1','我国成品油出口现爆发式增长','','2017-03-12 15:42:41','<p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　海关总署最新发布的数据显示，</span>2016<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">1</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月至</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">10</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月，我国成品油出口量达到</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">3811</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">万吨，同比增长</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">37.4%</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">，已经超过去年全年总量。从净进口到净出口，再到出口量不断创新高，我国成品油进出口贸易格局在短短几年内发生了翻天覆地的变化。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　国内炼油产能在不断增加，而成品油整体需求增速放缓，出口成为平衡国内市场的重要途径。与此同时，深度参与国际贸易竞争，也是检验我国成品油产业竞争力的重要手段。业内专家预计，</span>“十三五”期间，我国成品油出口量仍将不断扩大。</span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　据中国石化经济技术研究院副院长毛加祥介绍，</span>2010<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年以来，我国成品油消费年均增速已降到</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">4.2%</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">。其中，</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">2015</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年我国柴油消费已达到峰值，预计在</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">2025</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年和</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">2035</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年汽油消费和航空煤油消费也会先后达到峰值。在供应市场，目前我国炼油能力超过</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">7</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">亿吨，产能过剩严重，而且“十三五”期间炼油产能仍将进一步扩大。这意味着炼油能力过剩的问题将进一步凸显。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　中国联合石油有限责任公司总裁赵勇在第五届中国国际石油贸易大会上表示，其实今年前三季度我国成品油出口量就已超过去年总量。目前，我国成品油主要向东南亚出口，也有部分资源流向澳大利亚和南美市场。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　赵勇介绍，</span>2015<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年我国炼油能力达到每年</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">7.3</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">亿吨，</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">2020</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年或达到每年</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">8</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">亿吨，每年产能过剩约</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">8000</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">万吨。在此背景下，预计我国成品油出口或继续扩大。从全球成品油贸易市场环境来看，近年来，全球新增炼油能力主要集中在中东、印度和中国。预计</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">2020</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年全球成品油需求量达到</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">49.5</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">亿吨，不过，从全球炼能扩展的速度来看，全球成品油市场也呈现供应过剩的局面。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　曾经有人提出质疑，为什么我国大量进口原油却还要向海外出口成品油</span>?<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">其实，原油进口和成品油出口并不存在对立关系。相反，日本、韩国、新加坡这些几乎</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">100%</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">依赖进口原油的国家一直是亚太地区活跃的成品油出口国，而且成品油加工已经成为这些国家的重要经济产业。近年来，我国炼油能力不断提升，使得国内成品油市场由供应短缺变为富裕过剩，进而成品油出口成为调节国内市场平衡的重要工具。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　随着我国成品油出口不断放大，亚太地区成品油贸易格局也发生了改变。毛加祥表示，我国成品油出口面临着与日本、韩国、新加坡等国的竞争。这些国家对成品油出口实施免税的鼓励政策，呼吁我国也加大对成品油出口的支持力度，提升我国成品油出口的国际竞争力。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　其实，国际成品油贸易市场新近崛起的</span>“明星”不是只有中国。据剑桥能源咨询石油市场研究经理刘海全介绍，<span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">2013</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年以来，美国炼厂的成品油出口呈现爆发式增长。中东地区也在延长其石油产业链，从上游向中下游拓展。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　毛加祥表示，如果我国成品油出口半径只局限于亚太地区的话，我国仍有一定的竞争优势。但如果继续扩大出口面，就需要配套大型成品油出口设施，包括码头、仓储、运力等。</span></span></p><p><br/></p>','我国成品油出口现爆发式增长','　　海关总署最新发布的数据显示，2016年1月至10月，我国成品油出口量达到3811万吨，同比增长37.4%，已经超过去年全年总量。从净进口到净出口，再到出口量不断创新高，我国成品油进出口贸易格局在短短几年内发生了翻天覆地的变化。','1','1','2017-03-12 15:41:24','','0','','','0','{\"thumb\":\"\"}','1','0','0','0','','');INSERT INTO ts_posts ( `id`, `post_author`, `post_keywords`, `post_source`, `post_date`, `post_content`, `post_title`, `post_excerpt`, `post_status`, `comment_status`, `post_modified`, `post_content_filtered`, `post_parent`, `post_type`, `post_mime_type`, `comment_count`, `smeta`, `post_hits`, `post_like`, `istop`, `recommended`, `page_tpl`, `page_tpls` ) VALUES  ('365','1','欧佩克将讨论减产协议 ','','2017-03-12 20:09:40','<p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　欧佩克将于</span>11<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">30</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">日召开维也纳会议，讨论让各方满意的减产协议细节。会议临近，欧佩克官员正在努力缩小部分成员国之间的分歧，避免会议成果受挫。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　今年</span>9<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月份，欧佩克达成减产意向，试图缓解全球原油供应过剩的局面，提振原油市场。但由于欧佩克内部对如何落实减产存在分歧，导致磋商过后各方未能达成任何具体减产配额，最终敲定减产计划细节问题的艰巨任务则留在</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">11</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月末的维也纳会议上进行讨论。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　此后，主要产油国召开了多次会议，包括欧佩克内部会议和欧佩克与非欧佩克共同会议等商讨细节，并取得了部分成果。比如，在份额分配计算方法上有所进展。非欧佩克国家也纷纷释放出友好的态度，如俄罗斯能源部长称，对俄罗斯与欧佩克达成协议更有信心。阿曼表示，愿意减产，但在欧佩克内部达成一致前，该国仍然无法就具体的减产数字作出承诺。阿塞拜疆对于与欧佩克合作也非常感兴趣，希望能够进一步了解欧佩克为维持油市稳定所作出的努力，并且希望能够找到非欧佩克国家在其中可以扮演的角色。即便是明确表示不会干涉国内产量的巴西，也希望能加强与欧佩克的合作。大部分国家已达成共识，主要分歧来自伊拉克和伊朗。但从最新消息看，这两国的态度也在发生变化。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　上周末，欧佩克召开的多哈会议上传来的消息，提振了</span>11<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月底协议达成的预期，欧佩克可能将原油产量限制在每日</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">3250</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">万桶水平上。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　俄罗斯能源部长诺瓦克表示，多哈会议具有建设性，他确定欧佩克会在</span>11<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">30</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">日的会议中达成协议。诺瓦克还称，俄罗斯准备好限产，准备好加入欧佩克协议。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　伊拉克石油部长阿鲁艾比表示，对欧佩克产油国在下次会议上达成协议持乐观态度，已经和欧佩克在解决双方分歧上获得进展。阿鲁艾比</span>11<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">20</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">日又表示，伊拉克将在维也纳会议上提出三项建议讨论实施欧佩克的减产计划，这意味着该国正在逐步解决与欧佩克之间的分歧。阿鲁艾比表示，伊拉克的提案料将与欧佩克政策一致。阿鲁艾比补充道：“我们的可替代方案是建立在其他变量基础上的，这将令欧佩克成员更容易作出决定。所有的选项都是符合逻辑的且与欧佩克政策一致。”</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　伊朗一直是本次减产协议的主要障碍，因为伊朗政府希望豁免本次减产，在今年</span>1<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月份的西方制裁被取消之后，伊朗一直试图夺回原先在石油市场的份额。根据欧佩克此前的限产意向，解除制裁不久的伊朗，以及利比亚和尼日利亚都可能获得豁免权。据报道，多哈会议上，欧佩克成员国提议伊朗石油产量限制在大约</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">392</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">万桶。为了尽快达成协议，欧佩克在多哈会议上实际上对伊朗产量作出了让步，希望加大月底达成协议的可能。欧佩克秘书长巴尔金都明确表示，希望伊朗在欧佩克维也纳会议上与其他成员国团结一致。而没有参加多哈会议的伊朗石油部长赞加内上周五晚间也表示，维也纳会议会有很高可能性达成协定，他对未来发展前景持乐观态度。不过，他认为，在改善油市状况方面，产量越高的国家拥有的责任越大。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　尽管欧佩克减产协议的利好消息不断，但美元走强仍令油价涨势受限。</span></span></p><p><br/></p>','欧佩克将讨论减产协议 产量限制在每日3250万桶','　　欧佩克将于11月30日召开维也纳会议，讨论让各方满意的减产协议细节。会议临近，欧佩克官员正在努力缩小部分成员国之间的分歧，避免会议成果受挫。','1','1','2017-03-12 20:06:46','','0','','','0','{\"thumb\":\"\"}','0','0','0','0','','');INSERT INTO ts_posts ( `id`, `post_author`, `post_keywords`, `post_source`, `post_date`, `post_content`, `post_title`, `post_excerpt`, `post_status`, `comment_status`, `post_modified`, `post_content_filtered`, `post_parent`, `post_type`, `post_mime_type`, `comment_count`, `smeta`, `post_hits`, `post_like`, `istop`, `recommended`, `page_tpl`, `page_tpls` ) VALUES  ('366','1','北京国Ⅰ国Ⅱ车不准进五环','','2017-03-12 20:16:27','<p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\">　　11<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">21</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">日，记者从北京市政府新闻办举行的发布会上获悉：从</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">2017</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">2</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">15</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">日起，北京市将对本市及外埠的国Ⅰ国Ⅱ排放标准轻型汽油车，实施五环路</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">(</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">不含</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">)</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">以内道路工作日限行。对于机动车违反规定进入限行区域道路行驶的，公安交通管理部门按照相关法律规定，给予罚款</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">100</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">元，每</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">4</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">小时计罚一次。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　同时，为鼓励车主更新淘汰高污染排放老旧车，政府配套出台了鼓励淘汰的补助政策。其中，</span>2017<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">6</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月底前淘汰可比</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">2017</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">7</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月至</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">12</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月底淘汰多得政府补助</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">2000</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">元。具体而言，</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">2017</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">6</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月底前淘汰国Ⅰ排放标准小型客车可获</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">10000</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">元补贴，淘汰国Ⅱ排放标准小型客车可获</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">12000</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">元补贴。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　虽然国</span>Ⅰ国Ⅱ机动车在北京机动车总量中占比并不大，但从绝对数量看，仍有<span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">40</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">万家庭会受到此项新政的影响，为此，记者就政策出台的来龙去脉采访了相关部门负责人。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\">　　</span><strong><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;font-size: 14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">问北京大气污染，机动车影响有多大</span></span></strong></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><strong><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;font-size: 14px\">　　PM2.5<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">本地污染中，机动车排放占</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">31.1%</span></span></strong></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　从淘汰黄标车，到空气重污染红色预警实施单双号限行，再到此次国</span>Ⅰ国Ⅱ轻型汽油车工作日不得进入北京市五环路，北京市对机动车的管理可谓是越来越严格。</span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　北京市环保局副局长、新闻发言人方力介绍，目前北京市机动车保有量已达</span>570<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">万辆，每年排放污染物总量约为</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">50</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">万吨，排放的一氧化碳、氮氧化物、挥发性有机物，分别占到该类污染物全市排放总量的</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">86%</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">、</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">56%</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">、</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">38%</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　在细颗粒物</span>(PM2.5)<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">本地污染贡献中，北京全年机动车排放贡献比例达</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">31.1%</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">，其中非采暖季机动车排放更是达到本地源排放的</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">40%</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">以上。可以说，机动车排放污染是北京本地</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">PM2.5</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">的最大来源。例如，今年</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">10</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">14</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">日至</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">16</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">日发生的空气重污染过程中，</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">PM2.5</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">中硝酸盐占比高达</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">35%</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">左右，成为占比最大的</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">PM2.5</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">组分，反映出机动车污染排放在本次重污染中作用较大，因此北京治理大气污染必须突出机动车污染减排。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　另一方面，北京虽然重视机动车尾气治理，但也并不是只拿机动车</span>“说事儿”。<span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">2015</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年北京</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">PM2.5</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">平均浓度是</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">80.6</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">微克</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">/</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">立方米，到明年要达到</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">60</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">微克</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">/</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">立方米的目标，意味着要在短短两年时间下降</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">1/4</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">。“毫无疑问这是一项艰巨的任务，必须采取方方面面的有效措施，哪一方面存在短板都难以如期完成目标。”方力说。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　事实上，北京针对各类污染来源均采取治理措施，综合施治。比如，针对燃煤污染，</span>2015<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年年燃煤总量已由</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">2012</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年的</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">2300</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">万吨下降到</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">1200</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">万吨以内，今年进一步削减至</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">1000</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">万吨以内。在非采暖季，北京二氧化硫的浓度只有几微克，与欧盟的平均水平相当，这意味着非采暖季的燃煤问题已经基本解决。为治理采暖季的燃煤污染，今年北京在农村</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">463</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">个村实施了规模空前的“煤改电”改造，几乎相当于此前</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">13</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年工作总量的一半。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><strong><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;font-size: 14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　问国</span>Ⅰ国Ⅱ车限行，对治污作用有多大</span></strong></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><strong><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;font-size: 14px\">　　</span></strong><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;font-size: 14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">减少氮氧化物、挥发性有机物将占轻型汽油车排放的</span>15%<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">和</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">12%</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">左右</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　随着机动车保有量仍进一步增长，车龄大、里程长的高污染排放老旧车问题突出。高污染排放车是一个相对概念，是指在现有机动车结构内排放标准低、年头多、里程长、车况差、污染重的车辆，这部分车辆虽然在机动车总量中占比不高，但其污染排放占比较大。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　北京在黄标车基本淘汰完毕后，国</span>Ⅰ国Ⅱ标准车辆就成为汽油车中排放污染最严重的车辆。综合测算，同等行驶里程条件下，<span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">1</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">辆国Ⅰ标准轻型汽油车的排放相当于</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">6</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">辆以上国Ⅴ标准轻型汽油车，</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">1</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">辆国Ⅱ标准轻型汽油车的排放相当于</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">3</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">辆国Ⅴ标准轻型汽油车。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　目前，北京市国</span>Ⅰ排放标准车辆至今最短已使用<span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">13</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年，国Ⅱ排放标准车辆至今最短也已使用</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">10</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年。虽然保有量只占全市轻型汽油车保有量的</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">8%</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">，而排放氮氧化物约占全市轻型汽油车排放的</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">30%</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">以上，挥发性有机物约占</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">25%</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　北京市环保局机动车排放管理处处长李昆生介绍，经测算，国</span>Ⅰ国Ⅱ轻型汽油车执行五环路<span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">(</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">不含</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">)</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">内工作日限行措施后，将减少氮氧化物排放占轻型汽油车排放的</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">15%</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">左右，减少挥发性有机物排放占轻型汽油车排放的</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">12%</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">左右。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　据介绍，对高排放机动车实施限行，是国内外的通行做法。目前，伦敦、斯德哥尔摩、米兰、柏林、慕尼黑等国际大城市均采取机动车低排放区政策，对高排放车的限制措施最高已升级至</span>“欧Ⅲ”标准<span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">(</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">相当于我国“国Ⅲ”标准</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">)</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">车辆。上海市从</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">2015</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">4</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">1</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">日和</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">2016</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">1</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">1</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">日起，分别实施国Ⅰ汽油车和</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">2005</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年前注册的国Ⅱ标准汽油车外环</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">(</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">含</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">)</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">内道路限行，并准备将限行范围进一步扩大。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\">　　“借鉴国内外治理经验，并依据《北京市大气污染防治条例》第七十二条及第七十八条规定，我市制定了关于对国Ⅰ及国Ⅱ排放标准轻型汽油车采取交通管理措施的政策。”李昆生介绍。</span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\">　</span><strong><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;font-size: 14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　问大气污染会传输，光北京限行管用吗</span></span></strong></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><strong><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;font-size: 14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　区域间联防联控的基础是做好自己该做的事</span></span></strong></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　在方力看来，大气传输机制下京津冀地区空气质量相互影响，使得建立区域间联防联控非常必要。然而，区域间联防联控的基础是首先要根据自己的污染源做好自己该做的事情。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　北京是首都，在治理大气污染方面也承担着更多的责任。在国务院的</span>“大气十条”里，只有北京有一个明确的绝对值任务——就是到<span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">2017</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年细颗粒物年均浓度控制在</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">60</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">微克</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">/</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">立方米左右，其他地区都是相对数，比如京津冀、长三角、珠三角等区域细颗粒物浓度分别下降</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">25%</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">、</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">20%</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">、</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">15%</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">左右。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　生态环境保护是京津冀协同发展</span>3<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">个率先突破的重点领域之一，大气污染则是北京市面临的最突出、最紧迫、最受关注的环境问题。北京市将大气污染防治作为全市工作的重中之重，作为推动京津冀协同发展的重要突破口，采取一切可能的措施完成党中央、国务院的部署，许多举措在全国领先。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　就拿治理机动车污染而言，自</span>2004<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年起，北京市制定并实施严于国家标准的地方油品标准，分别于</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">2004</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年、</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">2005</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年、</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">2008</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年、</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">2012</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年率先在全国实施了第二、三、四和五阶段地方油品标准。明年</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">1</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">1</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">日起，北京将率先实施第六阶段车用燃油标准。同时，北京市分别于</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">1999</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年、</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">2002</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年、</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">2005</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年、</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">2008</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年和</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">2013</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年率先在全国执行了机动车国Ⅰ、国Ⅱ、国Ⅲ、国Ⅳ和国Ⅴ排放标准，每次执行新标准均提前全国</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">2</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">至</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">3</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\">　　“各地经济发展水平不一，污染源头相异，这也必然带来工作重点不同。”方力表示，针对大气污染的传输问题，国家有关部门高度重视。近年来，在京津冀及周边地区大气污染防治协作小组的领导下，北京联合环境保护部以及周边六省<span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">(</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">区、市</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">)</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">，大力开展联防联控，取得实质性进展，相信在这方面会做得越来越好。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　链接</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\">　　</span><strong><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;font-size: 14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">如何辨别国</span>Ⅰ国Ⅱ车</span></strong></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　首先</span>“算时间”，可以根据行驶本上标注的车辆注册登记日期来辨别。在本市<span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">2006</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">6</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">30</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">日之后买的车就不是国Ⅰ国Ⅱ车了。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　二是</span>“数星星”，也就是看机动车年检发放的环保标志。如果是没有星星、<span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">1</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">颗星或</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">2</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">颗星的绿色标志的，就是国Ⅰ国Ⅱ车。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　三是</span>“看材料”，根据购买新车时汽车厂家出具的机动车整车出厂合格证等材料标注的车辆排放标准。</span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　四是</span>“求帮助”，可以登录北京市环保局网站“机动车排放标准查询”栏目查询；或者直接拨打“<span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">12369</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">”北京环保投诉举报咨询电话，请工作人员帮助您直接查询。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;font-size: 14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　此外，车主怎样才能领取政府补助呢？</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　首先将老旧机动车送交具有正规资质的汽车解体厂报废解体，然后通过平台信息系统或业务办理网点填写老旧机动车报废政府补助申请，交易平台会审核车主信息，审核通过后车主到办理网点提交相关资料，审核合格后</span>20<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">个工作日内，北京市环保局将补助资金划拨至以车主名义设立的单位开户银行账户或个人指定建行活期储蓄账户。</span></span></p><p><br/></p>','北京国Ⅰ国Ⅱ车不准进五环','　　11月21日，记者从北京市政府新闻办举行的发布会上获悉：从2017年2月15日起，北京市将对本市及外埠的国Ⅰ国Ⅱ排放标准轻型汽油车，实施五环路(不含)以内道路工作日限行。','1','1','2017-03-12 20:15:55','','0','','','0','{\"thumb\":\"\"}','0','0','0','0','','');INSERT INTO ts_posts ( `id`, `post_author`, `post_keywords`, `post_source`, `post_date`, `post_content`, `post_title`, `post_excerpt`, `post_status`, `comment_status`, `post_modified`, `post_content_filtered`, `post_parent`, `post_type`, `post_mime_type`, `comment_count`, `smeta`, `post_hits`, `post_like`, `istop`, `recommended`, `page_tpl`, `page_tpls` ) VALUES  ('367','1','国际油价23日下跌 ','','2017-03-12 20:17:40','<p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　国际油价</span>23<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">日下跌。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　美国能源信息局当天公布的数据显示，上周美国全国商业原油库存为</span>4.89<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">亿桶，环比下降。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　市场分析人士表示，美元当天走强，降低了以美元计价的石油投资吸引力，令油价微跌。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　截至当天收盘，纽约商品交易所</span>2017<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">1</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月交货的轻质原油期货价格下跌</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">0.07</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">美元，收于每桶</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">47.96</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">美元，跌幅为</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">0.15%</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">。</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">2017</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">1</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月交货的伦敦布伦特原油期货价格下跌</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">0.17</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">美元，收于每桶</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">48.95</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">美元，跌幅为</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">0.35%</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">。</span></span></p><p><br/></p>','国际油价23日下跌 收于每桶47.96美元','　　国际油价23日下跌。','1','1','2017-03-12 20:16:53','','0','','','0','{\"thumb\":\"\"}','1','0','0','0','','');INSERT INTO ts_posts ( `id`, `post_author`, `post_keywords`, `post_source`, `post_date`, `post_content`, `post_title`, `post_excerpt`, `post_status`, `comment_status`, `post_modified`, `post_content_filtered`, `post_parent`, `post_type`, `post_mime_type`, `comment_count`, `smeta`, `post_hits`, `post_like`, `istop`, `recommended`, `page_tpl`, `page_tpls` ) VALUES  ('368','1','北京为何限行“国一、国二”轻型汽油车？','','2017-03-12 20:20:11','<p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　最新修订的《北京市空气重污染应急预案》自１２月１５日起施行，此后空气重污染橙色、红色预警时，国一、国二轻型汽油车全市禁行。此外，针对北京现存国一、国二轻型汽油车的限行新规也将于明年２月１５日起生效，即</span>“五环路（不含）以内道路工作日限行”。</span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　记者了解到，此番</span>“限行”新政，意在促进“末位淘汰”，改善北京市机动车排放结构，而淘汰更新方案中的政府补助较高、银行贷款灵活，显示出经济政策撬动减排。</span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\">　　</span><strong><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;font-size: 14px\">“国一、国二”排放有多“凶猛”？</span></strong></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　得益于多年持续综合施治，目前，北京市已基本解决非采暖季燃煤污染，工业污染亦获得有效控制，ＰＭ２．５贡献占比居首的机动车，成为最大</span>“心肺之患”。</span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\">　　“在非采暖季，二氧化硫浓度长期稳定低于１０微克／立方米，意味着北京基本解决非采暖季燃煤污染，立足于深耕本地污染减排，低排放标准的机动车成为治理重点。”北京市环保局副局长、新闻发言人方力说，在ＰＭ２．５本地污染贡献中，全年机动车排放贡献比例达３１．１％，其中非采暖季机动车排放占比超过４０％。</span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　专家指出，重型柴油车污染严重，在于其黑烟排放，其中含有大量ＰＭ１直排。而轻型汽油小客车排放的挥发性有机物，占机动车排放总量的８０％至９０％。</span>“黑烟”和“挥发性有机物”都是机动车污染的重要贡献者，治理需双管齐下。</span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\">　　“轻型汽油车对ＰＭ２．５的贡献，在于二次反应过程。”北京市环保局机动车排放管理处处长李昆生说，机动车排放的氮氧化物、挥发性有机物，约５０％会转化成ＰＭ２．５。</span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　目前，北京市机动车保有量达５７０万辆，年均排污总量约５０万吨。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　方力说，国一、国二轻型汽油车虽然只占北京轻型汽油车保有量８％，但排放的氮氧化物、挥发性有机物分别约占全市轻型汽油车排放的３０％、２５％。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　经综合测算，同等行驶里程条件下，１辆</span>“国一”轻型汽油车的排放相当于６辆以上“国五”标准轻型汽油车，１辆“国二”轻型汽油车的排放相当于３辆“国五”标准轻型汽油车。</span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\">　　“国一、国二车限行”目的是优化机动车结构，这仅仅是北京治理机动车的一个方面，综合施策还包括“为在用车提供更好的燃油”“让新车更加干净”“严格执法控制超标排放车上路”等。据介绍，车用燃油“京六”排放标准，将于明年１月起施行。</span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　李昆生说，限行新政实施后，将减少氮氧化物排放占轻型汽油车排放的１５％左右，减少挥发性有机物排放占轻型汽油车排放的１２％左右。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><strong><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;font-size: 14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　北京并非国内首创</span></span></strong></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　对高污染排放车辆进行限行、促进淘汰，从而改善整个地区车辆结构，是国际上减少机动车污染行之有效的措施，北京也并非国内首创。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　方力介绍，上海市从２０１５年４月１日、２０１６年１月１日起，分别实施了</span>“国一”标准汽油车、２００５年前注册的“国二”标准汽油车外环路（含）道路禁行。</span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　国际上，欧美许多大城市对机动车污染治理的措施，也严于北京。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　方力说，欧洲有超过２００个</span>“低排放区”。英国伦敦设定大伦敦地区为低排放区，只允许“欧四”（相当于国四）及以上标准的车辆进入。德国为柏林、汉诺威、科隆等大城市的某些区域设立“低排放区”，限制“欧三”小客车等车辆进入。在意大利米兰，部分区域禁止“欧三”及以下排放标准的柴油小客车、“欧零”汽油车行驶。在墨西哥城，符合最严排放标准的车辆可每天进入城市中心及“低排放区”，其他排放标准车辆必须每周停驶一天。</span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\">　　</span><strong><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;font-size: 14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">加大补贴促进公众主动减排</span></span></strong></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　此番在给予车主更新淘汰</span>“国一”“国二”老旧车的补助政策的同时，政府引导银行推出购车优惠贷款产品。明年６月底前淘汰，比明年７月至１２月底淘汰，多得政府补助２０００元，例如“国二”排放标准小型客车可获得最高等级的１．２万元补助。车主可通过第三方交易平台“北京环境交易所”申请政府补助。</span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　方力指出，北京市机动车污染的集合，是５７０万辆机动车加上每天几万辆过境车辆共同导致，在保有量不断增加的前提下，减少污染排放，优化结构是关键。</span>“促进高污染排放的车辆所占比例尽量减少，实施限行政策，目的就是加快高污染排放车辆末位淘汰，优化排放结构。”</span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　生活类污染正在成为北京市最大的污染源，这是２０００多万人口的特大城市不容回避的矛盾。</span>“北京机动车中的代步工具约５００多万辆，是公众生活所需，其排污治理，需要全社会共同努力。”方力说。</span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\">&nbsp;</span></p><p><br/></p>','北京为何限行“国一、国二”轻型汽油车？','　　最新修订的《北京市空气重污染应急预案》自１２月１５日起施行，此后空气重污染橙色、红色预警时，国一、国二轻型汽油车全市禁行。','1','1','2017-03-12 20:18:00','','0','','','0','{\"thumb\":\"\"}','2','0','0','0','','');INSERT INTO ts_posts ( `id`, `post_author`, `post_keywords`, `post_source`, `post_date`, `post_content`, `post_title`, `post_excerpt`, `post_status`, `comment_status`, `post_modified`, `post_content_filtered`, `post_parent`, `post_type`, `post_mime_type`, `comment_count`, `smeta`, `post_hits`, `post_like`, `istop`, `recommended`, `page_tpl`, `page_tpls` ) VALUES  ('369','1','福州柴油批发价每吨涨300元','','2017-03-12 20:21:20','<p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\">&nbsp; &nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14px; line-height: 150%;\">　昨天记者采访获悉，近日福州柴油批发价连续上涨，两周时间每吨上涨了</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14px; line-height: 150%;\">5%</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14px; line-height: 150%;\">以上，超过了最高批发限价。据了解，按我国的成品油定价机制，由于近期国际原油期货价格上涨，本周我国成品油的零售限价或又将上调。</span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　近来福州柴油的批发价格逐渐上涨，到昨天为止，柴油批发价每吨</span>6100<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">元</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">~6150</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">元，与上周相比每吨上涨了</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">300</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">元左右，涨幅超过</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">5%</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">，已超过了我省柴油每吨</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">6090</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">元的最高批发限价。不过，福州汽油的批发价相对稳定，比如国五</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">92</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">号汽油的批发价在每吨</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">6000</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">元至</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">6050</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">元之间。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　福州柴油批发价上涨主要是由于近期国际原油期货价格总体走高。受</span>OPEC<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">联合限产的消息提振，</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">NYMEX</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">原油期货价格由原来的每桶</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">44</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">美元左右涨到</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">48</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">美元左右，布伦特原油期货价格从原来的每桶</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">45</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">美元左右涨到最高</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">49</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">美元左右。这也拉升了我国成品油价格变化率指数，根据相关机构的核算，到近日国内成品油价格变化率指数为</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">4.38%</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">，预测对应上调幅度</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">180</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">元</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">/</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">吨。本周三又到了我国成品油调价的时间窗口，如按目前的指数，成品油每升将上涨</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">0.1</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">元以上。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　目前福州国五</span>0<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">号柴油最高零售限价为</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">5.5</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">元</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">/</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">升，国五</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">92</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">号汽油为</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">5.9</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">元</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">/</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">升，国五</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">95</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">号汽油为</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">6.3</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">元</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">/</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">升。</span></span></p><p><br/></p>','福州柴油批发价每吨涨300元 本周或继续上调','   　昨天记者采访获悉，近日福州柴油批发价连续上涨，两周时间每吨上涨了5%以上，超过了最高批发限价。据了解，按我国的成品油定价机制，由于近期国际原油期货价格上涨，本周我国成品油的零售限价或又将上调。','1','1','2017-03-12 20:20:26','','0','','','0','{\"thumb\":\"\"}','2','0','0','0','','');INSERT INTO ts_posts ( `id`, `post_author`, `post_keywords`, `post_source`, `post_date`, `post_content`, `post_title`, `post_excerpt`, `post_status`, `comment_status`, `post_modified`, `post_content_filtered`, `post_parent`, `post_type`, `post_mime_type`, `comment_count`, `smeta`, `post_hits`, `post_like`, `istop`, `recommended`, `page_tpl`, `page_tpls` ) VALUES  ('370','1','油价30日或年内第八次上调 ','','2017-03-12 20:22:23','<p><span style=\"outline: none; border: 0px; padding: 0px; font-style: inherit; margin: 0px; font-family: inherit; font-size: medium; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\"></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\">&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14px; line-height: 150%;\">　今日</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14px; line-height: 150%;\">24</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14px; line-height: 150%;\">时，油价或迎来年内的第八次上调。记者昨日从业内获悉，新一轮成品油调价窗口将在今日</span><span style=\"font-size: 14px; line-height: 150%; font-family: Calibri;\">24</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14px; line-height: 150%;\">时打开，预计油价涨幅将超过</span><span style=\"font-size: 14px; line-height: 150%; font-family: Calibri;\">140</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14px; line-height: 150%;\">元</span><span style=\"font-size: 14px; line-height: 150%; font-family: Calibri;\">/</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14px; line-height: 150%;\">吨，折合每升汽油约涨</span><span style=\"font-size: 14px; line-height: 150%; font-family: Calibri;\">0.1</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14px; line-height: 150%;\">元。</span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　据了解，受欧佩克减产计划前景不明朗等因素影响，近期国际油价波动较大，整体呈现小幅上涨态势。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\">&nbsp;</span></p><p><span style=\"outline: none; border: 0px; padding: 0px; font-style: inherit; margin: 0px; font-family: inherit; font-size: medium; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\"></span><br/></p><p><span style=\"outline: none; border: 0px; padding: 0px; font-style: inherit; margin: 0px; font-family: inherit; font-size: medium; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\"><br/></span></p><p><br/></p>','油价30日或年内第八次上调 汽油约涨0.1元/升','  　今日24时，油价或迎来年内的第八次上调。','1','1','2017-03-12 20:21:34','','0','','','0','{\"thumb\":\"\"}','1','0','0','0','','');INSERT INTO ts_posts ( `id`, `post_author`, `post_keywords`, `post_source`, `post_date`, `post_content`, `post_title`, `post_excerpt`, `post_status`, `comment_status`, `post_modified`, `post_content_filtered`, `post_parent`, `post_type`, `post_mime_type`, `comment_count`, `smeta`, `post_hits`, `post_like`, `istop`, `recommended`, `page_tpl`, `page_tpls` ) VALUES  ('371','1','2016年10月成品油运行简况','','2017-03-12 20:44:30','<p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　据运行快报统计</span>(<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">下同</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">),10</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月份</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">,</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">原油产量</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">1593</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">万吨</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">,</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">同比下降</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">11.2%;</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">原油加工量</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">4497</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">万吨</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">,</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">增长</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">9.0%,</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">成品油产量</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">2746</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">万吨</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">,</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">增长</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">7.6%;</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">成品油消费量</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">2495</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">万吨</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">,</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">增长</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">1.0%,</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">其中汽油增长</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">8.1%,</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">柴油下降</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">5.6%</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">。月底成品油库存环比下降</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">29</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">万吨</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">,</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">较去年同期提高</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">33</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">万吨</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">,</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">仍保持较高水平。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\">　　1-10<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">,</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">原油产量</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">16533</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">万吨</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">,</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">同比下降</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">7.0%;</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">原油加工量</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">43159</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">万吨</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">,</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">增长</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">9.0%,</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">成品油产量</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">26680</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">万吨</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">,</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">增长</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">7.1%;</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">成品油消费量</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">24015</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">万吨</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">,</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">增长</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">3.8%,</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">其中汽油增长</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">10.9%,</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">柴油下降</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">2.3%</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">。</span></span></p><p><br/></p>','2016年10月成品油运行简况','　　据运行快报统计(下同),10月份,原油产量1593万吨,同比下降11.2%;原油加工量4497万吨,增长9.0%,成品油产量2746万吨,增长7.6%;成品油消费量2495万吨,增长1.0%,其中汽油增长8.1%,柴油下降5.6%。','1','1','2017-03-12 20:31:20','','0','','','0','{\"thumb\":\"\"}','1','0','0','0','','');INSERT INTO ts_posts ( `id`, `post_author`, `post_keywords`, `post_source`, `post_date`, `post_content`, `post_title`, `post_excerpt`, `post_status`, `comment_status`, `post_modified`, `post_content_filtered`, `post_parent`, `post_type`, `post_mime_type`, `comment_count`, `smeta`, `post_hits`, `post_like`, `istop`, `recommended`, `page_tpl`, `page_tpls` ) VALUES  ('372','1','中国原油首次大幅减产 ','','2017-03-12 20:55:22','<p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　国际原油价格维持低位运行，再加上国内油气消费增速放缓，引发连锁反应：</span>2016<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年，我国原油产量首次出现大幅度减产，三桶油在油气勘探开发上的投入也开始下降。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　这种趋势，引发业内专家的警戒。在昨天举行的《</span>2016<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">中国能源报告》发布会上，中国石油经济技术研究院研究员刘克雨说：“近几年，随着国际石油价格断崖式的暴跌，和中国经济增速的回落，中国油气消费增速明显放缓，消费结构发生了重大变化。</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">2016</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年，油气市场不仅延续了上述态势，供应侧也发生了重大的变化，原油首次出现大幅度减产，这在过去是不可想象的。这在我国石油工业发展史上是从来没有出现过的情况。受低油价影响，</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">2016</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年前三季度三大石油公司上游板块全面亏损。”</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\">　　</span><strong><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;font-size: 14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">上游勘探开发投入下降</span></span></strong></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　来自国家统计局的数据显示，</span>9<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月份单月，规模以上工业原油产量同比下降</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">9.8%</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">，而前三季度原油产量同比下降超过</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">6%</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　低油价引发的连锁反应，还包括</span>“三桶油”上游勘探开发投入下降。刘克雨说：“由于石油资源中，高丰度资源大部分已经动用了，新发现的大多是低丰度，以及非常规资源。在低油价条件下，真正能转化为可采储量，加以动用的比例更小。另外，受低油价影响，国内三大石油公司大幅收缩了石油勘探开发投入。<span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">2015</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年，已经从</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">2013</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年高峰时期的</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">4200</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">亿元，降到了</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">2800</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">亿元。</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">2016</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年，计划的</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">2500</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">亿元，但是计划完成情况，除了中海油以外，中石油和中石化</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">1</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">到</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">9</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月份完成了</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">30%</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">不到，长此以往，勘探开发投入减少，产量必然下降。”</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　国内原油减产的同时，伴随的是原油和成品油的</span>“大出大进”。数据显示，前<span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">10</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">个月，石油进口同比上涨</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">13.57%</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">；而成品油出口量同比暴涨</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">37.4%</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">，已经超过去年全年总量。刘克雨对此表示不无担忧：“原油进口量大幅增长，同时，生产出来的成品油在国内消费遇阻，又要大幅出口，这对我们国家来说，是不是合适？”</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\">　</span><strong><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;font-size: 14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　能源期货市场定价功能薄弱</span></span></strong></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　作为石油进口大国，我国石油行业一直努力增加石油的定价权和话语权，但《</span>2016<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">中国能源报告》针对国内石油期货市场的研究表明，我国能源期货市场定价功能仍然极为薄弱。报告作者、北京理工大学能源与环境政策研究中心副主任唐葆君说：“期货市场的定价功能极为薄弱，也难以为能源企业提供有效的风险规避手段。与此同时，中国的石油期货体系尚不健全，远不能满足市场主体的套期保值的需求。结算制度、准入制度、合约设计这些方面也不尽完善。导致交易的流动性非常低，市场参与度也很低。”</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　因此，《</span>2016<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">中国能源报告》建议健全能源期货市场的监管模式，降低准入门槛，鼓励符合条件的能源企业进入期货市场。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\">　</span><strong><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;font-size: 14px\">　10<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月末中国原油库存环比下降</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">1.89%</span></span></strong></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　石油价格系统</span>28<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">日发布的中国石油库存数据显示，</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">10</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月末中国原油库存</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">(</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">不含储备库存</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">)</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">环比下降</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">1.89%</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">，汽柴煤库存环比下降</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">1.88%</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">。其中，汽油库存环比微增，柴油、煤油库存环比均下降。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　原油方面，</span>10<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月份中国原油净进口量环比大幅下滑</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">12.66%</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">，而国内原油产量环比微增；消耗方面，原油加工量创纪录高位，环比增幅较大。综合来看，</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">10</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月监测范围内原油商业库存环比下降。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　汽柴煤方面，从供应情况来看，</span>10<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月汽柴煤产量环比增加；当月汽油净出口量环比略有增加，柴油净出口量环比有所下滑，但依然处于较高水平。从需求情况来看，国庆假日结束后，天气转凉，且居民出行减少，汽油终端需求有所回落。柴油方面，</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">10</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月，“秋收、秋耕、秋种”仍在持续，工矿、基建等整体开工率维持高位，柴油资源消耗速度较快；此外，因国五油品质量升级工作的进行，局部地区柴油资源偏紧，推动库存降低。综合来看，监测范围内汽油库存环比增加，柴油库存环比下降。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　中国石油库存数据是新华社石油价格系统自主研发的石油系列数据产品之一，是利用新华社遍布国内的信息采集网络进行采集，结合对相关专家的调查，综合考虑价格、季节、定价机制等因素后，由石油专家顾问团队评估的结果。中国石油库存数据每月中下旬通过新华社石油价格系统对外发布。</span></span></p><p><br/></p>','中国原油首次大幅减产 上游勘探开发投入下降','　　国际原油价格维持低位运行，再加上国内油气消费增速放缓，引发连锁反应：2016年，我国原油产量首次出现大幅度减产，三桶油在油气勘探开发上的投入也开始下降。','1','1','2017-03-12 20:54:10','','0','','','0','{\"thumb\":\"\"}','3','0','0','0','','');INSERT INTO ts_posts ( `id`, `post_author`, `post_keywords`, `post_source`, `post_date`, `post_content`, `post_title`, `post_excerpt`, `post_status`, `comment_status`, `post_modified`, `post_content_filtered`, `post_parent`, `post_type`, `post_mime_type`, `comment_count`, `smeta`, `post_hits`, `post_like`, `istop`, `recommended`, `page_tpl`, `page_tpls` ) VALUES  ('373','1','中国将进一步开放油气、铀勘探开发市场','','2017-03-12 20:56:22','<p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\">　　“十三五”期间，我国将稳步推进油气勘查开采体制改革，逐步放开上游勘探开发市场，同时加大铀矿勘查开发体制改革，有序放开铀矿勘查开发市场。</span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　国土资源部副部长赵龙</span>29<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">日在此间介绍《全国矿产资源规划</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">(2016-2020</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">)</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">》时说，为增强矿业发展活力，将开放油气、铀勘探开发市场。依据油气体制改革总体方案，将加快新疆改革试点经验总结推广，稳步推进油气勘查开采体制改革，逐步放开上游勘探开发市场，引入社会资本。按勘查社会化、矿业权市场化、投资多元化、开采专业化原则，加大铀矿勘查开发体制改革，有序放开铀矿勘查开发市场，积极引导社会资本进入铀矿勘查领域，加快铀矿勘查开发进程。与此同时，进一步推进探矿权采矿权实行招标拍卖挂牌方式出让，吸引社会资本和风险投资。调整下放矿业权审批权限，推进权力清单制度。推进矿产资源税费制度改革，实施矿产资源税从价计征。加强矿产资源税收优惠政策管理，提高资源综合利用效率。将资源所有者权益和生态环境损害等纳入自然资源及其产品开发利用成本。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　根据规划，到</span>2020<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年我国将基本建成统一开放、竞争有序、富有活力的现代矿业市场体系。国内资源保障基础进一步夯实，力争新发现</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">5-8</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">个亿吨级油田和</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">5-10</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">个千亿方级气田，新发现大中型矿产地</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">300-400</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">处。石油储采比保持在</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">12</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">以上，天然气储采比达到</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">30</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">。建设</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">103</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">个能源资源基地，划定</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">267</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">个国家规划矿区，铁、铜、铝土矿、钾盐等战略性矿产国内安全供应能力得到巩固。划定</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">28</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">个对国民经济具有重要价值的矿区，强化重要矿产保护与储备。</span></span></p><p><br/></p>','中国将进一步开放油气、铀勘探开发市场','　　“十三五”期间，我国将稳步推进油气勘查开采体制改革，逐步放开上游勘探开发市场，同时加大铀矿勘查开发体制改革，有序放开铀矿勘查开发市场。','1','1','2017-03-12 20:55:44','','0','','','0','{\"thumb\":\"\"}','2','0','0','0','','');INSERT INTO ts_posts ( `id`, `post_author`, `post_keywords`, `post_source`, `post_date`, `post_content`, `post_title`, `post_excerpt`, `post_status`, `comment_status`, `post_modified`, `post_content_filtered`, `post_parent`, `post_type`, `post_mime_type`, `comment_count`, `smeta`, `post_hits`, `post_like`, `istop`, `recommended`, `page_tpl`, `page_tpls` ) VALUES  ('374','1','国家级油气交易平台运行','','2017-03-12 20:58:28','<p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　国家级油气现货交易平台</span>——上海石油天然气交易中心<span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">26</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">日正式投入运行，能源市场化改革再进一步。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\">　　“能源市场化改革，从根本上是要解决产业放开和市场开放的问题。”中国国际经济交流中心副研究员景春梅说，过去我国油气产业集中度较高，价格主要以政府指导价为主，没有形成市场决定价格的机制。交易中心的建立，将为油气供需双方搭建交易平台，目标是构建起油气现货交易市场，让市场决定价格，这正是能源市场化改革的一部分。</span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　交易中心自</span>2015<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">7</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月投入试运行以来，在推进油气市场化交易方面已逐渐发挥作用。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　数据显示，交易中心的市场交易规模正在逐步扩大，预计今年天然气单边交易量将突破</span>150<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">亿立方米，占全国天然气消费总量的比重达到</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">8%</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">左右。截至</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">2016</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">10</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月底，交易中心已累计吸纳会员</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">269</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">家，其中，交易类会员</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">260</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">家，除中石油、中石化、中海油外，许多民营油气企业、城市燃气企业、管网公司也积极参与交易。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　交易中心还发布了中国</span>LNG(<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">液化天然气</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">)</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">出厂价格指数、中国华南</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">LNG</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">交易价格指数和中国汽、柴油批发价格指数等多项反映中国油气市场运行情况的指数，为行业提供价格参考。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\">　　“作为民营液化天然气生产商，我们希望中国能有一个权威的石油天然气交易中心。”</span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　哈纳斯集团</span>LNG<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">事业部首席执行官米歇尔·马克说，“交易中心为大宗天然气、</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">LNG</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">交易创造了条件，为市场提供需要的流动性，允许市场参与者对冲风险，有助于我们及时补充资源，在客户需要时向他们供应产品。”</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\">　　“交易中心将传统能源与互联网有机结合，有效提高了能源产业链运行效率，助力国内上游油气资源有效开发，以及包括煤层气在内的非常规能源的合理高效利用。”亚美能源控股有限公司总裁李京表示。</span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　专家认为，未来交易中心发挥的作用会越来越大，将进一步助推国家能源市场化改革步伐。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\">　　“从国际经验看，交易中心要发挥功能需要三个前提条件：交易主体多元、管道公平开放、价格放开。近两年国家能源价格改革政策积极有为，体制改革正在推进，未来这三个条件将逐渐具备，交易中心也将发挥越来越重要的作用。”景春梅说。</span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\">　　2015<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年以来，我国已出台多个油气改革政策，从加强天然气输配价格监管、油气管网设施信息公开、放开储气设施和化肥用气价格，到推进天然气门站市场化价格改革等，都在为理顺油气产业链价格传导机制、促进交易主体多元化扫清障碍。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　交易中心负责人表示，按照规划，交易中心将先气后油，先现货后中远期，先国内后国际，打造具有国际影响力的石油天然气交易平台。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　三大石油公司负责人积极评价上海石油天然气交易中心在推动油气市场化改革和提升国际能源影响力上发挥的重要作用。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\">　　“交易中心正式运行，将成为我国石油天然气市场化改革政策落地的有力抓手。”中国石油天然气集团公司董事长王宜林说，交易中心作为一个公平、公正、公开的交易平台，不仅能真实反映我国天然气消费的季节性区域性特点，发现天然气真实市场价值，通过市场化手段解决供需矛盾、稳定市场供应，同时有利于积极应对我国天然气对外依存度不断攀升的实际，有效发挥天然气消费大国的买方优势。</span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　王宜林表示，未来中国石油将逐步扩大上线交易气量，全力支持交易中心尽快开展天然气期货业务。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\">　　“在我国建设一个公平、公正、公开、规范的油气交易中心，是加强国际能源合作的需要，这对于保障国家能源安全、促进经济社会发展具有重要的意义。”中国石油化工集团公司董事长王玉普认为。</span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\">　　“交易中心试运行一年多来，行业影响力初步显现。”中国海洋石油总公司董事长杨华说，交易中心正式投入运行，标志着我国建立国家级天然气交易市场获得重大突破。</span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　国家发展和改革委员会主任徐绍史说，随着我国能源领域油气价格改革取得重大进展，市场决定价格作用明显增强，</span>80%<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">的气源价格已经由市场主导形成。交易中心的建设，既是油气价格市场化改革的重要成果，又是深化改革的重要支撑。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　交易中心落户上海，将使上海的要素市场进一步集聚。上海市市长杨雄表示，交易中心正式运行，有助于增强上海能源要素市场的国际影响力，对加快上海</span>“四个中心”和自贸试验区建设，都具有非常重要的意义。</span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\">　　“交易中心的建设是配合和服务国家能源价格改革的重要举措。”新华社社长蔡名照说，“新华社积极参与到交易中心的建设中来，是为了获取及时、权威、全面的石油天然气交易信息，提供专业化的能源信息服务产品，以更好地促进我国能源市场的健康有序发展。”</span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\">　　“国家发改委将继续支持交易中心发展，希望三大石油公司和下游用户积极进场交易，尽快推动形成更具代表性、更具影响力的交易价格，促进交易中心发挥更大作用。”徐绍史说。</span></p><p><br/></p>','国家级油气交易平台运行','　　国家级油气现货交易平台——上海石油天然气交易中心26日正式投入运行，能源市场化改革再进一步。','1','1','2017-03-12 20:57:13','','0','','','0','{\"thumb\":\"\"}','1','0','0','0','','');INSERT INTO ts_posts ( `id`, `post_author`, `post_keywords`, `post_source`, `post_date`, `post_content`, `post_title`, `post_excerpt`, `post_status`, `comment_status`, `post_modified`, `post_content_filtered`, `post_parent`, `post_type`, `post_mime_type`, `comment_count`, `smeta`, `post_hits`, `post_like`, `istop`, `recommended`, `page_tpl`, `page_tpls` ) VALUES  ('375','1','中国再生资源行业持续低迷','','2017-03-12 21:00:28','<p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　受国内外经济形势影响，再加上行业没有准入门槛，行业发展先天不足，我国再生资源行业正经历着市场寒冬。记者从近日举行的第二届中国再生资源企业领袖峰会上了解到，许多再生资源企业效益低迷，不少中小企业处于停产或半停产状态，再生资源行业面临着严峻的挑战及发展环境。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\">　　</span><strong><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;font-size: 14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">再生资源回收总量与产值</span>“背道而驰”</span></strong></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　记者从峰会上了解到，由于主要品种再生资源价格持续下跌，再生资源回收利用企业产值和利润持续走低，整个行业呈疲软状态。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　据了解，截至</span>2015<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年底，我国废钢铁、废有色金属、废塑料、废轮胎、废纸、废弃电器电子产品、报废汽车、报废船舶、废玻璃、废电池十大类别的再生资源回收总量约为</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">2.46</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">亿吨，同比增长</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">0.3</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">％。其中，增幅最大的是报废汽车；降幅最大的是报废船舶。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　虽然回收总量有所增加，但是回收总值却大幅下降。商务部的数据显示，</span>2015<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年，我国十大品种再生资源回收总值为</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">5149.4</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">亿元，受主要品种价格持续走低影响，同比下降</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">20.1</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">％。其中报废船舶降幅最大，同比下降</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">47.2</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">％。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　梳理峰会传出的信息可以看出，我国再生资源主要品种回收量继续下降。分品种看，由于铁矿石价格的大幅下滑，钢铁企业在困境中大部分用铁矿石，减少废钢铁比例，致使废钢铁消耗量出现负增长，导致废钢铁回收大幅下降。</span>2015<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年，我国回收废钢铁为</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">14380</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">万吨，同比下降</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">5.6</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">％，价格也大幅下降，平均降幅为</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">30</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">％左右，下滑幅度之大是历史罕见的。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　中国再生资源回收利用协会会长蒋省三说，受国内经济下行和国际石油价格大幅下降的影响，我国塑料加工工业表现不佳。记者了解到，去年国内废塑料回收量约为</span>1800<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">万吨，同比下降</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">10</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">％。目前，废塑料回收利用行业规模较大，但整体质量水平较低，加上废塑料价格普遍下跌，行业利润呈下滑趋势，去年我国废塑料回收利用企业的开工率在</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">50</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">％左右。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><strong><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;font-size: 14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　无准入门槛</span></span></strong></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><strong><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;font-size: 14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　导致行业先天不足</span></span></strong></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　商务部的数据显示，</span>2015<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年，全国回收企业有</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">13</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">万家，比前年减少</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">7000</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">家；各类回收站（点）</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">30</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">万个，比前年减少</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">5</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">万个；回收行业从业人员</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">1500</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">多万人，比前年减少</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">300</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">多万人。一方面，企业数量和从业人员不断减少，另一方面，由于再生资源回收行业没有市场准入门槛，导致行业先天不足。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　首先是行业竞争力不强。由于再生资源回收行业没有市场准入门槛，从业人员以</span>“<span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">40</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">、</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">50</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">”人员、残疾人、农民工为主，人员素质普遍较低。中国社科院循环经济重点研究室副主任彭绪庶说，我国大部分再生资源回收企业多采取粗放式经营和管理方式、产业链条短、产品单一、生产工艺门槛低、增值水平低、同质化现象明显，具有一定规模的企业回收量仅占回收总量的</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">10%</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">至</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">20</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">％，行业小、散、差的特点明显，组织化程度低，市场竞争力较差。此外，再生资源回收企业政策依赖度高、抗风险能力差，有政策支持的领域如废弃电器电子回收拆解企业发展较好，其他缺乏政策支持的品种，一旦政策、市场或价格发生变化，企业就面临倒闭风险，不能适应市场快速发展的要求。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　其次是行业发展不平衡。我国有各类回收站（点）</span>30<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">多万个，从回收网点的建设看，大部分回收站点集中在中心城区，非中心城区和乡镇农村等地站点数量很少，回收站点的覆盖率有待提高。从回收品种看，普遍存在“利大抢收，利小少收，无利不收”的现象，传统的产业废弃物，如废钢铁、废有色金属等品种回收水平较高，基本形成了较完整的回收利用产业链条，生活废弃物中废纸、废塑料等品种回收率较高，但废玻璃、废电池、废节能灯、废纺织品等品种，由于回收成本高、利用价值较低和利用水平有限等多种因素，回收率较低。从企业结构看，个体经营户是主体，且以手工作业为主，组织化程度较低。具有科技研发能力，采用现代化技术和设备，开展网上交易、精细拆解等现代业态的企业较少。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　再次是行业创新能力不足。目前，我国再生资源回收企业自设或建立长期稳定合作关系的研发机构数量很少，研发能力不足，普遍重生产轻研究开发，重引进轻消化吸收，重模仿轻创新，创新层次低，很多企业处在有</span>“制造”无“创造”的状态。在“产学研”结合中，企业基本处于从属地位。</span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　另外，政策支撑不配套。业内反映，由于再生资源回收的专门性法规仅有《再生资源回收管理办法》，法律效力较低，执行难度较大，行业统计、标准工作相对滞后，再加上相关管理部门没有形成长效联动机制和有效监管，再生资源回收行业无序竞争和不正当竞争等不良现象依然存在。部分重点品种缺乏相关立法，废玻璃、废节能灯等低值品种，回收成本高、利润薄，靠市场机制难以调动企业积极性，需要政策给予支撑。此外，行业管理职权分散、缺乏合力，扶持政策和工作措施缺乏配套性。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\">　　</span><strong><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;font-size: 14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">行业发展</span></span></strong></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><strong><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;font-size: 14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　有望迎来新生</span></span></strong></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　总体来看，再生资源行业发展形势依然严峻。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　蒋省三认为，从国内经济环境看，</span>2016<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年中国经济形势依然比较严峻，由于原有支撑再生资源回收行业发展的因素削弱或消失，新的支撑因素尚在形成之中，所以再生资源回收行业的调整还将持续一段时间，这将对再生资源价格及回收企业经济效益的回升构成沉重压力。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　利好消息是，宏观调控正为再生资源行业发展创造良好环境。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\">　　2016<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年，我国经济进入了深层次的创新改革发展新阶段，国家将以大数据战略为发展主线，加快信息技术和大数据在再生资源回收领域的渗透与应用，推进信息化与工业化深度融合，在政府调控和市场调节的双向作用下，再生资源回收行业将迎来良好的发展环境。随着粗放式发展主基调退出历史舞台，环保与节能减排的政策压力与日俱增，企业革新理念、优化成本，通过淘汰落后产能和更换老旧设备，达到转型升级、节能减排的目的。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　另外，政策法规也将带动行业转型升级。去年，国家出台了一系列方针政策，大力推进绿色发展、循环发展、低碳发展成为我国经济发展的主旋律，同时对符合行业规范条件的再生资源加工企业给予即征即退</span>30<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">％－</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">70</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">％增征税优惠政策。随着新环保法和污染物排放标准的正式施行，再生资源回收利用企业面临的环保要求将进一步提高，更严格的环保标准和监管措施有利于鼓励企业在环保装备和管理方面加大投入，有利于创造更加公平合理的市场竞争环境，有利于淘汰落后产能，更好地规范行业发展。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　去年国家还出台了《再生资源回收体系建设中长期规划（</span>2015<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">－</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">2020</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年）》，针对我国再生资源行业发展现状、问题及特点，明确了再生资源回收体系建设的中长期目标，部署了分类建立回收体系、完善回收节点功能、培育龙头回收企业、健全回收管理制度等工作任务。今年</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">6</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">部委又印发了《关于推进再生资源回收行业转型升级的意见》，提出推广“互联网＋回收”的新模式、探索两网协同发展的新机制、提高组织化的新途径、探索逆向物流的新方式、鼓励应用分拣加工新技术等推进再生资源回收行业转型升级的意见。在未来几年内，在一系列利好政策推动和市场引导下，我国再生资源回收行业将向现代化、集约化、科学化方向发展。</span></span></p><p><br/></p>','中国再生资源行业持续低迷','　　受国内外经济形势影响，再加上行业没有准入门槛，行业发展先天不足，我国再生资源行业正经历着市场寒冬。','1','1','2017-03-12 20:58:41','','0','','','0','{\"thumb\":\"\"}','2','0','0','0','','');INSERT INTO ts_posts ( `id`, `post_author`, `post_keywords`, `post_source`, `post_date`, `post_content`, `post_title`, `post_excerpt`, `post_status`, `comment_status`, `post_modified`, `post_content_filtered`, `post_parent`, `post_type`, `post_mime_type`, `comment_count`, `smeta`, `post_hits`, `post_like`, `istop`, `recommended`, `page_tpl`, `page_tpls` ) VALUES  ('376','1','国内汽柴油迎年内第八涨 ','','2017-03-12 21:01:47','<p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\">&nbsp;<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　国家发改委今日下午宣布</span>30<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">日</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">24</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">时起国内汽柴油价格每吨分别上调</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">175</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">元和</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">170</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">元。福建成品油价格同步调整。明日零时起，福建</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">92</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">号汽油每升上调</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">0.14</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">元，最高零售价每升</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">6.04</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">元。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　根据福建省物价局的通知，明日零时起，福建省</span>92<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">号汽油最高零售价从</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">7855</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">元</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">/</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">吨调整为</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">8040</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">元</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">/</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">吨；</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">95</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">号汽油最高零售价从</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">8299</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">元</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">/</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">吨调整为</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">8495</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">元</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">/</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">吨；车用</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">0</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">号柴油最高零售价从</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">6425</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">元</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">/</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">吨调整为</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">6595</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">元</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">/</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">吨。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　调整后，</span>92<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">号汽油、</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">95</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">号汽油、车用</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">0</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">号柴油最高零售价依次为</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">6.04</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">元</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">/</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">升、</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">6.45</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">元</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">/</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">升、</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">5.65</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">元</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">/</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">升，分别较此前上调</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">0.14</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">元</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">/</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">升、</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">0.15</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">元</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">/</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">升、</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">0.15</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">元</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">/</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">升。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　这是国内汽柴油价格年内第</span>8<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">次上调，一辆油箱为</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">50</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">升的普通家用车加满</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">92</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">号汽油，将多花</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">7</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">元。截至目前，今年来我国汽、柴油价格已经历了五次下调、七次上调、四次搁浅、六次因国际油价低于每桶</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">40</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">美元的“地板价”而不调整。</span></span></p><p><br/></p>','国内汽柴油迎年内第八涨 福建92号汽油涨至6.04元/升',' 　国家发改委今日下午宣布30日24时起国内汽柴油价格每吨分别上调175元和170元。福建成品油价格同步调整。明日零时起，福建92号汽油每升上调0.14元，最高零售价每升6.04元。','1','1','2017-03-12 21:00:49','','0','','','0','{\"thumb\":\"\"}','2','0','0','0','','');INSERT INTO ts_posts ( `id`, `post_author`, `post_keywords`, `post_source`, `post_date`, `post_content`, `post_title`, `post_excerpt`, `post_status`, `comment_status`, `post_modified`, `post_content_filtered`, `post_parent`, `post_type`, `post_mime_type`, `comment_count`, `smeta`, `post_hits`, `post_like`, `istop`, `recommended`, `page_tpl`, `page_tpls` ) VALUES  ('377','1','产油国“抱团”','','2017-03-13 08:53:53','<p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　当地时间</span>11<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">30</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">日，石油输出国组织</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">(</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">欧佩克</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">)</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">第</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">171</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">届部长会议在维也纳举行。会议决定将原油日产量减少</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">120</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">万桶，并将原油日产量限额定为</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">3250</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">万桶。这是该组织</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">2008</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年以来首次决定减产。作为欧佩克中产量最多的成员，沙特带头减产</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">48.6</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">万桶</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">/</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">天。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　受欧佩克减产协议提振，国际原油市场出现了强劲反弹。截至当天收盘，纽约商品交易所</span>2017<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">1</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月交货的轻质原油期货价格上涨</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">4.21</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">美元，收于每桶</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">49.44</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">美元，涨幅为</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">9.31%</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">。</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">2017</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">1</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月交货的伦敦布伦特原油期货价格上涨</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">4.09</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">美元，收于每桶</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">50.47</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">美元，涨幅为</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">8.82%</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">。分析人士认为，欧佩克减产的重要意义，除了实际减少产量之外，更重要的是欧佩克为国际原油市场明确了未来一段时间的走势。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　专家认为，对国际原油市场造成最大冲击的因素并不是利好或利空，而是市场上的不确定性。自</span>9<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月份欧佩克成员在阿尔及利亚就减产问题达成初步协议以来，国际原油市场就显示出较为乐观的情绪，国际油价一度突破</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">50</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">美元</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">/</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">桶的关口。此次欧佩克的减产决定，向国际原油市场释放了一个明确的信号，即欧佩克希望国际油价回到上升通道，将油价提高至一个相对合理的水平。同时，欧佩克仍然会通过调节产量积极参与国际原油市场博弈。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　不过，随着油价上涨，美国页岩油产能将开始大规模回归市场，重新对油价回升形成阻力，并开始挤占欧佩克市场份额。此前国际能源署已经作出预测，一旦国际油价企稳于</span>50<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">美元</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">/</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">桶以上，美国页岩油产能将很快重回市场，这对欧佩克减产协议和国际油价的稳定将再次形成挑战。欧佩克将如何应对这一局面，还有待观察。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　专家认为，若要从根本上改善国际原油市场供求关系，推动国际油价稳步回升，还取决于全球原油需求回暖。市场分析认为，随着明年全球经济，特别是新兴市场好转，全球原油需求增长有可能出现较为乐观的形势，届时配合欧佩克的减产行动，国际油价有望维持在欧佩克所期望的价格区间。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　值得注意的是，欧佩克已经开始加强与非欧佩克产油国的协调。此次欧佩克作出减产决定，也得到了俄罗斯等非欧佩克产油国的支持，部分非欧佩克产油国也加入了减产行动。据悉，俄罗斯已经同意将产量缩减</span>30<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">万桶</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">/</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">天，非欧佩克成员国削减产能总量将达到</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">60</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">万桶</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">/</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">天。俄罗斯的这一举动显示出其对通过减产稳定油价的极大诚意。欧佩克将于</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">12</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">9</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">日与非欧佩克产油国举行会谈，共同协调减产政策。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　专家认为，今后国际原油市场中的供给方将不断加强政策协调，从而确保国际油价的合理稳定。虽然欧佩克与非欧佩克产油国，甚至欧佩克内部都存在各种各样的分歧，但此次减产协议可以说是近年来产油国协调产能政策较为成功的一次，为这些国家之间今后进一步强化产能协调奠定了基础。这表明，欧佩克正在以新方式重新获取国际原油市场的主导权。与以往不同，欧佩克不再将其他产油国视为对立面，而是与这些国家开展对话与合作，寻求利益共同点，这样的策略将使欧佩克和非欧佩克产油国同时受益。</span></span></p><p><br/></p>','产油国“抱团”显现市场新动向','　　当地时间11月30日，石油输出国组织(欧佩克)第171届部长会议在维也纳举行。会议决定将原油日产量减少120万桶，并将原油日产量限额定为3250万桶。这是该组织2008年以来首次决定减产。作为欧佩克中产量最多的成员，沙特带头减产48.6万桶/天。','1','1','2017-03-13 08:52:42','','0','','','0','{\"thumb\":\"\"}','1','0','0','0','','');INSERT INTO ts_posts ( `id`, `post_author`, `post_keywords`, `post_source`, `post_date`, `post_content`, `post_title`, `post_excerpt`, `post_status`, `comment_status`, `post_modified`, `post_content_filtered`, `post_parent`, `post_type`, `post_mime_type`, `comment_count`, `smeta`, `post_hits`, `post_like`, `istop`, `recommended`, `page_tpl`, `page_tpls` ) VALUES  ('378','1','石油和化工行业主营收入两年来首现正增长','','2017-03-13 08:55:33','<p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　中国石油和化学工业联合会日前公布</span>10<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月份全行业经济运行报告。报告显示</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">,10</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月份全行业经济运行总体保持平稳向好态势</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">,</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">主营收入两年来首次实现增长。但行业经济效益分化继续加剧</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">,</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">固定资产投资降幅扩大</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">,</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">化工市场进出口压力依然不减</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">,</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">行业经济运行中的下行压力仍不容忽视。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　今年</span>1~10<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">,</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">石油和化工行业累计增加值增长</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">7.8%,</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">比</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">1</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">～</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">9</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月回落</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">0.2</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">个百分点。其中</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">,</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">化学工业增加值增长</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">8.8%,</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">比</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">1</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">～</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">9</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月减缓</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">0.2</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">个百分点</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">;</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">石油天然气开采业下降</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">3.5%,</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">降幅扩大</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">0.2</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">个百分点</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">;</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">炼油业增幅</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">8%,</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">减缓</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">0.1</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">个百分点。同期</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">,</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">全行业主营业务收入</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">10.71</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">万亿元</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">,</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">同比增长</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">0.2%,</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">两年来首次实现增长。其中</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">,</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">专用化学品、农药和合成材料制造业等主营收入增速领先</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">,</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">分别为</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">7.1%</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">、</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">6.3%</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">和</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">5.7%</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　主要化学品生产企稳</span>,<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">油气产量则继续下滑。前</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">10</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">,</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">全国油气总产量</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">2.74</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">亿吨</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">(</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">油当量</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">),</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">同比下降</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">3%,</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">降幅比</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">1</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">～</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">9</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月扩大</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">0.5</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">个百分点</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">;</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">主要化学品总量增长约</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">2%,</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">增速与前</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">9</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月持平。其中</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">,</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">甲醇、涂料、烧碱、电石、合成树脂、合成纤维单体、轮胎外胎等产量增速较快。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\">　　10<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月份</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">,</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">石化行业固定资产投资继续下降。</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">1~10</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">,</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">油气开采业实际投资</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">1671</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">亿元</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">,</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">同比下降</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">34.7%,</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">降幅比前</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">9</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月扩大</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">2.7</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">个百分点</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">;</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">化学原料和化学品制造业投资</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">1.21</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">万亿元</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">,</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">降幅</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">3.3%,</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">收窄</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">0.9</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">个百分点。行业投资依然疲软。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　前</span>10<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">,</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">全行业效益整体上企稳向好</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">,</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">但效益分化继续加剧。全行业共实现利润总额</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">5050.4</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">亿元</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">,</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">同比持平</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">,</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">二季度以来首现止降回升。报告预测</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">,</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">四季度中后期石化行业经济运行将延续“总体平稳</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">,</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">稳中向好”的态势</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">,</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">走势继续分化。</span></span></p><p><br/></p>','石油和化工行业主营收入两年来首现正增长','　　中国石油和化学工业联合会日前公布10月份全行业经济运行报告。报告显示,10月份全行业经济运行总体保持平稳向好态势,主营收入两年来首次实现增长。但行业经济效益分化继续加剧,固定资产投资降幅扩大,化工市场进出口压力依然不减,行业经济运行中的下行压力仍不容忽视。','1','1','2017-03-13 08:54:57','','0','','','0','{\"thumb\":\"\"}','2','0','0','0','','');INSERT INTO ts_posts ( `id`, `post_author`, `post_keywords`, `post_source`, `post_date`, `post_content`, `post_title`, `post_excerpt`, `post_status`, `comment_status`, `post_modified`, `post_content_filtered`, `post_parent`, `post_type`, `post_mime_type`, `comment_count`, `smeta`, `post_hits`, `post_like`, `istop`, `recommended`, `page_tpl`, `page_tpls` ) VALUES  ('379','1','下周成品油零售限价有望上调350元 将创年内新高','','2017-03-13 08:56:18','<p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　本轮第</span>5<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">个工作日，中宇资讯测算原油变化率为</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">11.55%</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">，原油估价</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">51.692</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">美元</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">/</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">桶，基准价涨</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">5.354</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">美元</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">/</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">桶，暂预计</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">12</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">15</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">日零时成品油零售限价上调</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">350</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">元</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">/</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">吨，上调幅度有望创年内新高。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　中宇资讯成品油分析师胡雪在接受《证券日报》记者采访时表示，国内成品油经历过前期的疯狂后，主营单位报价稳中有涨，涨势较昨日有所放缓，地炼柴油曾出现小幅回落现象。</span>OPEC<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">目前产量与减产目标</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">3250</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">万桶</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">/</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">日之间的差值较</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">120</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">万桶</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">/</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">日减产总数尚存</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">50</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">万</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">/</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">桶的空缺，再加冻结成员国身份的印尼，以及拿至豁免的伊朗、利比亚、尼日利亚，对减产的质疑已经令国际油价在</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">7</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">日亚洲时段下跌近</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">1%</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　本轮调价伊始，自</span>11<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">30</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">日</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">OPEC</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">与俄罗斯宣布明年联合减产以提振油市之后油价大涨</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">19%</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">。但因</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">OPEC</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">和俄罗斯双双公布创纪录的产量，外界就对计划中的减产规模是否足以结束油市供应过剩产生了质疑。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\">　　“<span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">12</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">10</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">日</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">OPEC</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">邀请</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">14</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">国在维也纳召开会议，意在扩大减产范围，本次达成合作的可能较大。所以除非协议完全瓦解，油价不太可能跌回上周减产协议之前的水准。再加上本轮成品油零限价上调幅度可创年内新高，主营单位年前大单多不出库，在销售压力较小情况下降价意愿较低。考虑柴油靠近零售限价，涨价空间有限，高位窄幅整理可能较大，汽油仍以稳中上扬为主。”胡雪表示。</span></span></p><p><br/></p>','下周成品油零售限价有望上调350元 将创年内新高','　　本轮第5个工作日，中宇资讯测算原油变化率为11.55%，原油估价51.692美元/桶，基准价涨5.354美元/桶，暂预计12月15日零时成品油零售限价上调350元/吨，上调幅度有望创年内新高。','1','1','2017-03-13 08:55:48','','0','','','0','{\"thumb\":\"\"}','2','0','0','0','','');INSERT INTO ts_posts ( `id`, `post_author`, `post_keywords`, `post_source`, `post_date`, `post_content`, `post_title`, `post_excerpt`, `post_status`, `comment_status`, `post_modified`, `post_content_filtered`, `post_parent`, `post_type`, `post_mime_type`, `comment_count`, `smeta`, `post_hits`, `post_like`, `istop`, `recommended`, `page_tpl`, `page_tpls` ) VALUES  ('380','1','发改委部署2017年天然气价格改革监管重点工作','','2017-03-13 08:57:02','<p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\">　　12<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">4-6</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">日，价格司在北京召开会议，就《天然气管道运输价格管理办法</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">(</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">试行</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">)</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">》和《天然气管道运输定价成本监审办法</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">(</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">试行</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">)</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">》</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">(</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">以下简称两个《办法》</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">)</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">开展培训。</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">30</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">个通气省份价格主管部门、</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">12</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">家具有独立法人资格的跨省长途管道运输企业以及上海石油天然气交易中心等单位共计</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">160</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">多人参加了培训。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　培训会上，价格司司长施子海同志通报了</span>2016<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年资源性产品价格改革取得的成果，部署</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">2017</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年天然气价格改革监管重点工作，并要求大家认真学习，开动脑筋，深入研讨，踊跃建言，集思广益，确保培训取得实效。业内专家和价格司相关处室同志介绍了全球天然气市场基本情况、部分国家天然气价格管理的演变历程以及管道运输定价的一般原理，逐条解读了两个《办法》的内容，组织进行了现场交流和答疑。会议讨论热烈，发言踊跃，参会代表普遍认为培训十分及时、高效，学有所获，对准确理解掌握相关规则和操作办法，做好下一步天然气管道运输价格管理工作帮助很大。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　培训期间，价格司还召开专题会议，通报今冬明春天然气保供严峻形势，要求各地高度重视保供期间天然气价格工作，坚决贯彻好、落实好、完善好相关价格政策措施，充分利用价格杠杆保障冬季供应。</span></span></p><p><br/></p>','发改委部署2017年天然气价格改革监管重点工作','　　12月4-6日，价格司在北京召开会议，就《天然气管道运输价格管理办法(试行)》和《天然气管道运输定价成本监审办法(试行)》(以下简称两个《办法》)开展培训。30个通气省份价格主管部门、12家具有独立法人资格的跨省长途管道运输企业以及上海石油天然气交易中心等单位共计160多人参加了培训。','1','1','2017-03-13 08:56:30','','0','','','0','{\"thumb\":\"\"}','0','0','0','0','','');INSERT INTO ts_posts ( `id`, `post_author`, `post_keywords`, `post_source`, `post_date`, `post_content`, `post_title`, `post_excerpt`, `post_status`, `comment_status`, `post_modified`, `post_content_filtered`, `post_parent`, `post_type`, `post_mime_type`, `comment_count`, `smeta`, `post_hits`, `post_like`, `istop`, `recommended`, `page_tpl`, `page_tpls` ) VALUES  ('381','1','国际油价8日上涨 ','','2017-03-13 08:57:43','<p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　国际油价</span>8<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">日上涨。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　市场对原油产量供大于求的担忧有所缓解，支撑当天油价上涨。石油输出国组织</span>(<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">欧佩克</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">)</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">与非欧佩克产油国将于</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">10</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">日召开会议讨论非欧佩克产油国日均减产</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">60</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">万桶的协议细则。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　截至当天收盘，纽约商品交易所</span>2017<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">1</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月交货的轻质原油期货价格上涨</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">1.07</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">美元，收于每桶</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">50.84</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">美元，涨幅为</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">2.15%</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">。</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">2017</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">2</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月交货的伦敦布伦特原油期货价格上涨</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">0.89</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">美元，收于每桶</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">53.89</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">美元，涨幅为</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">1.68%</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">。</span></span></p><p><br/></p>','国际油价8日上涨 收于每桶50.84美元','　　国际油价8日上涨。','1','1','2017-03-13 08:57:13','','0','','','0','{\"thumb\":\"\"}','2','0','0','0','','');INSERT INTO ts_posts ( `id`, `post_author`, `post_keywords`, `post_source`, `post_date`, `post_content`, `post_title`, `post_excerpt`, `post_status`, `comment_status`, `post_modified`, `post_content_filtered`, `post_parent`, `post_type`, `post_mime_type`, `comment_count`, `smeta`, `post_hits`, `post_like`, `istop`, `recommended`, `page_tpl`, `page_tpls` ) VALUES  ('382','1','全国成品油价格指数平稳运行','','2017-03-13 08:58:33','<p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　依据新华</span>(<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">大庆</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">)</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">国际石油资讯中心发布的报告，截至</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">12</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">9</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">日，全国成品油价格指数为</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">693.99</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">，涨幅</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">0.14%</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">，全国成品油价格指数平稳运行。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　全国成品油价格指数运行结果表明，上周</span>93<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">＃汽油平均价格报收于</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">6104</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">元／吨，较前一报告周期上涨</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">10</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">元／吨</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">(</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">与前一报告期基本持平</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">)</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">；</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">0</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">＃柴油平均价格报收于</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">6251</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">元／吨，较前一报告周期上涨</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">8</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">元／吨</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">(</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">与前一报告期基本持平</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">)</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">。综合来看，全国汽柴油平均价格起伏不大，带动全国成品油价格指数平稳运行。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　新华</span>(<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">大庆</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">)</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">国际石油资讯中心分析师李振国认为，近期市场对非欧佩克产油国减产的乐观情绪升温，国际原油期货价格震荡上行。国内市场成品油需求依旧疲弱，市场交投无明显改善。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　李振国分析认为，本周国内市场因限产协议达成，原油价格持续上涨，受此利好消息提振，国内汽柴油价格涨至高位，但国内成品油的需求依旧延续疲软状态，市场交投无明显改善。北方地区因基建、工程等建设项目停工，柴油用量较少，价格走势平稳，南方部分地区柴油资源紧张价格上扬，整体油品市场保持稳定。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　国际市场方面，美国能源信息署</span>(EIA)<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">近日公布的数据显示，截至</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">12</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">2</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">日当周，美国原油库存减少</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">238.9</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">万桶至</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">4.858</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">亿桶，降幅高于预期并连续三周下降，该消息利好国际油价。观望后市，美国原油库存继续下降但成品油库存升高加之美联储加息预期打压油价，预计短期内国际油价将维持震荡格局。</span></span></p><p><br/></p>','全国成品油价格指数平稳运行','　　依据新华(大庆)国际石油资讯中心发布的报告，截至12月9日，全国成品油价格指数为693.99，涨幅0.14%，全国成品油价格指数平稳运行。','1','1','2017-03-13 08:58:00','','0','','','0','{\"thumb\":\"\"}','2','0','0','0','','');INSERT INTO ts_posts ( `id`, `post_author`, `post_keywords`, `post_source`, `post_date`, `post_content`, `post_title`, `post_excerpt`, `post_status`, `comment_status`, `post_modified`, `post_content_filtered`, `post_parent`, `post_type`, `post_mime_type`, `comment_count`, `smeta`, `post_hits`, `post_like`, `istop`, `recommended`, `page_tpl`, `page_tpls` ) VALUES  ('383','1','国际油价12日上涨 收于每桶52.83美元','','2017-03-13 08:59:49','<p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\">　</span><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\">&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">国际油价</span>12<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">日上涨。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\">　　11<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">个非欧佩克产油国</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">10</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">日在维也纳达成减产协议，决定从明年</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">1</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月起将其原油日产量减少</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">55.8</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">万桶。协议有效期为</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">6</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">个月，是否续期将视市场行情而定。此前，欧佩克已于</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">11</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月底在维也纳会议上决定将其原油日产量减少</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">120</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">万桶。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　受此消息提振，国际油价</span>12<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">日上涨。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　截至当天收盘，纽约商品交易所</span>2017<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">1</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月交货的轻质原油期货价格上涨</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">1.33</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">美元，收于每桶</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">52.83</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">美元，涨幅为</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">2.58%</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">。</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">2017</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">2</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月交货的伦敦布伦特原油期货价格上涨</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">1.36</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">美元，收于每桶</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">55.69</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">美元，涨幅为</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">2.50%</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\">&nbsp;</span></p><p><br/></p>','国际油价12日上涨 收于每桶52.83美元','　  国际油价12日上涨。','1','1','2017-03-13 08:59:22','','0','','','0','{\"thumb\":\"\"}','2','0','0','0','','');INSERT INTO ts_posts ( `id`, `post_author`, `post_keywords`, `post_source`, `post_date`, `post_content`, `post_title`, `post_excerpt`, `post_status`, `comment_status`, `post_modified`, `post_content_filtered`, `post_parent`, `post_type`, `post_mime_type`, `comment_count`, `smeta`, `post_hits`, `post_like`, `istop`, `recommended`, `page_tpl`, `page_tpls` ) VALUES  ('384','1','国内成品油价或迎四年来最大涨幅','','2017-03-13 09:00:33','<p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　新一轮成品油调价窗口将于</span>12<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">14</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">日</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">24</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">时开启。由于产油国减产协议推动国际原油价格大幅走高，机构预测国内油价将迎四年以来的最大涨幅。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\">　　12<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">10</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">日，石油输出国组织</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">(OPEC)</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">成员国与非</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">OPEC</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">成员国达成减产协议，以缓解原油供应过剩、油价低迷的问题，这是双方</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">15</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年来首次实现联合减产。两周前，</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">OPEC</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">内部也达成了</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">8</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年来首个减产协议。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　减产协议的达成提振了国际原油市场，本计价周期原油价格大幅攀升。截至</span>12<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">22</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">日，当日，美国</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">WTI</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">原油期货涨</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">1.33</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">美元，报收</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">52.83</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">美元</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">/</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">桶；布伦特原油期货涨</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">1.36</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">美元，报收</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">55.69</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">美元</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">/</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">桶。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　卓创资讯监测数据显示，截至</span>12<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">12</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">日，参考原油变化率为</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">12.29%</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">，对应汽柴油上调</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">405</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">元</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">/</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">吨。隆众资讯预计本次汽柴油上调</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">420-440</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">元</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">/</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">吨，折合每升约</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">0.31-0.37</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">元，将迎</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">2012</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">10</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月以来的最大涨幅。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\">　　“今年以来，最大的一次上调出现在<span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">10</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月，幅度高达</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">340-355</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">元</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">/</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">吨，当时油价大涨的主要原因是</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">9</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月底</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">OPEC</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">达成限产声明，”隆众资讯油品分析师李彦说，而本轮上调的原因与之非常相似，是因为</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">OPEC</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">达成减产协议撼动市场，力度更胜之前。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　李彦指出，本轮汽柴油上调幅度较大，部分</span>92/93<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">号汽油将重回</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">6</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">元时代。对于私家车主来说，加满一箱油较之前需多花费</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">16-20</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">元。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\">　　“加油站方面，受国际油价影响，近期柴油批发价格大涨，不少民营加油站柴油销售出现亏损局面，”卓创资讯成品油分析师徐娜说，据了解，目前国内不少地区柴油批发价甚至涨超零售限价，加上运输以及人工成本，民营加油站柴油陷入了负盈利的境地。</span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　若油价上调，本次调价将成为</span>2016<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年内第</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">9</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">次上调，</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">2016</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年国内成品油调价将呈现“九涨五跌十搁浅”的格局。根据国内成品油定价机制，</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">12</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">28</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">日</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">24</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">时将迎来</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">2016</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年最后一次汽柴油调价节点。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\">&nbsp;</span></p><p><br/></p>','国内成品油价或迎四年来最大涨幅','　　新一轮成品油调价窗口将于12月14日24时开启。由于产油国减产协议推动国际原油价格大幅走高，机构预测国内油价将迎四年以来的最大涨幅。','1','1','2017-03-13 08:59:56','','0','','','0','{\"thumb\":\"\"}','1','0','0','0','','');INSERT INTO ts_posts ( `id`, `post_author`, `post_keywords`, `post_source`, `post_date`, `post_content`, `post_title`, `post_excerpt`, `post_status`, `comment_status`, `post_modified`, `post_content_filtered`, `post_parent`, `post_type`, `post_mime_type`, `comment_count`, `smeta`, `post_hits`, `post_like`, `istop`, `recommended`, `page_tpl`, `page_tpls` ) VALUES  ('385','1','国际油价13日上涨 收于每桶52.98美元','','2017-03-13 09:01:10','<p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14px; line-height: 24px; text-align: justify;\">　　国际油价</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14px; line-height: 24px; text-align: justify;\">13</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14px; line-height: 24px; text-align: justify;\">日上涨。</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"></span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　国际能源署当天发布的月度报告说，如果欧佩克产油国和非欧佩克产油国严格遵守减产协议，原油市场明年上半年甚至可能从供过于求转为供不应求。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　受此消息提振，国际油价</span>13<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">日上涨。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　截至当天收盘，纽约商品交易所</span>2017<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">1</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月交货的轻质原油期货价格上涨</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">0.15</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">美元，收于每桶</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">52.98</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">美元，涨幅为</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">0.28%</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">。</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">2017</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">2</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月交货的伦敦布伦特原油期货价格上涨</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">0.03</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">美元，收于每桶</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">55.72</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">美元，涨幅为</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">0.05%</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\">&nbsp;</span></p><p><br/></p>','国际油价13日上涨 收于每桶52.98美元','　　国际油价13日上涨。','1','1','2017-03-13 09:00:40','','0','','','0','{\"thumb\":\"\"}','2','0','0','0','','');INSERT INTO ts_posts ( `id`, `post_author`, `post_keywords`, `post_source`, `post_date`, `post_content`, `post_title`, `post_excerpt`, `post_status`, `comment_status`, `post_modified`, `post_content_filtered`, `post_parent`, `post_type`, `post_mime_type`, `comment_count`, `smeta`, `post_hits`, `post_like`, `istop`, `recommended`, `page_tpl`, `page_tpls` ) VALUES  ('386','1','','','2017-03-13 09:02:58','<p><img src=\"/data/upload/ueditor/20170320/58cf46f2a7d8c.gif\" title=\"闪动.gif\" alt=\"闪动.gif\"/></p>','销售网络','销售网络','1','1','2017-03-13 08:59:30','','0','2','','0','{\"thumb\":\"\"}','0','0','0','0','page','pages');INSERT INTO ts_posts ( `id`, `post_author`, `post_keywords`, `post_source`, `post_date`, `post_content`, `post_title`, `post_excerpt`, `post_status`, `comment_status`, `post_modified`, `post_content_filtered`, `post_parent`, `post_type`, `post_mime_type`, `comment_count`, `smeta`, `post_hits`, `post_like`, `istop`, `recommended`, `page_tpl`, `page_tpls` ) VALUES  ('387','1','油价今迎年内最后一次调价 ','','2017-03-13 09:03:21','<p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　今日，国内成品油零售价格调整窗口再次开启，这将成为</span>2016<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年最后一次调价。多家机构预测，本次汽柴油价格上调幅度在</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">100</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">元</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">/</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">吨左右，有望创年内最小涨幅。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　本次调价周期内国际原油价格高位震荡，虽多头消息仍以看好</span>“原油限产”为主，但美元强势格局限制油价涨幅。前两次调价窗口，国内油价均为上调，本次若上调将构成“三连涨”，也为<span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">2016</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年内第</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">10</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">次上调。至此，</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">2016</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年国内成品油调价将呈现“十涨五跌十搁浅”的格局。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　据隆众资讯统计，</span>2016<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年以来，成品油调价已完成</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">10</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">次搁浅，其中</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">3</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">次正常搁浅，而</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">6</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">次因地板价新政而不作调整；</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">9</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">次上调，共计上调汽油价格</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">1950</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">元</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">/</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">吨，柴油价格</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">1885</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">元</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">/</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">吨，折合约</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">1.4-1.6</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">元</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">/</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">升；</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">5</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">次下调，共计下调汽油价格</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">670</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">元</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">/</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">吨，柴油价格</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">650</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">元</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">/</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">吨，折合约</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">0.5-0.6</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">元</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">/</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">升。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　卓创资讯认为，</span> 2016<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年国内成品油零售限价上涨仍为主要基调，主要是受国际原油筑底反弹提振。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　若此轮成品油价格上调，中宇资讯统计数据显示，以上调</span>100<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">元</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">/</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">吨计算，除海南省外，我国大部分省份汽油零售价将在</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">6.3-6.5</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">元</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">/</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">升。以北京国五汽油为例，经价格调整后最高零售升价为</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">6.48</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">元</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">/</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">升。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　隆众资讯油品分析师李彦表示，本轮汽柴油价格上调幅度较小，折合升价或不到</span>1<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">角，加满一箱油较之前多花的费用不会给私家车主的出行成本带来过大的压力。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　中宇资讯分析师许磊测算，以上调</span>100<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">元</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">/</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">吨计算，加满一辆</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">50</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">升油箱的私家车，大约要多花</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">3.8</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">元钱。载重</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">50</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">吨的卡车重载行驶百公里油耗在</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">40L</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">左右，月跑</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">10000</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">公里，调价兑现后月度油耗成本将增加</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">360</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">元左右。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　李彦认为，第四季度的产油国减产协议成为影响油价走势的重要因素。减产协议将于</span>2017<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">1</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">1</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">日起执行，因此明年的</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">1-2</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月，减产协议的落实情况将直接决定国际油价的走向，进而影响到国内成品油调价的趋势。若减产协议落实顺利，则积极气氛的带动下，短期内成品油价格仍将有趋涨态势；而若减产协议落实过程中出现障碍，则成品油价格下调也将在明年</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">1</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月更快的出现。</span></span></p><p><br/></p>','油价今迎年内最后一次调价 “三连涨”完成收官','　　今日，国内成品油零售价格调整窗口再次开启，这将成为2016年最后一次调价。多家机构预测，本次汽柴油价格上调幅度在100元/吨左右，有望创年内最小涨幅。','1','1','2016-12-28 10:04:00','','0','','','0','{\"thumb\":\"\"}','2','0','0','0','','');INSERT INTO ts_posts ( `id`, `post_author`, `post_keywords`, `post_source`, `post_date`, `post_content`, `post_title`, `post_excerpt`, `post_status`, `comment_status`, `post_modified`, `post_content_filtered`, `post_parent`, `post_type`, `post_mime_type`, `comment_count`, `smeta`, `post_hits`, `post_like`, `istop`, `recommended`, `page_tpl`, `page_tpls` ) VALUES  ('388','1','国际油价反弹难言乐观','','2017-03-13 09:04:05','<p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\">　　1<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">3</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">日，国际油价受美元走强影响承压下行，截至当日收盘，纽约商品交易所</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">2</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月交货的轻质原油期货价格下跌</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">1.39</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">美元，收于每桶</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">52.33</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">美元，跌幅为</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">2.59%</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">。</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">3</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月交货的伦敦布伦特原油期货价格下跌</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">1.35</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">美元，收于每桶</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">55.47</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">美元，跌幅为</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">2.38%</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　据路透社</span>3<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">日报道，知名评级机构穆迪发布报告称，预计未来一年国际油价仍将在一定区间内继续波动，同时，全球油气产业价格将持续疲软。分析人士认为，虽然石油输出国组织</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">(</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">欧佩克</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">)</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">和非欧佩克产油国在</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">2016</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">12</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月达成了历史性的协议，从今年</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">1</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">1</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">日起每日减产</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">120</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">万桶，但受减产协议的执行力度、页岩油产量回归以及美元汇率不断走强等因素影响，</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">2017</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年国际油价回升势头或仍难言乐观。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　来自国际能源署的统计称，</span>2016<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">11</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月欧佩克产油国产量飙升，达到日均</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">3420</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">万桶的高点。这意味着欧佩克即使严格执行减产协议中</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">120</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">万桶的减产计划，也很难达到日均限产</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">3250</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">万桶的目标。另一方面，协议能否执行到位，是否会有国家在遵守协议时“偷工减料”，都会影响减产协议在稳定市场上的真正作用和效果。凯投宏观分析师托马斯·皮尤表示，“我们预测该协议仅会被部分落实，许多非欧佩克国家及较小的欧佩克成员国可能不会坚持遵守协议。”值得注意的是，减产是通过人为手段暂时调整国际原油供需平衡状况，而由于未来全球经济不景气或将持续，新兴经济体经济增速放缓，以及全球努力减少碳排放，使得对原油需求受到抑制，对原油的需求短期内很难发生根本性变化，一旦人为力量消失，原油市场又会重新回到供大于求的基本面，使得国际油价不再具有继续上涨的动力。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　穆迪在报告中称，</span>2017<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年北美在石油和天然气行业的探勘及生产将增加。分析认为，当国际油价处于每桶</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">50</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">美元上方时将促使能源公司重新回归，进一步刺激页岩油生产商增加产量。</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">2017</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年，美国页岩油生产存在大幅提高产量的可能性，从而把市场再度拉回到供过于求的局面，使得油价短期内上涨后会承压下行。国际最大的商品交易商嘉能可首席执行官伊凡·格拉森博格认为，产油国与页岩油的博弈或在今年步入高潮，他表示：“欧佩克与美国页岩油企业之间将上演一场‘猫鼠游戏’。”</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　此外，美元走强也将在一段时间内持续打压油价。随着新一届美国总统即将就职，在</span>2017<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年美国政府可能会出台财政刺激政策和美联储加息步伐加快的预期推动下，美元在今年有望继续维持强势。汤森路透原油研究和预测分析师乔治·巴勒里斯认为，已经涨至数年以来高位的美元是阻碍油价复苏的一个重要因素，美元将最终对油价产生加压，并且可能限制基本面收紧带来的涨幅。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　受诸多潜在风险的影响，</span>2017<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年国际油价反弹势头仍将面临重要挑战，企稳回升之路恐怕并不平坦。</span></span></p><p><br/></p>','国际油价反弹难言乐观','　　1月3日，国际油价受美元走强影响承压下行，截至当日收盘，纽约商品交易所2月交货的轻质原油期货价格下跌1.39美元，收于每桶52.33美元，跌幅为2.59%。3月交货的伦敦布伦特原油期货价格下跌1.35美元，收于每桶55.47美元，跌幅为2.38%。','1','1','2017-01-05 09:14:00','','0','','','0','{\"thumb\":\"\"}','2','0','0','0','','');INSERT INTO ts_posts ( `id`, `post_author`, `post_keywords`, `post_source`, `post_date`, `post_content`, `post_title`, `post_excerpt`, `post_status`, `comment_status`, `post_modified`, `post_content_filtered`, `post_parent`, `post_type`, `post_mime_type`, `comment_count`, `smeta`, `post_hits`, `post_like`, `istop`, `recommended`, `page_tpl`, `page_tpls` ) VALUES  ('389','1','全国成品油价格指数小幅回升','','2017-03-13 09:04:37','<p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　依据新华</span>(<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">大庆</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">)</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">国际石油资讯中心发布的报告</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">,</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">截至</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">2016</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">12</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">30</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">日</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">,</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">全国成品油价格指数为</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">741.43,</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">涨幅</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">0.79%,</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">全国成品油价格指数小幅回升。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　全国成品油价格指数运行结果表明</span>,<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">本报告周期</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">92#</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">汽油平均价格报收于</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">6616</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">元／吨</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">,</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">较前一报告周期上涨</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">46</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">元／吨</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">(</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">折合</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">0.03</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">元／升</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">);0#</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">柴油平均价格报收于</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">6634</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">元／吨</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">,</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">较前一报告周期上涨</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">55</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">元／吨</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">(</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">折合</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">0.05</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">元／升</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">)</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">。综合来看</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">,</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">全国汽柴油平均价格均上涨</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">,</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">带动全国成品油价格指数小幅回升。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　新华</span>(<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">大庆</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">)</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">国际石油资讯中心分析师李振国认为</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">,</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">受投资者乐观情绪及美国原油库存增加影响</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">,</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">近期国际油价呈震荡上行走势。国内成品油市场需求低迷</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">,</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">油品市场整体持稳。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　李振国分析认为</span>,<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">近期国际油价继续走高</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">,</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">一揽子原油价格变化率正向加深</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">,</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">然而国内市场终端需求持续疲弱继续打压市场行情</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">,</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">国内成品油价格整体以稳为主小幅波动。地炼方面</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">,</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">山东地炼因出货不畅</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">,</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">价格持续下滑</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">,</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">观望氛围浓厚。观望后市</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">,</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">市场对石油减产预期持续看好</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">,</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">但美元仍维持强势地位</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">,</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">预计短期内油价将维持震荡格局。</span></span></p><p><br/></p>','全国成品油价格指数小幅回升','　　依据新华(大庆)国际石油资讯中心发布的报告,截至2016年12月30日,全国成品油价格指数为741.43,涨幅0.79%,全国成品油价格指数小幅回升。','1','1','2017-01-05 09:10:00','','0','','','0','{\"thumb\":\"\"}','2','0','0','0','','');INSERT INTO ts_posts ( `id`, `post_author`, `post_keywords`, `post_source`, `post_date`, `post_content`, `post_title`, `post_excerpt`, `post_status`, `comment_status`, `post_modified`, `post_content_filtered`, `post_parent`, `post_type`, `post_mime_type`, `comment_count`, `smeta`, `post_hits`, `post_like`, `istop`, `recommended`, `page_tpl`, `page_tpls` ) VALUES  ('477','1','','','2017-03-20 11:32:01','<p style=\"line-height: 1.75em; text-align: center;\">　<img src=\"http://mh.tuishang.com.cn/data/upload/ueditor/20170320/58cf4cf6a7d8c.jpg\" title=\"mmexport1489745587206_副本.jpg\" alt=\"mmexport1489745587206_副本.jpg\"/>　</p><p style=\"line-height: 1.75em; text-align: center;\"><img src=\"http://mh.tuishang.com.cn/data/upload/ueditor/20170320/58cf4d100f424.jpg\" title=\"mmexport1489745679301_副本.jpg\" alt=\"mmexport1489745679301_副本.jpg\"/></p><p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;\">　<span style=\"font-size: 16px;\">　近日，福清市市委书记王进足一行到江阴港区11#码头视察闽海能源有限公司码头及油库综合建设情况。</span></p><p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\">　　王进足实地听取了闽海能源有限公司负责人徐诚坚的汇报，详细了解了目前码头及库区的建设情况，并亲切询问企业当下有什么困难和难题。王进足指出，福清市政府高度重视江阴港区建设，努力为项目推进创造最好的服务条件，在这样的大环境下，企业要牢牢抓住当前发展的好时机，尽快完成手续审批，力争早投产、早见效。</span></p><p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\">　　江阴港11#码头项目是由闽海能源有限公司投资10亿元人民币建设的液体化工码头及配套石化仓储库区。码头及库区总面积1000亩，海岸线长度871米，设计年吞吐量500万吨，码头最大可停靠10万吨级油轮，库容达55万立方米，是福建省最大的成品油库之一。码头及库区目前已进行消防验收，近期将投入试运行。</span></p><p style=\"text-indent: 37px; line-height: 150%;\"><br/></p>','福清市领导视察闽海江阴油库 为企业鼓劲','近日，福清市市委书记王进足一行到江阴港区11#码头视察闽海能源有限公司码头及油库综合建设情况。','1','1','2017-03-20 11:26:48','','0','','','0','{\"thumb\":\"20170320\\/58cf4d9d4c4b4.jpg\"}','20','0','0','0','','');INSERT INTO ts_posts ( `id`, `post_author`, `post_keywords`, `post_source`, `post_date`, `post_content`, `post_title`, `post_excerpt`, `post_status`, `comment_status`, `post_modified`, `post_content_filtered`, `post_parent`, `post_type`, `post_mime_type`, `comment_count`, `smeta`, `post_hits`, `post_like`, `istop`, `recommended`, `page_tpl`, `page_tpls` ) VALUES  ('390','1','新年全球市场展望之油价：回升势头仍受限','','2017-03-13 09:05:46','<p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　全球产油国经过一年的博弈，在</span>2016<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年年末通过减产协议，油价终于在持续走低一年后重回</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">50</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">美元关口，并以一年半来的高位为全年收官。尽管市场对</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">2017</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年原油市场达到供需再平衡的前景非常乐观，但一些机构和分析师指出，油价回升长期来看还有许多限制。</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">2016</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年初油价暴跌。</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">1</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">15</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">日国际油价跌破每桶</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">30</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">美元，创</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">12</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年来低点。此后近一年来，市场受供过于求的担忧情绪影响，油价一直在低价徘徊。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　专家分析，低油价常态已严重影响包括沙特阿拉伯、伊朗、科威特等中东产油国的财政收入，虽然欧佩克内部对于减产实行和测算的分歧长期存在，但为了稳定油价，使财政收支平衡，各产油国不得不互相退让达成减产协议。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　去年</span>11<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">30</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">日欧佩克国家达成减产协议宣布日均减产</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">120</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">万桶后，油价当天攀至</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">50</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">美元，此后连续上涨</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">4</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">天。</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">12</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">10</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">日，非欧佩克产油国达成日均减产</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">55.8</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">万桶协议后，布伦特油价一度接近每桶</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">58</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">美元，纽约油价曾触及每桶</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">54.51</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">美元，均为</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">2015</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">7</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月以来最高点。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　去年</span>12<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月以来，产油国纷纷公开承诺履行减产协议的要求，减少原油供应量。沙特阿拉伯、科威特和阿联酋的国家石油公司向亚洲客户表示，将下调</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">1</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月的原油供应。沙特阿拉伯还向欧美客户表示将减少原油运输。科威特表示</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">1</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月起削减供应的幅度可能超过预期。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　受利好消息影响，多个机构调整</span>2017<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年原油供需和油价的预期。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　国际能源署在最新的月度报告中说，如果各方遵守减产协议，</span>2017<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年上半年，原油市场供过于求的局面会转变成供不应求，供求缺口约为日均</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">60</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">万桶。而此前，该机构认为市场在</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">2017</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年年底才能看到原油供需再平衡。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　美银美林发布的</span>2017<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年能源市场展望中预计布伦特油价将维持在平均每桶</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">61</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">美元，纽约油价则为平均</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">59</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">美元。到年中，油价可能攀升至每桶</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">70</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">美元。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　不过，从供需及美元情况来分析油价未来的走势，一些机构和分析师认为不应该对油价有过于乐观的估计。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　海港全球证券公司分析师弗里德兰德说，上涨的油价将刺激美国页岩油生产商大幅提高产量，从而把市场再度拉回到供过于求的局面，油价短期内上涨后会承压下行。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\">　　“油价上涨持续时间不会很长。<span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">2017</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年油价可能在每桶</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">53</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">美元至</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">57</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">美元区间波动。但是到</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">2018</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年，我们又会看到供过于求的市场，产量会比需求高日均</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">60</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">万桶，”弗里德兰德说。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　同时，市场普遍担心某些欧佩克国家不会遵守减产协议。如果欧佩克成立的监督机构没有执行力，那么减产协议将成为一张废纸，其稳定市场的作用可能因此大打折扣。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　此外，美联储升息也将在一段时间内打压油价。伴随美联储宣布加息，美元一度涨至接近</span>14<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年来最高点，一些产油国的货币相对美元贬值，这些国家的货币走弱意味着以美元计算的开采成本降低，将在一定程度上拉低油价。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　另有专家指出，包括美国等地区的商业原油存储仓库目前已接近饱和，这意味着生产出来的过剩原油无法存放，更将给油价带来下行压力。</span></span></p><p><br/></p>','新年全球市场展望之油价：回升势头仍受限','　　全球产油国经过一年的博弈，在2016年年末通过减产协议，油价终于在持续走低一年后重回50美元关口，并以一年半来的高位为全年收官。尽管市场对2017年原油市场达到供需再平衡的前景非常乐观，但一些机构和分析师指出，油价回升长期来看还有许多限制。2016年初油价暴跌。1月15日国际油价跌破每桶30美元，创12年来低点。此后近一年来，市场受供过于求的担忧情绪影响，油价一直在低价徘徊。','1','1','2017-01-05 09:06:00','','0','','','0','{\"thumb\":\"\"}','2','0','0','0','','');INSERT INTO ts_posts ( `id`, `post_author`, `post_keywords`, `post_source`, `post_date`, `post_content`, `post_title`, `post_excerpt`, `post_status`, `comment_status`, `post_modified`, `post_content_filtered`, `post_parent`, `post_type`, `post_mime_type`, `comment_count`, `smeta`, `post_hits`, `post_like`, `istop`, `recommended`, `page_tpl`, `page_tpls` ) VALUES  ('391','1','成品油今迎2017年首次调价 ','','2017-03-13 09:06:44','<p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\">　　2017<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年首轮成品油调价窗口将于</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">1</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">12</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">日</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">24</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">时开启。多家机构预测油价将迎来上涨，这不仅是</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">2017</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年首次上调，也将实现跨年“四连涨”。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　隆众资讯、卓创资讯等机构预测本轮上调幅度或较小。此前油价在</span>2016<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">11</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">30</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">日、</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">12</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">14</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">日以及</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">12</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">28</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">日三个调价窗口均为上调。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　隆众资讯统计数据显示，截至</span>1<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">10</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">日，原油综合变化率</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">3.24%</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">，按当前原油水平来测算，预计本轮成品油上调幅度为</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">100-110</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">元</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">/</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">吨，折合升价为</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">0.07-0.09</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">元</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">/</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">升。另据卓创资讯测算，预计汽柴油上调</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">80</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">元</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">/</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">吨。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\">　　“国际油价连续两天大幅下滑，本轮国内油价上涨幅度持续收窄，”卓创资讯成品油分析师徐娜说，伊拉克原油出口创新高令市场质疑其是否履行减产协议，加之美元走强等利空因素打压了国际油价。</span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　徐娜指出，按当前预计的</span>80<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">元</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">/</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">吨调整幅度测算，四次连涨后汽油累计涨幅或高达</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">790</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">元</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">/</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">吨，柴油累计涨幅或为</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">765</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">元</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">/</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">吨，折合升价为</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">92</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">号汽油</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">0.62</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">元，</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">0</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">号柴油</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">0.65</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">元。近两个月内消费者用油成本连续增加。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　另据中宇资讯测算，如果此轮油价上调，除海南省外，我国大部分省份汽油零售价将在</span>6.35-6.6<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">元</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">/</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">升。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　虽然本轮成品油最高零售限价将迎来上调，但国内批发市场相对平淡。隆众资讯油品分析师张萌表示，年底临近，且受持续天气因素影响，柴油消费进入淡季，价格一再下滑，而汽油节前备货尚未完全开始，批发价较上轮调价有所下跌。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　中宇资讯分析师胡雪表示，上一计价周期，</span>92<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">号汽油已经全面回归</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">6</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">元时代，车主用车成本上涨。临近春节，用车增多，汽油需求转好，短期对汽油价格形成有力支撑，后期国内汽油价格或将陆续抬头。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　胡雪说，柴油商家目前倾向于降价销售，维持低位库存，整体市场成交积极性较低，市场以震荡下行为主。</span></span></p><p><br/></p>','成品油今迎2017年首次调价 机构预测跨年四连涨','　　2017年首轮成品油调价窗口将于1月12日24时开启。多家机构预测油价将迎来上涨，这不仅是2017年首次上调，也将实现跨年“四连涨”。','1','1','2017-01-12 09:12:00','','0','','','0','{\"thumb\":\"\"}','2','0','0','0','','');INSERT INTO ts_posts ( `id`, `post_author`, `post_keywords`, `post_source`, `post_date`, `post_content`, `post_title`, `post_excerpt`, `post_status`, `comment_status`, `post_modified`, `post_content_filtered`, `post_parent`, `post_type`, `post_mime_type`, `comment_count`, `smeta`, `post_hits`, `post_like`, `istop`, `recommended`, `page_tpl`, `page_tpls` ) VALUES  ('392','1','国内油价节前或无缘','','2017-03-13 09:07:26','<p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　国内下一轮成品油价格调整将于</span>1<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">25</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">日开启，这也将是</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">2017</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年春节前最后一次调价。国际原油价格受诸多利空消息打压，震荡下行，受此影响国内成品油跨年度“四连涨”后，此轮国内成品油调整或小幅下调，节前无缘“五连涨”。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\">　　1<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">20</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">日，是本轮汽、柴油计价周期的第六个工作日，多家机构预测成品油价格将下调。卓创资讯分析师胡慧春认为，目前减产协议的执行情况不明朗，美元汇率高位震荡，原油价格上涨动力不足，下一计价周期内，欧美原油价格或维持高位企稳，不排除有回落的可能性。同时，近日原油持续两日大跌将拉低下一个计价周期内原油均价水平。在综合因素的影响下，下一计价周期内，重新计算后参考原油变化率将处于负值内震荡，国内成品油零售价或无缘“五连涨”，下调的概率极大。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　中宇资讯数据显示，截至北京时间</span>1<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">20</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">日，中宇资讯测算的原油变化率为</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">-0.65%</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">，中宇原油估价</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">54.9</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">美元</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">/</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">桶，较基准价跌</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">0.36</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">美元</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">/</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">桶，亚洲原油估价</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">54.379</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">美元</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">/</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">桶，较基准价跌</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">0.440</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">美元</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">/</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">桶。中宇资讯分析，本轮成品油零售限价或下调</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">50</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">元</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">/</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">吨。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　金联创测算，截至</span>1<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">19</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">日第五个工作日，参考原油品种均价为</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">53.92</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">美元</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">/</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">桶，变化率</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">-0.64%</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">，对应的汽柴油零售价应下调</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">30</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">元</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">/</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">吨。进入下周，国际原油价格或震荡走低，但幅度较小，变化率波动幅度有限，本轮零售价调价窗口或将关闭。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　金联创讯市场分析师王晶认为，主要产油国积极推进减产进度及美元震荡下跌为油价带来支撑，但中国海关数据不尽如人意引发市场对于中国经济放缓的担忧。俄罗斯方面在减产协议到期后再度推高原油产量的预期及近期美国页岩油产量增长势头引发了投资者的悲观预期，加大了油价的下行压力。整体来看，与上周相比，国际油价跌势较为明显。预计近期国际油价将延续震荡格局，主流运行区间将下移至</span>51-54<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">美元</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">/</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">桶左右。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　国内成品油行情整体震荡下行，仅山东地炼市场表现相对强劲。具体来看，国际原油走势较为震荡，市场观望气氛加重，再加上年底临近，下游用户陆续放假停工，柴油需求进一步减弱，对后期行情难有支撑。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　放假期间，国内高速将启动限行，省外远距离客户到地炼采购资源大减，因此大部分炼厂仍积极出货，控制库存水平，实际出货优惠依然较大。整体来看，本周是节前备货的黄金周，主营以及地方炼厂多促销赶量，整体购销相对活跃。</span></span></p><p><br/></p>','国内油价节前或无缘“五连涨” 下调概率极大','　　国内下一轮成品油价格调整将于1月25日开启，这也将是2017年春节前最后一次调价。国际原油价格受诸多利空消息打压，震荡下行，受此影响国内成品油跨年度“四连涨”后，此轮国内成品油调整或小幅下调，节前无缘“五连涨”。','1','1','2017-01-22 10:00:00','','0','','','0','{\"thumb\":\"\"}','2','0','0','0','','');INSERT INTO ts_posts ( `id`, `post_author`, `post_keywords`, `post_source`, `post_date`, `post_content`, `post_title`, `post_excerpt`, `post_status`, `comment_status`, `post_modified`, `post_content_filtered`, `post_parent`, `post_type`, `post_mime_type`, `comment_count`, `smeta`, `post_hits`, `post_like`, `istop`, `recommended`, `page_tpl`, `page_tpls` ) VALUES  ('393','1','成品油或迎今年首度下调 ','','2017-03-13 09:11:44','<p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　如果没有突发因素，春节前国内成品油将结束此前的</span>“四连涨”，迎来<span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">2017</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年的首度下调。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　根据多家成品油分析机构的预测，</span>2017<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">1</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">25</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">日</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">24</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">时，国内成品油的下调幅度为</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">70</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">元</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">/</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">吨至</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">80/</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">吨。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　隆众资讯成品油分析师李彦表示，虽然产油国的减产协议在</span>2017<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">1</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月开始执行，沙特等官方表态也非常积极，但由于缺乏更多的权威数据佐证减产效果，使得国际油价的涨势被抑制。进入</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">1</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月下旬，成品油迅速迎来下调，很可能将抵消掉之前的上调幅度。对于私家车主来说，加满一箱油较之前可节省</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">2.5</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">元至</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">3</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">元。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　但也有分析师认为，如果突发因素对原油的走势影响较大，本次国内成品油零售价的调整幅度又处于</span>50<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">元</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">/</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">吨的调价红线附近，则不能完全排除搁浅的可能。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　据悉，下一轮调价窗口将于</span>2017<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">2</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">14</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">日</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">24</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">时开启，也就是说要等到元宵节过后，油价再进行变化。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\">&nbsp;</span></p><p><br/></p>','成品油或迎今年首度下调 加满一箱油可节省2.5至3元','　　如果没有突发因素，春节前国内成品油将结束此前的“四连涨”，迎来2017年的首度下调。','1','1','2017-01-24 09:19:00','','0','','','0','{\"thumb\":\"\"}','1','0','0','0','','');INSERT INTO ts_posts ( `id`, `post_author`, `post_keywords`, `post_source`, `post_date`, `post_content`, `post_title`, `post_excerpt`, `post_status`, `comment_status`, `post_modified`, `post_content_filtered`, `post_parent`, `post_type`, `post_mime_type`, `comment_count`, `smeta`, `post_hits`, `post_like`, `istop`, `recommended`, `page_tpl`, `page_tpls` ) VALUES  ('394','1','北京3月前完成','','2017-03-13 09:12:49','<p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\">　　1<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">1</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">日起，北京市开始实施第六阶段车用燃油标准，也就是俗称的“京六”。记者从中国石化燕山石化了解到，预计</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">2</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月中旬中国石化在京</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">562</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">座加油站将全部供应“京六”油品。在置换期结束后，从</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">3</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">1</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">日起北京市工商部门将加大成品油质量抽查检测频次，严禁生产、销售不符合新标准要求的车用燃油。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　根据北京市环保局预测，使用</span>“京六”油品后，在用汽油车颗粒物排放降幅达<span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">10%</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">；在用柴油车排放颗粒物下降</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">9.1%</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\">　　“京六”迈入国际成品油排放最高标准之列</span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\">　　“‘京六’油品参考了欧Ⅵ以及更加严格的美国加州标准，与‘京五’油品相比，芳烃、烯烃含量大幅降低，对苯含量、馏程、蒸汽压等多个指标都进行了调整，达到了国际最先进水平。”<span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">1</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">22</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">日，中国石化燕山石化副总经理焦阳在“治霾·京津冀在行动”北京站的媒体见面会上表示，首批“京六”油品已从去年底开始供应北京市场。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　焦阳称，从无铅汽油到京标</span>Ⅵ汽柴油，中国石化燕山石化公司在成品油质量升级方面投入资金超过<span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">21</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">亿元，成功迈入国际成品油排放最高标准的行列。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\">　　2016<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">10</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月，北京市环保局发布实施北京市第六阶段《车用汽油》《车用柴油》地方标准。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　据了解，第六阶段《车用汽油》、《车用柴油》两项地方标准的技术指标参照了目前国际上最严格的车用燃油标准，硫含量维持不变，进一步加严汽油中的烯烃、芳烃、苯、蒸气压、馏程和柴油中的多环芳烃、密度、闪点、清净剂等主要环保指标。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　不断改善车用燃油品质，已成为减少机动车污染排放的重要措施之一。北京市环保局此前发文称，车用燃油品质的提高不但保障新车的正常使用，还会提高净化器转化效率，使得全部在用车排放同步大幅削减。北京市于</span>2004<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年、</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">2005</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年、</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">2008</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年、</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">2012</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年在全国率先实施了第二、三、四和五阶段地方油品标准。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　品质升级、价格未变汽油车颗粒物将减排</span>10%</span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　油品升级中，有车一族们最为关心的一个是油品性能；另一个就是价格高低。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\">　　“油品性能高就表现为使用效率高，在保障高性能的同时，还要控制其排放量要低，在这中间就需要找到一个平衡点。”燕山石化一位工作人员告诉中新网记者，要达到这一目标需要从技术创新着手，生产成本也随之增加。</span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　而据记者了解，目前燕山石化生产的</span>“京六”油品价格并未提高。在焦阳看来，虽然生产成本增加会压缩企业利润，但清洁环保是未来的发展趋势，更是企业核心竞争力。焦阳介绍称，燕山石化“京六”汽油月产能<span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">25</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">万吨，年供应量可达</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">300</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">万吨，约占北京汽油使用量的</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">75%</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　油品升级后，对控制机动车污染排放、改善空气质量将有怎样的实际效果</span>?</span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　根据北京市环保局的预测，使用第六阶段油品后，在用汽油车颗粒物排放降幅达</span>10%<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">，非甲烷有机气体和氮氧化物总体上能够达到</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">8-12%</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">的排放削减率；在用柴油车氮氧化物下降</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">4.6%</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">，颗粒物下降</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">9.1%</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">，总碳氢化合物下降</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">8.3%</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">，一氧化碳下降</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">2.2%</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\">　　3<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">1</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">日起将严禁销售非新标车用燃油</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　为了保证安全和置换质量，按照惯例，</span>“京六”新标准在实施过程中，实行自然置换。</span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　北京市环保局介绍称，车用油品标准置换期为</span>1<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">1</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">日至</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">2</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">28</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">日。置换期结束后，即</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">3</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">1</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">日起，北京市工商部门将依据相关法规及新标准加大对流通领域成品油商品质量抽查检测频次，加强车用燃油质量监管力度，严禁生产、进口、销售不符合新标准要求的车用燃油。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　多方权威机构监测均显示，机动车排放污染已成为北京市</span>PM2.5<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">的最大来源。主要是机动车排放的氮氧化物和挥发性有机物在一定气象条件下，约一半会转化成</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">PM2.5</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　为此，北京市环保局还多措并举治理机动车污染。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　从</span>2017<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">2</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">15</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">日起，北京市将对本市及外埠的国</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">I</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">国Ⅱ排放标准轻型汽油车，实施五环路</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">(</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">不含</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">)</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">以内道路工作日限行；同时，强化管控重型柴油车，严厉查处在用重型柴油车超标排放行为，打击“假国Ⅲ”、“假国Ⅳ”柴油车，重点整治渣土车，明确渣土车的监管责任。</span></span></p><p><br/></p>','北京3月前完成“京六”油品置换','　　1月1日起，北京市开始实施第六阶段车用燃油标准，也就是俗称的“京六”。记者从中国石化燕山石化了解到，预计2月中旬中国石化在京562座加油站将全部供应“京六”油品。在置换期结束后，从3月1日起北京市工商部门将加大成品油质量抽查检测频次，严禁生产、销售不符合新标准要求的车用燃油。','1','1','2017-01-24 09:15:00','','0','','','0','{\"thumb\":\"\"}','1','0','0','0','','');INSERT INTO ts_posts ( `id`, `post_author`, `post_keywords`, `post_source`, `post_date`, `post_content`, `post_title`, `post_excerpt`, `post_status`, `comment_status`, `post_modified`, `post_content_filtered`, `post_parent`, `post_type`, `post_mime_type`, `comment_count`, `smeta`, `post_hits`, `post_like`, `istop`, `recommended`, `page_tpl`, `page_tpls` ) VALUES  ('395','1','预计2017油价继续上涨 ','','2017-03-13 09:13:30','<p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　综合华尔街日报等</span>1<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">23</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">日报道，预测</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">2017</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年油价将继续上涨﹐美国一些石油生产商纷纷提高了年度石油开采预算。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　综合一些公司最近几周公布的</span>2017<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年预算情况，包括</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">Hess Corp (HES)</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">和</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">Noble Energy Inc (NBL)</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">在内的十几家美国页岩油开采商的预算平均增长了</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">60%</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">，这与过去两年来这些公司为应对油价长期低迷而缩减开支并裁员的景象形成鲜明对比。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　预计未来几周会有更多能源公司将宣布增加开支并提高油气产量。在业内领先的先锋资源公司</span>(Pioneer Natural Resources)<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">和</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">EOG Resources</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">等表示﹐由于在油价下滑期间采用先进技术并提高效率﹐这些公司不但能在</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">55</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">美元</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">/</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">桶的油价水平上生存，还能繁荣发展。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　根据英国投资银行巴克莱集团近期对</span>215<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">家能源公司进行的调查﹐</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">2017</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年全球油气生产商的支出预计将增长</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">7%</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">。</span></span></p><p><br/></p>','预计2017油价继续上涨 美石油开发商提高预算','　　综合华尔街日报等1月23日报道，预测2017年油价将继续上涨﹐美国一些石油生产商纷纷提高了年度石油开采预算。','1','1','2017-01-24 09:13:00','','0','','','0','{\"thumb\":\"\"}','2','0','0','0','','');INSERT INTO ts_posts ( `id`, `post_author`, `post_keywords`, `post_source`, `post_date`, `post_content`, `post_title`, `post_excerpt`, `post_status`, `comment_status`, `post_modified`, `post_content_filtered`, `post_parent`, `post_type`, `post_mime_type`, `comment_count`, `smeta`, `post_hits`, `post_like`, `istop`, `recommended`, `page_tpl`, `page_tpls` ) VALUES  ('396','1','全力打造多元石油供应安全体系','','2017-03-13 09:14:34','<p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　近日，《石油发展</span>“十三五”规划》发布。《石油发展“十三五”规划》指出，在储量目标方面，“十三五”期间，年均新增探明石油地质储量<span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">10</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">亿吨左右；在石油供应方面，</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">2020</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年国内石油产量</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">2</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">亿吨以上，构建开放条件下的多元石油供应安全体系，保障国内</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">2020</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">5.9</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">亿吨的石油消费水平；在基础设施能力方面，“十三五”期间，建成原油管道约</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">5000</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">公里，新增一次输油能力</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">1.2</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">亿吨</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">/</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年；建成成品油管道</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">12000</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">公里，新增一次输油能力</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">0.9</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">亿吨</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">/</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年。到</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">2020</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年，累计建成原油管道</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">3.2</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">万公里，形成一次输油能力约</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">6.5</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">亿吨</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">/</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年；成品油管道</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">3.3</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">万公里，形成一次输油能力</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">3</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">亿吨</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">/</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　加快石油储备能力建设</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　《石油发展</span>“十三五”规划》写明，要加强勘探开发保障国内资源供给。陆上和海上并重，加强基础调查和资源评价，加大新区、新层系风险勘探，深化老区挖潜和重点地区勘探投入，夯实国内石油资源基础。巩固老油田，开发新油田，加快海上油田开发，大力支持低品位资源开发，实现国内石油产量基本稳定。《规划》指出，要推进原油、成品油管网建设。整体规划、科学布局、充分发挥市场在资源配置中的决定性作用，优化管输流向，加强多元供应，提高管输比例和运行效率，有效降低物流成本。原油管道重在优化和提升陆上、海上原油进口能力，成品油管道重在解决区域油品不平衡问题和提高管输比例。加强科技创新，提高管道装备制造和工程技术水平，推进装备国产化，加快实现管道系统智能化、网络化。落实管道第三方公平开放，优先考虑利用现有管道向目标市场输送资源。加强管道保护和安全隐患治理。着力构建布局合理、覆盖广泛、安全高效的现代石油管道网络。《规划》强调，要加快石油储备能力建设。一方面，加快国家石油储备基地建设，推进国家石油储备二期、三期项目建设。加强国家对政府储备基地的统一管理。加快成品油政府储备基础设施建设。另一方面，稳步落实储备规划，协调推进国家石油储备基地收储工作。积极利用符合规定的企业库容代储国家储备原油。鼓励社会资本参与商业仓储设施投资运营。此外，健全石油储备制度，尽快出台《国家石油储备条例》，建立企业义务储备，推动建立完善政府储备、企业义务储备和企业生产经营库存有机结合、互为补充的储备体系，多方式、多途径提高国家石油保障能力。</span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　大力发展清洁替代能源</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　记者了解到，《规划》在石油节约利用与清洁替代能源方面提出了发展要求。《规划》写明，要坚持石油节约利用。推进石油行业能效提升，优化基础设施、产能建设项目等用能工艺，选用高效节能设备，切实加强节能管理。努力提高原油商品率，采取增加伴生气回注、油气混输技术、伴生气凝液回收技术等措施加强油田伴生气回收利用。持续开展工业、交通和建筑等重点领域节能，推进终端燃油产品能效提升和重点用能行业能效水平对标达标。实施内燃机、锅炉等重点用能设备能效提升计划，推进工业企业余热、余压利用。实施更加严格的燃油标准。加快发展轨道交通和水运等资源节约型、环境友好型运输方式。《规划》指出，要大力发展清洁替代能源。大力推广电能、天然气等对燃油的清洁化替代。积极支持天然气汽车、船舶发展，加快电动汽车等节能环保和新能源汽车应用。在</span>“禁煤区”将排放不达标的燃油工业锅炉和窑炉列入禁燃范围，重点开展<span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">20</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">蒸吨</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">/</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">小时以下的燃油工业锅炉天然气、电能替代。实施港口气化示范工程，推广港口岸电系统。推进煤制油、煤制气产业示范。已建成的示范项目实现安全、环保、稳定运行，自主技术和装备可靠性得到验证，煤制清洁燃料和化工原料得到市场认可和应用，装备自主化率进一步提高，推动形成技术路线完整、产品种类齐全的煤炭深加工产业体系。促进生物质能的开发和利用。合理扩大生物乙醇汽油生产和消费，适当发展生物柴油、生物航煤等先进生物燃料，提升可再生燃料比重。超前部署微藻制油等技术和产业化攻关。</span></span></p><p><br/></p>','全力打造多元石油供应安全体系','　　近日，《石油发展“十三五”规划》发布。《石油发展“十三五”规划》指出，在储量目标方面，“十三五”期间，年均新增探明石油地质储量10亿吨左右；','1','1','2017-01-24 09:10:00','','0','','','0','{\"thumb\":\"\"}','4','0','0','0','','');INSERT INTO ts_posts ( `id`, `post_author`, `post_keywords`, `post_source`, `post_date`, `post_content`, `post_title`, `post_excerpt`, `post_status`, `comment_status`, `post_modified`, `post_content_filtered`, `post_parent`, `post_type`, `post_mime_type`, `comment_count`, `smeta`, `post_hits`, `post_like`, `istop`, `recommended`, `page_tpl`, `page_tpls` ) VALUES  ('397','1','我国石油产业机遇与挑战并存','','2017-03-13 09:15:31','<p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\">　“十三五”期间，我国石油产业发展机遇与挑战并存，一方面，我国石油产业在国际合作上迎来新机遇，另一方面，我国石油产业的可持续发展存在制约。</span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\">　　</span><strong><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;font-size: 14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">石油产业国际合作迎来新机遇</span></span></strong></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　《石油发展</span>“十三五”规划》写明，我国石油产业发展面临的机遇体现在多个方面：首先，全球石油供需形势总体宽松。美国页岩革命带动了页岩油、致密油等非常规、低品位资源勘探开发，<span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">2015</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年全球石油产量</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">43.6</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">亿吨，储采比</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">55</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">。预计“十三五”时期全球石油供应持续宽松、油价维持低位、需求稳定增长、消费重心东移。新常态下我国经济长期向好的基本面没有改变，“十三五”时期石油需求仍将稳步增长，但增速进一步放缓，石油在一次能源消费中的占比保持基本稳定。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　其次，体制机制改革全面深化。国内外油气供需总体宽松的态势为深化油气行业改革提供了难得的历史机遇。</span>“十三五”时期我国油气体制改革将在放宽市场准入、完善管网建设运营机制、落实基础设施公平接入、市场化定价、完善行业管理和监管等方面深入推进，充分发挥市场在资源配置中的决定性作用。</span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　再次，国际合作迎来新机遇。当前地缘政治和国际能源格局深刻调整的战略机遇期为我国积极拓展国际石油合作，参与全球能源治理提供了新空间。党中央提出建设</span>“丝绸之路经济带”和“<span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">21</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">世纪海上丝绸之路”的合作倡议，能源合作是其中重要内容之一，有助于加大与相关国家在油气勘探开发、投资贸易、技术服务等领域合作，加强能源基础设施互联互通，共同维护跨境管道安全。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\">　　</span><strong><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;font-size: 14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">石油产业可持续发展存在制约</span></span></strong></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　与此同时，我国石油产业也面临着诸多挑战。《规划》强调，第一，石油供应安全面临挑战。国内石油总体进入低品位资源勘探开发的新阶段，产量大幅增长难度大，开放条件下的石油供应安全仍是面临的重要问题。原油进口主要集中在中东等地缘政治不稳定地区、海上运输过于依赖马六甲海峡、陆上跨国管道突发事件等风险依然存在。石油储备规模及应急响应水平、国际石油合作质量还不能完全适应近年来国际油价波动幅度加大、频率加快的市场格局。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　第二，国内石油勘探投入不足。油气领域勘探开发主体较少，区块退出和流转机制不健全，竞争性不够。加之不同地区地质认识和资源禀赋差异，各公司勘探主要集中在资源丰度高地区，风险勘探积极性不高，部分地区勘探投入不足。一些国内企业通过</span>“走出去”已获得国外区块，积累了技术和管理经验，但国内准入仍存在诸多限制，制约了多元化资本投入。</span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　第三，行业可持续发展存在制约。国内老油田已进入开发中后期，历史包袱和社会负担重、人员冗余，经营成本相对较高。大型国有企业经营机制不灵活、治理结构不完善，管理水平较国际一流企业仍存在较大差距。石油海外投资迅速增长，但控制和抵御风险能力不强，盈利能力持续下滑，国际话语权较弱。伴随</span>2014<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年以来油价大幅下跌，国内石油行业市场化体系不健全、竞争力不足等体制性问题凸显。同时，低油价下企业大幅削减投资，油田作业量减少，员工收入下降，可能带来老油区社会稳定等风险隐患。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　第四，项目建设和管道安全面临压力。随着我国城乡经济发展和城镇化率提高，石油产能建设及基础设施项目与城乡规划、土地利用、生态保持的冲突时有发生，用地保障难度加大，部分管道路由难以协调。管道建设与其他基础设施相遇相交日益增多，管道占压和第三方破坏、损伤比较严重，管道安全运营风险加大，管道检验检测和完整性管理还未推广，检验检测技术水平不适应安全需求。渤海等近海海域用海矛盾日益突出。国家对海洋石油开发及管输环境保护和作业安全提出更高要求。</span></span></p><p><br/></p>','我国石油产业机遇与挑战并存','　“十三五”期间，我国石油产业发展机遇与挑战并存，一方面，我国石油产业在国际合作上迎来新机遇，另一方面，我国石油产业的可持续发展存在制约。','1','1','2017-01-24 09:05:00','','0','','','0','{\"thumb\":\"\"}','2','0','0','0','','');INSERT INTO ts_posts ( `id`, `post_author`, `post_keywords`, `post_source`, `post_date`, `post_content`, `post_title`, `post_excerpt`, `post_status`, `comment_status`, `post_modified`, `post_content_filtered`, `post_parent`, `post_type`, `post_mime_type`, `comment_count`, `smeta`, `post_hits`, `post_like`, `istop`, `recommended`, `page_tpl`, `page_tpls` ) VALUES  ('398','1','我国光伏发电新增和累计装机容量均为全球第一','','2017-03-13 09:16:56','<p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　记者</span>4<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">日从国家能源局获悉，截至</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">2016</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年底，我国光伏发电新增装机容量</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">3454</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">万千瓦，累计装机容量</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">7742</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">万千瓦，新增和累计装机容量均为全球第一。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　根据国家能源局公布的</span>2016<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年光伏发电统计信息，我国光伏发电向中东部转移，中东部地区新增装机容量超过</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">100</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">万千瓦的省份达</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">9</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">个，分别是山东、河南、安徽、河北、江西、山西、浙江、湖北、江苏。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　此外，分布式光伏发电装机容量发展提速，</span>2016<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年新增装机容量</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">424</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">万千瓦，比</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">2015</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年新增装机容量增长</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">200%</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">。</span></span></p><p><br/></p>','我国光伏发电新增和累计装机容量均为全球第一','　　记者4日从国家能源局获悉，截至2016年底，我国光伏发电新增装机容量3454万千瓦，累计装机容量7742万千瓦，新增和累计装机容量均为全球第一。','1','1','2017-02-06 09:23:00','','0','','','0','{\"thumb\":\"\"}','2','0','0','0','','');INSERT INTO ts_posts ( `id`, `post_author`, `post_keywords`, `post_source`, `post_date`, `post_content`, `post_title`, `post_excerpt`, `post_status`, `comment_status`, `post_modified`, `post_content_filtered`, `post_parent`, `post_type`, `post_mime_type`, `comment_count`, `smeta`, `post_hits`, `post_like`, `istop`, `recommended`, `page_tpl`, `page_tpls` ) VALUES  ('399','1','中国新能源陷“边建边弃”怪圈','','2017-03-13 09:18:09','<p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　一方面是不断增加的弃风弃光，一方面是不断增加的装机总量，我国新能源越来越陷入</span>“边建边弃”的怪圈：长期存在的输送消纳问题不仅没有缓解，近两年反而更加恶化。“边建边弃”的背后，是我国新能源过剩的危机，庞大的投资在广袤的原野里晒太阳。</span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　弃风弃光十余年形势更趋恶化</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　从嘉峪关往西，沿着</span>G30<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">国家高速百余公里，就进入我国第一个千万千瓦级风电基地酒泉风电基地，成片的风车沿公路两旁排列，绵延</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">300</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">余公里，宛如“白色森林”。截至</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">2015</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年底，酒泉风电装机</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">900</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">万千瓦，光伏装机</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">165</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">万千瓦。记者看到，虽然寒风凛冽，但是八成以上的风机静静耸立，任凭朔风猎猎，我自岿然不动。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\">　　“装机<span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">20</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">万千瓦的风电场，只发一万千瓦的都有。”已经在甘肃瓜州县戈壁滩上风吹日晒了近十年的许广生，谈起风电时更多的是忧虑，“风电产业要被弃风拖垮了。”</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">许广生所在的甘肃中电酒泉风力发电公司是甘肃最早进行风电开发的企业之一，目前有装机</span>107<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">万千瓦，</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">2016</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年弃风率为</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">54%</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　和中电酒泉风力发电公司一样，在酒泉风电基地，所有的风电企业无一例外地陷入生产经营困境，这个困境就是居高不下的弃风，十余年来，新能源的这个顽疾就没有好转过。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　记者了解到，目前甘肃风电装机为</span>1277<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">万千瓦，位居全国第三位。国家能源局的数据显示，</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">2015</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年甘肃弃风率为</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">39%</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">，</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">2016</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年上半年达到</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">47%</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">，风电利用小时数由</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">2013</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年的</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">1806</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">小时减少到</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">2015</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年的</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">1184</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">小时，</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">2016</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年前三季度为</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">870</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">小时。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　甘肃弃风仅仅是我国新能源的缩影，我国</span>“三北”地区规划的六个千万千瓦级风电基地全部存在弃风现象。国家能源局的数据显示，<span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">2015</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年全国风电弃风率为</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">15%</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">，成为有史以来弃风最严重的年份，</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">2016</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年一季度弃风率攀升至</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">26%</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">，而</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">2016</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年前</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">9</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">个月“三北”地区的平均弃风率更是逼近</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">30%</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　中国可再生能源学会风能专业委员会秘书长秦海岩表示，</span>2015<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年的弃风电量合计约</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">350</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">亿千瓦时，直接经济损失约</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">180</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">亿元，这意味着全年的弃风损失几乎抵消了</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">2015</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年全年风电新增装机的社会经济效益。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　弃风的同时，弃光也在不断刷新历史纪录。中利腾晖光伏公司在嘉峪关有</span>150<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">兆瓦的光伏装机。“</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">2016</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年近</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">70%</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">的装机在闲置，是弃光最多的一年。”电站负责人陶生柱说。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　记者了解到，金昌是甘肃第一个百万千瓦级的光伏基地，</span>2015<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年底光伏装机达到</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">180</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">万千瓦，光伏发电比例不足装机容量的</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">40%</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　甘肃目前是我国光伏装机容量居第二位的新能源大省，光伏装机</span>678<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">万千瓦。国家能源局的数据显示，</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">2016</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年一季度，全国弃光主要发生在甘肃、新疆和宁夏，其中甘肃弃光限电</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">8.4</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">亿千瓦时，弃光率</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">39%</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">，甘肃是国内弃风弃光的“双料冠军”。国家可再生能源中心主任王仲颖介绍，</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">2016</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年上半年，全国弃风电量</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">326</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">亿千瓦时，弃光电量</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">37</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">亿千瓦时。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　除了已并网的装机闲置严重外，还有一些已经建成却无法并网的装机，正在戈壁滩上晒太阳。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\">　</span><strong><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;font-size: 14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　救命措施不断出台实际效果有限</span></span></strong></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　面对愈演愈烈的弃风弃光，国家不断采取措施进行化解。甘肃、宁夏、新缰、内蒙古、吉林等省区通过新能源与自备电厂电量置换、大用户直购点、发展高载能产业、实施清洁供暖等措施扩大就地消纳规模，国家电网则通过建设远距离特高压输电线路，加大外送力度。但是有史以来最严重的弃风弃电显示，这些措施效果有限。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　新能源界的人士认为，用电需求增长放缓、消纳市场总量不足；新能源增速太快、电网调峰能力不足；通道建设与电源建设不匹配、电网送出能力有限；电网存在薄弱环节、部分区域受网架约束影响消纳等问题，是我国弃风弃光长期存在的根本原因。我国新能源快速发展的这十年中，一开始就存在的这些问题，就没有很好地解决过。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　在就地消纳不了、外送无法实现的情况下，</span>2016<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">3</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月份，国家发改委出台了《可再生能源发电全额保障性收购管理办法》，已经陷入全面亏损的新能源企业，似乎看到了走出低谷的希望。“这是新能源行业的救命稻草。”采访时，所有的新能源企业负责人都这样评价。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　与此同时，国家能源局又发布了《关于做好风电光伏发电全额保障性收购管理工作有关要求的通知》，核定</span>“三北”地区风电场保障性收购小时数在<span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">1800</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">到</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">2000</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">小时之间。对于这个小时数，新能源行业认为，虽不是全额收购，但尚能保证企业合理盈利。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　但是，此后部分省区出台的保障性收购小时数显示，保障性收购难以落实，在省级层面就打了折扣。目前，只有河北、新疆、宁夏等省区出台了保障性收购小时数，河北最低小时数为风电</span>2000<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">小时、光伏</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">1400</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">小时，新疆风电、光伏分别为</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">700</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">小时和</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">500</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">小时，宁夏风电、光伏分别为</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">1050</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">小时、</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">900</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">小时，甘肃为风电</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">500</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">小时、光伏</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">400</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">小时。只有河北省达到了国家的要求，其余三省区都没有达到。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　新能源界认为，保障性收购的这种尴尬，其实反映出的是我国新能源</span>“边建边弃”的难解困局。</span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\">　</span><strong><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;font-size: 14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　盘活存量才能破解</span>“边建边弃”</span></strong></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　我国已成为全球新能源装机最大的国家，</span>2016<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年上半年，全国风电累计并网容量达到</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">1.37</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">亿千瓦，同比增长</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">30%</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">；</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">2016</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">11</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月，全国累计并网光伏电站超过</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">7400</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">万千瓦，同比增长</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">40%</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">。在产能严重过剩的情况下，新能源装机并未减少，导致弃风弃光率不断刷新纪录，向常态化、恶性化发展。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　在弃风弃光严重的同时，新能源财政补贴资金缺口也越来越大。国家能源局副局长李仰哲表示，</span>2016<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年上半年，我国可再生能源补贴缺口达到</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">550</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">亿元，原有的补贴模式难以为继。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　采访中，新能源界人士认为，面对</span>“边建边弃”的困局，目前亟待盘活存量，控制增量。否则，我国新能源产业会陷入东西南北中全面“趴窝”的困境。</span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\">&nbsp;</span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　首先要盘活现有存量装机资源。盘活存量就相当于有了增量，就甘肃而言，目前光伏装机容量是</span>678<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">万千瓦，有</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">70%</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">约</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">470</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">余万千瓦的装机闲置。如果闲置装机率下降到</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">30%</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">，相当于增加了</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">332</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">万千瓦的装机，比东部一个省的光伏装机都多。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　光伏业内人士估算，如果盘活存量资源，将西北五省累计并网的约</span>2300<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">万千瓦光伏发电弃光率降低一半，就相当于增加了近千万千瓦的光伏装机，这已经接近于目前中东部和南方地区的光伏装机。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　国家能源局总工程师韩水表示，未来几年将把弃风弃光率力争控制在</span>5%<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">以内的合理水平。记者采访的甘蒙青的新能源企业负责人认为，这个目标在风光电装机较少、电力短缺的时候都没有完成，在目前庞大的装机体量下更不可能实现。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　但是，新能源界对盘活存量并不乐观。</span>2016<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年底发布的电力发展和风电发展“十三五”规划提出，</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">2020</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年全国风电装机将达到</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">2.1</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">亿千瓦以上，年均新增约</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">1600</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">万千瓦，光伏发电装机要达到</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">1.1</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">亿千瓦以上。水电水利规划设计总院副院长易跃春说，在我国整体能源需求放缓、风电装机过剩的情况下，风电、火电、水电都要抢占发电空间，竞争将十分激烈。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　其次调整新能源发展规划，为</span>“三北”地区预留更大的消纳空间。<span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">2016</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年初，国家能源局叫停了甘吉蒙新等“三北”省区新增新能源项目，近期出台的《风电发展“十三五”规划》在布局上将风电开发主战场从“三北”地区调整到了消纳能力好的中东部和南方区。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　采访中，甘肃、内蒙古、青海的能源管理部门认为，</span>“十三五”风光电的重点区，恰恰是“三北”地区新能源外送的目标区，这就意味着“三北”新能源大基地的外送空间已经十分狭窄，只能侧重于就地消纳，即使目前在建的多条特高压输电工程建成，外送仍然有限。　新能源企业认为，国家核准“三北”<span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">6</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">个千万千瓦级风电基地时，基本思路就是建设大基地，融入大电网，将“三北”新能源向“三华”地区输送，现在新能源布局的调整，基本上砍断了“三北”新能源外送后路。虽然“十三五”规划提出解决“三北”</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">4000</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">万千瓦风电的外送消纳问题，但没有可操作的细则，如何外送，送到哪里，都是未知数。在电力市场蛋糕不增反减的情况下，各省市首先确保消纳本区域内的电力电量，谁又给外省电力让出市场份额呢？业界认为，当新能源“村村冒烟”的时候，就预示着这个产业已经没有发展空间了。</span></span></p><p><br/></p>','中国新能源陷“边建边弃”怪圈','　　一方面是不断增加的弃风弃光，一方面是不断增加的装机总量，我国新能源越来越陷入“边建边弃”的怪圈：长期存在的输送消纳问题不仅没有缓解，近两年反而更加恶化。“边建边弃”的背后，是我国新能源过剩的危机，庞大的投资在广袤的原野里晒太阳。','1','1','2017-02-06 09:18:00','','0','','','0','{\"thumb\":\"\"}','2','0','0','0','','');INSERT INTO ts_posts ( `id`, `post_author`, `post_keywords`, `post_source`, `post_date`, `post_content`, `post_title`, `post_excerpt`, `post_status`, `comment_status`, `post_modified`, `post_content_filtered`, `post_parent`, `post_type`, `post_mime_type`, `comment_count`, `smeta`, `post_hits`, `post_like`, `istop`, `recommended`, `page_tpl`, `page_tpls` ) VALUES  ('400','1','国际油价7日下跌 ','','2017-03-13 09:19:08','<p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　国际油价</span>7<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">日下跌。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　美国能源信息局</span>7<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">日公布的数据显示，</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">2016</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年美国原油日均产量为</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">890</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">万桶，今年将达</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">900</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">万桶。到</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">2018</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年，美国原油日均产量将攀升至</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">950</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">万桶左右。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　市场担忧美国原油产量增加可能部分抵消欧佩克及其他产油国的减产努力，令油价当天承压下行。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　当天，美元对多数主要货币汇率上涨。美元走强降低了以美元计价的石油的投资吸引力，也使油价承压。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　截至当天收盘，纽约商品交易所</span>3<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月交货的轻质原油期货价格下跌</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">0.84</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">美元，收于每桶</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">52.17</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">美元，跌幅为</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">1.58%</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">。</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">4</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月交货的伦敦布伦特原油期货价格下跌</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">0.67</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">美元，收于每桶</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">55.05</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">美元，跌幅为</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">1.20%</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">。</span></span></p><p><br/></p>','国际油价7日下跌 收于每桶52.17美元','　　国际油价7日下跌。','1','1','2017-02-08 11:00:00','','0','','','0','{\"thumb\":\"\"}','3','0','0','0','','');INSERT INTO ts_posts ( `id`, `post_author`, `post_keywords`, `post_source`, `post_date`, `post_content`, `post_title`, `post_excerpt`, `post_status`, `comment_status`, `post_modified`, `post_content_filtered`, `post_parent`, `post_type`, `post_mime_type`, `comment_count`, `smeta`, `post_hits`, `post_like`, `istop`, `recommended`, `page_tpl`, `page_tpls` ) VALUES  ('401','1','专家：油气改革 应“三箭齐发”','','2017-03-13 09:20:14','<p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　国家发改委日前印发《石油发展</span>“十三五”规划》、《天然气发展“十三五”规划》。规划预计，“十三五”时期石油需求增速进一步放缓，天然气供求总体上将进入宽平衡状态，并从储量、供应、基础设施三方面制定了石油天然气发展目标。分析人士认为，未来石油天然气体制改革中管网分开是大方向，当务之急是突破国企改革所有制的缺失和产权不明的瓶颈。同时，油气体制改革应上中下游改革“三箭齐发”，从价格、市场主体、准入、税费等方面综合推进。</span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\">　　</span><strong><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;font-size: 14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">产权不明制约改革</span></span></strong></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　对于混合所有制改革，能源领域多家企业已率先</span>“出招”。</span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　中石油在</span>2016<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">12</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">20</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">日召开的全面深化改革领导小组第十五次会议上，便研究推进市场化改革、混合所有制改革指导意见。会议指出，将建立完善现代企业制度，创新商业模式，做强做优主业，退出无效低效业务，实施分类推进、完善公司治理等主要改革举措。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　中石化混改也在稳步推进。</span>2016<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年底，中石化油气管网混改取得实质性进展。中石化发布公告称，川气东送天然气管道有限公司增资引进投资者，中国人寿和国投交通拟分别以现金</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">200</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">亿元及</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">28</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">亿元认购川气东送管道有限公司合计</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">50%</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">股权。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　据了解，</span>“两桶油”不仅在理论层面对混合所有制改革予以明确，实践方面也已悄然开始。比如中石油在<span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">2016</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年中就重组旗下资产，将金融板块及工程建设板块整合上市；中石化也于近期入股九州证券，或为混改做铺垫。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　但在这背后，目前仍有许多因素掣肘企业混合所有制改革发展。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\">　　“深化油气改革的重要一步是突破国企改革所有制的缺失和产权不明的瓶颈。”业内人士认为，表面上是股权层面国资与非国资混合，股权结构合理化，破解所有者缺位，以及在一定程度上化解国进民退等国资、非国资之间的对立问题。但深层次是健全现代企业制度，更好地发挥企业家作用，重塑市场在资源配置中的决定性作用。</span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　方正证券分析师马宝玲表示：</span>“国企发展混合所有制，关键在于努力营造国有股东和中小股东平等行使权利、共生共赢的环境，只有实现权利平等，实现双方权利行使的公平，国资和民资才能有效地混合，进而才能形成国资和民资的合力，也才能实现国资和民资最大程度的增值。”随着天然气产业快速发展，部分原有政策已不适应新的发展形势，储气能力严重滞后，保供难度日益增加。勘探开发和管道输送环节主体少，竞争不足，管道运营不透明，难以实现第三方市场主体公平接入，行业行政垄断和区域分割较严重，市场化体制机制不健全，价格变化难以完全真实反映市场供求关系等矛盾日益突出。</span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\">　　</span><strong><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;font-size: 14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">改革瘦身降本增效</span></span></strong></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　中国企业研究院首席研究员李锦认为，</span>2017<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年将是混合所有制改革的落地年。垄断领域混改一直是难啃的“硬骨头”，但对整个混改乃至国企改革有牵引作用。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　油气改革重点和路径是</span>“四放开”：放开竞争性环节气价，向社会资本放开上游勘探开发业务，放开管网的第三方准入，积极放开原油进口权。马宝玲认为：“当前改革重点是鼓励各类资本参与投资、实现管网相对独立，鼓励第三方准入，目标是实现管网产权独立和强制公开准入。”</span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\">　　“油气体制改革不能仅局限于某一环节，而应上中下游改革‘三箭齐发’。”国家发展和改革委员会价格监测中心刘满平强调，不能仅局限于价格改革等某一方面的“单兵突进”，而应从价格、市场主体、税费等方面综合推进。</span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　李锦指出，此次油气改革将涉及全产业链，具体包括体制改革和国企改革两条主线。油气产业链分为：上游勘探开采和原油进口，中游管网，下游销售。在改革方向上：包括常规油气和非常规油气在内的矿权准入有望放开、原油进口权有望加速放开。在油气行业国企改革领域，要关注专业化重组。从国际经验看，专业化重组和主辅分离是近年来的趋势。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　第一财经研究院研究员杨驿昉认为，财税体制改革方面，需厘清各方关系、兼顾各方利益，并着重考虑税费设计与能源和环保、税费改革与油气行业特点、税费水平与资源并符合消费导向、税与费，以及中央与地方财权分配等关系的处理。定价改革方面，油气价格市场化改革将继续推进，市场在油气价格形成过程中的作用将进一步增强。</span></span></p><p><br/></p>','专家：油气改革 应“三箭齐发”','　　国家发改委日前印发《石油发展“十三五”规划》、《天然气发展“十三五”规划》。','1','1','2017-02-08 09:37:00','','0','','','0','{\"thumb\":\"\"}','4','0','0','0','','');INSERT INTO ts_posts ( `id`, `post_author`, `post_keywords`, `post_source`, `post_date`, `post_content`, `post_title`, `post_excerpt`, `post_status`, `comment_status`, `post_modified`, `post_content_filtered`, `post_parent`, `post_type`, `post_mime_type`, `comment_count`, `smeta`, `post_hits`, `post_like`, `istop`, `recommended`, `page_tpl`, `page_tpls` ) VALUES  ('402','1','国际油价回暖 ','','2017-03-13 09:23:01','<p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\">　　1<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月以来，国内外油田服务公司陆续发布</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">2016</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年业绩快报，行业大额亏损引发业界关注。油田服务业真的不行了</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">?</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">同是亏损，谁在疲于应付，谁能蓄力反击</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">?2017</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年会成为回暖之年吗</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">?</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\">　　</span><strong><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;font-size: 14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">油气行业不景气，国际巨头也发愁</span></span></strong></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\">　　1<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">20</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">日至</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">1</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">21</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">日，国内油服行业两大巨头中海油服、石化油服分别发布了</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">2016</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年业绩预告。实际上，受低油价影响，全球油田服务业一片萧条，亏损目前并不只限于国内。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　近两年来，全球第一大油服公司斯伦贝谢已经宣布裁员</span>5<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">万个工作岗位，但在</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">1</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">20</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">日交出的</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">2016</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年全年成绩单中，净利润亏损</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">16.87</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">亿美元，折合人民币约为</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">116</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">亿元。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　合并计划流产的哈里伯顿和贝克休斯两大公司情况更为惨烈。哈里伯顿公司全球裁员至少超过</span>9%<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">，</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">2016</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年前三季度亏损</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">55</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">亿美元左右，折合人民币约为</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">400</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">亿元。据说，为避免进一步裁员和缩减支出，哈里伯顿公司宣布将出售其在美国休斯顿一处面积约为</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">48</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">英亩的办公大楼。从</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">2016</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">9</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">14</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">日起，哈里伯顿公司还对部分员工开始正式实行“停薪休假”。该计划将持续</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">90</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">天到</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">2016</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年年底，哈里伯顿公司的“小时工”每周工作时间将被缩短，而“受薪雇员”则必须休假一个星期、且无薪水。这一计划将影响到</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">500</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">名从美国休斯顿、卡罗尔顿到拉斐特的生产制造部门的雇员。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　贝克休斯公司</span>2016<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年前三季度亏损超过</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">23</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">亿美元，折合人民币将近</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">160</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">亿元，这还未计入第四季度的经营情况。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\">　　“孤立地看待油田服务业的发展是不科学的。”中国石油大学<span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">(</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">北京</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">)</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">中国油气产业发展研究中心主任董秀成认为。整个油气行业发展都很不景气，油田服务业作为其中一个重要环节肯定会受到影响，甚至从更大的角度，从全球能源行业、全球经济发展来看，油田服务业的寒冬是很自然的。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　银河证券首席研究员裘孝锋认为，油田服务业目前业绩不佳是可以理解的。从历史来看，油服公司对油价的反应有一定的滞后性，一般来说是之后的</span>6-12<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">个月。国际油价从</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">2014</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年年底开始下跌，</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">2016</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年上半年见底。据银河证券统计，全球上市油公司的资本支出</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">2016</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年比</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">2013</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年减少</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">50%</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">，那么传导到油田服务公司，</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">2016</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年出现业绩低谷是合理情况。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\">　</span><strong><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;font-size: 14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　亏损</span>“出血点”不同，公司潜力差别大</span></strong></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　当出现全行业亏损的时候，如何区别不同公司的真实情况和发展潜力</span>?<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">关键要看亏损的“出血点”在哪。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　据观察，在中海油服的亏损中，近</span>70%<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">是一次性商誉和资产减值，去除资产减值，生产经营的实际亏损并没有那么严重。根据财报预计，贝克休斯公司</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">2016</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年资产减值数额也比较大。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　资产减值本质上是由于油价下跌，根据每个公司不同的模型对自己长期资产和商誉进行减值。而生产经营性的亏损，则是一种</span>“真金白银”的亏损。“低油价下，油田服务公司的业绩压力主要来自生产经营亏损和资产减值，但两者有所不同。”裘孝锋认为。生产经营亏损意味着公司成本较高，同时也会影响现金流；而资产减值则是一种“账面亏损”，不影响现金流，如果未来油价上涨，行业景气性提升，还可以对冲回来。直观地说，如果两家公司同样亏损<span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">100</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">亿元，</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">A</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">公司是</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">80</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">亿元生产经营亏损和</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">20</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">亿元资本减值，</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">B</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">公司是</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">50</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">亿元生产经营亏损和</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">50</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">亿元资本减值，那么两家公司中</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">B</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">公司的成本把控能力更强，一定程度上显示了其更好的竞争力。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　资产减值也被认为是上市公司的一种经营策略。董秀成认为，暂时的亏损可能是为了下一步的盈利做准备。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\">　　</span><strong><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;font-size: 14px\">2017<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">油价回暖，油服业绩反弹可期</span></span></strong></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　尽管去年油田服务行业全体遭遇严重亏损，但业内专家表示随着国际油价重归平衡，油服行业业绩下滑或已触底。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　实际上，国际油价自去年</span>11<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">30</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">日以来涨幅已经超过</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">15%</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">，这在很大程度上得益于产油国正式落实减产协议。</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">2017</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年初以来，多个</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">OPEC</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">产油国已经遵守甚至超额完成了减产目标。</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">2016</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">12</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">13</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">日，沙特石油产量降至近两年低点，不到</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">1000</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">万桶</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">/</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">日，科威特和阿尔及利亚石油部长均表示这两个国家也已超额完成了减产目标。英国咨询机构</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">OilMovements</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">在</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">1</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">12</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">日表示，截至</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">1</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">28</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">日的四周内，未计入安哥拉和厄瓜多尔的石油输出国组织</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">(OPEC)</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">日均海运石油出口量较</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">12</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">31</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">日止的四周内减少</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">11</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">万桶，为</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">2414</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">万桶。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　浙商证券分析指出，石油供需已重新进入供需紧平衡阶段，未来油价将缓慢震荡上行，其中</span>2017<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年将在</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">50-70</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">美元间振荡，下半年油价区间将为</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">60-80</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">美元。根据麦肯锡公司的预测，未来原油市场尽管仍存在较大不确定性，但预计在未来几年，油气市场有望达到一种“新常态”，油价回升至</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">65-75</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">美元</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">/</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">桶。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　裘孝锋认为，原油供需将在今年上半年达到平衡，油价也会逐步稳定在</span>50-60<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">美元，甚至可能达到</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">65</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">美元</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">/</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">桶。他预计，到了今年下半年，随着油价回暖，全球主要油公司将会增加资本支出的力度，那么油服公司业绩也将向好。国内油田服务公司的业绩与油公司资本支出密切相连。据广发证券的数据分析，中海油的资本支出走出新一轮的上升周期，今年资本支出总额为人民币</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">600-700</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">亿元，其中，勘探、开发和生产资本化支出分别占比约</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">18%</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">、</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">66%</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">和</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">15%</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">，海油工程、中海油服将是其中的核心受益者。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　油价上升将带来油田服务业回暖，拥有较强的技术实力、稳定的现金流和健康的财务状况的公司将迎来机遇。董秀成认为，目前的寒冬虽然是油田服务公司的困境，但油田服务公司可以趁这个机会调整自身结构、降低成本，只有在困境中加强创新抓住机遇的油田服务企业才能顺利突围。</span></span></p><p><br/></p>','国际油价回暖 油服业有望触底反弹','　　1月以来，国内外油田服务公司陆续发布2016年业绩快报，行业大额亏损引发业界关注。油田服务业真的不行了?同是亏损，谁在疲于应付，谁能蓄力反击?2017年会成为回暖之年吗?','1','1','2017-02-08 09:16:00','','0','','','0','{\"thumb\":\"\"}','2','0','0','0','','');INSERT INTO ts_posts ( `id`, `post_author`, `post_keywords`, `post_source`, `post_date`, `post_content`, `post_title`, `post_excerpt`, `post_status`, `comment_status`, `post_modified`, `post_content_filtered`, `post_parent`, `post_type`, `post_mime_type`, `comment_count`, `smeta`, `post_hits`, `post_like`, `istop`, `recommended`, `page_tpl`, `page_tpls` ) VALUES  ('403','1','国际油价陷拉锯战 ','','2017-03-13 09:25:39','<p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　《经济参考报》记者从多家社会监测机构了解到，近期国际油价整体小幅震荡，陷入</span>“拉锯战”。<span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">2</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">14</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">日（周二）我国将迎来今年春节后首个成品油调价窗口，预计将遭遇搁浅，这也是</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">2017</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年首次出现这一局面。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　自</span>1<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">25</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">日国内油价年内首降之后，国际石油市场多空双方势均力敌，价格小幅震荡。纽约原油期货价格基本稳定在每桶</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">52</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">美元到</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">53</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">美元附近，布伦特原油期货价格则在每桶</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">55</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">美元到</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">56</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">美元附近上下波动。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　受此影响，北京时间</span>2<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">10</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">日，本轮第</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">8</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">个工作日，中宇资讯测算原油变化率为</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">1.65%</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">，中宇原油估价</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">55.788</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">美元</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">/</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">桶，较基准价涨</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">0.905</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">美元</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">/</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">桶，亚洲原油估价</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">54.841</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">美元</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">/</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">桶，较基准价涨</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">0.632</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">美元</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">/</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">桶，而新华社石油价格系统</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">2</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">10</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">日发布的数据显示，最新的一揽子原油平均价格变化率为</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">1.29%</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">。隆众资讯监测的成品油价格变化率指数则为</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">1.69%</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">，对应的成品油价格涨幅约每吨</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">30</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">元。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　根据我国《石油价格管理办法》，国内汽、柴油价格根据国际市场原油价格变化每</span>10<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">个工作日调整一次。当调价幅度低于每吨</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">50</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">元时，不作调整，纳入下次调价时累加或冲抵。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　隆众资讯原油分析师李彦也认为，近期市场投资者持观望态度，等待欧佩克官方发布的数据以判断减产协议履行的力度。除非出现黑天鹅事件引起国际油价突然暴涨，否则按照目前的国际油价水平来看，本轮国内成品油调价对应的涨幅或难以满足调价门槛，因此，调价遭遇搁浅的概率较大。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　据了解，本轮调价周期是</span>2017<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年我国第三轮成品油调价周期。今年以来，我国成品油价格已经历了一涨一跌两次调整，但由于涨跌幅一致，故整体价格维持在去年年末水平。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　中宇资讯分析师孙晓飞判断，随着元宵节的结束，国内工程将陆续开工，柴油需求或将增加，柴油价格或有小幅反弹可能；汽油方面，伴随春运返程结束，需求量也将出现下滑。预计后期国内油价将呈现涨跌互现的走势。</span></span></p><p><br/></p>','国际油价陷拉锯战 国内油价调整或遇今年首次搁浅','　　《经济参考报》记者从多家社会监测机构了解到，近期国际油价整体小幅震荡，陷入“拉锯战”。2月14日（周二）我国将迎来今年春节后首个成品油调价窗口，预计将遭遇搁浅，这也是2017年首次出现这一局面。','1','1','2017-02-13 10:26:00','','0','','','0','{\"thumb\":\"\"}','0','0','0','0','','');INSERT INTO ts_posts ( `id`, `post_author`, `post_keywords`, `post_source`, `post_date`, `post_content`, `post_title`, `post_excerpt`, `post_status`, `comment_status`, `post_modified`, `post_content_filtered`, `post_parent`, `post_type`, `post_mime_type`, `comment_count`, `smeta`, `post_hits`, `post_like`, `istop`, `recommended`, `page_tpl`, `page_tpls` ) VALUES  ('404','1','开局良好 今年经济料维持平稳增长','','2017-03-13 09:27:17','<p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　根据国家统计局和海关总署近日发布的</span>1<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">PMI</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">指数以及进出口数据来看，今年经济开局呈良好态势，为全年经济平稳增长打下了良好基础。业内人士表示，我国经济结构正在逐步转变，今年经济运行或维持相对平稳的增长态势。货币政策方面可望保持稳健中性，财政政策则将更加积极助力稳增长。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\">　　</span><strong><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;font-size: 14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">经济或维持平稳态势</span></span></strong></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\">　　“近期中国经济出现企稳迹象。”中国银行国际金融研究所研究员王有鑫表示，<span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">2016</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年四季度</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">GDP</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">增长率为</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">6.8%</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">，近</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">11</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">个季度以来首次出现上涨，</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">PMI</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">指数连续</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">6</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">个月处于荣枯线之上，政府通过货币政策开始在去杠杆、防风险和稳增长中实现平衡。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　而对于</span>PMI<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">持续位于荣枯线以上较高水平，华泰证券首席宏观研究员李超认为，经济增长基础进一步巩固，中央经济工作会议“防控资产泡沫”等因素说明目前我国经济没有大幅下滑风险。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　方正证券首席经济学家任泽平认为，今年市场对宏观经济走势分歧较大，有看法认为随着地产、汽车行业景气回落，二三季度经济运行将遭遇压力。不过，二三季度经济虽可能二次探底，幅度却不会深。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　农银国际分析师姚少华认为，尽管今年中国经济前景仍面临挑战，但在供给侧改革逐见成效的背景下，经济将维持相对平稳的增长态势。基建投资维持强劲增速、工业部门适度改善以及消费增速保持平稳将是经济增长主要动力。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　从内需方面看，姚少华表示，制造业及基建投资有望保持稳定增长，但在严格执行房地产调控措施的情况下，整体固定资产投资料小幅放缓。受惠于居民稳定的收入及就业增长，消费将保持平稳增长。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　总体而言，李超认为，今年宏观经济的风险点主要在房地产产业链，但在需求侧托底及消费对经济贡献上升的对冲下，没有失速风险，</span>GDP<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">增速很难出现大幅下行；全年经济增速保</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">6.5%</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">问题不大，预计</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">GDP</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">全年增速可能会在</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">6.6%</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\">　　</span><strong><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;font-size: 14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">货币政策保持稳健中性</span></span></strong></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　就今年的政策要点来看，齐鲁资管首席经济学家李迅雷认为，在稳增长可把握的前提下深化改革，国企改革与金融监管体制改革是两大侧重点。近年来稳增长的代价是货币与投资的畸形增长，名义</span>GDP<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">与国债收益率的鸿沟即是货币超发的重要体现。</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">M2</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">持续高增长的代价之一就是全社会杠杆率的快速增长，要在控制总杠杆率的前提下，把降低企业杠杆率作为重中之重。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　对于货币政策和财政政策，李迅雷认为，今年货币政策趋稳健加中性，财政政策会更加积极。从经济增长的角度来说，增速高低影响企业盈利进而影响市场，经济减速背景下只有结构性机会。</span>“十三五”路径规划带来发展新机遇，新型消费、信息经济、智能制造成为三条产业主线。</span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　李超表示，今年工业领域继续去产能，货币政策稳健中性，防范金融风险，降杠杆、控泡沫仍为主旋律，在预算内财政政策矛盾加剧的情况下，准财政政策将继续发力拉动基建投资。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　兴业银行首席经济学家鲁政委表示，春节前夕，央行在推出临时流动性便利的同时，将</span>MLF<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">利率调高</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">10</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">个基点。这表明央行意在寻求流动性平稳与去杠杆之间的平衡。在通胀抬升和去杠杆的背景下，未来一个季度的货币政策或继续呈现稳健中性、边际收紧的主题。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　南京银行发布的研究报告指出，从近期央行操作来看，防风险是第一要务，市场资金面大概率处于</span>“松<span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">+</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">紧”的循环转换中。今年需实时关注特朗普经济政策的执行力度，及其对我国货币政策和国际市场的影响并据此及时调整操作策略。</span></span></p><p><br/></p>','开局良好 今年经济料维持平稳增长','　　根据国家统计局和海关总署近日发布的1月PMI指数以及进出口数据来看，今年经济开局呈良好态势，为全年经济平稳增长打下了良好基础。业内人士表示，我国经济结构正在逐步转变，今年经济运行或维持相对平稳的增长态势。货币政策方面可望保持稳健中性，财政政策则将更加积极助力稳增长。','1','1','2017-02-13 10:18:00','','0','','','0','{\"thumb\":\"\"}','2','0','0','0','','');INSERT INTO ts_posts ( `id`, `post_author`, `post_keywords`, `post_source`, `post_date`, `post_content`, `post_title`, `post_excerpt`, `post_status`, `comment_status`, `post_modified`, `post_content_filtered`, `post_parent`, `post_type`, `post_mime_type`, `comment_count`, `smeta`, `post_hits`, `post_like`, `istop`, `recommended`, `page_tpl`, `page_tpls` ) VALUES  ('405','1','重庆成立石油天然气交易中心','','2017-03-13 09:28:10','<p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　重庆石油天然气交易中心于日前挂牌成立。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　据国家发改委相关负责人介绍，近年来</span>,<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">我国经济体制改革特别是价格改革步伐明显加快，石油天然气价格市场化程度不断提高，成品油价格机制化调整成为常态，天然气</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">80%</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">以上的气源价格由市场主导形成。为进一步深化我国石油天然气价格改革，形成有国际影响力的价格基准，更好地融入国际能源合作，国家决定推动建设石油天然气交易中心。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　该负责人介绍，重庆石油天然气资源丰富，特别是页岩气开发全国领先，工业大用户集中，管网运输发达，金融市场较为成熟。这是石油天然气交易中心成立的主要原因。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　记者了解到，重庆石油天然气交易中心股东涵盖石油天然气行业上中下游</span>10<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">余家大型企业及创新能力强的金融企业。</span></span></p><p><br/></p>','重庆成立石油天然气交易中心','　　重庆石油天然气交易中心于日前挂牌成立。','1','1','2017-02-14 11:03:00','','0','','','0','{\"thumb\":\"\"}','2','0','0','0','','');INSERT INTO ts_posts ( `id`, `post_author`, `post_keywords`, `post_source`, `post_date`, `post_content`, `post_title`, `post_excerpt`, `post_status`, `comment_status`, `post_modified`, `post_content_filtered`, `post_parent`, `post_type`, `post_mime_type`, `comment_count`, `smeta`, `post_hits`, `post_like`, `istop`, `recommended`, `page_tpl`, `page_tpls` ) VALUES  ('406','1','首个国土规划纲要发布：能源领域成重点','','2017-03-13 09:28:45','<p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\">　　2<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">4</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">日，国务院对外印发《全国国土规划纲要</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">(2016</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">—</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">2030</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">)</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">》，《纲要》对国土空间开发、资源环境保护、国土综合整治和保障体系建设等作出总体部署与统筹安排，是我国首个全国性国土开发与保护的战略性、综合性、基础性规划。在能源领域，《纲要》着墨颇多，并明确提出要构建能源安全保障体系。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　具体来讲，要加强能源矿产勘查。按照深化东</span>(<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">中</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">)</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">部、发展西部、加快海域、开辟新区、拓展海外的思路，加强渤海湾、鄂尔多斯、四川、塔里木、东海等重点盆地油气勘查，获取规模储量；加大银额、羌塘等含油气盆地及中上扬子地区勘查力度，实现油气资源战略接替。以优质动力煤和炼焦煤为重点，加快神东、陕北、晋北等国家大型煤炭基地资源勘查进程。加强铀矿资源调查和潜力评价，加快探明一批新的矿产地。实施油页岩和油砂资源调查与潜力评价，积极推进页岩气、煤层气、致密油</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">(</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">气</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">)</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">等非常规油气资源勘查，在海域和陆域具备成藏条件的地区，探索开展天然气水合物勘查开发。开展全国地热资源远景调查评价。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　要提高能源开发利用水平。推动能源生产和消费革命，优化能源结构，以开源、节流、减排为重点，确保能源安全供应。重点建设山西、鄂尔多斯盆地、内蒙古东部地区、西南地区、新疆五大重点综合能源基地和东部沿海核电带，构建</span>“五基一带”能源开发利用格局。加强深海油气资源开发，加快常规天然气增储上产，推进油页岩、页岩气、天然气水合物、油砂综合利用技术研发与推广。加强煤层气和煤炭资源综合开发，提高综合利用水平。切实提高煤炭加工转化水平，强化煤炭清洁高效利用。在保护生态前提下，有序稳妥开发水电，安全发展核电，高效发展风电，扩大利用太阳能，有序开发生物质能。实施新能源集成利用示范工程，因地制宜推进新型太阳能光伏和光热发电、生物质气化、生物燃料、海洋能等可再生能源发展，大幅提高非化石能源消费比例。</span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　要完善高效快捷的电力与煤炭输送骨干网络。强化智能电网与分布式能源系统的统筹建设，逐步降低煤炭消费比重特别是非电用煤比重。坚持输煤输电并举，逐步提高输电比重，扩大北煤南运和西电东送规模。结合大型能源基地布局，稳步建设西南能源基地向华东、华中地区和广东省输电通道，鄂尔多斯盆地、山西、锡林郭勒盟能源基地向华北、华中、华东地区输电通道。加快区域和省际超高压主网架建设，加快实施城乡配电网建设和改造工程，提高综合供电能力和可靠性。优化煤炭跨区流向，重点建设内蒙古西部地区至华中地区的北煤南运战略通道；建设山西、陕西和内蒙古西部地区至唐山地区港口、山西中南部至山东沿海港口等西煤东运新通道；结合兰新铁路扩能改造和兰渝铁路建设，完善疆煤外运通道。</span></span></p><p><br/></p>','首个国土规划纲要发布：能源领域成重点','　　2月4日，国务院对外印发《全国国土规划纲要(2016—2030年)》，《纲要》对国土空间开发、资源环境保护、国土综合整治和保障体系建设等作出总体部署与统筹安排，是我国首个全国性国土开发与保护的战略性、综合性、基础性规划。在能源领域，《纲要》着墨颇多，并明确提出要构建能源安全保障体系。','1','1','2017-02-14 10:28:00','','0','','','0','{\"thumb\":\"\"}','1','0','0','0','','');INSERT INTO ts_posts ( `id`, `post_author`, `post_keywords`, `post_source`, `post_date`, `post_content`, `post_title`, `post_excerpt`, `post_status`, `comment_status`, `post_modified`, `post_content_filtered`, `post_parent`, `post_type`, `post_mime_type`, `comment_count`, `smeta`, `post_hits`, `post_like`, `istop`, `recommended`, `page_tpl`, `page_tpls` ) VALUES  ('407','1','国际油价13日下跌','','2017-03-13 09:29:26','<p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　国际油价</span>13<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">日下跌。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　美国油田技术服务公司贝克休斯</span>10<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">日发布的数据显示，美国上周运营的油田钻井数量达</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">591</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">个，比前一周增加</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">8</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">个。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　截至当天收盘，纽约商品交易所</span>3<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月交货的轻质原油期货价格下跌</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">0.93</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">美元，收于每桶</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">52.93</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">美元，跌幅为</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">1.73%</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">。</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">4</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月交货的伦敦布伦特原油期货价格下跌</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">1.11</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">美元，收于每桶</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">55.59</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">美元，跌幅为</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">1.96%</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">。</span></span></p><p><br/></p>','国际油价13日下跌 收于每桶52.93美元','　　国际油价13日下跌。','1','1','2017-02-14 10:24:00','','0','','','0','{\"thumb\":\"\"}','1','0','0','0','','');INSERT INTO ts_posts ( `id`, `post_author`, `post_keywords`, `post_source`, `post_date`, `post_content`, `post_title`, `post_excerpt`, `post_status`, `comment_status`, `post_modified`, `post_content_filtered`, `post_parent`, `post_type`, `post_mime_type`, `comment_count`, `smeta`, `post_hits`, `post_like`, `istop`, `recommended`, `page_tpl`, `page_tpls` ) VALUES  ('408','1','美国扩大出售战略储备原油','','2017-03-13 09:30:02','<p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　美国能源部近日表示将在</span>2<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月底再出售</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">1000</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">万桶战略储备原油，这是美国今年第二轮出售战略储备原油。出售原油数量虽不算太大，但时间节点较为敏感：前不久石油输出国组织</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">(</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">欧佩克</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">)</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">国家及包括俄罗斯在内的非欧佩克产油国达成减产稳价协议，国际油价重回每桶</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">50</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">美元以上，美国页岩油公司也大幅恢复生产。美国能源部此时扩大出售战略储备原油，恐将加重原油在国际市场上供大于求的局面，令国际油价再度承压，引起国际社会广泛关注。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　根据去年</span>12<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月签署的《</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">21</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">世纪治愈法案》，美国在未来</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">3</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年将售出</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">2500</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">万桶战略储备原油，所得收入将存入美国财政部，作为医疗研究的经费来支持美国国立卫生研究院的创新项目。今年</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">1</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月，荷兰皇家壳牌石油公司买入</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">620</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">万桶储备原油，美国炼油企业菲利普斯</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">66</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">公司买入</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">20</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">万桶，美国能源部原计划今年全年出售</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">1000</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">万桶，但新年刚过</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">1</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">个多月就决定扩大销售量，难免引起人们的揣测和担忧。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　按照美国能源部的说法，出售战略储备原油主要为了实现油储现代化，</span>“战略原油储备系统已经陈旧，出售石油可以允许能源部对其进行修缮”。但业内专家认为，美国能源部的如此举动显示出两个动向：</span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　首先，维持了半个世纪的美国战略原油储备增加趋势正在悄悄改变。自从</span>1973<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年阿拉伯产油国实施原油禁运之后，美国便开始从</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">1975</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年建立长效储备机制，将石油储存在路易斯安那州和得克萨斯州</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">60</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">处戒备森严的岩盐洞穴中，以防突发情况。目前美国原油战略储备约为</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">6.95</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">亿桶，可以满足美国国内大约</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">5</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">周的使用量，成为全球规模最大的官方紧急石油储备。而如今由于国际油价低迷以及美国石油和天然气生产能力上升，美国决策者认为战略原油储备计划已经没有那么重要了，无需花费巨资维持储备。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　其次，出售战略储备原油达到一箭双雕的目的。一方面可为设备维护换来必要的资金，从而保证整个系统能够维持更长年限；另一方面，</span>2015<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年至</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">2016</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年国际油价基本在低位徘徊，最近欧佩克国家和非欧佩克产油国达成减产协议，促使油价开始明显回升，此时美国再度出手扩大销售战略储备原油，可提高本国对国际油价的话语权。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　整体上，国际油价虽有抬头之势，但仍处于疲软阶段。美国扩大出售战略储备原油，很有可能在国际石油市场上掀起新的风波。</span></span></p><p><br/></p>','美国扩大出售战略储备原油','　　美国能源部近日表示将在2月底再出售1000万桶战略储备原油，这是美国今年第二轮出售战略储备原油。出售原油数量虽不算太大，但时间节点较为敏感：前不久石油输出国组织(欧佩克)国家及包括俄罗斯在内的非欧佩克产油国达成减产稳价协议，国际油价重回每桶50美元以上，美国页岩油公司也大幅恢复生产。','1','1','2017-02-14 10:22:00','','0','','','0','{\"thumb\":\"\"}','1','0','0','0','','');INSERT INTO ts_posts ( `id`, `post_author`, `post_keywords`, `post_source`, `post_date`, `post_content`, `post_title`, `post_excerpt`, `post_status`, `comment_status`, `post_modified`, `post_content_filtered`, `post_parent`, `post_type`, `post_mime_type`, `comment_count`, `smeta`, `post_hits`, `post_like`, `istop`, `recommended`, `page_tpl`, `page_tpls` ) VALUES  ('409','1','油价迎鸡年“第一涨”','','2017-03-13 09:30:39','<p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\">　　2<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">14</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">日</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">24</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">时，</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">2017</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年第三次成品油调价窗口开启！之前，多家机构预测，春节后首个成品油调价窗口将遭遇搁浅，这也是</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">2017</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年首次出现这一局面。但记者从国家发改委获悉，国际市场原油价格总体水平小幅上升，受此影响，国内成品油价格迎春节后“第一涨”。汽油、柴油每吨均将上调</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">50</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">元。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　简单回顾之前油价涨跌历程：</span> 2016<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">11</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">30</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">日、</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">12</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">14</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">日、</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">12</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">28</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">日以及</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">2017</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">1</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">12</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">日四个调价窗口均为上调，形成跨年“四连涨”，而在上个调价窗口，也就是</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">1</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">25</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">号油价调整终结了连涨趋势。而今天，</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">2017</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年第三次成品油调价窗口，国内油价再回上升通道。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　从全国平均来看，国内成品油的价格浮动具体情况如下：</span>90<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">号汽油每升上调</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">0.04</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">元，</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">92</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">号汽油每升上调</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">0.04</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">元，</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">95</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">号汽油每升上调</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">0.04</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">元，</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">0</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">号柴油每升上调</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">0.04</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">元。按一般家用汽车油箱</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">50L</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">容量估测，加满一箱</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">92</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">号汽油将多花约</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">2</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">块钱。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\">　　</span><strong><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;font-size: 14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">国际油价陷拉锯战</span> <span style=\"font-family:宋体\">多空交织终小幅上升</span></span></strong></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　国际原油市场多空因素交织，受欧佩克限产协议落实预期较高和原油需求增长影响，国际市场原油价格总体水平小幅上升，布伦特、</span>WTI<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">原油期货平均价格比上轮上涨</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">1.52%</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">。</span></span></p><p><br/></p>','油价迎鸡年“第一涨” 97号汽油逼近7元大关','　　2月14日24时，2017年第三次成品油调价窗口开启！之前，多家机构预测，春节后首个成品油调价窗口将遭遇搁浅，这也是2017年首次出现这一局面。但记者从国家发改委获悉，国际市场原油价格总体水平小幅上升，受此影响，国内成品油价格迎春节后“第一涨”。汽油、柴油每吨均将上调50元。','1','1','2017-02-14 10:15:00','','0','','','0','{\"thumb\":\"\"}','2','0','0','0','','');INSERT INTO ts_posts ( `id`, `post_author`, `post_keywords`, `post_source`, `post_date`, `post_content`, `post_title`, `post_excerpt`, `post_status`, `comment_status`, `post_modified`, `post_content_filtered`, `post_parent`, `post_type`, `post_mime_type`, `comment_count`, `smeta`, `post_hits`, `post_like`, `istop`, `recommended`, `page_tpl`, `page_tpls` ) VALUES  ('410','1','去年全球油气资源发现量创60年新低','','2017-03-13 09:31:29','<p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　知名数据编制和调研机构</span>IHS Markit<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">于</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">14</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">日最新公布的数据显示，</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">2016</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年全球油气资源发现量约为</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">82</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">亿桶油气当量，创下过去</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">60</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年以来的新低，主要是由于持续的油价下跌导致油气公司纷纷削减勘探支出，此外大型油气田也更加难以被发现。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　该机构数据还显示，去年全球范围仅有</span>174<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">个新油气资源被发现，较</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">2013</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年前的平均每年</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">400</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">至</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">500</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">个的数量大幅下滑。勘探成果的减速显示全球可能将更加依赖美国页岩油气等非常规资源，以满足未来几十年的能源需求。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　分析人士指出，由于从发现到投产的典型周期为五到七年，因此油气发现的减少预示着未来十年全球油气供应或趋向收紧，这一定程度可能推动油价走强。不过今年常规油气资源的勘探也出现回升迹象，一些公司也正在加快钻探活动，这也得益于去年下半年油价开始企稳回升，油气公司的经营情况也度过了此前最为艰难的时刻。</span></span></p><p><br/></p>','去年全球油气资源发现量创60年新低','　　知名数据编制和调研机构IHS Markit于14日最新公布的数据显示，2016年全球油气资源发现量约为82亿桶油气当量，创下过去60年以来的新低，主要是由于持续的油价下跌导致油气公司纷纷削减勘探支出，此外大型油气田也更加难以被发现。','1','1','2017-02-16 10:11:00','','0','','','0','{\"thumb\":\"\"}','0','0','0','0','','');INSERT INTO ts_posts ( `id`, `post_author`, `post_keywords`, `post_source`, `post_date`, `post_content`, `post_title`, `post_excerpt`, `post_status`, `comment_status`, `post_modified`, `post_content_filtered`, `post_parent`, `post_type`, `post_mime_type`, `comment_count`, `smeta`, `post_hits`, `post_like`, `istop`, `recommended`, `page_tpl`, `page_tpls` ) VALUES  ('411','1','中巴石油贸易开启“多赢时代”','','2017-03-13 09:32:17','<p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　去年底，一系列</span>“贷款换原油”的协议在巴西里约热内卢诞生。巴西石油公司与中国国家开发银行以及中石油、中化工和振华石油三家油企签署了一系列有关贷款、贸易等双边及多方协议。根据协议，国开行给予巴油<span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">50</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">亿美元贷款，三家中国油企共计获得每日</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">10</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">万桶、每年约</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">500</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">万吨的十年期巴西原油供应合同。这是</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">2009</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年在巴西首次合作后，我国石油企业与金融机构强强联手打出的又一漂亮战役。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　记者了解到，</span>2007<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年以来巴西在东南部水域发现了盐下层石油，据估计石油储量可能高达</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">700</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">亿桶，被认为是新千年以来世界上最大的石油资源。至此，巴西一举摘掉了贫油国的帽子，成为名至实归的原油生产大国。目前，我国已经成为巴西开发盐下层石油的重要合作伙伴，四大石油公司均已进入巴西发展。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　发现市场后，如何快速打开市场就显得迫在眉睫。与石油公司单打独斗开拓市场不同，金融机构介入后，形成石油公司、金融机构、外方</span>“三足鼎立”局势，互为支撑又互有制约，更有助于企业海外市场的开拓。</span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">记者了解到，在本次协议中，国开行向巴油提供长期稳定贷款，有了资金支持，巴油能不断增加原油产量。原油产出后，巴油又需要市场进行原油销售，而中石油等中资企业背后站着天然的大市场中国。对巴油来说，有了运转资金用于生产，也有了市场保证销售渠道。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　对国开行来说，贷款放给巴油后，后期由中资石油企业负责还款，还贷方面有保障，该贷款又协助中资石油公司获取了稳定的资源，促进了中巴两国能源贸易合作。而对中资的石油公司来说，在中国金融机构的支持下获取稳定的巴西原油资源，对促进我国原油进口来源多样化，分散能源进口风险有着重要的意义。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\">　　“这种合作模式下，三家相互支持，各取所需，最终形成三赢局面。”中石油国际事业巴西公司总经理朱文晋说。</span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　记者了解到，石油公司和金融机构合作在全球范围内看不是新鲜事物，中资石油公司在开拓委内瑞拉、厄瓜多尔、俄罗斯等市场时也都尝试过这种合作模式。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　而这一系列协议体现了我国石油公司在海外布局正悄然发生变化。记者了解到，目前我国的石油公司走出国门发展业务，主要为上游业务的投资经营，而对整个石油产业链的中下游涉及不多。而壳牌、</span>BP<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">、道达尔等国际老牌石油公司在全产业链延伸和全球布局方面走在了前面。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\">　　“我们也意识到了这一点，近些年在着力调整。”朱文晋说，“中石油探索海外市场做的比较早，上游业务发展比较成熟，贸易业务也形成了较大规模，下一步，我们要加强海外中下游业务的拓展，争取在分销、零售领域实现突破，提升中石油在全球范围内优化资源和进行石油产品供应的能力，打出中石油品牌。”</span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　其实，</span>“卖油”到巴西，中资油企已经迈出了第一步。<span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">2015</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年，中石油首次进入巴西市场开展成品油销售业务。</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">2016</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年，巴西的成品油销售市场逐步被打开，中石油售出</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">20</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">船货，共计</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">70</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">万吨，其中一部分来自中石油国内炼厂。“国内石油企业销售成品油到巴西市场，尚属首次。”朱文晋说。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　记者了解到，尽管新油田的发现使巴西变成了原油生产和出口大国，但是由于其炼化能力不足，成品油长期依赖进口，又是名副其实的成品油进口大国。</span>“此前巴西进口成品油基本来自美国，进口来源较为单一，而吸纳中国成品油进入市场，也可以给巴西的成品油进口提供多样性。”朱文晋分析，“实际上我们是在跟美国石油企业争抢巴西市场。”</span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　记者了解到，目前国内石油炼化领域存在着较为严重的炼能过剩，不仅是几大石油公司，许多地方炼厂也非常需要出口渠道。而现阶段我国的成品油出口主要是销往亚太区。把成品油销往拉美，对优化亚太区过剩资源和提高炼厂毛利有一定意义。</span>“下一步，我们还要进一步增强在拉美的成品油销售能力，逐渐实现对拉美市场的全覆盖并在重点国家进入分销零售领域，希望能尽快在拉美大地上见到中石油加油站。”朱文晋说。</span></p><p><br/></p>','中巴石油贸易开启“多赢时代”','　　去年底，一系列“贷款换原油”的协议在巴西里约热内卢诞生。巴西石油公司与中国国家开发银行以及中石油、中化工和振华石油三家油企签署了一系列有关贷款、贸易等双边及多方协议。根据协议，国开行给予巴油50亿美元贷款，三家中国油企共计获得每日10万桶、每年约500万吨的十年期巴西原油供应合同。','1','1','2017-02-16 10:09:00','','0','','','0','{\"thumb\":\"\"}','1','0','0','0','','');INSERT INTO ts_posts ( `id`, `post_author`, `post_keywords`, `post_source`, `post_date`, `post_content`, `post_title`, `post_excerpt`, `post_status`, `comment_status`, `post_modified`, `post_content_filtered`, `post_parent`, `post_type`, `post_mime_type`, `comment_count`, `smeta`, `post_hits`, `post_like`, `istop`, `recommended`, `page_tpl`, `page_tpls` ) VALUES  ('412','1','亚洲最大原油码头首靠全球最大船','','2017-03-13 09:32:47','<p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　今天，亚洲最大原油码头</span>——宁波舟山港大榭港区实华二期<span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">45</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">万吨原油码头首次挂靠全球最大船“泰欧”轮，该轮此次装载</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">33.96</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">万吨原油，创下挂靠宁波舟山港单艘油轮实际装载量最大纪录。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　大榭港区实华二期</span>45<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">万吨原油码头于</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">2010</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">12</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月建成，</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">2012</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">5</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">16</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">号正式投产，为亚洲最大、中国首个正式投用的</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">45</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">万吨原油码头。</span></span></p><p><br/></p>','亚洲最大原油码头首靠全球最大船','　　今天，亚洲最大原油码头——宁波舟山港大榭港区实华二期45万吨原油码头首次挂靠全球最大船“泰欧”轮，该轮此次装载33.96万吨原油，创下挂靠宁波舟山港单艘油轮实际装载量最大纪录。','1','1','2017-02-16 10:07:00','','0','','','0','{\"thumb\":\"\"}','1','0','0','0','','');INSERT INTO ts_posts ( `id`, `post_author`, `post_keywords`, `post_source`, `post_date`, `post_content`, `post_title`, `post_excerpt`, `post_status`, `comment_status`, `post_modified`, `post_content_filtered`, `post_parent`, `post_type`, `post_mime_type`, `comment_count`, `smeta`, `post_hits`, `post_like`, `istop`, `recommended`, `page_tpl`, `page_tpls` ) VALUES  ('413','1','国际油价15日下跌 ','','2017-03-13 09:33:22','<p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　美国能源信息局当天公布的数据显示，上周美国全国商业原油库存增加</span>950<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">万桶，达到</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">5.181</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">亿桶，油价承压下行。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　截至当天收盘，纽约商品交易所</span>3<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月交货的轻质原油期货价格下跌</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">0.09</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">美元，收于每桶</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">53.11</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">美元，跌幅为</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">0.17%</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">。</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">4</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月交货的伦敦布伦特原油期货价格下跌</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">0.22</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">美元，收于每桶</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">55.75</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">美元，跌幅为</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">0.39%</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">。</span></span></p><p><br/></p>','国际油价15日下跌 收于每桶53.11美元','　　美国能源信息局当天公布的数据显示，上周美国全国商业原油库存增加950万桶，达到5.181亿桶，油价承压下行。','1','1','2017-02-16 10:04:00','','0','','','0','{\"thumb\":\"\"}','1','0','0','0','','');INSERT INTO ts_posts ( `id`, `post_author`, `post_keywords`, `post_source`, `post_date`, `post_content`, `post_title`, `post_excerpt`, `post_status`, `comment_status`, `post_modified`, `post_content_filtered`, `post_parent`, `post_type`, `post_mime_type`, `comment_count`, `smeta`, `post_hits`, `post_like`, `istop`, `recommended`, `page_tpl`, `page_tpls` ) VALUES  ('414','1','福建气价上涨 专家称与国际价格同步','','2017-03-13 09:34:30','<p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\">　</span><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\">&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><strong><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;font-size: 14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">福建天然气价格上涨清洁取暖助推气价市场化</span></span></strong></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　目前福建是国内很少的没有长输天然气管道的省份，因此中海油进口</span>LNG<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">在福建有很大的市场，“因此目前福建天然气市场价格很其他省份都不同，其天然气价格与国际</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">LNG</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">价格同步”，一位石油央企总部专家介绍。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\">　　“因为印尼进口<span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">LNG</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">价格上涨，因此福建居民天然气价格也同样上涨了，”</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">2</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">14</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">日安迅思资深天然气行业分析师陈芸颖表示，“其</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">IC</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">卡用户自</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">2</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">1</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">日起执行，抄表用户自</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">3</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月抄见气量起执行。”</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　据她介绍，今年因为国际油价上涨，因此中海油进口的印尼</span>LNG<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">价格也大幅上涨，从</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">1.752</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">元</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">/</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">立方米上涨至</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">2.141</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">元</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">/</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">立方米，涨幅为</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">0.389</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">元</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">/</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">立方米，而且其天然气居民价格开始进行阶梯计价。其第一阶梯</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">(</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">基础阶梯</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">)</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">销售价为</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">3.272</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">元</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">/</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">立方米，用气量为</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">240(</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">含</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">)</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">立方米</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">/</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">户·年；第二阶梯销售价为</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">3.926</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">元</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">/</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">立方米，用气量为</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">240</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">至</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">360(</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">含</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">)</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">立方米</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">/</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">户·年；第三阶梯气价为</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">4.908</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">元</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">/</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">立方米，用气量为</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">360</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">立方米以上</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">/</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">户·年。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　之所以福建天然气价格体系与其他地方不同，是因为目前福建天然气是中海油进口</span>LNG<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">为主，而其价格是与国际油价联系，与国际</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">LNG</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">价格同步，因此“当</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">2014</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">-2016</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年国际油价暴跌时，其价格也很低，甚至比北京、上海、广东还低，而随着</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">2016</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年下半年国际油价上涨后，其价格也逐步上涨，这也是天然气价格改革的方向”，有石油央企总部专家坦言。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　据了解，随着国内雾霾治理的加速，国内天然气价格改革不断深入。</span>14<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">日国家能源局局长努尔·白克力表示，</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">5</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年内有条件地区要基本实现清洁取暖，要尽快制定出台冬季清洁取暖支持政策，搞好顶层规划设计。能源行业研究人士据此判断，发展清洁取暖将是未来</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">5</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年我国能源领域的一项工作重点。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　而湖北、河北等地发改委也宣布，将进一步完善天然气价格形成机制，科学合理制定天然气价格。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\">　</span><strong><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;font-size: 14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　福建：新的价格联动方式</span></span></strong></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　目前福建是国内很少的没有长输天然气管道的省份，因此中海油进口</span>LNG<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">在福建有很大的市场，“因此目前福建天然气市场价格跟其他省份都不同，其天然气价格与国际</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">LNG</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">价格同步”，前述石油央企总部专家介绍。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　据</span>2017<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年《福建省物价局关于中海福建天然气有限责任公司印尼合同气量门站销售价格等有关问题的通知》</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">(</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">简称通知</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">)</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">介绍，按每</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">3</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">个月为一个联动调整周期，在周期内加权平均购气成本变动幅度达到或超过</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">8%</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">时，门站销售价格按购气成本变动幅度进行相应调整；当周期内加权平均购气成本变动幅度未达到</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">8%</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">时，门站销售价格不作调整，其购气成本变动幅度滚动纳入下一周期一并计算。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　当购气成本变动幅度达到或超过</span>10%<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">且时间达到或超过</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">3</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">个月，或购气成本变动幅度达到或超过</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">15%</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">且时间达到或超过</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">2</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">个月时，按购气成本变动情况相应调整销售价格。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\">　　“联动方式完善的主要原因是在<span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">2016</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年的实践过程中，联动调整周期的不确定性及成本变动幅度较大给上游测算成本造成了一定困难。新的联动方式有了明确的调整周期和相对较小的成本变动幅度将有利于价格联动的执行，”前述石油央企总部专家坦言，“这是目前与国家天然气价格不同的地方，它进一步市场化了。”</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　此次通知称，中海福建天然气有限责任公司的气化管输费按照补偿合理成本、依法计入税金和合理回报的原则每年进行联动调整。</span>2017<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年度气化管输费按</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">0.349</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">元</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">/</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">方</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">(</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">不含税</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">)</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">执行。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　陈芸颖表示，气化管输费已包含在印尼气源销售价格，这一方式也是贯彻了</span>2016<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年出台的《天然气管道运输价格管理办法</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">(</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">试行</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">)</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">》的第二十四条，“省级价格主管部门可以参照本办法对本省</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">(</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">自治区、直辖市</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">)</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">内短途管道运输价格进行管理，或参照本办法，结合本省</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">(</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">自治区、直辖市</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">)</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">实际情况，制定本省</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">(</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">自治区、直辖市</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">)</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">短途管道运输价格管理办法。”</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　与过去不明晰的定价方式相比，根据企业实际投入每年测定的气化管输费更为透明，在一定程度上有利于未来向第三方的公平开放使用。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\">　　</span><strong><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;font-size: 14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">进一步市场化</span></span></strong></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　天然气市场化是中央政府的目标，因此此次福建的变化是应该提倡的。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\">　　14<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">日国家能源局局长努尔·白克力强调，因地制宜加快提高清洁能源供暖比重，</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">5</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年内有条件地区要基本实现清洁取暖，要尽快制定出台冬季清洁取暖支持政策，搞好顶层规划设计。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\">　　“因为治理雾霾等原因，天然气市场化获得中央政府的推动，去年底出台中央《天然气管道运输价格管理办法<span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">(</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">试行</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">)</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">》；而目前各省也开始推动天然气的市场化”，那位石油央企总部专家说。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　在湖北物价局网站中称，未来天然气门站价格居民、非居民逐步并轨；完善天然气管道运输价格形成机制，为管道向第三方开放创造条件。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　这意味着天然气市场改革按照</span>“管住中间、放开两头”进一步深化推进。可以预见各省将会陆续推出。</span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　而在福建，随着上游销售价格上调的确定，下游各地方城市燃气公司开始陆续对当地的天然气销售价格进行调整。以厦门为例，管道天然气非居民用气最高销售价格从现行的</span>3.13<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">元</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">/</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">立方米上调为</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">3.51</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">元</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">/</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">立方米</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">(</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">车用气除外</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">)</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　陈芸颖表示，值得关注的是，随着印尼气源合同气量销售价格的上调，此前中石油进入福建的价格难题也得到了一定程度的缓解，或有利于西三线气源进入福建。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　根据《福建省</span>“十三五”能源发展专项规划》，到<span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">2020</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年全省天然气消费量占一次能源消费的比重提高到</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">10%</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">。从绝对数量上来看，规划规定的最低目标，是到</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">2020</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年实现年消费天然气</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">65.06</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">亿立方米。</span></span></p><p><br/></p>','福建气价上涨 专家称与国际价格同步','　  福建天然气价格上涨清洁取暖助推气价市场化','1','1','2017-02-16 10:00:00','','0','','','0','{\"thumb\":\"\"}','2','0','0','0','','');INSERT INTO ts_posts ( `id`, `post_author`, `post_keywords`, `post_source`, `post_date`, `post_content`, `post_title`, `post_excerpt`, `post_status`, `comment_status`, `post_modified`, `post_content_filtered`, `post_parent`, `post_type`, `post_mime_type`, `comment_count`, `smeta`, `post_hits`, `post_like`, `istop`, `recommended`, `page_tpl`, `page_tpls` ) VALUES  ('415','1','伊朗发现20亿桶页岩油储量','','2017-03-13 09:35:00','<p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　伊朗国家石油公司</span>18<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">日证实</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">,</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">在伊朗西部洛雷斯坦省发现的页岩油储量大约为</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">20</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">亿桶。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　伊朗半官方的塔斯尼姆通讯社援引伊朗国家石油公司勘探部门高管巴赫曼</span>·苏莱马尼的话报道<span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">:</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">“通过研究</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">,</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">预计洛雷斯坦省内页岩油的储量为</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">20</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">亿桶……这些原油是轻质的。”</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　苏莱马尼说</span>,<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">他们还在调查这一地区是否还储藏着页岩气</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">,</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">研究工作将于</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">10</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月完成。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　按路透社的说法</span>,<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">伊朗已探明石油储量为</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">1600</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">亿桶</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">,</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">接近全球储量的</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">10%,</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">排名世界第四。</span></span></p><p><br/></p>','伊朗发现20亿桶页岩油储量','　　伊朗国家石油公司18日证实,在伊朗西部洛雷斯坦省发现的页岩油储量大约为20亿桶。','1','1','2017-02-20 09:23:00','','0','','','0','{\"thumb\":\"\"}','1','0','0','0','','');INSERT INTO ts_posts ( `id`, `post_author`, `post_keywords`, `post_source`, `post_date`, `post_content`, `post_title`, `post_excerpt`, `post_status`, `comment_status`, `post_modified`, `post_content_filtered`, `post_parent`, `post_type`, `post_mime_type`, `comment_count`, `smeta`, `post_hits`, `post_like`, `istop`, `recommended`, `page_tpl`, `page_tpls` ) VALUES  ('416','1','欧佩克酝酿延长减产协议','','2017-03-13 09:35:54','<p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　据外媒报道，石油输出国组织</span>(<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">欧佩克</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">)</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">正酝酿延长减产协议或加大减产力度，以保证油价上涨至满意价位。然而伊朗等成员国正考虑加大产能，对欧佩克的计划和油价上幅形成不确定因素。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　路透社日前援引欧佩克组织内部消息人士表态称，如果全球原油库存未能降至目标水平，该组织可能从</span>7<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月开始延长同非欧佩克产油国之间的减产协议，甚至可能加大减产力度。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　去年底，欧佩克和俄罗斯等</span>11<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">个非欧佩克产油国先后在奥地利首都维也纳达成原油减产协议。按照协议，从</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">2017</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">1</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月起的六个月内，欧佩克日均减产</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">120</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">万桶，</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">11</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">个非欧佩克产油国日均减产</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">55.8</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">万桶。减产救市措施令已经跌至低谷的国际油价“起死回生”。阿尔及利亚能源部长布塔法说，欧佩克成员国及其他产油国将在</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">2</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月达到日减产</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">180</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">万桶的目标。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　消息人士认为，要让全球石油库存下降约</span>3<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">亿桶至五年平均水平，产油国必须百分之百遵守减产协定，同时原油需求必须保持良性增长。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\">　　“如果所有人都完全遵守承诺，库存将会下降，到今年中期一定时候可能回到五年平均水准附近。但只有百分之百履行协议时才会这样。”一位消息人士说，“问题在于，他们会削减多少？对此只能等着看。”</span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　欧佩克下次开会决定供应政策的时间为</span>5<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">25</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">日，非欧佩克成员国也可能受邀参加。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　根据国际能源署的估算，欧佩克在减产协议生效首月</span>1<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月减产已达协议的</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">90%</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">，是欧佩克历次减产行动中力度较大的一次。</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">1</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月欧佩克成员国原油日产量降至</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">3210</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">万桶，其中沙特阿拉伯等国家的减产幅度甚至超过了减产协议要求。非欧佩克产油国中，初步数据显示俄罗斯</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">1</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月日均减产</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">10</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">万桶。俄罗斯此前承诺，将逐步实现日均减产</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">30</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">万桶的目标。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　国际能源署报告认为，全球原油需求增长将比此前预计的更加强劲，</span>2016<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年全球原油日需求比前一年增长</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">160</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">万桶，</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">2017</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年全球原油日需求将在此基础上进一步增长</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">140</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">万桶。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\">　　2016<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年初国际油价跌破每桶</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">30</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">美元，创</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">12</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年来低点。此后近一年，受市场供过于求的担忧情绪影响，油价一直在低位徘徊，直至去年末全球产油国达成减产协议，油价才开始大幅反弹。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　然而油市企稳、油价涨幅受到成员国内部的不确定性影响，以伊朗为代表的成员国正酝酿逐步增产，未来可能影响欧佩克减产政策的效力。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　据伊朗媒体</span>18<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">日报道，伊朗国家石油公司总经理阿里·考尔东日前表示，伊朗原油日产量在今年</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">4</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月中旬以前将达到</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">400</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">万桶，未来五年计划新上马</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">500</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">口油井，以将原油日产量提升至</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">470</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">万桶的水平。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　考尔东对伊朗学生通讯社表示，伊朗原本打算在伊朗新年结束前</span>(2017<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">3</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">20</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">日以前</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">)</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">实现原油日产量</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">400</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">万桶的目标，但要真正实现这一目标需要往后推迟一个月。他还表示，伊朗在过去某段时期内的原油日产量曾经达到过</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">420</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">万桶的水平，但后来出现下降。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　另据伊朗石油部下属的沙纳通讯社援引考尔东的话称，伊朗将在今年</span>3<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月开始执行的下一个五年计划的目标是新上马</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">500</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">口油井，这是要实现原油日产量</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">470</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">万桶的目标需要采取的措施。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　根据在去年底召开的欧佩克石油会议上签署的减产协议，伊朗被要求只能在去年</span>10<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月产量的水平上稍微增加。伊朗《财经论坛报》称，欧佩克组织近期发布的月度数据显示，伊朗今年</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">1</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月的原油日产量为</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">375</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">万桶，由于统计标准不同，这一数据比伊朗石油部公布的</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">390</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">万桶少了</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">15</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">万桶，这意味着伊朗没有超出减产协议的产量限制要求。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　另外，该国新探原油储量也为增产铺平道路。伊朗塔斯尼姆通讯社</span>18<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">日援引伊朗国家石油公司高管的讲话称，该国西部罗瑞斯坦省发现</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">20</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">亿桶轻质原油的页岩油储量。该公司探勘部副部长索雷马尼表示，对该地区页岩气储量正在进行探勘工作，今年</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">10</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月预计将完成研究。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　不过，为了支撑油价，包括沙特能源部长法利赫在内的</span>13<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">个欧佩克成员国官员已表示，石油库存有必要下降至接近五年平均值的水平，欧佩克才会认定油市已转为供需均衡。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　国际能源署最近称，去年</span>12<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月底，全球石油库存降至</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">30</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">亿桶下方，但仍比五年平均水平高</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">2.86</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">亿桶。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\">&nbsp;</span></p><p><br/></p>','欧佩克酝酿延长减产协议','　　据外媒报道，石油输出国组织(欧佩克)正酝酿延长减产协议或加大减产力度，以保证油价上涨至满意价位。然而伊朗等成员国正考虑加大产能，对欧佩克的计划和油价上幅形成不确定因素。','1','1','2017-02-20 09:18:00','','0','','','0','{\"thumb\":\"\"}','1','0','0','0','','');INSERT INTO ts_posts ( `id`, `post_author`, `post_keywords`, `post_source`, `post_date`, `post_content`, `post_title`, `post_excerpt`, `post_status`, `comment_status`, `post_modified`, `post_content_filtered`, `post_parent`, `post_type`, `post_mime_type`, `comment_count`, `smeta`, `post_hits`, `post_like`, `istop`, `recommended`, `page_tpl`, `page_tpls` ) VALUES  ('417','1','我国南方尝试以天然气分户式供暖温暖过冬','','2017-03-13 09:36:57','<p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\">　 “南方湿冷，一到冬天，身上裹得厚，空调、电暖炉、电热毯还要齐上阵。有了地暖，穿个短袖就能在家里自在活动，舒服多了。”家住浙江省杭州市江干区的杜女士今年冬天用上了分户式供暖设备，正在度过她的第一个“暖冬”。</span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　从今年</span>3<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月开始，杭州燃气集团将正式推出天然气家庭分户式供暖，分为地暖和墙暖两种，用户可以根据自己实际情况自由设置供暖时长、温度，用热可单独计量。“分户供暖就是每户有一个独立的供暖系统，根据设备和热源的不同，实现不同的独立供暖。”杭州燃气用具经营有限公司总经理顾利加说。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　近年来，寒冷冰冻天气多次席卷南方，南方是否需要集中供暖的话题成为持续热议的焦点。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　我国供暖区域过去以</span>“秦岭—淮河”为界，该界限以北省市为采暖区，以南则为非强制供暖区域，然而包括上海、杭州、武汉等城市在内的南方城市“夏热冬冷”，冬季室温常低于<span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">10</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">摄氏度，也低于不少北方采暖区</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">16</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">度的室温标准。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　随着经济生活水平的提高，南方供暖需求日益强烈。在不少南方城市，以天然气为能源的家庭分户式供暖成为应对严寒冬天的主要选择之一。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\">　　2016<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年，湖北省武汉市天然气公司申请申报独立采暖用户的数量已超过</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">11.5</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">万户，湖南长沙使用地暖、墙暖等分户式采暖用户已超过</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">10</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">万户，冬季高峰期日均超过</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">200</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">万方天然气的采暖负荷，杭州地暖用户总量也达到</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">3</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">万户。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　据顾利加介绍，杭州市绝大多数开通管道燃气的住宅，没有预留冬季采暖所需的地热容量，不少家庭都倾向于安装更为简单的壁挂式天然气暖气片。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　业内人士认为，中国南方地区气候条件、建筑保温设施、居民居住习惯与北方存在差异，不宜照搬北方集中供暖的模式，采取家庭分户式供暖更适宜南方的气候条件、建筑保温设施和居民居住习惯。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　然而记者了解到，相较于空调、电暖炉等广为使用的取暖设施，天然气分户式供暖设备上万元人民币的设计安装费用，以及天然气较为高昂的价格令不少人</span>“望而却步”。</span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　以实行天然气阶梯价格的杭州为例，使用燃气地暖之后，气价将达到</span>4.65<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">元人民币／立方米，这一价格是天然气阶梯价格中的最高档。业内估算，一套</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">100</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">平方米的房子，如果全部使用地暖，每月燃气费会在</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">3000</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">元人民币左右，若使用墙暖，注意节能，花费也将会在</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">2000</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">元人民币左右。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　研究人员认为，以燃煤为主要能源进行供暖已对大气环境造成一定污染，天然气家庭分户式供暖更为便捷和绿色，清洁能源应成为未来能源应用发展方向。</span></span></p><p><br/></p>','我国南方尝试以天然气分户式供暖温暖过冬','　“南方湿冷，一到冬天，身上裹得厚，空调、电暖炉、电热毯还要齐上阵。有了地暖，穿个短袖就能在家里自在活动，舒服多了。”家住浙江省杭州市江干区的杜女士今年冬天用上了分户式供暖设备，正在度过她的第一个“暖冬”。','1','1','2017-02-20 09:15:00','','0','','','0','{\"thumb\":\"\"}','1','0','0','0','','');INSERT INTO ts_posts ( `id`, `post_author`, `post_keywords`, `post_source`, `post_date`, `post_content`, `post_title`, `post_excerpt`, `post_status`, `comment_status`, `post_modified`, `post_content_filtered`, `post_parent`, `post_type`, `post_mime_type`, `comment_count`, `smeta`, `post_hits`, `post_like`, `istop`, `recommended`, `page_tpl`, `page_tpls` ) VALUES  ('418','1','煤制油示范项目将免征消费税','','2017-03-13 09:38:12','<p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　记者日前从宁夏回族自治区国资委获悉，经国家七部委研究，已同意给予煤制油示范项目消费税免征</span>5<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年的优惠政策。该项政策现已上报国务院审批。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　该政策大礼包在国内煤化工业界掀起震动，大家普遍认为，国内煤制油产业正深陷低油价、高煤价的漩涡之中，这一政策利好对于</span>“十三五”时期全国煤制油“正规军”的升级示范和整个现代煤化工产业的持续健康发展将发挥引领作用。</span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　此前，煤制油品要和普通炼油产品一样缴纳消费税。</span>“与按照从量计征消费税的石油炼化项目相比，煤制油项目投资大、固定成本高，产品售价却随原油价格波动。而现行消费税政策出台较早，未考虑对煤制油项目区别对待。”中科合成油公司技术顾问唐宏清接受中国化工报记者独家采访时表示，消费税事实上已成为影响煤制油项目顺利建成运营的关键因素。</span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　业内专家给记者算了一笔账，煤制油单位完全成本约</span>5200<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">元</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">/</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">吨。其中柴油消费税</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">1411</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">元</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">/</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">吨、石脑油</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">2105</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">元</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">/</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">吨，综合看营业税金及附加费约为</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">1746</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">元</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">/</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">吨，仅消费税一项就占成本近</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">30%</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">，大幅降低了煤制油项目的盈利能力。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　中讯化工信息研究院分析师崔军告诉记者，免征消费税对煤制油企业构成重大利好。以神华</span>400<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">万吨</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">/</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年煤制油项目为例，该项目年产合成油品</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">405.2</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">万吨，其中柴油</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">273.3</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">万吨、石脑油</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">98.3</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">万吨。按照国家</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">2015</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">1</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">31</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">日执行的汽、柴油消费税标准，以柴油消费税</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">1.2</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">元</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">/</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">升、石脑油消费税</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">1.52</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">元</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">/</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">升计算，神华宁煤项目每年可少缴消费税约</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">58.9</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">亿元。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　北京中能网讯咨询公司冉泽经理认为，探寻煤炭资源的清洁高值利用新途径迫在眉睫，而煤制油等现代煤化工就是一条出路。通过消费税免除大力支持煤制油</span>“正规军”做大做强，对于现代煤化工的升级示范意义重大。</span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　唐宏清介绍，目前我国煤制油示范项目主要以煤间接液化为主，目前共核准了</span>8<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">个项目，包括神华宁煤</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">400</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">万吨</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">/</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年项目、兖矿陕西榆林</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">100</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">万吨</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">/</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年项目、山西潞安</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">180</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">万吨</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">/</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年项目、内蒙古伊泰</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">200</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">万吨</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">/</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年项目，以及较早前建设的神华、伊泰、潞安三套</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">16</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">万吨</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">/</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年等</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">7</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">个煤间接液化示范项目。此外，还有</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">1</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">个神华</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">108</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">万吨</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">/</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年煤直接液化项目。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　另据记者了解，截至</span>2017<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">1</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月底，国内煤制油在建和获得“路条”的企业有</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">7</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">家，合计煤制油能力为</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">1170</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">万吨</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">/</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年，到</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">2020</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年总能力将达到</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">1826</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">万吨</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">/</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年。照此粗略计算，如果这些项目全部达产，年免征消费费将达</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">268</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">亿元。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　中国煤炭经济研究院院长岳福斌指出，随着煤制油消费税免除政策的出台，人们对煤制油的很多担心和质疑也有了答案。他希望煤制油产业坚持项目建设适度集中的原则，大力发展混合所有制经济，通过各方合力，加快把煤制油打造成为中国高技术产业的新名片，使煤制油产业成为中国的</span>“第四桶油”。</span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　据了解，</span>2016<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年全国两会期间，宁夏自治区政协牵头向国家有关部委提交了提案，建议对煤制油品行业制定专门的消费税，推进煤炭清洁高效利用。该重点提案所提建议经国家七部委研究，终于在今年全国两会前得到了圆满答复。</span></span></p><p><br/></p>','煤制油示范项目将免征消费税','　　记者日前从宁夏回族自治区国资委获悉，经国家七部委研究，已同意给予煤制油示范项目消费税免征5年的优惠政策。该项政策现已上报国务院审批。','1','1','2017-02-20 09:13:00','','0','','','0','{\"thumb\":\"\"}','1','0','0','0','','');INSERT INTO ts_posts ( `id`, `post_author`, `post_keywords`, `post_source`, `post_date`, `post_content`, `post_title`, `post_excerpt`, `post_status`, `comment_status`, `post_modified`, `post_content_filtered`, `post_parent`, `post_type`, `post_mime_type`, `comment_count`, `smeta`, `post_hits`, `post_like`, `istop`, `recommended`, `page_tpl`, `page_tpls` ) VALUES  ('419','1','2016年石油化工行业经济增长显著分化','','2017-03-13 09:39:31','<p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　中国石油和化学工业联合会</span>16<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">日发布的报告显示，</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">2016</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年，我国石油和化工行业经济增长显著分化，利润向下游转移。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　中国石油和化学工业联合会的统计数据显示，</span>2016<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年，石油和化学工业规模以上企业</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">29624</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">家，全行业增加值同比增长</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">7.0%</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">；实现主营业务收入</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">13.29</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">万亿元，增长</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">1.7%</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">；利润总额</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">6444.4</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">亿元，与上年基本持平；完成固定资产投资</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">2.15</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">万亿元，下降</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">5.9%</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">，占全国工业投资总额的</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">9.4%</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　分行业看，</span>2016<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年，石油和天然气开采业规模以上企业</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">293</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">家，行业增加值同比下降</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">3.6%</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">；利润净亏损</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">543.6</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">亿元，这是该行业历史上首次出现亏损，上年为盈利</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">857.8</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">亿元；完成固定资产投资</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">2331.0</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">亿元，下降</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">31.9%</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　石油加工业规模以上企业</span>1397<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">家，行业增加值同比增长</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">7.3%</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">；利润总额达</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">1703.6</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">亿元，增长</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">120.4%</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">；资产总计</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">1.79</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">万亿元，增长</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">8.9%</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">；完成固定资产投资</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">2125.3</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">亿元，增长</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">7.3%</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　化学工业规模以上企业</span>26409<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">家，行业增加值同比增长</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">8.0%</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">；利润总额</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">5073.2</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">亿元，增长</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">11.7%</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">；完成固定资产投资</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">1.61</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">万亿元，下降</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">0.7%</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">；资产总计</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">8.04</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">万亿元，增长</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">5.2%</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　数据显示，从</span>2012<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年开始，石油和天然气开采业利润逐年下降，而石油加工业和化学工业利润呈上升趋势，显示行业利润率向下游转移。</span></span></p><p><br/></p>','2016年石油化工行业经济增长显著分化','　　中国石油和化学工业联合会16日发布的报告显示，2016年，我国石油和化工行业经济增长显著分化，利润向下游转移。','1','1','2017-02-20 09:10:00','','0','','','0','{\"thumb\":\"\"}','1','0','0','0','','');INSERT INTO ts_posts ( `id`, `post_author`, `post_keywords`, `post_source`, `post_date`, `post_content`, `post_title`, `post_excerpt`, `post_status`, `comment_status`, `post_modified`, `post_content_filtered`, `post_parent`, `post_type`, `post_mime_type`, `comment_count`, `smeta`, `post_hits`, `post_like`, `istop`, `recommended`, `page_tpl`, `page_tpls` ) VALUES  ('420','1','2016年行业经济运行报告出炉','','2017-03-13 09:40:15','<p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　中国石油和化工行业经济运行形势发布会</span>2<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">16</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">日在京举行。会上，《</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">2016</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年中国石油和化工行业经济运行报告》发布。《报告》显示，去年我国石油和化工行业经济运行稳中有进，稳中向好，实现了“十三五”良好开局。从当年</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">12</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月的行业景气指数来看，全行业已经开始走暖，但各子行业间依然存在显著分化。</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">2017</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年，全行业将显现难中趋稳、稳中求进的发展态势，预计全行业工业增加值同比增长</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">7.5%</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　石化联合会信息与市场部主任祝昉指出，联合会发布的景气指数显示，</span>2016<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">12</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月，中国化学工业景气指数为</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">92.38</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">，较上月上升</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">1.52</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">点；油气行业景气指数为</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">94.08</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">，较上月大幅上升</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">7.59</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">点。两大指数均创两年来新高，显示行业开始走暖，但不同行业的效益出现较大分化，应该引起足够关注。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　《报告》显示，</span>2016<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年全行业发展呈稳中向好、分化调整、压力犹存三大特点。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\">　　2016<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年，全行业增加值同比增长</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">7%</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">，其中化学工业增加值增长</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">8%</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">，石油加工行业增加值同比增长</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">7.3%</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">，但石油和天然气开采业行业增加值则下降</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">3.6%</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">。化学工业中，专用化学品、农药和合成材料制造等增加值增速均在</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">10%</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">以上，但是化肥制造和化学矿采选等增加值增速只有</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">3.6%</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">和</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">5.4%</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　在全行业中，化学工业的表现较为亮眼。除工业增加值增速领先外，</span>2016<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年化学工业实现主营收入</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">9.21</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">万亿元，同比增长</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">5.3%</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">；利润总额</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">5073.2</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">亿元，增幅</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">11.7%</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">；资产总计</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">8.04</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">万亿元，增长</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">5.2%</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">，均表现突出。</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">2016</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年，化学工业主营收入利润率为</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">5.51%</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">，同比上升</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">0.32</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">点。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\">　　2016<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年国内油气开采业效益恶化。</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">2016</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年，油气开采业历史上首次出现净亏损，全年亏损额达</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">543.6</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">亿元，亏损情况持续加剧。收入也深度下滑，全年降幅达</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">17.3%</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">，连续第二年下降。油气开采业效益恶化的直接原因是油价大幅下降。监测显示，尽管</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">2016</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年国际油价震荡回升，但均价水平仍处于历史较低位，我国大庆原油</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">(</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">现货</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">)</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年均价格</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">36.97</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">美元</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">/</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">桶，为</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">2004</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年以来最低，同比跌幅</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">21%</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">；胜利原油年均价格为</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">34.98</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">美元</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">/</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">桶，跌幅</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">25.4%</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">。由于油气开采业效益严重恶化，导致石油和化工全行业经济回升显得乏力。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　石化联合会副会长傅向升在对</span>2017<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年行业形势进行预测时表示，</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">2017</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年开局好于预期，但世界经济的复杂性、不稳定性和不确定性进一步凸显，全行业去产能任务仍然艰巨，新旧动能转换还需时日，企业运营成本上升和投资环境亟待改善。预计</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">2017</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年全行业工业增加值同比增长</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">7.5%</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">，主营收入增长</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">6%</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">～</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">8%</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">，达到约</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">14</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">万亿元；利润增长</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">7%</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">～</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">9%</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">，约</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">6900</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">亿元；进出口扭转负增长态势。其中，化工行业增加值同比增长</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">8.5%</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">左右，主营业务收入增长</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">8%</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">左右，达到约</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">9.95</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">万亿元；利润增长</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">10%</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">左右，约</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">5600</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">亿元。</span></span></p><p><br/></p>','2016年行业经济运行报告出炉','　　中国石油和化工行业经济运行形势发布会2月16日在京举行。会上，《2016年中国石油和化工行业经济运行报告》发布。《报告》显示，去年我国石油和化工行业经济运行稳中有进，稳中向好，实现了“十三五”良好开局。从当年12月的行业景气指数来看，全行业已经开始走暖，但各子行业间依然存在显著分化。2017年，全行业将显现难中趋稳、稳中求进的发展态势，预计全行业工业增加值同比增长7.5%。','1','1','2017-02-20 00:00:00','','0','','','0','{\"thumb\":\"\"}','1','0','0','0','','');INSERT INTO ts_posts ( `id`, `post_author`, `post_keywords`, `post_source`, `post_date`, `post_content`, `post_title`, `post_excerpt`, `post_status`, `comment_status`, `post_modified`, `post_content_filtered`, `post_parent`, `post_type`, `post_mime_type`, `comment_count`, `smeta`, `post_hits`, `post_like`, `istop`, `recommended`, `page_tpl`, `page_tpls` ) VALUES  ('421','1','新轮成品油调价窗口今开启 ','','2017-03-13 09:41:20','<p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　新一轮成品油调价窗口将于</span>2<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">28</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">日</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">24</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">时开启，多家机构预测本轮调价将迎来</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">2017</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年首次搁浅。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　隆众资讯、卓创资讯、中宇资讯等多家机构分析称，本轮计价周期内，国际油价持续窄幅震荡，导致原油变化率在正值低位波动，所对应的成品油上调幅度不足</span>50<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">元</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">/</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">吨，预计本次调价或搁浅。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　根据《石油价格管理办法》，国内汽柴油最高零售价与国际油价挂钩。</span>“当调价幅度低于每吨<span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">50</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">元时，不作调整，纳入下次调价时累加或冲抵。”</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\">　　“欧佩克成员国减产协议执行率高达<span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">90%</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">，减产的利好助推国际原油价格，但来自美国方面页岩油的增产、钻井数的攀升、美联储加息预期等一系列利空消息持续制约原油上涨，”中宇资讯分析师孙晓飞说，受上述因素影响，近期原油价格保持窄幅震荡的走势。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　进入</span>2017<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年后，国内成品油调价已呈现“两涨一跌”之势，涨跌幅抵消后相当于汽柴油小幅上调</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">50</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">元</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">/</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">吨，略高于</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">2016</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">12</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月的价格水平。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　目前，多数地区汽柴油价格在</span>6<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">元</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">/</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">升以上。以北京为例，目前中石油、中石化</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">89</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">号汽油零售价为</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">6.11</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">元</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">/</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">升，</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">92</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">号汽油为</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">6.53</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">元</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">/</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">升，</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">95</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">号汽油为</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">6.95</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">元</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">/</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">升，</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">0</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">号柴油为</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">6.17</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">元</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">/</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">升。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　孙晓飞说，由于此次成品油调价呈现搁浅态势，零售加油站方面购销气氛并未出现明显紧张现象，加油站车流量较为平稳。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　隆众资讯分析师王倩倩说，从零售方面来看，若本轮汽柴油调价搁浅，加油站售价将基本保持不变，部分加油站将根据实际情况继续优惠活动，建议车主选择有正规进货渠道的加油站按需加油。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　下一次调价窗口将在</span>3<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">14</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">日</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">24</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">时开启。卓创资讯分析师王芦青认为，目前国际原油方面，减产利好与美国原油库存增加等消息持续博弈，下个周期国际原油走势依旧缺乏明确指引，国际油价继续窄幅震荡的概率较大，故而预计下周期国内油价调整很可能继续搁浅。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\">&nbsp;</span></p><p><br/></p>','新轮成品油调价窗口今开启 或迎2017年首次搁浅','　　新一轮成品油调价窗口将于2月28日24时开启，多家机构预测本轮调价将迎来2017年首次搁浅。','1','1','2017-02-28 09:40:00','','0','','','0','{\"thumb\":\"\"}','2','0','0','0','','');INSERT INTO ts_posts ( `id`, `post_author`, `post_keywords`, `post_source`, `post_date`, `post_content`, `post_title`, `post_excerpt`, `post_status`, `comment_status`, `post_modified`, `post_content_filtered`, `post_parent`, `post_type`, `post_mime_type`, `comment_count`, `smeta`, `post_hits`, `post_like`, `istop`, `recommended`, `page_tpl`, `page_tpls` ) VALUES  ('422','1','炼油行业切勿盲目扩产','','2017-03-13 09:42:16','<p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　尽管炼油行业效益持续增长，</span>2016<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年利润总额超过</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">1700</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">亿元，增幅超</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">120%</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">。但炼油行业整体大而不强、装置利用率低及产能过剩问题却不容忽视。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　一方面，在国内成品油定价机制影响下，尽管国际油价低迷，但国内炼化企业实现了较好盈利，继续追加投资的冲动开始抬头；另一方面，受制于原油进口渠道狭窄，</span>2016<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年以前地方炼厂无论开工率还是扩张意愿并不高，随着原油进口权和使用权进一步放开，地方炼厂扩大产能的热情再次高涨。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　同时，终端需求增速进一步减弱令过剩之忧愈加凸显。数据显示，</span>2016<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年，受投资增速总体放缓、经济转型升级，以及高铁、新能源汽车快速发展等因素共同影响，成品油消费增长区间下移。估计全年成品油表观消费量为</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">3.13</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">亿吨，较</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">2015</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年下降</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">1%</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">，增速较</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">2015</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年回落</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">6.2</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">个百分点。在供需格局逆转的前提下，相关调控若不及时到位，国内炼油能力将严重过剩，待过剩后再去产能，将带来更大损失，并引发一系列问题。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\">　　2017<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年炼油业整体产能仍偏过剩，必须持续淘汰落后产能、鼓励高效产能、优化整体炼油能力，主动控制好成品油资源总量，防止出现钢铁、煤炭等行业产能过剩乱象，这是</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">2017</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年炼化行业亟需解决的课题，也是提升行业整体运行质量的关键。</span></span></p><p><br/></p>','炼油行业切勿盲目扩产','　　尽管炼油行业效益持续增长，2016年利润总额超过1700亿元，增幅超120%。但炼油行业整体大而不强、装置利用率低及产能过剩问题却不容忽视。','1','1','2017-02-28 09:41:00','','0','','','0','{\"thumb\":\"\"}','2','0','0','0','','');INSERT INTO ts_posts ( `id`, `post_author`, `post_keywords`, `post_source`, `post_date`, `post_content`, `post_title`, `post_excerpt`, `post_status`, `comment_status`, `post_modified`, `post_content_filtered`, `post_parent`, `post_type`, `post_mime_type`, `comment_count`, `smeta`, `post_hits`, `post_like`, `istop`, `recommended`, `page_tpl`, `page_tpls` ) VALUES  ('423','1','海洋石油行业复苏可能早于预期','','2017-03-13 09:42:41','<p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　据道琼斯</span>2<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">24</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">日消息，尽管石油行业中的大部分看到了复苏迹象，但海洋石油行业是个例外，一些分析师表示，海洋石油行业在</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">2018</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年或</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">2019</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年前都不会开始改善。但在海洋石油行业巨头</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">Transocean</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">公布了乐观的第四财季业绩后，</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">Evercore</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">公司分析师表示，海洋石油钻探行业可能比预期更早触底。该公司表示，海洋钻井平台的计日费率似乎将在现金收支平衡水平上方见底，投标活动也有所改善。但是，数据表明行业持续疲软。贝克休斯最新的钻井数据显示，美国目前只有</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">18</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">个活跃海洋钻井平台，不到</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">2014</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">9</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月活跃钻井平台数</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">(66</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">个</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">)</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">的三分之一。</span></span></p><p><br/></p>','海洋石油行业复苏可能早于预期','　　据道琼斯2月24日消息，尽管石油行业中的大部分看到了复苏迹象，但海洋石油行业是个例外，一些分析师表示，海洋石油行业在2018年或2019年前都不会开始改善。','1','1','2017-02-28 09:42:00','','0','','','0','{\"thumb\":\"\"}','2','0','0','0','','');INSERT INTO ts_posts ( `id`, `post_author`, `post_keywords`, `post_source`, `post_date`, `post_content`, `post_title`, `post_excerpt`, `post_status`, `comment_status`, `post_modified`, `post_content_filtered`, `post_parent`, `post_type`, `post_mime_type`, `comment_count`, `smeta`, `post_hits`, `post_like`, `istop`, `recommended`, `page_tpl`, `page_tpls` ) VALUES  ('424','1','我国北方油气勘查新添3套新层系','','2017-03-13 09:43:19','<p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\">　　2<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">23</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">日，中国地质调查局在</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">2017</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">全国地质调查工作会议上发布《支撑服务能源资源重大突破地质调查报告》。报告显示，经过十余年的科技创新，我国北方盆地油气资源勘查拓展出</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">3</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">套新层系，累计新增勘查新区</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">50</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">万平方公里，圈定</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">20</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">处油气远景区。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　中国地质调查局创新性提出我国北方石炭系</span>—二叠系不存在区域变质的新认识，首次发现<span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">4</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">套烃源岩，证实了石炭系—二叠系是我国北方油气调查重要新层系。在此基础上，银额盆地开辟勘查新区</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">12</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">万平方公里，优选</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">6</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">个有利勘查区块竞争性出让，获高产工业油气流，打造出公益性地质调查引领商业性油气勘探实现重大突破的成功典范。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　该局通过地质地球物理综合调查和调查井钻探，证实松辽盆地主力勘查层系白垩系之外，火山岩覆盖下的侏罗系是重要新层系。在这一新认识指导下，开辟了辽西地区</span>20<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">万平方千米火山岩覆盖区侏罗系勘查新区。此外，在辽宁省凌源市证实了中新元古界为松辽盆地外围油气调查新层系。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　报告还显示，新疆塔里木、准噶尔等盆地周缘矿业权空白区和退出区块共开辟</span>18<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">万平方千米勘查新区。中国地调局圈定了新疆柯坪冲断带、松辽盆地外围阜新—金羊—凌源、银额盆地居延海凹陷等</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">20</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">处油气远景区，开展油气战略选区调查工作；在羌塘盆地勘查新区识别出</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">2</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">个大于</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">100</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">平方千米的大型圈闭，为下一步油气勘探提供新的方向。</span></span></p><p><br/></p>','我国北方油气勘查新添3套新层系','　　2月23日，中国地质调查局在2017全国地质调查工作会议上发布《支撑服务能源资源重大突破地质调查报告》。报告显示，经过十余年的科技创新，我国北方盆地油气资源勘查拓展出3套新层系，累计新增勘查新区50万平方公里，圈定20处油气远景区。','1','1','2017-02-28 09:42:00','','0','','','0','{\"thumb\":\"\"}','2','0','0','0','','');INSERT INTO ts_posts ( `id`, `post_author`, `post_keywords`, `post_source`, `post_date`, `post_content`, `post_title`, `post_excerpt`, `post_status`, `comment_status`, `post_modified`, `post_content_filtered`, `post_parent`, `post_type`, `post_mime_type`, `comment_count`, `smeta`, `post_hits`, `post_like`, `istop`, `recommended`, `page_tpl`, `page_tpls` ) VALUES  ('425','1','国际油价27日微涨','','2017-03-13 09:43:48','<p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　纽约油价</span>27<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">日微涨。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　分析人士表示，美国原油产量不断增加令国际油价承压，而市场乐观情绪助推纽约油价当天上涨。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　截至当天收盘，纽约商品交易所</span>4<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月交货的轻质原油期货价格上涨</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">0.06</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">美元，收于每桶</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">54.05</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">美元。</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">4</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月交货的伦敦布伦特原油期货价格下跌</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">0.06</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">美元，收于每桶</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">55.93</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">美元。</span></span></p><p><br/></p>','国际油价27日微涨 收于每桶54.05美元','　　纽约油价27日微涨。','1','1','2017-02-28 00:00:00','','0','','','0','{\"thumb\":\"\"}','1','0','0','0','','');INSERT INTO ts_posts ( `id`, `post_author`, `post_keywords`, `post_source`, `post_date`, `post_content`, `post_title`, `post_excerpt`, `post_status`, `comment_status`, `post_modified`, `post_content_filtered`, `post_parent`, `post_type`, `post_mime_type`, `comment_count`, `smeta`, `post_hits`, `post_like`, `istop`, `recommended`, `page_tpl`, `page_tpls` ) VALUES  ('426','1','石化行业结束利润负增长态势 ','','2017-03-13 09:44:37','<p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　石化行业终于结束了连续</span>20<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">个月的负增长态势，炼油业、化学工业效益持续增长，产业提质转型步伐加快。不过，虽然业绩开始逐步好转，但行业内部发展分化显著，利润差距较大，接近下游终端市场的行业明显好于上游细分行业。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　据经济日报</span>3<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">1</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">日消息，来自中国石油和化学工业联合会的信息显示，</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">2016</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年，石化行业全年主营业务收入</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">13.28</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">万亿元，同比增长</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">1.7%</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">，利润总额</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">6444</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">亿元，与</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">2015</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年基本持平；其中化工行业主营收入</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">9.21</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">万亿元、同比增长</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">5.3%</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">，利润总额</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">5073</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">亿元、同比增长</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">11.7%</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">。中国石油和化学工业联合会副会长傅向升表示，在</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">2015</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年石化全行业主营收入下降</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">6.1%</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">、利润下降</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">18.2%</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">、进出口总额下降</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">22.1%</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">的情况下，</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">2016</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年实现收入增长及部分行业实现利润增长，结果好于预期。更难能可贵的是，扭转了行业连续</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">20</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">个月负增长趋势。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　业绩好转首先来源于产业整体提质增效。具体来说，</span>2016<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年炼油业产品结构调整继续加快，国</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">V</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">汽柴油升级改造全面完成。由于成本下降及优质优价的原因，去年炼油业效益持续高速增长，利润总额逾</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">1700</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">亿元，创历史新高，增幅超过</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">120%</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">。同时，化学工业效益也持续改善，利润创新纪录，增幅近</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">12%</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">。“特别是基础化学原料提质增效最为显著，利润增速达</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">38.1%</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">，对化工行业利润贡献率达</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">70%</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">；合成材料利润也呈现高速增长势头，增幅达</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">41.8%</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">，位居化工各行业之首，贡献率超过</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">38%</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">。”中国石油和化学工业联合会信息与市场部副主任祝昉说。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　有分析认为，全行业实现</span>2016<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年的“尾部反转”也得益于行业价格总水平回暖。数据显示，</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">2016</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年石化业价格总水平连续第</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">5</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年下降，但石油和主要化学品市场呈现触底回升走势，价格降幅不断收窄，特别是进入去年三季度后，回升明显加快。价格指数显示，石油和天然气开采业全年价格总水平下降</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">16.4%</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">，同比收窄约</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">21</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">个百分点，比上半年收窄</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">12.8</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">个百分点。化学原料和化学品制造业下降</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">2.8%</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">，为</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">5</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年来最低降幅，同比收窄</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">3.9</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">个百分点，比上半年收窄</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">2.8</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">个百分点。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\">　　2016<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年石化业经济运行的一个明显特征是行业经济增长分化显著。业内专家分析认为，分化是产业结构和产品结构调整的必然结果，且很可能成为长期现象。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　从主要产品产量看，原油产量降幅达</span>6.9%<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">，为</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">2010</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年以来首次下降。汽油、煤油产量增幅分别为</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">6.4%</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">和</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">8.9%</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">，柴油则下降</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">1.3%</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">。主要化学品中，无机化学原料产量增幅仅为</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">2.2%</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">，但有机化学原料和合成材料增幅分别为</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">5.7%</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">和</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">8.0%</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　利润差距大，是行业分化的另一个重要表现。举例说，一些细分行业中企业的民营化程度较高，市场竞争充分有效，经营模式多样化，既保证了较为平衡的供需关系，也确保了产品价格稳定。再比如，精细化工及化工新材料领域企业利润率较高，这大多得益于企业对目标市场把握明确、产品更有针对性；产品结构单一、产品类型和质量缺乏竞争力的</span>“大路货”则面临产能过剩问题，相关企业发展状况也不乐观。</span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　从石化行业整体运行情况来看，处于或接近上游的行业经济运行情况较差，越接近终端市场的行业运行情况越好。</span>“行业的分化调整不仅体现在主营收入、利润及细分行业增加值上，企业、产品结构以及区域的分化也越来越明显。”祝昉说。</span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　来自石化联合会的信息显示，无机酸碱、化肥、轮胎等大宗基础化学品过剩，化工新材料、电子化学品等高端产品严重缺乏。</span>2016<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年，石化业贸易逆差达</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">1360.8</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">亿美元，逆差最大的合成树脂达</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">326.8</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">亿美元、有机化学品达</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">105.9</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">亿美元、合成纤维单体达</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">54.1</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">亿美元、专用化学品达</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">24.1</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">亿美元；一些高端化工产品自给率不足</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">40%</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">，还有一些产品的对外依存度甚至超过</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">50%</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">，这些化工产品在建筑、汽车、电子信息、航空航天等领域的巨大需求尚待满足。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　傅向升将石化行业产能结构性过剩形容为</span>“低端拥挤、高端短缺”，“石化行业产能结构性过剩矛盾依然严重。尤其是在市场向好的时候，去产能面临的挑战更加艰巨，必须有决心、有恒心、持续发力”。</span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　祝昉表示，在一些产能严重过剩行业，落后产能和</span>“僵尸企业”仍未完全退出，在价格低位和环保核查严格环境下，有些只是暂时性的歇产或减产，一旦价格回升或环保核查放松，有可能死灰复燃。“另外，一些产能利用率较低的行业比如炼油业目前投资冲动仍很大，一些价格好转效益改善的行业如氯碱等投资冲动又开始显露苗头，值得关注。”</span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　在被寄予厚望的化工新材料领域，以高技术含量、高附加值、高对外依存度为特点，国内产品自给率低、市场需求缺口大。瞄准高端做</span>“加法”是行业共识，但需要科学的规划和布局作保障。“化工新材料领域已经或将会出现的产能过剩要引起注意。”傅向升表示，比如上游的有机硅单体呈现过剩趋势，但下游加工产品如高端密封材料、高端洗涤用品又相对短缺；碳纤维等装置建成和上马的不少，但产能并未有效发挥，这些领域的过剩苗头值得深入研究和及早防范。</span></p><p><br/></p>','石化行业结束利润负增长态势 为20个月首次','　　石化行业终于结束了连续20个月的负增长态势，炼油业、化学工业效益持续增长，产业提质转型步伐加快。不过，虽然业绩开始逐步好转，但行业内部发展分化显著，利润差距较大，接近下游终端市场的行业明显好于上游细分行业。','1','1','2017-03-02 09:43:00','','0','','','0','{\"thumb\":\"\"}','2','0','0','0','','');INSERT INTO ts_posts ( `id`, `post_author`, `post_keywords`, `post_source`, `post_date`, `post_content`, `post_title`, `post_excerpt`, `post_status`, `comment_status`, `post_modified`, `post_content_filtered`, `post_parent`, `post_type`, `post_mime_type`, `comment_count`, `smeta`, `post_hits`, `post_like`, `istop`, `recommended`, `page_tpl`, `page_tpls` ) VALUES  ('427','1','加快推广使用生物柴油','','2017-03-13 09:45:24','<p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　根据国家发改委等八部门去年底发布的《关于全国全面供应符合第五阶段国家强制性标准车用油品的公告》，</span>2017<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年起我国将在全国范围内全面供应符合国Ⅴ标准的车用汽油</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">(</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">含</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">E10</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">乙醇汽油</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">)</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">、车用柴油</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">(</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">含</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">B5</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">生物柴油</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">)</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">。受此政策推动，生物柴油产业有望迎来发展黄金机遇期。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　生物柴油，是以</span>“地沟油”等废弃油脂、油料作物等为主要原料生产的绿色能源。《可再生能源法》规定，国家鼓励清洁、高效地开发利用生物质燃料，鼓励发展能源作物。在政策支持下，我国生物柴油产业发展取得较大成就，产业成熟度明显提高，年生产能力已超<span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">500</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">万吨。不过，发展中也存在一些难题。比如</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">,</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">《可再生能源法》规定石油销售企业应按照国务院能源主管部门或者省级人民政府的规定，将符合国家标准的生物液体燃料纳入其燃料销售体系，但是在现行的石油石化内部体系中，销售公司只负责卖油，不具备调配、掺混生物柴油职能，缺乏调配生物柴油的专业技术人员和检测设备，生物柴油进入石油石化销售体系面临难题。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　实际上，我国推广乙醇汽油的做法是推广生物柴油可资借鉴的先例。乙醇汽油是在炼油加工环节由生产厂家调配，而不是由销售公司完成调配的。按照这样的流程设计，不增加投资和混配难度，不改变原石化柴油调拨结算程序，消除了销售公司混配难、销售难，即可打破市场壁垒，解决生物柴油入口问题。从国外经验看，生物柴油多采用强制封闭措施推广使用，规定石化柴油不添加生物柴油不能进入市场。如美国规定的生物柴油掺混比例为</span>5%<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">至</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">20%</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">，欧盟为</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">5%</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">至</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">7%</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">。我国在发展乙醇汽油时，也采取了封闭推广示范区做法。截至目前，陆续有</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">10</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">多个省份在封闭推广、强制使用车用乙醇汽油，乙醇汽油市场份额占全国汽油消费总量</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">25%</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">多，节能减排效果明显。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　借鉴国外做法和我国发展乙醇汽油所取得的经验，建立封闭示范区来推广生物柴油，应是个现实可行的方案。为此，可在部分省份或地区先行实验，再逐步扩大范围。示范区既可选择京津冀等物流发达、人口稠密、餐馆林立的区域，这样的区域地沟油原料丰富；亦可选择云贵川地区，这里高原缺氧，非常适合使用生物柴油，且具有良好的油料作物生长环境。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　在京津冀或云贵川建立生物柴油封闭示范区，将一举多得。不仅可以有效解决重卡柴油车使用劣质低品柴油的致霾难题，还能彻底消化封闭区内的地沟油，有效阻止地沟油回流餐桌的问题，保卫首都以及其他地区人民群众的餐桌安全。此举还可以驱逐低品劣质油，有利于高标准油品占领市场，更好地促进环境保护。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-left: 0px; text-indent: 0px; text-align: justify; line-height: 150%;\"><br/></p>','加快推广使用生物柴油','　　根据国家发改委等八部门去年底发布的《关于全国全面供应符合第五阶段国家强制性标准车用油品的公告》，2017年起我国将在全国范围内全面供应符合国Ⅴ标准的车用汽油(含E10乙醇汽油)、车用柴油(含B5生物柴油)。受此政策推动，生物柴油产业有望迎来发展黄金机遇期。','1','1','2017-03-02 09:44:00','','0','','','0','{\"thumb\":\"\"}','7','0','0','0','','');INSERT INTO ts_posts ( `id`, `post_author`, `post_keywords`, `post_source`, `post_date`, `post_content`, `post_title`, `post_excerpt`, `post_status`, `comment_status`, `post_modified`, `post_content_filtered`, `post_parent`, `post_type`, `post_mime_type`, `comment_count`, `smeta`, `post_hits`, `post_like`, `istop`, `recommended`, `page_tpl`, `page_tpls` ) VALUES  ('428','1','国际油价3月1日下跌','','2017-03-13 09:46:02','<p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　国际油价</span>1<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">日收盘下跌。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　美国能源信息局当天发布的数据显示，上周美国全国商业原油库存连续第八周上涨，达到</span>5.202<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">亿桶。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　分析人士表示，不断增加的美国原油产量加剧市场供过于求的担忧，令国际油价承压下行。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　截至当天收盘，纽约商品交易所</span>4<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月交货的轻质原油期货价格下跌</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">0.18</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">美元，收于每桶</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">53.83</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">美元，跌幅为</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">0.33%</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">。</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">5</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月交货的伦敦布伦特原油期货价格下跌</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">0.15</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">美元，收于每桶</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">56.36</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">美元，跌幅为</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">0.27%</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">。</span></span></p><p><br/></p>','国际油价3月1日下跌 收于每桶53.83美元','美国能源信息局当天发布的数据显示，上周美国全国商业原油库存连续第八周上涨，达到5.202亿桶。','1','1','2017-03-02 09:45:00','','0','','','0','{\"thumb\":\"\"}','2','0','0','0','','');INSERT INTO ts_posts ( `id`, `post_author`, `post_keywords`, `post_source`, `post_date`, `post_content`, `post_title`, `post_excerpt`, `post_status`, `comment_status`, `post_modified`, `post_content_filtered`, `post_parent`, `post_type`, `post_mime_type`, `comment_count`, `smeta`, `post_hits`, `post_like`, `istop`, `recommended`, `page_tpl`, `page_tpls` ) VALUES  ('429','1','国际石油周：油价恢复道阻且长','','2017-03-13 09:46:46','<p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\">　 &nbsp;2<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">22</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">日至</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">24</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">日，</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">2017</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年国际石油周</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">(International Petroleum Week)</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">在伦敦如期举行，吸引了全球油企高管和政府官员。油价走势成为最重要议题。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　维多石油首席执行官伊恩</span>·泰勒在会议期间表示，未来<span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">10</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年，油价水平将持续低迷，因为中国经济增长速度放缓，且美国页岩油业几乎扼杀了油价上涨的机会。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\">　　“石油业正面临着一场危机。”道达尔首席执行官潘彦磊说；<span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">BP</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">首席执行官杜德里也表示对市场感到“非常悲观”，面临供应过剩。他开玩笑说，用不了多久游泳池也将装满石油。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　高盛集团大宗商品研究主管</span>Jeff Currie<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">表示：“就算油价跌至十几美元，我也不会惊讶。”另有许多实际业绩优于预期的炼油商也不看好未来的发展前景。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\">　　2017<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年初，油价曾出现短暂回升，因为当时市场猜测欧佩克将与俄罗斯联合减产。但俄罗斯能源巨头却并不这样认为。“告诉我谁会减产？”俄油首席执行官谢钦说，“沙特会减产，还是伊朗、墨西哥或巴西会减产，到底谁会减产？”</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　谢钦表示，目前全球市场形势严峻，每天有高达</span>170<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">万桶的产量过剩，因此理论上减产</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">100</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">万桶会使油价更为“合理”。然而目前俄油仍专注于如何在市场竞争中保持市场份额。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　伍德麦肯锡则估计，全球石油产量仅有</span>0.1%<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">因无利可图被削减。花旗分析称，今年油市可能会经历快速的再平衡，因市场受到了</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">1</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">1</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">日起生效的欧佩克减产决定的影响，预计</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">2018</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年美国页岩油产出将继续使油价承压。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　欧佩克秘书长巴尔金多称，今年</span>1<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月数据显示，参与减产的欧佩克成员国执行减产力度达</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">90%</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">。卡塔尔能源部长</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">Mohammed Al Sada</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">称赞欧佩克减产协议的成功，积极地推动了油价走高。“这些努力和取得的共识对油价走势产生了积极的影响。”但他也强调，包括俄罗斯在内的</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">11</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">个非欧佩克产油国的执行力度只有约</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">50%</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　值得一提的是，阿联酋酋长国之一富查伊拉的政府代表在会上宣布，该国将智利成为全球能源中心。富查伊拉政府技术顾问</span>Salem Abdo Khalil<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">在“国际石油周”分会上发表主题演讲称：“当前的低油价和能源需求上升意味着，石油公司都经历着前所未有的变革，富查伊拉石油工业区建成了更多成熟的基础设施和存储设备，国家石油公司也以优质的服务不断扩大国内外业务。”</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　联合国气候变化框架公约执行秘书</span>Patricia Espinosa<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">在大会上呼吁，与会油气高管和政策制定者的决策应与巴黎气候协议目标保持一致，并符合联合国可持续发展目标。她希望后者能考虑长期影响、勇于创新。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\">　　BP<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">首席执行官杜德里也称，石油行业面临着竞争加剧的威胁，尤其是随着可再生能源成本下降。毫无疑问，可再生能源也存在一些问题，比如存储等，但石油行业不能因此忽略可再生能源，这是不明智的。</span></span></p><p><br/></p>','国际石油周：油价恢复道阻且长','2月22日至24日，2017年国际石油周(International Petroleum Week)在伦敦如期举行，吸引了全球油企高管和政府官员。油价走势成为最重要议题。','1','1','2017-03-02 09:46:00','','0','','','0','{\"thumb\":\"\"}','2','0','0','0','','');INSERT INTO ts_posts ( `id`, `post_author`, `post_keywords`, `post_source`, `post_date`, `post_content`, `post_title`, `post_excerpt`, `post_status`, `comment_status`, `post_modified`, `post_content_filtered`, `post_parent`, `post_type`, `post_mime_type`, `comment_count`, `smeta`, `post_hits`, `post_like`, `istop`, `recommended`, `page_tpl`, `page_tpls` ) VALUES  ('430','1','俄罗斯2月份平均日减12.4万桶石油产量','','2017-03-13 09:47:15','<p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　据路透社</span>2<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">28</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">日莫斯科报道，俄罗斯国际文传电讯社</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">28</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">日援引一名熟悉统计数据的消息人士的话报道说，与</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">1</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月份平均日减</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">11.7</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">万桶石油产量相比，俄罗斯在</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">2</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">1</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">日至</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">27</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">日的</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">27</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">天里平均每天比去年</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">10</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月份水平减少了大约</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">12.4</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">万桶石油产量。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　俄罗斯曾表示，俄罗斯在第一季度结束前将从去年</span>10<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月份水平平均日减</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">20</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">万桶石油产量并在</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">4</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月份平均日减</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">30</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">万桶石油产量。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　国际文传电讯社说，俄罗斯在</span>2<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月份的前</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">27</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">天里共生产了</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">4090</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">万吨</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">(1106</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">万桶</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">/</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">天</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">)</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">的石油。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　俄罗斯能源部长诺瓦克周一</span>(27<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">日</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">)</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">说，俄罗斯可能比此前预期更快削减石油产量。</span></span></p><p><br/></p>','俄罗斯2月份平均日减12.4万桶石油产量','据路透社2月28日莫斯科报道，俄罗斯国际文传电讯社28日援引一名熟悉统计数据的消息人士的话报道说，与1月份平均日减11.7万桶石油产量相比，俄罗斯在2月1日至27日的27天里平均每天比去年10月份水平减少了大约12.4万桶石油产量。','1','1','2017-03-02 09:46:00','','0','','','0','{\"thumb\":\"\"}','2','0','0','0','','');INSERT INTO ts_posts ( `id`, `post_author`, `post_keywords`, `post_source`, `post_date`, `post_content`, `post_title`, `post_excerpt`, `post_status`, `comment_status`, `post_modified`, `post_content_filtered`, `post_parent`, `post_type`, `post_mime_type`, `comment_count`, `smeta`, `post_hits`, `post_like`, `istop`, `recommended`, `page_tpl`, `page_tpls` ) VALUES  ('431','1','国际石油市场正在重建信心','','2017-03-13 09:47:54','<p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　日前，石油输出国组织</span>(<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">欧佩克</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">)</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">减产监督委员会在维也纳公布了相关国家执行减产协议情况。数据显示，欧佩克成员国和参与减产的</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">11</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">个非欧佩克成员国</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">1</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月份对减产协议的总体执行率达到</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">86%</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">。欧佩克对这一减产进度表示满意。与此同时，非欧佩克成员国的减产执行率也由</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">1</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月份的</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">40%</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">至</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">50%</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">上升至目前的</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">60%</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">左右。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　欧佩克秘书长巴金多在伦敦表示，有信心看到参与减产的成员国</span>100%<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">执行协议。他对未来一段时间国际原油市场走势表示“谨慎乐观”，认为市场正在重建信心。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　但是，并非所有参与减产的国家都看好油价上涨前景。其中，伊朗认为如果国际油价超过</span>55<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">美元</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">/</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">桶，恐将对欧佩克产生不利影响。原因是一旦国际油价持续上涨，会刺激未参与减产的产油国增加产量，从而挤占参与减产国家的市场份额。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　以美国为例，数据显示，自去年</span>11<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月底相关各方达成减产协议以来，美国石油钻机增加了近</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">100</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">台，目前总数已经达到</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">602</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">台，是</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">2015</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">10</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月份以来的最高水平。美国原油生产正在不断恢复，这充分显示出如果油价进一步上涨，国际市场份额的争夺将会更加激烈。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　有不少分析人士认为，欧佩克有必要延长减产协议以达到平衡国际市场供需关系的目标。但是巴金多表示现在作出决定还为时尚早。国际市场变化很快，因此减产的效果还有待观察。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　眼下，欧佩克致力于通过减产将库存削减至低于</span>5<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年平均值的水平。降低原油库存是欧佩克用来衡量减产协议效果的重要手段之一，因此这一数据指标也将成为欧佩克决定下一步行动的关键因素。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　值得注意的是，沙特等成员国虽然认真履行减产协议，但部分免于执行该协议的欧佩克成员国却显示出增产的迹象。数据显示，利比亚和尼日利亚</span>1<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月份分别增产</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">6.5</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">万桶</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">/</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">天和</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">10.18</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">万桶</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">/</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">天，伊朗增产幅度也达到了</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">5.02</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">万桶</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">/</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">天。显然，这将给减产协议带来一定压力。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　目前，市场焦点主要集中在欧佩克减产协议的效果上，以期能够为下一阶段国际原油价格走势勾画出一个略微清晰的走势。不少分析人士指出，留给欧佩克的时间已经十分有限。尽管参与减产各方目前都在积极努力履行减产协议，但国际油价的涨幅并未达到此前的预期。部分专家认为，如果短期内国际油价无法突破当前的上行阻力价位，那么油价极有可能再次走低。但部分较为乐观的分析则认为，欧佩克极有可能延长该减产协议，以便进一步提高油价。不过，这一决定可能要等到今年</span>5<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月份欧佩克再次召开部长会议时才会作出。</span></span></p><p><br/></p>','国际石油市场正在重建信心','日前，石油输出国组织(欧佩克)减产监督委员会在维也纳公布了相关国家执行减产协议情况。数据显示，欧佩克成员国和参与减产的11个非欧佩克成员国1月份对减产协议的总体执行率达到86%。欧佩克对这一减产进度表示满意。与此同时，非欧佩克成员国的减产执行率也由1月份的40%至50%上升至目前的60%左右。','1','1','2017-03-02 09:47:00','','0','','','0','{\"thumb\":\"\"}','2','0','0','0','','');INSERT INTO ts_posts ( `id`, `post_author`, `post_keywords`, `post_source`, `post_date`, `post_content`, `post_title`, `post_excerpt`, `post_status`, `comment_status`, `post_modified`, `post_content_filtered`, `post_parent`, `post_type`, `post_mime_type`, `comment_count`, `smeta`, `post_hits`, `post_like`, `istop`, `recommended`, `page_tpl`, `page_tpls` ) VALUES  ('432','1','国际油价6日下跌 ','','2017-03-13 09:48:26','<p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　纽约油价</span>6<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">日下跌。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　当天有消息说，伊拉克认为石油输出国组织</span>(<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">欧佩克</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">)</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">或需要延长减产协议。该消息在当天早些时候曾推高油价。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　此外，美国油田技术服务公司贝克休斯</span>3<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">日发布的数据显示，上周美国运营的油田钻井数量达</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">609</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">个，比前一周增加</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">7</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">个。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　分析人士说，市场对全球原油市场供过于求的担忧挥之不去，使国际油价承压。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　截至当天收盘，纽约商品交易所</span>4<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月交货的轻质原油期货价格下跌</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">0.13</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">美元，收于每桶</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">53.20</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">美元，跌幅为</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">0.24%</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">。</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">5</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月交货的伦敦布伦特原油期货价格上涨</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">0.11</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">美元，收于每桶</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">56.01</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">美元，涨幅为</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">0.20%</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">。</span></span></p><p><br/></p>','国际油价6日下跌 收于每桶53.20美元','当天有消息说，伊拉克认为石油输出国组织(欧佩克)或需要延长减产协议。该消息在当天早些时候曾推高油价。','1','1','2017-03-07 09:48:00','','0','','','0','{\"thumb\":\"\"}','5','0','0','0','','');INSERT INTO ts_posts ( `id`, `post_author`, `post_keywords`, `post_source`, `post_date`, `post_content`, `post_title`, `post_excerpt`, `post_status`, `comment_status`, `post_modified`, `post_content_filtered`, `post_parent`, `post_type`, `post_mime_type`, `comment_count`, `smeta`, `post_hits`, `post_like`, `istop`, `recommended`, `page_tpl`, `page_tpls` ) VALUES  ('433','1','18家地炼获得原油进口权','证券日报','2017-03-13 09:50:00','<p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;font-size: 14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　《证券日报》记者了解到，近日，有</span>5<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">家地炼再次获得原油进口资质。截至目前，共有</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">18</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">家地炼拥有原油进口资质。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;font-size: 14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　与此同时，日前，有消息称，日照石大石化、滨州天宏新能源两家地炼被央企收购。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;font-size: 14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　业内认为，随着国内炼油行业打破垄断格局，成品油价格逐步放开的大环境下，地炼未来仍有望再享政策红利。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;font-size: 14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　而这也是央企频繁收购地炼的主要原因。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;font-size: 14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　分析师表示，包括三大石油公司、中化集团等国有资本以及民营资本将逐步改变国内炼化板块的供应格局。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;font-size: 14px\">　　</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;font-size: 14px\">18<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">家地炼获得原油进口权</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;font-size: 14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　近日，商务部对</span>5<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">家地炼原油非国营贸易进口资质进行公示，包括中化工、清源集团、神驰化工、河北鑫海化工、金诚石化。</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">5</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">家地炼第一批进口原油配额共</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">1867</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">万吨，其中中化工</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">1203</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">万吨。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;font-size: 14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　据了解，中化工于</span>2013<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年即已获得千万吨进口配额，时隔四年，终于获得了非国营进口资质，“三证”齐全，意味着中化工打通了进口全流程，可以不通过中海油、中石油等公司代理。从</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">2013</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年年初获批配额至</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">2016</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年，中化工共计进口</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">3700</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">万吨左右。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;font-size: 14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　除中化工外，其余四家均为</span>2016<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年下半年获批的进口原油使用权。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;font-size: 14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　安迅思分析师邹敏珍向《证券日报》记者表示，较四家地炼先一步拿到发改委的进口原油使用权的恒源石化，因递交申报材料问题尚未获得进口资质，但从国家放开的态度来看，恒源石化获进口资质也是迟早的事情。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;font-size: 14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　她还指出，</span>5<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">家地炼正式获商务部批准后，将有</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">17</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">家地炼获得进口资质，包括由参股公司中化进口的中化弘润在内，</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">18</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">家地炼第一批进口配额共</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">5472</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">万吨。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;font-size: 14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　需要一提的是，海关数据显示，</span>2017<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年第一个月中国原油进口持续强劲。尽管并未刷新</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">2016</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">12</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月份的历史最高记录，但较</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">2016</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年全年平均水平继续稳健增长</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">7.2%</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;font-size: 14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　安迅思分析师李莉向《证券日报》记者表示，随着地方炼厂</span>“转正”审批节奏的放慢，山东的原油进口最初始的洪荒之力已释放大半，未来的增量潜力可能不超过<span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">15%</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">，山东地炼的进口原油正在进入增长的“高原期”。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;font-size: 14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　此外，宁波、湛江、锦州</span>(<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">经大连</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">)</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">、惠州受国家战略储备库或商业储备因素支撑，在</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">2017</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年部分月份的原油进口可能出现跳增，</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">2017</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年可能成为中国原油收储的密集年。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;font-size: 14px\">　</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;font-size: 14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　地炼被央企收购再改炼化格局</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;font-size: 14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　事实上，随着油气改革的步步深入，地炼在逐渐在以前的垄断领域分得一杯羹。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;font-size: 14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　自</span>2015<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年开始，我国地炼炼厂获得进口原油配额及相关原油进口、成品油出口的资质，民营炼厂发展一直受到市场的关注。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;font-size: 14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　卓创资讯分析师秦文平告诉《证券日报》记者，随着国内炼油行业打破垄断格局、成品油价格逐步放开的大环境下，民营炼厂未来仍有望再享政策红利。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;font-size: 14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　也正是看好未来民营炼厂发展前景，日前，关于日照石大石化、滨州天宏新能源、珠海宝塔石化被收购的消息便迅速传出。其中，前两家收购企业均为央企。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;font-size: 14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　这是继</span>2002<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年中海油收购中海沥青</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">(</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">滨化</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">)</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">、</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">2006</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年中化工集团收购六家民营炼厂、</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">2010</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年末中国中化集团增资控股弘润石化后的最新收购案。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;font-size: 14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　对于此次集中收购，秦文平表示，政策红利持续向民营炼厂倾斜，未来发展可期。</span>2015<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年和</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">2016</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年受国际原油低价及成品油定价机制影响，炼化板块利润可观，吸引非行业客户持续关注；被收购炼厂规模适中，原油及相关资质较全，并购后可满足开工生产条件，为收购企业降低了准入门槛。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;font-size: 14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　不过，她还认为，对于收购后的央企控股企业，体制问题能否适合市场化的要求，或成为其发展好坏的重要条件。但不可否认的是，此次集中并购事件将引起国内民营炼厂格局的新变化，届时三大石油公司、中化集团、中化工、中国兵器集团及其它国营资本、民营资本将逐步改变国内炼化板块的供应格局。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;font-size: 14px\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;font-size: 14px\">&nbsp;</span></p><p><br/></p>','18家地炼获得原油进口权','《证券日报》记者了解到，近日，有5家地炼再次获得原油进口资质。截至目前，共有18家地炼拥有原油进口资质。','1','1','2017-03-07 09:48:00','','0','','','0','{\"thumb\":\"\"}','12','0','0','0','','');INSERT INTO ts_posts ( `id`, `post_author`, `post_keywords`, `post_source`, `post_date`, `post_content`, `post_title`, `post_excerpt`, `post_status`, `comment_status`, `post_modified`, `post_content_filtered`, `post_parent`, `post_type`, `post_mime_type`, `comment_count`, `smeta`, `post_hits`, `post_like`, `istop`, `recommended`, `page_tpl`, `page_tpls` ) VALUES  ('434','1','新形势下中国能源行业发展展望','','2017-03-13 10:00:11','<p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;font-size: 14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　日前，中国能源网研究中心发布了《</span>China5e<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">能源行业研究季报</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">(2015</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年第一季</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">)</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">》。季报对我国石油、天然气、煤炭、电力等能源行业发展现状、重要政策和重大事件进行了梳理和分析，并对能源行业未来发展进行展望。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;font-size: 14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　其中，油气行业及电力行业发展展望摘选如下，希望能够给行业人士提供借鉴。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;font-size: 14px\">　　1.<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">油气行业发展展望</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;font-size: 14px\">　　1.1<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">石油</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;font-size: 14px\">　　(1)<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">尽管目前低油形势何时结束存在争议，但业内专家普遍预计，国际原油价格在</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">2015</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年继续颓势的可能性较大。中国能源网研究中心针对</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">2015</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年国际油价走势进行的调查问卷也支持同样的观点，调研结果如下图所示：</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;font-size: 14px\">&nbsp;<img src=\"http://mh.tuishang.com.cn/data/upload/ueditor/20170313/58c5fccb9c383.png\" title=\"石油-10290235811.png\" alt=\"石油-10290235811.png\"/></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;font-size: 14px\">5e<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">问卷调查结果</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">(</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">参与调查行业人士：</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">105</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">人</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">)</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">，资料来源：中国能源网研究中心 </span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;font-size: 14px\">　　(2)<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">由于油田开工率降低和钻进平台数量减少，短期内原油价格或将小幅反弹，但预计中期局面依然疲软。如，美国原油产量在众多大型油企削减资本开支以及钻井平台数量持续下降的情况下有所回落，但由于国际供过于求的基本局面仍无大的变化，加上原油库存的增加和部分国家产油的增多，预计短期维持在</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">60</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">美元上下。中期来看，美国和伊朗的原油将有可能更多流入国际市场，而</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">2015</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年主要产油国加大能源政策</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">(</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">主要降低能耗，提高能源效率</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">)</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">调整力度，将进一步抑制原油需求的增长，国际原油供过于求的程度有可能进一步加重，国际油价可能依然无法走出目前的颓势。受国际油价影响，短期内国内成品油有小幅反弹的可能，但中期来看价格整体依然将保持低位。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;font-size: 14px\">　　(3)<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">受油气资产贬值影响，我国资本或将积极参与石油行业收购和重组。纵观历次油价下跌，无不带来石油行业的并购和重组潮。</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">2015</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年也不例外。受国际油价持续走低的影响，石油企业的利润大幅下降，融资也将受到极大影响，比如北美的非常规油气田，可能是未来被收购的重点地区。而石油行业的不景气，却促进了我国民营资本的参与油气行业收购的积极性。我国正在倡导“一带一路”建设，鼓励沿线各国加强能源等领域的合作，这将促进我国资本</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">(</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">包括国有和民营</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">)</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">积极参与中亚油气产业的整合。但是部分国际油气企业认为油气资产有进一步贬值的可能，因此目前是否是收购的最佳时机还是“仁者见仁、智者见智”。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;font-size: 14px\">　　(4)<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">新电改方案落地之后，石油行业改革方案有望出台。自十八届三中全会提出全面深化体制改革以来，各行各业都在推进深化体制改革进程。当前，新的电改方案已经落地，油气改革方案成为行业新的期待。而关于改革方向存在巨大争议，中国能源网研究中心以及多位资深行业专家认为改革矿权制度</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">(</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">增强上游领域的竞争</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">)</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">、管道业务独立、油服公司从母体剥离等是未来改革发展的方向，但同样存在“两桶油合并”等相反的改革声音。随着讨论的深入，石油行业改革方案有望在不久的将来出台。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;font-size: 14px\">　　1.2<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">天然气</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;font-size: 14px\">　　(1)2015<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年天然气消费增速低迷的趋势恐难扭转。在行业发展综合分析时已经指出，</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">2015</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年一季度天然气表观消费量增速下降幅度很大。如果这种状况得不到改善，</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">2015</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年天然气消费增速将比</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">2014</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年的</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">8.9%</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">更低。多数用气行业对气价极为敏感，部分行业的价格承受能力已逼近极限，甚至出现了“气改煤”的反常现象</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">(</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">虽然</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">2015</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">4</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">1</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">日起非居民天然气门站价格并轨，但是由于存量气占比较大，因此市场刺激作用受到限制</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">)</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">。在需求不旺的情势下，</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">2015</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年天然气发展目标实现的难度也相应加大。为了提振需求，一方面政府要改变管道环节收益率过高的现状，逐渐平抑天然气价格，另一方面政府要推出支持天然气下游利用的政策以推动天然气市场的健康持续发展。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;font-size: 14px\">　　(2)<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">我国天然气价格的市场化将加速。目前，我国天然气价格市场化已经迈出重要一步，如非居民用天然气价格存量气和增量气已经并轨。在天然气价格改革领域，一直存在着完全放开非居民用天然气价格管理的声音。不管是先在沿海等经济发达地区实行全面放开，还是一步到位全国全面放开，市场化的改革方向可谓是行业内的共识。此外，未来上海石油天然气交易中心如果能够正式运行，将有力促进供应与需求直接对接，有可能形成管道气交易、</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">LNG</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">交割，“招标采购”，“供应商拍卖”，仓单，互换</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">(SWAP)</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">等多样化的交易机制。虽然上海石油天然气交易中心正式运行推迟，而且正式运行后会面临交易量、交易主体是否充足、是否积极等各种问题和挑战，但作为重要的国家战略，上海石油天然气交易中心正式运行只是一个时间问题。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;font-size: 14px\">　　(3)<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">从长期来看，我国与世界天然气价格联动性将增强。中俄天然气东线已经签署供应协议，西线也签署框架合作协议，亚洲和欧洲两大市场将通过中俄和中亚管道建立联系</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">;</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">美国的</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">LNG</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">出口到亚洲后，与亨利中心价格挂钩的定价机制将引入亚洲，对主要与油价挂钩的亚洲天然气市场价格机制形成挑战</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">;</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">更加灵活的</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">LNG</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">现货供应在全球供应占比将逐渐增加。以上发展趋势都将促进全球三大天然气市场价格的联动，甚至导致美、欧、亚三地价差的逐步缩小。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;font-size: 14px\">　　1.3<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">非常规天然气</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;font-size: 14px\">　　(1)<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">四川、重庆将继续引领我国页岩气产业。有预测表明，若在川渝两地设立试页岩气勘探开发验区并试行区块开放、多元开发等政策，</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">5-10</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年内仅在川渝试验区内就页岩气产量就可以突破</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">1000</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">亿立方米</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">/</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;font-size: 14px\">　　(2)<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">第三轮页岩气探矿权招标依然充满不确定性。考虑到客观实际，有专家建议将页岩气探矿权中标企业</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">3</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年的探矿期延长至</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">5</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年甚至更长。这一建议能否在第二轮探矿权中标区块中加以应用目前还不得而知，但这是第三轮探矿权招标时不得不考虑的因素。从目前多方披露的信息来看，页岩气第三轮招标区块规模和质量有望提高，但招标时间依然不确定。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;font-size: 14px\">　　(3)<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">煤制气项目环评压力加大，项目上马周期或将延长。基于我国节能环保的新形势，以及苏新煤制气项目环评被否，国家监管部门对煤制气相关企业环评力度加大属大势所趋。煤制气环评力度的加大，将促进煤制气企业对发展节能环保相关技术的重视，同时也将进一步延缓煤制气项目的上马。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;font-size: 14px\">　　(4)<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">煤层气未来发展谨慎乐观。由于煤层气发展目标多年来一直未能实现，这对投资者的信心造成了严重的负面影响。但国家始终高度重视煤层气的发展，致力于推动煤层气的科学发展和合理布局，在国家大力倡导节能环保和煤炭产业清洁利用的背景下，在《煤层气勘探开发行动计划》指引下，未来煤层气的发展谨慎乐观。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;font-size: 14px\">　　2.<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">电力行业发展展望</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;font-size: 14px\">　　2.1<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">未来电改发展方向展望</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;font-size: 14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　《意见》还只是一个指导性文件，如何落实还需要关注和研究。目前有如下几个方面需要优先解决：</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;font-size: 14px\">　　(1)<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">完善法规政策。电力体制改革要有序推进、确保平稳健康发展，首先需要完善法律法规，有法律依据，才能进入实质操作阶段。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;font-size: 14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　我国目前实行的《电力法》已远不能适应当前的电力工业环境，在当前电力体制改革推进的关键时刻，首先要修订完善《电力法》及其配套法规，真正体现依法治国的执政理念。旧有的《电力法》中有很多法规与国家出台的政策相抵触，按照《电力法》规定，</span>“一个供电营业区内只设立一个供电营业机构。”这意味，分布式光伏项目直接售电属于违法。法规政策的缺失将使得监管无从谈起，改革的效力将被削弱，更有可能会加大权利寻租的空间。</span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;font-size: 14px\">　　(2)<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">强化电力系统整体规划。随着第一个配套文件的出台，大规模可再生能源并网导致的电力稳定性问题将迫切需要解决，如何在规划层面和运行层面同时实现电力系统总体优化是面临的最有挑战性的问题。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;font-size: 14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　要加强电力系统整体规划，应当实施综合资源规划模式，就是要充分运用智能电网技术，实施</span>“源<span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">-</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">网</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">-</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">荷</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">-</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">储”协调规划和运行的体制机制政策，通过微网、智能配电网等技术以及需求侧管理机制，实现各种发电资源以及发输配售四部分之间的协调互补，横向源源互补，纵向源网荷储协调。只有在这种规划机制下，才能降低“双侧随机性”对电力系统安全稳定运行的不利影响，同时实现清洁能源的高效开发利用。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;font-size: 14px\">　　(3)<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">构建合理的售电市场规则。构建有效的售电侧电力市场是决定此次电改是否能够成功的关键，也是最为严峻的挑战。《意见》指出，要稳步推进售电侧改革，有序向社会资本放开配售电业务。有序向社会资本放开配售电业务标志着我国一直以来电网公司的传统模式被打破。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;font-size: 14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　通过售电侧市场的逐步开放，构建多元化的售电主体，从而扩大用户的选择权，形成</span>“多买方<span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">-</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">多卖方”的市场格局，并构筑“放开两头、监管中间”的行业结构，对提高市场效率、服务质量以及实现社会福利最大化的目标意义重大。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;font-size: 14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　但是，售电侧市场该如何放开，在售电侧放开的基础上如何刺激用户提高能效、如何有效地实施需求侧管理等等问题，都需要引起关注和研究。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;font-size: 14px\">　　2.2<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">中短期电力发展形势不容乐观</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;font-size: 14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　中电联年初预测</span>2015<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年用电量增长</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">4%-5%</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">，在随后的一季度预测中调低了增长预期为</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">3%-5%</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">，显示了权威机构对电力需求的担忧。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;font-size: 14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　结合今年我国预计</span>GDP<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">增长</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">7.0%</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">来看，全社会用电增幅将很难超过去年。去年我国</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">GDP</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">增长</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">7.4%</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">，全社会用电量增长</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">3.8%</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;font-size: 14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　当前，用电量增长存在着一些有利因素。</span>3<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月份，国家出于稳增长的考虑出台了一系列措施，国际社会上也出现了一些对中国经济有利的因素将缓解一季度用电量增速过低的窘境。具体来说，国家四月份出台政策调低了煤电上网电价以及电力销售电价，这项措施一定程度上缓解了工业用电大户的压力，调低的工业用电价格对于增加占总用电量</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">70%</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">的工业用户来说是一个积极的作用。同时在金融领域，国家进一步调低银行存贷款利率，为企业减负，释放企业活力</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">;</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">股票市场近期非常活跃，上市公司融资能力也得到加强，总的来说，企业负担减轻，有助于提高企业的生产积极性。国际环境上来看，欧洲央行</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">3</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月宣布新的</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">QE</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">计划，</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">3</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月开始实施每月购买</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">600</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">亿欧元资产至</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">2016</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">9</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月，此举是欧洲摆脱欧债危机一个积极的举措，将有助于提升作为中国第一大出口地区的消费能力，缓解目前国内订单下降的困难局面。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;font-size: 14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　然而，全社会用电量增幅依然不太乐观，我国电力结构调整，国内外消费不振等因素将持续存在。从大环境来看，</span>2015<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年新环保法开始施行，同时三月我国新一轮电改拉开序幕，客观上要求我国产业结构从目前的高耗能高污染低效率状态做出改变，这从一季度我国单位能耗下降可以看出端倪</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">;</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">从供需关系来看，目前用电量增幅过低的问题主要是国际增长放缓以及国内需求调整不到位所致。国际上看我国主要贸易国美国、日本和欧盟近期经济都处于低迷状态。美联储发布报告显示美国一季度经济发展几乎处于停滞状态，日本工业产出连续两个月下滑，国内消费低迷，欧洲虽然推出新的刺激政策，但总体形势依然不乐观，综合考虑我国外部需求低迷未见好转。国内经济数据也并不乐观，</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">PPI</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">一季度一直处于枯荣线附近，</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">CPI</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">三月环比下降，通货紧缩压力依然存在。总体需求低迷是目前用电量增幅过低的重要原因，长期来看，全球性的需求低迷将在一定时期内存在。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;font-size: 14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　综合以上两方面来看，</span>2015<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年以后全社会用电量增长缓慢将成为常态，本年增长</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">3%-5%</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">的压力很大，用电量增幅有可能低于</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">3%</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;font-size: 14px\">　　2.3<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">太阳能发电或将迎来高速发展期</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;font-size: 14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　在节能减排的背景下，作为技术最为成熟和最为居民接受的清洁能源，太阳能发电或将迎来高速发展期。</span>2015<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年两会前，一部《穹顶之下》引爆了人们对于节能环保的关注，在这个大背景下，发展非化石能源特别是分布式光伏成为一个可行的选项。目前全球光伏组件有半数以上来自中国，无论是技术和产能，中国都有着深厚的基础。最新的电改文件中，拥有分布式电源的用户可以参与组建售电市场，目前国内分布式电源方面，分布式光伏的技术最为成熟，民众接受度比较高，同时新的市场融资模式也在不断创新，根据《能源发展战略行动计划</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">(2014-2020)</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">》提出，到</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">2020</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年我国清洁能源占一次能源比例为</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">14%</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">。要实现这一目标，需要大规模发展风电和太阳能产业。因此，可以预见近期风电和太阳能还会得到政府从政策和规划上的大力支持。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;font-size: 14px\">　　2.4<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">燃气发电未来发展形势依然难言乐观</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;font-size: 14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　尽管天然气发电出现了一些有利因素，但总体来说未来发展形势依然难言乐观。一季度天然气并轨方案下发，四月起施行新的天然气门站价格，总体来说新的天然气价更有利于用气企业。同时对于天然气发电上网电价，去年年末下发的《关于规范天然气发电上网电价管理有关问题的通知》中规定建立气、电价格联动机制，当气价出现较大变化时，天然气发电上网电价应及时调整，但最高电价不得超过当地燃煤发电上网标杆电价或当地电网企业平均购电价格每千瓦时</span>0.35<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">元。结合天然气并轨后气价，天然气分布式发电相对其他能源将具有一定经济性，有利于缓解目前分布式能源产业的尴尬状态。尽管如此，但总体上来说天然气价格依然偏高，加之未来国际油价</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">(</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">以及</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">LNG</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">价格</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">)</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">走势存在很大不确定性，发电企业在投资燃气发电项目方面依然谨慎。</span></span></p><p><br/></p>','新形势下中国能源行业发展展望','　　日前，中国能源网研究中心发布了《China5e能源行业研究季报(2015年第一季)》。季报对我国石油、天然气、煤炭、电力等能源行业发展现状、重要政策和重大事件进行了梳理和分析，并对能源行业未来发展进行展望。','1','1','2017-03-13 09:56:47','','0','','','0','{\"thumb\":\"\"}','5','0','0','0','','');INSERT INTO ts_posts ( `id`, `post_author`, `post_keywords`, `post_source`, `post_date`, `post_content`, `post_title`, `post_excerpt`, `post_status`, `comment_status`, `post_modified`, `post_content_filtered`, `post_parent`, `post_type`, `post_mime_type`, `comment_count`, `smeta`, `post_hits`, `post_like`, `istop`, `recommended`, `page_tpl`, `page_tpls` ) VALUES  ('439','1','','','2017-03-13 16:01:24','<p>　　<span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;; font-size: medium; line-height: 21px; text-indent: 32px;\">日前，闽海集团广东塘西加油站的一名女职工得到公司爱心基金两万元的救助金，有效地缓解了这个因病致贫家庭的经济困难。这是闽海集团爱心基金成立后第一位得到救助的员工。</span><br style=\"outline: none; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;; font-size: medium; line-height: 21px; text-indent: 32px; white-space: normal;\"/><br style=\"outline: none; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;; font-size: medium; line-height: 21px; text-indent: 32px; white-space: normal;\"/><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;; font-size: medium; line-height: 21px; text-indent: 32px;\">　　闽海集团广东塘西加油站的这名女职工，因丈夫患纵膈恶性肿瘤无法工作，长期在家休养，2013年9月至2014年1月期间，先后进行肿瘤切除手术及四次化疗，治疗费用超出家庭负荷，生活困难。</span><br style=\"outline: none; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;; font-size: medium; line-height: 21px; text-indent: 32px; white-space: normal;\"/><br style=\"outline: none; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;; font-size: medium; line-height: 21px; text-indent: 32px; white-space: normal;\"/><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;; font-size: medium; line-height: 21px; text-indent: 32px;\">　　公司领导得知这一情况后，立刻启动闽海爱心基金帮扶程序，将两万元救助金送到员工手中，为员工带去公司的祝福和关怀。在此之前，加油站同事已经陆续为该名员工捐助7000余元。</span><br style=\"outline: none; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;; font-size: medium; line-height: 21px; text-indent: 32px; white-space: normal;\"/><br style=\"outline: none; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;; font-size: medium; line-height: 21px; text-indent: 32px; white-space: normal;\"/><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;; font-size: medium; line-height: 21px; text-indent: 32px;\">　　据悉，闽海集团每年组织职工开展一次爱心捐款活动，捐款全部纳入公司爱心基金，援助因重大疾病或意外事件致使家庭经济困难的公司职工。爱心基金为公司职工构筑起了一个团结友爱、互相帮助的温馨大家庭，为增强企业凝聚力发挥了积极作用。</span></p>','员工家属罹患癌症 闽海爱心基金首次启用','　　闽海集团每年组织职工开展一次爱心捐款活动，捐款全部纳入公司爱心基金，援助因重大疾病或意外事件致使家庭经济困难的公司职工。爱心基金为公司职工构筑起了一个团结友爱、互相帮助的温馨大家庭，为增强企业凝聚力发挥了积极作用。','1','1','2014-04-15 00:00:00','','0','','','0','{\"thumb\":\"\"}','5','0','0','0','','');INSERT INTO ts_posts ( `id`, `post_author`, `post_keywords`, `post_source`, `post_date`, `post_content`, `post_title`, `post_excerpt`, `post_status`, `comment_status`, `post_modified`, `post_content_filtered`, `post_parent`, `post_type`, `post_mime_type`, `comment_count`, `smeta`, `post_hits`, `post_like`, `istop`, `recommended`, `page_tpl`, `page_tpls` ) VALUES  ('435','1','供应过剩局面缓解将带动油价回升','','2017-03-13 10:03:33','<p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;font-size: 14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><img src=\"http://mh.tuishang.com.cn/data/upload/ueditor/20170313/58c5fdd56aa0e.png\" title=\"油价回升-11115736530.png\" alt=\"油价回升-11115736530.png\"/>　　</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;font-size: 14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">&nbsp; &nbsp; 世界银行日前发布的最新《大宗商品市场前景》报告预计，由于供应持续高企，包括能源、金属和农业原材料在内的工业类大宗商品在新兴市场和发展中经济体增长前景疲软，</span>2016<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年世界银行跟踪的所有主要大宗商品指标预计都会下跌。不过，报告认为，在市场情绪改善和美元走弱的情况下，全球原油市场供应过剩局面将逐渐缓解。世界银行据此预测，</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">2016</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年原油价格将由此前预计的每桶</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">37</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">美元调高至每桶</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">41</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">美元。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;font-size: 14px\">　　“预计今年市场在经历一段时间的供应过剩之后会重新恢复平衡，随之能源类大宗商品价格将会小幅上升。”世界银行高级经济学家、《大宗商品市场前景》报告主要作者约翰·巴菲斯则表示：“如果石油输出国组织<span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">(</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">欧佩克</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">)</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">大幅增产，且非欧佩克国家减产速度低于预期，能源价格就有可能进一步下跌。”目前，在伊拉克和尼日利亚原油生产中断和非欧佩克国家</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">(</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">主要是美国</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">)</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">页岩油减产之后，</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">4</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月份原油价格从</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">1</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月中旬每桶</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">25</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">美元的低点回弹至每桶</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">40</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">美元。不过，在</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">4</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月中旬的会议上关于主要产油国冻结产量的提议未能实现。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;font-size: 14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　世界银行报告预计，包括原油、天然气和煤炭在内的能源价格预计将比去年下跌</span>19.3%<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">。这一预计比</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">1</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月份预测的下滑</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">24.7%</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">有所回升。非能源类大宗商品如金属矿产、农产品和化肥预计今年下跌</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">5.1%</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">，跌幅大于</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">1</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月份预测的</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">3.7%</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">。此外，报告预计未来一年金属价格下跌</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">8.2%</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">，低于</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">1</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月份预测的</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">10.2%</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">，这也反映出对中国需求增长走强的预期。农产品价格下跌幅度预计将超过</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">1</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月份的预测，原因是预计今年大多数粮油类大宗商品又是一个丰收年，能源成本下降也拉低了农业类大宗商品价格。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;font-size: 14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　报告指出，大宗商品价格低迷削弱了很多资源富有国家的增长前景，这些国家在本世纪前</span>10<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年大宗商品繁荣期出现勘探、投资和生产猛增的情况。由于目前的原油和金属价格比</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">2011</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年初的峰值水平低</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">50%</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">至</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">70%</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">，一些新兴市场和发展中国家已经叫停或推迟了自然资源开发项目。世界银行发展预测局局长阿伊汗·高斯认为，这些项目延迟可能对难以承受此类挫折的国家带来不利影响，只有增强透明度，提高政府效率，改善宏观经济结构，才有可能缓解这类不利因素的干扰。受到影响的国家可能选择等到价格开始回升后再启动新的自然资源开发项目。</span></span></p><p><br/></p>','供应过剩局面缓解将带动油价回升','    ​世界银行日前发布的最新《大宗商品市场前景》报告预计，由于供应持续高企，包括能源、金属和农业原材料在内的工业类大宗商品在新兴市场和发展中经济体增长前景疲软，2016年世界银行跟踪的所有主要大宗商品指标预计都会下跌。','1','1','2017-03-13 10:02:26','','0','','','0','{\"thumb\":\"\"}','3','0','0','0','','');INSERT INTO ts_posts ( `id`, `post_author`, `post_keywords`, `post_source`, `post_date`, `post_content`, `post_title`, `post_excerpt`, `post_status`, `comment_status`, `post_modified`, `post_content_filtered`, `post_parent`, `post_type`, `post_mime_type`, `comment_count`, `smeta`, `post_hits`, `post_like`, `istop`, `recommended`, `page_tpl`, `page_tpls` ) VALUES  ('436','1','石油消费峰值已渐行渐近？ ','','2017-03-13 10:11:31','<p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;font-size: 14px\">　　4<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">25</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">日，普华永道发布《</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">2015</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年中国清洁能源及技术行业投资研究报告》。报告称，未来</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">10</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年，中国能源消费将逐渐放缓增长并达到峰值。次日，</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">BP</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">公司发布《</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">BP2035</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">世界能源展望》中文版。报告指出，到</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">2035</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年中国将超过美国成为全球最大的石油消费国和可再生能源增量最大的国家。综合这两则消息，我们是否可以据此推断：石油消费峰值已渐行渐近？我们又该如何理解石油消费峰值？</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;font-size: 14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　产量峰值无意义？</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;font-size: 14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　枯竭并非无稽之谈</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;font-size: 14px\">　　1974<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年，美国地质学家哈伯特做出预测，认为全球石油产量峰值将在</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">1995</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年到来。但是，由于新油田的不断发现与勘探开发技术的日新月异，</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">1965</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年至</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">2015</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年，全球原油产量一直在稳步上升。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;font-size: 14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　既然哈伯特的预言并未实现，且目前没有任何证据证明人类将迎来石油产量峰值，那我们为什么仍要关注石油峰值问题？</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;font-size: 14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　原因在于，无论石油产量峰值是否会到来、何时到来，我们都必须正视这样一个事实：石油资源是不可再生的，人类社会以惊人的速度持续消耗着石油；与此同时，尽管技术进步帮助我们找到越来越多的石油资源并将其开采出来，但不可否认的是，这一过程所需付出的成本与代价越来越大。而当这一成本超过现阶段经济社会所能承受的极限时，石油资源即便并未真正枯竭，对我们而言也与枯竭无异，因为高昂的石油消费无法继续支撑经济社会的进一步发展，人类社会即将迎来石油消费峰值。正如那句名言所说：</span>“石器时代的结束并不是因为石头用完了，石油时代同样如此。”</span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;font-size: 14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　因此，在可持续发展语境下，低碳高效的能源是为社会提供长久动力的唯一选择。实际上，人类自进入文明社会至今，能源替代便是以更高热值、更少排放、更易获取为规律的。在全球大多数国家正在进行（或已完成）工业化的今天，人类面临着比此前任何一个时期都更加严重的环境污染、资源短缺和人口膨胀问题，对低碳高效能源的需求更甚于以往。而近几年石油消费增速放缓，其本质就是石油消费峰值的临近，石油需求即将迎来拐点，被其他能源所替代。也就是说，石油消费峰值临近的背后，其实是能源替代规律使然。　　　</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-left: 0px; text-indent: 0px; text-align: center; line-height: 150%;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;font-size: 14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><img src=\"http://mh.tuishang.com.cn/data/upload/ueditor/20170313/58c5ff52578e1.jpg\" title=\"1-15171235050.jpg\" alt=\"1-15171235050.jpg\"/>　　　</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;font-size: 14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　　　　　　　　　　　　 &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 中国将减少对煤炭的依赖，能源结构显著改善</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;font-size: 14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　发达国家未达峰？</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;font-size: 14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　比例峰值早已到来</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;font-size: 14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　那么，石油消费峰值何时到来？</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;font-size: 14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　发达国家的石油消费轨迹为我们提供了极具现实意义的研究样本。由于石油在大部分发达国家是主力能源，且他们均已完成工业化，其石油消费轨迹对未来全球石油消费变化有一定参考价值。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;font-size: 14px\">　　20<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">世纪中叶，石油在发达国家得到大规模利用，并在</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">1967</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年超越煤炭成为全球消费量最大的能源。到</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">20</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">世纪</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">70</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年代，主要发达国家石油消费快速上升，日本的石油消费在其一次能源结构中的比重甚至一度高达</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">80%</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;font-size: 14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　然而，两次石油危机使发达国家的经济受到重创，他们开始反思严重依赖石油所引发的能源安全问题，并采取多种措施降低对石油的依赖。随着技术的不断进步，天然气、核能、水电及其他各类新能源在能源消费中的比例不断提高，而近年来国际油价的巨幅波动也使石油在能源消费结构中的比例进一步降低。尤其是</span>2008<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年金融危机之后，国际油价高企、核能发展受阻等都促使人们去寻找新的替代能源，全球可再生能源趁此机遇快速发展。同时，一些发达国家也把新能源产业作为新的经济增长点，给予其大量政策支持。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;font-size: 14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　从石油占一次能源消费结构的比例来看，发达国家的石油消费早在上世纪</span>70<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年代就已达峰（不同国家从</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">50%</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">到</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">80%</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">不等），此后便一路下降。如今，大部分发达国家的石油消费比重保持在</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">30%</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">至</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">40%</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">左右。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;font-size: 14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　由于当前石油消费需求的增长几乎全部来自非</span>OECD<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">国家，参考发达国家的石油消费轨迹，我们可以大致推导出这样的结论：在未来各国能源政策没有大变动的前提下，随着非</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">OECD</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">国家今后陆续完成工业化，石油消费峰值的到来基本只是时间问题。　　　</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-left: 0px; text-indent: 0px; text-align: center; line-height: 150%;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;font-size: 14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><img src=\"http://mh.tuishang.com.cn/data/upload/ueditor/20170313/58c5ff6ba7a9e.jpg\" title=\"2-15173071034.jpg\" alt=\"2-15173071034.jpg\"/>　　　　</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;font-size: 14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　　　　　　　　　　　　　　 &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 各类能源每年需求一览</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;font-size: 14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　未雨绸缪待何时？</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;font-size: 14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　产业转型不可盲目</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;font-size: 14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　石油行业长达半个多世纪的繁荣，让很多人忽视了能源行业发展的历史大棋局，轻视了技术创新在释放资源的巨大潜力。如今在低油价下，石油消费非但没有重现繁荣，反而出现明显的增速放缓。对于整个行业来说，这本身就是一记警钟。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;font-size: 14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　经济学认为，当不可再生资源的价格上升至一定水平时，必然会刺激相关替代品的开发与生产，其价格会因替代品的大量生产而下降，甚至低于原来的价格水平。这便是著名的</span>“霍特林原理”。</span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;font-size: 14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　尽管石油在目前看来属于最不易被替代的那一类不可再生资源，但不能忽视的是，第一次石油危机催生节能技术的突破，导致发达国家石油消费达峰后便迅速进入下行通道；前几年的高油价推动新能源产业快速崛起，如今已在全球能源体系中占有一席之地。历史和现实都无比清晰地告诉我们，石油对于经济社会发展的不可替代性正在慢慢减弱。而对于业务结构单一的石油公司来说，若不能及早认识规律、顺应大势、加速转型，它将不可避免地被历史所淘汰。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;font-size: 14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　不过，如果说石油时代的终结是能源更迭的规律使然，那其终结却未必意味着石油行业的告别。这一点可参考煤炭的发展。作为第一次工业革命的主力能源，煤炭虽然已完成其历史使命，但由于储备丰富和使用经济的特征，在能源多元化的今天，煤炭依然具备顽强的生命力。尤其是在中国、印度等发展中国家的能源结构中，煤炭依然是最主要的能源需求来源。虽然目前煤炭产业整体陷入困境，但其困境源于行业产能严重过剩，这恰恰反映出行业内部结构调整与产业升级的重要性与必要性。　</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-left: 0px; text-indent: 0px; text-align: center; line-height: 150%;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;font-size: 14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><img src=\"http://mh.tuishang.com.cn/data/upload/ueditor/20170313/58c5ff881a851.jpg\" title=\"3-15173537988.jpg\" alt=\"3-15173537988.jpg\"/>　　　　　　　　　</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;font-size: 14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　　　　　　　　　　　　 &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 化石能源仍是为世界经济提供动力的主导能源</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;font-size: 14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　因此，对于石油行业与企业来说，既要认识到石油消费峰值的必然性，又要对石油在短期内的不可替代性有清晰客观的理解。尤其是在尚未完成工业化的发展中国家，石油行业还有可观的发展空间。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;font-size: 14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　中国作为世界上少数几个没有完成由薪柴到煤炭、由煤炭到油气为主两大转变的国家之一，其未来油气消费还有很大的增长空间。根据第一财经研究院的研究，由于中国私人轿车拥有量相比发达国家还有很大提升空间，原油消费与经济发展还会在一定时期内保持强相关性；天然气在短期内也不会与经济增长脱钩，反而会随着治理空气污染和能源转型的努力成为新的快速增长的化石能源。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;font-size: 14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　因此，石油行业与企业应充分利用这一时间和空间，一方面要不断壮大自己，为转型做好资本积累，另一方面要把眼光放长远，把握机遇，及早谋划，占领先机。要立足传统油气资源的开发技术与市场布局，在提高生产运营能效、提供清洁高效产品，以及天然气业务等方面加速转型，为未来早做准备。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;font-size: 14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　同时，石油行业和企业还需根据国家政策动向与市场价格波动来配置传统能源与新能源，制定科学的新能源发展战略。目前，国家正在大力推广新能源汽车，石油企业可凭借自身较高的市场占有率和销售渠道，利用加油站发展充电桩业务，利用油气管网发展无线充电业务等，借助政策东风使新能源能够</span>“反哺”传统油气业务。待油价反弹时，石油企业应利用油气业务的高利润加快布局新能源，为未来的能源更迭奠定基础。</span></p><p><br/></p>','石油消费峰值已渐行渐近？ 石油企业应如何未雨绸缪','　　4月25日，普华永道发布《2015年中国清洁能源及技术行业投资研究报告》。报告称，未来10年，中国能源消费将逐渐放缓增长并达到峰值。次日，BP公司发布《BP2035世界能源展望》中文版。','1','1','2017-03-12 10:08:00','','0','','','0','{\"thumb\":\"20170313\\/58c5ffa494971.jpg\"}','9','0','0','0','','');INSERT INTO ts_posts ( `id`, `post_author`, `post_keywords`, `post_source`, `post_date`, `post_content`, `post_title`, `post_excerpt`, `post_status`, `comment_status`, `post_modified`, `post_content_filtered`, `post_parent`, `post_type`, `post_mime_type`, `comment_count`, `smeta`, `post_hits`, `post_like`, `istop`, `recommended`, `page_tpl`, `page_tpls` ) VALUES  ('437','1','','','2017-03-13 11:06:29','<p style=\"font-size: 14px; font-family: simsun; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-stretch: normal; line-height: 25px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">岗位职责：<br/>1、根据招聘需求，选择招聘渠道，发布及更新招聘信息；<br/>2、做好各部门人员需求调查，汇总，执行招聘计划，维护拓展招聘渠道；<br/>3、收集简历，聘前测试和简历的初步筛选，安排面试。<br/>任职要求：<br/>1. 本科以上学历，人力资源管理、管理类相关专业优先考虑；<br/>2. 熟练使用办公软件；<br/>3. 具备良好的沟通和协调能力，工作责任心强，亲和力佳；<br/>4. 高度的敬业精神及高涨的工作激情，工作态度积极乐观。</p><h1 style=\"font-size: 14px; font-family: simsun; margin: 12px 0px 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); line-height: 25px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">工作地址</h1><h2 style=\"font-size: 14px; font-family: simsun; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-weight: 400; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); line-height: 25px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">福州市五一中路88号平安大厦11层</h2><p><br/></p>','招聘主管','招聘','1','1','2017-03-13 10:54:48','','0','','','0','{\"thumb\":\"\"}','10','0','0','0','','');INSERT INTO ts_posts ( `id`, `post_author`, `post_keywords`, `post_source`, `post_date`, `post_content`, `post_title`, `post_excerpt`, `post_status`, `comment_status`, `post_modified`, `post_content_filtered`, `post_parent`, `post_type`, `post_mime_type`, `comment_count`, `smeta`, `post_hits`, `post_like`, `istop`, `recommended`, `page_tpl`, `page_tpls` ) VALUES  ('438','1','','','2017-03-13 15:48:13','<p>12456</p>','123','123456','1','1','2017-03-13 15:47:47','','0','','','0','{\"thumb\":\"\"}','0','0','0','0','','');INSERT INTO ts_posts ( `id`, `post_author`, `post_keywords`, `post_source`, `post_date`, `post_content`, `post_title`, `post_excerpt`, `post_status`, `comment_status`, `post_modified`, `post_content_filtered`, `post_parent`, `post_type`, `post_mime_type`, `comment_count`, `smeta`, `post_hits`, `post_like`, `istop`, `recommended`, `page_tpl`, `page_tpls` ) VALUES  ('440','1','','','2017-03-13 16:38:47','<p><span style=\"outline: none; border: 0px; padding: 0px; font-style: inherit; margin: 0px; font-family: inherit; font-size: medium; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\">　　4月18日下午，闽海爱心基金委员会召开工作会议，全体委员对闽海集团泉州泉安加油站上报的一位员工的申报材料进行了审议。<br style=\"outline: none;\"/></span><span style=\"outline: none; border: 0px; padding: 0px; font-style: inherit; margin: 0px; font-family: inherit; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: medium; line-height: 24px; text-indent: 24pt;\"><br style=\"outline: none;\"/></span></p><p><span style=\"outline: none; border: 0px; padding: 0px; font-style: inherit; margin: 0px; font-family: inherit; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: medium; line-height: 24px; text-indent: 24pt;\">　　这位已在油站工作五年的女员工是家中独女，父亲是家里唯一的男劳力，却因早年身体严重贫血从原单位退休，常年在家养病。母亲在工厂做工，奶奶已经退休，四口之家仅靠这3个人微薄的工资收入维持，除去日常开支和给父亲买药，家庭收入所剩无几。</span></p><p><span style=\"outline: none; border: 0px; padding: 0px; font-style: inherit; margin: 0px; font-family: inherit; font-size: medium; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\"><br style=\"outline: none;\"/>　　3月初，父亲突发疾病住院，在ICU病房昏迷不醒，短短几天时间里，住院费、治疗费就花光了家中所有的积蓄和向亲戚朋友借来的3万元，虽经多方急救,最终不治身亡。<br style=\"outline: none;\"/><br style=\"outline: none;\"/>　　83岁的奶奶因失去独子悲伤过度，生活无法自理，母亲只能辞职在家照顾老人。全家人的生计重担落在了这个年轻女孩子的身上，生活艰难，无力偿还外债，为减轻家庭负担，她向员工爱心基金提出救助申请。<br style=\"outline: none;\"/><br style=\"outline: none;\"/>　　爱心基金工作小组收到救助申请后，立刻展开了核实工作，并尽快组织了爱心基金各位委员召开会议对其救助申请进行审议。&nbsp;<br style=\"outline: none;\"/><br style=\"outline: none;\"/>　　经过委员会认真讨论，到会委员一致同意对其及其家庭提供救助，根据其工资及家庭收入的实际情况，资助两万元元。</span></p><p><span style=\"outline: none; border: 0px; padding: 0px; font-style: inherit; margin: 0px; font-family: inherit; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\"><span style=\"outline: none; border: 0px; padding: 0px; font-style: inherit; margin: 0px; font-family: inherit; font-size: medium;\"><br style=\"outline: none;\"/></span><span style=\"outline: none; border: 0px; padding: 0px; font-style: inherit; margin: 0px; font-family: inherit; font-size: medium;\">　　闽海爱心基金是公司领导大力倡导，广大职工积极响应建立起来的，贯彻“以人为本”的经营理念，使闽海员工在困难时候能够得到救助，感受到闽海大家庭的温暖，真正营造一个团结互助的氛围。</span></span><br style=\"outline: none;\"/></p><p><br/></p>','闽海爱心基金再助员工渡难关','　　闽海爱心基金是公司领导大力倡导，广大职工积极响应建立起来的，贯彻“以人为本”的经营理念，使闽海员工在困难时候能够得到救助，感受到闽海大家庭的温暖，真正营造一个团结互助的氛围。','1','1','2014-04-24 00:00:00','','0','','','0','{\"thumb\":\"\"}','1','0','0','0','','');INSERT INTO ts_posts ( `id`, `post_author`, `post_keywords`, `post_source`, `post_date`, `post_content`, `post_title`, `post_excerpt`, `post_status`, `comment_status`, `post_modified`, `post_content_filtered`, `post_parent`, `post_type`, `post_mime_type`, `comment_count`, `smeta`, `post_hits`, `post_like`, `istop`, `recommended`, `page_tpl`, `page_tpls` ) VALUES  ('441','1','','腾讯大闽网','2017-03-13 16:53:38','<p><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 28px; text-indent: 32px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">　　房间里，连壁钟都没有发出走动的声响，如果没有父母钉在探视窗外的身影，他也许不会察觉，城市正在新的一天中醒来。24小时输液让手臂肿胀发麻，稍微移动，痛感就会钻进皮肤。这里是造血干细胞移植病房，而今天，是他确诊急性淋巴细胞白血病第195天。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 29px; padding: 0px; line-height: 28px; font-family: 宋体, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; text-indent: 2em; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"text-indent: 2em;\">当生命仅剩下3天 我只能逆死而生</span><br/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 29px; padding: 0px; line-height: 28px; font-family: 宋体, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; text-indent: 2em; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">4月25日，林浩在家突然晕倒，白细胞数量超过常人百倍，不动手术活不过3天，母亲当场晕倒父亲赶来将其转院，医生为他下了病危通知……在这不知情的168个小时里，他最终不负众望，第一次踉跄走出鬼门关。大病临头，他一星期不愿开口说话，等待着自己从这场噩梦中苏醒，可惜却没有。进移植仓前，24岁的他发了一条朋友圈祝福亲友们中秋快乐，正如去年身体健康时一样。</p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 29px; padding: 0px; line-height: 28px; font-family: 宋体, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; text-indent: 2em; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">“我进仓已经39天了，现在要看移植的造血干细胞有没有发生排异，毕竟这是别人的”，林浩说。造血干细胞移植就是常人所理解的“移髓”，是急性淋巴细胞白血病（俗称血癌）危重阶段最有效的治疗方式。在移植前，超大剂量的化疗药进入身体，最大限度清理体内的病毒细胞，同时也引起连续的呕吐，进食变成万般煎熬的事。</p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 29px; padding: 0px; line-height: 28px; font-family: 宋体, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; text-indent: 2em; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">“如果一般化疗是炸弹的话，移植仓里的化疗就是氢弹、原子弹，我是在移植仓第18天才输入干细胞的”，然而移植后，他的身体又出现感染，即便如今已经退烧，呕吐却没有停止，身体已经疲惫不堪。在移植仓里多住一天，就意味着他举步维艰的家庭多欠下1万多元的外债。</p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 29px; padding: 0px; line-height: 28px; font-family: 宋体, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; text-indent: 2em; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">这场大病彻底搅乱他的生活，你的微薄之力，也许可以帮一个20出头的年轻人重回轨道。</p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 29px; padding: 0px; line-height: 28px; font-family: 宋体, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; text-indent: 2em; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">5年不发病就能治愈 36万医药费无着落</p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 29px; padding: 0px; line-height: 28px; font-family: 宋体, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; text-indent: 2em; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">儿子确诊之后，父亲林继辉离开岗位，和妻子全职照看病儿。每天清晨、午间、傍晚的送餐时间，他们才可以隔着移植仓玻璃看见孩子。唯一能为儿子做的三餐，他却实在难以下咽，一说起孩子吃不下饭，母亲眼眶就积起泪水，生怕孩子听见看见动摇了治疗的决心，说几句话都尽量躲进角落。</p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 29px; padding: 0px; line-height: 28px; font-family: 宋体, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; text-indent: 2em; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">母亲身体孱弱，不工作多年，父亲为照顾妻儿只能离职，家中就此失去仅剩的经济来源。林浩发病半年，60万的治疗费消耗殆尽，并不富裕的家庭已经欠债30多万。如果没有林浩公司送来的一笔救命钱，也许他还徘徊在冰凉的移植仓外，等候一线生机。</p><p>　　<span style=\"font-family: 宋体, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 28px; text-indent: 32px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">即便度过移植观察期，1年之内他依然没有远离凶险，这段至关重要时期，每周4千多元的治疗费成为家庭无力承担的巨担。而只要5年不发病，就能称之为治愈，不到30岁的他还能拥有精彩完整的人生。如今，前3年约36万的医药费却毫无着落。</span></p><p><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 28px; text-indent: 32px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">　　</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 29px; padding: 0px; line-height: 28px; font-family: 宋体, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; text-indent: 2em; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">24小时输液酸痛噬骨 仍被质疑博取同情</p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 29px; padding: 0px; line-height: 28px; font-family: 宋体, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; text-indent: 2em; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">“护士上辈子都是容嬷嬷变的，把我当紫薇了，天天扎针扎到手肿”，你想象不到，重病少年还能时常在病痛的夹缝中写日志拿自己身体打趣。实际上，他几乎24小时都在输液，有时甚至“3管齐下”，含有碳酸氢钠的吊瓶让每一秒注射都带来酸痛。他的日志里遍布带泪的笑点，病的不轻，也许就要让笑容为它减重。</p><p>　　<span style=\"font-family: 宋体, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 28px; text-indent: 32px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">独居在高冷的移植仓，手机成为治疗中温存的慰藉，亲友打来鼓励电话，发送关心信息……直到他看到几条质疑他博取同情的留言，抗病日志中断了好几天。大病之初，他悄悄向主治医生追问自己会给家庭带来多重的负担，父母和好友千方百计打消他的顾虑。他不敢成为家人生活上的拖累，现在也不忍让亲友为他蒙受不悦耳的闲言。</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 28px; text-indent: 32px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"></span><br/></p><p><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 28px; text-indent: 32px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">　　<span style=\"font-family: 宋体, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 28px; text-indent: 32px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">林浩的骨髓配型路并不平顺，他曾在中华骨髓库找到两位配对的捐赠者，一位毁捐，另一位匹配程度不高最终由父亲捐髓，4万元的体检费付之东流。</span></span></p><p><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 28px; text-indent: 32px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 28px; text-indent: 32px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">　　</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 29px; padding: 0px; line-height: 28px; font-family: 宋体, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; text-indent: 2em; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">发病前，他刚刚入职公司任会计不足7个月。确诊前一个星期，他每天下班后学车练车自学代码，同时还在准备注册会计师考试。重病半年后，他被隔离在移植仓厚重的玻璃窗内为自己加油，也许现在承受尽今生的苦难，余生就只剩幸福了。</p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 29px; padding: 0px; line-height: 28px; font-family: 宋体, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; text-indent: 2em; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">林浩抗病日志节选</p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 29px; padding: 0px; line-height: 28px; font-family: 宋体, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; text-indent: 2em; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">10.2</p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 29px; padding: 0px; line-height: 28px; font-family: 宋体, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; text-indent: 2em; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">到移植病房第4天，开始呕吐了，这是怀孕的节奏啊，加油加油。</p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 29px; padding: 0px; line-height: 28px; font-family: 宋体, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; text-indent: 2em; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">10.3</p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 29px; padding: 0px; line-height: 28px; font-family: 宋体, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; text-indent: 2em; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">看到国庆大家都去哪里玩，什么泰国的、韩国的、日本的、马代的还有台江的，而我只能待在协和，好嫉妒你们哇！</p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 29px; padding: 0px; line-height: 28px; font-family: 宋体, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; text-indent: 2em; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">10.8</p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 29px; padding: 0px; line-height: 28px; font-family: 宋体, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; text-indent: 2em; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">第十天了，过几天移植，保佑我一切都安好吧。</p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 29px; padding: 0px; line-height: 28px; font-family: 宋体, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; text-indent: 2em; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">10.14</p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 29px; padding: 0px; line-height: 28px; font-family: 宋体, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; text-indent: 2em; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">我在仓里发烧了，要加油。</p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 29px; padding: 0px; line-height: 28px; font-family: 宋体, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; text-indent: 2em; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">10.15</p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 29px; padding: 0px; line-height: 28px; font-family: 宋体, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; text-indent: 2em; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">爸爸的骨髓拿过来了，马上要输入了，加油。</p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 29px; padding: 0px; line-height: 28px; font-family: 宋体, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; text-indent: 2em; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">10.22</p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 29px; padding: 0px; line-height: 28px; font-family: 宋体, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; text-indent: 2em; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">今天主任查房说我耳朵很大，有福相。肯定会福如东海长流水，寿比南山不老松。</p><p><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 28px; text-indent: 32px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 28px; text-indent: 32px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"></span></span><br/></p>','血癌小伙写重病日志 全天输液全身剧痛怕被讽刺','这场大病彻底搅乱他的生活，你的微薄之力，也许可以帮一个20出头的年轻人重回轨道。','1','1','2017-03-13 16:40:31','','0','','','0','{\"thumb\":\"\"}','0','0','0','0','','');INSERT INTO ts_posts ( `id`, `post_author`, `post_keywords`, `post_source`, `post_date`, `post_content`, `post_title`, `post_excerpt`, `post_status`, `comment_status`, `post_modified`, `post_content_filtered`, `post_parent`, `post_type`, `post_mime_type`, `comment_count`, `smeta`, `post_hits`, `post_like`, `istop`, `recommended`, `page_tpl`, `page_tpls` ) VALUES  ('442','1','','腾讯大闽网','2017-03-13 16:54:06','<p><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 28px; text-indent: 32px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">　　房间里，连壁钟都没有发出走动的声响，如果没有父母钉在探视窗外的身影，他也许不会察觉，城市正在新的一天中醒来。24小时输液让手臂肿胀发麻，稍微移动，痛感就会钻进皮肤。这里是造血干细胞移植病房，而今天，是他确诊急性淋巴细胞白血病第195天。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 29px; padding: 0px; line-height: 28px; font-family: 宋体, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; text-indent: 2em; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"text-indent: 2em;\">当生命仅剩下3天 我只能逆死而生</span><br/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 29px; padding: 0px; line-height: 28px; font-family: 宋体, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; text-indent: 2em; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">4月25日，林浩在家突然晕倒，白细胞数量超过常人百倍，不动手术活不过3天，母亲当场晕倒父亲赶来将其转院，医生为他下了病危通知……在这不知情的168个小时里，他最终不负众望，第一次踉跄走出鬼门关。大病临头，他一星期不愿开口说话，等待着自己从这场噩梦中苏醒，可惜却没有。进移植仓前，24岁的他发了一条朋友圈祝福亲友们中秋快乐，正如去年身体健康时一样。</p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 29px; padding: 0px; line-height: 28px; font-family: 宋体, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; text-indent: 2em; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">“我进仓已经39天了，现在要看移植的造血干细胞有没有发生排异，毕竟这是别人的”，林浩说。造血干细胞移植就是常人所理解的“移髓”，是急性淋巴细胞白血病（俗称血癌）危重阶段最有效的治疗方式。在移植前，超大剂量的化疗药进入身体，最大限度清理体内的病毒细胞，同时也引起连续的呕吐，进食变成万般煎熬的事。</p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 29px; padding: 0px; line-height: 28px; font-family: 宋体, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; text-indent: 2em; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">“如果一般化疗是炸弹的话，移植仓里的化疗就是氢弹、原子弹，我是在移植仓第18天才输入干细胞的”，然而移植后，他的身体又出现感染，即便如今已经退烧，呕吐却没有停止，身体已经疲惫不堪。在移植仓里多住一天，就意味着他举步维艰的家庭多欠下1万多元的外债。</p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 29px; padding: 0px; line-height: 28px; font-family: 宋体, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; text-indent: 2em; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">这场大病彻底搅乱他的生活，你的微薄之力，也许可以帮一个20出头的年轻人重回轨道。</p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 29px; padding: 0px; line-height: 28px; font-family: 宋体, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; text-indent: 2em; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">5年不发病就能治愈 36万医药费无着落</p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 29px; padding: 0px; line-height: 28px; font-family: 宋体, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; text-indent: 2em; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">儿子确诊之后，父亲林继辉离开岗位，和妻子全职照看病儿。每天清晨、午间、傍晚的送餐时间，他们才可以隔着移植仓玻璃看见孩子。唯一能为儿子做的三餐，他却实在难以下咽，一说起孩子吃不下饭，母亲眼眶就积起泪水，生怕孩子听见看见动摇了治疗的决心，说几句话都尽量躲进角落。</p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 29px; padding: 0px; line-height: 28px; font-family: 宋体, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; text-indent: 2em; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">母亲身体孱弱，不工作多年，父亲为照顾妻儿只能离职，家中就此失去仅剩的经济来源。林浩发病半年，60万的治疗费消耗殆尽，并不富裕的家庭已经欠债30多万。如果没有林浩公司送来的一笔救命钱，也许他还徘徊在冰凉的移植仓外，等候一线生机。</p><p>　　<span style=\"font-family: 宋体, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 28px; text-indent: 32px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">即便度过移植观察期，1年之内他依然没有远离凶险，这段至关重要时期，每周4千多元的治疗费成为家庭无力承担的巨担。而只要5年不发病，就能称之为治愈，不到30岁的他还能拥有精彩完整的人生。如今，前3年约36万的医药费却毫无着落。</span></p><p><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 28px; text-indent: 32px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">　　</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 29px; padding: 0px; line-height: 28px; font-family: 宋体, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; text-indent: 2em; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">24小时输液酸痛噬骨 仍被质疑博取同情</p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 29px; padding: 0px; line-height: 28px; font-family: 宋体, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; text-indent: 2em; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">“护士上辈子都是容嬷嬷变的，把我当紫薇了，天天扎针扎到手肿”，你想象不到，重病少年还能时常在病痛的夹缝中写日志拿自己身体打趣。实际上，他几乎24小时都在输液，有时甚至“3管齐下”，含有碳酸氢钠的吊瓶让每一秒注射都带来酸痛。他的日志里遍布带泪的笑点，病的不轻，也许就要让笑容为它减重。</p><p>　　<span style=\"font-family: 宋体, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 28px; text-indent: 32px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">独居在高冷的移植仓，手机成为治疗中温存的慰藉，亲友打来鼓励电话，发送关心信息……直到他看到几条质疑他博取同情的留言，抗病日志中断了好几天。大病之初，他悄悄向主治医生追问自己会给家庭带来多重的负担，父母和好友千方百计打消他的顾虑。他不敢成为家人生活上的拖累，现在也不忍让亲友为他蒙受不悦耳的闲言。</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 28px; text-indent: 32px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"></span><br/></p><p><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 28px; text-indent: 32px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">　　<span style=\"font-family: 宋体, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 28px; text-indent: 32px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">林浩的骨髓配型路并不平顺，他曾在中华骨髓库找到两位配对的捐赠者，一位毁捐，另一位匹配程度不高最终由父亲捐髓，4万元的体检费付之东流。</span></span></p><p><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 28px; text-indent: 32px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 28px; text-indent: 32px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">　　</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 29px; padding: 0px; line-height: 28px; font-family: 宋体, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; text-indent: 2em; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">发病前，他刚刚入职公司任会计不足7个月。确诊前一个星期，他每天下班后学车练车自学代码，同时还在准备注册会计师考试。重病半年后，他被隔离在移植仓厚重的玻璃窗内为自己加油，也许现在承受尽今生的苦难，余生就只剩幸福了。</p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 29px; padding: 0px; line-height: 28px; font-family: 宋体, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; text-indent: 2em; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">林浩抗病日志节选</p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 29px; padding: 0px; line-height: 28px; font-family: 宋体, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; text-indent: 2em; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">10.2</p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 29px; padding: 0px; line-height: 28px; font-family: 宋体, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; text-indent: 2em; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">到移植病房第4天，开始呕吐了，这是怀孕的节奏啊，加油加油。</p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 29px; padding: 0px; line-height: 28px; font-family: 宋体, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; text-indent: 2em; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">10.3</p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 29px; padding: 0px; line-height: 28px; font-family: 宋体, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; text-indent: 2em; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">看到国庆大家都去哪里玩，什么泰国的、韩国的、日本的、马代的还有台江的，而我只能待在协和，好嫉妒你们哇！</p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 29px; padding: 0px; line-height: 28px; font-family: 宋体, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; text-indent: 2em; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">10.8</p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 29px; padding: 0px; line-height: 28px; font-family: 宋体, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; text-indent: 2em; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">第十天了，过几天移植，保佑我一切都安好吧。</p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 29px; padding: 0px; line-height: 28px; font-family: 宋体, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; text-indent: 2em; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">10.14</p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 29px; padding: 0px; line-height: 28px; font-family: 宋体, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; text-indent: 2em; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">我在仓里发烧了，要加油。</p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 29px; padding: 0px; line-height: 28px; font-family: 宋体, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; text-indent: 2em; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">10.15</p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 29px; padding: 0px; line-height: 28px; font-family: 宋体, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; text-indent: 2em; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">爸爸的骨髓拿过来了，马上要输入了，加油。</p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 29px; padding: 0px; line-height: 28px; font-family: 宋体, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; text-indent: 2em; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">10.22</p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 29px; padding: 0px; line-height: 28px; font-family: 宋体, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; text-indent: 2em; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">今天主任查房说我耳朵很大，有福相。肯定会福如东海长流水，寿比南山不老松。</p><p><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 28px; text-indent: 32px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 28px; text-indent: 32px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"></span></span><br/></p>','血癌小伙写重病日志 全天输液全身剧痛怕被讽刺','　　这场大病彻底搅乱他的生活，你的微薄之力，也许可以帮一个20出头的年轻人重回轨道。','1','1','2015-11-06 00:00:00','','0','','','0','{\"thumb\":\"\"}','7','0','0','0','','');INSERT INTO ts_posts ( `id`, `post_author`, `post_keywords`, `post_source`, `post_date`, `post_content`, `post_title`, `post_excerpt`, `post_status`, `comment_status`, `post_modified`, `post_content_filtered`, `post_parent`, `post_type`, `post_mime_type`, `comment_count`, `smeta`, `post_hits`, `post_like`, `istop`, `recommended`, `page_tpl`, `page_tpls` ) VALUES  ('443','1','','','2017-03-13 17:17:18','<p>１１１１１<br/></p>','携手同心共渡难关　为白血病同事组织捐款','　','1','1','2015-12-29 00:00:00','','0','','','0','{\"thumb\":\"\"}','4','0','0','0','','');INSERT INTO ts_posts ( `id`, `post_author`, `post_keywords`, `post_source`, `post_date`, `post_content`, `post_title`, `post_excerpt`, `post_status`, `comment_status`, `post_modified`, `post_content_filtered`, `post_parent`, `post_type`, `post_mime_type`, `comment_count`, `smeta`, `post_hits`, `post_like`, `istop`, `recommended`, `page_tpl`, `page_tpls` ) VALUES  ('444','1','','腾讯大闽网','2017-03-13 17:25:05','<p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 29px; padding: 0px; line-height: 28px; font-family: 宋体, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; text-indent: 2em; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">“妈妈，我的眼睛看不到了……”在家里，林浩躺在病床上喘着粗气，艰难地叙说着发生在自己身体的变化。他曾二度与死神搏斗。2016年8月20日，生命之火在他合上的双眼里，渐渐熄灭。</p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 29px; padding: 0px; line-height: 28px; font-family: 宋体, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; text-indent: 2em; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">他曾经也是个平凡的25岁的年轻人，下班学车练车，准备着注册会计师考试，有时抱怨，但依然憧憬着未来。</p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 29px; padding: 0px; line-height: 28px; font-family: 宋体, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; text-indent: 2em; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">他生前常写日记，记录抗癌心声。其中一句是这样写的：“护士上辈子都是容嬷嬷变的，把我当紫薇了，天天扎针扎到手肿。”</p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 29px; padding: 0px; line-height: 28px; font-family: 宋体, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; text-indent: 2em; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><strong>两度搏斗 曾经看到一线希望</strong></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 29px; padding: 0px; line-height: 28px; font-family: 宋体, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; text-indent: 2em; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">病魔夺走了林浩三分之一体重、25岁为自己打拼的生活、200万的医疗费用……林浩家庭原本步入正轨的生活，都从2015年4月25日，被确诊急性淋巴细胞白血病那天起改变了。</p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 29px; padding: 0px; line-height: 28px; font-family: 宋体, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; text-indent: 2em; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">林浩的父亲坐在自家居民楼的楼梯上，眼神还有些茫然：“（儿子）总要坚持自己爬楼梯……我每次想起来，都觉得很难受。”</p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 29px; padding: 0px; line-height: 28px; font-family: 宋体, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; text-indent: 2em; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">上楼梯时为什么不让家人扶一扶？林浩曾经说过：“锻炼一下总是好的……我也想向家人证明，这事情，我可以自己来。”</p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 29px; padding: 0px; line-height: 28px; font-family: 宋体, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; text-indent: 2em; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">去年11月林浩和病友同时进入造血干细胞移植（俗称“移髓”）仓治疗。协和医院主任医师杨婷告知林浩父母，依据临床经验，除非奇迹发生，孩子才能挺过来。十多天后，奇迹确实发生了。</p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 29px; padding: 0px; line-height: 28px; font-family: 宋体, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; text-indent: 2em; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">熬过化疗放疗、千辛万苦配型“移髓”、经过身体多个器官排异，如果肠道排异没有失败，只要再过1年，林浩就能进入维持治疗阶段，回归常人生活。</p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 29px; padding: 0px; line-height: 28px; font-family: 宋体, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; text-indent: 2em; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><strong>病室中的拉锯战：要不要继续治疗？</strong></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 29px; padding: 0px; line-height: 28px; font-family: 宋体, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; text-indent: 2em; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">父亲说：“他一直都是个懂事善良的孩子，一直为家里着想。”治病，几乎花光了父母卖房准备的2年生活费、医药费。</p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 29px; padding: 0px; line-height: 28px; font-family: 宋体, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; text-indent: 2em; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">大病之初，他曾私下里问医生诊疗费，担心自己成为本不宽裕的家庭的重负；在治疗过程中，他一次次看着父母满怀希望地掏空自己，又满脸憔悴地垂下头，他不止一次央求放弃治疗；在生命最后阶段，他仿佛有预感般，笑着对前来看望的同学同事说，“我们来个合影吧。”</p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 29px; padding: 0px; line-height: 28px; font-family: 宋体, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; text-indent: 2em; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">林浩与血癌搏斗的过程中，经历了正常人无法感同身受的苦难，他曾在移植骨髓后严重感染，在今年6月份又发生了肠道排异。全身皮肤多处淤青，胳膊因为长期输液一移动就会痛，如厕伴随着大量出血……</p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 29px; padding: 0px; line-height: 28px; font-family: 宋体, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; text-indent: 2em; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">医生无心地说出：“林浩，你想不想回家？”父母笨拙地掩盖，但敏感的林浩依然捕捉到什么。独处的时候，他直接了断地问：“医生，你上次说的话有什么意思吗？”</p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 29px; padding: 0px; line-height: 28px; font-family: 宋体, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; text-indent: 2em; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">林浩父亲说，对孩子隐瞒病情，是他们人生中最大的谎言。但如今的我们并不懂病重的林浩当时心里了解到了什么。而他总是让人感觉到温暖与放心。</p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 29px; padding: 0px; line-height: 28px; font-family: 宋体, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; text-indent: 2em; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><strong>网友捐助32万元 没能让他获救</strong></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 29px; padding: 0px; line-height: 28px; font-family: 宋体, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; text-indent: 2em; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">从确诊到逝世不到一年半的时间里，林浩与其它病人一样，成为病房里、移植仓内与外界隔离的一座孤岛。爸妈日夜陪伴鼓励，但病魔驱散不走的阴影和经济重担仍使其身心俱疲。林浩发病半年，200万的治疗费就已消耗殆尽，家里欠债几十万。幸好就职的公司雪中送炭，送来一笔救命钱。大闽网发起2次捐助，32万元爱心款一度让他感受到网友的信心。</p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 29px; padding: 0px; line-height: 28px; font-family: 宋体, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; text-indent: 2em; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">同学，同事们，网友们，一波波向孤岛聚集来的爱心。坚强的林浩掷出“心愿瓶”，为自己转发捐款链接，而朋友圈的人不单给予了金钱上的支持，还建了个微信段子群，说些自己遇到的有趣的小故事，为林浩长期桎梏在病房里的生活增添一抹亮色。如今林浩的父母仍欠债，但面对有心人的帮助，对命运的怨似乎也得以稀释。</p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 29px; padding: 0px; line-height: 28px; font-family: 宋体, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; text-indent: 2em; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><strong>笑中带泪 写抗癌日记为自己减负</strong></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 29px; padding: 0px; line-height: 28px; font-family: 宋体, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; text-indent: 2em; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">林浩生前有一本抗癌日记，他常用布满淤青的手执起笔，写下抗癌日常的只言片语，其中有许多带泪的笑点。林浩坚持用这种方式鼓励自己，直到他看到几条质疑他博取同情的留言，抗病日志才中断了好几天。</p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 29px; padding: 0px; line-height: 28px; font-family: 宋体, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; text-indent: 2em; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">8月20日，林浩在家中逝世；8月24日，林浩的遗体火化，而这本静静躺着，触手可及的日记，依旧向生者昭示着来过的生命，曾以这样的形态存在着：</p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 29px; padding: 0px; line-height: 28px; font-family: 宋体, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; text-indent: 2em; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">“我在仓里发烧了，要加油。”</p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 29px; padding: 0px; line-height: 28px; font-family: 宋体, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; text-indent: 2em; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">“爸爸的骨髓拿过来了，马上要输入了，加油。”</p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 29px; padding: 0px; line-height: 28px; font-family: 宋体, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; text-indent: 2em; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">“今天主任查房说我耳朵很大，有福相。肯定会福如东海长流水，寿比南山不老松。”</p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 29px; padding: 0px; line-height: 28px; font-family: 宋体, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; text-indent: 2em; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">林浩在生命的最后时刻，念叨着：“什么时候能跟高中同学们聚一聚啊。”。其实这个聚会下线下一直筹备，而他终究没能等到。</p><p><br/></p>','血癌小伙不能实现的心愿：聚会 2逃鬼门关抗争到最后','　　他曾经也是个平凡的25岁的年轻人，下班学车练车，准备着注册会计师考试，有时抱怨，但依然憧憬着未来。','1','1','2016-09-06 00:00:00','','0','','','0','{\"thumb\":\"\"}','14','0','0','0','','');INSERT INTO ts_posts ( `id`, `post_author`, `post_keywords`, `post_source`, `post_date`, `post_content`, `post_title`, `post_excerpt`, `post_status`, `comment_status`, `post_modified`, `post_content_filtered`, `post_parent`, `post_type`, `post_mime_type`, `comment_count`, `smeta`, `post_hits`, `post_like`, `istop`, `recommended`, `page_tpl`, `page_tpls` ) VALUES  ('445','1','爱心基金','','2017-03-13 17:39:43','<p><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;; font-size: medium; line-height: 28px;\">　“感谢公司的帮助，让我渡过生命中最无助的时期，等病好了，我一定会努力工作，努力表现，报答公司”，收到爱心基金的三万元善款，被捐助人黄某激动的说。</span><br style=\"outline: none; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;; font-size: medium; line-height: 28px; white-space: normal;\"/><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;; font-size: medium; line-height: 28px;\">　　黄某是集团下属便利店的一名基层员工，今年年初，不幸查出乳腺癌，目前已经进行了切除手术。黄某家境并不宽裕，夫妻二人到城里打工，农村老家还有老人和两个孩子需要供养，前期做手术的5万元已经花光了家中积蓄，后期仍然需要第二期第三期的化疗，高额的治疗费用已使这个家庭不堪重负，难以为继。</span><br style=\"outline: none; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;; font-size: medium; line-height: 28px; white-space: normal;\"/><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;; font-size: medium; line-height: 28px;\">　　黄某说是闽海爱心基金让她看到生的希望，她在申请中说“经过最初的绝望和无助，看到同事们都在为我努力，联系医生，查询药品，我不能倒下，我不是一个人，我的孩子不能没有妈妈，我还有好多好多的愿望没有实现，我仍然希望未来能通过自己的努力，让家人过上好一点的生活”。</span><br style=\"outline: none; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;; font-size: medium; line-height: 28px; white-space: normal;\"/><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;; font-size: medium; line-height: 28px;\">　　收到该员工提交的申请后，爱心基金工作小组迅速组织委员们开会讨论，一致同意救助申请，当天，这笔救命钱就发放到了员工手中。</span><br style=\"outline: none; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;; font-size: medium; line-height: 28px; white-space: normal;\"/><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;; font-size: medium; line-height: 28px;\">　　闽海集团一直秉承“以人为本”的经营理念，为使闽海员工在困难时候能够得到救助，感受到闽海大家庭的温暖，真正营造一个团结互助的氛围，特设立闽海集团爱心基金，据不完全统计，爱心基金自成立以来已救助了多名员工，支付金额达数十万元，帮助多个家庭渡过难关。</span><br style=\"outline: none; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;; font-size: medium; line-height: 28px; white-space: normal;\"/><br style=\"outline: none; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;; font-size: medium; line-height: 28px; white-space: normal;\"/><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;; font-size: medium; line-height: 28px;\">相关链接</span><br style=\"outline: none; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;; font-size: medium; line-height: 28px; white-space: normal;\"/><br style=\"outline: none; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;; font-size: medium; line-height: 28px; white-space: normal;\"/><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;; font-size: medium; line-height: 28px;\">如何申请闽海爱心基金</span><br style=\"outline: none; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;; font-size: medium; line-height: 28px; white-space: normal;\"/><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;; font-size: medium; line-height: 28px;\">救助对象：在闽海集团工作满一年的员工及其直系亲属。</span><br style=\"outline: none; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;; font-size: medium; line-height: 28px; white-space: normal;\"/><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;; font-size: medium; line-height: 28px;\">救助内容：因疾病、意外伤害或其他突发事件造成的经济困难均可提出申请。</span><br style=\"outline: none; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;; font-size: medium; line-height: 28px; white-space: normal;\"/><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;; font-size: medium; line-height: 28px;\">申请途径：需要援助的员工本人向本部门领导提出申请，并附上相关说明及单据。部门领导经调查核实后提出具体意见报爱心基金工作小组。</span><br style=\"outline: none; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;; font-size: medium; line-height: 28px; white-space: normal;\"/><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;; font-size: medium; line-height: 28px;\">咨询电话：0591-87117087转行政部爱心基金工作小组。</span></p>','闽海爱心基金救助患癌女员工渡难关','　　闽海集团一直秉承“以人为本”的经营理念，为使闽海员工在困难时候能够得到救助，感受到闽海大家庭的温暖，真正营造一个团结互助的氛围，特设立闽海集团爱心基金，','1','1','2016-11-10 00:00:00','','0','','','0','{\"thumb\":\"\"}','5','0','0','0','','');INSERT INTO ts_posts ( `id`, `post_author`, `post_keywords`, `post_source`, `post_date`, `post_content`, `post_title`, `post_excerpt`, `post_status`, `comment_status`, `post_modified`, `post_content_filtered`, `post_parent`, `post_type`, `post_mime_type`, `comment_count`, `smeta`, `post_hits`, `post_like`, `istop`, `recommended`, `page_tpl`, `page_tpls` ) VALUES  ('446','1','','','2017-03-13 18:00:38','<p style=\"text-indent: 28px; line-height: 2em;\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">财务部新来了一位年轻的小伙子，热情、开朗，他的笑容总是能轻松感染到周围的同事，</span></p><p style=\"line-height: 2em;\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　但天有不测风云，</span>2015<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年</span>4<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月，他在家突然晕倒，医院检查结果为：急性白血病。</span>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</p><p style=\"text-indent: 28px; line-height: 2em;\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">入院治疗</span>1<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">个月，各种检查费用和第一期化疗就花费了</span>8<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">万余元。医生保守估计，后续化疗至少还需要</span>4<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">个疗程，化疗完成后可进行骨髓配对移植，费用在百万左右。</span></p><p style=\"text-indent: 28px; line-height: 2em;\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">林浩的爷爷奶奶已经去世，母亲身体不好，只能在家休息，父亲原本是出租车司机，为照儿子只能离职，家庭仅有一套</span>45<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">平米的住房，经济条件很不理想。</span></p><p style=\"text-indent: 28px; line-height: 2em;\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">更糟的是，林浩刚参加工作不久，医保缴费年限太短，封顶才</span>2<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">万元，而他个人也无商业保险。得知公司专门设有爱心基金通道可以帮助有需要的职工，他的家人燃起了希望。</span>&nbsp;</p><p style=\"text-indent: 28px; line-height: 2em;\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">这是一条年仅</span>25<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">岁的年轻生命啊！尽管他来公司的时间并不长，很多人还不认识他，但是我们这个温暖的大家庭还是及时伸出了援手。</span></p><p style=\"text-indent: 28px; line-height: 2em;\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">爱心基金会经过投票商议，核实情况后，从</span>2015<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年到</span>2016<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年，基金会共拿出</span>5<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">万元进行救助，全体同事捐款</span>49875<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">元，公司领导两年个人捐款达</span>40<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">万元。共计</span>499875<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">元帮助林浩完成了</span>4<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">个疗程的化疗和骨髓配对，可谓雪中送炭。</span></p><p style=\"text-indent: 28px; line-height: 2em;\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">截止至</span>2016<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年</span>1<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月，院方已成功控制住了病情，癌细胞不再扩散，病变细胞也逐步得到清除。更可喜的是，林浩与其父亲骨髓配型成功，现在家修养，只须定期到医院复查，以等待最佳时机进行移植手术，据医院主治医生说，完全康复的可能性很大。林浩及其家人对闽海的领导、同事表示由衷的感谢，是大家的爱心挽救了这条鲜活的生命。</span></p><p style=\"text-indent: 28px; line-height: 2em;\">&nbsp;</p><p><br/></p>','为白血病同事组织捐款　携手同心共渡难关','　　从2015年到2016年，基金会共拿出5万元进行救助，全体同事捐款49875元，公司领导两年个人捐款达40万元。共计499875元帮助林浩完成了4个疗程的化疗和骨髓配对','1','1','2016-01-05 00:00:00','','0','','','0','{\"thumb\":\"\"}','7','0','0','0','','');INSERT INTO ts_posts ( `id`, `post_author`, `post_keywords`, `post_source`, `post_date`, `post_content`, `post_title`, `post_excerpt`, `post_status`, `comment_status`, `post_modified`, `post_content_filtered`, `post_parent`, `post_type`, `post_mime_type`, `comment_count`, `smeta`, `post_hits`, `post_like`, `istop`, `recommended`, `page_tpl`, `page_tpls` ) VALUES  ('447','1','爱心基金','','2017-03-13 18:10:30','<p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, SimSun; font-size: 16px;\">一、目的</span></p><p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, SimSun; font-size: 16px;\">　　为体现闽海石化“以人为本”的经营理念，使闽海员工在困难时候能够得到救助，感受到闽海大家庭的温暖，真正营造一个团结互助的氛围，特设立闽海石化爱心基金，并制定本管理办法。</span></p><p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, SimSun; font-size: 16px;\">二、适用对象及条件</span></p><p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, SimSun; font-size: 16px;\">　　在闽海工作满一年的员工及其直系亲属，因疾病或意外伤害或其他突发事件等造成的经济困难均可提出申请。</span></p><p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, SimSun; font-size: 16px;\">三、资金来源</span></p><p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, SimSun; font-size: 16px;\">　　资金的主要来源为员工捐款，公司每年组织一次员工捐款。为鼓励员工互助互济，员工捐款多少，公司捐赠同等金额款项。公司同时鼓励员工随时、自愿、不限金额的捐赠。</span></p><p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, SimSun; font-size: 16px;\">四、基金管理及职责</span></p><p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, SimSun; font-size: 16px;\">　　基金由管理委员会和工作小组进行分工管理。</span></p><p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, SimSun; font-size: 16px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px; font-family: 宋体;\">　　闽海石化爱心基金委员会构成</span> <span style=\"font-size: 16px; font-family: 宋体;\">：</span></span></p><p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, SimSun; font-size: 16px;\">　　召集人：丁总、徐总</span></p><p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, SimSun; font-size: 16px;\">　　委员：张纯恒、王一辉、杨榕敏、黄自清、张巍、李登云、张正建、王小妹、余桂珠、王丽、林巧梅</span></p><p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, SimSun; font-size: 16px;\">　　负责：</span></p><p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, SimSun; font-size: 16px;\">　　1<span style=\"font-size: 16px; font-family: 宋体;\">、基金管理制度的制定及修改；</span></span></p><p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, SimSun; font-size: 16px;\">　　2<span style=\"font-size: 16px; font-family: 宋体;\">、制定基金年度筹资计划；</span></span></p><p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, SimSun; font-size: 16px;\">　　3<span style=\"font-size: 16px; font-family: 宋体;\">、负责评定是否发放基金。</span></span></p><p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, SimSun; font-size: 16px;\">　　由“闽海石化爱心基金工作小组”负责具体的执行工作。闽海石化爱心基金工作小组，由行政人事部员工林巧梅、林清担任，负责：</span></p><p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, SimSun; font-size: 16px;\">　　1<span style=\"font-size: 16px; font-family: 宋体;\">、基金的日常管理；</span></span></p><p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, SimSun; font-size: 16px;\">　　2<span style=\"font-size: 16px; font-family: 宋体;\">、员工互助政策的咨询解答；</span></span></p><p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, SimSun; font-size: 16px;\">　　3<span style=\"font-size: 16px; font-family: 宋体;\">、员工捐赠的发起、落实与反馈；</span></span></p><p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, SimSun; font-size: 16px;\">　　4<span style=\"font-size: 16px; font-family: 宋体;\">、员工救助申请的受理、评估核实；</span></span></p><p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, SimSun; font-size: 16px;\">　　5<span style=\"font-size: 16px; font-family: 宋体;\">、不定期通报基金的使用情况；</span></span></p><p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, SimSun; font-size: 16px;\">　　6<span style=\"font-size: 16px; font-family: 宋体;\">、救助人的信息管理、资料建档等工作。</span></span></p><p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, SimSun; font-size: 16px;\">　　闽海爱心基金委托闽海石化财务部专人负责基金的发放、资金收支的财务记录与核对、资金的保管。</span></p><p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, SimSun; font-size: 16px;\">五、申请、审批、发放流程</span></p><p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, SimSun; font-size: 16px;\">　　1<span style=\"font-size: 16px; font-family: 宋体;\">、需要援助的员工本人向本部门领导提出申请，并附上相关说明及单据。部门领导经调查核实后提出具体意见报爱心基金工作小组；</span></span></p><p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, SimSun; font-size: 16px;\">　　2<span style=\"font-size: 16px; font-family: 宋体;\">、基金工作小组自收到援助申请之日起，在</span>7<span style=\"font-size: 16px; font-family: 宋体;\">个工作日内完成调查复核工作，并将结果反馈至基金管理委员会；</span></span></p><p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, SimSun; font-size: 16px;\">　　3<span style=\"font-size: 16px; font-family: 宋体;\">、基金管理委员会对救助申请进行表决，过半数委员通过的申请方可执行；救助金额由管理委员会讨论后决定；</span></span></p><p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, SimSun; font-size: 16px;\">　　4<span style=\"font-size: 16px; font-family: 宋体;\">、财务部根据委员会签字的申请书进行放款工作。</span></span></p><p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, SimSun; font-size: 16px;\">&nbsp;</span></p><p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, SimSun; font-size: 16px;\">　　本办法由闽海石化爱心基金委员会负责解释。</span></p><p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, SimSun; font-size: 16px;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;　　　　　　　　 &nbsp; &nbsp;<span style=\"font-size: 16px; font-family: 宋体;\">闽海石化行政人事部</span></span></p><p><br/></p>','闽海石化爱心基金管理办法（试行）','　　为体现闽海石化“以人为本”的经营理念，使闽海员工在困难时候能够得到救助，感受到闽海大家庭INSERT INTO ts_posts ( `id`, `post_author`, `post_keywords`, `post_source`, `post_date`, `post_content`, `post_title`, `post_excerpt`, `post_status`, `comment_status`, `post_modified`, `post_content_filtered`, `post_parent`, `post_type`, `post_mime_type`, `comment_count`, `smeta`, `post_hits`, `post_like`, `istop`, `recommended`, `page_tpl`, `page_tpls` ) VALUES  ('468','1','','','2017-03-15 17:49:48','<p><img src=\"http://mh.tuishang.com.cn/data/upload/ueditor/20170315/58c90e73ab7a7.jpg\" title=\"111090_副本.jpg\" alt=\"111090_副本.jpg\"/></p>','便利店1月零食专场',' ','1','1','2017-01-04 00:00:00','','0','','','0','{\"thumb\":\"20170315\\/58c90e2b81844.jpg\"}','7','0','0','0','','');INSERT INTO ts_posts ( `id`, `post_author`, `post_keywords`, `post_source`, `post_date`, `post_content`, `post_title`, `post_excerpt`, `post_status`, `comment_status`, `post_modified`, `post_content_filtered`, `post_parent`, `post_type`, `post_mime_type`, `comment_count`, `smeta`, `post_hits`, `post_like`, `istop`, `recommended`, `page_tpl`, `page_tpls` ) VALUES  ('469','1','','','2017-03-15 17:58:35','<p><img src=\"http://mh.tuishang.com.cn/data/upload/ueditor/20170315/58c91035be8d4.jpg\" title=\"initpintu_副本1.jpg\" alt=\"initpintu_副本1.jpg\"/></p>','便利店1月促销海报',' ','1','1','2017-01-11 00:00:00','','0','','','0','{\"thumb\":\"20170315\\/58c91040d1a01.jpg\"}','4','0','0','0','','');INSERT INTO ts_posts ( `id`, `post_author`, `post_keywords`, `post_source`, `post_date`, `post_content`, `post_title`, `post_excerpt`, `post_status`, `comment_status`, `post_modified`, `post_content_filtered`, `post_parent`, `post_type`, `post_mime_type`, `comment_count`, `smeta`, `post_hits`, `post_like`, `istop`, `recommended`, `page_tpl`, `page_tpls` ) VALUES  ('470','1','','','2017-03-16 09:24:52','<p><img src=\"http://mh.tuishang.com.cn/data/upload/ueditor/20170316/58c9e94681844.jpg\" title=\"initpintu_副本112.jpg\" alt=\"initpintu_副本112.jpg\"/></p>','2月便利店纸制品超值精选',' ','1','1','2017-02-01 00:00:00','','0','','','0','{\"thumb\":\"20170316\\/58c9e95d89256.jpg\"}','2','0','0','0','','');INSERT INTO ts_posts ( `id`, `post_author`, `post_keywords`, `post_source`, `post_date`, `post_content`, `post_title`, `post_excerpt`, `post_status`, `comment_status`, `post_modified`, `post_content_filtered`, `post_parent`, `post_type`, `post_mime_type`, `comment_count`, `smeta`, `post_hits`, `post_like`, `istop`, `recommended`, `page_tpl`, `page_tpls` ) VALUES  ('471','1','','','2017-03-16 09:32:49','<p><img src=\"http://mh.tuishang.com.cn/data/upload/ueditor/20170316/58c9eb2bd9413.jpg\" title=\"未命名7.jpg\" alt=\"未命名7.jpg\"/></p>','便利店3月海报精选',' 便利店3月海报精选','1','1','2017-03-16 09:27:17','','0','','','0','{\"thumb\":\"20170316\\/58c9eb3ca3d95.jpg\"}','7','0','0','0','','');INSERT INTO ts_posts ( `id`, `post_author`, `post_keywords`, `post_source`, `post_date`, `post_content`, `post_title`, `post_excerpt`, `post_status`, `comment_status`, `post_modified`, `post_content_filtered`, `post_parent`, `post_type`, `post_mime_type`, `comment_count`, `smeta`, `post_hits`, `post_like`, `istop`, `recommended`, `page_tpl`, `page_tpls` ) VALUES  ('448','1','','','2017-03-14 10:54:09','<p>1111</p>','1111','111','1','1','2017-03-14 10:53:50','','0','','','0','{\"thumb\":\"\"}','0','0','0','0','','');INSERT INTO ts_posts ( `id`, `post_author`, `post_keywords`, `post_source`, `post_date`, `post_content`, `post_title`, `post_excerpt`, `post_status`, `comment_status`, `post_modified`, `post_content_filtered`, `post_parent`, `post_type`, `post_mime_type`, `comment_count`, `smeta`, `post_hits`, `post_like`, `istop`, `recommended`, `page_tpl`, `page_tpls` ) VALUES  ('449','1','年会','','2017-03-14 11:54:00','<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><video src=\"/data/video/nh.mp4\" controls=\"controls\" width=\"750\" height=\"430\">赢战鸡年 &nbsp;再创辉煌！</video></p>','2017闽海年会短片','赢战鸡年  再创辉煌！','1','1','2017-02-08 00:00:00','','0','','','0','{\"thumb\":\"20170314\\/58c7665366d05.jpg\"}','69','0','1','0','','');INSERT INTO ts_posts ( `id`, `post_author`, `post_keywords`, `post_source`, `post_date`, `post_content`, `post_title`, `post_excerpt`, `post_status`, `comment_status`, `post_modified`, `post_content_filtered`, `post_parent`, `post_type`, `post_mime_type`, `comment_count`, `smeta`, `post_hits`, `post_like`, `istop`, `recommended`, `page_tpl`, `page_tpls` ) VALUES  ('451','1','','中国能源报','2017-03-14 18:15:17','<p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\">　　未来炼化市场将形成怎样的格局？地炼企业将扮演何种角色？</span></p><p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\">　　两会间隙，中国能源报上会记者专访到全国人大代表、山东东明石化集团董事局主席兼总裁、山东省工商联副主席，山东炼化协会会长李湘平，他表示“我们与油企是合作关系，不是竞争关系。”</span></p><p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;\"><!--advertisement code begin--><!--advertisement code end--></p><p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\"><strong>　　中国能源报：炼化行业低端产能过剩，高端产能不足，您认为主要原因是什么？有何建议？</strong></span></p><p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\">　　李湘平：目前山东地炼低端产能已经基本淘汰完了。地炼的特点都是从小发展到大，但目前都是具备一定规模和能力但不是特大规模的企业。目前200万吨以上规模符合国家政策，500万吨是一个比较经济的规模，下一步利用好现有规模。炼油规模不是越大越好。</span></p><p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\">　　中国能源报：国企千万吨级以上的炼厂仍在布局，未来炼化市场将形成怎样的格局？地炼企业将扮演何种角色？</span></p><p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\">　　李湘平：对炼油加工企业的发展，国家已经有了规划，七大石化产业基地，生产规模能力要提升至近1500万吨，国家管理部门要有担当，规划要管好。现在在规划以外，包括下游炼油能力，全国的地炼，扩大规模的条件已经不具备了，但是山东地炼已经具备了一定的规模，下一步要发展化工，拉长产业链，提高附加值，走化工转型的之路。</span></p><p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\"><strong>　　中国能源报：下一步在下游精细化方面有何布局？</strong></span></p><p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\">　　李湘平：我们计划整合山东和全国地炼，把生产的化工原料统一规划，大烯烃大芳烃集成化，建成后再做好精细化发展的文章。</span></p><p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\">　　目前我们也在跟山东省发改委协商规划。靠近资源最近的地方，比如东营滨州日照东明等地，具备独立发展的资源条件，但每一家单独发展精细化工条件还不是太具备，整合后要做好大化工也做好精细化工。</span></p><p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\"><strong>　　中国能源报：地炼跟国企竞争优势何在？</strong></span></p><p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\">　　李湘平：事实上我们与油企是合作关系，不是竞争关系。</span></p><p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\">　　第一，为了维护国际市场秩序，国际原料采购市场的秩序，我们成立了中国(独立炼厂)石油采购联盟，通过联盟跟外商统一谈判，拿到大单，实现低价采购，减少国家外汇支出。</span></p><p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\">　　第二，下一步山东炼化协会要整合山东地炼和中石油中石化共同维护下游市场，有利于市场稳定，保证企业效益。</span></p><p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\">　　第三，我们要把资源整合，合理规划资源装置进行充分利用，提升附加值。</span></p><p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\"><strong>　　中国能源报：目前中国(独立炼厂)石油采购联盟进展如何？</strong></span></p><p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\">　　李湘平：联盟从成立以来运行良好。具备了国际化运营素质和条件，在与大型石油供应商的交流沟通和谈判中有十足的能力、方法和措施。</span></p><p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\">　　通过联盟我们把山东地炼、原油配额统一起来，各个企业都在联盟的平台中，从而进行统一谈判，在谈判过程中可以降低价格，减少企业原料成本。</span></p><p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\"><strong>　　中国能源报：地炼在“一带一路”中有什么计划？是否有项目落地？</strong></span></p><p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\">　　李湘平：在“一带一路”的政策方向下，全国的地炼都在实施走出去，一是争取资源，二是在海外投资。已经有一些企业沿着“一带一路”走出去，像恒源石化到马来西亚收购了壳牌500万吨/年炼厂。</span></p><p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\">　　参与炼厂的发展和运营，这是“一带一路”的一个方向。山东地炼下一步要整合力量，统一走出去，现在东明石化原料资源已经走向国际，我们也帮助山东其他炼化企业，下一步在上游发力争取原油，在化工发展和新技术的应用方面做些工作。</span></p><p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\"><strong>　　中国能源报：山东地炼企业为什么会出现原油短缺？</strong></span></p><p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\">　　李湘平：主要原因还是国家给予进口原油配额计划指标不够。过去一年原油配额陆续配置，山东地炼产能很大但没有一次性给齐。所以没有那么大的进口量。去年的配额是6000万吨，山东地炼产能有一个多亿，有些是12月份才给配额，没有形成进口的能力。</span></p><p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\"><strong>　　中国能源报：规范成品油市场有何建议？</strong></span></p><p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\">　　李湘平：成品油市场的管理目前还是比较有秩序的，但是有个别调和商买一些化工品调和影响了市场，现在各级政府正在打击产品质量不合格的调和商。下一步来说，技术监督和工商管理部门要进一步规范，加大抽检检查和惩罚力度，这样成品油市场将更加规范。</span></p><p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;\"><!--function: content() parse end  0ms cost! --></p><p><br/></p>','李湘平：地炼与国家油企不是竞争关系','全国人大代表、山东东明石化集团董事局主席兼总裁、山东省工商联副主席，山东炼化协会会长李湘平，他表示“我们与油企是合作关系，不是竞争关系。”','1','1','2017-03-14 18:14:01','','0','','','0','{\"thumb\":\"\"}','10','0','0','0','','');INSERT INTO ts_posts ( `id`, `post_author`, `post_keywords`, `post_source`, `post_date`, `post_content`, `post_title`, `post_excerpt`, `post_status`, `comment_status`, `post_modified`, `post_content_filtered`, `post_parent`, `post_type`, `post_mime_type`, `comment_count`, `smeta`, `post_hits`, `post_like`, `istop`, `recommended`, `page_tpl`, `page_tpls` ) VALUES  ('452','1','','青岛日报','2017-03-14 18:19:35','<p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\">　　日前，山东省青岛海关和山东检验检疫部门消息称，2016年山东口岸进口原油约1.2亿吨，同比增加57%，进口量和增幅均创历史新高；平均价格为每吨1986元，下跌17.6%，创2004年以来新低。其中，青岛口岸进口原油5605万吨，占全省近一半，占全国进口总量的近七分之一，创历史最高水平，成为我国最大的原油进口口岸。</span></p><p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\">　　海关数据显示，2016年，山东口岸原油月度进口量高位运行，2月、3月、4月连续刷新历史纪录，随后波动回调，11月、12月再次攀升，连创历史新高。其中，12月进口1228万吨，同比增加32.6%，环比增加10.2%。价格方面，山东口岸原油月度进口均价3月份降至2004年1月份以来最低水平，随后进入上升通道，12月份为每吨2348元，同比上涨19.2%，环比上涨2.5%，达到2015年9月以来的最高值。</span></p><p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;\"><!--advertisement code begin--><!--advertisement code end--></p><p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\">　　从贸易方式看，一般贸易方式进口占比近八成，各贸易方式进口量均大幅增加。据统计，2016年，山东口岸以一般贸易方式进口原油9092万吨，增加54.6%；以海关特殊监管区域方式进口1819万吨，增加71.6%；以加工贸易方式进口692.4万吨，增加54.1%。</span></p><p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\">　　从进口来源地看，山东口岸进口原油来源地愈发分散。据统计，安哥拉、俄罗斯、委内瑞拉、巴西和阿曼为山东口岸主要的进口来源地。而青岛口岸进口原油则主要来自安哥拉、俄罗斯、沙特阿拉伯、伊朗、伊拉克等全球31个国家和地区，前14位国家和地区进口量占总进口量的九成。</span></p><p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\">　　分析认为，进口原油使用权和非国营原油进口资质的放开，是推动原油进口量创历史新高的主要动因。山东是我国地方炼企最为集中的省份。来自山东炼化协会的数据显示，山东省炼化企业共有66家，其中央企17家，本省地炼49家，地炼企业主营业务收入占全国炼化的七成以上。“从2015年起，我国进口原油使用权和非国营原油进口资质逐渐放开，以山东地炼为代表的民营企业全面进军原油进口领域，山东口岸原油进口主体结构发生显著变化，山东炼化格局发生剧变。”一位业内人士说。</span></p><p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\">　　数据印证了这位人士的说法。2016年，民营企业原油进口量占山东口岸原油进口总量的38.4%，比2015年提高26.2个百分点。其中，山东11家获得原油非国营进口资质的地炼企业自山东口岸进口原油3200万吨，比上年同期增加2664万吨，对山东口岸原油进口增量贡献度达63.2%。其中，仅山东东明石化集团有限公司一家就进口原油达682.6万吨，一跃成为比肩国有大型企业的主力原油进口企业。</span></p><p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\">　　同时，战略储备扩充需求也对原油进口起到了拉动作用。根据国家统计局公布的数据，至2016年年初，我国已建成舟山、镇海、大连、黄岛、独山子、兰州、天津及黄岛国家石油储备洞库等8个国家石油储备基地，利用上述储备库及部分社会企业库容，储备原油3197万吨。从储备库分布可以看出，山东在国家战略原油储备中占据重要地位，国家加速储备对山东口岸原油进口起到明显提振作用。</span></p><p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\">　　此外，国际市场供过于求致油价探底也在一定程度上刺激了原油进口。受全球经济复苏乏力和美国页岩油成本不断降低的影响，国际市场原油供大于求，主要产油国出于财政因素没有就限产达成一致，2015年下半年开始，国际油价一路走低，至2016年2月份，纽约商品交易所原油期货下跌至每桶26.22美元，创下此前13年以来低点。此后国际油价快速回升至每桶50美元以上，从2016年6月中旬至年末大部分时间在每桶40美元至50美元之间波动。但从总体看，2016年国际油价的总体水平仍然明显低于2015年的水平，使得山东口岸原油进口累计均价出现下跌，进口量快速增长。</span></p><p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;\"><!--function: content() parse end  0ms cost! --></p><p><br/></p>','青岛成国内最大原油进口口岸 ','　　青岛口岸进口原油5605万吨，占全省近一半，占全国进口总量的近七分之一，创历史最高水平，成为我国最大的原油进口口岸。','1','1','2017-03-14 18:18:46','','0','','','0','{\"thumb\":\"\"}','10','0','0','0','','');INSERT INTO ts_posts ( `id`, `post_author`, `post_keywords`, `post_source`, `post_date`, `post_content`, `post_title`, `post_excerpt`, `post_status`, `comment_status`, `post_modified`, `post_content_filtered`, `post_parent`, `post_type`, `post_mime_type`, `comment_count`, `smeta`, `post_hits`, `post_like`, `istop`, `recommended`, `page_tpl`, `page_tpls` ) VALUES  ('453','1','','新华社','2017-03-14 18:20:21','<p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\">　　依据新华(大庆)国际石油资讯中心发布的报告，截至3月10日，全国成品油价格指数为676.88，跌幅0.97%，全国成品油价格指数小幅下挫。</span></p><p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\">　　全国成品油价格指数运行结果表明，本报告周期92＃汽油平均价格报收于6504元／吨，较前一报告周期下跌24元／吨(折合0.02元／升)；0＃柴油平均价格报收于5837元／吨，较前一报告周期下跌76元／吨(折合0.07元／升)。综合来看，全国汽柴油平均价格均下跌，带动全国成品油价格指数小幅下挫。</span></p><p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;\"><!--advertisement code begin--><!--advertisement code end--></p><p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\">　　新华(大庆)国际石油资讯中心分析师李振国认为，近期因美国原油库存大幅增加，国际油价震荡下行。国内市场利空消息弥漫，投资者多持币观望，交投清淡。</span></p><p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\">　　李振国分析认为，目前国内基建工程等项目尚未完全开工，油品需求增长缓慢，业者多观望后市，按需购进，操作积极性下滑，加之国际油价下滑利空国内市场，成品油市场继续保持交投清淡态势。</span></p><p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\">　　国际市场方面，美国能源信息署(EIA)近日公布的数据显示，截至3月3日当周，美国原油库存增加820.9万桶至5.284亿桶，上周美国原油库存增幅超过预期，此消息利空国际油价。观望后市，美国原油库存高企加之原油市场供应过剩格局未改，预计短期油价将继续维持震荡趋势。</span></p><p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;\"><!--function: content() parse end  0ms cost! --></p><p><br/></p>','全国成品油价格指数小幅下挫 ','截至3月10日，全国成品油价格指数为676.88，跌幅0.97%，全国成品油价格指数小幅下挫。','1','1','2017-03-14 18:19:50','','0','','','0','{\"thumb\":\"\"}','22','0','0','0','','');INSERT INTO ts_posts ( `id`, `post_author`, `post_keywords`, `post_source`, `post_date`, `post_content`, `post_title`, `post_excerpt`, `post_status`, `comment_status`, `post_modified`, `post_content_filtered`, `post_parent`, `post_type`, `post_mime_type`, `comment_count`, `smeta`, `post_hits`, `post_like`, `istop`, `recommended`, `page_tpl`, `page_tpls` ) VALUES  ('455','1','','','2017-03-15 14:57:43','<p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;\"><strong><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">职位名称</span></strong><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">：消防班长</span></p><p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;\"><strong><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">工作地点</span></strong><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">：</span> <span style=\"font-family:宋体\">福清江阴</span></p><p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;\"><strong><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">岗位职责</span></strong><span style=\"font-fa